Comment: Broke well to lead, ceded advantage and taken back to 2nd spot 1000 metres out, renewed effort approaching home straight, responded well to hit the front over 200 metres out, won cozily.
Moderate start, soon picked up to just off the pace, remained close up in 3rd turning in, fought on steadily without threatening.
Taken back from a wide gate, settled wide towards the rear, one of the widest turning in, ran home strongly inside the final 250 metres.
Began fairly, settled in forward of midfield on the rail, just over 2L back in 5th turning for home, fought on steadily without threatening.
Midfield on the rail early, steadied and lost position approaching home turn, fought on steadily in straight without threatening.
Moderate start, settled in last few, baulked for a run in straight until the 200 metres, finished off race well late.
Taken back from the widest gate, travelled wide without cover towards the rear, took closer order to 8th coming onto home bend, went 5 wide turning for home, kept on at the one pace.

Began well, took up running from the 1000M going as much as 3L clear at the 700M, came back to the main body of the field approaching home turn, headed under pressure over 200M out, folded up quickly. (Tactic questioned)
Soon dropped to the rear, trailed the field to the straight, saved a lot of ground turning in, kept on steadily without quickening.
Jumped fairly, settled just off the pace on the rail, shuffled back to 4th passing the 1000 metres, chased leaders into straight, faded under pressure.
Inconvenienced at start, settled in midfield, went wide turning in, found nothing.
Jumped awkwardly losing ground, recovered to rear of the field passing the 1200 metres, snuck up on inside entering the straight, unable to sustain effort shortly afterwards.
Settled at the back from a wide gate, detached after straightening, found one worse passing the 200 metres.
Ridden early, settled just better than midfield to straight, dropped out. (Bled) (Lame next day)
Pushed forward, sat 2 wide, pace good, led 350M, closed off strongly to win.
Hard ridden to keep up just behind midfield on the rails, pace good, progressed steadily 300M for 2nd.
Pushed to hold the rail in midfield, pace good, made steady ground 300M for 3rd.
Pushed early, trapped 3-4 wide at back, pace good, progressed steadily 400M.
Pressed forward, 2 wide, pace good, just held ground in straight.
At rear along the fence, pace good, made ground 200M.
Bumped start, hard ridden to keep up at back, pace good, made some ground 200M.
Pushed forward, trapped 3 wide throughout without cover, pace good, weakened 200M.
Eased at start, took cover at rear, 2 wide, on heels 1000M, pace good, lack room in straight, made steady ground.
Pushed early but only briefly, midfield 2 wide, pace good, ran on ok in final stages.
Bumped start, at back 2 wide, pace good, no progress.
Pressed forward to take rail and led at good pace, soon out of fuel 350M.
Midfield, trapped 3-4 wide, emptied in straight.
Never a factor.
Jumped OK, settled midfield, widest on straightening, issued a strong challenge passing 200M, responded well to score.
Ridden along to settle outside the lead, took the lead at Home Turn, travelled strong in the straight, just missed by HD.
Began fairly, raced behind midfield on rail, asked for effort passing 600M, made ground passing 100M, finished solidly.
Moderate start, settled midfield on rail, commenced to improve at Home Turn, made ground passing 100M, worked home nicely.
Jumped fairly then taken back from wide gate, briefly held up in the early straight, made ground when got clear run passing 200M, came home nicely.
Travelled behind midfield, wide on straightening, gradually made ground in the straight, finished OK.
Began well then took box seat, weakened passing 100M, finished fairly.
Raced behind leaders, always niggling, approaching 100M was steadied away from heels, one-paced.
Urged at start, settled midfield, near 250M was inconvenienced, always back.
Settled midfield, always niggling, kept improving on rail at Home Turn, failed to run on in the straight.
Taken back at start, settled behind midfield on rail, no response when under pressure in the straight.
Travelled wide and without cover at handy position, weakened passing 200M, failed to finish off.
Taken back at start, always back, never in it.
Jumped nicely and ridden along to take lead, gradually gave ground at Home Turn, failed to run on.
Hard ridden to get forward position before seeking cover in midfield approaching turn. Swung wide into straight and finished strongly while hanging in under the whip to win close home.
Broke well, snatched box seat and trailed leading pair to straight. Got split between horses 400m, rolled forward to lead 250m, run down close home.
Outpaced, dropping one-out to behind midfield. Swung wide entering straight, finished strongly down centre track to snatch minor placing close home.
Jumped OK but raced keenly to turn, settling behind midfield along rail. Made grand hoe turn to within 2L of leader in straight before turning one-paced.
Steadied soon after start and shifted in from an outside draw to find cover towards the rear. Taken wide in straight and ran on steadily.
First out, shared pace before settling one-back, one-out. Moved forward to race 4-wide outside leader entering straight, kept on well to 200m before turning one-paced.
Ridden to obtain forward position bur held 3-wide 4L from leader on settling. Kept 3-wide mostly, boxed on gamely to 200m before tiring.
Hard ridden from an outside draw to lead passing 950m before crossing to fence. Set strong pace to 250m when ran out of steam and faded.
Hard ridding on jumping but failed to muster, dropping to rear along rail. Remained well back to straight, ran past beaten rivals final stages.
No early pace, racing along rail towards rear. Made up ground early in straight before running into dead-ends 200m and forced to shift out. Not properly tested.
Made use of inside draw to grab rail in midfield. Took closer order home turn to get within range. Kept on well till running out of steam 200m.
Pressed forward from widest draw to race outside leader on settling 950m. Rolled forward top of straight to look a chance before running on empty and dropping back.
Crowded out start but recovered quickly and pressed forward, settling one-out 4L from leader. Stayed behind the pace to 200m when tired and faded.
Shifted across behind horses from wide draw and last on settling. Remained at rear throughout and never in the hunt.
Crowded on jumping, failed to muster speed, raced wide at rear, improved from near 500M, finished off very strongly in straight and scored narrowly.
Began fairly, positioned 2 wide, 2 to 3 lengths back, there to turn, 3 wide with cover on turn, finished off very well to take 2nd.
Taken back from gate 8, raced at rear, 5 to 6 lengths back, still well back on turn, kept to inside after straightening and made good progress to take 3rd.
Away with them, raced 2 wide, 3 to 4 lengths back, similar position on turn, no daylight early in straight, made some progress when clear thereafter to make frame. (See Racing Incidents.)
Average to begin, raced 4 lengths or so back on rail, saved ground on turn, made reasonable headway in straight without threatening.
Bumped start and unbalanced, unable to slot in early, sent forward near 1100M, took the lead on turn, peaked early in straight, stayed on evenly thereafter.
Began only fairly, sent forward to take the early lead, headed near 800M, 2nd on turn, kept on well until near 150M, weakened thereafter.
Bumped start, taken back to race at tail, still last turning in, made good progress in straight to be nearest on line.
Away with them, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, there to turn, finished off one-paced. (Sustained a wound to the right front coronet.)
Moderately away from a tricky gate, unable to slot in, raced 3 wide in 5th, same position on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Began well, positioned 3 lengths or so back on rail, there to turn, awkwardly placed near 400M, showed no progress in straight. (Lost right hind plate near 700M.)
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned 1to 2 lengths back on rail, easy run on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped well, sent forward to race 2 wide, 1 to 2 lengths back, similar position on turn, showed no response in straight, emptied in the final stages.
Began well from a wide draw, sent forward to race prominently, 3rd on turn, emptied early in straight, eased final 150M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Raced in midfield, 3L behind the lead 3 wide with cover, badly held up till 150M, closed off well thereafter to score.
In box-seat initially, shifted 2 wide after 700M, always about 1L off the lead, fought on but just caught and settled for 2nd.
Travelled in one-off one-back position, sat 1-1/2L off the lead, taken to 3 wide after 700M, kept on fairly to the line.
Raced in worse than midfield, 4-1/2L behind 3 wide with cover, made ground and finished off well.
Settled to race in midfield, 2-1/4L behind along the rail, held up after 300M, closed off fairly after 200M once cleared.
Sent forward and shared lead in a 2 wide position, kept on going to the line.
Taken back and raced at the rear, 6-1/2L behind along the rail, made ground and ran on strongly to the line.
Eased and raced towards the rear, 5L behind along the rail, made ground and ran on.
Slotted in to race in about midfield, 2-3/4L behind 2 wide, was one paced to the finish.
Pushed and raced just in front of midfield, 2L behind but wide and without cover, remained one paced.
Bumped start, raced in behind midfield, 4-1/4L behind 2 wide, kept on one paced to the line.
Bumped start, settled in midfield, 3-1/2L behind along the rail, mostly one paced and eased out at 100M.
Sent forward, shared lead along the rail, kept on until passing 200M.
Eased back, at the rear throughout, never a factor.
Broke well, ridden to hold midfield position but wide. Swung wide into straight, finished strongly under whip to win final stages.
Jumped into the lead, set good pace till joined by two others 800m. Kicked clear on straightening, kept finding when pressured, run down final stages.
Jumped OK, ridden to hold position behind midfield but wide. Lost ground turning for home, taken to centre field on straightening, finished off well.
Ridden to hold box seat on settling. Closed in top of straight, looked chance 200m when surged forward out challenge but run ended close home.
Away well, pressed forward settling one-out 2L from leader. Kept on well in straight to 100m before turning one-paced.
Found pace too hot, dropping one-out towards rear. Ran on fairly between horses in straight to finish close behind place-getters.
Steadied shortly after start and shifted in for cover, settling at rear. Remained well back to straight when ran home steadily before hitting dead-end 250m. Boxed on when clear.
Unable match early pace, dropping to rear along fence. Picked up momentum home turn, rolled forward to within 2L of leader 200m before running out of steam.
Pressed forward from an outside draw but held wide until getting cover 900m 2L from leader. Lost position at turn-in, wide into straight, one-paced.
Hard ridden to stay with pace, travelling 3-wide outside leader around turn and into straight. Under pressure final 200m and faded.
Slow into stride, last on settling. Became detached from field at turn-in and never likely.
Hard ridden to stay with pace, moving forward at turn to eye-ball leader passing 800m. Spent force soon after straightening and faded.
Jumped well from a wide draw, sent forward to sit outside to the leader, travelled well on turn, kicked clear in straight and scored easily.
Began well, raced 2 wide in 5th, same position on turn, kept on very well in straight to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.
Away well, raced 2 wide in 3rd, awkwardly placed near 800M, kept on well in straight to get 3rd without threatening.
Taken back from gate 11, raced 3 wide at rear, 4 to 5 lengths back on turn, made good progress in straight to make frame without threatening the first few.
Began fairly from gate 1, showed no early speed, raced 4 to 5 lengths back on rail, saved ground throughout, finished the race well without threatening.
Began well from a wide draw, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well on turn, peaked and headed near 300M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Jumped with them, awkwardly placed near 1100M, travelled wide with no cover in midfield thereafter, there to turn, finished off evenly.
Average to begin, positioned 3 lengths or so back on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, kept to inside in straight and finished off evenly.
Hampered start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 3 to 4 lengths back, same position on turn, finished off one-paced.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide at rear, travelled keenly near 750M, still 5 lengths back on turn, no clear running early in straight, showed no progress when clear thereafter.
Away with them, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground throughout, weakened gradually in straight.
Jumped well from the widest draw, unable to slot in, travelled wide with no cover throughout, emptied early in straight when hard run took effect.
Average to begin, raced at tail throughout, never competitive.
Not pushed early, settling at rear. Not asked for effort until niggled at home turn, surged forward down centre track to hit front 250m, then kept finding when challenged close home.
Not pressured early, settling behind midfield. Began forward move 700m, rolled forward 4-wide into straight. Hit front momentarily, but kept fighting when overtaken, only to lose narrowly.
Jumped well, taken forward, settling one-back, one-out. Swung wide into straight, rolled forward to look a chance 200m, boxed on gamely.
Outpaced, racing at rear but away from fence. Still well back entering straight, taken to centre track and finished strongly
Used inside draw to hold rail 3L from leader. Surged forward turning for home to look a chance 200m, boxed on gamely.
Outpaced and kept mostly at rear close to fence. Picked up momentum in straight running on well between horses before steadied 300m when blocked. Kept on well when clear.
Pressed forward from widest draw to race in midfield but kept wide throughout, covering extra ground. Kept wide in straight and boxed on fairly.
Outpaced and last on settling. Remained well back to straight when picked up the bit and ran home steadily.
Hit stall on jumping, losing considerable ground. Made up ground along fence back stretch to race behind midfield but only one-paced in straight.
Pressed forward to race outside leader passing 1600m before dropping back slightly approaching turn. Rolled forward to race 3-wide outside leader at turn-in before running out of gas.
Away well, shared early pace till settling in box seat. Shifted out 800m when pace slacked, surged forward but wide outside leader to straight before running on empty and faded.
Used early to race with the pace from an outside draw, then moved forward to race outside leader 1200m. Surged to the front on straightening before running out of gas.
Used early from an outside gate to race 3-wide 2L from leader on settling. Kept wide thereafter and spent force soon after straightening.
Burrowed through along the rail to lead on settling, then slowed pace back stretch. Put under pressure home turn, spent force on straightening, faded.
Taken up early to be well placed 3rd/4th. Battled hard with 2nd down the straight, before outlasting him in the last 100m to win strongly.
Taken up to sit around midfield early. Awkward on heels 550m. Ran strongly and matched winner down the straight before peaking just near the line.
Cruised forward to sit just behind midfield. Came inside for clear running from 200m. Stayed on well when clear, but couldn't match the speed of first 2.
Tardy into action to be a clear last. Still last at 300m. Came widest in the straight and stayed on strongly to claim the majority of the field late.
Eased back from the wide draw to sit towards the rear of the field. Came wide and stayed on well early in the straight. Peaked in last 100m late.
Cruised out early to sit just behind midfield. On heels 1050m. Raced tight early in the straight, then hampered at 300m. Stayed on solidly without threatening late.
Tried to push forward early, before easing back to settle midfield. Clear running from 200m, but only stayed on fairly late.
Fairly away and dropped back to sit at the rear of the field. Plugged away fairly without threatening late.
Pushed up from the inside draw to be well placed 3rd/4th. 1 paced and didn't run on in the straight.
Challenged for the lead early, before settling 2nd. Nothing left in the straight dropped out from the 400m.
Broke quickly and pushed forward to lead. 1 paced in the straight, and not pushed out last 200m.
Cruised across from the wide draw to sit midfield, 3 wide with no cover. Giving ground from the top of the straight, and not pushed to the line from 250m.
Jumped well from a wide draw, raced wide with no cover in 3rd, still 3 wide on turn, stayed on well in straight to score.
Began well, positioned 2 to 3 lengths back on rail in midfield, easy run on turn, no daylight until final 150M, finished off strongly to get 2nd. (Lost left front plate.)
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, 5 lengths back, bumped and unbalanced turning in, finished off very strongly to take 3rd, nearest on line.

Average to begin, raced 2 wide in 5th early, found the rail near 950M, sat right behind the leader on turn, no clear running early in straight, angled out near 300M and made some progress, crowded near 150M, ran on evenly thereafter.
Away with them, sent forward to race prominently, just outside the leader, shared lead on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed near 150M, weakened thereafter, just missed frame.
Began well from gate 1, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well throughout, kept on well early in straight, headed near 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Bumped Start, positioned 2 wide in midfield, travelled keenly near 1200M, 3 to 4 lengths back on turn, finished off one-paced.
Checked start, positioned 3 to 4 lengths back on rail, there to turn, angled out early in straight and made minor progress.
Jumped well, raced 2 wide, a length or so back, similar position on turn, no daylight early in straight, one-paced when clear thereafter.
Average to begin, raced at rear, 6 to 7 lengths back, still well back on turn, made little progress in straight.
Began awkwardly and then hampered, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, same position on turn, failed to close off in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began awkwardly, raced 5 lengths back at rear, 2 wide on turn, taken wide in straight, showed no progress.
Moderately away from the widest draw, unable to slot in early, found cover near 900M, 2 wide in 6th on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Taken back from gate 13, raced at tail throughout, showed no progress in straight, finished last.

Ridden to share early pace, drew clear under pressure from the 200 metres to win readily.
Began well, settled in midfield on stands rail, improved to just behind the leaders in 5th coming onto course proper, fought on steadily without threatening.
Jumped awkwardly, settled in midfield, switched in sharply for a run passing the 400 metres causing interferences, fought on steadily under pressure without threatening.
Settled in last few, badly interfered with inside the 400 metres, ran on steadily under pressure to the line.
Jumped awkwardly, ridden along, settled just off the pace in 4th, did not find much room coming onto course proper, ran home one-paced in closing stages.
Ridden forward from the one gate, remained prominent to the 200 metres, lost touch under pressure.
Jumped awkwardly, settled in midfield, came under pressure from the 300 metres, kept on same pace without quickening.
Settled well behind, commenced move from half-way out, making good impression when hampered about 150 metres out.
Slightly slow out and soon dropped to the last, kept on past well-beaten horses in closing stages.
Jumped fairly, settled behind midfield on stands rail, steadied and lost position passing the 500 metres, ran past well-beaten horses closing stages.
Began well, settled just off the pace in 3rd, held some chance when level with the leader 300 metres out, soon weakened.
Settled better than midfield within 2L of the pace, baulked for a run before severely checked 150 metres out.
Jumped well, dropped to last few after the first 300 metres, ran home one-paced.
Moderate start, soon gained narrow lead one off the stands rail after the first 200 metres, led until headed passing the 500 metres, dropped out.
Hard ridden forward, 2 wide, not suited by the fast sectionals, drifted away 400M to score.
Eased to rear, trapped 3-4 wide, favoured by the fast pace, progressed steadily 300M for 2nd.
At back, trapped 2-4 wide, suited by the fast tempo, made steady ground 400M for 3rd.
At rear but along the fence, benefited by the fast tempo, progressed steadily 300M.
Hard ridden forward to take box seat, not suited by the fast pace, emptied 200M.
Took rail behind midfield, favoured by the fast pace, just held ground in straight.
Behind midfield, benefited by the fast pace, ran on ok in final stages.
Behind midfield, 2-4 wide, suited by the fast tempo, no progress.
Pressed forward, trapped 2-3 wide, harmed by the fast tempo, soon weakened 300M.
Hard ridden to take rail and lead, clocked fast sectionals, soon out of fuel 300M.
Slow away, hard ridden to keep up in midfield, 2-3 wide, weakened 250M.
Hard ridden forward, harmed by the fast pace, emptied 400M.
Never competitive, trapped 3-4 wide, tailed out.
Ridden along with good gate and made first turn on rail, raced behind the leader, shifted out at Home Turn for improving, fought well in the straight to score.
Urged along after start, settled midfield, commenced to improve at Home Turn, battled nicely in the straight, just missed by HD.
Taken back at start, improved passing 700M, widest on straightening, made up some nice late ground.
Settled at handy position on rail, unable to obtain clear running until after 300M, made ground passing 150M, finished nicely.
Became fractious and reared in barriers and broke rider's whip, settled at handy position, made ground in the early part of straight then kept on to the line.
Raced midfield, asked for effort near 500M, passing 150M shifted out away from heels, passing 50M awkwardly placed outside heels then still made ground.
Taken back at start from widest gate, commenced to improve at Home Turn, gradually made ground in the straight.
Travelled behind midfield, asked for effort passing 450M, limited response in the straight.
Urged along and made first turn wide, took lead passing 1300M, weakened passing 200M.
Slow to begin, raced behind midfield, drifted back near 600M, limited response in the straight.
Moderated start, raced behind midfield on rail, one-paced.
Raced midfield on rail, held the rail at Home Turn, faded out passing 200M.
Always back, no response when asked for effort.
Ridden along after start, travelled wide and without cover, gave ground in the straight.
Broke well, pressed forward settling one-out, one-back. Swung 4-wide into straight, hit from 200m, kept on strongly.
Allowed to stride forward from an outside draw to lead on settling, crossing to fence 1200m and slowing tempo. Kicked ahead on straightening, collared 200m, kept on strongly to line.
Pressed forward on jumping, crossing to fence 1400m before enjoying run of race in box seat from 1200m. Had clear passage from 300m but unable catch first two.
Used inside draw to hold fence, settling 3L from leader. Came off fence turning for home, bumped and unbalanced 350m, kept on fairly without looking dangerous.
Ridden to get forward position but held wide 1000m when field bunched up off slow pace. Covered extra ground throughout but boxed on gamely in straight.
Began well, pressed forward looking for cover but held wide in bunched-up field and allowed to stride forward to race outside leader 1000m. Kept tabs to 200m before tiring.
Outpaced, racing along fence at rear. Taken wide on straightening and boxed on one-paced, running past beaten horses.
Taken in for cover soon after start, nestling one-out towards rear. Dropped back turning for home, taken to centre field on straightening but only minor progress under the whip.
Taken in soon after start but held wide behind midfield on settling. Kept wide throughout and only one-paced in straight.
Taken in for cover soon after start and last on settling. Swung widest entering straight but made little headway under hard riding.
Jumped OK, then ridden to hold midfield position one-away from fence. Came under pressure turning for home and faded in straight.
Began awkwardly, pressed forward, holding fence in midfield. Improved position home turn, switched out in straight to make run but shortened stride noticeably and eased down.
Travelled strongly in midfield 3-4Ls off the pace, accelerated through the final 300M to snatch it late.
Began well from draw 2, always in touch behind leaders, into clear 200M, chased steadily to go 2nd near line.
Pushed to occupy leading spot, shared lead at a slow pace middle stages, caught 150M, battled on to hold 3rd.
Never far off the pace, raced keenly when pace slackened middle stages, no cover until 700M, made good progress turning in and hit the lead 150M, flattened late under top weight and edged out to 4th.
Caught 3-wide behind mid-division throughout, difficult to settle when pace slackened middle stages, closed off well final 400M off a tough run, nearest finish.
Reserved behind mid-division 4-5Ls off the steady pace, took a while to get going, did best work late.
Chased leaders along the 2-path, closed off moderately from 300M, couldn't close gap on leaders.
Driven forward from draw 14 to be racing just off the pace, kept battling to the line but outsprinted by rivals passing 300M.
Began well from draw 1 then restrained to race in midfield, saved ground on the inner but not able to obtain clear running in straight, not properly tested.
Settled down behind mid-division 5-6Ls behind leaders, worked home fairly over final 400M, no threat to leaders.
Slow to begin, held up 2nd last, 6Ls to make up 400M but never got going. (Lame next day.)
Caught wide from draw 13, no cover from 900M and strode forward to race outside leaders, remained wide to straight, gave ground passing 300M.
Slow to begin, detached last over 10Ls off the pace in early and middle stages, struggled to make an impression in the run home.
Held up in midfield, proved very difficult to settle during the race, wide on the bend and already a spent force turning home. (Unacceptable racing manners / Lame next day.)
Taken back and raced towards the rear, 7L behind 2 wide, picked up from 350M and kept on nicely to score.
In behind midfield, 6-1/2L behind 3 wide with cover, kept on well and just made 2nd prior going to the line.
Failed to muster, settled in just behind midfield, 5-1/4L behind along the rail, kept on going to take 3rd.
Settled to race in about midfield, 3-3/4L behind along the rail, continued to improve and kept on to the line.
Travelled towards the rear, 7-1/2L behind 2-3 wide with cover, made ground and ran on fairly.
Raced in about midfield, 2 wide with cover initially, shifted 3 wide and raced without cover after 900M, one paced in the straight. (Rider questioned)
Rolled forward to race in the box-seat, sat 2L off the lead, hard ridden but was very one paced.
Crowded start, raced at the rear, 8-3/4L behind along the rail, did not make any ground in the straight.
Niggled and settled in one-off one-back position, sat 2L off the lead, faded gradually in the straight.
In midfield but wide initially, allowed forward to sit outside the lead, flattened approaching 200M.
Travelled in about midfield, 5-1/4L behind 2 wide, found nothing and eased 200M out.
Hard ridden to take rail and led by a neck, weakened badly upon entering the straight.
Crowded at start, settled just in front of midfield, 3-1/2L behind 2 wide, faded when rounding Home Turn and then tailed out. Must trial.
In midfield, very wide throughout, under pressure prior to straightening and then tailed out. Must trial.
Bounced well, shared early pace before settling along outer fence 2L from leader 700m. Shaken up 400m, hit front 200m, kept on strongly to line.
Hard ridden from inside draw to lead 800m before crossing to outer fence 700m. Under pressure from 400m, overtaken 200m but battled on gamely.
Jumped with field, rolled forward, settling 2L from leader three-away from outer fence. Made forward move from 400m to look a chance 200m but unable match first two closing stages.
Crowded out start, outpaced, dropping towards rear along outer fence. Got clear running approaching 300m and boxed on gamely.
Jumped well, shared early pace before settling one-way from outer fence 2L from leader. Under pressure from 400m but found little, finishing one-paced.
Crowded out start, dropping towards rear, one-away from outer fence. Switched in 700m making up some ground before turning one-paced final 400m. (Rider dropped left rein 300m)
Outpaced early before making up some ground in midfield to 400m before turning one-paced.
Broke well, pressed forward, but raced fiercely and hard to settle. Spent force passing 400m and faded.
Began fairly, settled down 5Ls back in 9th, under gradual acceleration passing 400M, swept past leader near 50M and won going away.

Led as expected, pressed by rival passing 1000M setting fast pace in the 2nd quarter, shook off nearest pursuer 300M, kept on but no match with winner's turn of foot final 100M, got tired late but held on 2nd.
Taken back from wide barrier, held up near last on the inside, stayed on moderately to take 3rd in a blanket finish for minor placing.
Guided to a midfield spot along the fence, 3Ls off the pace middle stages, boxed on evenly in straight for 4th but no threat to runaway winner.
From wide draw shifted across behind runners early stages, towards the rear just over 6Ls off the pace, stayed on well down the outside.
Restrained to race behind midfield, saved ground along the rail, switched out 450M to challenge, couldn't quicken enough and only held ground to the line.
Restrained behind leaders, proved difficult to settle passing 1000M, moved up to 2nd 250M, wilted passing 150M.
Eased back to sit at the rear, 7Ls to make up 400M, picked up well but ran into traffic 200M-100M, could have done better.
Held up 2-wide in midfield 3Ls behind leaders, held ground turning in, weakened late stages.
Settled down 4Ls behind midfield, couldn't go on passing 300M, no threat on debut.
Hard ridden forward, pressed leader from 1000M, struggled to hold position 300M, checked inside 200M, lost ground and weakened towards the finish.
Chased leaders along the 2-path, one paced early straight, no extra inside 200M.
Lost ground start and last on settling. Made up ground home turn, blocked for run early straight, shifted in abruptly 250m to get clear, finished strongly under whip to win close home.
Ridden to get forward position before getting cover one-out in midfield approaching turn. Swung wide into straight, hit front 300m, run down close home.
Steadied on jumping, shifted in behind runners, settling one-out towards rear. Swung very wide entering straight, finished strongly to grab minor placing.
Ridden along early before finding cover one-out behind pacemakers approaching turn. Urged forward 3-wide at turn-in, boxed on gamely in straight.
Steadied on jumping and taken in for cover, dropping 3-wide towards rear. Kept wide around home turn and ran home gamely in straight under hard riding.
Jumped well, racing inside leaders before taking lead 1100m. Kept steady pace to 200m before running out of steam and fading.
Outpaced, dropping to rear, then proved difficult to settle around turn, dropping to last. Still last 200m before running on fairly final stages.
Pressed forward from widest draw to race outside early leader, then kept 3-wide without cover when another took over 1100m. Moved closer 400m but flattened soon after and dropped back.
No early pace, racing along rail behind midfield. Switched out on straightening to make run but found little under pressure, finishing one-paced.
Jumped well, ridden forward, settling midfield along rail. Took closer order around turn, kept on fairly to 200m before running on empty and dropping back.
Pushed forward, racing one-out 3L from leader on settling. Kept within range on straightening but inconvenienced 250m, dropping back.
Ridden forward from inside draw to grab box seat, 2L from leader on settling. Kept tabs to straight when asked for effort but found nothing.
Hard ridden from outside gate to lead but unable to cross to fence, allowing inside runner to take over 1100m. Moved up at turn-in, joint leader to 250m before tiring and dropping out.
Fairly away, crowded on jumping and dropped back towards the rear of the field. Came around off heels 200m. Got to lead at 75m, and stayed on strongly late.
Cruised forward early and settled just behind midfield. Ran strongly in the straight, and looked to be the winner 150m. Overtaken late and couldn't match winners speed.

Dropped back from the wide draw to sit a clear last. Still last at 400m, but proceeded to show good turn of foot. Hung out badly in the straight, despite running strongly, and finished the race along the outside rail.
Fairly away but recovered well from the inside draw to sit midfield. Stayed on well in the straight, but didn't have the same kick as the first 3.
Pushed forward early, eventually settling behind the leader, on the fence. Led in the straight until 120m. 1 paced late and swamped.
Crowded on jumping and then eased forward to settle midfield. Came around heels for clear run at 250m. Stayed on solidly late, without threatening.

Fractious in the barriers. Pushed forward early, before being steadied at 1400m for cover and racing keen. Eventually settled worse than midfield. Lay out on the turn and 300m. Stayed on OK under hands and heels.
Pressed forward early to settle 2nd/3rd, 1 off the fence. Still well placed at 200m, but went to the line 1 paced.
Pushed forward early to lead passing the 1200m. Didn't finish off, and was eased late. Jockey questioned.
Taken forward early to be well placed 4th/5th, on the fence. Only plugged away in the straight under minimal urging.
Bumped and unbalanced on jumping and then dropped back to sit 2nd last. Plugged away in the straight late.
Eased out early to sit just behind midfield, 3 wide with no cover. Gave nothing in the straight.
Began awkwardly and eased back towards the rear of the field. Didn't respond to riding and was eased late.
Crowded on jumping but recovered well enough to press forward to sit 4th/5th, 1 off the fence. Out of gas by the 400m and not persevered with after 200m.

Moderate start, settled one back in 4th on the rail, became 3rd in similar spot rounding home bend, ran on under pressure to prevail by a narrow margin.
Slightly slow out, settled in rear on the rail, full of running rounding home bend, saved ground turning in, fought on well only to be denied by a narrow margin.
Broke well, settled just off the pace 2-wide, just over 2L back in 4th turning for home, fought on steadily without threatening.
Jumped fairly, gradually drifted towards the rear, caught in a tight run after straightening, obtained clear passage 200 metres out, finished off race well.
Settled in midfield, kept on well in straight, nearest at finish.
Close up early, travelled mainly 3-wide 2L back in 5th to the straight, went wider turning in, made moderate progress without quickening, tightened near the line. (Lame next day)
Ridden along after a moderate start, hampered and lost position coming onto home bend, dropped next to last into straight, recovered good late ground.
Began from a wide gate, travelled 3-wide up with the pace far side, joined the leader rounding home bend, held every chance early in straight, unable to sustain effort inside the final 200 metres.
Moderate start, soon took up running on the rail, joined rounding home bend, unable to sustain effort and swamped inside the final 100 metres.
Jumped awkwardly losing ground, picked up steadily on the rail along back straight, reached midfield coming onto home bend, unable to sustain effort after straightening.
Soon dropped to the rear and found no response to early reminders, trailed the field to the straight, never on terms.
Began well from the widest gate, gradually taken back 4-wide to rear of midfield, similar position rounding home bend and into the straight, made no impression.
Pushed early, box seat, closed off well to score but only just by a short head.
Rolled forward, took rail easily and led at fast sectionals, hung on strongly, just beaten by a narrow margin in final stride.
Eased back, took rail, favoured by fast pace, made steady ground 200M for 3rd.
Eased at start, too cover at rear, benefited by the fast tempo, dashed well 250M whilst hanging in.
Hard ridden to keep up in midfield on the fence, benefited by the fast pace, just held ground in straight, lack room 50M.
Checked start, at back 2 wide, suited by the fast pace, made ground 300M.
At back along the fence, favoured by the fast tempo, however held up and checked badly 150M, not properly tested.
Eased at start, too cover at rear, 2 wide, suited by the fast pace, progressed steadily 250M.
Eased to sit in midfield, 2 wide, benefited by the fast tempo, just held ground in straight.
Hard ridden forward, sat 2 wide, not suited by the fast pace, weakened 200M.
Bumped start, failed to muster, trapped 3 wide, out of fuel 200M.
Trapped 3-4 wide in midfield throughout, emptied 350M.
Ridden along to settle behind leaders on rail, quickened passing 100M, finished unchallenged.
Pushed along and took lead passing 800M, asked for effort on straightening, kept on in the straight, came home solidly.
Ridden along after start then steadied to settle midfield, wide on straightening, gradually made ground in the straight, finished nicely.
Taken back at start, settled behind midfield on rail, kept improving on rail at Home Turn, fought hard in the straight, finished well.
Taken back at start, passing 600M checked away from heels, awkwardly placed rounding Home Turn, gradually made ground in the straight.
Raced behind leaders, asked for effort near 400M, battled hard in the straight.
Urged to go forward, got head up when being steadied in lead near 800M, gave ground passing 150M.
Travelled at rear, awkwardly placed approaching 1000M, limited response when asked for effort in the straight.
Taken back at start, became unbalanced when steadied approaching 1000M, raced at tail, one-paced.
At start bounded, on landing became badly unbalanced and lost ground, settled midfield on rail, passing 250M rider dropped his whip, one-paced.
Taken back at start, awkwardly placed for some distance after 1100M, approaching and passing 500M checked away from heels, gave ground passing 100M.
Travelled wide and without cover behind midfield, widest on straightening, no response in the straight.
Began well, raced 2 wide, 1 to 2 lengths back, travelled well to turn, improved near 500M, finished off well to score.
Bumped shortly after the start, unbalanced, raced 2 wide, 4 to 5 lengths back in midfield, similar position on turn, finished off very strongly to get 2nd.
Bumped shortly after the start, positioned 2 wide, 3 lengths back, same position on turn, closed off well to take 3rd.
Average to begin, position on rail behind midfield, 5 lengths or so back, angled out near 350M, made good progress in straight to make frame.
Jumped well from gate 10, slotted into midfield, 3 lengths back on rail, saved ground throughout, made minor progress in straight without threatening the first few.
Began well from a wide draw, sent forward to race outside the leader in 2nd, there to turn, peaked early in straight, kept on evenly to the line.
Fast into stride, took the lead easily, travelled well throughout, peaked early in straight, headed near 150M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Bumped start and crowded, raced 2 wide, 6 lengths or so back, slightly improved on turn, finished off evenly.
Average to begin, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, easy run to turn, no clear running in straight, not able to be tested properly.
Average to begin, raced at rear, 6 to 7 lengths back, same position on turn, made no progress in straight.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced 2 wide at rear, 8 lengths back, failed to close off in straight.
Bumped start, raced at tail throughout, never a threat.
Positively ridden, sat 2-wide just off leaders, moved up to tackle leader mid-straight, led near 100M and held sway from pursuing rivals.
Shifted across behind runners, settled down in 9th 6Ls off the pace, chased solidly over final 300M, nearest finish.
From draw 11 guided to a rail position ahead of midfield, just over 3Ls behind leader turning in, ran on well to go 3rd near line.
Jumped well to be leading along the rail on settling, set steady pace to straight, fought well to 100M, edged out to 4th near line.
Sent forward as expected, raced outside leader, had every chance turning home, held by leaders final 150M.
Eased on jumping from wide draw, got into a 2-wide spot in midfield, switched wide to challenge passing 350M, stayed on moderately.
Slowly away, in 2nd last for the first half of the race, driven along 550M, 7-8Ls back home turn, ran on well from off the pace.
Jumped with field, held up in mid-division 4-5Ls off the pace, kept to inside entering straight, ran on fairly no threat to leaders.
From wide draw crossed to race 2-wide in mid-division, taken to center field on straightening, couldn't sprint enough to challenge leaders.
Bustled along early stages, held up towards the rear, didn't pick up entering straight.
Began fairly, ended up detached last well off the pace, never got going.
Taken keen hold behind leaders, inclined to lay out 600M, checked away from heels 350M losing ground, didn't recover and weakened noticeably in in the straight. (Unacceptable Performance.)
Travelled in behind midfield, 4-1/2L behind 2 wide, kept battling and hit the line strongly to score by 3/4L.
Sent forward to take the rail and led by 1-1/4L, kept on going only to be headed by the winner in the final stages.
Taken back and at the rear, improved to sit around midfield after 1000M, 3 wide with cover, closed off well to take 3rd.
Crowded after the start, settled to race in about midfield, 2L behind along the rail, kept on fairly to the finish.
Rolled forward and took up racing in the box-seat, sat 2L off the lead, kept on one paced to the line.
Rolled forward and raced in one-off one-back position, sat 2-3/4L off the lead, held up till 200M, ran on fairly to the line.
Slow to jump, sat front of midfield, 2-1/4L off but wide and without cover, showed nothing and dropped off gradually.
Settled towards the rear despite hard ridden early, 5-1/2L behind 2 wide, kept on one paced.
Taken back, did not stretch out and remained detached until around 700M, improved slightly only. Must trial.
Jumped awkwardly, raced towards the rear, 5-1/2L behind along the rail, one paced home.
Pushed forward, sat 1-1/4L off and outside the lead, weakened badly passing 200M.
Jumped awkwardly losing ground, travelled in last few hugging inside rail, angled out for a run making home turn, ran on well to take charge inside the final 100 metres.
Restrained to 2L back in 5th, held similar position into straight, ran on under pressure to hold every chance 100 metres out but found winner too strong.
Broke well, tracked the leader to the straight, ran on under pressure to hit the front over 300 metres out only be headed passing the 100 metre mark.
Pressed forward from the wide gate settling wide in midfield, ran on steadily under hard driving in straight, never threatening.
Settled at the back from a wide gate, remained well behind before making a forward move on the bend, widest runner heading for home, finished off race nicely near the centre of the track.
Broke well from a middle draw, travelled wide without cover in 4th just over 2L off the pace, came under pressure rounding home bend, kept on before fading inside the final 200 metres.
Settled well behind, last and wide into straight when came under pressure, ran on past well-beaten horses inside the final 200 metres.
Jumped fairly settling towards the rear, raced keenly far side, saved ground on the inside turning in, ran home one-paced.
Soon crossed from the widest gate and settled 3-wide with cover mainly in midfield, commenced move rounding the home bend but unable to sustain effort in the straight.
Jumped fairly, soon ridden to the front, led and set a steady pace to the straight, headed shortly after and faded.
Settled in midfield, tight on the rail rounding stables bend, remained in midfield far side but lost position around home bend, no further impression in straight.
Broke well, ceded lead to settle just off the pace in 3rd on the rail, remained similar turning in, folded up quickly inside the final 250 metres. (Questioned for disappointing performance.)
Reserved in mid-division 5Ls behind leader, swung wide leaving the bend, ran on strongly to get up last stride.
Travelled strongly just behind leaders, waited with till 250M, looked the winner when hitting the lead 150M, caught last stride.
Held up 2-wide behind mid-division, 6Ls off the pace home turn, brought widest home and finished off strongest for a close 3rd.
Never far off from leaders, commenced his challenge down center of track, closed off steadily for 4th.
Taken back from wide barrier, settled down behind midfield 7Ls off the pace, ran on mildly over final 300M without threatening top 3.
Jumped well to take up a forward position as expected, tracked leader from 800M, battled away to the line but outsprinted by rivals over final 150M.
Away with them, sped to lead from 800M, headed 150M and flattened out.
Held up midfield along the rail, unable to quicken in straight with rider dropping his right rein from 300M to 100M.
Not hurried and dropped back to 10th position 8Ls away from leader, gave limited response in straight, never reached contention.
Dropped back, held up 2nd last 8-9Ls behind leader, didn't find much when pushed out 400M, soundly beaten.
Taken back from wide barrier, settled in last over 10Ls off the pace, made no real progress in straight. Never a factor.
Moved up to chase leaders, held ground early straight, run ended 200M and weakened noticeably to finish last.

Settled at the back waited with, stuck to inside run after straightening, came through strongly inside the final 100 metres for a commanding victory.

Hampered at start, soon recovered to midfield on the rail, inconvenienced rounding home bend, obtained clear passage shortly after straightening, ran on to hit the front briefly 100 metres out before outsprinted closing stages.
Began well, taken back just off the pace on the rail, shifted further back to 2L 4th rounding home bend, came to challenge after straightening but checked 250 metres out, one paced closing stages.
Stalked the leader to straight, took over from weakening leader passing the 300 metres only to be swamped over 150 metres out.
Settled in last few, soon came to challenge in straight, ran on down the centre of the track without threatening.
Tight at start, soon recovered to prominent position in 3rd, held some chance under strong pressure over 200 metres out, soon weakened.
Began well, gradually settled back just behind the midfield travelling wide, ran on steadily under pressure in straight, never threatening.

Checked at start losing ground, gradually recovered to rear of midfield, carried backward towards the rear rounding home bend, switched out onto the centre of the track after straightening, kept on without quickening.
Settled towards the rear on the rail, made no impression in the run home.
Ridden from a wide gate to take up running, obtained rails run coming onto home bend, led until finding no extra passing the 300 metres.
Ridden along and prominent briefly, inconvenienced and dropped to rear of midfield entering straight, made no further impression.
Close up early, drifted back to 3L 5th rounding home bend, faded in straight.
Soon dropped well behind, never seen with a chance.
Ridden along from a wide gate, soon dropped back to wide in midfield, one paced before weakening inside the final 200 metres.
Pushed forward, sat 2 wide, benefited by the slow pace, closed off strongly 300M to score.
Eased back, took rail, harmed by the slow tempo, unleashed strong finishing efforts 300M, just missed by a very narrow margin.
Hard ridden to keep up in midfield along the fence, not suited by the slow pace, blocked most straight, dashed strongly for 3rd.
Hard ridden forward, sat 2 wide just off the leader, benefited by the slow tempo, ran on well to the line.
Pushed to take rail and led at slow sectionals, ran on until 200M overhauled.
Eased back, 2 wide, lack room 400M, dashed strongly despite not suited by the slow pace.
Hard ridden to obtain box seat, held up 4-2, dashed fairly when clear.
Eased at start, attempted to take cover at back but failed, 3 wide, not suited by the slow tempo, dashed well 300M whilst hanging in.
Very slow away, trapped 3-4 wide at rear, dashed well 200M despite not suited by the slow pace.
Checked at start, 2 wide at rear, not suited by the slow tempo, dashed well 200M.
Eased back, raced 4 wide throughout, harmed by the slow pace, dashed well 300M, run ended 100M.
Began awkwardly and clipped heels shortly after start, 3 wide at back, harmed by the slow pace, lack room 400M, little dash when clear.
Hard ridden early but not muster, at rear on the fence, not suited by the slow tempo, ran on fairly.
Raced ungenerously in midfield, checked early, emptied in straight.
Began only fairly and then lost ground when crowded for room, settled at rear, asked for effort passing 400M, quickened passing 150M, finished strongly.
Jumped well, took lead and raced on outside rail, over final 400M lay in under pressure, finished strongly.
Raced behind the leader, after 500M lay out, commenced to improve passing 400M, came home well.
Passing 900M lay out, raced midfield on outside rail, fought hard over the concluding stages, finished well.
Moderate start, moved to handy position passing 700M, settled 4 wide to outside rail, one-paced when asked for effort.
Moved to midfield passing 600M, badly held up from approaching 400M to 50M, not fully tested.
Fractious in barriers, raced behind the leader, one-paced when asked for effort, stall test.
Raced behind midfield, over concluding stages was steadied when unable to improve.
Began awkwardly, crowded for room near 750M, settled at rear, steadied near 150M, not fully tested.
Taken back to get cover, shifted in for improving passing 500M, faded out passing 150M, rider and trainer questioned, must trial.
Quickly away, laid in and caused minor interference. Pressured for early lead, soon settled in second, shaken up 300m out and kept on strongly to the line.
Quickly away, sat easily in garden spot, never totally free until last 50m, came smartly late for second.
Clean jump, minor contact, recovered at once and settled near rear, came five-wide top of lane, kept on one pace to the line.
Good jump, ridden for speed at once, found a midfield spot, strong headway 3-deep without cover 650m out, stayed on strongly under heavy pressure.
Smooth jump, good early pace, in touch 5th, all chance coming home, outpaced under a strong drive.
Fair jump, midfield, settled in sixth from 600m out, never free in the straight, managed to switch path at 200m, good solid late finish.
Moderate jump, saved ground along the fence in rear, shaken up 700m when pace quickened, one pace under drive coming home.
Good jump, took check after impeded by the crossing-over of the widest draw horse, saved ground along the rail, kept on one pace coming home.
Quickly away, ridden rigorously for an early lead and soon led along the rail, unchallenged until reaching the top of the lane, never a threat under heavy pressure.
Fair jump, soon bumped hard and took a check, settled in last pair, shaken up 600m out, widest of all 7-deep top of straight, one pace to the finish.
Average to begin, raced 3 wide with no cover in midfield, slightly improved on turn, kept on very well in straight and scored by1-1/4L.
Away with them, positioned 5 lengths back on rail, 2 wide on turn, taken wide in straight and finished off strongly to get 2nd.
Began awkwardly and bumped, recovered to take the lead, kept on well after turning in, headed near 200M, stayed on for 3rd.
Taken back from gate 10, raced at tail, 8 lengths or so back, improved from 600M, finished off very strongly in straight to make frame, good debut.
Jumped with them, no early speed, raced 6 lengths back at rear, last turning in, made very good progress in straight to be nearest on line.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide in midfield, severely checked near 800M, shifted out off heels near 700M, no clear running early in straight, bumped near 200M, finished off evenly thereafter.
Began awkwardly, recovered to race 1-2 lengths back on rail, saved ground throughout, kept to inside after straightening, but finished off only one-paced.
Jumped well from the widest draw, positioned outside the leader in 2nd, there to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide in midfield early, carried wider on turn, no cover thereafter, peaked early in straight, bumped and unbalanced near 200M, finished off one-paced.
Began only fairly from a wide draw, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, same position on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Jumped well, positioned 3 lengths back on rail, similar position on turn, showed no progress in straight.
Began well, raced prominently, awkwardly placed and lost ground near 800M, no daylight after turning in, finished last. (See Racing Incidents.)
Sent forward to take the rail and led by 1-1/4L, maintained lead throughout and held on well to the line to score.
Travelled in midfield, about 3-1/2L behind 2 wide, fought on to the line, just missed by a short-head.
At the rear, about 8L behind along the rail, closed off strongly from 200M on centre track to take 3rd. (Rider questioned)
Raced in front of midfield, sat about 2-1/4L behind the lead, kept on fairly to the line to take 4th.
Niggled to race to the front, sat about 1-1/4L off the lead, kept on going to the post.
Settled to race in behind midfield, about 4-1/2L behind 2 wide, made ground gradually to the line.
Jumped well, then eased to be at the rear, about 7L behind 3 wide with cover, made ground and ran on to the line.
Settled in behind midfield, about 5L behind along the rail, made ground and closed off fairly.
Hard ridden forward, settled to race in the box-seat, sat about 2L behind, very one paced.
Raced towards the rear, 5-3/4L behind 2 wide, did not make ground.
Rolled forward to sit just in front of midfield along the rail, did not threaten. (Lame right front)
Slow to begin and lost ground, settled midfield and raced keenly, never in it.
Swiftly away, easily settled just behind the pace in fourth, shaken up 600m out, kept on strongly under pressure to lead 200m out, held well under top weight.

A touch slow when gates opened, soon recovered and dispute lead 4-wide first bend, settled in second without cover back straight, assumed lead 300m out, no match to the stronger winner, finished well for second.
Clean quick jump, settled in fifth along the fence, shaken up 500m out, ran on evenly and all out to keep third on the line.
Quick jump and ridden hard for early speed but outpaced, always the trailing three, strong drive 300m out after the leaders were long gone, strong finish and just missed third.
Fair jump, midfield 4-back along the fence, shaken up 450m out, came best under drive last 150m.
Jumped well, not as quick early, settled near rear, all chance coming home, one pace under an all-out drive.
Smooth jump, midfield, one pace, no threat.
Fair jump, unable to match early pace, rear pair, came 6-wide top of lane, one pace under drive.
Quickest of all, disputed lead and found easy garden spot in third at 1200m, shaken up 450m for more, found nothing when given his head.
Poor flat-footed start, trailed in last the entire trip until last 400m, came widest 7-deep top of lane, best strides inside the last 200m, finished well.
Good clean jump, ridden hard for early speed, disputing lead and using hard first bend, dropped in and lead 1200m, unchallenged back straight, beaten tamely 350m out.
Quickly away, chased early pace 5-2ide first bend, soon caught 3-deep without cover in midfield, weakened after straightening out in the lane, soon beaten.
Restrained in midfield along the 3-path, no cover from 800M, crept closer to leaders 600M when pace slackened, quickened to lead 250M, kicked right away to score.
From draw 13 went forward and crossed to the lead 1000M, led fast middle stages, given a breather 600M, headed by winner 250M, kept on soundly to hold 2nd.
Positively ridden from draw 11, crossed to fence chasing leaders in 3rd, fought hard in straight but always held by first 2, held on for 3rd in photo finish.
Away with them to be racing in midfield on settling, into clear 350M, stayed on steadily towards the finish.
Dropped back, travelled strongly towards the rear, held up 300M-150M, rattled home late to just miss 3rd.
Settled down midfield along the rail, held ground in the straight, no impact final 200M. (Blood in trachea.)
Chased the pace 2-wide, had every chance turning in but couldn't find extra under pressure, faded 150M.
Reserved towards the rear 7Ls off the pace, wide on the bend, battled on over final 400M without threatening.
Not far off in 5th, fought on one pace in straight, weakened away 150M.
Tardy away, settled down in rear 9-10Ls off the pace, swung wide into straight, didn't pick up and never any impression.
Behind midfield in 9th spot, shifted out 750M and soon ridden along, run ended 250M, eased. (Wounds LH cannon / Mucus / Lame next day.)
Towards the rear, 5Ls to make up 400M but never got going.
Guided to race behind midfield, raced ungenerously during the race, didn't finish off. (Unacceptable performance and racing manners.)
Raced keenly, caught wide no cover from 1100M-800M, chased leader home turn but soon gave way from 450M, Tailed off. (Unacceptable Performance.)
Clean break, good natural speed to take second position easily after 200m, shaken from 200m out, sprinted clear and held well for a close win.
A touch slow from the barrier, settled sixth along fence, ran on well for second inside the last 50m.
Missed jump, recovered at once and disputed lead, managed to take up third without cover after 400m, all out drive coming home 400m out, lost second near the line.
Slowly away, bumped hard, recovered and settled in seventh, shaken 500m for more, kept on well without threatening coming home.
Clean break, near rear, shaken up from 200m out, finished strongly and continued to gain inside the last 100m.
Clean jump, taken back to rear, shaken up 200m in the middle of the straight, came powerfully late.
Jumped well, ridden hard for early pace, led after 200m, dropped onto the fence at the 800m pole, one pace under drive from 350m out, beaten tamely from 150m.
Broke left and made contact, recovered at once and disputed lead 4-deep without cover in fifth, shaken 500m to keep up, kept on well under drive coming home.
Fair jump at best, rear group, ridden 600m when pace quickened, found little in the straight.
Slowly away, rear pair, never a factor.
Quickly away, good natural speed, taken back to fourth 3-deep without cover the entire trip, one pace under drive, weakened last 100m.
Broke awkwardly, trailed in last, never a threat.
Eased back early to settle worse than midfield, on the fence. Looked 1 paced at 250m, before showing a massive turn of foot. Kicked clear from 100m and went to the line hands and heels late.
Pushed out early to claim the lead. Stayed on solidly in the straight and looked the winner at 150m, but was beaten by a big run late.
Eased out early and settled midfield. Had a clear run in the straight, and stayed on strongly, without kicking, and was catching 2nd late.
Eased forward early to settle midfield, on the fence. Held up down the straight until 40m from the line. Ran strongly when clear to show what could have been.
Pushed forward early before dropping back at 1100m to sit forward of midfield. Bumped and slightly unbalanced at 150m, but still stayed on solidly late.
Taken up to challenge for the lead early, before settling 2nd 1 off the fence. Stayed on solidly early in the straight before running out of steam late.

Pushed forward early, eventually settling 3rd, on the fence. Held up when in a tight run at 300m, but 1 paced when clear from 250m. Not pushed out in the last 150m, and dropped back. Raced tight late.
Tardily away and dropped back early to sit at the rear of the field. Only stayed on fairly in the straight.
Cruised out to settle just in front of midfield. Mo clear run in the straight and was never fully tested.
Taken across from the wide draw to settle just behind midfield, 3 wide with limited cover. Only 1 paced in the straight.
Cruised forward to settle behind midfield. Keen from 1000m and awkward on heels 900m. Wider on the turn, but had nothing left late and went to the line hands and heels.
Dropped back early from the wide draw to sit last. Plugged away to the line without threatening.
Dropped back early from the wide draw to share last place. Plugged away to the line under minimal urging.
Crowded on jumping, but recovered well enough to sit forward of midfield but wide with no cover. Never ran on under minimal urging in the straight and was eased in the last 150m.

Settled just off the pace on the rail, tracked the leaders in 3rd turning for home, switched out to challenge upon straightening, just got up inside the final 50 metres.
Began well from a wide gate, settled towards the rear of the main body of the field, switched wide into the straight, finished off the race well down the centre of the track.
Began well from the widest gate, ridden to vie for lead out wide down back straight, gained slender lead rounding home bend, unable to sustain effort and headed inside the final 50 metres.
Settled just worse than midfield in 8th some 6L back on the rail, baulked and switched for a run 200 metres out, made up good late ground in the straight.
Began awkwardly losing ground, soon recovered along the rail to take up running 800 metres out, held narrow lead or disputed lead to the 200 metres, swamped under pressure.
Jumped fairly, soon dropped to the back of the main body of the field in 10th, ran on past well-beaten horses in the straight.
Jumped fairly, settled in mid-division of the main body of the field, slightly worse entering straight, ran home one-paced.
Began well, settled just off the pace in 4th or 5th, came under pressure rounding home bend, one-paced before finding no extra inside the final 200 metres.
Moderate start, picked up smoothly along the rail to be about 4L back in 6th or 7th, saved ground on the inside turning in, faded in straight.
Soon detached from the main body of the field, never seen with a chance.
Ridden along up with the pace, dropped to 3rd rounding home bend, folded up quickly in the straight.
Soon dropped to the tail-end from a wide gate, tailed-off despite reminders far side, never a factor.
Eased back, 2 wide, harmed by the slow pace, unleashed strong finishing efforts 250M to score.
3 back along the fence, harmed by the slow pace, dashed strongly 200M, just missed by a narrow margin.

Eased to sit in midfield early, however trapped very wide, moved forward 900M to sit outside the leader and take advantages of the slow pace, led 300M, closed off strongly to the line, overhauled in last stride.
Pushed forward, took rail steadily, favoured by the slow tempo, ran on well to the line, just missed 3rd.
Hard ridden early but not muster, at back on the fence, lack room in straight, dashed strongly despite not suited by the slow pace.
Pushed to sit in front of midfield, 2 wide, not suited by the slow pace, little dash 300M, run ended 100M.
At back, along the fence, not suited by the slow pace, little dash 150M.
Eased to rear, 2-3 wide, harmed by the slow tempo, dashed well 250M, run ended 100M.
Eased back, 2 wide, not suited by the slow pace, lack room 4-2, little dash when clear.
Hard ridden forward, benefited by the slow tempo, soon out of fuel 250M.
Slow away, at rear, harmed by the slow pace, no dash.
Pressed forward to take the rail and led at slow sectionals, ran on until 250M emptied.
Raced behind leaders, improved passing 400M, quickened passing 100M to score.
Ridden along to take lead, responded well when asked for effort in the straight, finished solidly.
Ridden along to take box seat, kept improving on rail and battled hard in the straight, came home solidly.
Urged to settle outside the lead, fought hard entire straight, finished nicely.
Raced at rear, near 550M was checked when crowded for room, made ground passing 100M, finished well.
Taken back at start, near 550M lay out, made ground passing 150M, close to the line was awkwardly placed.
Throughout the race travelled wide and without cover, gradually made ground passing 150M, close to the line was awkwardly placed.
Raced behind midfield, limited response in the straight.
Taken back at start, settled behind midfield on rail, shifted out to improve at Home Turn, one-paced.
On jumping was crowded for room, steadied to obtain cover in midfield after being ridden along, weakened badly passing 150M.
Travelled at back, widest on straightening, never in it.
Bounded at start then lost ground when bumped a runner, settled midfield on rail, travelled keenly in middle stages, tiring badly passing 200M, failed to close off.
Clean jump, ridden at once for lead, led just before first turn, had the race in total control with 1000m to go, shaken up 200m, sprinted strongly and won easily.
Good jump, settled in seventh 3-deep with cover back straight, strong headway 4-deep without cover 400m out, kept on strongly for second.
Fair start, midfield, dropped to eighth 600m out, came well to take third in the lane.
Quickest of all, garden spot, shaken up 500m out, one pace under an all-out drive coming home.
Broke with his head sideway, soon recovered, taken up second position in a slowly run race from 800m out, found little after entering the home straight.
Stumbled and missed jump, rear group, shaken up 500m for more, widest of all 6-deep top of the straight, no threat.
Fair jump at best, last along the fence, found little under drive.
Clean break, taken back by rider at once, last along fence at the top of the lane, not quickened.
Quickly away, chased early pace, settled in second without cover from 1200m, dropped to fifth 800m, challenged top of straight, never a factor.
A touch slow, unable to get cover and stuck 3-deep without cover the entire trip, no threat in the lane.
Broke awkwardly, settled ninth along fence, pulled hard on many occasions and took check top of straight, ran greenly under drive.
Broke well, settled in sixth along the fence in the back straight, hard driven from 600m out, laid in badly 250m and soon beaten.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, 7 to 8 lengths back, improved on turn, taken wide in straight and finished off very strongly to score.
Average to begin, positioned 2 wide better than midfield, same position on turn, made steady progress in straight to take 2nd.
Crowded out start, unable to slot in, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, improved from 400M, made steady progress in straight to be closest at the finish, just missed 2nd.
Began well from a tricky gate, showed early speed to take the lead easily, travelled well throughout, kept on well after turning in, headed close home.
Away with them, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, saved ground throughout, checked early in straight, finished off evenly.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide at rear, slightly improved on turn, 3 wide, widest in straight, made some progress before hampered in the final stages.
Jumped well from a wide draw, sent forward to sit outside the leader, there to turn, kept on evenly until final 100M, weakened thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began awkwardly and lost ground, raced at rear, 5 lengths back on rail, there to turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Away well, positioned on rail in midfield, unbalanced and lost ground near 1300M, saved ground throughout, no daylight in straight, not able to test properly.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 4 lengths back on turn, finished off one-paced.
Crowded on jumping, raced at tail, on rail, still well back on turn, finished off one-paced.
Slightly slow out from the widest draw, unable to slot in, travelled 3 wide and without cover throughout, weakened after turning in, eased close home. (Whip entangled in the reins near 250M.)
Raced in midfield, 2-1/4L behind 3 wide but with cover, kept on very well and held off late challenge to score by a neck.
Eased and raced towards the rear, 4-1/2L behind 2 wide, awkward to heels at 250M, made nice ground thereafter and pushed winner all the way with a strong finishing effort.
Travelled just in front of midfield, 2-1/4L behind 2 wide, showed good kick near 200M, ran on well to take 3rd.
Ridden to be forward, sat behind the lead, 1L off but 3 wide and without cover, kept on going to the line.
Raced in behind midfield, 4L behind the lead 2 wide, swung wide and remained one paced to the finish.
Sent forward, sat a neck off and outside the lead, remained one paced but kept on to the line.
Travelled in around midfield, 2-1/2L behind along the rail, closed off fairly inside final 150M.
Settled to race in one-off one-back position, sat 1L off the lead, in touch until couldn't find extra near 150M.
Taken back and raced 6L behind in a 2 wide position, swung widest, failed to continue to improve passing 200M.
Niggled forward to race in the box-seat, sat 1L off the lead, keen throughout, showed slight dash prior to 200M then failed to respond. Disappointing and must trial.
Pushed forward to take rail and led by about a neck, flattened half way down the straight.
Fair jump at best, always in the rear, shaken up 400m out, came widest 7-deep top of straight, responded strongly and gained head victory on the line.
Smooth swift break, led after 5 strides, found garden spot 1200m and travelled easily, shaken 250m out, led 100m and finished strong but got touched off on the line.
Quickly away, midfield fence, all out drive along the rail from 200m out, strong finish for third.
Good jump, taken back by jockey at once, calmly settled in eighth one off the fence, blocked and switched path 200m out, came on well and just missed the money.
Quickly away, chased early leaders at once, in touch in fifth, outpaced under drive.
Broke in air, settled last the entire trip, came widest 7-deep top of straight, strong late charge under top weight.
Fair jump, taken back to second last along the rail at once, blocked and bumped hard 250m out, came again 100m out, powerful finish.
Good clean jump, settled in seventh 3-deep with cover, shaken 400m out, hard contact 250m, kept on well under a strong drive to the wire.
Jumped awkwardly, recovered at once and disputed early lead, never relaxed, pulled to second without cover 800m, challenged 400m, led 300m, found no more.
Clean jump, settled ninth along the fence, one pace under drive.
Quickly away, disputed lead and caught 3-deep first bend, took lead at the 1200m pole, challenged before home bend, found little under drive.
Clean break, unable to find cover and stuck 3-deep without cover just behind the leaders, shaken up 400m out, weakened 200m out, soon beaten.
In 5th always in touch, hit front 150M, drew clear towards the finish.
Dropped back from wide gate, settled down 5Ls near the rear, finished off honestly to go 2nd near line in a blanket finish for minor honours. Couldn't get close to winner.
Away well enough to be chasing leaders along the 3-path, no cover during race, couldn't match acceleration of winner from 250M but stuck to task well under 7lb claimer to claim 3rd in a tight finish.
Not hurried early stages, taken back to sit behind midfield 4Ls off the pace, stayed on mildly towards the finish, just missed 3rd.
Positively ridden from wide barrier, settled just outside leader, briefly led 250M, couldn't hold off fast finishing winner, held 2nd until concluding stages when caught up by pursuers.
Shaken up to take the lead, set steady pace to straight, headed 250M, battled on towards the line, swamped by pursuing pack near the line.
Began fairly, recovered to sit in midfield, difficult to settle during race, ran home moderately for 7th but not beaten far by 2nd to 6th.
Taken back from wide draw, held up last 6Ls off the pace, switched widest to challenge, closed off steadily without serious threat.
Quickly into stride, travelled keenly when restrained behind leaders, checked and lost running 200M, not ridden out towards the finish.
Caught 3-deep in midfield, couldn't sprint enough over final 300M to pose any threat to leaders.
Outpaced by leaders early stages, held midfield spot along the fence, kept on same pace turning home, faded late stages. (Lame next day.)
Began awkwardly, no close than 3-wide behind midfield, gave limited response turning in, weakened away 150M.
