Began well from the one draw, settled wide near the centre of the track in a prominent position, moved up to join the leaders 400 metres out, hit the front under pressure inside the 200 metres, just held on to the line.
Restrained just off the pace, commenced move but not much room until the 200 metres, ran on under pressure to the line.
Well there, hit the front briefly 400 metres out, kept on.
Moderate start, always thereabouts on the rail, fought on steadily without threatening.

Slowly away losing ground, soon taken across for rails run, travelled keenly behind runners and unable to obtain a clear run until the 200 metres, sustained progress under pressure in the closing stages.
Soon dropped to last few near the centre of the track, gained slightly closer passing the 400 metres, one-paced under pressure in closing stages.
Settled in rear of the mid-division, gained slightly closer coming onto course proper, unable to sustain effort inside the final 100 metres.
Travelled keenly in first few, came under pressure from the 400 metres, crowded and lost position 300 metres out, never recovered.
Inconvenienced after the moderate start, taken across to stands rail at the back 700 metres out, ran on past well-beaten runners closing stages.
Led early, soon headed after coming onto course proper, weakened under pressure.
Soon dropped to last few, made short-lived effort after coming onto course proper.
Began fairly, settled in forward of the mid-division, folded up quickly inside the final 400 metres.
Moderate start, travelled in midfield to the 600 metres, faded. (Questioned for disappointing performance)
Soon dropped well behind, never seen with a chance.
Pushed forward, sat 2 wide, benefited by the slow tempo, closed off strongly to score but only by a narrow margin.
Eased back, 2-4 wide, harm by the slow pace, dashed strongly 300M whilst hanging in, just missed by a narrow margin.
Midfield, 2 wide, harmed by the slow pace, unleashed strong finishing efforts 300M.
Pushed to hold the rail in midfield, harmed by the slow pace, lack room 400M, dashed strongly when clear.
Pushed forward to share the lead at slow sectionals, just held ground in straight.
Eased back, trapped 3 wide, lack room 4-2, dashed strongly when clear despite not suited by the slow pace.
Slow away, hard ridden to keep up at back, harmed by the slow pace, lack room 4-2, little dash 100M.
Pushed forward, took rail, no dash, weakened 300M.
Eased back, 2-4 wide, not suited by the slow tempo, no turn of foot in straight.
Pushed forward to lead at slow sectionals, raced keenly, out of fuel 300M.
Never a factor at rear.
Eased back, 2 wide, harmed by the slow pace, lack room 400M, no dash when clear.
Hard ridden forward, trapped 3 wide throughout without cover, weakened 300M.
Hard ridden early, trapped 4-5 wide throughout in midfield, emptied 400M.
Ridden along to settle behind leaders, quickened passing 150M, finished unchallenged. Distressed.
Jumped well and took lead, travelled comfortably throughout the race, responded well in the straight, finished solidly.
Stumbled at start, raced behind midfield, gradually made ground in the straight, lay in over concluding stages, finished nicely.
Settled midfield, asked for effort on straightening, fought hard entire straight, came home well.
Urged along to take box seat, kept improving rounding Home Turn and straight, finished well.
Began awkwardly, settled midfield on rail, kept on in the straight, finished OK.
Fast out, raced outside the lead, one-paced when asked for effort in the straight.
Raced midfield, tried to improve near 400M, one-paced.
Settled at rear, commenced to improve near 500M, limited response in the straight.
On jumping bumped heavily with a runner and became unbalanced, after 1000M was left racing wide and without cover behind midfield, made the turn awkwardly, limited response in the straight.
Hampered at start then taken back, no response in the straight.
Settled behind midfield, always back, failed to run on.
Settled behind midfield on rail, never in it.
Began very awkwardly then taken back, widest on straightening, failed to run on.
Jumped well, bumped near 1200M, raced 2 wide, 2 to 3 lengths back, slightly improved from 600M, finished off very well to score.
Slightly slow out from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground to turn, angled out from 500M, finished off very strongly to take 2nd.
Away with them, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, still 3 wide on turn, widest in straight, finished off very strongly to be nearest on line.
Began only fairly, positioned 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, travelled keenly in the middle stages, angled out after turning in, crowded near 200M, finished off evenly thereafter.
Jumped well from gate 9, sent forward to race prominently, shared lead in the middle stages, kept on well early in straight, headed near 200M, stayed on evenly.
Slowly away, raced 2 wide at rear early, found the rail after 1000M, slightly improved on turn, angled out early in straight, made good progress to be nearest on line.
Bumped start and unbalanced, positioned 2 wide, 1 to 2 lengths back, there to turn, peaked early in straight, finished off evenly.
Bumped start, positioned 2 wide, slightly worse than midfield, similar position on turn, finished off one-paced.
Began well, showed early speed to take the lead, shared the lead with TRAVEL EMPEROR in the middle stages, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Very slowly away, raced at rear, 6 to 7 lengths back on rail, kept to inside throughout, failed to close off in straight.
Fractious in barrier, began awkwardly, raced 2 wide at rear, there to turn, made no progress in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back from the widest draw, raced 3 wide at rear, still well back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Crowded start, raced at rear throughout, never a threat.
Crowded on jumping, recovered to race wide in midfield, no cover after 1100M, peaked on turn, weakened early in straight when hard run took effect, finished last.

Bumped start, positioned 2 wide in 5th, travelled keenly and awkwardly placed near 1050M, same position on turn, no clear running early in straight, finished off strongly when clear thereafter to score.
Jumped well from gate 1, positioned 1to 2 lengths behind the leader, easy run on turn, kept on very well in straight to take 2nd.
Bumped start, raced 3 wide with cover, 4 lengths or so back at rear, travelled keenly in the middle stages, finished off very strongly in straight to be nearest on line.

Away with them, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, there to turn, found no daylight early in straight and checked near 300M, made some progress thereafter until awkwardly placed just before the finishing line.
Jumped well from a wide draw, unable to slot in, travelled 4 wide and without cover, 2 lengths or so back, still no cover on turn, kept on evenly to the line.
Began well from gate 13, raced 4 wide with cover, 3 lengths or so back, travelled well in the middle stages, made minor progress in straight without threatening. (See Racing Incidents.)
Bumped start, sent forward to sit outside the leader, there to turn, stayed on well early in straight, peaked near 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Average to begin, raced 4 to 5 lengths back on rail, saved ground on turn, angled out early in straight, found no daylight, not able to be properly tested in the final stages.
Jumped well from the widest draw, sent forward to the lead, travelled well on turn, kicked clear early in straight, peaked and headed near final 100M, weakened thereafter.
Began fairly, raced 3 wide with cover, 5 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, taken widest in straight, finished off one-paced.
Jumped well, taken back to race 2 wide behind midfield, similar position on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Average to begin, difficult to restrain early, positioned 2 wide, 5 to 6 lengths back, last turning in, failed to close off in straight.
Jumped with them, travelled keenly early, raced 3 wide with no cover throughout, emptied early in straight when hard run took effect.
Bumped start, raced 3 to 4 lengths back on rail, saved ground throughout, emptied early in straight, finished last.
Pushed and took the rail and led by about 1/2L, kept on to the line to score by 2L without being under the whip.
Sent forward and settled to race outside the lead, sat 3/4L off, kept on going but couldn't match the winner.
Eased and then settled to race towards the rear, 4-3/4L behind 2 wide, made nice ground and hit the line strongly.
Hampered after the start, settled in midfield, 3-1/4L behind 2 wide, made ground and ran on fairly to the line.
Travelled in midfield, 2-3/4L behind the lead 3 wide without cover, kept on one paced to the line.
Settled to race in worse than midfield, 4L behind along the rail, did not save ground but ran on to the line.
Bumped after the start, pushed to occupy the box-seat, sat 1/2L off, one paced and weakened near 200M.
Settled to race in behind midfield, 4-1/4L behind 3 wide with cover, did not improve but kept on going to the line.
Niggled along and settled in one-off one-back position, sat 1-1/2L off, couldn't maintain and lost ground passing 200M.
Eased after the start and raced at the rear, 6L behind the lead 2 wide, remained one paced.
Raced at the rear, 6L behind the lead 3 wide with cover, did not feature in the straight.
Bumped start, settled to race at the rear, 6-1/4L behind along the rail, only past tired runners.
Bumped after the start, raced just in front of midfield, 2-1/2L behind along the rail, couldn't find extra approaching 200M.
Pushed after the start, sat in behind midfield, 4L behind and very wide and without cover, found nothing.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide in midfield, same position on turn, finished off very well in straight to score by a nose.
Taken back from a tricky gate, raced at tail, 9 lengths back, improved from near 550M, taken widest in straight, finished off very strongly to take 2nd, just narrowly beaten.
Fast into stride, showed early speed to take the lead easily, travelled well on turn, kicked clear early in straight but just couldn't hold off the rivals late, finished 3rd.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide behind midfield, same position on turn, made good progress in straight to make frame.
Jumped well, sat 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground throughout, angled out after turning in, finished off evenly.
Jumped with them, sent forward to race prominently, 2nd on turn, kept on evenly in straight.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide in 4th, awkwardly placed near 1000M, similar position on turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Away with them, positioned on rail behind midfield, same position to near 550M, angled out thereafter and finished off evenly in straight.
Moderately away from a wide draw, unable to slot in, travelled 3 wide and without cover at rear throughout, made no progress in straight.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced 2 wide at rear, there to turn, failed to close off in straight.
Taken back from gate 11, positioned on rail at rear, kept to inside after turning in, made no progress in straight.
Average to begin, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground throughout, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter, finished last.
From wide draw guided to a 2-wide spot tracking leaders, travelled strongly to straight, quickened up well to lead 200M and had enough left to fend off the renewed challenge of 2nd.
Positively ridden to take the lead from 1300M, led uncontested at a steady pace, refused to give in when headed by winner 200M, went down fighting.
Reserved in midfield along the fence but never far off from the pace, held up nearing 200M, worked home well late, could have done better.
Jumped well, restrained to sit behind midfield on settling, awkwardly placed 350M, ran on without threat to leaders when clear.
Reined in after the start, keenly 1100M, pushed wide and improved to midfield home turn, only battled in the straight off a tough run.
Restrained in midfield, caught 3-wide no cover after 900M, took closer order making the turn but lacked a strong turn of foot when driven in the run home.
Gradually moved up to be tracking leader along the 2-path, held ground in straight, plodded home over final 200M.
Chased leaders along the inside, kept on same pace turning in, faded out of contention 200M.
Settled down 2nd last, blocked for a run straightening up and unable to obtain clear running at any stage.
Dropped back to last, raced keenly middle stages, 5Ls off leader 400M, couldn't quicken to challenge.
Jumped well, raced 2 wide in midfield, hampered near 950M, improved from 600M, very wide turning in, finished off very strongly to score with still plenty gas in tank.
Away well, positioned 3 to 4 lengths back, easy run on turn, angled out near 500M, closed off well to take 2nd.
Quickly into stride, sent forward to race in 2nd, 2 lengths back, moved closer on turn, kept on well in straight but couldn't hold off the first two near final 200M, stayed on for 3rd.

Bumped start, taken back to race at rear, 6 to 7 lengths back, steadied near 950M, improved from near 550M, bumped turning in, made some progress in straight to make frame without threatening the first few.
Slowly away, positioned 6 to 7 lengths back on rail, saved ground throughout, angled out in straight and made some progress without threatening.
Slightly slow out, raced 4 to 5 lengths back in midfield, saved ground on turn, awkwardly placed near 600M, finished off evenly in straight.
Jumped well from gate 10, sent forward to take the lead, enjoyed the easy lead throughout, peaked and headed early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, 8 to 9 lengths back, last turning in, no clear running early in straight, passed a few tired runners when clear thereafter.
Bumped on jumping, unable to slot in early, 5 lengths back, found a 2 wide midfield position near 950M, bumped turning in, failed to close off in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Moderately away from a tricky gate, unable to slot in, raced wide without cover, 3 lengths or so back, still no cover on turn, emptied early in straight when hard run took effect.
Average to begin, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, there to turn, emptied early in straight and eased, finished last.
Pressed forward early to lead. Pulled away from the top of the straight. Given a couple of taps 150m, but won impressively and was easing late.
Settled around midfield. Keen and onto heels 800m. Ran strongly in the straight and was the only one making ground on the winner late.
Pressed forward to settle 2nd, 1 off the fence. Stayed o0n solidly in the straight, but couldn't match leader. Peaked late and lost 2nd.
Slowly away, but recovered well enough to sit midfield. Ran solidly in the straight, but peaked late.
Eased back early to settle midfield. Wider on the turn. Stayed on fairly without threatening a place.
Settled 3rd, on the fence. 1 paced in the straight and never threatened.
Taken forward early and settled 4th, 1 off the fence. Steadied off heels 300m.Didn't respond in the straight and went to the line 1 paced.
Bagan awkwardly and lost ground. Settled at the rear of the field. Stayed on fairly and made up some ground late.
Unsettled when being steadied back early and got head up. Finally steadied towards the rear of the field. Plugged away fairly in the straight.
Dropped back towards the rear of the field early. Wide no cover throughout. 1 paced in the straight.
Dropped back to the rear of the field early. Flat in the straight.
Settled around midfield, 3 wide no cover. Gave nothing in the straight.
Dropped back towards the rear of the field early. Never improved.

Niggled at early, settled in 6th in mid-division, quickened well inside the final 300 metres to snatch victory close to home.
Jumped fairly, gradually moved to the lead and obtained rails run over 800 metres out, led until collared close to home.
Ridden forward from a wide gate, settled 2-wide in 3rd just over 1L off the pace, became 2nd shortly after straightening, swamped for 2nd inside the 50 metres.
Soon dropped to the rear niggling along, saved ground on the inside turning for home, ran on well to be nearest at finish.
Sluggish at start, driven forward to 4th some 2L back coming onto home bend, came under pressure and reached 2nd just inside the 200 metres, unable to sustain effort closing stages.
Driven along early stages, settled in forward of midfield in 5th on the rail, ran home one-paced without quickening.
Soon dropped to last few, made no impression.
Moderate start, soon dropped behind midfield despite niggling along, travelled 3-wide without cover most of way, weakened after straightening. (Questioned for disappointing performance)
Chased the leader to straight, folded up quickly.
Moderate start, remained in last few despite niggling along, switched out to challenge entering straight, found nothing.
Never on terms despite ridden along.
Moderate start, soon dropped to last on the rail, made no impression.
Hard ridden forward, not suited by the fast tempo, drifted away 400M to score.
Eased back, trapped 3 wide, suited by the fast pace, dashed well 150M.
Eased back, 2 wide, benefited by the fast tempo, progressed steadily 300M for 3rd.
Pushed to keep up in midfield, 3 wide, benefited by the fast pace, progressed steadily 300M.
Pushed to hold the rail in front of midfield, just held ground in straight.
Checked at start, 2 wide at rear, favoured by the fast tempo, made steady ground 250M.
Pushed to obtain box seat, not suited by the fast pace, out of fuel 150M.
Pushed forward, sat 2 wide, harmed by the fast sectionals, ran on well until 100M weakened.
Hard ridden early, took rail at rear, benefited by the fast tempo, blocked most straight, made steady ground.
Hard ridden early but failed to muster, lack room 4-2, ran on fairly when clear.
Hard ridden to keep up with the fast pace, 2 wide, emptied 400M.
Pushed forward, trapped 3 wide, harmed by the fast pace, dropped off 400M.
Ridden along to settle outside the lead, improved passing 300M, travelled strongly to score.
Raced at handy position on rail, commenced to improve on straightening, worked home strongly, missed by 1/2L.
Settled midfield, asked for effort at Home Turn, gradually made ground in the straight, finished solidly.
Majority of the race travelled wide and without cover in midfield, kept on in the straight, finished nicely.
Ridden along to settle behind leaders, asked for effort near 700M, one-paced.
Began awkwardly and failed to muster speed despite being ridden along, raced midfield on rail, passing 200M lay in and rider had to stop riding and straighten, then one-paced to the line.
Majority of the race travelled wide and without cover behind midfield, wide on straightening, one-paced.
Taken back at start, settled behind midfield on rail, limited response in the straight.
Taken back at start, always back, never in it. Lame left front next day.
Settled behind midfield, no response when asked for effort.
Taken back after raced in restricted room, raced greenly in early and middle stages, hung out near 700M, never in it.
Urged along to take lead, weakened badly passing 300M, passing 200M was crowded for room and checked, failed to run on.
Moderately away, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, there to turn, took the lead early in straight, kept on strongly to score easily.
Jumped well, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 to 4 lengths back, angled out near 400M, closed off well to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.
Average to begin, raced 4 lengths back on rail, saved ground to turn, angled out early in straight, made reasonable headway in straight to take 3rd without threatening.
Inconvenienced after the moderate start, positioned 5 lengths or so back at rear, 2 wide on turn, taken wide in straight and made some progress to make frame.
Jumped with them, raced prominently, 3 wide with no cover throughout, peaked and headed after turning in, stayed on one paced to the line.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced 3 wide with cover at rear. 6 lengths back, still well back on turn, widest in straight, made some headway in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, 8 lengths back, slightly improved on turn, no clear running early in straight, made minor progress when clear thereafter.
Average to begin from gate 12, unable to slot in, travelled 4 wide and without cover, 1 to 2 lengths back, still no cover on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Jumped well from a wide draw, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, 4 wide on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Away with them, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, easy run to turn, angled out near 400M, kept on same pace early in straight, peaked near final 200M, weakened thereafter.
Began well, sent forward to share the lead early, positioned in 3rd after 1000M, 2 wide throughout, peaked early in straight, emptied final 200M.
Slowly away, raced at rear, 7 lengths back, found the rail in the middle stages, 4 lengths back on turn, emptied early in straight.
Jumped well from gate 1, shared the lead, peaked on turn, emptied early in straight, eased final 200M, finished tailed out.
Moderately away, sent forward to race 3 wide with cover, 2 lengths or so back, peaked in the middle stages, weakened on turn, eased early in straight. (Lame right front leg next day.)
Jumped well, sat a length behind the leader on rail, easy run throughout, closed off well to score by a neck.
Quickly into stride, showed early speed to take the lead, easy lead to turn, kept on very well in straight but couldn't hold off the winner late.
Average to begin, positioned 4 to 5 lengths back on rail, 2 wide on turn, made very good progress in straight to take 3rd, nearest on line.
Began well, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, same position on turn, made some progress early in straight, peaked near 200M, just stayed on for 4th.

Began awkwardly from the widest draw, unable to slot in, raced 4 wide at rear early, found cover near 1000M, improved from 500M, very wide turning in, made good progress in straight without threatening.
Average to begin, raced at rear, 5 to 6 lengths back, same margin back on turn, made some progress in straight.
Began well from a wide draw, sent forward to race 2 wide in 2nd, same position on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Began very awkwardly losing considerable ground, raced 7 lengths back at rear, slightly improved along the rail on turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Average to begin, raced at tail, 8 to 9 lengths back, still well back on turn, angled out in straight and made minor progress.
Slightly slow out, raced 2 wide in midfield, peaked on turn, stayed on one-paced in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Away with them, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, 7 lengths back, still well back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Jumped well from gate 1, positioned 3 lengths or so back on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, kept on evenly until near 200M, emptied thereafter.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide in midfield early, couldn't maintain position from near 1200M, 8 lengths back on turn, made no progress in straight, emptied near 200M, eased thereafter.
Moderately away from a wide draw, unable to slot in, travelled 3 wide and without cover in midfield, peaked on turn, emptied early in straight when hard run took toll.
Rolled forward to race in the box-seat, sat 1-1/4L off, pulled away from 250M, kept on to win by a comfortable 2L margin.
Niggled along to be prominent but wide, improved to take rail and led near 1200M, fought on gamely but was no match.
Raced just in front of midfield, sat 2-3/4L behind the lead along the rail, continued to improve and ran on well for 3rd.
Settled to race in midfield, 3-1/4L behind 2 wide, improved slightly and kept on fairly to the line.
Travelled ungenerously towards the rear, 5-3/4L behind 2 wide, made minor ground and stayed on to the finish.
Sent forward and raced prominently, sat 1-1/2L off 3 wide without cover, kept on until flattened near 200M.
Taken back and raced at the rear, 6L behind along the rail, did not save ground but kept on going to the line.
Eased and raced in behind midfield, 4-1/2L behind along the rail, very one paced in the straight.
Settled to race in behind midfield, 4-1/4L behind 3 wide with cover, taken wider at 700M, never threatened.
Raced in one-off one-back position, sat 2L off the lead, lost ground rounding turn and found nothing in the straight.
Prominent but wide, improved to sit 1/2L off and outside the lead after 1000M, weakened badly after 250M.
Ridden but trapped wide early, steadied then raced towards the rear, 4-1/2L behind but wide and without cover, never featured. (Lame right front)
Jumped well, positioned 3 lengths back on rail in 4th, easy run on turn, finished off strongly to score.
Average to begin, sent forward to race in 2nd, a length behind the leader, 2 wide near 800M, shared the lead turning in, kept on very well in straight, but couldn't hold off the winner late.
Began well from a wide draw, raced 2 wide in 3rd, got cover on turn, kept on well in straight to get a place.
Began awkwardly, recovered quickly to take the lead, travelled well to turn, kept on well in straight, headed near 200M, weakened thereafter, just stayed on for 4th.
Away with them, positioned 5 to 6 lengths back on rail, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after straightening, made good progress to be nearest on line.
Bumped start, positioned on rail in midfield, 3 to 4 lengths back, angled out near 500M, finished off evenly in straight without threatening.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 4 to 5 lengths back, finished off evenly in straight.
Bumped on jumping, showed no early speed, raced at tail, 7 lengths back, slightly improved on turn, taken widest in straight and finished off one-paced.
Slowly away, raced 7 lengths back at tail, still well back on turn, passed a few tired runners in straight.
Jumped well from a wide draw, raced 3 wide and without cover in midfield, found cover on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Moderately away from the widest draw, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, no cover on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Bumped start, raced at rear, 6 to 7 lengths back, peaked on turn, failed to close off in straight, finished last.
Began awkwardly, held up in midfield along the fence, into clear 350M, quickened up to lead near 200M, kept going for solid win.
Chased the pace on jumping from draw 1, responded well entering straight, couldn't match winner's pace final 250M but finished well clear of the remainders.
Away well enough to be tracking leaders on settling, held up behind two weakening horses rounding home turn and early straight, got out 300M running on well to claim 3rd near line.
Restrained in midfield but caught 3-wide throughout the race, tried hard on straightening but couldn't get closer to first 2, lost 3rd near line.
Not hurried, dropped back to race in last, 7Ls to make up leaving the bend, made some ground at the finish without threatening.
Steadied early stages to obtain cover, held up at the rear 6Ls off the good pace, had to switch lane for clear passage inside 300M, stayed on without serious threat.
Failed to muster despite ridden, caught wide then eased back for cover 5-6Ls from leader, widest runner on straightening, made minor headway over final 300M.
Bumped heavily at the start, taken back and guided to the fence, saved ground along the inside, 5Ls to make up at 400M, only held ground to the line.
Bumped heavily at the start, reserved behind midfield along the 2-path, switched out to challenge 400M but couldn't get close enough.
Held up behind midfield but no closer than 3-wide during the race, didn't run on in straight.
Emerged as leader passing 1400M, maintained a good gallop to straight, caught inside 250M, weakened away. (Lame RF leg.)
Settled down 2-wide in midfield about 4Ls off the good pace, couldn't quicken leaving the turn, never in it.

Hard pressed to go forward, tracked leader along 2-path, came under pressure inside 600M, eased down passing 300M. (Unacceptable Performance / Jockey said his mount might not appreciate being ridden forward.)
Unable to slot in from draw 13 and travelled wide no cover during the race, strode closer to be chasing leaders entering home turn, weakened away rapidly inside 300M.

Jumped awkwardly losing ground, improved from well back to 10th and just behind the midfield, travelled keenly coming onto home bend, obtained a clear run shortly after straightening, ran on well to just get up on line.

Broke well from a middle gate, settled off the pace and gradually drifted back to midfield coming onto home bend, commenced move entering straight, hit the front 150 metres out but only to be caught final strides.
Jumped fairly, settled in midfield, switched out for a run 200 metres out, finished off the race well.

Settled just better than midfield on the rail, became 5th in similar distance off the pace 1000 metres out, came 4-wide for a run entering home straight, kept on same pace under pressure without threatening.
Settled in midfield on the rail, snuck up to heels of leader entering home straight, tightened and checked passing the 400 metres, kept on steadily without threatening.
Began well from a wide gate, soon dropped to the last despite ridden along, trailed the field into straight, produced good late impression inside the final 200 metres.
Taken back from a wide gate, settled well back on the rail, came under pressure upon straightening, kept on same pace without quickening.
Began well from a wide gate, soon taken 2L back for cover in 4th, switched out for a run entering home straight, kept on until swamped inside the final 200 metres.
Moderate start, soon driven up to chase the leader onto home bend, hit the front on straightening and flattered, headed inside the 200 metres.
Ridden forward after a moderate start, chased the leaders mainly in 3rd to the 400 metres and gradually faded under pressure, beaten when hampered at the 100 metres.
Settled in last few from a wide draw, kept on before finding no extra inside the final 300 metres.
Never seen with a chance racing in last few on the rail most of the way.
Gradually taken back from a wide gate settling just worse than midfield, tired noticeably after straightening. (Blood in trachea)
Took up running 1200 metres out and crossed to the rail shortly after, folded up quickly after headed early in straight.
Pushed forward, box seat, pace good, progressed steadily 500M to score.
Pushed forward, 2-3 wide, pace good, led 400M, hung on well until 50M overhauled, ran on for 2nd.
Pushed to hold the rail in midfield, pace good, made steady ground 300M for 3rd.
Eased to rear for cover, 2-4 wide, pace good, progressed steadily 400M.
At back along the fence, pace good, made steady ground 200M.
Pushed forward 2-3 wide, pace good, weakened 200M.
Pushed early, behind midfield, 2-4 wide, pace good, moved forward 800M, raced flat in straight.
Pushed to keep up in midfield, 2 wide, pace good, made ground 200M.
At back, 2 wide, pace good, lack turn of foot.
Eased at start, took rail at rear, pace good, no progress.
Hard ridden to take rail and led at good pace, soon out of fuel 350M.
At rear, 3-5 wide, pace good, moved forward 700M, weakened 300M.
Pushed forward, trapped 3 wide, pace good, dropped off 500M.
Trapped 3-4 wide in midfield, emptied 500M.
Urged along to take lead, asked for effort on straightening, rider dropped his whip approaching 300M, kept on and finished strongly to score.
Travelled wide and without cover in midfield, quickened passing 100M, came home solidly, just missed by neck.
Jumped well, difficult to settle in the early and middle stages, raced midfield, gradually made ground passing 100M, worked home solidly.
Ridden along to settle outside the lead from widest barrier, battled hard entire straight, finished solidly.
Raced behind midfield, near 900M was bumped and became badly unbalanced then raced wide and without cover, improved to handy position at Home Turn, kept on to the line.
Taken back at start, raced behind midfield, widest on straightening, gradually made ground passing 150M, finished well.
Travelled midfield, asked for effort near 600M, gradually made ground passing 150M, finished well.
Ridden along after start then settled behind leaders, one-paced.
Settled midfield on rail, kept improving on rail at Home Turn, one-paced in the straight.
Taken back at start, only made ground passing final 50M.
Raced behind leaders on rail, limited response in the straight.
Sat back and lost ground at start, settled behind midfield on rail, no response in the straight.
After start was crowded for room, raced behind midfield, wide on straightening, failed to run on.
Slow to begin, always detached.
Jumped well from a wide draw, raced 2 wide, 2 to 3 lengths back, there to turn, kept on very well in straight to score.
Average to begin, positioned 2 to 3 lengths back on rail, saved ground on turn, made good progress in straight to take 2nd.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, same position on turn, finished off strongly in straight to take 3rd, without threatening the first two.

Fast into stride, raced prominently, took the lead near 1000M, enjoyed the easy lead on turn, kicked clear early in straight, peaked and headed near 150M, weakened gradually thereafter, just stayed on for 4th.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, 10 lengths back, still well back on turn, taken widest in straight and finished off very strongly to be nearest on line.
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after straightening and finished off evenly.
Moderately away from a wide draw, raced 3 wide in midfield, no cover after 900M, finished off evenly in straight.
Slow to begin, positioned on rail at rear, there to turn, no clear running until final 200M, made minor progress thereafter.
Taken back from gate 13, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, 7 lengths back on turn, taken wide in straight, finished off one-paced.
Began fairly and bumped, raced at rear, 9 lengths back on turn, taken very wide in straight, made no progress, emptied final 150M.
Jumped well from a wide draw, raced prominently, 2 wide throughout, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter, eased final 150M.
Away with them, raced 2 wide, 4 lengths or so back, there to turn, failed to close off in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Bumped start, raced prominently, travelled keenly in the middle stages, weakened gradually after turning in, eased final 100M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began fairly, raced at rear, 7 to 8 lengths back, there to turn, showed no response early in straight, eased final 200M. (Lost left hind plate in the early stages.)
Moderately away from a tricky gate, raced 2 wide, 5 to 6 lengths back, there to turn, angled out from 500M, finished off very strongly in straight to score.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, same position on turn, showed good progress in straight to take 2nd.
Average to begin, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, angled out early in straight and made reasonable headway to take a place.
Moderately away from a wide draw, unable to slot in early, sent forward near 1000M, took the lead on turn, kicked clear early in straight, peaked and headed near 150M, just stayed on for 4th.

Taken back from the widest draw, difficult to settle early, raced at rear, 6 lengths back, similar position on turn, no daylight early in straight, made good progress when clear thereafter to be nearest on line, just missed frame.
Out in line, raced 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, finished off evenly.
Began with them, raced 3 wide and without cover in midfield, still no cover on turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Fast into stride, took the rail easily and led, headed near 900M, 2nd on turn, kept on evenly early in straight, weakened gradually from final 150M.
Began fairly, raced 8 lengths or so back at rear, still well back on turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Began well from gate 1, positioned 2 lengths back on rail, easy run to turn, angled out near 500M, brushed early in straight, kept on evenly until near 200M, weakened thereafter.
Average to begin, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, 5 lengths or so back, there to turn, peaked early in straight, emptied in the final furlong.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 7 lengths back at rear, same position on turn, made no progress in straight. (Blood in trachea.)
Crowded on jumping, failed to muster speed, raced at tail throughout, finished tailed off, unacceptable performance. (Jockey reported his horse did not feel comfortable in the race.)
Sent forward and sat inside the lead, about a neck off stand side, pulled away from 150M and won impressively by 2L.
Settled to race in front of midfield, 2-1/4L behind stand side, fought on gamely to the line, just took 2nd.
Pushed and raced prominently, sat 1-1/2L off stand side, stayed on well, missed out on 2nd in final strides.
Bumped start, settled to race in front of midfield, 2-1/2L off stand side, finished off well to the line.
Raced in behind midfield, 4-3/4L behind along the outside rail, had no daylight until final 100M. (See Racing Incident)
Travelled in worse than midfield, 4-1/2L behind on centre track, made ground and ran on okay to the line.
Settled to race just behind midfield, 4-1/2L behind stand side, slight dash after 200M and kept on fairly to the line.
Sent forward, raced behind the leaders on the outside rail, 1-3/4L off, checked passing 300M, one paced thereafter.
Bumped start, ridden to take lead along the outside rail, led by about a neck, emptied and headed at 250M.
Bumped start, then ridden and raced prominently behind the leaders, 2L off stand side, flattened near 250M.
At the rear, about 7L behind along the outside rail, ran on mostly one paced.
Niggled along and settled in about midfield, 3-1/2L behind on centre track, flattened approaching 200M.
Crowded start, raced at the rear on centre track, ridden prior to 400M, did not threaten.
Taken back, at the rear on centre track, urged early and weakened out approaching 200M. Must trial.
Moderately away, raced 3 wide and without cover behind midfield throughout, finished off very strongly in straight to score.

Jumped well, positioned 2 wide in midfield, travelled well to turn, showed good progress early in straight, took the lead near 200M, kept on well but couldn't hold off the winner late. (Dead-heat 2nd.)
Slowly away, raced at tail, 4 lengths or so back on rail, same margin back on turn, finished off very strongly to take a place. (Dead-heat 2nd.)
Slightly slow out, positioned 3 lengths back on rail, saved ground on turn, angled out early in straight, no clear running until near 200M, finished off strongly to make frame.
Began well, positioned 2 wide in 2nd, shared lead on turn, kept on well early in straight, headed near 200M, stayed on evenly thereafter.
Away with them, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, easy run on turn, angled out early in straight, finished off evenly.
Fast into stride, took the lead easily, travelled well throughout, peaked and headed early in straight, stayed on one pace thereafter.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide at rear, 3 lengths or so back on turn, showed no response in straight, finished last. (See Racing Incidents.)
Held up in midfield, travelled strongly into contention 400M, quickened up smartly to lead near 200M, continued on well to the line holding rivals at bay.
Began well, sat just behind leaders in a steadily run race, took a while to get going in straight, did best work final 200M to cut down winner's lead to half a length.
Caught wide from draw 11, no cover from 1400M, keen and allowed to stride forward tracking leader, couldn't contain the winner inside 250M but battled on well under pressure, lost 2nd late stages.
Dropped back to last and trailed the field most of the way to straight, widest on straightening, produced good late charge and just missed 3rd.
Held up near the rear as expected, brought wide to challenge, rattled home late to just miss frame.
Bean awkwardly, waited with near the rear, saved ground on the fence, 4Ls to make up 400M, worked home solidly.
Settled just off leader early stages, 3-wide no cover from 700M, moved up to challenge 350M, gave out near 100M and swamped.
Slow to begin, held up towards the rear along the inside, shifted outwards 500M for clear running, responded well initially but flattened final 150M.
Soon led and crossed to the fence 1300M, set steady pace, caught by rivals inside 250M, weakened towards the line.

Slow out, ended up towards the rear, raced keenly and allowed to stride forward but no cover from 900M, held ground early straight then weakened 200M. (Jockey: not able to finish off due to circumstances in the race.)
Held up towards the rear, driven wide 550M, lacked the dash, kept on without threat.
Settled down behind mid-division 5-6Ls from leaders, responded only fairly on straightening, raced tight over final 200M but not going the pace to challenge.
Moved up to track leaders early stages, shuffled back to midfield halfway, couldn't go on with it inside 300M, awkwardly placed 200M losing some momentum but made little difference to the results.
Jumped well, sent forward to take the lead, enjoyed the easy lead throughout, kicked clear after turning in, scored easily.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide at rear, 7 lengths back, slightly improved on turn, taken wide in straight and finished off very strongly to take 2nd.
Good clean jump, raced wide behind midfield, improved from near 750M, very wide turning in, made good progress early in straight, peaked near 200M, stayed on evenly thereafter.
Began only fairly from gate 11, unable to slot in, travelled wide with no cover in 4th, similar position on turn, finished off evenly to make frame without threatening.
Slowly away, positioned behind midfield, 5 to 6 lengths back, saved ground on turn, no daylight early in straight, made some progress when clear thereafter, never a threat to the first few.

Average to begin, positioned on rail in midfield, 3 to 4 lengths back, travelled keenly in the early stages, same margin back on turn, no clear running early in straight, finished off evenly thereafter.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide in 2nd, travelled keenly in early and middle stages, same position on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Bumped start, positioned 2 wide, 3 lengths or so back, there to turn, made minor progress early in straight, peaked near 250M, weakened thereafter.
Bumped on jumping, difficult to settle early, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, 4 lengths back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Began awkwardly and bumped, raced at tail, 10 lengths or so back, well back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Away with them, raced 7 to 8 lengths back at rear, still well back on turn, emptied early in straight, eased near 300M, finished tailed out.
Jumped well from gate 1, positioned 2 lengths or so back on rail, peaked on turn, emptied early in straight and eased thereafter, finished tailed out, unacceptable performance. (Roarer)
Pressed forward early and handily placed behind the early leader, on the fence. Clear run in the straight and nabbed the lead 300m. Pulled clear and had plenty in hand. Only hands and heels last 50m.

Cruised forward early to sit forward of midfield, on the fence. Bumped and unbalanced on the turn. Stayed on strongly in the straight. Only hands and heels in the last 50m, and nabbed for a share of 2nd on the line.
Slow into stride and settled midfield. Awkward on heels at 700m. Started to run on from 300m. Big turn of foot in last 150m to share 2nd on the line.
Lifted front feet on jumping and away tardily. Recovered and pushed forward to sit midfield. Across heels 300m for a clear run. Stayed on solidly, but slightly 1 paced.
Bumped on jumping and eased back to sit at the rear of the field. Steadied off heels 1000m and awkwardly placed at 700m. Widest on the turn and stayed on solidly. Only hands and heels last 100m.
Pressed forward, eventually having outright lead at 1000m. Still in front at 300m, but had nothing left in the tank and drifted back.
Dropped back early to sit last. Improved to a handy position at 300m, but 1 paced in the straight.
Cruised forward early, eventually settling around midfield. Wider on the turn. Plugged away to the line in the straight.
Eased back early to sit at the tail of the field. Inconvenienced on the turn, and plugged to the line under minimal urging in the straight.
Hampered on jumping and eased back to sit towards the rear of the field. Checked and lost momentum on the turn. Plugged away in the straight under minimal urging and still went past some slower ones.
Bumped and badly unbalanced on jumping, before pushing forward to lead. Didn't respond to riding in the straight.
Pushed forward early to share the lead, before dropping back to the 2nd group at 1200m. Hampered on the turn and not persevered with in the straight.

Bumped and badly unbalanced on jumping. Recovered to push forward and be handily placed, but 3 wide no cover. Steadied off heels 1200m. Bumped and unbalanced at the top of the straight. Didn't run on in straight.

Hampered at start, settled just over 2L back in 5th 3-wide down far side, commenced move 4-wide entering straight, quickened up well to snatch victory near the line.
Began well, taken 2L back to stalk the leaders in 4th, came wide to challenge entering straight holding every chance, only to be outsprinted by the winner close to home.
Always thereabouts, hit the front briefly on straightening, unable to sustain effort and headed inside the final 100 metres.
Held up just off the pace on the rail, saved ground turning in, kept on steadily without quickening under pressure.
Settled within 3L of pace on the rail in 6th, swung off the rail in similar position turning for home, ran on under pressure but did not find much and checked over 50 metres out.
Began well from a wide gate, settled wide in midfield, switched wider into the straight, kept on same pace without quickening.
Jumped awkwardly losing ground, settled in last few on the rail, produced very good late impression in the run to the line.

Taken back towards the rear from a wide gate, gained closer order past impeded runners rounding home bend, widest runner on straightening, kept on steadily without quickening down the centre of the track.
Made running to the 300 metres, weakened under pressure.
Slightly crowded at the start, settled just worse than midfield, hampered and lost position at the 500 metres, one-paced in the straight.
Always well behind and never seen with a chance.
Slowly away, soon picked up to rear of midfield, badly hampered on the rail at the 500 metres, never recovered.
Settled well in front of midfield, benefited by the slow tempo, closed off strongly 300M to score.
Very slow away, at rear but along the fence, harmed by the slow pace, unleashed strong finishing efforts 250M.
Eased back, sat 2 wide, made early move 900M to take advantages of the slow tempo, ran on well for 3rd.
Hard ridden early but not muster, midfield 2-3 wide, harmed by the slow pace, dashed well 250M.
Pressed forward, sat 2 wide, on heel 600M and lost ground, lack room 400M, dashed well 250M despite not suited by the slow pace.
Pushed to take rail and led at advantageous slow sectionals, hung on until 200M weakened.
Eased to rear, 2-4 wide, harmed by the slow pace, little dash 200M.
Eased back, 2-3 wide, not suited by the slow tempo, lack room 300M, little dash when clear.
Pushed early, hold the rail behind midfield, harmed by the slow pace, just held ground in straight.
Pushed to obtain box seat, no progress in straight.
Pushed early, midfield, 2-3 wide, never travelled comfortably, emptied 400M.
At rear, not suited by the slow pace, no dash.
Urged along to race behind leaders, commenced to improve on straightening, gradually made ground in the straight to score.
Ridden along to settle outside the lead, asked for effort passing 500M, travelled strongly in the straight, just missed by nose.
Travelled midfield, wide on straightening, made ground passing 100M, worked home solidly.
Taken back at start, commenced to make ground in the straight, finished nicely.
Settled at box seat, fought hard entire straight, finished well.
Taken back at start, raced midfield on rail, awkwardly placed for some distance approaching 100M then was steadied when disappointed for running, finished OK.
Taken back at start, settled behind midfield on rail, made some ground in the straight, ride's whip entangled in reins near 150M then dropped his right rein for the remainder of race.
Raced behind midfield, one-paced in the straight.
Travelled keenly and proved difficult to settle in early and middle stages, passing 900M raced wide and without cover, passing 100M was steadied, after that one-paced to the line.
Travelled keenly in the lead, emptied passing final 100M.
Raced wide behind midfield, widest on straightening, failed to run on.
Began awkwardly, checked away from heels approaching 1300M, never in it.
Jumped with them, raced at tail, 5 to 6 lengths back, saved ground on turn, finished off very strongly in straight to score.
Began well from a tricky gate, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well throughout, kept on very well in straight but couldn't hold off the winner late.
Away with them, positioned on rail in midfield, easy run on turn, taken wide early in straight and made some progress to take 3rd.
Bumped on jumping, sent forward to race prominently, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, just stayed on for 4th.
Bumped start, positioned 2 wide, 1 to 2 lengths back, there to turn, improved from near 400M, made some progress early in straight, peaked near 100M, weakened thereafter.
Average to begin, raced at rear, 5 lengths back, same margin back on turn, made reasonable progress in straight.
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned 4 lengths back on rail, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after straightening, found no daylight, not able to test properly.
Began awkwardly, raced 2 wide behind midfield early, shifted out off heels near 700m, improved from 450M, very wide turning in, showed no progress in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, 5 lengths back, same position on turn, taken widest in straight, finished off one-paced.
Moderately away from the widest draw, unable to slot in, raced very wide and without cover early, slightly improved near 700M to sit 2 wide in 2nd, peaked on turn, weakened gradually in straight.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide in midfield, kept on hanging in after 900M, couldn't maintain position from 800M, 4 lengths back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Out in line, unable to slot in, travelled wide and without cover throughout, emptied early in straight when hard run took effect.
Jumped well, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, easy run on turn, finished off very well to score.
Crowded on jumping, positioned 4 lengths back on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after straightening and made good progress to take 2nd.
Crowded out start, positioned 5 lengths or so back on rail, improved from 450M, finished off strongly in straight to get 3rd.
Fast into stride, took the lead easily, travelled well throughout, headed near 200M, just stayed on for 4th.
Crowded on jumping, raced at tail, 8 lengths back, moved closer in the middle stages, but still 5 lengths back on turn, made some progress in straight.

Jumped well from the widest draw, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, half length behind the leader, there to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter. (Lame right front leg next day morning.)
Away with them, raced 2 wide, 4 to 5 lengths back, there to turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Fast to begin, positioned 2 wide, 2 to 3 lengths back, similar position to near 400M, slightly improved thereafter, one-paced in straight.
Taken back from gate 9, raced 2 wide at rear, 6 lengths back, still well back on turn, made no progress in straight.
Average to begin, positioned 2 wide, 1 to 2 lengths back, same position on turn, emptied early in straight, finished last.
In midfield, sat 3-3/4L behind along the rail, caught leader inside final 50M, held runner-up by 1/2L.
Pushed and settled in one-off one-back position, sat 2L off the lead, kept on well, only beaten in the concluding stages.
Slow to jump, in behind midfield, 5-1/4L off along the rail, continued to improve, closed off very well to take 3rd.
Raced at the rear, 7L behind along the rail, continued to make nice ground, steadied just prior going to the line.
Sent forward to take the rail and led by 3/4L, headed approaching 150M but maintained to the finish.
Kept niggling, sat 3/4L off and outside the lead, remained one paced to the line.
Niggled along and settled in midfield, 3-3/4L behind 2 wide, kept on fairly to the line.
Raced in worse than midfield, 5-1/4L behind 2 wide, remained one paced to the line.
Settled to race in behind midfield, 4-3/4L behind 3 wide without cover, remained one paced.
Pushed forward to obtain box-seat, sat 2L off the lead, raced keenly throughout, couldn't keep up after 150M.
Crowded start, travelled near the rear, 6-1/2L behind 2 wide, ran on but did not threaten.
Taken back and remained at the rear, never a factor.
Average to begin, positioned 4 lengths or so back rail, saved ground on turn, finished off very strongly in straight to score narrowly.
Jumped well from gate 1, positioned 3 lengths or so back on rail, easy run throughout, finished off very well to take 2nd, just missed by a narrow margin.
Bumped start, raced in 2nd, easy run throughout, kept on well after turning in, hit front near 200M, but couldn't hold off the first two late.
Away with them, raced 4 lengths back behind midfield, there to turn, made very good progress in straight to make frame.
Clean jump, raced 2 wide, 3 lengths back, there to turn, kept on evenly in straight.
Bumped at start, positioned 3 wide with cover behind midfield, same position on turn, bumped and unbalanced near 150M, finished off evenly.
Crowded on jumping, raced wide with cover at rear, 5 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, made minor progress in straight. (Lost right front plate.)
Jumped well from the widest gate, taken back to race 3 wide at rear, no cover on turn, finished off one-paced.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide, 5 lengths back, found rail on turn, made no progress in straight. (Blood in trachea.)
Bumped start, allowed an uncontested lead, travelled keenly in the middle stages, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter, bumped final 150M.
Crowded start, raced at tail throughout, never a threat.
Slowly away from a wide draw, unable to slot in, travelled 3 wide with no cover throughout, emptied early in straight when hard run took effect.
Settled well in mid-division, barged his way through 100M to challenge, edged ahead close home.
Reserved behind midfield, into clear passing 300M, made gradual progress, unbalanced 100M when brushed by rival, just missed out in a close finish.
Settled down 3-wide behind midfield, brought wide into straight, ran on well to the line only narrowly denied by first 2.
Dropped back near the rear racing along the 3-path, closed off well down the outside, went 4th just before line.
Positively ridden, chased leader 2-wide on settling, kept finding the line well, led the field to 100M, outgunned late.
Crowded for room after the start, travelled keenly towards the rear, 4Ls to make up 400M, stayed on moderately, bumped by rival 100M and awkwardly placed near the finish.
Always in touch, had every chance turning in, faded final 100M.
Emerged as leader passing 900M, led at steady pace, responded well under pressure on straightening and only gave way late stages.
Began awkwardly, chased leaders 3-wide, still in contention when severely checked 100M, eased down.
From wide draw shifted across behind runners after the start, given waiting ride at the rear, commenced his run along inside but awkwardly placed behind rivals forcing rider to stop riding.
Taken back from wide draw, towards the rear 5Ls back, was closing off the race when severely checked 150M and lost his chance.
Up with the pace, tracked leaders home turn, commenced to weaken from 200M. (Jockey: couldn't offer explanation for poor performance.)

Broke well, settled not far off the pace on the rail, ran on to hit the front 100 metres out, just held on to the line.

Jumped awkwardly losing ground, gradually recovered along the rail to rear of midfield, tight behind runners on the bend and baulked for a run in straight until the 200 metres, finished off race well.
Ridden for midfield position early, raced keenly around the bend, ran on well in straight to be nearest at finish.
Moderate start, settled in rear of midfield, switched for a clear run when straightening, ran on steadily without threatening.
Soon dropped to the tail-end, saved ground on the rail turning for home, ran on well under pressure inside the final 200 metres.

Raced wide throughout, prominent early and gradually drifting backward to midfield, dropped further back on the bend, inconvenienced on straightening, finished off race well down the centre of the track.
Never far off, unable to quicken under pressure in the run home.
Driven to lead setting a steady pace, held a 2L break upon straightening, unable to sustain effort and folded up quickly inside the final 200 metres. (Blood in trachea)
Began awkwardly from a wide gate but soon ridden forward to chase the leader, kept on under pressure after straightening before fading inside the 200 metres.
Travelled wide in last few throughout, widest runner turning for home, never seen with a chance.
Jumped fairly, travelled slightly worse than midfield far side, dropped further back rounding home bend, hampered after straightening, made no further impression.
Began fairly from a wide gate, remained wide just worse than midfield, made short-lived effort around the bend, folded up quickly after straightening. (Bled)
Eased to sit in midfield along the fence, not suited by the slow pace, blocked 4-2, dashed strongly when clear and score.
Slow away, at rear, 2-3 wide, harmed by the slow pace, unleashed strong finishing efforts 300M for 2nd.
Eased to sit in midfield, sat 3 wide, ran on well for 3rd.
At back, 2 wide, lack room 400M, dashed well when clear despite not suited by the slow pace.
Hard ridden forward to share the lead in 2 wide, clocked advantageous slow sectionals, out of fuel 250M.
Hard ridden to take rail and shared the lead at slow sectionals, emptied 250M.
Eased to sit in midfield, 2 wide, blocked most straight, not tested.
Very slow away, at rear, 2 wide, harmed by the slow tempo, little dash 200M.
Hard ridden to occupy box seat, not suited by the slow tempo, blocked whole straight, not tested.
Eased back, 3 wide, not suited by the slow pace, no progress.
At rear, harmed by the slow pace never improved.

Placing: DISQ
Comment: Eased back early, trapped 3 wide, moved forward 800M to take advantages of the slow pace, ran on until 150M weakened.
Took lead without asking for effort, improved straightening, quickened passing 300M, finished unchallenged.
Raced at back, commenced to improve at Home Turn, widest on straightening, near 250M rider momentarily dropped his left rein, lost left front plate approaching 200M, made up some nice late ground.
Travelled behind the leader, fought hard entire straight, finished OK.
Settled at box seat, one-paced in the straight.
Settled behind midfield, travelled keenly in the early and middle stages, worked home one-paced.
Settled midfield, gradually gave ground in the straight.
Slow to begin, raced at rear, never in it.
Crowded on jumping, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, finished off very strongly to score by a head.
Taken back from gate 13, raced at tail, 10 lengths back, still well back on turn, taken widest in straight and finished off very strongly to be nearest on line, just narrowly beaten.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide in midfield, travelled well throughout, showed good progress early in straight, took the lead near 250M, kept on well but couldn't hold off the rivals late.
Jumped well from a tricky gate, sent forward to sit a length behind the leader in 3rd, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after straightening and finished off evenly to make frame.
Began awkwardly and crowded, raced 9 lengths back at rear, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after straightening and made reasonable progress.

Average to begin, raced 2 wide at rear early, awkwardly placed near 1000M, carried wider with no cover thereafter, taken wide and made contact near 250M, then bumped near 150M, made good progress thereafter to be nearest on line.
Bumped start and unbalanced, positioned on rail at rear, saved ground on turn, no clear running early in straight, made some progress when clear thereafter.
Began well from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, easy run on turn, brushed near 300M, finished off one-paced.
Jumped well from the widest gate, sent forward to race prominently, 2nd on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Quickly into stride, sent forward to take lead, easy lead on turn, peaked and headed near 250M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Crowded on jumping, raced 2 wide, 6 to 7 lengths back, similar position on turn, taken wide in straight, made contact and unbalanced near 250M, then bumped near 150M, ran on one-paced thereafter.
Slightly slow out, positioned on rail in midfield, difficult to settle after passing the 1100M, saved ground to near 500M, failed to close off in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 8 to 9 lengths back at rear, still well back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Jumped well from a wide draw, unable to slot in, raced 3 wide in 4th early, 2 wide on turn, weakened early in straight, brushed near 300M, eased final 50M, finished last.
Began well, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 lengths or so back, same position on turn, finished off very well to score easily.

Average to begin, raced at rear, 6Ls back, travelled keenly and awkwardly placed near 1000M, still 4 to 5Ls back on turn, taken wide in straight and finished off strongly to take 2nd without posing threat to the winner.
Slightly slow out from the wide draw, raced 2 wide behind midfield, there to turn, made good progress in straight to get 3rd without threatening the winner.
Out with rest, positioned on rail in midfield, easy run on turn, found no daylight early in straight, made some headway when clear thereafter to make frame without threatening the first few.
Jumped with them, positioned 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, easy run on turn, kept to inside in straight and got traffic, made some headway when clear final 150M.
Began fairly, unable to slot in early, sent forward near 1400M to race in 2nd, there to turn, niggled early in the straight, but found little.
Jumped well from gate 9, showed early speed to take the lead, travelled well throughout, headed near 250M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Slightly slow out, no early speed, raced at tail early, slightly improved along the rail in the middle stages, failed to close off in straight.
Average to begin, raced wide at rear, 6 to 7 lengths back, last turning in, failed to close off in straight.
Away with them, raced 2 wide, 2 lengths back, travelled well to turn, showed no response after turning in, eased in the final stages. (See Racing Incidents.)
Eased then raced in worse than midfield, 5-3/4L behind 3 wide with cover, fought on strongly to the line to score by 1/2L.
Rolled forward and settled into box-seat near 700M, sat about 2L off, obtained lead after 200M, kept on well but couldn't hold off the winner, missed out by 1/2L.
Niggled along, settled in front of midfield, 2-3/4L off 2 wide, kept on fairly, just held onto 3rd.
In midfield, sat 4-1/2L behind 2 wide, slightly crowded at 400M, made nice ground and ran on well to the line.
Settled to race in midfield, 4L behind the lead 3 wide without cover, ran on well to the line.
Travelled towards the rear, 6-3/4L behind along the rail, kept on and made minor inroad late.
Rolled into a midfield position, sat 4L behind along the rail, held up prior to 300M, ran on well until steadied near 100M.
Crowded start and lost ground, at the rear 8L behind 2 wide, showed dashes and ran home well inside final 100M.
Eased then travelled in worse than midfield, 5-1/2L behind along the rail, one paced and weakened gradually.
Sent forward, settled to race outside the lead, sat about a neck off, weakened passing 300M.
Ridden forward, settled one-off one-back, sat about 1L off, dropped off near 250M.
Niggled along, took rail and lead with ease, maintained till 250M, failed to response thereafter.
Taken out at start, settled at the rear, eased at 150M when well beaten.
Taken back, gave ground rounding Home Turn, not a factor.

Moderately away, raced 2 wide in midfield, got its head up when awkwardly placed on heels near 1000M, raced tight and unbalanced near 600M, no daylight early in straight, finished off very strongly thereafter and scored.

Jumped with them, unable to slot in, raced 3 wide with no cover early, improved from 1200M to sit in 2nd, 2 wide, a length behind the leader, kept on very well in straight, just couldn't hold off the winner late.
Slowly away and inconvenienced, raced 3 wide in midfield, no cover on turn, closed off well to take 3rd. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back from gate 8, raced 5 lengths back at rear, improved from 600M, taken wide turning in, made good progress in straight to make frame without threatening.
Jumped well, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, there to turn, finished off evenly.
Bumped start, raced tight near 1300M, positioned 3 to 4 lengths back on rail, saved ground on turn, no clear running until near final 200M, made minor progress thereafter.
Taken back from gate 9, raced wide with cover at rear, 4 lengths back, travelled keenly early, improved on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter. (Bled.)
Slowly away, raced at tail to turn, very wide turning in, passed the emptied horses in straight.
Fast into stride, took the lead easily, enjoyed the easy lead on turn, kept on well early in straight, headed near 200M, dropped off tamely thereafter.
Average to begin, positioned 2 lengths back on rail, easy run on turn, showed no response early in straight, weakened thereafter, finished last. (Bled.)
Held up behind midfield in 9th spot, got split 300M, closed powerfully and wrapped it final 50M.
Chased leaders, under a good hold coming into straight, driven out 300M, stuck to task well just couldn't hold off winner final 100M.
Settled down in 6th place ahead of midfield, taken wide passing 500M, responded well and looked a possible winner at 250M, kept going to the line just held by first two.
Away well then restrained to sit in midfield, swung widest 500M, chased well early straight but effort levelled off in the final 150M.
Began only fairly, reserved near the rear in 11th, took some time to wind up in straight, produced some good late impression to go 5th near the line.
Behind midfield in 10th spot, had to bustle along 600M out, stayed on without threatening the leaders.
Went forward from draw 14 to be tracking leader, briefly led early straight, faded passing 200M.
Jumped on terms, moved up to chase leaders along the rail, stayed in touch till final 150M, no extra.

Didn't muster speed despite ridden along early, ended up 2nd last on settling, shifted out under pressure on straightening, responded only fairly when ridden final stages. (Jockey questioned re his riding in straight.)
Taken back from wide draw to be last along the rail over 10Ls off the pace on settling, ran past a few weakening rivals only.
Guided to the rail and travelled in midfield 6Ls off the pace middle stages, failed to quicken on straightening, kept on same pace to the finish.
Never far off from leaders, came under pressure 600M, couldn't go on passing 250M, weakened.
Restrained from wide gate, settled down near the rear along the fence, struggled behind them passing 500M, never a threat.
Rushed forward from draw 13, led them along at sound pace, was tackled at the 400M, soon weakened away.
Good clean jump, raced 2 wide in midfield early, severely checked near 900M, soon recovered, improved on turn, took the lead early in straight, kept on strongly to the line and scored easily.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide in midfield, similar positon on turn, finished off well to take 2nd without posing any threat to the winner.
Began only fairly, failed to muster speed, positioned on rail behind midfield, steadied near 950M, saved ground on turn, made reasonable headway in straight to get 3rd.
Average to begin, raced 4 lengths back at rear, 4 lengths or so back, same position on turn, made some progress in straight to make frame without threatening the first few.
Jumped well from the widest draw, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well throughout, peaked and headed early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground throughout, finished off evenly in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced wide at rear, 5 lengths or so back, there to turn, finished off one-paced.
Slowly away, failed to muster despite ridden and soon detached from the main group, 8 lengths or so back on turn, ran on past beaten horses in straight.
Taken back from a tricky gate, raced wide at rear, 4 lengths back, 3 wide on turn, failed to close off in straight. (Bled.)
Away with them, sent forward to race in 2nd, raced ungenerously and hung out in the middle stages, eased after turning in. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began well, raced prominently, hampered and carried wider near 900M, no cover throughout, emptied early in straight when hard run took toll, finished tailed out.
Taken forward to be well placed 3rd as the two leaders got away at 900m. Cruised up to take the lead at 200m, and pulled away under hands and heels. Easing late.
Began awkwardly and scrubbed up in the back straight to eventually lead passing 900m. Passed in front at 200m, but stayed on solidly to hold 2nd, despite fading late.
Eased back early to settle just behind midfield. Widest on the turn, and solid early in the straight. Showed great turn of foot from 150m, and strong to the line to grab 3rd late.
Began well, before easing back to settle midfield. Stayed on solidly in the straight, but just rolled for 3rd in the shadows of the post.
Bumped on jumping, but recovered well enough to push forward and be the early leader. Under pressure from the 200m, and was swamped for a place late.
Slow to begin and dropped back to last. Steadied out of run 500m. Quietly ridden early in the straight before coming off heels at 150m. Stayed on strongly under the stick late. Jockey questioned.
Started to press forward early, but steadied to find cover at 1200m. Trapped 4 wide no cover and raced keenly. Bumped900m, and finally got cover 800m. Stayed on solidly late, but no threat.
Cruised forward to settle midfield, on the rail. Staid on fairly in the straight, but was no threat.
Taken up to settle 4th, on the fence, but a long way off the leader. 1 paced in the straight under hands and heels.
Settled just behind midfield. 1 paced in the straight.
Eased forward from the inside draw to sit 3rd last. Plugged away to the line under minimal urging in the straight.
Dropped back from the wide draw to settle behind midfield. Promised nothing turning for home and delivered it in the straight
Taken up early to settle forward of midfield, 1 off the fence. Gave nothing in the straight and dropped out very quickly.
Slow to begin, dropped to the rear and never improved.
