Settled in midfield, baulked for a run approaching home turn, quickened well once into the clear inside the 200 metres, just got up.
Broke well, held up for distant 5th, took closer order climbing up the Rock to reach 4th 2L back onto home bend, quickened to hit the front 150 metres out, pipped at post. (Bled)
Taken back from a wide gate travelling in last few, commenced move at the 450 metres, ran on steadily without troubling first two.

Jumped awkwardly, quickly driven forward to a prominent position passing the winning post the first time, upside of leader leaving the Rock when pace slackened, hit the front briefly after straightening, headed under pressure 150M out.

Moderate start from a middle draw, quickly obtained rails run at the tail-end, circled the field at the 600 metres and the widest runner towards the rear entering home straight, ran on to be nearest at finish.
Ridden along in midfield racing wide without cover most of way, came under pressure to challenge entering home straight but unable to quicken to threaten.
Moderate start from the widest gate settling well back, hampered passing the 600 metres, made up good ground down the centre of the straight.
Jumped well, settled in midfield in 6th on the rail, carried backward passing the Rock, baulked for a run early in straight, kept on at the one pace inside the final 200 metres.

Began awkwardly, settled just worse than midfield on the rail, checked and lost position passing the Rock, came under pressure entering the straight but could only keep on at the one pace without quickening.

Worked his way forward for a close-up position on the rail, chased behind pacesetter early in back straight, became 1.5L 3rd when pace slackened going up the Rock, folded up quickly under pressure inside the final 200 metres.
Jumped well settling off the pace mainly in 4th, lost position passing the Rock, saved ground on the rail turning in, soon weakened.
Began from a wide draw, took up running 1200 metres out producing a fast early section, steadied pace from approaching the Rock, headed into home straight and folded up quickly.
Behind midfield on the rails, harmed by the slow pace but saved significant amount of ground round the home turn, dashed well 250M to score.
Eased to sit in midfield along the fence, not suited by the slow pace, dashed well 300M.
At back, 2-3 wide, made early move from 700M, closed off well for 3rd.
Hard ridden early but not muster, midfield 2 wide, improved 800M to take advantages of the slow pace, ran on well in the lead until 100M out of fuel.
Hard ridden to occupy box seat, benefited by the slow tempo, just held ground in straight.
Pushed to take rail and led at advantageous slow sectionals, hung on until 200M weakened.
Pressed forward, sat 2 wide, lost ground 700M, on heel 400M, dashed strongly 200M despite not suited by the slow pace.
Pushed early, midfield trapped 3 wide, moved forward steadily, emptied 250M.
At back, 2-3 wide, harmed by the slow tempo, lack turn of foot in straight.
Eased back, took rail, harmed by the slow pace, attempted to improve around the field 3-5 wide, no dash.
Eased back, trapped 3 wide throughout, never a factor.
Trapped 3-4 wide throughout at back, tailed out.
Raced in the lead, asked for effort passing 400M, in the straight held strongly to score.
Settled outside the lead, commenced to improve near 450M, finished strongly, missed by Nose.
Travelled behind leaders, gradually made ground passing 200M, missed by SH.
Box seat, niggled in middle stages, responded well in the straight, missed by HD.
Raced at tail on rail, made ground passing 150M, finished nicely.
Settled midfield on rail, fought hard entire straight, finished well.
At start was hampered then taken back, widest on straightening, one-paced.
Taken back at start, limited response when asked for effort.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide, 2 lengths back, steadied off heels near 1000m, travelled well thereafter, finished off well to score by a neck.

Clean break, positioned 3 to 4 lengths back on rail, steadied off heels near 1000m, awkwardly placed near 800M, saved ground on turn, caught in traffic early in straight, finished off very strongly when clear thereafter to get 2nd.
Bumped on jumping, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 4 lengths or so back on turn, finished off very strongly in straight to take 3rd.
Bumped start, sent forward to take the lead, enjoyed the easy lead in the middle stages, kept on well after turning in, headed near final 50M, slightly weakened thereafter.
Hampered at start, raced at rear, 6 to 7 lengths back, there to turn, finished off very strongly to be nearest on line. (See Racing Incidents.)
Out in line, raced 2 wide in midfield, similar position on turn, made some headway in straight without threatening.
Bumped start, positioned 5 lengths back on rail, saved ground on turn, angled out from near 400M, made minor progress in straight.
Bumped start, recovered to sit a length behind the leader on rail, easy run on turn, awkwardly placed early in straight, peaked thereafter, weakened in the closing stages.
Quickly into stride, positioned 2 lengths back on rail, awkwardly placed near 800M, saved ground on turn, angled out early in straight, kept on one-paced, brushed near final 100M.
Jumped well from a tricky draw, sent forward to race 2 wide in 2nd, peaked on turn, weakened gradually in straight.
Bumped start, raced at rear, 7 to 8 lengths back, still well back on turn, emptied early in straight.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail throughout, never competitive.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, 8 lengths back, still well back on turn, angled out in straight and finished off very strongly to score narrowly.
Slowly away, raced behind midfield, saved ground on turn, no clear running until after 100M, finished off very strongly thereafter, just beaten on line.
Jumped well from gate 1, raced prominently, checked and lost ground near 600M, kept on well after turning in, just could not hold off the first two late.
Away with them, positioned 2 wide in 3rd, carried wider on turn, fought on steadily in straight. (Jockey dropped his whip at 200M.)
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide, 5 lengths back, awkwardly placed near 850M, taken wide after turning in, finished off strongly to be nearest on line.
Average to begin, raced at rear, 4 to 5 lengths back on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Began only fairly, sent forward to take the lead, peaked after turning in, headed near 150M, badly hampered close home.
Began fairly, positioned on rail in midfield, moved closer on turn, bumped and checked after turning in, made no progress thereafter, hampered close home.
Jumped with them, bumped early, trapped wide with no cover in midfield, there to turn, failed to close off in straight.
Out in line, bumped and unbalanced early, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, there to turn, made no progress in straight, dropped off tamely from final 150M.
Out in line, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, 2 wide on turn, emptied early in straight, finished last.
Sent forward to lead from barrier 1, led by 1-1/2L, kept on going, never looked likely to be caught.
Niggled along, sat in front of midfield, 3-3/4L off the lead 2 wide, fought on gamely but could not catch the winner.
Ridden forward and obtained box-seat, sat 2L off the lead, kept on going, just hung onto 3rd.
Didn't jump well, settled in worse than midfield, 7-3/4L behind 2 wide, made ground steadily and finished off okay whilst laying in. (Rider questioned)
Travelled just behind midfield, 7-1/4L behind along the rail, ran on fairly to the line.
Rolled into a position in midfield, 6-1/4L behind 2 wide, one paced in the straight.
Settled to race just in front of midfield, 4-1/2L behind along the rail, kept on one paced to the line.
Eased then raced towards the rear, 9-1/4L behind 2 wide, saved minor ground in the straight.
Eased then taken to the rail and raced at the rear, hardly made any improvement.
Sent forward, sat outside the lead, weakened badly passing 300M. (Rider and trainer questioned)
Taken back, raced at the rear throughout, never a factor.
Awkward start, raced near the tail, found nothing and eased down passing 200M.
Began well from a middle draw, sent forward to race prominently, took the lead near 800M, travelled well throughout, kept on very well in straight to score.
Average to begin, positioned 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, easy run on turn, kept to inside early in straight, angled out near 150M, closed off well to take 2nd.
Jumped well, positioned one-out-one-back, there to turn, kept on well in straight to take 3rd.
Taken back from a tricky gate, raced at tail, 5 lengths or so back, still well back on turn, showed good turn of foot early in straight, blocked near 150M, closed off well thereafter.
Moderately away, positioned 2 wide in midfield, similar position on turn, caught in traffic after turning in, made minor progress when clear thereafter. (Had blood at mouth before the race.)
Average to begin, raced 2 wide, 4 lengths back at rear, same margin back on turn, no clear running early in straight, finished off strongly when clear final 150M, nearest on line.
Jumped with them, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, there to turn, made minor progress in straight.
Jumped well from gate 1, showed early speed to take the early lead, travelled well on turn, kept on well until near final 100M, weakened thereafter.
Away with them, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, same position turning, failed to close off in straight.
Out in line, taken back to race at rear, 4 to 5 lengths back, slightly improved from near 400M, showed no progress in straight.
Moderately away from the widest draw, unable to slot in, travelled wide and without cover in 3rd, weakened gradually after turning in when hard run took effect.
Began only fairly, then crowded, raced 4 lengths back on rail, saved ground on turn, showed no response in straight, never a threat.
Slotted into a 2-wide position in midfield, moved strongly into contention 300M, took lead inside 150M, kicked away for dominant win.
Taken back after the start, settled down 7Ls towards the rear, bustled along 600M out, made sweeping run on the outside to go 2nd late stages. Not reached winner.
From draw 12 taken across behind runners at the start, towards the rear 6Ls off the pace in middle stages, driven out for solid finish to go 3rd near line. Sound debut at the Valley.
Sent forward from draw 1, led steadily before quickening up 700M, headed inside 150M, edged out to 4th final stages.
Never far off from the pace, stayed in touch with leaders leaving the bend, lacked the turn of foot, only battled away.
Settled down behind midfield in 8th place, brought wide into straight, made some ground at the finish without threatening.
Taken back from wide barrier, always towards the rear, widest on straightening, lay in under pressure proving difficult to ride, made limited progress only.
Tracked the leader to 200M, couldn't go on.
Began only fairly, held up midfield along the fence, battled on one paced in the straight without threatening.
Chased leaders, tried hard over final 300M but failed to improve position.
Failed to muster speed, raced as the back marker from 900M, never going the pace to challenge leaving the corner.
Began only fairly, hard ridden forward, caught wide no cover chasing leaders, gave ground 300M.

Bumped at start, held narrow lead early stages, kept on well to win unchallenged.
Jumped awkwardly, settled just off the pace near stands rails, made modest headway under pressure inside the final 200 metres to snatch 2nd late.
Ridden from a low gate to soon join the leaders near stands rails, unable to sustain effort inside the final 200 metres.
Never far off, kept on same pace under pressure without quickening.
Began awkwardly, remained in last few early, improved from the 800 metres to 3L back in 6th coming onto the course proper, kept on without quickening closing stages.
Settled in midfield mostly 4L off the pace, ran home one-paced down the centre of the track.
Niggled along in midfield on stands rails, made no impression in the run to the line.
Jumped awkwardly losing ground, soon recovered to 6L back in 9th, made no impression in closing stages. (Questioned for disappointing performance)
Moderate start, disputed lead to the halfway mark, soon dropped out of contention.
Jumped fairly, soon dropped to last few, made no impression.
Never better than midfield.
Always in last few, never seen with a chance.
Slowly away, trailed the field most of the way.
Just worse than midfield early stages, but soon dropped to last few.
Pushed forward to take rail and lead, clocked fast sectionals, hung on well to win.
Hard ridden early but not muster, eased back, 2-3 wide, suited by the fast tempo, progressed steadily 350M.
Pushed forward, sat 2 wide, harmed by the fast pace, held up 400M, progressed steadily when clear, just missed by a narrow margin.
Midfield, 2 wide, made steady ground 300M, no heels 150M.
Pushed to sit in front of midfield, 2 wide, not suited by the fast tempo, ran on strongly 300M until 100M emptied, on heels 50M.
At back on the fence, favoured by the fast pace, lack room 300M, made steady ground.
Pushed forward, trapped 3 wide early, harmed by the fast sectionals, out of fuel 250M.
Eased to rear, took rail, benefited by the fast tempo, made late ground 200M.
Box seat, not suited by the fast pace, emptied 250M.
Behind midfield along the fence, lack room in straight, ran on fairly.
Tailed out, never competitive.
Urged to take lead, travelled comfortably throughout race, responded well and finished strongly to score.
Raced midfield in rail, travelled keenly in the middle stages, passing the 500M was bumped and became badly unbalanced, in the straight shifted out for clear running, made good ground passing 100M.
Ridden at start, near 1400M travelled keenly, settled behind leaders, battled hard in the straight, finished solidly.
Taken back at start, settle at rear, passing the 500M was inconvenienced, kept on rail to save ground at Home Turn, gradually gained ground in the straight, finished nicely,
Raced at box seat, asked for effort on straightening, fought hard to the line.
Raced midfield, approaching 700M was left racing wide and without cover, near 600M was taken wider, one-paced to the line.
At start sat back and bounded in the air, on jumping stumbled and lost ground, proved difficult to settle, lay in at Home Turn and straight, barrier and racing manners unacceptable, must trial.
Raced outside the lead, under pressure and gradually lost ground in the straight.
Taken back at start, widest on straightening, failed to run on.
Raced behind midfield, no response when asked for effort.
Quickly into stride, Travelled wide and without cover in 3rd, slightly improved after 700M, shared lead on turn, kept on strongly to score by 1-1/4L.
Jumped with them, unable to slot in, raced 4 wide with no cover early, still 3 wide on turn, made steady progress in straight to take 2nd despite being difficult to ride.
Slowly away, raced at rear, 6 to 7 lengths back, still well back on turn, finished off very strongly to be nearest on line.
Taken back to race 3 wide behind midfield, 2 wide turning, taken wide in straight and made very good progress to make frame.
Began well, took the lead easily, travelled well throughout, kept on well after turning in, peaked near final 150M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Began only fairly, showed no early speed, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, there to turn, made some headway in straight without threatening.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced wide with cover at rear, 5 to 6 lengths back, still well back on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, 9 lengths or so back on turn, only passed the emptied horses in straight.
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, finished off one-paced.
Away with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, same position on turn, showed no response in straight, eased late.
Jumped well from a middle draw, raced prominently, peaked after turning in, dropped off tamely final 200m. (Blood in trachea.)
Slightly slow out, recovered to sit 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, peaked on turn, emptied early in straight, finished last.
Moderately away from a tricky draw, sent forward to race prominently, 2nd on turn, kept on very well in straight and scored narrowly. (See Racing Incidents.)
Bumped start and unbalanced, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 lengths or so back, there to turn, took inside after straightening and made very good progress to be nearest on line, just beaten narrowly.

Bumped start and unbalanced, showed no early speed, positioned on rail at rear, 6 to 7 lengths back, last turning in, no clear running early in straight, finished off strongly when clear thereafter to take 3rd.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, 7 lengths back, improved from near 500M, widest in straight, finished off very strongly to make frame.
Slowly away, gradually recovered along the rail, 3 to 4 lengths back on turn, awkwardly placed near 500M, no daylight early in straight, made some headway thereafter without threatening.
Away with them, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, similar position on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced wide and without cover at rear early, found cover on turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Jumped well, failed to muster, raced 2 wide, 5 lengths back, found rail on turn, finished off evenly. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began fairly, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, showed no turn of foot, just finished off one-paced.
Bumped start, recovered quickly and took the lead, travelled well on turn, raced tight near 350M, headed and weakened thereafter.
Began well from a wide draw, sent forward to race in 3rd, 3 wide throughout, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, 5 to 6 lengths back, 2 wide on turn, peaked early in straight, steadied near 250M, emptied thereafter.
Began fairly, raced 3 wide in midfield, there to turn, kept on evenly early in straight, weakened from final 200M.
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned 2 to 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, peaked on turn, emptied early in straight, eased final 150M.
Niggled along, settled one-off one-back, sat 2-1/2L off, kicked away from 300M, never looked likely to be caught.
Raced in just behind midfield, 4-3/4L behind 3 wide with cover, continued to progress but couldn't catch the winner.
Stumbled at start, settled to race in midfield, 3-1/4L behind 3 wide without cover, ran on well to take 3rd.
Travelled towards the rear, 6-1/4L behind 2 wide, made ground steadily and kept on the line.
Hard ridden forward and raced outside the lead, sat 3/4L off, remained one paced to the line.
Stumble at start, then sent forward to take the rail and led by 3/4L, headed prior to 200M, kept on but one paced.
Crowded after start, sat just behind midfield, 5-1/4L behind along the rail, held up from 200M to 100M, ran on late.
Bumped start, hard ridden but couldn't muster, raced at the rear, 6-1/4L behind wide but with cover, made ground.
Pushed and settled just in front of midfield, 3-1/2L behind along the rail, mostly one paced.
Awkward start and lost ground, raced towards the rear, 6-3/4L behind on the rail, did not make ground.
Hard ridden forward and settled to race in the box-seat, sat 2L off, stayed on till 150M.
Steadied then slotted into midfield, 4-1/4L behind 2 wide, eased near 250M. (Blood in trachea and lame right front)
In midfield, 3-3/4L behind but wide and without cover throughout, found nothing.
Slightly slow to begin, raced the rear and finished tailed out. Must trial.
Clean jump, positioned on rail in 3rd, easy run throughout, finished off very well to score.
Began well from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground to 550M, angled out thereafter, finished off strongly to take 2nd, always held by the winner.
Jumped with them, sent forward to take the early lead, headed near 1100M, sat right behind the leader on turn, kept on well in straight to take 3rd without threatening.
Stumbled start, raced 2 wide in midfield, carried wider near 550M, kept on well early in straight, peaked near 300M, just stayed on for 4th.
Away with them, raced 2 wide in 4th, there to turn, unable to find an extra gear in straight and only kept on evenly to the line.
Taken back to race at tail, 7 lengths back on rail, similar position on turn, made some headway in straight without threatening.
Began only fairly, positioned on rail at rear, steadied off heels near 750M, angled out from near 500M, kept on evenly early in straight, no clear run over the final stages and not fully tested.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide at rear, 6 lengths or so back, there to turn, made no progress in straight.
Bumped start, raced at tail, 7 lengths back, last turning in, made no progress in straight, never a threat.
Bumped on jumping, unable to slot in early, sent forward from near 1400M to race prominently, took the lead near 1100M, easy lead on turn, headed early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Settled down 3Ls off the pace in midfield, saved ground on the inside, ran on strongly to take lead 250M, kept on to win comfortably.
Slow to begin from draw 1, held up behind mid-division 6Ls off the pace, swung wide into straight and ran on steadily to take 2nd, unable to reel in the winner.
Reserved in midfield along the 2-path, held up for clear running in early straight, ran on moderately over final 300M, couldn't reach winner.
Steadied on jumping to obtain cover, towards the rear 6-7Ls off the pace, stayed on mildly, failed to look a winning chance.
Dropped back from widest draw, settled down last along the fence, kept to inside turning in, ran on without threat to winner, narrowly missed out on a placing.
Held up behind midfield, angled out to challenge 400M, effort levelled off 150M.
Towards the rear first half of the race, made home turn awkwardly, widest on straightening, kept on fairly to the line.
Eased back to the rear, 6Ls to make up 400M, made some progress to the line but never threatened.
Emerged as leader passing 1100M, increased tempo from 800M, headed 250M, weakened to the line.
Chased leader, struggled to keep up 550M, weakened away on straightening.
Failed to muster speed despite ridden, caught wide no cover in 4th/5th place, run ended 250M, dropped out.
Up with early pace, tracked leader along rail from 950M, failed to run on entering straight, outsprinted by rivals 300M,
Bumped start, sent forward to race prominently, took the lead near 800M, travelled well on turn, kept on well in straight to score easily.
Jumped well, sent forward to race prominently, steadied near 800M, kept on well after turning in but unable to match pace of winner inside the final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Average to begin, positioned 2 wide in midfield, raced tight near 800M, 3 wide with cover on turn, made some headway in straight to take 3rd.
Began only fairly and inconvenienced, recovered to race prominently, sat right behind the leader on turn, kept on evenly to the line. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began well, positioned in midfield, raced tight near 800M, 2 wide on turn, angle out in straight and finished off evenly.
Average to begin, showed no early speed, positioned 3 lengths or so back on rail, saved ground on turn, finished off evenly.
Out in line, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, 3 to 4 lengths back, wider on turn, finished off evenly.
Crowded on jumping, raced at rear, 4 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, finished off one-paced.
Moderately away from a middle draw, raced prominently, travelled wide and without cover throughout, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Jumped well from the widest draw, unable to slot in early, taken back to race at rear, very wide on the first turn, last turning in, failed to make any progress in straight.
Bumped start, raced very wide with no cover at rear throughout, never seen with a chance.
Clean jump, raced very wide with no cover at rear, slightly improved after 600M, soon peaked, weakened gradually after turning in, finished last.

Eased out early to settle worse than midfield, on the fence. Came wider across heels for a run 300m, but only looked to be running fairly. Showed good turn of foot in last 200m and ran to the line strongly.
Taken forward early to settle 4th, but still 4L off the leaders. Nosed in front at 200m, but was peaking late and just held onto 2nd.
Eased away early to sit just forward of midfield. Stayed on solidly in the straight but slightly 1 paced late.
Dropped back from the wide draw to sit 2nd last. Stayed on strongly in the straight. Came of heels at 150m and made up ground late.

Dropped back early and eventually settled last in a very strung out field. Still 3L behind the 2nd last horse on the turn. Came widest in the straight and made plenty of ground, but ultimately had too much to do.
Eased forward early to settle just behind midfield. Only responded fairly under the stick early in the straight before staying on solidly late.
Pushed forward early to share the lead. Had nothing left in the tank late and dropped back from the 200m. Jockey questioned.
Cruised out early and settled 3rd last. Wider on the turn and only plugged away slowly in the straight.
Sent forward early to share the lead in a fast tempo. Tried to keep going in the straight, but had nothing left late and faded out from 200m.
Pushed forward early to share the lead, but stuck 3 wide no cover. Eased back 800m to settle 3rd with cover. Gave nothing in the straight and was eased out from the 100m.
Cruised ahead from the wide draw to settle around midfield. Steadied off heels at 300m and never ran on from that point.
Fractious in the barrier and slow to begin. Recovered to press forward and sit just forward of midfield. Gave nothing in the straight and dropped out quickly.

Settled in last few, switched wide for a run into straight, ran on to be nearest at finish.
Settled behind midfield in 8th on the rail, saved ground on the inside turning in, ran on steadily to be nearest at finish.
Travelled mainly 3L off the pace in 4th, commenced move entering the straight, fought on steadily under pressure without threatening.
Given reminders after beginning from a wide gate, settled 2-wide just over 1L off the pace to the straight, came under pressure on straightening, ran home one-paced.
Settled towards the rear in 9th, circled the field on the bend, carried very wide into home straight, one-paced under pressure.
Settled at the back from the widest gate, came under pressure rounding the home bend and went very wide into the straight, ran home one-paced down the centre of the track.
Jumped fairly, held up in midfield racing keenly past the 1400 metres, in similar position entering home straight, inconvenienced early on, kept on at the one pace.
Broke well, settled just off the pace on the rail, chased the leader in 3rd into straight, soon weakened under pressure.
Settled about 3L back in joint 4th on the rail after beginning from the one draw, in similar position entering home straight, faded under pressure.
Interference at the start, settled at the back on the rail, made no impression in home straight.
Travelled wide in midfield, came under pressure rounding the home bend, soon faded after straightening.
Hard ridden to take rail and led at advantageous slow sectionals, made all.
Eased at start, 3 wide at back, harmed by the slow pace, unleashed strong finishing efforts 250M.
Hard ridden forward, sat outside the lead, benefited by the slow tempo, ran on well for 3rd.
Hard ridden to obtain box seat, enjoyed the slow pace, just held ground in straight.
Pushed forward, sat 2 wide, benefited by the slow tempo, out of fuel 200M.
Eased back to rear, trapped 3-4 wide throughout, harmed by the slow pace, dashed well 200M despite all negative racing situations.
Eased back, 2 wide, not suited by the slow pace, on heels 250M, little dash 100M.
Hard ridden to keep up in midfield trapped 3 wide, bumped 300M and then hung in and checked badly 250M, not tested.
At back, 2-3 wide, harmed by the slow tempo, checked badly 250M, little dash 100M.
Eased back early however trapped wide, progressed forward to take advantages of the slow pace, but still 3 wide, emptied 250M.
At back along the fence, harmed by the slow pace, checked 250M, no progress.
Pushed to keep up in midfield, 2 wide, severely checked 250M, not tested.
Raced at box seat, improved on straightening, continued to gain ground in the straight, finished unchallenged.
Raced at rear, quickened passing 100M and made good late ground.
Ridden along to take lead, asked for effort at Home Turn, kept on to the line.
Lay out in early and mid-race, settle midfield on rail, gradually made ground in the straight.
Began very awkwardly and lost ground, settled behind midfield on rail, kept improving on rail at Home Turn to save ground, finished well.
Ridden along and settled behind leaders, commenced to improve near 500M, limited response in the straight.
Urged along to settle outside the lead, gave ground passing 200M, failed to make impression.
Taken back from widest barrier, raced at rear, widest on straightening, one-paced.
After 1300M was left racing wide and without cover at handy position, commenced to improve passing 550M, weakened passing 150M.
Settle midfield wide and with cover, no response in the straight, wound right hind.
On jumping was crowded for room, settled midfield, failed to run on, must trial.
Always back, never in it, must trial.
Clean jump, took the lead easily, travelled well throughout, kicked clear after turning in and scored.
Jumped well, sent forward to race in 2nd, 2 wide throughout, kept on well after turning in to finish 2nd.
Slightly slow out, raced 5 lengths or so back, saved ground on turn, made good ground in straight to take a place.
Jumped well, positioned 1-2 lengths behind the leader on rail, easy run on turn, kept on evenly in straight.
Away with them, steadied off heels early, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, same position on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Average to begin, raced 3 wide without cover in midfield, similar position on turn, ran on evenly to the line.
Began fairly, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, finished off evenly.
Steadied on jumping and shifted in, raced at rear, 7 lengths back, slightly improved on turn, one-paced in straight. (Roarer.)
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, 7 to 8 lengths back, still well back on turn, only passed a few tired horses in straight.
Began awkwardly, bumped early, recovered to race 2 wide, 2 lengths back, there to turn, weakened gradually in straight.
Out in line, bumped early, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, peaked early in straight.
Raced at rear, 6 lengths back on rail, there to turn, emptied early in straight, finished last, never a competitive.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide, 2 to 3 lengths back, improved from 450M, finished off very strongly to score by 3-1/4L.
Jumped well from the widest draw, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, headed early in straight, stayed on well thereafter to take 2nd.
Steadied on jumping, positioned on rail at rear, difficult to settle near 1200M, still 6 lengths back on turn, kept to inside after straightening and finished off very strongly, just missed 2nd.
Slowly away, raced at tail, 8 lengths back, slightly improved from 800M, bumped near 650M, 3 wide on turn, made good progress in straight to make frame.
Jumped well from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground to 400M, finished off evenly in straight.
Slowly away, positioned on rail behind midfield, there to turn, finished off evenly.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail early, slightly improved from 1100M, positioned 2 to 3 wide with cover in midfield in the middle stages, peaked early in straight, ran on one-paced.
Quickly into stride, raced prominently, saddle shifted near 1300M, still positioned in 2nd thereafter, peaked after turning in, weakened thereafter.
Began well from a wide draw, sent forward to race prominently, sat right behind the leader in the middle stages, peaked near 150M, weakened thereafter.
Jumped well, raced 2 wide behind midfield, peaked on turn, ran home one-paced.
Taken back from gate 9, raced 2 wide at rear, bumped near 1000M and 650M, 3 wide turning, failed to close off in straight.
Jumped well from a middle draw, unable to slot in, travelled 3 wide and without cover throughout, weakened on turn, emptied early in straight, finished tailed out.
Sent forward to take the rail and led by about 1L, kicked away from 200M and ran on nicely to score by 2L.
Asked and settled to race in the box-seat, sat about 2L off, kept on going but was no match to the winner.
Settled to race just behind midfield, about 4L off along the rail, saved ground and kept on well to the wire.
Pushed to settle one-off one-back, sat about 2L off the lead, remained one paced to the line.
Niggled along before being shifted to find cover, near the tail at turn 5L behind on the rail, made ground and ran on fairly.
Travelled in midfield, about 3L behind 3 wide with cover, made minor ground and continued to the line.
Pushed and settled in worse than midfield, about 5L behind wide but with cover, swung wide and made slight ground.
Jumped awkwardly and settled at the rear, about 6L behind on the rail, made minor ground and ran on whilst laying in. (Rider questioned)
Asked to go forward, prominent 2L off the lead 3 wide without cover, swung wide and was only one paced.
Raced in behind midfield, about 4L behind 2 wide, one paced and did not threaten.
Sent forward and sat outside the lead, faded gradually from on straightening.
Pushed, sat in front of midfield but wide and without cover, gave ground rounding Home Turn.
Began well from gate 1, positioned 3 lengths or so back on rail, angled out near 750M, checked near 550M, same margin back on turn, finished off strongly in straight to score.
Jumped well from a middle draw, sent forward to take the early lead, headed near 850M, sat comfortably in 2nd thereafter, kept on well in straight to take 2nd.
Clean jump, positioned 2 to 3 lengths back on rail, easy run on turn, closed off well to get 3rd.
Began fairly, raced at rear, 8 lengths back, still well back on turn, finished off very strongly to make frame.
Taken back from gate 11, positioned on rail at rear, 7 lengths back, similar position on turn, kept to inside after straightening and made some progress.

Jumped well from a wide draw, sent forward to race prominently, took the lead near 850M, enjoyed the easy lead on turn, kept on well early in straight, headed near 150M, weakened gradually thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Slowly away, raced behind midfield, 6 to 7 lengths back, hampered near 550M, 2 wide on turn, finished off one-paced.
Average to begin, positioned 5 to 6 lengths back on rail, checked near 550M, same margin back on turn, failed to close off in straight. (Bled.)
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, 9 to 10 lengths back, still well back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Away with them, raced 2 wide, 5 lengths back, hampered and taken wider near 550M, 3 wide on turn, made no progress in straight.
Began well from a tricky draw, raced 2 wide behind midfield, severely checked and carried wider near 550M, well back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Average to begin, sent forward to race 2 wide, a length behind the leader, no cover after 800M, emptied after turning in, eased final 200M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Reserved after the start, sat in midfield along the inside, loomed up to challenge seriously 300M, slipped away with a winning break inside 200M, held sway under pressure late stages.
Up with early pace, tracked leaders from 1000M, ran on steadily to the line and gradually gained ground on the winner towards the finish.
Held up 2-wide in mid-division, pushed along 600M, battled on well over final 300M to claim 3rd in a blanket finish for minor honours.
Settled down in 5th never far off from leaders, moved closer to pace 700M, dueled for the lead mid-straight, held ground late stages, lost 3rd near line.
Taken back from wide barrier, held up last 8Ls off the pace, stayed on strongly down the inside for close 5th.
Eased back to a 2-wide spot towards the rear, 4Ls to make up 400M, chased solidly between runners.
Began only fairly, taken back behind runners, settled in the rear pair 8Ls off the pace, brought widest to challenge 250M, ran on mildly.
Settled down 2-wide behind midfield, kept on one pace when switched clear 250M, no serious threat to leaders.
Guided to the fence after the start, held up 6Ls towards the rear, failed to quicken on straightening, never a winning chance.
Crossed to the lead 1000M, vied for the lead with rival, no extra and dropped away 250M.
Chased leaders, wide no cover from 850M, gave ground from 500M and soon left behind by rivals entering straight.
Caught wide 1st turn, moved up to sit outside the pace, vied for the lead middle stages, weakened rapidly passing 400M to finish a well beaten last.

Ridden early from a wide draw before quickly taken backward to just worse than midfield, remained wide throughout, ran on doggedly to assert authority final strides.

Moderate start, soon recovered to midfield, travelled keenly in forward of midfield from the 900 metres, soon came to challenge after straightening hitting the front over 150 metres out, caught close to home.
Niggled along in midfield 3-wide, hampered and carried wider 750 metres out, finished off well inside the final 200 metres.
Settled just worse than midfield from a wide gate, remained in a similar position into the straight, ran on steadily to be nearest at finish.
Taken back from a wide gate and waited with, switched widest entering straight, ran on well down the centre of the track to be nearest at finish.
Began well, restrained 2L back in 4th, checked and lost position 700 metres out, one back in 5th turning for home, shifted in for a run passing the 250 metres, one-paced.

Hard ridden early stages, settled 3-wide without cover when 2L back in 5th 900 metres out, remained wide home bend while gaining closer, joined the leaders turning in holding every chance in straight until the 100 metres.
Jumped awkwardly losing ground, settled in last few on the rail, switched off rail for a run entering straight, made modest progress without threatening.
Settled in rear from the widest gate, shifted wider turning for home, made modest progress without quickening.
Moderate start, settled just worse than midfield on the rail, fought on steadily under pressure without threatening.
Settled just off the pace on the rail, came under pressure shortly after straightening, kept on before fading inside the final 200 metres. (Questioned for disappointing performance)
Jumped fairly from the one draw, settled in forward of midfield within 3L of pace on the rail, faded under pressure after straightening.
Ridden forward from a wide gate, tracked the leader around the bend, hit the front turning in, folded up quickly inside the final 200 metres.
Well there, took up running from the 1000 metres, held narrow lead until headed into straight, dropped away quickly.
Pushed to occupy box seat, not suited by the fast tempo, closed off strongly 300M to score with some in hands.
Pushed to take rail and lead, clocked fast sectionals, ran on until 250M overhauled, ran on for 2nd.
Midfield along the fence, favoured by the fast tempo, lack room 400M, progressed steadily when clear.
Eased to sit just off midfield, 2-3 wide, benefited by the fast pace, made steady ground 300M without threats.
Pressed forward, sat 2 wide, harmed by the fast sectionals, held ground in straight.
Awkward away, at back, 3-4 wide, suited by the fast tempo, progressed steadily 300M.
Midfield, 2 wide, suited by the fast tempo, blocked 4-2, progressed steadily when clear.
At back, 2-3 wide, favoured by the fast tempo, made steady ground 300M.
At back, 2 wide, benefited by the fast tempo, lack room 4-2, ran on ok when clear.
Hard ridden forward, 2 wide, not suited by the fast pace, weakened 250M.
Eased back, 3-4 wide, favoured by the fast pace, hung in badly as usual in straight, ran on fairly.
At rear, on the fence, benefited by the fast tempo, however never improved.
Eased to sit in midfield, 3 wide, out of fuel 300M.
Pushed forward, trapped 3 wide, not suited by the fast pace, emptied 350M.
Jumped smartly, steadied to settle midfield position, kept making ground in the straight, finished strongly.
Taken back at start, travelled at tail, quickened near 150M, made good late ground.
Began only fairly then ridden along to obtain box seat, improved near 350M, battled hard and worked home strongly.
Urged along to settle outside the lead, asked for effort at Home Turn, fought hard entire straight, finished solidly.
Travelled at rear, kept on rail at Home Turn to save ground, from near 400M until passing 100M was held up for running, came home nicely.
Taken back at start, wide on straightening, made nice late ground.
Settled midfield, tried to improve at Home Turn, kept on to the line.
Ridden along to take lead, passing 100M gradually gave ground.
Began only fairly and was steadied when crowded for room, then niggled to settle midfield on rail, gradually gave ground passing 150M.
Settled at rear, one-paced when asked for effort in the straight.
Travelled midfield, weakened passing 100M, failed to run on.
Urged at start to settle behind leaders, niggled passing 850M, emptied passing 150M.
Throughout the race travelled wide and without cover at handy position, weakened badly passing 400M.
Taken back at start, widest on straightening, never in it.
Bumped on jumping, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, bumped near 700M, similar position on turn, taken wide early in straight, finished off very strongly to score on his debut.

Began only fairly, raced 2W at rear, 7L back, improved on turn, made some headway early in straight, taken wide near final 150M to avoid the traffic, finished off very strongly, just missed by narrow margin.
Began well, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well throughout, kept on well after turning in, but couldn't hold off the challengers late.
Moderately away from gate 2, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, saved ground throughout, made steady progress in straight to make frame.

Moderately away from the widest gate, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, hampered and taken wider near 700M, very wide turning in, kept on well early in straight, peaked near 200M, stayed on evenly thereafter.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 8 lengths back at tail, moved closer on turn, made some progress in straight without threatening.
Bumped start, raced at tail, 8 lengths back, moved slightly closer on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Clean jump, positioned 3 wide with cover, 2 lengths back, bumped near 700M, improved thereafter, peaked early in straight, battled on until final 100M.

Away with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, difficult to settle in the middle stages, bumped near 650M, improved thereafter, very wide turning in, kept on evenly early in straight, raced tight and crowded near final 100M.
Average to begin, raced at rear, 5 lengths or so back, slightly improved on turn, taken wide in straight but failed to make any progress.
Shifted in and bumped start, raced prominently 3 wide, same position on turn, bumped near 500M, weakened gradually in straight, eased final 100M. (Rider concerned horse's action.)
Slowly away, recovered to race prominently, 2nd on turn, bumped near 500M, emptied early in straight.
Bumped start, positioned 3 lengths back on rail, there to turn, failed to close off in straight.
Jumped well, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths back, same position on turn, finished off strongly to score by a head.
Away with them, raced 2 wide, 5 lengths back, same margin back on turn, finished off very strongly to take 2nd, just narrowly beaten.
Moderately away from the widest gate, raced 3 wide in 5th, no cover on turn, kept on very well in straight, just beaten by a head.

Bumped and unbalanced on jumping, no early speed, raced 7L back at rear, still well back on turn, no clear running near 200M, finished off very strongly when clear thereafter, nearest on line. (See Racing Incidents.)
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, kept battling in straight before racing tight concluding stages and not ridden out, good debut.
Crowded on jumping, positioned 5 lengths or so back on rail, angled out near 500M, made good progress early in straight raced tight final 150M, not able to be ridden out near the finish.

Fast into stride, showed early speed to take the rail, sat 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader, easy run on turn, kept to inside after straightening, found no daylight, kept on evenly when clear thereafter.

Taken back from a wide draw, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, 6 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, no clear running early in straight, made some headway when clear thereafter to be nearest on line.
Began well from a wide draw, sent forward to race prominently, sat outside the leader in 2nd on turn, kept on one-paced in straight.
Quickly into stride, showed early speed to take the lead, enjoyed the easy lead on turn, kept on well early in straight, headed and peaked near 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Began well from a wide draw, unable to slot in, raced 4 wide without cover at rear throughout, made no progress in straight.
Taken back from barrier 13, raced at tail, 7 lengths back, still well back on turn, made no real progress in straight.
Moderately away from a tricky gate, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, carried wider on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, angled out near 700M, showed no response after turning in, eased final 150M.
Sent forward and sat just off the lead on centre track, kept on going and held off a late challenge to score by 1/2L.
Settled to race towards the rear, about 4L behind on the outside rail, produced a spirited run from 250M to take 2nd.
Awkward start, raced close to the tail, 4L off on stand side, taken to centre track after 400M, ran on okay for 3rd.
Urged but took a sit behind the pace when unable to lead, sat about 2L off on centre track, kept on going to the line. (Rider questioned)
Settled in front of midfield, about 2L off on stand side, awkward to heels after 250M, mostly one paced.
Awkward start, settled in midfield, about 4L behind on centre track, kept on going to the line.
Slow to jump, travelled at the rear, 6L behind on stand side, improved gradually and ran on well in final 100M.
Raced at the tail, about 6L behind on centre track, showed response and made ground after 300M, kept on fairly.
In midfield, about 3L behind on the outside rail, saved ground until held up after 100M, ran on okay.
Began fairly only, then asked to lead on the outside rail, ran on till 200M when flattened. (Lame right front)
Pushed forward and shared lead on stand side, kept on only till 200M and then faded.
Sent forward and shared lead on stand side, emptied at 250M and was disappointing.
Settled behind the leaders, about 2L off on stand side, showed nothing when asked.
Raced behind the leaders, about 2L off on stand side, flattened after 350M.
Average to begin, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground to near 600M, found no daylight after turning in, finished off very strongly when clear final 100M, scored by a head.

Moderately away, raced prominent but trapped wide early, slightly improved near 1400M to sit 2W, 1L behind the lead in 2nd, there to turn, kept on very strongly and took the lead near 200M, but just couldn't hold off the winner late.
Slightly slow out, raced at rear on rail, 6 to 7 lengths back, closer on turn, taken wide in straight and finished off strongly to take 3rd, nearest on line.
Began fairly, raced 2 wide in midfield, 4 lengths or so back, improved from 700M, 4 wide turning in, kept on well, just missed 3rd on line. (Lost right hind plate.)
Clean jump, positioned 2 to 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, easy run throughout, kept on well in straight, just missed frame.
Moderately away from the widest gate, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield early, 2 wide from near 1300M, moved closer on turn, finished off evenly.
Began well, raced 2 wide, 2 to 3 lengths back, similar position on turn, kept on evenly in straight.
Jumped well, took the lead easily, travelled well throughout, peaked and headed near 200M, stayed on one-paced thereafter.
Began well, raced 2 wide at rear, checked near 1300M, last on turn, ran on well, but made no real progress.
Moderately away from a wide draw, raced at rear, trapped 3 wide with no cover after 1300M, improved on turn, emptied early in straight when hard run took effect.
Slowly away, raced at rear throughout, never a threat.
Chased leaders in 4th, picked up well to lead inside 200M, courageous right to the line holding off late challenge from runner-up.
Settled down 5th of 8 just over 3Ls off the pace, hit the line well late, just couldn't reel in the winner.
Held up 3Ls off the leader in a strongly run race, chased steadily to the finish.
Settled at the rear 4-5Ls behind leader in a fast run race, stayed on moderately final 250M making minor late headway.
Held up in rear pair, 4-5Ls off the pace middle stages, kept grinding away over final 300M, didn't close gap on first 3.
Away well to lead on settling, set good pace to straight, ran on gamely early straight, caught 200M, faded towards the line.
Raced just outside the pace, couldn't go on passing 250, tired.
Crossed to the rail tracking leader in a race run at good pace, didn't find much entering straight, dropped away. (Jockey reported his mount didn't travel comfortably at any stage. / Lame next day.)
Jumped well, positioned 2 to 3 lengths back on rail, easy run to turn, angled out near 550M, finished off very strongly to score.
Clean jump, positioned 4 lengths or so back on rail, saved ground to near 500M, finished off very well to take 2nd.
Quickly into stride, showed early speed to take the lead, travelled well throughout, kicked clear early in straight, headed near final 150M, stayed on for 3rd.
Slowly away, raced at rear, 6 lengths or so back on rail, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after straightening and made good progress to make frame. (Lost right front plate.)
Began awkwardly and bumped, raced at tail, travelled keenly after 1400M, still last on turn, no daylight early in straight, made good progress when clear thereafter. (Lost left front plate.)
Taken back to race at rear, 3 wide with cover, similar position on turn, made some progress in straight without threatening.
Began well from gate 11, took the 2 wide position close to the leader, 1 out 1 back, travelled well throughout, stayed on until final 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, angled out near 500M, made no progress in straight. (Lame right front leg next day.)
Away with them, raced 2 wide, 5 to 6 lengths back, same position on turn, made some progress early in straight, peaked near 200M, weakened thereafter.
Began well from a tricky gate, positioned 2 wide in 3rd, same position to turn, carried wide near 600M, peaked early in straight, emptied final 200M.
Moderately away from the widest draw, raced 3 wide in midfield, no cover after the 1200M, very wide turning in, failed to close off in straight.
Began awkwardly, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, still 5 lengths back on turn, failed to close off in straight.

Crowded on jumping, positioned on rail at rear, slightly improved along the rail in the middle stages, saved ground on turn, angled out near 300M, into traffic jam, finished off strong when clear final 100M to score.

Hampered start, raced 2 wide in midfield, 4 to 5 lengths back, there to turn, taken wide in straight and finished off strongly to be nearest on line, just narrowly beaten. (Lost right front plate at the start.)
Began well from gate 1, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, easy run throughout, angled out after straightening and finished off well to take 3rd, good debut.
Jumped well from the widest draw, showed early speed to take the lead, travelled well throughout, kicked clear after turning in, kept on very well but just couldn't hold off the first few late.
Moderately away, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back in 3rd, same position on turn, kept on evenly in straight. (Lost right front plate near 500M.)
Bumped start, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, there to turn, made some progress in straight without threatening.
Taken back from gate 13, raced at tail for the majority of the race, taken wide after straightening and finished off well to be nearest on line, made good impression on debut.
Bumped start, sent forward to sit outside the leader, 3/4L back in 2nd, same position on turn, kept on until weakening inside final 200M.
Crowded out start, positioned 9 lengths back on rail, saved ground throughout, made some headway in straight.
Clean jump, hampered early, unable to slot in, travelled 3 wide and without cover in 5th, same position on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Hampered on jumping, travelled keenly early, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, kept on evenly early in straight, weakened from final 200M.
Jumped well, raced 3 wide behind midfield, 5 lengths back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Began only fairly, positioned on rail in midfield, 4 lengths back, saved ground on turn, emptied early in straight, eased late.
Hampered at start, raced 2 wide, 6 to 7 lengths back, there to turn, showed no response in straight, finished last.
Held up in midfield 4Ls off the good pace, picked up strongly to lead near 200M, drew away for dominant win.
Crowded for room on jumping, ridden along to maintain contact with the field, 8Ls off the pace on the turn, closed off fastest to go 2nd 50M, couldn't reel in the winner.
Chased leader 2-wide, battled on over final 400M, no match with winner at 200M, lost 2nd 50M out but held on for placing.
Settled down behind midfield, 5Ls off the pace 400M, made moderate progress but never a winning chance.
Sent forward from wide draw, crossed to the lead 1000M, set good pace middle stages, kept grinding in straight, headed mid-straight and faded 100M out.
Pushed along to be 4th close up, travelled keenly 800M, couldn't sprint enough from 350M, held ground only. (Blood in trachea.)
Began awkwardly, slotted into a 2-wide spot behind midfield, 5Ls off the pace 400M, kept on mildly to line.
Jumped on terms to be 5th on settling, 3Ls off the pace midway, couldn't pick up speed when driven out inside 400M, faded 100M.
Ridden along early then steadied for cover 1300M, 3-wide towards the rear, ran on fairly down outside of straight, passed a few late without threatening.
Not hurried after the start, held up 2nd last along the fence, failed to make up any ground on leaders over final 400M.
Raced prominently behind leader, lacked a response entering straight, weakened 200M, eased towards the line.
In mid-division along the rail, gave ground rapidly from 400M.
Eased back to race near the rear 11th of 13, didn't pick up leaving the turn, eased when no chance 150M.

Ridden to lead and made all the running, kicked some 2.5L clear after straightening, held on to the line.
Settled just worse than midfield, ran on well in straight to snatch 2nd late.
Broke well, settled not far off in 4th, shuffled back coming onto home bend, ran on steadily to reach 2nd over 150 metres out, headed for 2nd in the shadow of the post.
Settled just worse than midfield on the rail, shifted out for a run after straightening, ran on quite well to be nearest at finish.
Moderate start, niggled along in 5th becoming 3rd some 2L back leaving the Rock, in similar position on the rail entering home straight, ran home one-paced.
Settled at the back and waited with, finished off the race well.
Began fairly from a wide gate, gradually dropped towards the rear despite ridden along, produced good late impression in closing stages.
Failed to muster, travelled one from last to the straight, ran past well-beaten horses closing stages.
Jumped awkwardly losing ground, towards the rear most of the way, never seen with a chance.
Pressed forward from the widest gate down back straight, chased behind the leader rounding home bend, weakened under pressure inside the final 200 metres.
Hard ridden to be up with the pace, settled just over 2L back in 4th approaching the home bend, dropped out tamely after straightening.
Slightly slow out, ridden to midfield in 6th on the rail some 3L back, soon weakened after straightening.
Pushed forward, sat outside and off the leader, made early move 600M to attack the leader, closed off strongly to win.
Hard ridden to take rail and led at advantageous slow sectionals, hung on until 100M overhauled, ran on for 2nd.
Pushed to sit in midfield 2 wide, dashed well 250M for 3rd.
Eased at start, took rail, raced keenly, harmed by the slow pace, dashed strongly 250M, lack room 150M.
Pushed to obtain box seat, raced flat until 200M made some ground.
Eased back, harmed by the slow pace, never a factor.
Settled midfield, asked for effort at Home Turn, issued a strong challenge and lay in near 150M, finished strongly to score.
Ridden along to take lead, responded well in the straight, just missed by Neck.
Raced midfield, commenced to improve on straightening, close to the line was steadied to avoid heels, distressed.
Ridden along to take box seat, battled hard to the line, finished well.
Taken back at start, kept improving on rail at Home Turn to save ground, fought hard to the line.
Taken back at start, settled behind midfield, made some ground passing 100M.
Travelled behind midfield on rail, close the finished line was crowded for room, kept on to the line.
Raced behind leaders, crowded for room near 150M, then one-paced to the line.
Slow to begin, raced at rear, wide on straightening, gradually made ground passing 200M.
Taken back from wide gate, widest on straightening, no response in the straight.
Urged along to settle outside the lead, gradually gave ground on straightening, near 150M was severely checked then failed to close off.
Raced midfield, emptied passing 200M, failed to run on.
Moderately away from a wide draw, positioned 1-out 1-back, there to turn, finished off very strongly to score.
Jumped well from the widest gate, sent forward to race prominently, 3 wide and without cover throughout, kept on well in straight to take 2nd.
Jumped with them, positioned on rail at rear, saved ground on turn, made very good progress in straight to take 3rd.
Began awkwardly and bumped, raced 2 wide, 3 lengths back, same position on turn, made good progress in straight to make frame.
Bumped start, raced 3 wide in midfield, similar position on turn, made some progress in straight.
Bumped start, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, easy run on turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Bumped on jumping, positioned 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, same margin back on turn, angled out in straight and finished off evenly.
Fast into stride, sat outside to the leader, shared lead on turn, peaked and headed early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Bumped on jumping, sent forward to take the lead, shared lead at turn, found no extra gear in straight, headed final 200M, weakened gradually thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Out in line, taken back to race wide with cover behind midfield, 4 lengths back on turn, no clear running in straight until final 50M.
Jumped with them, crowded early, raced wide at rear, 6 lengths back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Bumped on jumping, raced at tail throughout, emptied early in straight, finished last. (Lame left front fetlock next day morning.)
Slightly slow out, bumped near 1500M, raced 2 wide, 5 lengths back, moved closer on turn, taken wide in straight and finished off very strongly to score.
Bumped start, sent forward to race 2 wide in 4th, 1 to 2 lengths back, similar position on turn, closed off well to take 2nd.
Bumped on jumping, sent forward to sit 2 wide in 2nd, there to turn, took the lead near 400M, kept on well in straight but couldn't hold off the first two late.
Moderately away, bumped early, raced 2 wide in midfield, closer on turn, made some progress in straight to make frame.
Clean jump, bumped early, took the rail near 1300M, sat a length behind the leader in the middle stages, easy run to turn, kept to inside after straightening and finished off evenly.
Began awkwardly, taken back to race at rear, 8 lengths or so back, still there to turn, taken wide in straight and finished off strongly without threatening the first few.
Slowly away, raced at tail, 9 lengths or so back, still well back on turn, made good progress in straight.
Taken back from the widest draw, positioned 6 lengths back on rail, improved from near 500M, made no further progress in straight.
Began well, positioned 2 to 3 lengths back on rail, saved ground to 400M, kept on well early in straight, peaked near 150M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide at rear, 6 to 7 lengths back, 3 wide on turn, made no progress in straight.
Began fairly from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground throughout, peaked on turn, showed no response in straight.

Jumped well from a wide draw, bumped early, hard ridden thereafter and took the lead near 1200M, easy lead in the middle stages, peaked and headed near 400M, emptied early in straight and gradually dropped away.
Slotted into a position in midfield, 3-3/4L behind 2 wide, pulled away from 150M and scored comfortably by 2-1/4L.
Settled to race in midfield, 3-1/4L behind along the rail, ran on well for 2nd but was no match.
Pushed but settled in behind midfield, 5L behind wide and without cover, made ground and closed fairly.
Took cover and raced at the rear, 7L behind along the rail, made ground and ran on fairly to the line.
Eased then raced towards the rear, 6L behind 2 wide, niggled till 600M to prevent a runner to cross, swung wide and made ground steadily to the line.
Pushed forward, settled for cover and raced in the box-seat, sat about 1-1/2L, kept on one paced to the line.
Taken back, raced at the rear throughout, 7L behind 2 wide, swung widest, made ground and kept on to the line.
Pushed, settled to race in front of midfield, 2-1/4L behind 2 wide, found no extra to keep up near 200M.
Hard ridden forward, took lead and led by 1-1/2L, weakened and headed passing 200M.
Bumped at start when being eased, settled behind midfield 5L behind along the rail, did not threaten.
Crowded on jumping, raced 2 wide in midfield, moved closer on turn, finished off strongly in straight and scored.
Bumped start, raced wide with cover at rear, improved on turn, made very good progress in straight to take 2nd.
Bumped on jumping, unable to slot in, travelled 3 wide with no cover in midfield, similar position on turn, kept on well in straight to get 3rd.
Slightly slow out, positioned on rail behind midfield, improved from 500M, made reasonable headway in straight to make frame.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide, 2 lengths back in 3rd, same margin back on turn, finished off evenly.
Taken back from a wide draw, positioned on rail at rear, still 5 to 6 lengths back on turn, made some progress in straight.
Taken back from gate 10, raced at tail to turn, improved from 500M, taken widest in straight and made minor progress.
Began well from the widest draw, positioned 3 wide behind midfield early, improved from near 750M, 2nd on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Clean jump, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 5 to 6 lengths back, same margin back on turn, made no progress in straight.
Began only fairly, sent forward to race 2 wide, a length behind the leader in 2nd, similar position on turn, checked near 350M, weakened gradually in straight.
Moderately away, took the lead easily, travelled well throughout, found no extra gear in straight, weakened gradually, eased final 100M.
Began well, positioned 2 to 3 lengths back on rail, couldn't maintain position from 600M, eased final 400M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Positively ridden on jumping from wide draw, tracked leader before taking over 350M, quickened to a commanding lead mid straight, well on top 100M out, coasted home.
Dropped back from draw 12, settled last for the first 600M, brought widest on straightening, kept on solidly for 2nd but couldn't pose serious threat to the easy winner.
Couldn't slot in racing wide no cover in midfield, chased steadily over final 300M to just miss 2nd on the line, no match to easy winner though.
Began well from draw 1 to be chasing leaders in 3rd, kept battling in the straight without getting closer to the winner, unable to hold off 2nd and 3rd final 100M.
Restrained in midfield about 4Ls off leader, saved ground on the rails, kept grinding home and unable to improve position.
Emerged as leader passing 1000M, given a breather 700M, relinquished the lead 350M, fought on to 150M, faded towards the finish.
Never far off from leaders, 4th turning home and well placed to strike, had his chance, only held ground over final 200M.
Hampered shortly after the start and ended up in the 8th spot further back than intended, caught 3-wide in midfield, kept on only fairly on straightening, never a winning chance.
Drifted back to near the rear, kept to inside throughout, only one paced home.
Held up 2-wide in mid-division 4Ls behind leader, found the line only fairly. No threat to leaders.
Sluggish away, ended up towards the rear, 5Ls to make up at 400M, couldn't finish off.
Checked shortly after the jump and lost position, ended up in rear, still long way back turning in and did not find much under pressure, checked late stages.
Crowded on jumping, raced 2 wide at rear, 10 lengths back, improved on turn, finished off very strongly to score on line.
Jumped well from a tricky gate, sent forward to race in 2nd, 2 to 3 lengths back, same margin back on turn, kept on very well, took the lead near 100M but couldn't hold off the winner late.
Began awkwardly from barrier 1, raced at rear, 11 lengths back, moved closer on turn, made very good progress in straight to take 3rd.
Bumped start, raced in 4th, easy run in the middle stages, improved from 500M, kept on well early in straight, peaked near 150M, weakened thereafter.
Average to begin, raced wide with cover in midfield, 5 to 6 lengths back, under pressure turning, finished off only evenly. (Lost left hind plate in the early stages.)

Began only fairly from the widest draw, recovered to take the lead, bumped and unbalanced near 950M, not able to settle shortly thereafter, uncontested lead on turn, peaked early in straight, headed and weakened thereafter.
Began well from a wide draw, raced 2 wide with cover behind midfield, 7 to 8 lengths back, awkwardly placed near 400M, no clear running early in straight, finished off evenly when clear thereafter.
Clean jump, positioned on rail in midfield, severely checked by the riderless horse near 1100M, 5 lengths or so back on turn, finished off one-paced in straight.
Began well from gate 7, raced in 3rd, hampered and carried wider near 1000M, no cover throughout, peaked on turn, showed no response in straight.
Fractious in gate, reared at start and lost considerable ground, raced at tail throughout, never recovered.
Moderately away, raced at rear throughout, never a factor. (Lame left front leg next day morning.)

Placing: UR
Comment: Fractious in gate, reared abruptly at start dislodging rider and left gate riderless. (Lame right front leg next day morning.)
