Ridden but soon dropped to forward of midfield, shaken up after straightening, ran on under pressure to just get up on line.
Began well, held up in 3rd some 2L back, became 4th rounding home bend, commenced move shortly after straightening, hit the front over 100 metres out, caught final strides.
Raced wide throughout, travelled in rear of midfield to straight, ran on to be nearest at finish.
Pressed forward from the widest gate to soon lead on the rail, held 2L break turning into straight, unable to sustain effort and headed over 100 metres out.
Soon dropped to the rear of midfield, baulked for a run early in straight, ran on to be nearest at finish.
Settled in midfield, kept on well in the run to the line.

Quickly recovered from a moderate start to chase behind the leader, some 2L back in 2nd rounding home bend and into the straight, kept on under pressure before finding no extra inside the final 200 metres.
Soon dropped towards the rear, travelled keenly on the rail in back straight, shaken up after straightening for home, produced late impression closing stages.
Close up early settling over 2L back in 4th, gained 3rd in similar position 3-wide rounding home bend, soon weakened after straightening.
Hard ridden early, soon dropped to midfield, dropped further back around the bend, made no impression thereafter.
Moderate start, settled in last few, gained slightly closer rounding home bend, wide into straight, ran home one-paced.(Questioned for disappointing performance)
Always in last few and never seen with a chance.
Raced greenly early and soon dropped to the rear, made no impression thereafter.
Pressed forward, took rail and led at good pace, made all.
At back, pace good, dashed well 300M for 2nd.
Eased to sit in midfield along the fence, pace good, lack room 400M, made steady ground when clear for 3rd.
Eased back, 2-3 wide, pace good, progressed steadily 400M, run ended 100M.
One out one back, pace good, just held ground in straight.
Hard ridden forward, sat 2 wide, pace good, emptied 200M.
Eased back to rear, 2-3 wide, pace good, progressed steadily 300M.
Raced midfield, asked for effort near 650M, quickened passing 150M to score.
Urged along to race outside the lead, improved near 400M, fought well to the line, just missed by Neck.
Rider's saddle shifted forward when steadied away from heels passing 1900M, settled midfield, gained ground passing 150M and finished strongly.
Settled behind midfield, wide on straightening, made ground 150M, finished nicely.
Taken back at start, widest on straightening, made up some good ground passing 150M.
Raced at back, tried to improve near 800M, limited response in the straight.
Settled behind midfield, commenced to improve approaching 800M, one-paced.
Lost its left front plate after start, pushed forward to take box seat, gave ground passing 150M.
Throughout the race travelled wide and without cover at handy position, gave ground near 200M.
Travelled midfield, under pressure and no response in the straight.
Settled at handy position, gave ground passing 200M, failed to make impression.
Moderate start, settled midfield on rail, no response in the straight.
Raced behind midfield on rail, awkwardly placed close to heels passing 150M, not fully tested.
Began awkwardly, travelled keenly in the lead, emptied near 200M, distress after race, lame right front next day.
Jumped well from a wide draw, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well throughout, kept on very well in straight to score.
Began well, sat a length behind the leader on rail, easy run on turn, closed off well to take 2nd.
Taken back to race 3 wide with cover at rear, 5 lengths back, 2 wide on turn, finished off very strongly in straight to be nearest on line to get 3rd.
Away with them, positioned 2 wide in midfield, carried wider on turn, finished off strongly to make frame, nearest on line.
Out in line, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, slightly improved on turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Bumped start and unbalanced, raced 2 wide at tail, 7 lengths back, last turning in, made very good progress in straight, good debut.
Jumped with them, raced 3 wide, 4 lengths back, travelled keenly near 1000M, same margin back on turn, ran on evenly, had to be steadied off heels when making ground in the final stages.
Taken forward after start from the widest draw, raced wide and without cover throughout, ran on evenly in straight.
Bumped start and unbalanced, positioned 2 wide in midfield, raced ungenerously near 900M, similar position on turn, finished off evenly.
Slowly away, recovered to race 4 lengths back on rail, slightly improved along the rail on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Average to begin, raced at tail, 7 lengths back, moved a little bit closer on turn, finished off one-paced in straight.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide, 4 lengths or so back, found rail on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Jumped well from gate 10, positioned outside to the leader, shared lead on turn, emptied early in straight, dropped off gradually thereafter.
Moderately away from a wide draw, raced wide with cover in midfield, same position on turn, 6 lengths back, finished off very strongly in straight to score impressively.
Fast into stride, raced 2 wide in 3rd, 5 lengths back on turn, fought on steadily in straight to take 2nd, never a threat to the winner.
Jumped well from gate 1, positioned on rail in 4th, 6 lengths back on turn, kept on well in straight to get 3rd.
Began fairly, raced 2 wide at rear, 8 lengths or so back, slightly improved on turn, made good progress in straight to make frame.
Quickly into stride, sent forward to take the lead, over-raced in the middle stages, cleared out early in straight, caught near 200M, weakened gradually thereafter. (See racing incidents.)
Jumped well from the widest draw, sent forward to race in 2nd, 2 to 3 lengths back on turn, kept on evenly in straight.
Bumped start, raced 3 wide at rear, 9 lengths back on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Began very awkwardly and crowded, raced in midfield, 8 lengths back on turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Slightly slow out and bumped, raced at tail early, slightly improved on turn, still 8 lengths or so back, made some progress early in straight and awkwardly placed closing stages.
Jumped well, raced in midfield, 6 lengths back on turn, ran on evenly early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, still well back on turn, made no progress in straight.
Slightly slow out, raced at tail, still 12 lengths back on turn, made no progress in straight.
Began well, taken back to race 10 lengths back on rail, same margin back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Jumped well, raced 2 to 3 wide in midfield, brushed and came off bridle rounding the home bend, gave ground abruptly thereafter, eased final 300M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Raced towards the rear, 7-1/4L behind wide but with cover, produced a spirited run home to score by a head.
Sat towards the tail, 6-1/2L behind 3 wide with cover, battled on gamely, just missed by a head.
Raced at the rear, 8L behind the lead 2 wide, made ground steadily and ran on well to the line.
Settled to race in midfield, 4-3/4L behind but trapped very wide, made ground and ran on okay. (Rider questioned)
Rolled forward to race in the box-seat, sat 2L off the lead, kept on going to the line.
Sent forward, sat 1-1/4L off the lead but trapped wide and without cover, in touch until swamped at 100M.
Travelled keenly in behind midfield, 4-1/2L off 3 wide with cover, one paced mostly but ran on to the line.
Sent forward to take rail and led by 1-1/4L, remained one paced and headed passing 150M.
Failed to muster, raced in front of midfield, 2-3/4L behind 3 wide with cover, one paced and run ended near 150M.
Rolled into position in front of midfield, 3L behind 2 wide, steadied at 200M, one paced mostly.
Failed to muster, settled to race behind midfield, 5-1/4L behind along the rail, one paced.
Niggled along to race outside the lead, sat 1-1/4L off, faded gradually from on straightening.
Began only fairly, then asked to sit in midfield, 3-1/2L behind along the rail, couldn't keep up after 300M.
Raced in midfield, 4-1/2L behind along the rail, found nothing. (Bled from both nostrils)
Moderately away, positioned 2 wide, 4 lengths or so back, moved closer on turn, took the lead early in straight, kept on strongly to score by 2 lengths.
Away with them, positioned 6 lengths back on rail, saved ground on turn, finished off strongly to take 2nd.
Taken back from gate 12, raced 3 wide with cover at tail, 9 lengths back, improved from 650M, very wide turning in, made very good progress in straight to get 3rd on line.
Taken back to race 2 wide, 8 to 9 lengths back at rear, improved from near 600M, made good progress in straight, just missed 3rd on line.
Crowded start, positioned on rail at rear, 7 to 8 lengths back, saved ground to 600M, 2 wide turning in, no clear running early in straight, finished off strongly when clear final 150M.
Began awkwardly and unbalanced the rider, raced 2 wide, 6 lengths back, crept closer on turn when pace slackened, finished off evenly in straight.
Slightly slow out from a wide draw, raced at tail, 10 lengths back, saved ground throughout, no daylight early in straight, made some headway in straight when clear thereafter.
Began well, sat 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, slightly improved from 800M, shared lead turning in, headed near 300M, weakened gradually from final 150M.
Fractious in barrier, began awkwardly, raced 3 wide with cover, 8 lengths back, bumped near 650M, closer on turn, finished off evenly.
Crowded on jumping, raced 2 wide, 7 lengths back, taken wide and bumped near 650M, found no daylight after turning in, taken wide near 350M and made minor progress thereafter.
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, ideal run to turn, made no progress in straight.
Bumped start, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths back in 3rd, similar position on turn, found no extra gear in straight, weakened from final 200M.
Average to begin, raced 3 wide with no cover, 6 to 7 lengths back, moved closer on turn, peaked early in straight, crowded for room near 200M, eased thereafter.
Jumped well from a wide draw, showed early speed to take the lead, travelled well to turn, challenged near 600M, headed early in straight, emptied thereafter, finished last.

Crossed to the lead 1650M, pressed by rival from 1500M setting fast pace to straight, headed by WERTHER early straight but courageous fought back to re-gain lead near 100M to win in track record time.
Settled down in 5th mid-pack, 4Ls off the strong pace, moved closer to leaders 700M, quickened to a narrow lead 300M but winner fought back late stages. (Bled.)
Towards the rear in a strongly run race, moved closer nearing top of straight and loomed a strong threat 300M, kept on solidly and pushed leaders to the line.
Slow to begin, recovered to be tracking leaders in a strongly run race, tried hard final 300M, held by leaders in the run home but nevertheless a creditable performance after lengthy absence.
Reserved to race near the rear in fast run race, last making the turn for home, stayed on final 400M without reaching leaders.
Reigned back to race in a rearward position, bustled along 550M but only ran past beaten horses in the run home. (Jockey reported his horse never comfortable in its action / Lame LF leg.)
Began awkwardly, keen early, chased leaders in a fast run race, couldn't sustain run passing 400M and weakened away.
Held up behind midfield in a strongly run race, faded turning in, never involved.
Moved up to press leader on the outside, set fast pace middle stages, couldn't keep up passing 800M, soon retreated to last and finished tailed out. (Unacceptable Performance.)
Clean jump, sent forward to race outside the leader in 2nd, same position on turn, took the lead early in straight, kept on very well to score.
Away with them, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, easy run to turn, finished off very well to get 2nd, but always held.
Moderately away, positioned 1 out 1 back, there to turn, angled out from near 500M, ran on well to take 3rd.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, same position on turn, kept on well in straight to make frame.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, 6 lengths or so back, closer on turn, taken widest in straight and made good progress to be nearest on line.
Began well from a wide draw, ridden forward but trapped 4 wide, drifted back slightly near 1000M to race 3 wide in 5th, still no cover on turn, ran on evenly to the line.
Slowly away, raced 2 wide at rear, 4 to 5 lengths back, improved from near 700M, very wide turning in, made no progress in straight.
Slowly away, raced at rear, 6 lengths back, moved closer on turn, still 3 lengths or so back, made no real progress in straight.
Average to begin, positioned 2 wide, 4 lengths back, there to turn, failed to close off in straight.
Jumped with them, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Jumped well, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, headed after turning in, dropped off rapidly thereafter, finished tailed out.

Eased forward to settle midfield, 3 wide with limited cover. Progressed to a prominent position at the top of the straight. Huge turn of foot under minimal urging from 200m to win very easily, and was eased late.
Pressed forward early to settle just forward of midfield. Stayed on strongly in the straight for easy 2nd, but no hope of catching winner.
Pushed forward early from the wide draw to initially share the lead, before dropping back to 2nd at 900m. Raced tight 650m. Ran solidly for most of the straight, but running on tired legs late.
Cruised forward early to sit around midfield. Struck on heels and unbalanced 600m. 2nd last on the turn. Stayed on well in the straight, and was working through the field.
Dropped back from the wide draw to settle worse than midfield, 3 wide. Bumped and unbalanced 750m. Wider on the turn and stayed on well early in the straight, before running 1 paced late.
Pressed forward from the wide draw to settle 3rd, 1 off the fence. Made a move at 600m, but was 1 paced in the straight.
Pushed forward from the wide draw to assume the lead. Still in front at 300m, but battled home 1 paced and eased late.
Eased forward early and eventually settled around midfield. Went for a skinny run at 750m, but was bumped and unbalanced. Wider in the straight, but only plugged away fairly to the line.
Cruised forward early to settle just behind midfield. Came off heels 750m. No threat in the straight, and not pushed hard late.
Eased back early to sit 2nd last. Hampered and taken 4 wide at 750m. Widest in the straight. Only responded timidly early in the straight, and was not pushed out in the 200m.
Fairly away, then crowded and lost ground. Settled last, 4-5L off the next horse. Plugged away fairly in the straight, but had too much to make up.
Tardy to begin, before settling 3rd last. Checked off heels and unbalanced 600m. Gave nothing early in the straight and cruised to the line late under minimal urging.
Raced keenly early when being settled, before sitting midfield. Lay out rounding the turns. Had nothing left in the tank in the straight.
Pushed forward early to sit 4th, on the fence. Gave nothing in the straight and dropped out from the 300m.
Away well, positioned on rail in midfield, angled out near 550M, no daylight early in straight, finished off very strongly when clear thereafter to score.
Moderately away from a wide draw, raced 2 to 3 wide with cover in midfield, improved from near 550M, kept on very well in straight to take 2nd.
Quickly into stride, showed early speed to take the lead, enjoyed the easy lead to turn, kept on very well in straight but couldn't hold off the first two late.
Began well from the widest gate, sent forward to race 2 wide in 2nd, same position on turn, fought on steadily to the line, just missed 3rd.
Average to begin, raced 3 wide at rear, improved from near 600M, made good progress in straight to be nearest on line.
Taken back to race at tail, 8 to 9 lengths back, still 5 lengths back turning in, finished off strongly in straight. (Whip entangled in the reins near 300M.)
Jumped well, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 to 4 lengths back, angled out from 550M, made some headway early in straight, peaked and raced tight near 200M, weakened closed home.
Slightly slow out from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, severely checked early in straight, finished off evenly thereafter. (Lame left front leg next day morning.)
Slightly slow out, raced 2 wide at rear, 7 to 8 lengths back, there to turn, taken wide in straight and made minor progress.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide behind midfield, travelled keenly near 1100M, 6 lengths or so back on turn, finished off evenly.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 8 to 9 lengths back at tail, moved closer but carried wider on turn, finished off evenly.
Jumped well from gate 13, positioned 1 out 1 back, there to turn, weakened gradually in straight.
Average to begin, positioned 6 to 7 lengths back on rail, saved ground on turn, no clear running early in straight, finished off one-paced when clear thereafter.
Fast into stride, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, easy run on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened rapidly final 200M.

Prominent and wide from a wide draw settling in midfield around the bend, commenced run entering straight, responded well to hit the front inside the final 100 metres.
Settled just worse than midfield, commenced move entering home straight, fought on steadily under pressure to snatch 2nd late.
Broke well from a wide gate, settled not far off 3-wide in 3rd, ran on steadily under pressure to hit the front briefly 150 metres out, found no extra late.
Niggled along towards the rear, overraced and shifted very wide rounding home bend, finished off the race well.
Soon picked up to 2nd under reminders, chased the leader to the 200 metres, weakened under pressure.
Crowded at start, ridden to lead, obtained rails run and steadied pace approaching home bend, led until tiring inside the final 200 metres.
Settled at the back from the widest gate, took closer order on the rail rounding home bend, kept on one pace without quickening in straight.
Prominent early, gradually dropped to midfield approaching home bend, hampered and lost position 600 metres out, kept on steadily without quickening in straight.
Soon dropped to the rear despite niggling along, well behind when carried very wide rounding home bend, produced some late recovery early in straight.
Raced wide in rear of midfield, carried very wide rounding home bend, never recovered.
Slowly away, recovered steadily along the rail to reach 2.5L 3rd coming onto home bend, similar turning into straight, folded up quickly from approaching the 200 metres.
Quickly recovered from a moderate start, settled in forward of midfield, dropped away quickly out of contention on top of home bend.
Box seat, benefited by the slow pace, closed off strongly 300M to score.
Eased back, trapped 3 wide, harmed by the slow pace, unleashed strong finishing efforts 300M.
Pushed to take rail and led at advantageous slow sectionals, hung on well until last few strides, just beaten by narrow margin.
Eased sit just off the leaders in 3 wide, favoured by the slow tempo, closed off strongly 300M.
At rear, 2-4 wide, harmed by the slow pace, dashed well 300M, run ended 50M.
Hard ridden but not muster, trapped 3-4 wide in midfield, not suited by the slow tempo, just held ground in straight.
Hard ridden to keep up in midfield, 2 wide, weakened 200M.
Behind midfield along the fence, not suited by the slow pace, little dash 200M.
Eased back, took rail, harmed by the slow pace, little dash 200M.
Pushed forward, sat outside the leader to enjoy the slow pace, emptied 250M.
Trapped 4-5 wide at back, never a factor.
Never competitive and tailed out.
Jumped well and ridden along to take lead, travelled comfortably, in the straight responded strongly to score.
Settled behind midfield, kept improving at Home Turn to save ground, quickened near 150M, finished solidly.
Travelled wide and without cover at handy position, made up some nice late ground, worked home solidly.
Travelled behind midfield, asked for effort near 450M, continued to make ground passing 200M.
Settled midfield, fought hard entire straight, lame right front.
Hard ridden from wide gate, settled midfield, widest on straightening, limited response in the straight.
Stumbled at start, raced at back, passing 600M was inconvenienced, struggled in the straight, roarer.
At start was bumped and became badly unbalanced, urged along to race outside the lead, weakened near 150M.
On jumping was hampered and lost ground, raced at rear, made the turn awkwardly and checked away from heels, no response in the straight.
Always niggled in the early and middle stages, settled at back on rail, failed to run on.
Travelled midfield, near 250M continued to give ground, failed to make impression.
Slow to begin then raced at tail, never in it.
Moderately away from a wide draw, raced 3 wide and without cover in midfield, gradually improved after 800M, kicked clear early in straight for a convincing 3 lengths victory.
Away with them, raced 2 to 3 wide at rear, 6 lengths back, bumped near 700M, improved on turn, finished off well in straight to take 2nd without threatening the winner.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced wide with cover at rear, 7 to 8 lengths back, moved closer on turn, brushed early in straight, made very good progress to get 3rd.
Average to begin, positioned 2 wide, 3 lengths back in 5th, similar position on turn, kept on evenly to the line. (Lame left front leg next day morning.)
Began well, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths back, moved closer on turn, kept on evenly in straight.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 5 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, angled out from 450M, brushed early in straight, made minor progress in straight.
Slightly slow out, positioned on rail behind midfield, severely checked near 1500M, 6 lengths back in the middle stages, same margin back on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, still 7 lengths back on turn, taken wide after straightening and made minor progress.
Jumped well from gate 1, showed early speed to take the lead, led narrowly to near 300M, headed and weakened thereafter.
Began well, positioned 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, no clear running in straight, not able to be properly tested.
Began fairly, sent forward to race in 2nd, outside to the leader, there to turn, peaked early in straight, dropped off gradually from final 200M.
Taken back from gate 9, raced at rear, checked near 1500M, 7 lengths back in the middle stages, similar position on turn, made no progress in straight.
Average to begin, failed to muster speed, awkwardly placed near 1600M, raced 4 lengths back in midfield, saved ground on turn, emptied early in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 4 wide with no cover at rear, peaked on turn, emptied early in straight when hard run took toll, finished tailed out.
Bumped on jumping, positioned 2 to 3 lengths back on rail, slightly improved along the rail on turn, bumped early in straight, finished off well to score.
Began well from gate 1, raced prominently, sat a length behind the leader in the middle stages, saved ground to near 600M, bumped and unbalanced early in straight, ran on well to take 2nd.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, 7 to 8 lengths back, moved closer in the middle stages, improved 4 wide on turn, finished off very strongly in straight to get 3rd, nearest on line.
Began well from a tricky gate, positioned 3 wide with cover, 2 lengths back, hampered and taken wider near 650M, raced tight early in straight, finished off evenly.
Bumped start, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths back, there to turn, raced tight early in straight, finished off evenly.
Moderately away from the widest draw, raced at rear, 6 lengths or so back, slightly improved near 900M, still 5 lengths back on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Taken back from barrier 13, raced 4 to 5 lengths back on rail, same margin back on turn, angled out near 450M, finished off one-paced.

Out in line, raced very wide at rear early, travelled keenly after entering the back straight, allowed to improve thereafter, took the lead near 700M, headed passing 250M and gradually dropped away. (See Racing Incidents.)
Fast into stride, sent forward to race prominently, took the lead after entering the back straight, headed 700M, stayed in 2nd until emptied near 250M, dropped off gradually thereafter.
Moderately away from a wide draw, raced 3 wide in midfield, hampered and taken wider near 650M, weakened thereafter, emptied early in straight. (Lame left front leg next day morning.)
Crowded on jumping, raced at rear, 5 lengths or so back, peaked on turn, emptied early in straight.
Average to begin, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, weakened on turn, awkwardly placed on heels near 600M, finished tailed out.
Away with them, raced 2 wide behind midfield, same position to near 700M, weakened thereafter, finished tailed out.
Began fairly, sent forward to race prominently, 3 wide to near 900M, weakened sharply on turn, finished tailed out.
Sent forward to share the lead in a 2 wide position, battled on and held off second place-getter to score by a head.
Niggled along and shared the lead along the rail, kept on in a neck-to-neck battle to the line, missed by a head.
Asked to go forward after the start, obtained the box-seat, sat 1-1/2L off, kept on well to take 3rd.
Travelled in front of midfield, 2-3/4L off along the rail, continued nicely to the line.
Eased and then raced towards the rear, 5-1/2L behind 3 wide with cover, made ground and ran on to the line.
Rolled into position in front of midfield, 2-3/4L off 3 wide and without cover at times, kept on going to the line.
Travelled in front of midfield, 2-3/4L off 2 wide, swung wide, made ground in final 200M, ran on well.
Slotted into a position in midfield, 4-1/4L behind 3 wide with cover, showed no response in the straight.
Jumped awkwardly and lost ground, hard ridden and settled behind midfield, 4-3/4L off along the rail, one paced.
Began only fairly, raced at the rear, 6-1/4L behind along the rail, kept on one paced.
Taken out at start, then raced towards the rear, 5-3/4L behind 2 wide, found nothing and eased at 200M.
Taken back and raced at the rear, 7L behind 3 wide with cover, never a factor. (Trainer questioned)
Pushed, settled one-off one back, 1-1/2L off the lead, gave ground from 600M. Must trial.
Away with them, raced prominently, on rail, travelled well throughout, kept on very well in straight and scored by half length.
Began awkwardly from gate 1, positioned on rail at rear, 5 lengths back, same margin back on turn, finished off very strongly in straight to take 2nd.
Fast into stride, sent forward to take the lead, led narrowly to near 350M, headed thereafter, but still stayed on for a place. (See Racing Incidents.)
Moderately away from a tricky draw, positioned wide with cover in midfield, bumped near 900M, similar position on turn, made some headway in straight to make frame.
Jumped well from barrier 11, sent forward to race prominently with no cover, 3 wide on turn, kept on evenly in straight.
Bumped start, positioned 2 wide, 1 to 2 lengths back, there to turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked on run near 200M, slightly weakened thereafter. (Blood in trachea.)

Moderately away, raced prominently without cover early, slightly taken back after 1000M, but still travelled wide with no cover, bumped near 700M, 5 lengths back on turn, made some progress in straight.
Average to begin, positioned 3 lengths back on rail, saved ground on turn, angled out early in straight, made no progress thereafter, bumped near final 100M, ran home one-paced.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, 6 lengths back, there to turn, kept to inside after straightening, angled out near 150M, finished off one-paced.
Slightly slow out, raced at rear, bumped near 900M, still 6 lengths back turning in, failed to close off in straight.
Jumped with them, raced wide with cover at rear, still well back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Bumped on jumping, positioned 3 wide, a length behind the leader, peaked on turn, weakened gradually in straight, finished last. (Lame right front leg.)
Sent forward, taken on by rivals in the lead, shook off pursuers 300M and opened up a sizeable margin, well in control final 100M to score his 4th win over the course and distance.
Away fairly and hampered near 1100M, improved to be chased leaders middle stages, lacked winner's acceleration early straight, got going final 200M but came up short.
Awkwardly away, held up towards the rear in a fast run race, stayed on well to go 3rd near line.
Jumped very awkwardly and lost ground, checked 1100M and raced much further back than usual in near last, held up at crucial stage inside 300M, made good ground when clear. Could have done better.
Sent forward from wide draw vying the lead along the 3-path, no match with winner's acceleration turning in, kept on evenly, edged out to 5th late stages.
Crowded for room on jumping, 2-wide towards the rear and about 5Ls off the pace home turn, made some ground at the finish without threatening.
Moved up to prompt the pace, held ground only early straight, faded passing 200M.
Failed to muster speed after being hampered after the jump, ended up in last much further back than usual, hard ridden to the turn, stayed on final 300M down the outside passing beaten rivals.
Slotted into a 2-wide position in midfield, ran on same pace final 300M, never threatened.
Eased back on jumping, improved passing 1000M to be racing in midfield, just over 3Ls off the pace 400M but failed to make any impression in the run home.
Dropped back on jumping from widest draw, settled down behind midfield, pushed along 500M out but never got going.
Chased leading trio in a fast run race, couldn't go on passing 300M, dropped off to last.

Slowly away, settled at the back early stages, switched in onto the centre of the track for a run coming onto course proper, ran on to hit the front over 50 metres out, won readily.

Broke well to lead early 4 off the stands rails, taken one back approaching the 800 metres, quickened well to hit the front 250 metres out, unable to sustain effort and headed inside the 50 metres. (Bled)
Crowded at start, soon dropped just behind the midfield, switched off the stands rail coming onto course proper, ran on until finding no extra inside the final 50 metres. (Cast plates early stages)
Moderate start, soon recovered towards the midfield, made headway down the centre of the track past the halfway mark, unable to sustain effort inside the final 200 metres. (Cast plate 600 metres out)
Moderate start, travelled just off the pace, soon came to challenge coming onto course proper and reached within 2L of the lead passing the 200 metres, kept on same pace to the line.
Settled mainly 3L off the speed, inconvenienced and switched in for a run coming onto course proper, kept on same pace without quickening under pressure.
Travelled keenly to the front while hanging out, held slender lead until 200 metres out, weakened under pressure.
Settled just worse than midfield, came under pressure coming onto course proper, found nothing.
Hard ridden early, soon dropped to midfield on the rail, baulked behind runners coming onto course proper, switched off stands rails inside the 300 metres but failed to quicken to feature.
Never better than midfield travelling down the centre of the track. (Bled)
Well there from stands side draw, came under pressure to hold place coming onto course proper, soon weakened.
Soon dropped to the tail-end, only went past well-beaten horses closing stages.
Soon dropped to last few, never a danger.
With leaders to the 300 metres, folded up quickly.
At rear, 3-4 wide, favoured by the fast pace, progressed steadily 300M to score.
Eased to sit behind midfield, 2 wide, benefited by the fast tempo, progressed steadily 400M for 2nd.
Hard ridden early to keep up in front of midfield, 2 wide, not suited by the fast pace, made ground 500M, ran on well for 3rd.
Midfield, 3 wide, favoured by the fast tempo, progressed steadily 400M, raced flat 100M.
Slow away, at rear, 3 wide, suited by the fast pace, made steady ground 350M.
At back, along the fence, favoured by the fast tempo, lack room 300M, ran on fairly when clear.
Hard ridden to sit in front of midfield, not suited by the fast pace, ran on ok in straight.
Pushed to share the lead in 2 wide, harmed by the fast sectionals, weakened 200M.
Hard ridden forward, harmed by the fast pace, weakened 200M.
Eased back, 2 wide, benefited by the fast tempo, lack room 400M, made minor ground when clear.
Very slow away, at rear, 2 wide, benefited by the fast pace, however lack room in straight, not fully tested.
At rear, took rail, suited by the fast tempo, ran on ok, lack room 200M.
Pushed to hold the rail and shared the lead at fast sectionals, out of fuel 350M.
Pushed to obtain box seat, harmed by the fast pace, emptied 350M.
Settled at rear, commenced to improve passing 500M, kept making ground passing 300M, came home strongly to score.
Gradually took lead in the back straight, responded well when asked for effort in the straight, finished nicely.
Travelled keenly and proved difficult to settle in the early and middle stages, settled behind midfield, fought hard entire straight, worked home well.
Pushed along at start, settled behind leaders, moved to outside the lead near 700M, one-paced in the straight.
Settled midfield on rail, kept on rail at Home Turn, one-paced.
Travelled at back, wide on straightening, gave ground in the straight, failed to run on.
Began awkwardly, raced at handy position, emptied near 250M, failed to run on.
Bumped on jumping, raced behind midfield, 5 lengths back, moved closer on turn, no clear running early in straight, finished off strongly when clear thereafter to score narrowly.
Away with them, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, reluctant to shift out early in straight, finished off well when clear final 200M, narrowly beaten. (See Racing Incidents.)
Slowly away, raced at tail, 8 lengths or so back, closer on turn, angled out early in straight, finished off very strongly to be nearest on line.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide at rear, angled out from near 550M, showed very good response early in straight, peaked near 150M, ran on evenly to the line. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began well, sent forward to race 2 wide in 2nd, same position on turn, bumped early in straight, hung on well until near final 100M flattened.
Moderately away, raced at tail, 8 lengths back, moved closer on turn, made some headway in straight without threatening.
Jumped well from gate 1, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, bumped early in straight, ran on evenly until steadied close home.
Quickly into stride, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well throughout, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed near 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide, 2 to 3 lengths back, same position on turn, made no progress in straight.
Began fairly from the widest gate, raced 3 wide with no cover in midfield, there to turn, failed to close off in straight.
Bumped start, positioned on rail at rear, there to turn, kept on evenly early in straight, peaked near 200M, weakened thereafter.
Bumped on jumping, raced 3 wide at rear, no cover after 800M, bumped and taken wider near 500M, peaked early in straight, emptied final 200M, finished last.
Began well from the widest draw, sent forward to race 2 wide in 2nd, same position on turn, kept on very well in straight to score.
Bumped start and unbalanced, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths back, there to turn, made good progress in straight to take 2nd without threatening the winner.
Began only fairly from gate 1, positioned 4 lengths back on rail, saved ground to near 550M, no daylight early in straight, finished off well when clear final 300M to get 3rd.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, 5 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, made very good progress in straight to make frame.
Jumped well, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, saved ground throughout, dipped near 650M, showed limited response after turning in, ran on one-paced. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began well from a tricky gate, raced 3 wide with no cover in midfield, moved closer from 900M, 3rd on turn, peaked early in straight, kept on evenly to the line.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 lengths back, steadied near 1200M, similar position on turn, angled out turning in, finished off evenly.
Away with them, raced 2 wide at rear, 4 lengths back, there to turn, made minor progress in straight.
Taken back from a wide gate, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, slightly improved on turn, bumped and taken wider near 500M, failed to close off in straight.
Began well from gate 12, sent forward to take the lead, headed after turning in, weakened gradually thereafter.
Average to begin, raced at rear, 5 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, found nothing in straight under hard riding.
Moderately away, positioned on rail in midfield, there to turn, emptied early in straight.
Fractious in gates and turned its head to the left when the gates opened, left a long way behind at the start and virtually took no part.
Hard ridden forward to take rail and led by 3/4L, never challenged and ran on to score comfortably by 1-3/4L.
Travelled towards the rear, 7-1/2L behind 3 wide but with cover, swung wide and closed off strongly to the line.
Bumped start, raced towards the rear, 7-3/4L behind along the rail, made ground steadily and ran on well for 3rd.
Bumped start, hard ridden forward to sit outside the lead, sat 3/4L off, one paced but kept on to the finish.
Bumped start, raced at the rear, 8-1/2L behind 2 wide, swung widest, closed off well inside final 150M.
Pushed and settled in one-off one-back position, sat 2-1/4L off the lead, kept on going to the line.
Bumped start, settled in midfield, 4-3/4L behind along the rail, one paced in the straight.
Travelled close to the tail, 6-3/4L behind 2 wide, awkward to heels at 350M, ran fairly to the line.
Bumped start, ridden to settle in behind midfield, 6-1/4L behind along the rail, kept on one paced to the line.
Bumped start, raced just in front of midfield, 3-1/4L behind along the rail, remained one paced.
Jumped fairly only, then asked to take up box-seat, sat 1-1/2L off, found no extra after 150M.
In midfield early, tried to find cover but trapped wide throughout, settled behind midfield 6L off, very one paced.
Travelled in midfield, 5L behind 2 wide, found nothing in the straight.
Settled to race in midfield, 3-3/4L behind 2 wide, raced keenly throughout, finished tailed out. Must trial.
Away with them, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, easy run to turn, finished off strongly in straight to score by a head.

Began well from gate 1, positioned a length behind the leader in 2nd, travelled well throughout, took the lead after turning in, kept on very well thereafter but just couldn't hold off the winner late.
Out in line, raced 2 wide, 6 lengths back, moved closer on turn, taken wide in straight and finished off strongly to get 3rd.
Clean jump, positioned 2 wide in midfield, 3 to 4 lengths back, same position on turn, closed off well to make frame without threatening.
Shifted in abruptly on jumping, raced at tail, 7 lengths back, last turning in, made some progress in straight.
Moderately away, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths back in 4th, there to turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Began fairly, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, headed early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Average to begin, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, failed to close off in straight. (Mucus in trachea.)

Taken back to race at tail, 8 lengths back, Inconvenienced near 1350M, slightly improved along the rail in the middle stages, 3 lengths back turning in, difficult to ride in straight and only showed limited response.

Led steadily in the first half under 7lb claimer, upped the tempo from middle stages, opened up 2Ls lead turning in, kept on strongly and raced away final 200M to score in class record time, never challenged.
Chased leaders in 3rd, pace fast from 1200M, improved to 2nd 300M out but couldn't bridge the gap on runaway winner.
Held up 6th in a fast run race, 5Ls off the leader and eventual winner 400M, stayed on mildly for distant 3rd.
Slow to begin, ended up 2nd last over 8Ls off the good pace, battled on over final 400M to take 4th without looking dangerous at any stage.
Reserved towards the rear in 8th spot, 8Ls off the good pace middle stages, on straightening failed to make appreciable ground.
Never far off in 4th, couldn't find another gear in the straight and kept grinding to the line only.

Settled just behind leader, pace fast from 1200M, held ground in the straight, faded over final 150M. (Jockey reported his mount not able to sustain its run due to leader increasing the tempo throughout the race.)
Dropped back at the start and stayed at the tail of the 10-horse field, 9Ls to make up leaving the corner, made limited progress only.
Held up midfield 5Ls off the good pace, improved wide from 600M, couldn't sustain run from 300M, no extra final stages.
Settled down behind midfield, 7Ls off the pace 400M, couldn't run on, weakened steadily passing 250M.
Jumped well, showed early speed to race prominently, bumped and took the lead after passing 300M, kept on very strongly to score.
Began well from gate 11, showed good speed to take the lead, bumped and headed after passing 300M, stayed on for 2nd. (Rider dropped right rein 50M.)
Jumped well, raced at rear on the stands rail, still 5 lengths back at 400M, finished off strongly to take 3rd, nearest on line.
Slightly slow out, raced behind midfield, 3 lengths or so back, closed off well to make frame without threatening.
Away with them, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on the stands rail, travelled well throughout, finished off evenly.
Bumped start, raced closer to the middle of the track, 2 to 3 lengths back, finished off evenly.
Fractious in gates and missed the start, gradually recovered, still 4 lengths or so back at 400M, kept on evenly to the line. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began well, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader, peaked near 250M, slightly weakened thereafter.
Began fairly, raced at rear near to the stand side, still 5 lengths back at 400M, kept on evenly thereafter. (Lame right front leg next day morning.)
Raced closer to the middle of the track, 2 lengths back, made no progress and weakened final 400M.
Away with them, raced 4 lengths behind the leader near to the stands rail, showed no response final 400M.
Bumped start, recovered to race prominently, peaked on run near 600M and gradually dropped away. (Lame right hind leg.)
Average to begin, raced a length or so back in 4th, 2 away from the stands rail, weakened gradually final 400M.
Began only fairly from gate 1, raced at rear throughout, never a threat.
Pushed forward early to settle 3rd/4th, 1 off the fence. Well placed on the turn, and was solid early in the straight. Kicked from 200m. Nabbed leader at 50m, and stayed on well late.
Eased forward early to settle around midfield. Stayed on strongly in the straight, and was making progress on the winner late.
Pushed out early to assume the lead. Still in front before peaking at 100m, and ran like a tired horse late.
Cruised forward early and settled around midfield. Looked a spent force at 300m, but found a second wind and stayed on solidly late to be a clear 4th.
Cruised forward early to settle around midfield. Styed on solidly in the straight, without ever threatening.

Lifted front feet on jumping, fairly away and settled behind midfield. Widest on the turn, but only plugged away early in the straight. Kicked and made up some ground last 100m, despite losing the stick at 50m.
Moved forward steadily early to settle midfield. Plugged away steadily in the straight, without ever threatening.
Began well and taken forward from the wide draw to sit 2nd. 1 paced in the straight and was no threat.
Dropped back early from the wide draw to sit 2nd last and slightly detached from main field. Only clear in last 150m, but only plugged away to the line under minimal urging. Jockey questioned.
Pushed forward from the wide draw, 3-4 wide no cover, before eventually settling just forward of midfield. Battled on 1 paced for the majority of the straight, before easing out at 75m.

Got head up early when taken across from the wide draw to settle forward of midfield, 1 off the fence. Came off heels at 300m for a run, but nothing came of it and went to the line tamely and was eased last 50m.
Didn't push out early before settling 3rd last. 2nd last on the turn, and made no impression in the straight.
Reluctant to stretch out early and dropped back to a clear last. Made up very little ground in the straight. Jockey questioned. Unacceptable performance.
Taken forward from the inside draw to settle 3rd/4th, on the fence. Showed no kick in the straight and wasn't pushed out the last 200m.

Jumped well from gate 1, took the lead easily, travelled comfortably throughout, kicked clear after turning in and scored easily.
Out in line, positioned 4 lengths behind the leader on rail, moved closer on turn, kept on well in straight to take 2nd.
Slightly slow out, raced 7 to 8 lengths back on rail, similar position on turn, finished off very strongly to get 3rd.
Began well, raced 2 wide, 5 lengths back, same margin back on turn, closed off well to make frame without threatening.
Moderately away, hard ridden early to race 5 to 6 lengths back on rail, same position on turn, kept on evenly in straight.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide a rear, 7 to 8 lengths back, still well back on turn, kept to inside after straightening and made some progress.
Began well from a wide draw, sent forward to race outside the leader in 2nd, 3/4L back, peaked on turn, slightly weakened in straight.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, more than 10 lengths back early, improved from 800M, 3 wide with no cover thereafter, made no progress in straight.
Crowded on jumping, raced at tail, more than 10 lengths back early, slightly improved near 700M, still 8 lengths back on turn, kept on evenly to the line.
Away with them, raced 2 wide, 6 to 7 lengths back, there to turn, failed to close off in straight.
Hampered start, positioned on rail at rear, 10 lengths or so back, last turning in, failed to close off in straight.

Jumped with them, sent forward to race 2 to 3 lengths behind the leader, peaked on turn, showed no response early in straight, eased thereafter. (Jockey reported his horse did not feel comfortable in its action.)
Hard ridden to take rail and led at advantageous slow sectionals, drifted away 300M to score with plenty in hands.
Hard ridden forward, sat outside the leader, benefited by the slow tempo, ran on strongly for 2nd.
Slow away, at back, 2 wide, not suited by the slow pace, dashed well 200M for 3rd.
Pressed forward early but trapped wide, eased back, still 3-4 wide, harmed by the slow pace, dashed well 200M despite all negative racing situation.
Failed to muster, at back along the fence, harmed by the slow pace, lack dash.
Eased back, took rail, progressed steadily to box seat, benefited by the slow tempo, weakened 200M.
Hard ridden early, failed to keep up with leaders, forced to race 3 wide from barrier 2, emptied 300M.
Settled behind leaders on rail, asked for effort near 500M, made ground passing 250M, finished strongly to score.
Slow to begin and raced at tail, mid-race moved to midfield position, kept making ground in the straight, came line solidly
Travelled wide and without cover at handy position until 500M, improved outside the lead at Home Turn, fought well in the straight, worked home nicely.
Travelled midfield, commenced to improve near 650M, battled hard and responded well in the straight.
Raced behind midfield, very wide on straightening, kept on to the line, cut on left hind cannon.
Settled behind midfield, wide on straightening, limited response in the straight.
Settled midfield on rail, kept on rail to save ground at Home Turn, under pressure but only one-paced in the straight.
Travelled behind midfield on rail, at 300M struck heels and became badly unbalanced, one-paced.
Raced at back, moved to midfield near 1000M and again moved to handy position near 550M, gave ground passing 150M.
Jumped well, settled behind leaders, near 600M lay in and became awkwardly placed, then was severely check at 450M, after that no response in the straight, failed to make impression.
Hard ridden to take lead, gave ground near 200M, failed to run on.
Urged along to race outside the lead, came under pressure and gave ground near 600M, failed to close off.
Average to begin, positioned 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, slightly improved along the rail on turn, kept to inside after straightening and finished off strongly to score.
Jumped well, sat right behind the leader on rail, easy run to turn, kept on well in straight to take 2nd.
Began well from a wide draw, unable to slot in, raced 3 wide with no cover in midfield, carried wider on turn, finished very well to take a place despite hard run.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide behind midfield, there to turn, taken wide in straight and made good progress to make frame.
Bumped on jumping, positioned on rail at rear, 7 lengths back, checked near 900M, slightly improved along the rail on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide at rear, 7 lengths back, last turning in, made good progress in straight without threatening.
Away with them, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, there to turn, finished off evenly.
Lifted front feet off the ground and lost ground on jumping, raced at tail, 8 lengths back, checked near 900M, closer on turn, finished off evenly.
Moderately away, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths back, 3 wide on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide in midfield, same position on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, there to turn, failed to close off in straight.
Fast into stride, sent forward to take the lead, enjoyed the easy lead to 400M, headed early in straight, weakened sharply thereafter.
Moderately away from gate 1, sat right behind the leader on rail, easy run to turn, kept on very well in straight to score.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 7 lengths back at rear, improved from 900M, 3 wide in 3rd on turn, kept on well in straight to take 2nd.
Taken back from gate 11, positioned on rail at rear, 7 lengths back, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after straightening and finished off very strongly to get 3rd.
Moderately away from a middle draw, unable to slot in early, sent forward thereafter to sit outside the leader in 2nd, there to turn, fought on steadily to the line.
Fast into stride, took the lead easily, travelled comfortably throughout, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed near final 150M, slightly weakened thereafter.
Average to begin, position on rail in midfield, 3 lengths back, same margin back on turn, checked near 450M, angled out early in straight, finished off evenly.
Began well from the widest draw, sent forward to race 2 wide, 1 to 2 lengths back, made contact and unbalanced near 450M, finished off evenly.
Crowded out start, raced 2 wide at rear, 6 lengths back, moved closer to midfield after 750M, carried wider near 600M, very wide with no cover on turn, finished off evenly.
Taken back from gate 9, raced at tail, 7 lengths back, hampered near 1200M, still well back on turn, 2 wide from 600M, made minor progress in straight.
Began fairly, showed no early speed, positioned on rail behind midfield, 4 to 5 lengths back, Reluctant to shift out after turning in, finished off one-paced. (Lost left front plate.)
Average to begin, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 4 to 5 lengths back, peaked on turn, kept on one-paced.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide, 2 to 3 lengths back, 3 wide with cover from 650M, showed no response in straight, (Jockey reported his horse did not feel comfortable in its action.)
In behind midfield, 6-1/2L off 2 wide, steadied on straightening, improved on inner track, won well by 1-1/4L.
Pushed to take the rail and shared lead, kept on well but could not match the winner's finishing effort.
Sent forward and raced prominently, sat 1-1/2L off but trapped wide throughout, ran on well to take 3rd.
Rolled forward to race in the box-seat, sat 2-1/2L off the lead, kept on fairly to the line.
Ridden and settled in one-off one-back position, sat 1-1/2L off the lead, kept on to the finish.
Travelled in midfield, 4L behind 2 wide, swung widest then lay in in the straight, ran on to the line.
Pushed and raced in front of midfield, 2-3/4L off 2 wide, kept on one paced to the line.
Jumped fairly only, settled in midfield, 4L behind along the rail, kept on going to the line.
Travelled towards the rear, 8-1/2L behind 2 wide, made ground and ran on.
Eased and raced towards the rear, 8-1/4L behind along the rail, saved minor ground late.
Sent forward to sit outside the lead, showed no response and was disappointing.
Slow to jump, at the back throughout, did not improve.
Reserved in midfield one off the fence, into clear 300M, kept coming under gradual acceleration to prevail by narrow margin from the unlucky runner-up.
Eased back on jumping, settled down behind midfield 5Ls off the pace along the fence, unable to obtain running 250M-100M, ran on well late just failed by a whisker. Could have won.
Jumped fairly, held 5th position just over 2Ls behind in a fast run race, driven hard to briefly lead near 100M, headed by first 2 final stages.
Dropped back to 3rd last 5-6Ls off the good pace, took a while to wind up entering straight, stayed on to go 4th near line.
Held up in midfield 3-4Ls behind leader, kept grinding to the line but well held by leaders.
Taken back to 2nd last from wide barrier, 6Ls off leader making the turn, bustled along 500M, battled steadily down the outside without serious threat.
Soon led, took them along at good pace, caught near 100M and tired.
Began awkwardly, recovered to be tracking leaders passing 900M, not quickened early straight, looks beaten already when severely hampered inside 150M.
Sluggish away on seasonal debut, raced as the back-marker 8Lls off the good pace, made some progress over final 300M but never reached contention.
Bustled along after the start to be tracking leader in a fast run race, stayed prominent and in contention until 150M, hampered 100M and faded.
From draw 11 caught 3 deep in mid-division, failed to make appreciable ground when asked early straight.
From draw 9 chased leaders in a 3-wide position without cover, dropped out badly mid-straight, eased.
Settled in midfield along the fence, travelled strongly into contention, quickened up smartly inside 300M, hit lead 150M and ran away from them for 3rd win on a trot.
Dropped back to near last, about 7Ls off the pace home turn, widest on straightening, hit the line well to claim 2nd just before line, couldn't reach runaway winner.
Taken across behind runners, settled 3rd last 7Ls off the good pace, ran on strongly between horses to go 3rd just before line. Encouraging debut.
Chased leaders in a fast run race, no match with winner's turn of foot but battled on well to just miss 3rd in blanket finish for minor honours.
Reserved behind midfield about 5Ls off the good pace, turned 3-wide back straight, on straightening stayed on without threat to the runaway winner.
Held up 2-wide in mid-division, 4Ls to make up top of the straight, kept on moderately in the run home.
Away with them, held rail position tracking leaders, ran on fairly in straight, outsprinted by rivals over final 200M.
Up with leaders but unable to slot in and caught wide no cover throughout, flattened 200M and quickly brushed aside by rivals.
Pressed leader on the outside ensuring a strong pace from 1200M, took over top of the straight, caught inside 150M, weakened rapidly late stages.
Restless in stalls, began awkwardly and lost ground, ended up last 8Ls back, ran past a couple of beaten rivals only in the straight. Never a factor.
Caught 3-wide in midfield, couldn't go on passing 300M, eased when no chance.
Led along fence, pressed by rival setting fast pace middle stages, weakened badly passing 300M. (Bled.)

Moderate start, settled not far off the lead in 5th, came to challenge entering straight, hit the front from the tiring leader over 200 metres out, won readily.
Niggled along in midfield in 6th on the rail, ran on to reach 2nd 100 metres out, never threatening.
Travelled wide from the widest gate though never far off, kept on before finding no extra nearing finish.
Settled towards the rear, quickened well inside the 200 metres, ran on to be nearest at finish.
Soon dropped well behind, trailed the field into straight, produced good late finish closing stages.
Bumped at the start, soon dropped the rear despite ridden along, remained in last few on the rail to the straight, made modest progress under hard driving in the run to the line.
Taken back from a wide gate for rails run, picked up along the rail to be just worse than midfield, kept on steadily in straight.
Soon taken back to 3-wide in midfield, came to challenge under pressure early in straight, unable to sustain effort closing stages.
Raced wide towards the rear from a wide gate, kept on same pace in straight.
Soon took up running setting a smart pace far side, held over 1L advantage rounding home bend and into the straight, swamped over 200 metres out.
Prominent from a wide gate, chased the leader to straight, dropped out tamely inside the final 250 metres.
Awkward start racing freely early stages, in last few throughout, made no impression.
Crowded after a moderate start, soon recovered to rear of midfield in 8th, kept on in home straight before fading the inside final 200 metres.
Chased leader in back straight, became 3rd and some 2L back rounding home bend, dropped away quickly after straightening.
Hard ridden forward, shared the lead in 2 wide, benefited by the slow sectionals, closed off strongly to score.
Hard ridden to keep up in midfield, 2-3 wide, harmed by the slow pace, unleashed it usual strong finishing efforts 300M.
Hard ridden to obtain box seat, blocked most straight, ran on well for 3rd.
Hard ridden to take rail and shared the lead at slow sectionals, out of fuel 200M.
Bumped badly at start, took rail at back, harmed by the slow pace, dashed strongly 400M, lack room 200M.
Hard ridden to hold the rail in midfield, lack room 4-2, dashed well despite not suited by the slow pace.
Pushed forward, 2 wide just off the leaders, suited by the slow tempo, weakened 100M.
Very slow away, at back, 2 wide, not suited by the slow tempo, dashed well 250M.
At back, trapped 3-4 wide, harmed by the slow pace, little dash 200M.
Midfield, trapped 3 wide, made early move 600M to take advantages of the slow tempo, but soon emptied 400M.
Eased back, hung out badly, very green, never competitive.
Very slow away, detached and tailed out.
Ridden along to take lead, travelled comfortably, ran on and worked home unchallenged.
Urged to settle outside the lead, fought hard entire straight, finished well.
Raced behind leaders on rail, asked for effort passing 450M, battled hard in the straight.
Stumbled at start, settled behind midfield on rail, made some ground in the straight.
Settled midfield, one-paced in the straight. Next day sore right front fetlock and stiff and restricted action.
Raced at rear, wide on straightening, hung in and proved difficult to shift out in the early straight, failed to make impression.
Travelled keenly in the early and middle stages, crowded for room near 1600M, raced behind midfield, gave ground in the straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, improved on turn, hampered near 650M, finished off very strongly in straight to score by a neck.
Jumped with them, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, same position on turn, hit the front 300M, kept on very well but just couldn't hold off the winner late.
Away with them, raced 2 wide in midfield early, found rail near 900M, saved ground on turn, kept to inside early in straight, angled out near 300M, finished off well to take 3rd.
Moderately away from a wide draw, raced 3 wide with no cover behind midfield in the early stages, slotted into a 2 wide spot on turn, hampered near 650M, closed off well to make frame.
Slowly away, positioned on rail at rear, made home turn awkwardly, raced tight near 350M, made some headway in straight without threatening.
Jumped well, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, difficult to settle near 1000M, saved ground on turn, caught in traffic after turning in, made some progress when clear final 150M.
Bumped on jumping, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 to 4 lengths back, finished off evenly.
Bumped start, sent forward to take the lead, enjoyed the easy lead to turn, headed after passing 300M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Began well, sent forward to race 2 wide in 2nd, there to turn, peaked early in straight, one-paced to the line.
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned 3 lengths or so back on rail, crowded near 900M, saved ground on turn, angled out early in straight, failed to make any progress.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, still 7 lengths back on turn, finished off one-paced.
Began awkwardly, raced 2 wide at rear, unbalanced near 1100M, slightly improved on turn, raced tight near 350M, showed no response thereafter.
Slowly away, positioned on rail at rear, 6 lengths back on turn, showed no response in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Raced at rear throughout, never competitive.

Settled just worse than midfield racing 3-wide down the back straight, circled the field round the home bend and the widest runner turning in, quickened well to hit the front passing the 200 metres, held on well to the line.

Settled at the back, switched wide in last few down back straight, commenced move coming onto home bend, quickened well under pressure after straightening near the centre of the track, just failed to get up on line.
Held up in midfield on the rail, carried backward behind runners approaching the home bend, shaken up on straightening, finished off the race well.

Steadied first bend, travelled wide without cover in midfield down back straight, renewed effort after on home turn, quickened under pressure to hold some chance early in straight, unable to sustain effort closing stages.

Raced very wide around the first bend, reached 3rd while 3-wide early in back straight improving to 2nd 800M out and disputing the lead into straight, hit the front briefly over 200M out but unable to sustain effort late.
Settled at the back after beginning from the widest gate, remained well behind to straight, saved ground turning in, ran on under pressure to be nearest at finish.

Given reminders after beginning from a wide gate, circled the field round the first bend and sustained headway to hit the front 1000 metres out, led on the rail until finding no extra inside the final 300 metres.
Began well, settled just off the pace for cover on the rail, left flat-footed coming onto home bend, kept on steadily without quickening.
Ridden prominently, settled just over 2L off the pace down far side, inconvenienced on straightening, kept on at the one pace without quickening. (Lame next day)
Began well from a wide draw, ridden forward to dispute lead turning into back straight, remained prominent to home straight, faded under pressure. (Lame next day)
Sluggish at start, soon ridden to rear of midfield, inconvenienced behind runners and shuffled back to last few early in back straight, one-paced in the run home. (Bled)
Settled well behind racing wide down the back straight, never seen with a chance.
Vied for lead, hit the front briefly turning into back straight, ceded advantage half-way down back straight, dropped out tamely in the run home.
Prominent early, steadied to midfield early in back straight, came under pressure to hold position rounding home bend, folded up quickly.
Sent forward and shared lead on the rail, pulled away from on straightening and kept on to record an imposing win.
Travelled in front of midfield, 3-1/4L behind along the rail, kept on nicely but never threatened the impressive winner.
Raced close to the tail, 8-1/2L behind 2 wide, made ground and ran on well to the line.
Asked but settled to race in midfield, 5L behind 2 wide, ran on fairly and just beaten for 3rd on the line.
Settled to race in behind midfield, 6-1/4L behind 2 wide, kept on one paced to the line.
Sent forward and shared the lead in the 2 wide position, kept on till 300M when couldn't find extra.
Raced at the rear, 10-1/4L behind 3 wide but with cover, only past tiring runners.
Steadied after a good jump, raced in front of midfield, 4-1/2L behind wide but with cover, swung wide and did not put up a challenge. (Trainer and rider questioned)
Settled in behind midfield initially, pressured to improve along the back straight, found nothing.
Rolled forward to race in the box-seat, sat 2-1/4L off, asked from 600M out, not competitive.
Sent forward, settled in one-off one-back position, dropped off from on straightening.
Raced prominently but trapped wide throughout, lost ground from rounding home turn. Must trial.
Jumped well from gate 1, positioned on rail behind midfield, 3 lengths back, saved ground on turn, finished off very strongly in straight to score.
Average to begin, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well throughout, kept on very well in straight, just couldn't hold off the winner late.
Jumped with them, sent forward to race 2 wide in 2nd, same position on turn, stayed on evenly in straight to take 3rd.
Away with them, checked early, raced 2 wide, 4 lengths back, same margin back on turn, made very good progress in straight to make frame, nearest on line.
Quickly into stride, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, easy run on turn, fought on steadily in straight without threatening.
Average to begin, raced 3 wide with cover, 4 to 5 lengths back, there to turn, taken wide in straight and made some headway without threatening.
Began very awkwardly, raced at tail, 5 lengths back, saved ground throughout, made reasonable progress in straight.
Moderately away, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths back, same position on turn, peaked early in straight, stayed on one-pace to the line.
Began very awkwardly, raced at tail, 5 lengths back, improved from 550M, very wide turning in, failed to close off in straight. (Lost both front plates.)
Out in line, raced 3 wide with no cover in midfield, there to turn, peaked early in straight, failed to close off in straight. (Mucus in trachea.)
Jumped with them, unable to slot in, raced 4 wide with no cover throughout, emptied early in straight when hard run took effect. (Blood in trachea.) (See Racing Incidents.)
Tracked leaders in a steadily run race, inclined to lay out 750M, got split 400M, moved up quickly to take the lead at 150M, kept finding to hold pursuers at bay.
Jumped evenly, never far off the pace and saved ground along the fence, held up behind leader 400M to 200M, challenged winner up the rail final stages but held.
Towards the rear along the 2-path, 4Ls off leader 400M, awkwardly placed early straight, chased strongly once into clear 250M, went 3rd just before line.
Positively ridden, crossed to the rail before turn sharing the lead at steady pace, collared by winner inside 200M, failed to hang on but kept battling to the finish, lost 3rd last stride.
Unable to slot in from draw 10, caught 4-wide no cover chasing leaders, on straightening kept on mildly for 5th off a tough run.
Dropped back to the rear, brought wide 550M, ran on well down outside making ground final 200M but was unable to reel in leaders.
Slowly away, held up at the rear 4-5Ls off the steady pace, saved ground on the inside but failed to make appreciable ground passing 400M.
From widest draw crossed to race just outside leader, kept on until 200M, was outsprinted from there.

Up with leaders early then restrained for cover, crowded for room 750M and lost ground further 600M, just plugged to the line, no impression. (Jockey: failed to run on due to crowding in mid-stages. / Mucus.)
From draw 5 ended up in a 3-wide midfield spot on settling, held ground in the straight, no real impact.
Pushed up to be prominent outside leaders, remained wide no cover to straight, swamped by rivals passing 300M, weakened out of contention. (Jockey dropped whip 200M.)
Restrained near the rear, 3-wide making the turn for home, just over 3Ls to make up turning in but did nothing in the straight and failed to improve.
Jumped well, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well throughout, kept on very well in straight to score easily.
Began awkwardly, raced 3 wide with cover, 3 lengths or so back, 2 wide on turn, taken wide in straight and finished off very strongly to take 2nd.
Moderately away, positioned 1-1/2L behind the leader on rail, easy run on turn, angled out near 300M, finished off evenly to get 3rd.
Began awkwardly, raced 2 wide at rear, 5 to 6 lengths back, similar position on turn, taken wide in straight and made very good progress to make frame.
Slightly slow out, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths back, same position on turn, kept on evenly in straight.
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, 3 lengths back, saved ground on turn, kept on evenly to the line.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, still 6 lengths back on turn, made some headway in straight without threatening.
Fast into stride, sat outside to the leader, shared lead turning in, peaked near 300M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Taken back from gate 12, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, 5 lengths back, slightly improved on turn, finished off one-paced.
Jumped with them, raced 3 wide, 2 lengths back, similar position on turn, weakened gradually in straight.
Average to begin, sent forward to race prominently, 3 wide with no cover throughout, emptied early in straight when hard run took effect.
Crowded early, raced 2 wide, 4 lengths back, awkwardly placed and unbalanced near 1000M, found rail on turn, made no progress in straight, eased final 150M.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear, 6 lengths or so back, peaked on turn, showed no response in straight, eased final 200M.
Away with them, steadied off heels early, unable to slot in, raced wide with no cover throughout, emptied early in straight, finished tailed out.

Allowed to go forward, lead and set a reasonable tempo. Pulled a couple of lengths clear at 250m, and stayed on well. Running like a tired horse late, but was far enough clear to hold off late challengers.

Steadied off heels on jumping and eased back towards the rear of the field. Still towards the rear and had a wall of horses in front on the turn. Weaved through the field and stayed on strongly. Running down the winner late.
Cruised forward early to settle midfield. Came wider on the turn, stayed on strongly late and was making ground slowly on 1st and 2nd.

Bumped and unbalanced early and dropped back to be a clear last, 2L from the closest horse. Wider on the turn, when progressing, before going to the extreme outside rail in the straight. Ran strongly late. Jockey questioned.
Taken forward from the wide draw to settle 2nd. Slightly keen and lay out in middle stages. Stayed on steadily in the straight, but running 1 paced late.
Eased back early and settled a clear 2nd last. Came wider in the straight looking for runs and stayed on solidly late.
Pushed forward early to be handily placed in 3rd. Loomed up at 300m for a run, but gave nothing and went tamely to the line.
Dropped back early from the wide draw to settle worse than midfield. Wanted to hang out from the 300m, then shifted in under the whip last 200m and was never fully pushed out.
Taken up to settle forward of midfield, 1 off the fence. Came off heels at 250m, but was already a beaten horse and giving ground.
Dropped back from the wide draw to settle towards the rear of the field. Picked up a couple that were easing late, but never in the race.
Taken up to be handily placed 4th/5th, but stuck 3 wide with no cover. Battled on 1 paced early in the straight, before being eased out from the 150m.
Bumped and unbalanced on jumping and eased forward to settle around midfield. Never responded early in the straight, and eased last 200m.
Settled forward of midfield early. Never responded in the straight, was eased from 175m and dropped out rapidly.
Began awkwardly, but recovered well and pushed aggressively to be 4th/5th on the rail. Nothing in the tank in the straight and not pushed out last 200m.
