Taken back from the widest gate, quickened well inside the final 150 metres to snatch victory close to home.

Broke well from a middle gate to share early lead, soon taken back for cover but to no avail, raced 3-wide without cover in 5th over 2L back rounding home bend, hit the front under pressure over 150M out but outsprinted close to home.
Settled wide in rear of midfield, in similar position turning into home straight, ran on to be nearest at finish.
Midfield early, shuffled backward at the 1000 metres, renewed effort and saved ground rounding home bend, ran on under pressure to reach half-length 2nd briefly 100 metres out, no extra.

Given reminders to hold position amongst leaders early, soon dropped to over 2L back in 6th on first bend, shuffled further back rounding home bend, produced good impression in home straight but hampered near finish.
Jumped fairly, led or disputed lead on the rail from the 800 metres, driven 1L clear after straightening, unable to sustain effort and headed 150 metres out.
Slightly slow out, ridden and improved steadily to close-up position just behind the leaders at the Rock, kept on before finding no extra inside final 200 metres.
Settled wide in last few from a wide gate, went wider into the straight, produced good late impression closing stages.
Moderate start, never better than midfield, dropped towards the rear onto home bend, kept on steadily along inside rail, hampered late. (Lame next day)
Settled in last few, saved ground on the inside turning for home, made no impression.

Recovered steadily from a moderate start, sustained headway on the outside down back straight, joined the leader going up the Rock, unable to sustain effort after straightening, dropped away quickly passing the 200 metres.
Driven to lead early but gradually drifting backward to 3rd at the Rock, folded up quickly after straightening.
Pushed to take rail and led at good pace, made all.
Eased back, on the fence, pace good, dashed well 250M, just missed by a narrow margin.
Eased to sit in midfield along the rails, pace good, just held ground in straight.
Eased to sit behind midfield, 2 wide, raced keenly, pace good, lack room 300M, dashed well when clear.
Box seat, pace good, out of fuel 150M.
Eased back, 2-3 wide, pace good, little dash 200M.
Eased to sit in midfield along the fence, pace good, no turn of foot.
Midfield, trapped 3-4 wide, pace good, no progress.
Hard ridden forward, trapped 3 wide throughout, pace good, emptied 200M.
Eased back, 2 wide, pace good, no dash.
At rear, pace good, no progress.
Very slow away, commenced to buck for some distance approaching and passing the winning post on the first occasion, losing a considerable amount of ground, never competitive.
Began only fairly, raced at box seat, made ground passing 150M, finished strongly to score.
Raced behind leaders, quickened near 50M, worked home solidly.
At start was hampered, settled midfield, gradually made ground passing 200M, came home nicely.
Slow to begin, raced at back on rail, wide on straightening, made up some nice late ground.
Ridden along to take lead, under pressure and gave some ground passing 100M.
Fast out and raced outside the lead, fought hard in the straight, gave ground near 50M.
Settled midfield, passing 250M shifted in to obtain clear running, finished OK.
Throughout the race travelled wide and without cover at handy position, gave ground passing 100M, bled after race and lame right front next day.
On jumping was crowded for room, travelled behind midfield on rail, passing final 100M was unable to obtain clear running, not fully tested.
Throughout the race travelled wide and without cover at midfield position, widest on straightening, limited response in the straight.
Taken back at start, widest on straightening, never in it.
Began only fairly then settled at rear, always back.

Began fairly, positioned on rail in midfield, 3 lengths or so back, saved ground on turn, showed very good response early in straight, took the lead 200M, kept on well to hold off the late challengers to score narrowly.

Taken back from the widest draw, outpaced and became detached from the field in the early stages, gradually recovered, 5 lengths or so back on turn, finished off very strongly, just missed by a head. (See Racing Incidents.)

Taken back from a wide draw, positioned on rail at rear, 5 to 6 lengths back, gradually moved closer in the middle stages, 4 lengths back on turn, angled out early in straight and finished off well to take 3rd.
Away with them, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well throughout, headed near 200M, kept on evenly to the line.
Taken back to race at rear, 6 lengths back, same margin back to turn, made some progress in straight without threatening.

Moderately away from a wide draw, unable to slot in, raced 4 wide, 2 lengths back early, 3 wide in the middle stages but still without cover, slightly improved from 450M, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide in midfield, similar position to turn, angled out from 450M, failed to close off in straight.
Taken back from gate 9, raced 2 to 3 wide, 5 lengths back, similar positon on turn, very wide turning in, finished off evenly.
Average to begin, sat 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, showed no response early in straight, dropped off gradually from 150M.
Away with them, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, peaked on turn, weakened early in straight, eased final 100M. (Blood in trachea.)
Fast into stride, sent forward to sit outside the leader in 2nd, got cover from near 700M, peaked on turn, emptied early in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped with them, raced prominently but wide, shared lead for a short distance after 800M, peaked on turn, emptied early in straight, dropped off gradually thereafter.
Quickly into stride, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, easy run to turn, finished off strongly in straight to score narrowly.
Bumped on jumping, raced 2 to 3 wide in midfield, there to turn, finished off very strongly in straight to take 2nd, just missed by narrow margin.
Jumped well from the widest draw, sent forward to take the lead, enjoyed the easy lead throughout, kept on well in straight but just couldn't hold off the challengers late.
Slightly slow out, recovered to race 2 wide in 2nd, same position on turn, kept on evenly to the line.
Clean jump, positioned on rail behind midfield, crowded near 550M, saved ground on turn, angled out early in straight and made some progress without threatening. (See Racing Incidents.)
Bumped start, unable to slot in, raced 4 wide without cover behind midfield, found cover on turn, taken very wide in straight and made some progress.
Bumped shortly after start, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground to near 400M, finished off one-paced.
Average to begin, bumped near 1000M, made the turn awkwardly, raced 2 wide, 1-3/4L back, angled out from 450M, kept on well early in straight, peaked near 100M, weakened thereafter.
Began fairly, raced at tail, 6 lengths or so back, still last on turn, made no real progress in straight. (Lost left hind plate.)
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned on rail at rear, 5 to 6 lengths back on turn, finished off one-paced.
Taken back from gate 11, raced 2 to 3 wide with cover at rear, 5 lengths or so back, kept on evenly early in straight, in traffic final 100M, not able to test properly.
Bumped shortly after start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, awkwardly placed rounding the home turn, showed no response in straight, finished last.
Raced in behind midfield, 4-1/2L behind 2 wide, swung wide and ran on strongly to score by 1-1/2L.
Settled to race in midfield, stayed 3L behind 2 wide, battled on nicely to take 2nd.
Niggled along and raced in the box-seat, sat 2L off the lead, led from 250M until headed at 50M, ran on well.
Travelled in behind midfield, 4-3/4L behind 2 wide, swung widest and improved steadily to the line.
Taken back and raced towards the tail, 5-1/2L behind along the rail, held up till 200M, made ground thereafter.
Settled to race in midfield, 3-1/2L behind along the rail, kept on to the line but only one paced.
Jumped well, then eased to be at the rear, 6-1/2L behind along the rail, dashed at 200M and ran on.
Awkward start, ridden to race in one-off one-back position, sat 1-1/2L off, showed nothing.
Pushed to race in the lead, stayed 2 wide throughout, emptied passing 200M.
Sent forward to take the rail and shared lead, weakened badly near 150M.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear, 5 lengths back on turn, taken very wide in straight and finished off very strongly to score.
Jumped well, took the lead easily, travelled comfortably throughout, kept on very well in straight but just couldn't hold off the winner late.

Taken back from gate 10, raced 2 wide at rear, unbalanced near 800M, 4 lengths back on turn, made very good progress in straight to take 3rd, nearest on line. (Sustained a cut to the left front coronary band.)
Average to begin, raced 3 wide without cover in midfield in the early stages, found cover on turn, kept on well in straight to make frame. (Not able to be ridden out near the finish.)
Average to begin, sent forward to sit a length behind the leader on rail, bumped near 550M, saved ground on turn, fought on steadily.
Fast into stride, showed early speed to sit outside the leader in 2nd, peaked after turning in, ran on evenly to the line.
Began only fairly, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Began only fairly, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after straightening and finished off evenly. (Lost left front plate.)
Slowly away, positioned on rail, 3 to 4 lengths back, saved ground on turn, made some progress early in straight, peaked near 100M, ran on one-paced.
Moderately away from the widest draw, sent forward to take the 1-out 1-back position, bumped and unbalanced near 550M, wider on turn, peaked on run 150M, weakened thereafter.
Away with them, raced 3 wide with cover, 3 to 4 lengths back, similar position on turn, emptied early in straight.
Slowly away, raced at tail throughout, never competitive.
Settled down 2-wide in midfield, had over 5Ls to make up passing 400M, motored home strongly, edged clear 50M to win two in a row.
Began well from draw 1, 5th on settling never far off from leader, gave a sustained run on straightening, found the line well but winner too strong final 150M.
Slotted into a position behind midfield, 6Ls off the fast pace home turn, finished off well to take 3rd just before line but couldn't trouble winner.
Crossed to the lead 1300M, led steadily before quickening up 700M, kept trying turning home, outgunned final 100M, lost placing last stride. (Jockey questioned re his riding from 700M.)
Hugged the rail from draw 2, chased leader on settling, pace fast from 700M, held ground and failed to improve position in the straight.
Taken back from wide draw, 7-8Ls off the pace in 2nd last spot, brought wide 400M and made some ground down the outside without threatening.
Held up in mid-division 5-6Ls off the pace, failed to accelerate turning home, no threat to leaders.
Switched off to race near the rear, 8Ls off the fast pace home turn, ran on mildly passing a few beaten rivals, no impression on leaders.
Chased pace in 4th first half, shuffled back to midfield 500M from home, couldn't come on in straight, failed to make up ground.
Raced keenly when being steadied looking for cover, caught wide from 1400M, gradually improved to track the pace 700M, couldn't quicken early straight, weakened 200M.
Chased the pace along the 2-path, struggled to keep up when pace quickened 700M, weakened away on straightening.
Steadied and taken in behind runners, became detached from the field 1000M, never involved.

Settled just better than midfield on the rail, saved ground rounding home turn, ran on under pressure between runners to hit the front close to home. (Questioned for improved performance)
Held up just off the pace in 3rd on the rail, remained similar turning into straight, hit the front under pressure 200 metres out, led until headed over 50 metres out.
Shared early pace down the centre of back straight, crossed to lead on the rail and steadied pace from the 1100 metres, led until headed passing the 400 metres, just held on for 3rd.

Jumped awkwardly from a wide gate settling at the back, circled field when pace slackened from the 1100 metres, widest runner into straight when 2.5L 6th turning in, kept on steadily without quickening.

Moderate start, settled just worse than midfield, raced awkwardly when pace slackened before taking closer order around home bend, switched wide for a run after straightening, fought on steadily without threatening.
Held narrow lead early, taken one back to 2nd 1100 metres out, renewed effort to hit the front again passing the 400 metres, but unable to sustain effort and swamped inside the 200 metres.

Settled just better than midfield in 5th some 4L back, became 7th when pace slackened on the bend, switched out for a clear run when within 3L of pace 300 metres out, kept on steadily without quickening.
Broke well, soon taken back to midfield on the rail, inconvenienced in general bunching coming onto home bend, fought on steadily to the line.
Settled in midfield, suffered from slow pace and lost position coming onto home bend, dropped to last few turning for home, kept on well past beaten horses.
Settled not far off in 4th, failed to quicken under pressure early in straight.
Settled in last few, inconvenienced coming out of back straight, wide around home bend, made no impression in the straight.
Settled well behind, trailed the field into straight, made modest progress past beaten horses down near the centre of the track.

Soon dropped to last few despite niggled along, remained towards the rear to the straight including inconvenienced coming onto home bend, kept on steadily without quickening. (Questioned for disappointing performance)

Settled in rear from the widest gate, took closer order to 11th passing the 1200 metres, circled the field from the 1000 metres to reach 1L 3rd approaching the home turn, folded up quickly after straightening.
Midfield, along the fence, benefited by the fast pace, progressed steadily 300M to score.
Hard ridden forward, box seat, held up 4-2 and checked severely, made good ground when clear.
Hard ridden forward to cross, sat just off the leader, harmed by the fast pace, bumped 400M, ran on well for 3rd.
Hard ridden to keep up in midfield, 2 wide, favoured by the fast tempo, progressed steadily 300M.
Hard ridden to take rail and lead, clocked fast sectionals, hung on until 200M weakened.
Behind midfield on the rails, benefited by the fast pace, lack room 300M, made some ground in final stages.
Eased back, 2 wide, benefited by the fast tempo, made steady ground 250M.
Eased to sit behind midfield, favoured by the fast tempo, just held ground in straight.
Pushed forward, 2 wide, checked 1200M, not suited by the fast pace, soon emptied 300M.
Struggled to keep up at rear, 3-4 wide, suited by the fast pace, made minor ground 200M.
Eased back, trapped 3-4 wide, suited by the fast tempo, ran on fairly.
Eased back, 2 wide, favoured by the fast tempo, no dash.
Slow away, at rear along the fence, suited by the fast pace, no progress.
Travelled nicely to lead, asked for effort on straightening, over the concluding stages shifted out under pressure, finished strongly to win.
Settled midfield, commenced to improve at Home Turn, ran on and worked home solidly, just missed by SH.
Raced at box seat, fought hard in the straight, came home nicely.
Travelled behind midfield, improved near 650M, finished well to the line.
Settled at handy position, tried to improve near 550M, limited response in the straight.
Taken back at start, widest on straightening, one-paced in the straight.
Began well, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground to near 500M, finished off well to score.

Jumped well, sent forward to race prominently, a length behind the leader in 2nd, travelled well throughout, took the lead after turning in, kept on well thereafter but couldn't hold off the winner final 100M.
Moderately away from a wide draw, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 7 lengths back, improved from near 600M, very wide turning in, finished off well in straight to take 3rd.

Average to begin, positioned on rail behind midfield, 7 lengths back, saved ground to 600M, no daylight early in straight, then crowded near 300M, finished off very strongly when clear thereafter to be nearest on line.
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned 4 lengths back on rail in 4th, moved closer along the rail on turn, finished off evenly.

Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, difficult to settle after passing 1500M then blundered when checked off heels near 1450M, still well back on turn, kept to inside after straightening and finished off very strongly.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide at rear, awkwardly placed near 1000M, taken wide turning in, made minor progress in straight without threatening.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide better than midfield, angled out from 600M, bumped and unbalanced after passing 300M, finished off one-paced. (Had a small wound to the outside of the right hind cannon.)
Fractious in the barriers, slowest away, raced at rear, 10 lengths back on rail, moved slightly closer on turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Away with them, positioned on rail behind midfield, 6 lengths back, saved ground to near 600M, failed to close off in straight.
Taken back from a tricky gate, raced 2 wide at rear, 10 lengths back, still well back on turn, taken widest in straight, failed to make any progress.
Jumped well from the widest draw, sent forward to race prominently, took the lead near 1500M, travelled comfortably in the middle stages, headed after turning in, dropped off gradually thereafter.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide, 2 to 3 lengths back, same position on turn, emptied early in straight, eased final 150M. (Blood in trachea.)
Average to begin, raced 2 wide in midfield, angled out near 700M, very wide turning in, showed no progress, hampered near 250M, emptied and eased thereafter.
Jumped well from a middle draw, took the lead easily, travelled comfortably throughout, kicked clear after turning in and scored very easily.
Began well, sat 1-3/4L behind the leader on rail, easy run on turn, kept on well in straight to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.
Clean jump, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, finished off well to get 3rd without threating.
Away with them, unable to slot in, raced wide with no cover in midfield early, 3 wide with cover on turn, finished off well to make frame without threatening.
Slowly away, positioned 5 lengths back on rail, same margin back on turn, kept to inside after straightening and made some progress, useful debut.
Moderately away from a wide draw, sent forward to race outside the leader in 2nd, there to turn, peaked early in straight, slightly weakened thereafter.
Got head up early when being steadied back from the widest draw, raced at tail, 6 to 7 lengths back, saved ground on turn, made some progress in straight.
Out in line, raced 2 wide, 2 to 3 lengths back, similar position on turn, kept on evenly early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Began awkwardly, raced 2 wide, 5 to 6 lengths back at rear, travelled keenly near 1000M, similar position on turn, made no real progress in straight.
Crowdedoutshortly after start,raced at rear, 7 lengths back, difficult to settle and checked off heels near 700M, same margin back on turn, made no real progress in straight.
Jumped well, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 to 4 lengths back on turn, kept on one-paced in straight.
Average to begin, raced 3 wide with cover, 5 lengths back, same margin back on turn, made no progress in straight.
Slightly slow out from gate 11, unable to slot in, travelled wide and without cover in midfield, same position on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Taken back from gate 9, raced 3 wide with cover, 6 to 7 lengths back, there to turn, showed no response in straight, finished last.
Settled to race in the box-seat, sat 1-3/4L off, kept on going and held off a late challenge to score by a short-head.
In front of midfield, 3-1/4L behind along the rail, battled on strongly once cleared from 300M, missed by a short-head.
Sent forward to race outside the lead, sat 1L off, kept on very well to the finish to take 3rd.
Awkward start and lost ground, raced near the rear, 7-1/4L behind 2 wide, improved steadily and ran on well to the line.
Sent forward to take the rail and led by about 1L, maintained lead until near 200M, one paced but ran on.
Rolled forward and settled to race in front of midfield, 4L off 2 wide, got tired passing 200M.
Travelled in midfield, 5L behind along the rail, one paced in the straight but ran on.
Crowded at start and lost ground, raced towards the rear, 7-1/2L behind along the rail, kept on one paced to the line.
Taken back to be at the tail, 9-1/4L behind 2 wide, made ground and ran on fairly.
Settled in one-off one-back position, sat 2-1/2L off the lead, failed to keep up after 350M.
In behind midfield initially but wide and raced keenly, improved after 800M before giving ground in the straight.
Raced just in behind midfield, 5-3/4L behind 2 wide, found nothing.
Began well from gate 1, sat 1-1/2 length behind the leader on rail, easy run on turn, bumped and unbalanced early in straight, finished off very well to score.

Jumped well from gate 9, unable to slot in, raced very wide with no cover early, taken back 1000M to get cover, 2w, 1-2L back on turn, showed good response and took the lead early in straight, headed near 150M, stayed on for 2nd.
Began well, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, angled out from near 500M, no daylight early in straight, made good progress when clear thereafter to take 3rd.
Began very awkwardly and lost ground, raced 5 lengths back on rail, moved closer along the rail on turn, caught in traffic early in straight, finished off well when clear thereafter to make frame.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, 7 lengths back, improved from 800M, very wide turning in, made minor progress in straight.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced 3 wide behind midfield, improved on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked near 150M, weakened gradually thereafter.

Away with them, raced 2 wide behind midfield early, awkwardly placed close to the heels near 750M, 4 lengths or so back turning in, no daylight early in straight, made some progress when clear thereafter.
Out in line, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 lengths back, steadied off heels near 800M, same margin back on turn, finished off evenly. (Blood in trachea.)
Fractious in gates and slowest away, raced 7 lengths back at rear, still last turning in, reluctant to shift out early in straight, made no real progress thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began fairly, raced 2 wide at rear, 5 lengths or so back, 3 wide on turn, finished off one-paced. (Lost right hind plate.)
Moderately away, sent forward to take the lead, headed after passing 300M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Jumped with them, showed good speed to race in 2nd, half length behind, same position on turn, bumped and unbalanced early in straight, weakened gradually from 300M.
Average to begin, unable to slot in, raced wide with no cover in 3rd, there to turn, emptied early in straight when hard run took toll.

Switched off to last after the start, over 10Ls off the pace early stages, driven wide passing 500M, quickened up strongly, dashed to the lead near 100M and charged away to win the Derby impressively.

Chased leaders early before settling down in 7th spot 4-5Ls back in midfield, into clear 450M, picked up well early straight to issue serious challenge, had every chance but no match for winner final 150M.
Taken back behind runners, settled 2nd last 8Ls off the good pace, peeled out wide 600M, kept running on well for a late-closing 3rd.
Tracked leaders in a race run at solid tempo, headed the chase from 400M, kept fighting on to the line, outsprinted by first 3 late stages.
Showed his pace and crossed to the lead 1600M, set good pace in middle sections, led down the straight, fought hard but unable to hold off first four over final 150M. Gap to rest.
Shifted across behind runners from draw 14, assumed a 3-wide spot in midfield 5-6Ls off the pace, loomed a chance early straight but outstayed by leaders final 200M.
Jumped well from inside draw, shuffled back to race in midfield 5Ls behind leader, had no clear run 300M but not going the pace to challenge leaders when clear.
Began well, restrained to a position behind midfield 6Ls away on settling, worked home fairly on straightening, no threat to leaders.
Held up towards the rear along the fence, shuffled back to last 400M, plodded past a few weakening rivals but never reached contention.
Pushed forward early to take the rail spot then restrained behind leaders 3-4Ls away, held ground early straight, run ended passing 200M.
Pressed forward from wide draw, never far away from leaders in 4th, bustled along 500M, battled on steadily early straight but no extra passing 200M. (Jockey : his mount didn't see out the distance.)
Began only fairly, settled towards the rear 7Ls behind leader, driven wide 600M, gave only brief response, weakened noticeably 250M.
Caught wide making the first turn, pressed on to race outside leader, struggled to hold his spot 550M, weakened away in the straight.
In midfield, caught 3-wide no cover from 1400M, weakened from 400M to finish tailed out after a difficult trip.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 5 lengths back, similar position on turn, taken wide in straight and finished off very strongly to score narrowly.
Jumped with them, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, there to turn, hit the front near 200M, kept on very well thereafter but just couldn't hold off the winner late.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, 9 lengths back, last turning in, taken widest in straight and finished off very strongly to be nearest on line.
Crowdedoutshortly after start,positioned on rail in midfield, easy run on turn, had difficulty obtaining clear run near 200M, awkwardly placed close heels final 50M, not able to be properly tested.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, kept on well in straight until peaking in the last 50M.
Crowdedoutshortly after start,sent forward to sit 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, easy run on turn, took the lead early in straight, headed and peaked near 200M, slightly weakened thereafter.
Began fairly from a wide draw, raced wide with cover at rear, 6 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, made some progress in straight without threatening.
Jumped well, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, headed early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Fast into stride, sent forward to race outside the leader in 2nd, difficult to settle when being steadied after 1000M, peaked after turning in, weakened gradually thereafter.

Average to begin, raced 2 wide at rear, 6 lengths back, found rail on turn, angled out early in straight, only showed limited progress. (Jockey reported his horse did not feel comfortable in its action in straight.)
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned 5 lengths back on rail, saved ground on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Slightly slow out, unable to slot in, raced wide with no cover at rear, slightly improved on turn, peaked early in straight, emptied final 200M, finished last.
Taken up early to share the lead, on the fence. Clear leader and pulled clear early in the straight. Peaked late, but was too far clear and held on to win.
Eased out to settle around midfield. Struggled to get a run early in the straight, before coming around off heels 250m. Showed good turn of foot in last 150m, and was quickly getting winner late.
Leapt out of the barrier and slowly away, before settling around midfield. Awkward on heels 1000m. Wider on the turn and stayed on solidly, but slightly 1 paced.
Bumped on jumping but recovered well to be early leader, before easing back to settle in 3rd. Battled on solidly without threatening in the straight.
Dropped back from the wide draw to settle last. Ran on well early in the straight. Came off heels 150m and stayed on solidly late.
Eased across from the wide draw to share the lead. Bumped 400m. Battled on 1 paced in the straight.
Eased away early to settle forward of midfield. Stuck 3 wide no cover from 800m. Bumped 400m. Awkward on heels 150m, but was already fading out at that stage.
Eased back early to settle worse than midfield. Taken out and raced wide with no cover from 700m. 1 paced in the straight. Jockey questioned.
Eased back to the rear of the field early. Didn't run on in the straight. Jockey questioned.
Pushed forward from the inside draw to settle 3rd/4th, on the fence. Never responded in the straight and eased out late.
Wide no cover in the back straight and pushed forward to eventually lead at 700m. Not much left in the tank late and dropped out quickly in the straight.
Dropped back early to sit at the rear of the field. Didn't respond in the straight, and not pushed hard late.
Slow to begin and got back, before pushing forward to settle just behind midfield. Never responded in the straight.

Settled in midfield, took off at the 800 metres to hit the front 700 metres out, kicked 2L clear under pressure early in straight, held on to the line.

Moderate start, pulled forward from 6th early stages to be up with the pace down home straight the first time, quickened with the pace to hold position passing the Rock, fought on steadily without threatening.
Travelled wide towards the rear, took closer order going up the Rock, remained wide entering home straight, ran on under pressure to be nearest at finish.

Prominent, shifted to the rail for cover entering home straight the first time, dropped back to 3L 5th when pace quickened near the Rock, came under pressure rounding home bend, fought on steadily without threatening.

Pressed forward from a wide gate, settled just over 2L back in 4th in middle stages, commenced move 3-wide leaving the Rock disputing 2nd under pressure entering home straight, kept on same pace without quickening.
Soon taken back to last few, commenced move leaving the Rock, continued to circle the field on home bend, widest runner turning in, ran on steadily to be nearest at finish.
Settled in last few, came to challenge under pressure rounding home bend, fought on steadily to be nearest at finish.
Taken well back from the widest gate, commenced move round the field on home bend, widest runner turning in, ran on past well-beaten horses.
Made the running setting a slow pace from the 1600 metres, headed 700 metres out, 2L 4th under pressure rounding home bend, faded gradually in the straight.
Travelled keenly and mainly in midfield, checked about 500 metres out, one-paced in home straight.

Awkward start, soon ridden to midfield, slightly worse when shuffled backward in slow pace down the home straight the first time, dropped to tail-end when pace quickened passing the Rock, found nothing.

Prominently early, shuffled back in slow pace down the home straight the first time, some 3L off in 5th on the rail on far side, left flat-footed when pace quickened at the Rock, failed to make any impression in the run home.
Hard ridden to occupy box seat, pace good, closed off strongly to score.
Hard ridden to take rail and led at good pace, hung on well until 50M, just missed by a narrow margin.
Eased at start, took rail at back, pace good, dashed well 250M for 3rd.
Hard ridden forward, 1 out 1 back, pace good, made minor ground 200M.
Eased at start, took rail, pace good, progressed steadily 200M.
Slow away, pushed along the rail to obtain a midfield spot, pace good, made steady ground 250M, lack room 100M.
Pushed forward, sat outside the leader, pace good, ran on until 100M weakened.
Eased back, trapped 3 wide, pace good, progressed steadily in straight.
Eased to sit behind midfield, 2 wide, pace good, made steady ground 300M, lack room 100M.
At rear, took rail, pace good, never improved.
At back, 2 wide, pace good, no progress.
Eased to rear, trapped 3 wide, pace good, no dash.
Ridden along to settle outside the lead, held its position when been challenged in the back straight, travelled strongly to score in the straight.
Slow to begin, raced at rear then moved to behind midfield in the back straight, quickened passing 100M, worked home solidly.
Taken back at start, settled behind midfield, wide on straightening, responded well in the straight.
Taken back at start, raced at back, moved to midfield in the back straight, made up some nice late ground.
Settled midfield on rail, kept on rail on straightening, raced tight passing 200M, finished nicely.
Began awkwardly, raced at box seat, asked for effort near 350M, one-paced.
Began only fairly, mid-race moved to outside the lead but three wide without cover in back straight, gave ground passing 100M, rider questioned.
Began awkwardly then urged along to take lead, one-paced in the straight.
Raced behind leaders, niggled and under pressure in the back straight, weakened near 200M.
Settled midfield, travelled keenly in middle stages, no response in the straight.
Slow to begin, always back, never in it.
Moderate start, travelled wide and without cover until near 800M at handy position, failed to run on.
Jumped well from a wide draw, sent forward to take the lead, easy lead on turn, fought offstiff challenge to hold on.
Moderately away from the widest draw, sent forward to race 2 wide in 2nd, same position on turn, kept on very well in straight but always held by the winner.
Began well, positioned 3 lengths or so back on rail, saved ground on turn, angled out early in straight and finished off strongly to be nearest on line.
Jumped well, sat 1-1/2L behind the leader on rail, easy run on turn, kept on evenly in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 7 lengths back at tail, similar position on turn, taken wide in straight and finished off very strongly. (See Racing Incidents.)
Bumped on jumping, raced 2 wide in midfield, 4 lengths or so back, angled out near 500M, finished off evenly in straight.
Began fairly, positioned 6 lengths back on rail, there to turn, made some progress in straight without threatening.
Moderately away, positioned 2 wide, 2 to 3 lengths back, similar position on turn, peaked early in straight, finished off one-paced.
Bumped start, raced at tail, 7 lengths back, still well back on turn, taken wide in straight and made minor progress.
Taken back from gate 9, raced 3 wide with no cover behind midfield, carried wider on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Jumped with them, crowded early, raced 2 wide at rear, 6 lengths back, moved slightly closer on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Began fairly from gate 1, positioned on rail behind midfield, 4 lengths back, same margin back on turn, showed no response in straight, finished last.
Quickly into stride, showed early speed to take the early lead, allowed the rival to cross near 800M, sat comfortably in 2nd thereafter, finished off well in straight to score.
Moderately away from a middle draw, sent forward to race prominently, took the lead near 800M, enjoyed the easy lead on turn, kept on well in straight but could not hold off the winner final 100M.
Jumped well from a wide draw, unable to slot in, positioned 3 wide, 2 to 3 lengths back, no cover from 700M, kept on well in straight to take 3rd.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide behind midfield, hampered 1050M, travelled keenly near 950M, similar position on turn, taken wide in straight and made very good progress to make frame.
Steadied soon after start, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, difficult to settle passing 1000m when checked off heels, same position on turn, made minor progress in straight without threatening.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide, 2 to 3 lengths back, bumped near 1050M, similar position on turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Average to begin, positioned 3 to 4 lengths back on rail, saved ground on turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Jumped well, sent forward to race prominently in 3rd, 2 wide throughout, peaked early in straight, slightly weakened thereafter.
Began well from gate 1, positioned 2 to 3 lengths back on rail, bumped and unbalanced near 1050M, saved ground on turn, peaked on run near 150M, weakened gradually thereafter.

Slowly away, positioned on rail at rear, checked off heels and unbalanced near 1000M, travelled keenly thereafter, still 6 lengths back on turn, failed to close off in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back to race at tail, 7 to 8 lengths back, still well back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear throughout, never a threat. (Bled)
Taken in at start, then raced in behind midfield, 5L off 2 wide, battled on strongly and scored by a short-head.
Settled to race outside the lead, 1/2L off, kept on very well but not enough to hold off the late challenge, just missed.
Rolled forward to race in the box-seat, sat 2-1/4L off, ran on well to the line to take 3rd.
Slow to muster, settled to race just in front of midfield, 3-3/4L behind along the rail, ran on fairly.
Failed to muster and at the tail initially, improved to race outside the lead, 3/4L off but wide, one paced to the line.
Taken back and raced at the rear, 7-3/4L behind 2 wide, made ground steadily and ran on okay.
Ridden along but at the tail initially, trapped wide until 700M when taken to 2 wide in front of midfield, one paced in the straight but ran on.
Eased at start, settled to race just behind midfield, 4-1/2L behind 3 wide, one paced only.
Rolled forward, took the rail and led by 1/2L, kept on till 200M and then weakened badly.
Slow to jump, raced towards the rear, 6-1/4L behind 2 wide, did not threaten.
Badly crowded at start, raced in behind midfield, 5-1/2L behind along the rail, made no impression.
One-off one-back initially, dropped to midfield after 800M, hung in throughout and not properly tested. Must trial.
Jumped with them, positioned 2 wide, 2 to 3 lengths back, improved from near 600M, 3 wide with cover on turn, finished off very well in straight to score by a head.
Out in line, positioned 2 wide in midfield, improved from 700M, shared lead on turn, kept on well in straight but couldn't hold off the winner late.
Began well, took the lead easily, travelled well throughout, kept on well early in straight, headed near final 100M, just stayed on for 3rd.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, 8 lengths back, improved from 750M, 3 wide, 4 lengths back on turn, finished off very strongly in straight to be nearest on line.
Moderately away from barrier 11, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 5 to 6 lengths back, moved closer on turn, taken wide in straight and made some headway without threatening the first few.
Began awkwardly, positioned 2 lengths or so back on rail, easy run throughout, kept on evenly in straight.
Away with them, raced 2 wide, 1 to 2 lengths back, checked near 600M, similar position on turn, kept on evenly in straight.

Taken back from gate 9, raced 2 wide at rear, 7 lengths or so back, travel keenly for some distance after 850M, slightly improved from 600M, still 5 lengths back on turn, showed limited response in straight.
Average to begin, bumped early, positioned 4 lengths back on rail, saved ground throughout, failed to close off in straight.
Moderately away, sent forward to sit outside to the leader in 2nd, there to turn, peaked early in straight and weakened gradually thereafter.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, 8 to 9 lengths back, still well back on turn, made no progress in straight.
Jumped with them, raced at rear, 6 to 7 lengths back on rail, there to turn, showed no response in straight, finished last.
Handily placed behind leaders in a race run at solid tempo, took lead 150M, raced away for a comfortable win.
Began well from draw 1, taken on by rival in the lead, kept on well to line but couldn't match winner's pace final 150M.

Away well but couldn't go with the pace and shuffled back to near the rear, had to navigate through traffic mid-straight, did best work final 150M, got up for 3rd near line. (Jockey questioned re his ride in straight.)
Tracked leaders along the fence, stuck to inside on straightening, stayed on moderately for 4th in a bunched finish for minor placing.
Held up 2-wide in midfield, bustled along home turn, only battled away to the line for 5th in a bunched finish for minor placing, no threat to first two.
Restrained after the start, crossed to rail and improved to a midfield position middle stage, kept on mildly in straight, no impression on first two. (Jockey lost whip 150M.)
Taken back to the rear 6Ls off the pace, brought widest into straight, stayed on without serious threat.
Began only fairly, travelled 3-wide in midfield, awkwardly placed behind weakening rivals nearing home straight, into clear 250M making minor progress.
Dropped back from wide barrier, settled down in 10th 4-5Ls off the good pace, stayed on fairly final 300M, no threat to leaders.
Pressed forward from widest barrier, crossed to race outside leader 700M, couldn't go on inside 200M, weakened away.
Caught 4-wide from draw 10, unable to slot in and lost cover from 700M, weakened 300M after difficult trip.
Chased leaders 3-wide, dropped out rapidly entering straight.

Ridden to lead, obtained rails run passing the 1000 metres, kicked over 2L clear early in straight, held on under pressure.
Settled in rear, took closer order along the rail coming onto home bend, saved ground entering home straight, ran on well under pressure to be nearest at finish.
Never far off on the rail, just over 2L back in 3rd into the straight, fought on steadily without threatening.
Close up early, settled just over 2L back in 4th to home straight, gradually faded.
Soon outpaced, detached until joining the main body of the field coming onto home bend, sustained progress down home straight, did best work late.
Settled wide in rear, came under pressure turning into straight, ran on steadily down the centre of the track without threatening.
Moderate start, niggled along in midfield in 7th, in similar position into straight, ran home one-paced. (Questioned for disappointing performance)
Settled wide just worse than midfield, gained closer to 4L 5th approaching home bend, in similar position turning in, found nothing.
Ridden prominently on the rail, soon weakened after straightening.
Travelled wide in rear of midfield, came under pressure entering home straight, made no impression after straightening. (Lame next day)
Always in last few, dropped out under pressure in straight.
Broke well, dropped steadily towards the rear by home bend, trailed the field into the straight, no further impression.
Pushed forward, shared the lead at fast sectionals, drifted away easily 200M to score.
Settled in front, ran on strongly to the line for 2nd.
Eased back, benefited by the fast pace, progressed steadily 250M for 3rd.
Hard ridden to share the lead at fast sectionals, ran on well until 150M weakened.
Hard ridden to keep up with the field, raced greenly, suited by the fast tempo, however held up badly, on heels 250M, made steady ground.
Pushed forward, not suited by the fast pace, emptied 200M.
Hard ridden at back, favoured by the fast tempo, made steady ground.
Slow away, at rear, suited by the fast pace, however lack room in final furlong, made some ground.
Pushed to sit just off the leaders, not suited by the fast sectionals, weakened 200M.
At back, benefited by the fast tempo, no progress.
Hard ridden to share the lead at fast pace, soon out of fuel 500M.
Eased to sit just off the leaders, emptied 300M.
Slow away, never better than midfield.
Hard ridden to keep up with the fast pace, dropped off 400M.
Sent forward, sat inside the lead along the rail, 1/2L off, ran on okay, held off the others to score by a neck.
Bumped start and lost ground, in behind midfield 7L off along the rail, improved steadily and closed off well for 2nd.
Taken back and raced at the rear, 7-3/4L behind 2 wide, finished off strongly inside 200M to take 3rd.
Pushed forward, led by 1/2L in a 2 wide position, headed near 100M, ran on but awkward to heels on the line.
Among leaders early stages. 2Ls off lead making turn. Kept on well but unable to draw closer in the straight.
Jumped only fair and improved to settle on fence at midfield. 5Ls off the leader rounding home turn. Ran on well in the straight.
Off slowly and raced in rear section. Switched out home turn and rallied in the straight to be closest at finish.
Raced 4 wide among leaders early. Eased off from the pace after 1000M and slotted in to be 2-wide making turn. 3Ls off the leader home turn. Kept same pace in the straight.
Settled 2-wide and no worse than midfield. Ran on fairly in the straight.
Behind midfield, no progress.
Eased back, made minor ground.
Eased back, ran on fairly.
Midfield, weakened in straight.
At rear, never competitive.
Jumped well, sat 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, moved closer in the middle stages, took the lead near 700M, kept on well in straight to score by a neck.
Began well from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, slightly improved on turn, crowded early in straight, then raced in restricted room, closed off well when clear final 200M to take 2nd.
Away with them, raced 2 wide, 3 to 4 lengths back, moved closer in the middle stages, angled out near 500M, kept on well in straight to take 3rd.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, angled out from 500M, finished off evenly in straight to make frame.
Slowly away, positioned on rail behind midfield, slightly improved along the rail on turn, no daylight early in straight, finished off evenly when clear thereafter.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced wide with cover at rear, moved closer on turn, still 4 to 5 lengths back, very wide turning in, made good progress in straight without threatening.
Began fairly, sent forward to race in outside the leader in 2nd, 3 wide turning, kept on well early in straight, slightly weakened from 150M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back to race 7 to 8 lengths back on rail at rear, saved ground on turn, but still 3 to 4 lengths back, angled out early in straight and finished off evenly.
Out in line, unable to slot in, raced 3 wide with no cover behind midfield, moved closer in the middle stages, 3 lengths back on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide behind midfield, angled out near 550M, very wide turning in, failed to close off in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide at rear, 8 lengths back, closer on turn but still 5 lengths back, very wide turning in, failed to close off in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped well from barrier 12, sent forward to take the lead, headed near 800M, peaked on turn, emptied early in straight and eased, unacceptable performance.
Raced at tail throughout, never competitive.
Moderately away from a tricky gate, sent forward to take the lead, enjoyed the easy lead throughout, kicked clear after turning in and scored.
Moderately away from the widest draw, raced 2 wide in 2nd, same position on turn, kept on well in straight to get 2nd.
Average to begin, showed no early speed, positioned on rail at tail, angled out near 650M and slightly improved, taken wide in straight and finished off strongly to take 3rd.
Crowded out start, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground throughout, angled out after turning in, finished off evenly to make frame.
Bumped on jumping, sat 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, easy run on turn, finished off evenly. (Saddle shifted in straight.)
Began well, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 5 lengths back, slightly improved on turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Average to begin, positioned on rail at rear, 5 to 6 lengths back, saved ground on turn, kept on evenly to the line.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide at rear, 7 lengths or so back, there to turn, taken widest in straight and passed the tired ones.
Jumped with them, positioned 2 wide in midfield, similar position on turn, raced tight near 500M, failed to close off in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Crowded on jumping, raced at tail, 8 lengths back, still well back on turn, finished off one-paced.
Bumped start, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths back, travelled well to turn, showed no response in straight and gradually dropped away, unacceptable performance. (See Racing Incidents.)
Sent forward to take the rail and led by 1/2L, ran on to score impressively by 6L despite laying in badly in straight.
Slotted into midfield, sat 2-3/4L behind 3 wide but with cover, made inroad and kept on well to take 2nd.
Pushed to sit outside the lead in a 2 wide position, sat about 1/2L off, ran on okay to take 3rd.
Settled to race in just behind midfield, 3-1/4L behind 2 wide, made good ground and kept on well to the line.
Sent forward to race prominently, sat about 1L off the lead, ran on till flattened just after 150M.
Asked to sit in one-off one-back position, sat 1-3/4L off the lead, kept on one paced to the line.
Began fairly only, raced towards the rear, 4-1/2L behind along the rail, ran on fairly to the line.
Taken back to be at the rear, 6-1/2L behind along the rail, awkward to heels on straightening, improved slightly.
Settled to race close to the rear, 5L behind but wide and without cover, swung widest and was mostly one paced.
Bumped start, then asked to take up the box-seat, sat 1-1/2L off, dropped off gradually in the straight.
Raced towards the rear, 4-3/4L behind 3 wide with cover, eased out approaching 100M.
Slow to jump, recovered to sit in midfield, 3L behind along the rail, hung out at turn, run ended upon straightening.

Jumped with them, sent forward to race prominently on rail, took the lead near 700M, travelled well throughout, kept on well in straight to hold off the rival and scored. (Sustained a minor wound to left hind coronet.)
Began well from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, finished off very well to take 2nd.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide in midfield, angled out near 550M, made some headway in straight to take 3rd without threatening the first two.
Jumped well from a wide draw, sent forward to race prominently, 3 wide with no cover early, 2 wide on turn, kept on evenly in straight.
Average to begin, positioned on rail at rear, 5 to 6 lengths back, similar position on turn, made reasonable progress in straight without threatening.
Away with them, raced 2 wide at rear, 5 to 6 lengths back, there to turn, made minor progress in straight without threatening.
Moderately away, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, awkwardly placed near 600M, 4 lengths back on turn, kept on evenly to the line.
Began awkwardly, raced wide with cover at rear, still well back on turn, finished off one-paced in straight.
Moderately away from a wide draw, sent forward to race prominently, sat outside the leader on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter. (Blood in trachea.)
Average to begin, sat a length behind the leader on rail, same position on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Stumbled start, raced 4 wide behind midfield, no cover throughout, failed to close off in straight.
Out in line, unable to slot in, raced 4 wide behind midfield early, peaked on turn, emptied early in straight, finished last.
Soon crossed to the stands' rail chasing the pace, cruised past leader 300M, drew further clear when driven, won in dominant fashion.
Held up in mid-division, stayed on moderately to go 2nd near line but never any threat to the runaway winner.
Pressed forward, led from 800M at good pace, couldn't hold off the impressive winner inside 300M, fought on under pressure, lost 2nd near line.
Towards the rear over 5Ls behind leader, closed off well from 300M but momentarily held up 200M, ran on again to the line, just failed to make it to the podium.
Moved up to chase the pace, tried hard final 400M but lacked the necessary kick, faded final stages.
Along the stands' rail never far off from leaders, finished off one-paced, effort petered out late.
Began awkwardly, no clear run 300M, picked up fairly when clear, made limited headway.
Travelled behind midfield 4-5Ls behind leader, gave brief response passing 400M, held ground from 200M.
Reserved in midfield, 4Ls off the pace 400M, held ground in the run home.
Settled in 5th spot just over 2Ls behind leader, couldn't quicken 400M, only plodded home. (Blood in trachea.)
Not hurried after the jump, settled near rear 6Ls off the pace, only battled away over final 400M, never in the reckoning.
Slow to begin and always near the rear, failed to run on passing 400M, never in the picture.
Close up behind leaders early stages, scrubbed along to hold position midway, weakened noticeably inside 400M.
Raced towards the center of track, no cover throughout, couldn't go on passing 400M, quickly dropped out.
Average to begin, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, there to turn, finished off very well to score.
Moderately away from a wide draw, raced 2 wide in midfield, improved from 600M, 3 wide turning in, finished off well to take 2nd, narrowly beaten.
Fast into stride, race prominently in 2nd, same position on turn, kept on well in straight but couldn't hold off the first two in the final stages.
Moderately away from the widest draw, sent forward to take the lead, found rail near 1000M, travelled well on turn, headed near 300M, stayed on evenly for 4th.
Jumped with them, positioned 6 lengths back on rail, angled out near 550M, made some progress in straight without threatening.

Slightly slow out and bumped, raced at tail, 7 to 8 lengths back, still well back on turn, finished off strongly in straight to be nearest on line, never a threat to the first few. (Lame left front leg next day.)
Bumped start, sent forward to take the rail, sat a length behind the leader, easy run on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Slowly away, positioned on rail behind midfield, 4 to 5 lengths back, same position on turn, made no progress in straight.
Began well, positioned on rail in midfield, 3 lengths back, same margin back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Away with them, raced 2 wide at rear, 6 lengths or so back, carried wider on turn, showed no response in straight, finished last.

Placing: PU
Comment: Jumped well, ridden forward before breaking down passing 1500M and pulled up.
3-4 wide in the back straight before eventually assuming the lead at 900m. Took command in the straight and had too much in the tank. Went to the line under hands and heels late.
Crowded on jumping and cruised across to settle midfield. Ridden for luck in the straight, and weaved through the field. Just held onto 2nd in a bob on the line.
Dropped back from the wide draw to sit at the rear of the field. Came widest in the straight. Good turn of foot last 200m, and almost stole 2nd on the line.
Crowded on jumping and eased forward to settle around midfield. Stayed on solidly in the straight, and just run over the top of for 3rd late.
Taken up to be handily placed 3rd/4th. Hampered 250m, but recovered to go to the line solidly late.
Taken forward before eventually settling around midfield. 1 paced early in straight. Checked off heels 250m. Recovered late and stayed on well.
Cruised forward to be early leader. Didn't respond in the straight and dropped out quickly last 200m. Jockey and trainer questioned. Unacceptable performance.
Dropped back early to settle at the rear of the field. Wider in the straight, but only plugged to the line 1 paced.
Cruised forward to be handily placed 3rd/4th. 1 paced in straight. Eased late.
Settled midfield early. Stayed on OK early in the straight, but peaked 200m and not pushed out late.
Only eased away early to eventually settle behind midfield. Plugged away 1 paced and no threat in the straight.
Dropped back from the wide draw to settle last. Struggled to run on and only picked up a couple of slow ones late.
Settled at the rear of the field early. Never improved.
Pressed forward early and settled forward of midfield, 3 wide no cover. Checked off heels and eased out from the 250m. Vet- Lame near fore.

Slightly slow out, settled in rear of midfield on the rail, shaken up rounding home bend, saved ground turning in, ran on well to snatch victory near the line.
Settled some 3L back in 4th, commenced move from the 800 metres gaining narrow advantage after straightening, only to be caught close home.
Slightly slow out, held up in forward of midfield on the rail, came under pressure leaving the Rock, saved ground for 3L 4th turning for home, finished off race nicely despite crowded 100 metres out.
Broke well, gradually took up running and obtained rails run 1200 metres out, led until headed upon straightening, swamped for a placing near the line.
Awkward at start losing considerable ground, trailed the field to the home bend, saved ground turning into straight, ran on well but forced to check near finish.
Settled at the back from a wide gate, went wide into straight, produced strong late run inside the final 200 metres.
Began well, settled 2L off the pace in 3rd on the rail, came under pressure to hold place rounding home bend, kept on until swamped close to home.
Settled towards the rear from a wide gate, given reminders rounding home bend, made modest headway without quickening in the straight.

Pressed forward from the widest gate, closer up before travelling wide in forward of midfield just over 3L back in 5th or 6th down back straight, made no impression in the run home. (Tactic questioned)
Soon dropped to midfield despite reminders, yielded ground from rounding home bend, crowded after straightening and ran home one-paced.
Niggled at early, taken back towards the rear but remained wide throughout, yielded ground from rounding home bend. (Questioned for disappointing performance - lame next day)
Jumped fairly, travelled in 1L 2nd to halfway, gave ground from rounding home bend. (Bled)
Hard ridden to keep up in midfield, 2 wide, benefited by the fast tempo, dashed strongly 300M to score.
Hard ridden to hold the rail in midfield, favoured by the fast pace, lack room 400M, progressed steadily for 2nd.
Eased back, 2 wide, benefited by the fast tempo, lack room 4-2, progressed steadily for 3rd.
Hard ridden forward, 2 wide just off the leader, harmed by the fast pace, ran on until 100M weakened.
Eased back, took rail, suited by the fast pace, checked badly 550M, blocked most straight, kept making steady ground.
Hard ridden to take rail and led at fast sectionals, hung on well until 150M weakened.
Very slow away, at rear, 2-3 wide, benefited by the fast tempo, made steady ground 250M.
Eased at start, 2-3 wide, favoured by the fast pace, lack room 4-2, made steady ground.
Trapped 3 wide throughout in midfield, held ground in straight.
Box seat, harmed by the fast sectionals, weakened 250M, lack room 100M.
Settled in front, 2 wide, not suited by the fast tempo, out of fuel 200M.
Pushed forward, trapped 3 wide throughout, harmed by the fast pace, emptied 250M, on heels 100M.
Jumped well to settle behind leaders on rail, improved on straightening, quickened passing 150M, scored unchallenged.
Fast out, settled outside the lead, asked for effort on straightening, finished solidly.
Raced behind midfield on rail, improved on rail at Home Turn to save ground, ran on and worked home solidly.
Settled behind midfield, travelled keenly and checked near 600M, commenced to improve near 400M, made up some nice late ground.
Ridden to settle behind leaders, asked for effort passing 500M, fought hard entire straight.
Jumped nicely, urged along to take lead, gave ground near 50M.
Taken back at start, tried to improve at Home Turn, made some ground in the concluding stages.
Taken back at start, one-paced in the straight.
Raced at back on rail, one-paced when asked for effort.
Travelled wide and without cover in midfield, wide on straightening, on response in the straight.
Raced behind midfield, widest on straightening, no response in the straight.
Checked after start, always detached, never competitive.
Jumped well, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths back, there to turn, angled out from near 500M, finished off well to score by a neck.
Fast into stride, took the lead easily, travelled comfortably throughout, kept on well in straight but couldn't hold off the winner final 100M.
Began only fairly, positioned on rail behind midfield, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after straightening and finished off strongly to take 3rd.
Began well from gate 1, sat 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, kept on evenly to the line.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced wide with cover at rear, 6 to 7 lengths back, similar position on turn, no clear running near 200M, made some headway when clear thereafter.
Crowded on jumping, raced at tail, 7 to 8 lengths back, still well back on turn, made good progress in straight without threatening.
Away with them, raced 2 wide at rear early, found rail near 700M, saved ground on turn, angled out early in straight and finished off evenly.
Taken back to race at rear, 7 lengths back on rail, same margin back on turn, finished off evenly.
Bumped start and unbalanced, raced 3 wide without cover behind midfield early, 2 wide on turn, finished off one-paced.
Jumped well from a wide draw, unable to slot in, raced wide and without cover throughout, 5 lengths back, finished off one-paced in straight.
Bumped start and unbalanced, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, failed to close off in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Moderately away from a wide draw, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter. (Irregular heart rhythm.)
Clean jump, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, kept on well in straight to score.
Began well, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths back, same position on turn, kept on well in straight to take 2nd, bumped and unbalanced close home.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide in midfield, angled out from near 500M, made good progress after turning in to take a place, bumped and unbalanced close home.
Jumped well, sent forward to race 2 wide in 2nd, there to turn, kept on well in straight, just missed 3rd on line.
Bumped on jumping, positioned on rail behind midfield, 4 lengths back, saved ground to near 450M, made good progress early in straight, hampered near final 100M, missed frame close home.
Taken back to race 2 wide behind midfield, 4 lengths or so back, improved from 500M, made minor progress in straight without threatening.

Moderately away, positioned 2 to 3 lengths back on rail, brushed the rail near 600M, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after straightening, made minor progress before badly hampered after passing final 100M.
Jumped well from a tricky gate, taken back to race at rear, 7 lengths back, improved on turn, taken wide in straight but made no real progress.
Jumped well from gate 1, sat a length behind the leader on rail, there to turn, kept on evenly early in straight, checked near final 100M, weakened thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Raced at tail throughout, never competitive.
Moderately away from a wide draw, sent forward to race prominently, trapped 3 wide and without cover throughout, emptied early in straight when hard run took effect.
Crowded shortly after the start, at rear and detached until near 650M, continued well and held off rivals to score.
Raced in behind midfield, 3-3/4L behind 2 wide, switched out in the straight, closed off strongly to miss by a head.
Travelled in about midfield, sat 2-1/2L behind 2 wide, ran on well in the straight to take 3rd.
Sent forward to take the rail and led by about a neck, headed passing 100M but continued to the line.
Raced in front of midfield, 2L behind 3 wide and no cover from near 600M, switched wide and closed off fairly.
Sent forward, prominent but wide, improved to race outside lead prior to 600M turn, kept on one paced to the line.
Rolled forward to race in the box-seat, sat 1-3/4L off, one paced but ran on to the line.
Jumped only fairly, taken back to be near the tail, 5-1/2L behind 2-3 wide, swung wide, made minor ground.
Sent forward and sat outside the lead until 600M when another improved, kept on until passing 200M.
Raced in just behind midfield, 3-1/2L behind along the rail, one paced and weakened late. (Blood in trachea)
Hard ridden to be in midfield but trapped very wide throughout, showed nothing and eased passing 150M.
Jumped well, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 lengths or so back, improved from near 400M, finished off very well to score with some in tank.
Began well, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths back, there to turn, made good progress in straight to take 2nd.
Jumped well from gate 1, sat a length behind the leader on rail, easy run on turn, took the lead early in straight, kept on well but couldn't hold off the first two late.
Moderately away, sent forward to race 2 wide in 2nd, there to turn, kept on well early in straight, raced tight near 150M, slightly weakened thereafter.
Taken back from a tricky draw, positioned on rail at rear, 5 lengths back, same margin back on turn, made some progress in straight without threatening.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide, 5 lengths back, there to turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Taken back from a wide barrier, raced 2 wide at rear, 6 to 7 lengths back, taken widest after turning in and made minor progress.
Average to begin, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well throughout, peaked and headed early in straight, slightly weakened thereafter.
Jumped with them, unable to slot in, trapped 3 wide in midfield, carried wider turning in, finished off one-paced in straight.
Moderately away, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, kept on evenly early in straight, awkwardly placed close heels close home, not able to be ridden out.
Hampered on jumping, positioned on rail at rear, 6 to 7 lengths back, there to turn, kept to inside after straightening, failed to make any progress.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, 10 lengths back, detached from field on turn, eased early in straight.
Dropped back to near the rear early stages, moved closer to leaders along the 3-path from 800M, quickened to lead 250M and raced away for a strong win.
Settled down in 8th behind midfield, finished off honestly to go 2nd 100M, no threat to runaway winner.
Began awkwardly, reined in to be 11th, switched 4-wide 700M to go forward, stayed on to claim 3rd but no impression on winner.
Guided to the fence chasing leaders early stages, shuffled back to midfield halfway, stayed on fairly on straightening.
Away with them from draw 1, reserved in midfield along the fence, got shuffled back to the rear halfway, shifted in under pressure 250M then got held up, ran on again towards the finish.
Raced in midfield 3-wide, no cover from 1300M strolled to race outside leader, fought on one paced in straight.
Taken back to last early stages, brought wide on straightening, passed a few down outside of track but never likely.
Shared lead early stages then tracked leader from 1100M, rails run straightening, only plugged away to the line.
Jumped on terms, moved up to be 5th on settling, failed to come on when driven out passing 350M.
Sent forward, crossed to the lead 1100M, led a good gallop to straight, weakened away 250M. (Mucus.)
Towards the rear, just over 4Ls off the pace 400M, on heels of weakening rivals from 150M and no clear run to the line. Not tested.
Chased leaders along the 2-path, bustled along home turn to keep up, no extra 250M, dropped out to last. (Lame RF leg.)
