Ridden to lead, kicked over 2L clear midway down the straight, just held on to the line.
Taken back about 3L off the pace and for rails run, saved ground turning in, fought on well to just fail to get up on line.
Checked at start dropping to last few, gained closer rounding home bend, ran on to be nearest at finish.
Moderate start, settled just worse the midfield, races fiercely around the bend, shifted out for a run entering the straight, produced good late impression closing stages.
Amongst leaders, settled one out one back coming into home bend, in similar position turning into the straight, one paced before finding no extra closing stages.
Slow out, shifted onto the rail shortly after, remained in last few turning in, switched out for a run turning in, ran on past well-beaten horses down the centre of the straight.
Ridden along to hold prominent position, 3-wide without cover rounding home bend, faded under pressure closing stages. (Tactic questioned)
Ridden along to join the rear of the leading group some 4L off the pace, switched out for a run upon straightening, one-paced under pressure in the run to the line.
Missed the break badly losing considerable ground, trailed the field into straight, saved ground on the rail turning in, ran on to be nearest at finish.
Soon in rear, remained in rear into the straight, finished off the race well down the center of the track.
Soon driven forward to one back in 3rd on the rail, baulked for a run in straight until the 200 metres made no further impression. (Tactic questioned)
Settled in midfield from a wide draw, in similar position turning in, ran home one-paced.
Driven forward from a wide gate to join the leaders, came under pressure to challenge rounding home bend, kept on before fading inside the final 200 metres.
Eased to sit in midfield, 2-3 wide, benefited by the fast pace, progressed steadily 300M to score.
Settled in prominent spot, ran on well to the line for 2nd.
Pushed to keep up with the pace just behind midfield, 2-3 wide, progressed steadily 300M for 3rd.
Eased to rear, 2-3 wide, benefited by the fast tempo, blocked most straight, made steady ground.
Eased back, trapped 3-4 wide, suited by the fast pace, progressed steadily 350M, run ended 100M.
Pushed to hold the rail in front of midfield, held ground in straight.
Pushed to keep up in midfield on the fence, favoured by the fast pace, ran on ok in straight, checked 200M.
Hard ridden forward, trapped 3 wide, out of fuel 250M.
Hard ridden forward to cross in front, led at fast sectionals, hung on well until 100M weakened.
At back along the fence, benefited by the fast pace, made some ground 250M, lack room 100M.
Very awkward away, midfield, trapped 3 wide, no progress in straight.
Bumped start, eased to rear, benefited by the fast pace, no dash.
Bumped start, hard ridden forward, not suited by the fast tempo, emptied 350M.
Raced at handy position on rail, commenced to improve near 400M, gradually made ground in the straight, finished strongly to score.
Taken back at start, widest on straightening, made up some nice late ground.
Pushed to share lead on rail, ran on in the straight, finished nicely.
Travelled behind leaders, made some ground passing 150M, came home well.
Settled midfield on rail, kept improving on rail at Home Turn and in the straight, finished OK.
Began awkwardly then taken back, lay in throughout race, gained some ground final 100M.
Throughout the race travelled wide and without cover, gave ground near 200M.
Took lead at one-off position, pushed hard but weakened passing 200M.
Settled midfield, no response when under pressure, failed to run on.
Raced at handy position, no response in the straight.
Began very awkwardly, always detached, must trial.
Jumped with them, raced prominently, trapped 3 wide and without cover throughout, took the lead after turning in, kept on very well and scored, impressive debut.
Fast into stride, sent forward to take the lead, shared the lead with rival on turn, headed early in straight, stay on very well to take 2rd.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 3 wide at rear, 6 lengths back, taken widest turning in, finished off very strongly in straight to take 3rd, nearest on line.
Jumped with them, positioned on rail behind midfield, saved ground on turn, no clear running early in straight, made some headway when clear thereafter to make frame.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide at rear, 6 lengths back, same margin back on turn, taken wide in straight and made very good progress to be nearest on line.
Average to begin, sent forward to race prominently, shared the lead on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened slightly thereafter.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, 4 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Began awkwardly and crowded, positioned on rail at rear, 6 lengths back, saved ground on turn, made minor progress in straight.

Bumped start, travelled keenly early, hampered near 1000M, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, similar position on turn, failed to close off in straight, raced tight close home. (Lost left front plate.)
Jumped well, positioned 2 wide, 1-1/2L back, there to turn, finished off one-paced in straight.
Began fairly from gate 1, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, failed to quicken under pressure in straight.
Away with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 lengths back, there to turn, weakened gradually in straight.
Jumped well from a wide draw, travelled keenly early, raced very wide with no cover in 3rd, lost position on turn, gave ground in straight.
Taken back from the a wide draw, raced 2 wide at rear, 4 lengths back on turn, emptied early in straight, finished tailed out.
Bumped on jumping, raced 2 wide, 3 lengths back, travelled well throughout, finished off strongly in straight to score.
Jumped well, raced in 2nd, 2 lengths behind the leader, easy run on turn, took the lead near 300M, kept on well but couldn't hold off the winner final 50M.
Away with them, raced 3 wide in midfield, no cover throughout, closed off well to take 3rd without threatening the first two.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide in midfield, 4 lengths or so back on turn, made some headway in straight to make frame.
Bumped start, raced behind midfield, 5 to 6 lengths back, 3 wide with cover on turn, made some progress in straight.
Fast into stride, sent forward to take the lead, bumped near 1000M, led by 2 lengths on turn, headed near 300M, slightly weakened thereafter.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, 10 lengths back, still 7 lengths back on turn, taken widest in straight and made minor progress.
Began fairly, positioned 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, failed to quicken under pressure in straight. (Lost right hind plate.)
Bumped on jumping, raced 2 wide at rear, there to turn, finished off one-paced in straight.
Bumped start, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Slightly slow out, positioned on rail at rear, still 6 lengths back on turn, showed no response in straight, eased final 150M.
In midfield, 4-1/2L off along the rail, shifted out for clear running at 300M then closed off nicely to score by 1/2L.
In worse than midfield, sat 5-1/2L behind along the rail, continued to improve and drove the winner to the line.
Raced close to the tail but keen, 6-1/2L behind 2 wide, made ground and closed off strongly inside final 200M.
Rolled forward and raced in the box-seat, sat 2-1/2L off the lead, kept on well to the line.
Sent forward to take the rail and led by 1-1/4L, caught when approaching final 50M, ran on to the line.
Taken back and raced at the tail, 7-1/2L behind 2-3 wide, switched wide, continued to make ground until 100M.
Rolled forward to be outside the lead, sat 1-1/4L off, remained in touch until weakened badly passing 200M.
Pushed forward, settled in front of midfield, 3-1/2L behind 2 wide, mostly one paced in the straight.
Bumped start, settled to race in midfield, 3-3/4L behind but wide, kept on until flattened passing 200M.
Keen when eased after the start, settled in worse than midfield, 5-1/2L behind but very wide, did not threaten.
Settled to race in behind midfield, 5-1/2L behind 2 wide, eased slightly after 300M, but showed nothing in general.
Bumped start then taken back, remained close to the rear throughout, never a factor.
Niggled along, raced prominently but wide, gave ground soon after straightening.
Began fairly, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground to near 500M, finished off very strongly in straight to score easily.

Moderately away from the widest draw, unable to slot in early, sent forward after passing 1100M to take the lead, led by 2 lengths on turn, kept on very well in straight but couldn't hold off the winner final 150M.
Out in line, raced in 2nd, 2 lengths back on turn, kept on well in straight to take a place.
Jumped well, raced 2 wide in midfield, 4 to 5 lengths back on turn, made minor progress in straight to make frame without threatening.
Away with them, positioned on rail behind midfield, 5 to 6 lengths back, saved ground on turn, angled out early in straight and made minor progress.
Away well, took the early lead, steadied near 1100M to allow the rival to cross, 3 lengths back on turn, peaked early in straight, finished off one-paced.
Taken back to race at tail, 7 to 8 lengths back, same margin back on turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Began well, raced 2 wide at rear, 6 lengths back, there to turn, made no progress in straight.
Restrained from a tricky gate, difficult to settle early, raced 3 wide with no cover behind midfield, gave ground on turn, eased early in straight, unacceptable performance.
Saved ground along the fence in midfield, caught up behind leaders early straight before switching out 250M, burst through late to get up last stride.
Moved up along the 2-path to be tracking leaders on settling, kept on well turning in, narrow lead 150M, nabbed last stride.
Emerged as leader passing 1000M, responded well under pressure on straightening, headed 150M, rallied and fought hard right to the line.
Lacked early pace, raced near the rear 3-wide, widest straightening worked home strongly to claim a close 4th. Nearest finish.
Behind midfield along the 3-path, never far off 3-4Ls off the pace, stayed on well late to be nearest at the finish. Sound effort.
Reserved 2-wide in mid-division, 3Ls off the pace 400M, couldn't get close enough to the leaders in the run home.
Taken back for cover, 2nd last making the turn for home and raced keenly 600M, 5Ls to make up top of straight, made minor headway to the line.
From draw 1 stayed close to the leaders along the fence, held ground on straightening then weakened 150M.
Went forward from wide draw early stages, restrained to a 3-wide spot chasing leaders in 5th, fought on one-paced over final 400M, never a serious threat.
Taken back to be last on the inside, 6Ls back on straightening, no clear run early straight, made some progress final 200M but steadied again 100M. (Jockey questioned re his ride in the Straight.)
Bustled along after the jump, crossed to race outside leader, held ground early straight, no extra and yielded his position 200M.
Held up in midfield, under the pump 550M, found nothing in the straight, eased final 150M when no chance.

Went forward under 10 lb. claimer, unable to cross from wide draw then dropped back to midfield, caught 4-wide no cover, tough run told mid-straight, weakened away. (Trainer questioned re riding tactics.)
Raced towards the rear after awkward start, keenly middle stages, didn't respond to riding and finished well down the track. (Jockey questioned re riding position.)
Began fairly, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 4 to 5 lengths back, there to turn, finished off very strongly in straight to score by a neck.
Bumped on jumping, recovered to race in 2nd, 2 wide, 3/4L back on turn, took the lead early in straight and kept on very well, just couldn't hold off the winner late.
Taken back to race at tail, 8 lengths back, moved closer along the rail on turn, taken wide in straight and finished off strongly to take 3rd. (Blood in trachea.)
Taken back from the widest draw, raced 2 wide at rear, 6 lengths back, same position on turn, made very good progress in straight to make frame. (Rider had his whip knocked from his grasp near 100M.)
Jumped well from a tricky gate, positioned 1 out 1 back, there to turn, kept on evenly to the line.
Taken back from gate 10, positioned 5 lengths back on rail, saved ground on turn, in traffic early in straight, made good progress when clear final 150M to be nearest on line.
Bumped start, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, no clear running early in straight, finished off evenly when clear thereafter.
Jumped well from barrier 11, sent forward to take the lead, led by 3/4L, headed after turning in, kept on evenly to the line. (See Racing Incidents.)
Moderately away, very difficult to settle early, raced very wide behind midfield, travel keenly on turn, carried wider near 550M, finished off evenly in straight.
Bumped start, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Jumped with them, trapped 3 wide with no cover in midfield, weakened gradually after turning in when hard run took effect.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide in midfield, angled out from near 550M, no daylight early in straight, weakened away passing 200M to finish last. (Blood in trachea.)
Cruised across from the wide draw to settle just behind midfield. Began to chase from the top of the straight. Strong run late to grab the leader at 30m, and pull well clear.

Pressed forward to lead by 3L at 1000m and set a quick tempo mid race. Still well clear at 200m, but was beginning to fade quickly. Lost the lead 30m out and was very lucky to hold 2nd late. Jockey questioned.

Crowded start and didn't muster early, settling towards the rear of the field. Ran well from the rear, but wanted to lay in from 200m. Had to correct twice and off heels at 50m and lost an iron. Almost certainly cost him 2nd.
Crowded on jumping and settled at the rear of the field. Off heels at 400m and stayed on solidly to the line.
Cruised forward early to settle midfield. Briefly held 2nd at 300m, but 1 paced from that point and no threat.
Dropped back early from the wide draw to settle at the rear of the field. Wider on the turn, and slightly off heels at 350m. Stayed on solidly late.
Eased back early to settle last. Widest in the straight, but only ran fairly to the line.
Eased forward early to settle midfield. Stayed on timidly late under minimal urging.
Began well, but eased back early to settle around midfield. Stuck wide with no cover from 1000m. Pushed forward to sit 2nd at 300m, but never ran on and faded out late.
Pushed early, before easing back to settle forward of midfield. Only responded fairly to riding and was never a threat.
Eased out early to settle worse than midfield. Off heels 300m, but never ran on in the straight.
Pressed forward to sit 3rd, 3-4L off the leader. Used up very early in the straight and was eased from the 200m.
Taken forward to sit 2nd. Gave nothing in the straight, and was eased a long way from home.
Taken up to sit 4th. Gave nothing in the straight and was packed up very early.

Settled off the pace, raced greenly coming onto course proper, quickened well inside the final 200 metres to assert authority close to home.
Led or disputed lead most of the way, outsprinted close to home.
Began fairly, settled just worse than midfield, shuffled further back coming onto course proper, produced good late impression inside the final 200 metres.
Never far off racing near the centre of the track without cover, quickened to hold some chance after coming onto course proper, unable to sustain effort closing stages.
Well there on stands rail, shared the pace coming onto the course proper and until the 200 metres when outsprinted, checked and lost position shortly afterwards.
Began well, settled just off the pace on stands rail, shuffled slightly further back coming onto course proper, ran home one-paced.
Settled towards the rear from a low draw racing keenly coming onto the course proper, failed to quicken under pressure.
Settled well behind, ran on under pressure past well-beaten horses inside the final 200 metres.
Missed the break, trailed the field most of the way, ran on past well-beaten horses in the run to the line.
Showed speed to share the lead early, came under pressure coming onto the course proper, soon faded out of contention.
Held up in forward of midfield, came under pressure coming onto course proper, dropped out tamely.
Raced in last few without cover from the one draw, dropped out under pressure closing stages.
Soon dropped to last few, never seen with a chance.
Moderate start, settled in forward of midfield, faded under pressure inside the final 300 metres.
Eased back, 2 wide, moved forward 1000M, led 800M, benefited by the slow sectionals, hung on well to win.
Pushed forward, box seat early, benefited by the slow sectionals, closed off strongly for 2nd.
Eased to sit in front of midfield along the fence, ran on well to the line for 3rd.
Pushed to sit in midfield, trapped 3-4 wide, made early move 700M to take advantages of the slow pace, just held ground in straight.
Eased to sit behind midfield, harmed by the slow tempo, dashed well 300M, hampered 100M.
Hard ridden to keep up in midfield, 2 wide, dashed well 200M despite not suited by the slow pace.
Eased back, trapped 3-4 wide, harmed by the slow pace, little dash 200M.
At rear, 2 wide, not suited by the slow tempo, no dash.
Eased back, raced very keen and checked early, 2-3 wide, harmed by the slow pace, no progress.
Pressed forward, trapped 3 wide, emptied 250M.
Eased back, raced 4-5 wide throughout, never improved.
Never a factor.

Placing: UR
Comment: Near 100M unable to avoid a fallen horse and made heavy contact with that horse, resulting its rider to be dislodged.

Placing: FE
Comment: Near 150M went amiss in its left front leg and fell, resulting in its rider being dislodged.
Raced behind midfield, kept on rail at Home Turn, quickened passing 300M when obtained clear running, finished unchallenged.
Fast out and took lead, responded well in the straight, worked home solidly.
Bounded at start and lost ground, raced at back, wide on straightening, made up some nice late ground.
Settled at handy position, commenced to improve near 500M, battled hard entire straight, came home well.
Settled at back on rail, asked for effort passing 500M, raced tight over the concluding stages, finished well.
Raced front of midfield on rail, asked for effort on straightening, near 300M raced in restricted room, ran on to the line.
Slow to begin and settle at rear, widest on straightening, fought hard entire straight, finished OK.
Moderate start, settled behind midfield, tried to improve passing 500M, finished OK.
Travelled midfield on rail, one-paced in the straight.
Slow to muster speed despite being ridden along, raced midfield, one-paced.
Jumped nicely to settle outside the lead, gave ground passing 200M, near 150M rider dropped his whip.
Urged along to race behind leaders, limited response in the straight.
Moderately away from a wide draw, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths back, mover closer from near 700M, 3 wide turning in, hit the front near 200M, kept on very well to score.

Slowly away, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground to near 500M, commenced to hang in early in straight, awkwardly placed until over the concluding stages, closed off well thereafter to take 2nd. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped with them, positioned 2 wide, 3 lengths back, similar position on turn, angled out from near 500M, kept on well in straight to get 3rd.
Slowly away, raced 4 lengths back on rail, saved ground on turn, no clear running early in straight, shifted in to get run thereafter and made some progress. (See Racing Incidents.)
Bumped start, sent forward to race 2 wide in 2nd, same position on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked near 200M, weakened thereafter.
Moderately away, sat a length behind the leader on rail, easy run on turn, held up near 350M, finished off evenly when clear thereafter.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 7 lengths back at rear, moved closer on turn, still 4 to 5 lengths back, made some progress in straight. (See Racing Incidents.) (Irregular heart rhythm.)
Average to begin, raced 3 wide with cover, 4 lengths or so back, there to turn, finished off one-paced in straight.
Taken back from barrier 11, 6 lengths back at rear, saved ground on turn, finished off one-paced in straight.
Bounded in the air and lost ground at start, raced 7 lengths back at rear, checked off heels near 800M, still 5 lengths back turning in, made no progress in straight.
Bumped start, unable to slot in, travelled wide and without cover in midfield throughout, emptied in straight when hard run took effect.
Jumped well, showed early speed to take the lead, challenged around turn, headed early in straight and faded. (Jockey concerned over the horse's action.)
Bumped start, raced wide with cover at rear, 6 lengths back, improved from 500M, finished off very strongly to score.
Never far off from the pace, took a while to get going, worked home well final 200M, held by winner late stages.
Jumped well, took the early lead,surrended lead near 950M, sat a length behind the leader thereafter, hit the front near 300M, kept on well but couldn't hold off the first two late.
Jumped well from a wide draw, raced prominently, 2 wide, 3rd on turn, kept on evenly to the line.
Moderately away from gate 1, showed no early speed, positioned 4 lengths back on rail, same margin back on turn, kept to inside after straightening and finished off evenly. (See Racing Incidents.)
Away with them, settled 2 wide better than midfield, improved from near 500M, peaked early in straight, kept on evenly until awkwardly placed near final 100M.
Average to begin, raced 3 wide with cover, 4 lengths back, awkwardly placed near 1400M, checked off heels near 700M, 7 lengths back turning in, made some progress in straight.

Moderately away from a tricky draw, trapped very wide early, sent forward after entering the back straight, took the lead near 950M, unchallenged on turn, headed early in straight and weakened gradually thereafter.
Average to begin, trapped wide in midfield, still no cover on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Taken back from a wide barrier, raced wide at rear throughout, failed to close off in straight.
Bumped start, raced3 wide with cover, 3 lengths or so back, crowded near 700M, 5 lengths back turning in, made no progress in straight.
Slowly away, raced at tail, 6 lengths back, slightly improved along the rail on turn, kept on evenly early in straight, emptied near 200M, eased thereafter.

Out in line, difficult to settle early, hung out near 1400M and reluctant to shift in to race closer to the rail, raced 2 wide at rear thereafter, well back on turn, finished tailed out. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began awkwardly from the widest draw, trapped very wide early, sent forward after entering the back straight but still raced wide, emptied on turn, finished tailed out, unacceptable performance.
Slow to muster, settled in the box-seat, sat 2L behind, held up until passing 300M, closed off well thereafter to score.
Race in the one-off one-back position, sat 3L off the lead, kept on well to the line to finish 3/4L behind.
Took cover after being ridden along, at the rear 10-1/4L behind 2 wide, made ground and battled on strongly for 3rd.
Eased and then raced at the rear, 9-1/4L behind along the rail, saved ground and finished off well to the line.
Raced in midfield, sat 6L behind along the rail, held up till 100M in the straight, closed off well once cleared.
Sent forward to take the rail and led by 1-1/2L, headed approaching 100M but ran on to the line.
Travelled in midfield, 6-3/4L behind 2 wide, made slight ground and ran on okay to the line.
Settled to race near the rear, 9L behind 2 wide, remained mostly one paced in the straight.
Rolled forward to be outside the lead, sat 1-1/2L off, flattened passing 200M.
Sat in just behind midfield, 8L behind 2 wide, made slight ground and ran on.
Niggled along to be in front of midfield, 5L behind 2 wide, dropped off gradually in the straight. (Rider expressed concern with its action)
In behind midfield along the rail, wasn't in it.
Taken back to race at rear, 5 lengths or so back, 3 wide with cover on turn, finished off very strongly to score by a neck.
Jumped well, positioned a length behind the leader in 2nd, same position on turn, took the lead near 250M, kept on strongly thereafter but just couldn't hold off the winner late.
Slightly slow out from gate 1, positioned 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, no clear running early in straight, made good progress when clear thereafter to take 3rd.
Moderately away, sent forward to take the lead, enjoyed the easy lead throughout, peaked early in straight, headed near 250M, stayed on evenly to the line.

Slightly slow out, raced 2 wide at rear, 4 lengths back, awkwardly placed near 900M, difficult to settle for some distance thereafter, raced tight near 400M, made some progress in straight without threatening.
Crowded on jumping, raced 2 wide in midfield, awkwardly placed near 950M, same position on turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Began well, positioned 3 lengths back on rail, saved ground on turn, no clear running early in straight, made no progress when clear thereafter.
Taken back to race at rear, positioned 3 wide, 4 lengths or so back, no cover on turn, raced tight early in straight, failed to make any progress, finished last. (Lame right front leg.) (Roarer.)
Eased back, settled towards the rear of the field and well suited to the fast pace, wound up strongly passing 400M from outside, led near 100M for an upset win.
Restrained to race in midfield 5L back along the rail, closed well seeing daylight 300M, crowded for room 200M, continued to make good headway to the line. Brave in defeat.
Went forward early then shifted across behind leaders 1300M, into clear 350M, made sustained progress to be not far away on line. Honest effort.

Shuffled back to the rear, reluctant to stretch out 1200M and lost ground, hard ridden to get back to it, 6Ls back in last at 400M, closed off strongly down outside to just miss 3rd. (To BT 1600M on turf)
Tracked leaders in a fast run race, difficult obtain run early straight, came through to challenge from 300M, outsprinted by rivals late under a 5lb penalty.
Held up 2-wide in midfield just over 4Ls off the pace when they settled, tried hard and kept grinding to the line but couldn't reel in the leaders.
Eased back on jumping, moved forward passing 1300M to be 4th chasing leaders, loomed a chance 300M, held slender lead to 200M, outsprinted towards the line. (Jockey dropped right rein 200M-150M.)

Rolled forward to press leader on the outside in a strongly run race, couldn't quicken passing 300M, eased when beaten over final 150M. (Jockey : Not able to finish off due to strong tempo early stages.)
Shifted across behind runners early, settled 9th of 10 6Ls off the fast pace, never got going, no threat to leaders at any stage.
Led as anticipated, set fast pace to straight, joined in at 350M, couldn't hold off rivals from 250M, weakened to last. (Jockey : disappointed in its failure to respond when challenged by rivals.)
Began smartly, raced closer to the middle of the track, 3 lengths back, travelled well throughout, hit the front near 150M and scored by 3/4 length.
Away with them, raced in midfield, 3 away from the stands rail, finished off well to take 2nd.
Bumped shortly after start, raced at tail, 5 to 6 lengths back, finished off very strongly to take 3rd.
Moderately away from gate 1, raced behind midfield nearer to the middle of the track, ran home strongly to make frame.
Bumped shortly after start, raced at rear on the stand side, 4 to 5 lengths back, made good progress final 400M.
Bumped start, raced prominently early, slightly taken back to sit a length behind the leader near 600M, awkwardly placed near 300M, finished off evenly when clear thereafter.
Bumped on jumping, raced prominently, took the lead near 300M, peaked shortly thereafter, weakened in the concluding stages.
Slightly slow out and crowded, raced at rear close to the stands rail, made some progress but never threatened.
Began well, sent forward to take the lead, headed near 300M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Bumped start, raced behind midfield closer to the stand side, made no impression final 400M.
Began awkwardly and bumped, positioned 4 lengths behind the leader on the stand side, made no progress final 400M.
Average to begin, raced at rear nearer to the middle of the track, 5 lengths or so back, failed to make any progress final 400M.
Bumped and unbalanced shortly after start, sent forward to race prominently, no response to riding final 400M and dropped away tamely.
Bumped on jumping, raced prominently, weakened from 500M, eased near 250M, finished tailed out. (Jockey reported his horse did not appear comfortable in its action.)
Cruised forward early to sit just behind midfield, and slightly keen early. Wider on the turn. Kept grinding away down the straight, and just fell in on the line.
Cruised across from the wide draw to settle midfield. Had a clear run in the straight and grabbed the lead at 150m. Solid to the line and just run over in the last 2 strides.
Early contender for the lead, before easing back into the trail run in 3rd. Nosed in front for a short lived lead at 300m. Running on empty late and just held 3rd.
Taken up early to be handily placed in 4th. Stayed on solidly early in the straight. Stronger late and was rapidly running down 3rd.
Cruised forward early and settled worse than midfield. Steady early in the straight, before winding up late. Awkward on heels 100m, and not properly tested in the last 50m.
Dropped back from the wide draw to settle towards the rear of the field. Widest on the turn. Stayed on solidly, and was making up good ground late.
Settled just forward of midfield. Battled on quietly in the straight and never threatened.
Cruised forward early to settle around midfield. Came inside off heels after missing a run at 350m. Stayed on fairly and did his best work late under minimal urging.
Pushed forward from the wide draw to share the early lead. Never got better than 1 paced in the straight and never a threat.
Hit the side of the barrier, awkwardly away and slow to begin. Consequently settled last. Plugged away to the line in the straight.
Tardy to jump and settled towards the rear of the field. Made no impression in the straight and was packed up at the 200m.
Pushed early to share the lead, before taking control at 900m. Nothing left in the straight and dropped out from 300m.
Eased back early, but was stuck 3 wide and just behind midfield. Drifted to the line under minimal urging and eased last 100m.
Dropped back to the rear of the field early. Gone before the turn, and eased a long way from home.

Never far off on the rail after beginning from the one gate, came to challenge under pressure into the straight, hit the front passing the 200 metres, won readily.
Ridden early, held rails run sharing the pace, gained slender lead passing the 800 metres, led until headed inside the 200 metres, hung on under pressure for 2nd.
Outpaced early, remained well behind into straight, baulked for a run until the 200 metres, finished off the race well.
Jumped well settling just worse than midfield, raced keenly and lost position at the 600 metres, saved ground and renewed effort turning in, kept on steadily without quickening.
Soon dropped to last few, racing wide without cover down the back straight, inconvenienced between runners shortly after straightening for home, fought on steadily under pressure. (Tactic questioned)
Well there early, soon taken back to forward of midfield in 6th on the rail, angled out for a run entering straight, ran home one-paced.
Sluggish at start, raced keenly in last few dropping to last going up the Rock, commenced run rounding home bend and swung widest turning in, ran on to be nearest at finish.
Bumped and unbalanced at the start, settled towards the rear, gained slightly closer on the rail briefly at the Rock, saved ground turning in, kept on before fading inside the final 200 metres.
Travelled wide in midfield from the widest gate, slightly worse rounding home bend and swung very wide into the straight, kept on same pace under pressure without quickening.
Moderate start from a poor gate, travelled wide without cover in a prominent position to the 400 metres, faded under pressure.
Well there, taken back for cover in vain passing the 800 metres before moving forward to dispute the lead coming onto home bend, dropped out tamely in the straight.
Given early reminders holding slender lead early in back straight, dropped to 3rd approaching the 600 metres, folded up quickly after straightening. (Tactic questioned)
Hard ridden to take rail and lead, made all.
Eased back, 2-3 wide, dashed strongly 400M for 2nd.
Eased to rear, 2 wide, unleashed strong finishing efforts 300M.
Behind midfield on the fence, held up 4-2, dashed strongly when clear.
Hard ridden to obtain box seat, just held ground in straight.
In front of midfield along the fence, weakened 200M.
Eased to rear, 2-3 wide, dashed well 200M.
Behind midfield, 2-3 wide, no turn of foot in straight.
Eased to sit in midfield, 2-3 wide, no progress.
Eased back, trapped 3-5 wide, never nearer.
Hard ridden forward, sat outside the leader, out of fuel 250M.
Pushed forward, 2 wide, emptied 300M.
Ridden along to take lead, travelled nicely, ran on in the straight, scored unchallenged.
Jumped well, settled in box seat, asked for effort passing 450M, responded well in the straight.
Hard ridden at start, settled midfield, commenced to improve near 500M, made up some nice late ground.
Raced midfield on rail, kept on rail at Home Turn to save ground, fought hard entire straight, worked home well.
Moderate start, settled behind midfield, gained ground passing 100M.
Jumped nicely, travelled behind leader, under pressure and gave ground near 100M.
Taken back at start, wide on straightening, one-paced.
Raced at rear, widest on straightening, limited response.
Raced behind midfield on rail, limited response in the straight.
Travelled midfield, under pressure and no response in the straight.
Raced at tail, checked near 200M, failed to run on.
Raced wide and without cover in early and middle stages, passing 600M came under heavy pressure, gave ground in the straight.
Moderately away, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths back, moved closer after entering the back straight, took the lead turning in, kept on strongly in straight to score.
Began well, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, 2 wide from near 800M, there to turn, closed off well to take 2nd. (See Racing Incidents.)

Bumped start, sent forward to race prominently, took the lead near 1100M, enjoyed the easy lead thereafter, challenged from near 450M, headed turning in, kept on evenly until weakened close home, just stayed on for 3rd.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, slightly improved after entering the back straight, carried wider near 800M, no cover thereafter, finished off evenly in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, positioned 6 lengths back on rail, saved ground to near 500M, made some progress in straight without threatening.
Began awkwardly, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground throughout, kept on evenly to the line.
Broke with rest, raced 2 wide at rear, 5 lengths or so back on turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Taken back from gate 11, positioned 7 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, made no real progress in straight.
Out in line, raced 2 to 3 wide in midfield, improved from 500M, 4 wide turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened in the closing stages. (Lame both front legs.) (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back from the widest draw, raced 2 wide at rear, 8 lengths back, still well back on turn, made no progress in straight.
Slowly away, raced at tail, 10 lengths back, still well back on turn, made no progress in straight.
Bumped on jumping, sent forward to take the early lead, headed near 1100M, sat right behind thereafter, saved ground on turn, showed no response early in straight and gradually dropped away.
Jumped well, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well throughout, kept on strongly in straight and scored easily. (Lame right hind leg next day morning.)
Quickly into stride, sent forward to race outside the leader, there to turn, kept on well in straight to take 2nd.

Moderately away from gate 1, raced greenly early, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, same position on turn, made some progress in straight to take 3rd without posing any threat to the first two.
Began well, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, easy run on turn, kept on evenly to the line.
Slightly slow out and checked, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 4 lengths back, slightly improved on turn, kept on evenly in straight.
Away with them, raced 4 to 5 lengths back at rear, lay out near 500M, made minor progress in straight.
Taken back from gate 9, raced at tail, 5 to 6 lengths back, last turning in, taken widest in straight and made some progress.
Jumped well from the widest draw, raced 4 wide behind midfield, bumped near 600M, still very wide on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Began only fairly, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, bumped near 600M, there to turn, finished off one-paced in straight.
Began awkwardly, positioned 3 to 4 lengths back on rail, saved ground on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Began well from a wide draw, unable to slot in, raced 3 wide, 2 lengths back, no cover throughout, emptied early in straight when hard run took effect.
In worse than midfield, sat 8L behind 2 wide, taken to 3 wide at 500M, ran home strongly to clinch it by a head.
Sat in front of midfield, 4L behind 2 wide, looked likely from near 100M but couldn't' hold off winner in final stride.
In the lead until crossed near 1000M, shifted away from the rail after 800M, led from 300M to 100M, stayed on for 3rd.
Raced in midfield, sat 5-1/2L behind along the rail, continued on well to be closest at the finish.
Travelled near the tail, made ground after 600M to be 4-3/4L off before straightening, kept on going to the line.
Eased and raced towards the tail 10L behind, shifted to 3 wide prior to 600M turn, made minor ground.
Settled in front of midfield, 3-1/2L behind along the rail, couldn't find extra approaching 150M.
Taken back, 12L behind at 800M, shifted wide and improved to be closer thereafter, failed to make an impression.
Niggled along but couldn't hold ground, raced near the tail, 10-1/2L behind along the fence, hardly improved.
Sent forward and continued to pursue the lead and rail, led by 1-1/2L at 800M, weakened upon straightening.
Eased to find cover, in midfield, 5-3/4L behind 2 wide, not competitive.
Asked to be prominent, sat 2-3/4L off, without cover until 700M, found nothing.

Moderately away, sent forward to race prominently, a length behind the leader, slightly improved from near 800M and took the lead thereafter, hard ridden turning in, kept on very well in straight to score.
Bumped start and unbalanced, raced 2 wide, 2 to 3 lengths back, similar position in the middle stages, hard ridden turning in, closed off well to take 2nd.
Out in line, positioned 2 to 3 lengths back on rail, saved ground throughout, finished off well to take a place.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, finished off evenly.
Clean jump from gate 9, sent forward to take the lead, surrended lead after 700M, peaked on turn, ran on evenly to the line.
Crowded on jumping, positioned on rail behind midfield, 5 lengths back on turn, made no progress in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, set huge task, still 9 lengths back on turn, made minor ground in straight. (Rider dropped rein near 50M.)
Slowly away, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 7 lengths back on turn, made no progress in straight. (See Racing Incidents.) (Lame left front leg next day.)
Bumped start and unbalanced, positioned on rail at rear, still well back on turn, made no progress in straight.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide at rear, checked near 1000M, well back on turn, showed no response in straight. (Lost right front plate.)
From draw 1 tracked leader along the fence, worked home strongly came with a sustained run to lead nearing 50M, fought off late challenge to prevail.
Reserved in midfield along the rail, stayed on well final 250M, threw in a strong challenge on winner late, just missed.
Soon led, set steady pace early before quickening up home turn, opened up 2L lead 300M, under siege 120M and headed by first 2 close home, awkwardly placed late but held on for 3rd.
Pressed forward to race outsider leader, kept battling away in the straight, just missed 3rd.
Settled down 3-wide towards the rear, widest on straightening, did best work final 200M making good late impression.
From its wide barrier steadied and shifted in behind runners to be 11th, 7Ls off leader at 400M, worked home mildly.
On jumping was crowded for room, settled last, 8Ls off 400M, made some progress in the straight without threatening.
Never far off from leaders, failed to finish off leaving the bend, ran on same pace to the line.

Hampered at the start, raced near the rear on his Valley debut and further back than intended, failed to pick up early straight, no clear run final 150M and eased towards the line. (Inquiry into performance.)
Chased leaders, proved difficult to settle when steadied to obtain cover 1000M, raced wide no cover for majority of race, faded 200M.
From draw 9 caught wide no cover in midfield for majority of the race, lacked finishing effort turning in, never threatened.
Rushed along after the start to take up a midfield position, under pressure 450M, weak in the run home.

Well there on stands rail, hit the front coming onto course proper, spread-eagling the field inside final 200 metres.
Crowded at start, soon recovered to share the pace, no response to winner's turn of foot inside the 200 metres, kept on for distant 2nd.
Jumped awkwardly racing greenly throughout, never far off the pace in 5th on the rail, kept on without quickening in closing stages.
Soon dropped to the last, kept on past well-beaten horses closing stages.
Held slender lead early, well there to the halfway mark, weakened under pressure.
Began awkwardly, settled just off the pace, dropped out under pressure from the halfway mark.
Moderate start, soon moved up to join the leaders, dropped out from the halfway mark.
Midfield, trapped 4 wide throughout, pace good, progressed steadily 400M to score.
Pushed forward, sat 2 wide, pace good, shuffled back slightly 800M, made steady ground 400M for 2nd.
Hard ridden to take rail and led at good pace, overhauled 250M, ran on for 3rd.
Hard ridden forward, trapped 3 wide, pace good, hung on well until 100M weakened.
Pressed forward, sat 2 wide, pace good, out of fuel 200M.
Hard ridden to keep up in midfield, on heels early, 3-4 wide, pace good, ran on only fairly in straight.
Hard ridden to keep up in midfield, 2 wide, pace good, no dash.
Slow away, hard ridden early but not muster at back, no progress.
Eased back, trapped 3 wide, pace good, never improved.
Very slow away, at rear on the rails, hampered 350M, no progress.
Hard ridden early, never travelled, raced 4-5 wide at rear.
Hard ridden forward, dropped off 500M.
Began only fairly, raced midfield on rail, quickened passing 150M, scored unchallenged.
Urged along to take lead, asked for effort on straightening, finished solidly.
Began only fairly then was steadied away from heels, raced at tail, wide on straightening, made some nice ground passing 100M.
Ridden along to take box seat, commenced to improve on straightening, fought hard and worked home OK.
Travelled at handy position, battled hard in the straight, came home OK.
Raced midfield, tried to improve near 500M, one-paced.
Settled behind midfield on rail, kept on rail to save ground at Home Turn, limited response in the straight.
Raced behind midfield, no response in the straight.
Jumped well, pushed along to settle outside the lead, weakened passing 400M when under pressure, failed to run on.
Taken back at start, widest on straightening, never in it.
Jumped well from gate 9, positioned nicely in 3rd, travelled well throughout, finished off strongly in straight to score.
jumped with them, raced 2 wide at rear, still well back on turn, taken widest in straight and finished off very strongly to take 2nd, nearest on line.
Jumped well from the widest draw, sent forward to take the lead, enjoyed the easy lead throughout, kicked clear after turning in, kept on well but just couldn't hold off the first two late.
Slowly away, recovered to race in midfield, 6 lengths back on turn, made good progress in straight to make frame without threatening.
Began well, showed no early speed, raced behind midfield, 8 lengths back on turn, made good progress in straight to be nearest on line.
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, there to turn, finished off evenly. (See Racing Incidents.)
Bumped shortly after start, raced wide with no cover in midfield, 5 lengths back turning in, finished off evenly.
Began awkwardly, raced wide with no cover at rear, 8 lengths back on turn, finished off evenly. (Riderdropped whip150M.)
Began well, sent forward to race prominently, a length behind the leader on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked near 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.

Clean jump from gate 10, raced wide with cover behind midfield, well back on turn, made no progress in straight, eased close home. (Jockey reported his horse did not feel comfortable in its action.) (Lame left front leg next day.)
Crowded out start, raced at rear throughout, never a factor.
Raced at tail throughout, never competitive.
Began only fairly, raced 2 wide at rear, 6 to 7 lengths back, similar position on turn, taken widest early in straight, finished off very strongly to score by a neck.
Bumped start, sent forward to take the lead, easy lead on turn, kept on very well in straight but couldn't hold off the winner close home.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide, 4 lengths back, there to turn, made very good progress in straight to take 3rd.
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, saved ground throughout, no daylight after turning in, finished off evenly when clear final 150M.
Fast into stride, sent forward to race prominently but wide, 2nd on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked near 150M, slightly weakened thereafter.
Average to begin, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, angled out early in straight, finished off evenly.
Jumped well, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, bumped and carried wider near 600M, very wide turning in, made minor progress early in straight, weakened from final 150M.
Bumped start and unbalanced, raced 2 wide, better than midfield, bumped near 600M, showed good response early in straight, peaked near 200M, weakened thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)

Taken back from a wide draw, 9 lengths back, last turning in, kept to inside after straightening, made good progress before ran into traffic final 150M. (Lost right front plate.) (See Racing Incidents.)
Crowded on jumping, positioned 5 lengths back on rail, saved ground to near 500M, raced tight early in straight, finished off one-paced.

Taken back from the widest draw, positioned on rail at rear, 6-7 lengths back, saved ground to turn, angled out from 550M, made some progress before blocked near 200M, finished off one-paced when clear thereafter.
Taken back from gate 10, raced wide with cover at rear, 4 to 5 lengths back, similar position on turn, made no progress in straight.
Moderately away from a wide draw, raced 3 wide, 2 lengths back, no cover on turn, emptied early in straight and gradually dropped away.
Bumped start, sent forward to race prominently, travelled keenly near 1100M, awkwardly placed near 700M, 2 lengths back on turn, emptied early in straight, eased final 100M.
Travelled in midfield, 4L behind along the rail, continued on well to the line well and scored by a head.
Crowded start, sat towards the rear 6-1/4L off along the rail, reverted to the inside after being disappointed at 350M, continued to make inroad and closed off nicely for 2nd.
Eased to be in midfield but trapped wide, improved to be near the lead after 1200M, kept on well to take 3rd.
Settled towards the rear, 6-1/2L behind 2 wide, switched wide from Home Turn, made ground and closed off well.
Raced in behind midfield, sat 4-1/2L behind 3 wide with cover, saved ground on outer straight, hit the line well.
Niggled along and raced in the box-seat, sat 2L off, no daylight early and held up in the final 150M, not fully tested.
Rolled forward into one-off one-back position, sat 2L off, kept on fairly to the line.
Travelled just in front of midfield, 2-3/4L behind 3 wide with cover, one paced in the straight.
Sent forward to take rail and led by 1/2L, flattened and headed approaching 200M.
Raced in behind midfield, 5L behind 2 wide, was one paced until crowded at 100M.
Taken back and raced at the rear, 8L behind along the rail, mostly one paced.
Asked to go forward and raced outside the lead, 1/2L off, started to weaken passing 250M.
Sat in front of midfield, 3-1/4L off 2 wide, checked at 350M, did not improve thereafter.
Jumped with them, raced closer to the middle of the track, 2 lengths or so back, hit the front near 200M and scored by 1/2 length.
Bumped start, raced closer to the middle of the track, 3 lengths or so back, finished off very well to take 2nd.
Jumped well, positioned nearer to the stands rail, 2 lengths back, kept on very well final 400M to take a place.
Clean jump, no early speed, raced at tail, still 9 lengths back at 400M, finished off very strongly to be nearest online. (See Racing Incidents.)
Bumped start, raced prominently in the middle of the track, kept on evenly to the line.
Bumped on jumping, positioned behind midfield on the stands rail, 4 lengths to make up 400M, made some headway before ran into traffic near 150M, closed off well when clear thereafter.
Bumped start, raced prominently, near to the stands rail, peaked on run near 400M, weakened in the concluding stages.
Jumped with them from a middle draw, raced behind midfield close to the stands rail, made some headway before blocked near 200M, taken to centre track thereafter, but only showed limited response.
Began only fairly, raced at rear, closer to the middle of the track, only showed limited response in the final 400M. (Sustained a small wound to the left hind fetlock.)
Jumped well, showed good speed to take the lead on the stands rail, travelled well throughout, peaked and headed near 200M, weakened gradually thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Bumped and unbalanced early, raced in the middle of the track, 3 to 4 lengths back, showed no response to riding final 400M.
Crowded on jumping, raced at rear on the stands rail, made no impression final 400M.
Jumped well, raced prominently, 2 away from the stands rail, peaked near 500M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Slightly slow out from gate 1, raced at rear in the middle of the track, finished tailed out, never competitive.
Pressed forward from draw 1 to track leaders in 4th, took on leader 500M, led 350M out and kept on stoutly to the line.
Restrained after the start to be 2nd last 6-7Ls behind leader, challenged wide 600M, inconvenienced 250M when closing off strongly, continued good work to the finish to go 2nd near line.
Began only fairly, guided to the fence holding a rearward position 6Ls off the pace, bustled along 650M, stayed on well down inner for 3rd.
Raced along the rail 4Ls back in midfield, got split 400M, chased leaders hard but held. Gap to rest.
Crowded for room on jumping, held up behind midfield 4-5Ls off the pace, shifted wide to make his move 650M, run ended 200M.
Crossed to the lead 2000M, quickened up the tempo 900M, headed 350M, faded towards the finish.
Positioned 2-wide ahead of midfield, awkwardly placed behind weakening rival from 600M, couldn't quicken enough when clear 300M out.
Taken across behind runners, settled last 8-9Ls off the pace, brought wide off the bend but ran on fairly, no extra 200M.

Tracked leader on the outside, dropped back to 4th passing 1000M, hard ridden 700M but didn't respond, soon out of contention. (Jockey : would not relax early and middle stages with rival on outside / Blood in trachea.)
Caught wide no cover outside the pace, dropped away turning home after difficult trip. (Jockey questioned and advised to make all reasonable attempt to ride to his instructions)
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, still 8 lengths or so back on turn, took inside run in straight and finished off very strongly to score narrowly.
Began well, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, there to turn, finished off well to get 2nd, just narrowly beaten.
Average to begin, positioned 2 wide in midfield, angled out from near 550M, finished off well in straight to take a place.
Jumped with them, positioned on rail behind midfield, saved ground on turn, made good progress early in straight, no clear running near 200M, closed off well when clear final 100M.
Jumped well from a wide draw, sent forward to take the lead, enjoyed the easy lead on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed final 100M, just missed frame late.
Began fairly, raced 2 wide at rear, 7 lengths back, same margin back on turn, taken wide in straight and finished off strongly to be nearest on line.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, there to turn, checked early in straight, made very good progress thereafter to be nearest on line.
Away with them, sent forward to race prominently, sat 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on turn, kept on evenly early in straight, weakened from final 100M.
Taken back from gate 13, positioned on rail at rear, 6 lengths back on turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Out in line, positioned 2 wide behind midfield, 5 lengths or so back on turn, finished off one-paced.
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, same position on turn, peaked on run near 200M, awkwardly placed 150M, weakened thereafter.
Slowly away, positioned on rail at rear, still 7 lengths back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Moderately away from a wide draw, unable to slot in, raced wide with no cover in midfield, weakened gradually after turning in when hard run took effect.
Jumped with them, raced 3 wide with no cover in midfield, got cover on turn, failed to close off in straight, finished last.
Pushed hard early to be the clear leader. Pulled away in the straight and made the others chase. Fading late and being quickly run down, but held on.
Eased forward early to sit worse than midfield, but kept pushing to sit 3rd/4th turning for home. Good turn off foot in the straight and was quickly running down the winner on the line.
Dropped to the rear of the field and never closer than 3-4 wide. Ran strongly in the straight and was rapidly catching the first 2 on the line.
Tardy early and settled at the rear of the field. Still at the rear at 250m, but made good ground late to feature in the finish.
Settled forward of midfield, 1 off the fence. Slightly keen in the back straight. Stayed on solidly in the straight under minimal urging.
Cruised forward early to settle midfield. Steadied off heels 700m. Solid early in the straight and improved late, but no threat.
Went across from the wide draw to be handily placed 2nd/3rd, 3 wide with no cover. 1 paced and holding 2nd early in the straight, before fading late.
Eased forward early to be forward of midfield, on the fence. Faded out quickly in the straight. Vet- Lame in near fore leg.
Well placed early, 3rd/4th. Didn't respond to pressure in the straight and was eased out late.
Slow to begin and dropped back towards the rear of the field. Plugged away to the line under minimal urging in the straight.
Taken forward early to be well placed 2nd/3rd on the fence. Gave nothing in the straight and dropped out quickly in last 200m.
Stayed wide in the back straight and dropped back to last. Never improved and was eased a long way from home.
Jumped with them, taken back to race 2 wide behind midfield, 5 lengths back on turn, taken widest in straight and finished off very strongly to score.
Average to begin, unbalanced early, raced 2 wide in midfield, got its head up when awkwardly placed near 800M, same position on turn, finished off strongly in straight to take 2nd.
Fast into stride, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well throughout, kicked clear after turning in, but couldn't hold off the first two late final 100M.
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, easy run on turn, kept on evenly in straight.
Began well, positioned 4 to 5 lengths back on rail, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after straightening and finished off evenly.

Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide at rear, 7L or so back, there to turn, made good progress early in straight, severely checked when disappointed for running near 200M, finished off evenly thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Moderately away from a wide draw, raced 3 wide in midfield, same position on turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Average to begin, positioned on rail at rear, 7 lengths back, similar position on turn, showed limited response in straight.
Began awkwardly, raced at tail, 8 to 9 lengths back, last turning in, kept to inside after straightening, made some progress before ran into traffic near 200M, unable to stretch out thereafter.
Jumped well, raced prominently, parked close 2nd outside leader on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Away with them, raced 2 wide, 3 to 4 lengths back, there to turn, failed to close off in straight and eased final 100M.
Began fairly, sent forward to race prominently, 3 wide with no cover throughout, peaked early in straight, emptied final 150M.

Jumped fairly, settled better than midfield on the rail, came within 2L of the pace rounding home bend, sustained effort in straight to assert authority inside the final 200 metres.

Soon taken back across for rails run, improving towards midfield when steadied passing the Rock, saved ground turning in, ran on under pressure to hold every chance but unable to peg back the winner the length of the straight.
Travelled in midfield on the rail, soon came to challenge after straightening, ran on to be nearest at finish.
Settled at the back from a wide gate, trailed the field to the 400 metres, saved ground turning for home, ran on well to be nearest at finish.
Broke well from the two draw settling just off the pace, hit the front on top of home bend, unable to sustain effort and headed under pressure over 100 metres out.
Settled in midfield, shuffled further back when pace slackened coming off the Rock, inconvenienced for a run early in straight but produced good late impression closing stages.
Raced wide towards the rear, commenced move rounding home bend, widest runner turning in, finished off the race well down the centre of the track.
Settled in last few from the widest draw remaining wide throughout, came under pressure turning in, ran on past beaten horses near the centre of the track.
Hard ridden before settling for 3rd some 3 to 4L back down far side, weakened shortly after straightening.
Soon dropped to last few despite niggled along, steadied and lost position passing the Rock dropping to last into straight, one-paced under pressure.
Ridden to lead, steadied pace near the Rock, headed into home straight, soon weakened under pressure.
Began well from a wide draw settling mainly in forward of midfield, soon weakened after straightening.
Eased to sit in midfield, 2-3 wide, harmed by the slow tempo, dashed strongly 300M to score.
Pushed forward, took rail and led at advantageous slow sectionals, hung on well until 50M overhauled, ran on for 2nd.
Midfield, along the fence, bumped 250M, dashed well despite not suited by the slow tempo.
Pushed to occupy box seat, enjoyed the slow sectionals, just held ground in straight.
Eased back, took rail, not suited by the slow tempo, unleashed strong finishing efforts 200M.
Eased back, 2 wide, harmed by the slow pace, dashed well 250M.
Eased back, took rail, lack room 4-2, dashed well despite not suited by the slow pace.
Eased back, 2-3 wide, not suited by the slow pace, dashed fairly in straight.
Pressed forward, sat 2 wide, benefited by the slow tempo, emptied 200M.
Eased to rear, harmed by the slow pace, little dash 200M.
Hard ridden to obtain a midfield spot, 2 wide, harmed by the slow pace, badly hampered 250M, ran on fairly.
Never a factor at rear.
Raced behind the lead on rail, asked for effort near 300M, made good ground in the straight to score.
Taken back at start and raced at tail, improved passing 350M, quickened passing 100M, just missed by SH.
Moderate start, raced behind midfield on rail, responded well in the straight, worked home solidly.
Hard ridden but failed to muster speed in the early stages, settle midfield, improved to outside the lead after 750M, made ground passing 100M, finished solidly.
Crowded on jumping then raced at back on rail, fought hard in the straight, ran on well.
Raced behind midfield, moved to midfield passing 750M, commenced to improve near 600M, widest on straightening, came home OK.
Travelled very keenly and difficult to settle in the lead, weakened passing 150M.
Urged along at start to settle at handy position, one-paced when asked for effort in the straight.
Raced midfield on rail, no response in the straight, bled.
Taken back at start and raced at rear, wide on straightening, failed to run on.
Bumped start, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths back, there to turn, finished off very strongly in straight and scored.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide at rear, 4-3/4L back, improved from near 450M, taken wide in straight and finished off very strongly to take 2nd.
Taken back from gate 11, raced at tail, 6 lengths or so back, still last turning in, made very good progress in straight to take 3rd, nearest on line.
Taken back from a wide draw, positioned 4 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after straightening and made good progress to make frame. (See Racing Incidents.)
Fast into stride, raced outside to the leader, 3/4L back, travelled well throughout, showed good response early in straight, peaked near 100M, slightly weakened thereafter.
Slowly away, raced 3 wide with no cover, a length or so back, similar position on turn, kept on evenly to the line.
Bumped start, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, 3 lengths back on turn, finished off evenly.
Average to begin, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Jumped well from the widest draw, showed good early speed to take the lead, travelled well throughout, peaked and headed near 150M, weakened thereafter.
Began awkwardly from gate 1, positioned 2 wide, 3 lengths or so back, same position on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Began well, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, easy run on turn, emptied early in straight and eased.
Began fairly, unable to slot in, trapped very wide in midfield, peaked and weakened on turn, finished last.
Out in line, positioned 4 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, finished off very strongly in straight to score by a nose. (Rider had his whip knocked from his grasp near 100M.)
Jumped well, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths back, same position on turn, finished off very strongly to take 2nd, but just couldn't hold off the winner on line.
Average to begin, sent forward to race in 2nd, 3/4L back, hit the front after turning in, kept on well thereafter, but just couldn't hold off the first two late.
Slightly slow out from gate 1, recovered to sit a length behind the leader on rail, easy run on turn, kept to inside after straightening and finished off evenly.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 lengths back on turn, taken wide in straight and made good progress.
Began well, raced in midfield, found rail near 550M, saved ground on turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide at rear, 4 lengths back on turn, taken wide in straight and made minor progress.
Quickly into stride, showed early speed and took the lead easily, led by L, headed near 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Bumped start, positioned on rail at rear, 5 to 6 lengths back, there to turn, kept to inside after straightening, finished off one-paced.
Jumped well from a wide draw, unable to slot in, raced 3 wide with no cover, 1-1/2L back, still no cover on turn, peaked early in straight and weakened gradually thereafter.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced 3 wide at rear, 5 lengths or so back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Crowded out start, steadied off heels early, raced at tail, difficult to settle near 800M, 7 lengths back on turn,showed nothing in straight, finished last.
In midfield, sat 4-1/4L behind along the rail, gradually pulled away from 150M and scored comfortably by 2L.
Settled to race in midfield, 2 wide until shifted out after 600M, ran on strongly inside final 100M to take 2nd.
Niggled along to find the box-seat, sat 1-3/4L off, ran on very well and held onto 3rd when going to the line.
Taken back and raced at the tail, sat 7-1/4L behind 2 wide, continued on well and hit the line strongly, just missed 3rd.
Eased back and raced at the rear, 7-1/2L behind along the rail, continued to make ground to the line.
Jumped awkwardly and lost ground, sat in behind midfield, 5-3/4L behind along the rail, saved minor ground.
Urged to obtain lead from barrier 1, led by 3/4L, caught and found no extra passing 200M.
Asked forward, settled in one-off one-back position, sat 2-1/2L off, swung wide and was one paced.
Pushed forward and raced outside the lead, sat 3/4L off, weakened out passing 150M.
Settled to race in behind midfield, 5-1/2L behind 2 wide, kept on one paced to the line.
Taken back to be near the rear, 6-3/4L behind 3 wide with cover, did not improve.
Jumped well, settled at the rear and raced 3 wide throughout, did not feature.
Jumped well, sat a length behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after straightening and finished off well to score.
Began fairly, positioned 5 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground to near 400M, finished off strongly in straight to take 2nd.
Began well from gate 1, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well throughout, headed after turning in, but fought on well thereafter to take a place.
Fast into stride, sent forward to race 2 wide in 2nd, improved from 400M, took the lead after turning in, peaked and headed near 150M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Average to begin, race 2 wide, 4 lengths back, improved from near 450M, very wide turning in, made minor progress in straight.
Began fairly, positioned on rail in midfield, 3 lengths back, saved ground on turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Clean jump, positioned 2 wide, better than midfield, there to turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Bumped start and unbalanced, raced 2 wide, 6 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced 2 wide at rear, 7 to 8 lengths back, still well back on turn, made no progress in straight.
Bumped on jumping, sent forward to race prominently but wide, no cover throughout, peaked on turn, weakened early in straight.
Hampered start, raced at tail throughout, never competitive.
Crossed to the lead near 1400M, quickened up pace halfway, kept responding to riding, well on top nearing 100M and never in danger from there.
Began awkwardly from draw 1, held up ahead of mid-pack, finished off honestly final 300M but couldn't peg back the winner.
Tracked leaders in 4th along the fence, enjoyed a ground saving trip, tried hard in straight but unable to get closer to winner, lost 2nd inside 50M but hung on for 3rd placing.
Settled down 2-wide in midfield in 7th place, 4-5Ls off leader making home turn, battled on moderately towards the finish, held by leaders.
Niggled along after the start to be tracking leaders in 5th, raced keenly early stages due to slow pace, held similar position to turn, stayed on mildly over final 300M.
From draw 11 crossed to race 3-wide in midfield, dropped back to 9th back-straight, took a while to stoke up on straightening, made some ground late.
Dropped back from wide draw to be near the rear on settling, 6L to make up 400M, worked home fairly without threatening.
Raced on pace just behind leader along the 2-path, pace fast from 1200M, kept on one pace early straight, flattened 150M.
Steadied after the jump to be 2nd last 8Ls away on settling, failed to get into contention leaving the bend.
Pushed along after jumping, caught 3-wide no cover outside leader for most part, run ended 200M, weakened away.
Not hurried after the start, held up behind midfield 5-6Ls back, couldn't come on straightening. Never dangerous.
Switched off to last, 10Ls off the pace middle stages, failed to run on, never involved.
