Soon took up running, led or disputed lead on stands rail, held slender advantage from coming onto course proper despite hanging in, won readily.
Settled just off the pace near stands rail, came to challenge inside the final 300 metres, ran on to be nearest at finish.
Pressed forward from the one gate to share the lead on stands side, unable to peg back the winner under pressure throughout closing stages, pipped for 2nd late.
Moderate start, settled towards the rear, commenced move inside the final 400 metres, ran on well.
Settled in last few on stands rail, made up good ground inside the final 250 metres.
Moderate start settling just off the pace, came under pressure to hold place coming onto course proper, faded gradually inside the final 200 metres. (Tongue over bit)
Broke well, settled in rear of midfield on stands rail, came under pressure coming onto course proper, kept on steadily without quickening.
Began awkwardly losing ground, travelled well behind, switched inside onto the centre of the course proper, fought on under pressure.
Bumped at the start, soon outpaced despite niggled along, switched off stands rail onto the centre of the track for a run coming onto course proper, went past well-beaten horses.
Not far off the pace early stages, gradually dropped to last few.
Settled in rear of midfield without cover from a low draw, soon faded under pressure after coming onto course proper.
Jostled at start, soon came forward to join the leaders near stands rail, unable to sustain effort inside the final 400 metres. (Lame next day)
Travelled awkwardly early stages, continued to travel keenly after switching onto the centre of course proper, weakened noticeably. (Jockey questioned)
Settled in midfield, faded under pressure shortly after coming onto course proper.
At back, 2 wide, benefited by the fast tempo, dashed well 350M to score.
Hard ridden to hold the rail just behind the pace, progressed steadily 400M for 2nd.
Pushed to take rail and led at fast sectionals, hung on well until 100M overhauled, ran on for 3rd.
At back along the fence, suited by the fast tempo, made steady ground 250M.
At rear, 2-3 wide, favoured by the fast pace, progressed steadily 300M.
Hard ridden early, trapped 3 wide throughout in midfield, made steady ground 300M.
Hard ridden to keep up in front of midfield, 2-3 wide, held ground in straight.
Hard ridden to obtain box seat, not suited by the fast tempo, weakened 150M.
Pushed forward, sat 2 wide, harmed by the fast sectionals, emptied 250M.
Hard ridden early to keep up in midfield along the fence, benefited by the fast tempo, no dash.
At rear, race 3-5 wide, never improved.
Began awkwardly and lost ground, raced midfield, improved on rail at Home Turn and in the straight, issued a challenge passing 100M, finished strongly to score.
Fast out then ridden along to settle outside the lead from the widest barrier, ran on in the straight, just missed by SH.
Raced behind leaders, commenced to improve after 500M, responded well in the straight.
Crowded then taken back at start, near 200M shifted out to obtain clear running, then passing 100M made up some nice ground.
Settled at back, widest on straightening, made ground in final stages, worked home nicely.
Travelled behind midfield, difficult to settle in middle stages, gained ground passing 50M.
Moderate start, settled behind midfield, worked home OK.
Began awkwardly, lost left hind plate near 900M, raced behind midfield on rail, held up from 300M until 100M, made some ground passing 50M.
Urged along to take lead, in the straight under pressure then weakened passing 150M.
Settled in box seat, tried to improve on straightening, near 100M was crowded for room then gave ground.
Near 1200M lost right front plate, raced midfield, one-paced.
Travelled wide and without cover in midfield position, approaching 100M was checked when crowded for room.
Taken back at start, no response in the straight.
Lost right front plate at 1000M, travelled wide and without cover, gave ground in the straight.
Away with them, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, angled out early in straight, finished off strongly to score. (Lost right front plate near 800M.)
Moderately away from a wide draw, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well throughout, kept on very well in straight but just couldn't hold off the winner late.
Slowly away, raced at rear on rail, saved ground on turn, angled out after turning in, closed off well to take 3rd.

Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 to 3 wide with cover at rear, bumped and unbalanced near 900M, then bumped again near 750M, still 6 lengths back turning in, made very good progress in straight to make frame, good debut.
Jumped well from gate 9, sent forward to race 2 wide in 2nd, 1-1/4L back, same position on turn, peaked early in straight, slightly weakened thereafter.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, 9 lengths back, still last turning in, made reasonable progress in straight.
Began awkwardly and shifted out abruptly, positioned 3 lengths behind the leader on rail early, 2 wide from near 800M, peaked early in straight, kept on evenly to the line.
Fast into stride, sent forward to race prominently, positioned a length behind the leader on turn, lacked an extra gear in straight, finished off one-paced.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, failed to close off in straight.

Began awkwardly, raced 2 wide at rear, checked near 900M, bumped near 750M, awkwardly placed rounding the home turn, responded fairly early in straight, checked off heels near 200M, made no progress thereafter.
Slow to begin, positioned on rail behind midfield, there to turn, failed to close off in straight. (Had blood at its right nostril.)
Average to begin, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 5 lengths or so back, same position on turn, showed no response in straight, finished last.
Jumped well, positioned on rail in 3rd, a length behind the leader on turn, angled out early in straight and finished off strongly to score.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced wide with cover at rear, 4 to 5 lengths back, improved from 500M, made very good progress in straight to get 2nd.
Began awkwardly, raced at tail early, moved closer in the middle stages, 4 lengths or so back on turn, taken widest in straight and finished off very strongly to take 3rd.
Began well, sent forward to race in 2nd, 2 wide, half length back on turn, took the lead early in straight, but couldn't hold off the first few late.
Taken back to race 2 wide behind midfield, checked off heels 1100M, 3 wide with cover from near 900M, carried wider on turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, raced tight near 500M, finished off evenly in straight.
Clean jump, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground throughout, 3 lengths or so back on turn, finished off evenly.
Slightly slow out, positioned on rail at rear, 5 lengths back on turn, made no real progress in straight.
Away with them, raced 3 wide with no cover in midfield, closer in the middle stages but still wide, throughout, weakened in straight when hard run took effect.

Began well, sent forward to take the lead, led by 2 lengths early, slowed the tempo in the middle stages, challenged on turn, headed early in straight, dropped off gradually thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Sent forward to take the rail and led by 1L, kept on well to hold on and scored by a neck.
Niggled along to take the box-seat, sat 2-1/2L off the lead, ran on nicely to finish a neck behind the winner.
Urged and then settled to race in midfield, 4L behind 2 wide, sustained a good run to the finish to take 3rd.
Settled at the rear, 8L behind the lead along the rail, continued to make nice inroad along the inner track.
Sat near the rear, 7L behind 3 wide but with cover, swung widest and continued to make nice ground to the line.
Raced towards the tail end, sat 6-3/4L behind the lead 2 wide, made ground steadily in the straight.
Settled to race in about midfield, sat 5-1/4L behind 2 wide, improved steadily to the line.
Raced in behind midfield, 5-1/2L behind 3 wide but with cover, commenced to improve at 200M and hit the line well.
Travelled in midfield, 4-1/4L behind along the rail, ran on until couldn't find extra approaching 100M.
Pushed and settled in front of midfield, 4-1/4L wide and without cover, continued one paced to the line.
Raced in worse than midfield, 6-1/4L behind along the rail, was one paced and eased down late.
Sent forward, settled in one-off one-back position, sat 2-1/2L off, found nothing in the straight.
Asked to go forward, sat outside the lead 1L off, emptied soon after straightening.
At the rear throughout, never a factor.
Clean jump, sent forward to take the lead, enjoyed the easy lead throughout, kicked clear after turning in and scored easily.
Moderately away from a wide draw, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, 1-1/2 length back on turn, kept on well in straight to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.
Average to begin, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, same position on turn, taken wide in straight and finished off strongly to take a place, nearest on line.
Fast into stride, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, easy run to turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Began well, positioned 2 wide in midfield, awkwardly placed near 900M, checked off heels near 700M, showed limited response after turning in, just kept on evenly to the line.
Away with them, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after straightening, finished off only fairly.
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned 4 lengths behind the leader on rail, same margin back on turn, made no real progress in straight.
Clean jump, unable to slot in, travelled wide with no cover in midfield, 4 wide turning, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Slowly away and crowded, raced at tail, 5 to 6 lengths back, made no progress in straight.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced wide with cover at rear, started to race ungenerously from 900M, 5 lengths or so back on turn, failed to make any progress in straight.
Jumped with them, raced 3 wide with no cover, better than midfield, difficult to settle near 1000M, similar position on turn, emptied early in straight and eased.
Away well enough, stayed in touch behind leaders, quickened up well to wrestle the lead 150M, kept going soundly for convincing victory.
Reserved after the jump, switched off to last 9Ls off the pace in middle stages, got split 400M, closed off strongly to go 2nd near the line.
Pressed forward from draw 13, had uncontested lead, quicken up tempo 600M, kept going well in straight only run down by winner 150M, lost 2nd close home.
Showed speed to be tracking the pace in 3rd, saved ground on the inside, chased evenly final 300M, held by leaders.
Raced handily behind leader, kept chasing leaving the bend but couldn't reel in leader, awkwardly placed 250M, battled away to the finish.
Began fairly, lost ground when bumped, restrained behind midfield, got held up from home turn to early straight, closed off reasonably well over final 300M. Didn't have all favours.
Settled down 5Ls off the pace in midfield, well covered, kept battling away in straight without threatening.
In 5th spot ahead of midfield, wide no cover for most part, kept on same pace in straight and never a real danger to leaders.
From outside barrier dropped back to race in rear, moved closer passing 550M, got badly unbalanced top of straight when unable to improve, ran on only fairly thereafter.
Moderate jump, improved to race in midfield 4-5Ls back on fence, lacked the turn of foot, never a threat to leaders.
Restrained behind midfield 5Ls off the pace middle stages, pushed along 500M, kept on same pace to line, no threat to leaders.
Jumped on terms, eased back towards the rear 7Ls behind leader, into clear 450M but unable to quicken up under 10lb claiming rider.
Dropped back to be near last 8L off the pace, didn't run on entering straight, never a factor.
From wide barrier crossed to a 3-wide spot near the rear, over 8Ls off the pace 400M, failed to close off turning home, eased. (Jockey concerned horse's action.)
Bumped start, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, shared lead turning in, kept on very strongly in straight and scored easily.

Began well from a tricky gate, unable to slot in, positioned 3 wide with no cover, a length or so back, similar position on turn, kept on well in straight to take 2nd without posing any threat to the winner.
Hampered start, showed no early speed, raced at tail, 5 to 6 lengths back on turn, taken wide in straight and made very good progress to take 3rd.
Clean jump, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 3 to 4 lengths back on turn, made good progress in straight to make frame without threatening.
Hampered start, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths back, same margin back on turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Average to begin, no early speed, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, there to turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Bumped start, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well on turn, headed and peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Shifted out at start and made contact with rivals, positioned on rail at rear, 4 lengths or so back on turn, finished off one-paced in straight.
Moderately away, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, easy run on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Away with them, positioned on rail in midfield, there to turn, weakened gradually in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, wider on turn, emptied early in straight and eased. (Jockey reported his horse did not feel comfortable in its action during the race.)
Jumped well from the widest draw, unable to slot in, raced 4 wide with no cover throughout, weakened on turn, ran on empty in straight.

Pressed forward to be well placed early, 4th/5th on the fence. Ground away early in the straight, before getting a nose in front at 150m. Stayed on strongly in the straight, and held of late challengers.
Cruised forward early to settle just behind midfield. Came around heels at 350m for clear run. Strong in the straight, but was struggling to make up ground on winner late.
Began well, but eased back to settle around midfield. Missed a run at 300m and had to come inside off heels. Strong to the line when clear from 200m.
Eased out early to settle worse than midfield. 2nd last on turn for home. Came across heels to be widest in the straight from 250m. Finished strongly and only just missed a minor place.
Began awkwardly, but recovered well and pushed forward to share the lead. Solo leader down the straight until 150m, but couldn't hold out challengers and 1 paced late.
Tardy to begin and settled at the rear of the field. Made up good ground early in the straight and was staying on solidly late.
Eased back from the wide draw to settle at the rear of the field. Stayed on solidly in the straight without threatening.
Crowded on jumping and eased back to settle around midfield, 4 wide with limited cover and no cover after 700m. Made up ground early in the straight, and solid late without threatening.
Eased back early to settle just behind midfield. OK in the straight, but slightly 1 paced late. Vet  Lame near foreleg.
Went forward early to ensure he had a share of the lead, 1 off the fence. Battled on early in the straight, but out of steam from 250m and dropped out.
Got head up on jumping, missed the kick and got a long way back. 3-4L last in the back straight, and had too much to do in the straight. Eased out late.
Pressed forward to be handily placed 3rd/4th. Never responded to pressure and dropped out in the straight.

Originally settled around midfield and wide, before pushing forward at 1000m to settle 3rd. Off heels at 850m, and still stuck 3 wide. Nothing left in the tank late and made no impression in the straight. Jockey questioned.
Settled around midfield early. Gave nothing in the straight, and dropped out quickly. Unacceptable performance.

Settled in midfield in 6th near the rail, switched 5 wide turning for home, hit the front 200 metres out, won easily.
Moderate start, settled just worse than midfield in 8th, came under pressure rounding home bend, fought on steadily down the centre of the straight to snatch 2nd late.
Led early, ceded advantage for one back rail position turning into back straight, angled out to challenge entering home straight but failed to quicken to threaten.
Niggled at early, settled just off the pace in 5th mainly some 3L back on the rail, saved ground turning in and held some chance early in straight, failed to quicken to threaten.
Taken back to rail from a wide gate, blundered passing the winning post the first time, gained closer to 9th approaching the Rock, saved ground turning in, fought on steadily under pressure.
Broke well from a wide-ish draw, settled 1L back in 2nd 2-wide, came under strong pressure turning in, ran home one-paced.

Slowly away, soon taken across for rails run towards the rear in 8th, gained slightly closer to 7th passing the 800 metres, came under pressure rounding home bend and saved ground turning in, ran home one-paced.
Pressed forward from a wide draw, took up running 1200 metres out, led until overhauled inside the final 200 metres.
Slightly slow out, soon picked up to 5th some 3L back, improved slightly to 4th in back straight, came under pressure rounding home bend, soon weakened under pressure after straightening.
Always struggling at the back.
Settled in last few, never seen with a chance. (Questioned for disappointing performance)
Eased to sit in midfield along the fence, harmed by the slow pace, unleashed strong finishing efforts 250M to score.
Hard ridden to secure box seat, favoured by the slow sectionals, ran on well for 2nd.
Hard ridden forward, sat 2 wide, benefited by the slow tempo, ran on well for 3rd.
Hard ridden to take rail and led at advantageous slow sectionals, hung on until 100M overhauled.
Eased to sit in front of midfield, 2 wide, not suited by the slow tempo, dashed well 200M.
Hard ridden to hold the rail in midfield, not suited by the slow pace, dashed well 300, lack room 150M.
Eased to rear, 2 wide, harmed by the slow pace, little dash 300M.
Eased back, took rail, not suited by the slow tempo, lack room 250M, little dash when clear.
Eased back, 2-3 wide, not suited by the slow pace, little dash 200M.
Eased back, trapped 3 wide throughout, harmed by the slow tempo, no dash.
Eased at start, harmed by the slow pace, no progress.
Never better than midfield.
Settled at tail, commenced to improve on straightening, quickened passing 100M, scored unchallenged.
Took lead in the early stages then passing 1500M raced in box seat, made ground passing 200M, finished solidly.
Travelled midfield, held up from 350M to 300M, gained ground passing 100M, worked home nicely.
Urged along to take forward position from widest barrier, took lead near 1500M, asked for effort passing 500M, fought hard entire straight, finished well.
Travelled at handy position, tried to improve passing 600M, made some ground in the straight.
Taken back at start, passing 500M under pressure, responded OK in the straight.
Travelled wide and without cover, then passing 1500M improved to outside the lead, one-paced in the straight.
Settled behind midfield, widest on straightening, limited response when under pressure.
Raced midfield on rail, gave ground passing 150M, failed to run on.
Settled midfield, wide on straightening, no response.
Taken back at start, near 600M lost ground when improved to tight running, emptied near 150M.
Began well from gate 1, positioned on rail in 4th, right behind the leader on turn, led near 200M, kept on very well to hold off the challenge and scored.
Steadied on jumping and shifted in, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground to near 400M, finished off strongly to take 2nd, just narrowly beaten.
Away with them, sent forward to race in 2nd, a length behind the leader, challenged the leader on turn, kept on very well in straight, just narrowly beaten by the first two.
Taken back from the widest draw, positioned on rail behind midfield, 7 lengths back, slightly improved along the rail on turn, kept on well in straight to make frame.
Clean jump, positioned 2 wide, 3 to 4 lengths back, 3 wide from near 650M, finished off evenly in straight, never a threat to the first few.
Taken back to race at rear on rail, moved closer on turn, but still 5 lengths behind, made minor progress in straight without threatening.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, finished off evenly in straight.

Fast into stride, took the lead easily and set the tempo, enjoyed the easy lead to turn, challenged near 400M, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed near 200M, weakened thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back from gate 11, raced 2 wide at rear, 8 to 9 lengths back, improved from near 450M, very wide turning in, made no real progress in straight.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide behind midfield, improved from near 400M, failed to make any progress in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, 10 lengths or so back, still last turning in, finished off one-paced.
Out in line, raced prominently but wide early, got cover from near 800M, showed no response after turning in, eased final 100M.
Jumped nicely, sent forward to take the lead, challenged on turn, kept on very well in straight to score.
Jumped well from a middle draw, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, positioned in 3rd on turn, finished off very well in straight, just narrowly beaten.
Average to begin, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, angled out early in straight and made good progress to take a place.
Began well, raced 2 wide in midfield, difficult to settle near 1000M, similar position on turn, made some progress in straight to make frame without threatening.
Taken back to race 2 wide behind midfield, 4 to 5 lengths back, similar position on turn, made some headway in straight without threatening, just missed frame on line.
Steadied on jumping, raced 3 wide at rear, 6 lengths or so back, 2 wide on turn, taken widest in straight and made some progress.
Steadied on jumping, positioned 6 lengths behind the leader on rail, there to turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened from near 150M, eased late.
Jumped with them, positioned 2 wide, better than midfield, 3 lengths back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Began fairly from a wide draw, unable to slot in early, moved forward from 1100M to race outside the leader, shared lead on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Began only fairly, raced 2 wide at rear, peaked on turn, showed no response in straight.

Slowly away, raced at tail, well back on turn, showed no response in straight, eased late. (Jockey reported his horse did not feel comfortable in its action.) (Lame left front leg with a stiff and restricted action next day.)
Pushed and sat outside the lead, gradually kicked away from 200M, continued and held off late challenges to score.
Raced in just behind midfield, sat 2-1/2L behind 2 wide, commenced a strong run home from 150M, missed by 1/2L.
Travelled at the rear, 4L behind the lead 2 wide, switched wide at the exit, saved nice ground and finished off strongly.
Slotted into midfield, sat 2-3/4L behind 3 wide with cover, made ground and finished off well to the line.
Sent forward to be prominent, sat 1-1/2L off 3 wide without cover, ran on okay to the finish.
Niggled along, settled in one-off one-back position, sat 1-1/4L off, kept on one paced to the line.
Urged forward to obtain the box-seat, sat 1-1/2L behind the lead, one paced and emptied late.
Steadied after the start, sat towards the rear 4-1/4L behind along the rail, slight dash early then one paced.
Taken back after failing to muster, 4-1/2L behind and 3 wide rounding turn, did not improve.
Sent forward to take rail and led, weakened out near 200M.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide behind midfield, gradually improved from 750M, took the lead near 500M, kept on strongly after turning in and scored.

Moderately away from a wide draw, raced 3 wide behind midfield early, sent forward on the first turn to race outside the leader in 2nd, similar position home turn, kept on well in straight to take 2nd.
Jumped well, sent forward to race prominently early, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths back in the middle stages, there to turn, closed off well to take 3rd.
Average to begin, raced 3 wide with cover in front of midfield early, took the lead near 1150M, headed near 500M, kept on evenly in straight.
Jumped well, positioned 2 wide in midfield, improved from 600M, 3 lengths back on turn, made some progress in straight.

Bumped start, positioned 4 lengths behind the leader on rail, 2 wide on turn, made some progress early in straight, angled out near 150M, no clear running over the concluding stages, not able to be ridden out near the finish.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide, better than midfield, travelled keenly near 1200M, improved from 600M, 3 wide turning, peaked early in straight, finished off one-paced. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began well from gate 1, positioned 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, same margin back on turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Jumped well, took the early lead, headed near 1150M, stayed 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, same position on turn, kept on evenly early in straight, weakened from 150M, eased late.
Out in line, raced 2 wide at rear, 7 lengths back, moved closer from 600M, 4 lengths back on turn, made no progress in straight.
Taken back to race at rear on rail, 7 lengths back, difficult to settle near 1300M, still 6 lengths back on turn, failed to make any progress in straight.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail throughout, showed no response in straight, finished last.
Led steadily, had uncontested lead to 450M, kept on solidly to the finish bravely holding off challengers from both sides.
Tracked leader, moved out from 500M to challenge eventual winner, raced on strongly to line, just held by nose.
Jumped on terms to be racing in midfield 2-3Ls back, strongly challenged and every chance throughout the final 200M, just held.
Reined in to be 5Ls off the pace near last, ran on well between horses but held by first 3.
Settled down 3-wide towards the rear, pulled wide on straightening, stayed on moderately.
Dropped back from wide barrier, held up in last 5-6Ls off the leader, made steady progress down outside to finish just behind the place-getters.
Settled down in midfield along the 3-path, passed a few over final 300M but never likely.
In mid-division, on straightening only held ground to the line, never reached contention.
Positively ridden out the gate, stayed in touch to pace, couldn't quicken when asked, no threat from 200M. (Mucus.)
Away well enough, restrained and shuffled back to near rear approaching home turn, couldn't engage with the others on straightening, wilted passing 200M.
Slow out, failed to muster early speed, driven into a more forward position after 800M but caught wide no cover to straight, struggled in the run home, soon out of contention.
Strolled forward to race just behind leader, couldn't go on leaving the bend, weakened noticeably 250M.

Broke well, settled just off the pace, soon hit the front after the 400 metres and soon drew over 1L clear, just held on to the line.
Settled in last few, snuck up on the rail rounding home bend, inconvenienced after straightening, ran on under pressure to be nearest at finish.

Niggled at early along the rail improving gradually to close-up 4th rounding home bend, gained 3rd into the straight and 2nd passing the 300 metres, kept on steadily but caught for 2nd inside the final 100 metres.
Travelled keenly in better than midfield, drifted back to just worse than midfield in 8th rounding home bend, shifted wide into the straight, ran on steadily without threatening. (Lame next day)
Travelled wide in midfield or just better, came from 4-wide to within 2L of lead turning in, unable to sustain effort closing stages.
Settled in rear from a wide gate, saved ground on the inside turning in, sustained progress down the home straight without threatening.
Well there, took up running after the first 400 metres, led the field until headed after straightening, folded up quickly.
Jumped awkwardly losing ground, tailed-off in back straight, commenced move rounding home bend and widest runner turning in, went past well-beaten horses early in straight.
Held up in prominent position, about 2L off the pace in 5th rounding home bend, found nothing under pressure after straightening.
Settled in last few, made no impression the run home.
Ridden from a wide gate to be prominent 3-wide, dropped away quickly after straightening.
Hard ridden to take rail, led at advantageous slow sectionals, made all.
Box seat, favoured by the slow tempo, closed off strongly 300M for 2nd.
Pushed forward, sat 2 wide, benefited by the slow sectionals, held ground for 3rd.
Eased back, 2-3 wide, harmed by the slow tempo, unleashed strong finishing efforts 250M.
Pushed early but not muster, at back along the fence, lack room 400M, harmed by the slow tempo, dashed well when clear.
Hard ridden to hold the rail in midfield, not suited by the slow tempo, just held ground.
Behind midfield, trapped 3-4 wide, harmed by the slow pace, dashed well 300M whilst hanging in.
Behind midfield, 2 wide, blocked 4-2, dashed well when clear despite not suited by the slow pace.
Eased back early, trapped 3 wide, moved forward 900M to take advantages of the slow pace, out of fuel 200M.
Midfield, trapped 3 wide, not suited by the slow pace, no turn of foot.
Eased back, trapped 3-4 wide, harmed by the slow tempo, no dash.
Very slow away, at rear, on the fence, raced keenly, harmed by the slow pace, no progress.
Hard ridden to sit in midfield, 2 wide, soon emptied 350M.
Eased back, never a factor.
Urged along to take lead from wide barrier, travelled comfortably, responded well in the straight, scored unchallenged.
Settled at back, asked for effort after 700M, gradually made ground in the straight, finished nicely.
Ridden to take box seat, kept on rail to save ground at Home Turn, came home well.
Jumped nicely, raced behind the lead, fought hard entire straight, worked home well.
Settled midfield on rail, battled hard in the straight, finished OK.
Settled midfield, made some ground passing 100M, finished fairly.
Taken back at start, raced behind midfield, under pressure and worked home fairly.
Began awkwardly, very difficult to settle, travelled wide and without cover after 1000M, widest on straightening, limited response in the straight, must trial.
Raced midfield on rail, one-paced in the straight.
Raced at back on rail, held up near 100M, limited response.
Taken back at start, no response when asked for effort.
Raced midfield, travelled keenly, weakened over concluding stages.
Settled behind midfield, failed to run on in the straight.
Always back, never in it.
Bumped on jumping, raced 3 wide in midfield early, moved forward to race in 3rd, still 3 wide with no cover on turn, finished off well in straight and scored.
Began well, no early speed, positioned on rail behind midfield, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after straightening and made very good progress to take 2nd, nearest on line.
Fast into stride, sent forward to race in 2nd, 2 wide on turn, kept on well in straight to take a place.
Away well, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 3 lengths back on turn, made good progress in straight to make frame.
Jumped well from the widest draw, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well throughout, kept on well early in straight, headed near 200M, weakened thereafter.
Bumped start, raced at tail, checked near 1200M, 5 to 6 lengths back on turn, taken widest in straight and made good progress to be nearest on line.

Slightly slow out, raced wide behind midfield, difficult to settle and checked off heels near 1200M, 3 wide turning, finished off evenly in straight. (Lame right front leg with a swollen right front cannon next day morning.)
Jumped well from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground throughout, only showed limited response in straight.
Raced at rear, difficult to settle near 1200M, 4 lengths or so back turning in, finished off evenly in straight.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide better than midfield, similar position on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Moderately away from a wide draw, raced 3 wide behind midfield, 3 lengths back on turn, showed no response in straight, finished last. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped well from gate 1, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, saved ground throughout, no daylight early in straight, finished off very strongly when clear thereafter to score.
Began only fairly and bumped, raced at rear, 6 lengths or so back, there to turn, finished off very strongly in straight to take 2nd. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began fairly, positioned 4 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after straightening and finished off strongly to take 3rd.
Moderately away from a wide draw, raced 3 wide better than midfield, no cover on turn, kept on very well early in straight, peaked final 100M, weakened thereafter.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide, 4 lengths back, same margin back on turn, angled out in straight and made some progress. (Bled.)
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 7 lengths back at rear, still 6 length back turning in, made very good progress in straight to be nearest on line.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide, 3 lengths back, there to turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Began awkwardly, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, similar position on turn, showed good response early in straight, peaked near 200M, slightly weakened thereafter.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, 8 lengths or so back on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Jumped well, positioned 2 wide, a length or so back, similar position on turn, kept on evenly early instraight, weakened from 150M.
Moderately away from a tricky gate, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well throughout, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed near 200M, weakened thereafter.
Bumped start, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, 4 lengths or so back turning in, made no progress in straight. (Lame left front leg next day morning.)
Slightly slow out,positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail,saved ground on turn, showed no response early in straight, weakened from 200M.
Jumped well from gate 13, sent forward to race prominently, 2ndon turn, peaked early in straight, weakened rapidly from 250M.
Pushed and stayed on the rail to lead from barrier 1, continued on nicely to maintain lead, scored by 1L.
Travelled in behind midfield, 4-1/2L behind 2 wide, made move prior to 600M, kept well to the line for 2nd.
Began well, niggled and settled to race in midfield, 2-3/4L behind 2 wide, dashed on strongly from 100M to the finish.
Jumped slowly, caught up to race at the rear, 5-3/4L behind 2 wide, made ground and closed off well to the line.
Urged along and settled to race outside the lead, sat 1L off, kept on one paced to the line.
Pushed forward and took box-seat, sat 1-1/2L off the lead, ran on until emptied late.
Crowded start and lost ground, made up to be in behind midfield, 4-1/2L off along the rail, showed no turn of foot.
Settled in midfield, 3L behind along the rail, weakened passing 300M.

Jumped well, raced prominently early, restrained and sat just off the pace afterpassing 1000M, travelled well on turn, hit the front near 300M, kept on very well thereafter to hold off the challengers.
Began well, positioned 2 to 3 lengths back in 4th, same position on turn, finished off the race very well but always held by the winner.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide at rear, 5 lengths or so back, improved on turn, finished off the race nicely to take a place.
Began only fairly, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Bumped start and unbalanced, positioned 2 wide, 4 lengths back,checked near 500M, same margin back turning in, finished off evenly.
Quickly into stride, sent forward to take the lead, joined over 800M out, headed near 300M, weakened thereafter.
Taken back to race at tail, 8 lengths back, closer on turn, angled out near 550M, failed to close off in straight.
Dropped back from gate 9, raced 2 wide at rear, still 5 lengths back turning in, failed to make any progress in straight.
Bumped start and unbalanced, soon pushed along to chase the leaders, shared lead on turn, peaked near 300M, weakened thereafter.
Away well from draw 1, handily placed just behind leaders in a fast run race, displayed sharp turnoff foot to lead 300M out, kicked clear at 200M and raced away for a big win.

Eased back from wide barrier, raced in last for first half of the race, moved closer to be 4Ls behind pace making home turn, stayed on well to go 2nd near 100M but couldn't get closer to runaway winner.
Jumped on terms, restrained to race in midfield 3-4Ls off the pace, kept working to the line for distant 3rd.
Held up near the rear about 7Ls off the good pace, ran on evenly to claim 4th but well behind the winner.
Settled in 4th place always in touch with leaders, well placed to strike 450M, worked home fairly, no threat from 150M.
Held up 6th of 8, 4Ls behind leader on settling, couldn't quicken in straight, didn't look to threaten at any stage.
Went forward, tracked leader in strongly run race, brief effort early straight vying for the lead, weakened from 200M.
Crossed to the lead near 1600M, set good pace to straight, under siege 300M, tired from the early work at 200M weakened to last. (Unacceptable Performance.)
Taken back from a wide draw, positioned 7 lengths or so back at rear, saved ground on turn, no daylight early in straight, angled out near 200M, finished off very strongly to score.
Bumped on jumping, raced prominently, 2 wide, travelled well throughout, took the lead near 200M, kept on well but couldn't hold off the winner late.
Away with them, positioned 5 lengths behind the leader on rail, same position on turn, showed very good progress in straight to take 3rd.
Out in line, raced 3 wide at rear, 6 lengths or so back, there to turn, taken wide in straight and finished off very strongly to be nearest on line.
Fast into stride, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, fought on steadily in straight.
Crowded on jumping, raced 2 wide in midfield, found rail on turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, 8 lengths back, slightly improved from 600M, taken wide in straight and made some progress in straight.
Jumped well from a wide draw, raced prominently but wide, took the lead near 700M, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed near 200M, emptied thereafter. (Lost right front plate.)
Crowded out start, recovered to take the lead, headed near 700M, 2nd on turn, kept on well to near 200M, emptied thereafter.
Began only fairly, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, made no progress in straight.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 5 lengths or so back, improved from near 600M, made minor progress early in straight, weakened from near 200M.
Jumped well from a wide draw, unable to slot in, trapped 4 wide, 2 to 3 lengths back, no cover throughout, weakened gradually in straight.
Away with them, raced 3 wide with cover, 2 lengths back, peaked on turn, no response in straight.
Average to begin, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, peaked on turn, showed no response in straight, eased final 200M.
Cruised out to settle around midfield. Came wider on the turn, with a lap full of horse. Pulled away from 300, and showed good turn of foot. No challengers late.
Pushed out to be the clear leader early. Solid in the straight, but couldn't match the turn of foot of the winner. No threat for 2nd late.
Eased forward to settle around midfield. No clear run in the straight until coming out off heels well after 300m. Ran strongly when clear and grabbed 3rd on the line.
Eventually settled forward of midfield, but stuck 3 wide no cover from 1000m. Ran strongly early in the straight, but slightly 1 paced late and lost 3rd near the line.
Crowded on jumping and eased back to settle towards the rear of the field. Wider in the straight and stayed on solidly without threatening.
Bounded out, heavily bumped and badly unbalanced on jumping. Lost a lot of ground and needed to push forward to settle at the rear of the field. Stayed on solidly and finished well late.
Pushed forward early, and keen when steadied 1300m. Handily placed behind the leader. Didn't run on in the straight and went to the line under hands and heels.
Taken up to be handily placed 4th. Prominent early in the straight, but went to the line 1 paced late.
Dropped back early to sit at the back of the pack. Wider on the turn, but only picked up some of the slower ones late.
Eased forward to settle around midfield. Only plugged away fairly under hands and heels in the straight.
Cruised out early to settle forward of midfield. Checked and unbalanced when racing keenly onto heels 700m and lost ground. Didn't respond in the straight.
Settled towards the rear of the field early. Gave nothing in the straight.
Leapt out of the barrier before sitting midfield. Unsettled and worked forward in back straight to sit 2nd at 1000m. Didn't kick in the straight and not pushed hard late.
Bounded out and landed heavily and missed the kick by many lengths. Settled a long last and was never involved.

Began from a wide gate, ridden along better than midfield before gaining closer to 3rd passing the 800 metres, remained 3-wide without cover turning for home, fought on steadily to hit the front inside the final 100 metres.
Settled in last few from a wide gate, inconvenienced 800 metres out, in similar position turning in, finished off the race well.
Moderate start, soon driven up to the lead, steadied pace after obtaining rails run passing the 800 metres, led until headed under pressure inside final 100 metres.
Settled in last few, snuck up on the rail turning in, sustained progress in straight, nearest at finish.
Ridden to close-up positon in 2nd, soon came under pressure after straightening, ran home one-paced.
Jumped fairly, settled mainly in midfield, came under pressure rounding home bend, ran on to be nearest at finish.
Jumped fairly from the one draw, settled not far off in 5th, shifted 2-wide coming onto home bend, kept on in straight despite tight run closing stages.
Dipped jumping out, soon dropped to midfield despite niggling along, shuffled slightly further back approaching home bend, some 5L back in 8th turning in, fought on steadily without threatening.
Settled wide in last few, went wider turning into the straight, fought on steadily running past well-beaten horses.
Settled wide in midfield from the widest gate, in similar position turning in, ran home one-paced.

Quickly recovered from a moderate start to be up with the pace briefly, taken 2L back to 4th on the rail and remained similar into the straight, folded up quickly after straightening.(Questioned for disappointing performance)
Soon outpaced, never seen with a chance.
Pushed forward, sat 2 wide, harmed by the fast pace, kicked strongly 300M to score.
Hard ridden forward, 2-3 wide, not suited by the fast sectionals, ran on well for 2nd.
Hard ridden early but not muster, midfield 2 wide, suited by the fast tempo, on heels 600M, progressed steadily 400M for 3rd.
Eased back, 2 wide, benefited by the fast pace, progressed steadily 300M.
Eased back, took rail, favoured by the fast tempo, held up and checked 450M, made some ground 200M.
At rear, 2 wide, benefited by the fast tempo, made minor ground in straight.
Very slow away, at back, trapped 4 wide throughout, moved forward 900M, emptied 350M.
Eased back, 3-4 wide, benefited by the fast pace, ran on fairly.
Hard ridden to take rail and lead, clocked fast sectionals, out of fuel 300M.
Hard ridden to hold the rail in front of midfield, not suited by the fast pace, weakened 450M.
Pushed early, trapped 4-5 wide in midfield or worst, never competitive.
At rear, 3-4 wide, suited by the fast tempo, checked 700M, however never improved.
Hard ridden to obtain box seat, harmed by the fast pace, faded rapidly 600M.
Hard ridden to keep up in midfield, 3 wide, checked severely 700M, dropped off.
Was crowded on jumping, detached in the early stages, quickened passing 200M and scored unchallenged.
Ridden along after start, travelled wide and without cover at handy position, made ground passing 200M, worked home nicely.
Raced behind midfield, always niggling, made up some late ground, finished well.
Urged along, settled midfield, widest on straightening, fought hard to the line.
Raced behind midfield on rail, gained some ground in concluding stages.
Pushed along to take lead, tried to improve on straightening, gave ground near 100M.
Ridden along for some distance to settle outside the lead, weakened near 200M.
Settled midfield on rail, tried hard but only one-paced.
Ridden along to settle box seat, gave ground passing 200M, blood trachea after race, lame left front next day.
Settled at back, no response in the straight.
Urged along after start, raced behind leaders, near 100M was checked and lost ground.
Always back, never in it, must trial.
Average to begin, taken back to race at tail, 6 lengths back, improved quickly from 600M, finished off very strongly in straight to score.

Moderately away, raced 3 wide and without cover early, sent forward after passing 1300M to take the lead, led by 2 lengths, kept on very well after turning in, but couldn't hold off the winner late. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began fairly, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 4 to 5 lengths back, same margin back on turn, finished off strongly in straight to take 3rd, nearest on line.

Began well from gate 1, took the early lead, allowed the rival to cross near 1000M, sat 2 to 3 lengths behind the leader on turn, made some progress in straight without threatening. (See Racing Incidents.)
Out in line, sent forward to race prominently early, then restrained to sit 2 wide in midfield, 3 lengths or so back on turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Away with them, unable to slot in, raced 4 wide with no cover early, moved forward thereafter to race in 2nd, peaked early in straight, kept on evenly to the line. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped well, positioned on rail behind midfield, saved ground throughout, showed no response in straight.
Jumped with them, no early speed, raced 3 wide behind midfield, 4 to 5 lengths back, similar position on turn, emptied early in straight, finished last.
Quickly into stride, unable to slot in, positioned 3 wide and without cover, 2 to 3 lengths back, still no cover on turn, finished off strongly in straight to score.
Bumped start, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well throughout, kept on very well after turning in, just couldn't hold off the winner late.
Jumped with them, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield early, inconvenienced near 750M, wider on turn, made good progress in straight to take 3rd.
Average to begin, sent forward to race outside the leader in 2nd, same position on turn, kept on evenly to the line.
Away with them, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 4 lengths back, raced tight and unbalanced near 750M, same margin back on turn, made some progress in straight without threatening.
Out in line, positioned 2 wide, a length or so back, there to turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Moderately away from barrier 11, taken back to race at rear, 5 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, kept to inside after straightening and made minor progress.
Bumped start and lost ground, recovered to race 4 lengths back on rail, saved ground on turn, in traffic and bumped early in straight, finished off evenly thereafter.
Jumped well, showed no early speed, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, bumped early in straight, finished off one-paced.
Began fairly from gate 1, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground throughout, showed no response in straight.
Slightly slow out, raced at tail, 8 lengths back on turn, made no progress in straight.
Began only fairly, raced at rear throughout, showed no response early in straight and eased thereafter, finished tailed off.
Raced towards the rear, 5-3/4L behind 2 wide, got going until halted slightly at 200M, resumed strongly to score.
In front of midfield initially, made move after 700M, led from 400M to final 50M, couldn't hold off the winner only.
Crowded after 200M from the start, in midfield 3-1/4L behind along the rail, kept on nicely to the line.
Niggled along, raced in the box-seat until 750M when another improved, ran on well to the finish.
Hampered after 200M from the start, in behind midfield 4-1/4L off, wide but with cover, made good ground on outer track, continued on well to the line. (Whip dropped at 400M)
Taken back but travelled keenly, strode forward and led from 750M, stayed on well to the line.
Eased and settled to race towards the rear, 5L behind wide but with cover, made slight ground and closed off okay.
Urged to take rail, shared lead until 750M when another moved, was one paced to the line.
Sent forward but trapped wide, took cover in one-off one-back, swung wide and was 3-1/4L off at 400M, one paced.
Raced in just behind midfield, 4L off the lead 2 wide, failed to save ground in the straight.
Taken back to be at the rear, 6-1/2L behind along the rail, kept on one paced to the line.
Crowded after 200M from the start, in behind midfield along the rail, very one paced and emptied last 150M.
Pushed but only settled in midfield, wide and without cover, found nothing in the straight.
Urged forward, in the lead until 750M when another improved, gave ground from rounding Home Turn.

Average to begin, positioned 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, 2 wide from near 700M, same margin back turning in, no clear running early in straight, finished off strongly to score when clear thereafter.
Taken back from gate 13, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, 3 to 4 lengths back on turn, finished off well in straight to take 2nd.

Began well, positioned on rail in midfield early, 3 to 4 lengths back, kept same margin back when others improved in the middle stages, saved ground on turn, made very good progress in straight to take a place, just missed 2nd.
Average to begin, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, 4 wide and without cover from near 800M, asked to improve from 500M, kept on well in straight despite being bumped near 200M.

Steadied on jumping, positioned 3 wide with cover in midfield early, slightly improved from 1000M, no cover from near 800M, kept on well after turning in, peaked near 200M, stayed on evenly to the line, just missed frame late.
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned 4 lengths or so back on rail, got its head up when awkwardly placed near 1000M, 2 wide at rear on turn, made some headway in straight.

Away with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 wide with cover on turn, raced tight early in straight, kept on steadily until crowded near 200M, ran on to the line fairly. (Lame left front leg next day morning.)
Jumped well, positioned 2 wide, better than midfield, there to turn, kept on well until crowded near 200M, ran on only fairly thereafter.
Average to begin, raced 3 wide with no cover in 3rd, sat just outside the leader from 900M, there to turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked near 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Out in line, sent forward to race prominently, took the lead near 1100M, travelled well on turn, headed near 250M and weakened rapidly thereafter.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced wide with cover at tail, crowded near 1200M, still 5 lengths back on turn, failed to close off in straight and eased.
Slowly away, raced 2 wide at rear, 4 to 5 lengths back, 3 wide turning, failed to close off in straight and eased.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced very wide with no cover at rear early, got cover near 800M but still wide, peaked on turn, emptied early in straight.
Began well, sent forward to take the early lead, headed near 1100M, positioned 1 to 2 lengths back on rail thereafter, emptied early in straight and eased.
Towards the rear 5-6Ls off leader on settling, helped by good pace, closed off well final 300M, got up just in time.
Showed good speed to cross from draw 11, led at good pace, sustained run from the turn, only caught final few strides.
Pressed along to race outside leader, chased hard on straightening but always held, lost 2nd close home.
Slow to begin, held up in midfield 4Ls off the good pace, ran on mildly towards the finish.
Assumed a midfield position along the 2-path, switched wide 450M to challenge but lacked a finishing kick, boxed on without threatening.
Failed to muster speed despite ridden along, ended up in rear pair 7Ls behind leaders, finished off only fairly, never a serious threat.
Outpaced early stages, settled down 7Ls off the pace in the rear pair, gave limited response on straightening passing tired runners only.
Away with them, chased leaders along the 2-path but couldn't go on passing 300M.
Ridden along to be close up behind leaders, failed to run on passing 400M, weakened noticeably mid-straight. (Bled.)
Jumped on terms, travelled 3-wide without cover behind leaders, gave ground turning in, eased final 100M when well beaten.

Broke well, shared the pace with two others early stages, engaged in a duel with the eventual runner-up coming onto the course proper, gained upper hand over 150 metres out.
Soon came up to share the lead, held every chance most of way until over 150 metres out.
Jumped awkwardly losing ground, settled in last of the small field and about 8L off the speed coming onto the course proper, fought on steadily running past well-beaten runners for distant 3rd.
Lacked early speed settling one from last in 5th, ran home one-paced.
Leaning in the stall when the gates opened, jumped awkwardly and ducked to the stands rail, niggled along just behind the leading trio early stages, weakened under pressure from half-way out.
With leaders until coming onto the course proper, dropped away quickly.
Behind midfield, 2 wide, benefited by the fast pace, progressed steadily 400M to score.
Hard ridden to take rail and lead, clocked fast sectionals, hung on until 200M overhauled, ran on for 2nd.
Hard ridden to obtain box seat, not suited by the fast pace, ran on ok for 3rd.
Eased back, 2 wide, favoured by the fast pace, progressed steadily 300M.
Eased back, took rail, benefited by the fast tempo, lack room 4-2, made steady ground when clear.
Hard ridden to hold the rail in midfield, just held ground in straight.
Pushed early, trapped 3-4 wide in midfield, just held ground in straight.
Pushed to sit in front of midfield, not suited by the fast sectionals, weakened 200M.
Eased to rear, 2 wide, benefited by the fast pace, made some ground 250M.
Hard ridden forward, trapped 3-4 wide, harmed by the fast tempo, out of fuel 250M.
At back, took rail, benefited by the fast tempo, no progress.
At rear, 2-4 wide, suited by the fast pace, never improved.
Hard ridden forward, sat 2 wide, harmed by the fast pace, emptied 350M.
Settled behind midfield, wide on straightening, quickened passing 200M, scored unchallenged.
Taken back at start, rider dropped his whip at 300M, made up some nice late ground.
Raced at tail, kept making ground passing 200M, finished nicely.
Began awkwardly and dipped, then urged along to take lead, lost some ground passing final 50M.
Ridden along at start, settled behind leaders, fought hard and gradually made ground in the straight.
Throughout the race travelled wide and without cover in midfield, awkwardly placed over concluding stages, not fully test.
Taken back at start, commenced to improve near 600M, widest on straightening, one-paced.
Jumped OK, lost left hind plate in the early stages, steadied passing 1200M, raced at handy position, one-paced.
Travelled midfield, gained ground in the early part of straight then gave ground passing 200M.
Ridden along to settle at handy position on rail, one-paced.
Moderate start then pushed along to race in box seat, emptied passing 250M.
Crowded on jumping, raced behind midfield on rail, eased near 200M, must trial.
Began only fairly then taken back, failed to close off, small wound on left hind cannon, must trial.
Settled midfield on rail, failed to run on, lame right front, must trial.

Bumped start and unbalanced, raced at rear early, sent forward when pace slackened near 1300M, took the lead after 1200M, travelled comfortably thereafter, kicked clear after turning in, very easily scored.

Jumped well from gate 1, positioned a length behind the leader in 2nd, angled out when pace slackened in the middle stages, hard ridden to maintain its position on turn, finished off evenly in straight to take 2nd.
Average to begin, raced at rear, 3 to 4 lengths back, travelled well throughout, same margin back on turn, made some progress in straight to take 3rd.
Moderately away, positioned on rail in midfield, 2 wide from near 1200M, 2 lengths or so back on turn, peaked early in straight, just ran on to the line with same pace.
Jumped with them, sent forward to take the lead, enjoyed the easy lead until headed near 1200M, positioned 1 to 2 lengths back thereafter, peaked on turn, weakened in straight.
Bumped start, raced at tail, 5 lengths or so back on turn, taken widest in straight, failed to close off in straight.
Away with them, raced 2 wide in midfield early, 3 wide after 1200M, no cover thereafter, similar position on turn, emptied early in straight, eased final 200M, finished tailed out.
Fast into stride, sent forward to take the lead, enjoyed the easy lead on turn, kept on strongly in straight and scored.
Moderately away, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, finished off strongly in straight to take 2nd without threatening the winner.
Jumped with them, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, 4 lengths back, same margin back on turn, made very good progress in straight to take 3rd.
Taken back from a wide draw, positioned 5 to 6 lengths back on rail, saved ground to near 600M, taken wide in straight and made very good progress to make frame.
Jumped well from gate 1, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, saved ground to near 600M, finished off evenly in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Moderately away from the widest draw, unable to slot in, raced very wide in midfield, no cover throughout, finished off evenly in straight.
Steadied on jumping and taken in for cover, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 4 lengths back, there to turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Taken back from a wide gate, raced 2 wide at rear, 5 lengths back, same margin back on turn, kept on evenly to the line.
Average to begin, positioned on rail behind midfield, 4 lengths back, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after straightening and finished off one-paced.
Began fairly, raced 2 wide in midfield, 2 to 3 lengths back, same position on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Inconvenienced start, raced wide with cover at rear, very difficult to settle near 1000M, 6 lengths or so back on turn, only passed a tired runner in straight.
Began well, unable to slot in, raced 3 wide with no cover early, slightly improved after 1000M, but still no cover on turn, peaked early in straight and weakened gradually thereafter, finished last.
Rolled forward to race prominently, sat 1-1/4L off but wide, ran on nicely to the line and scored by 3/4L.
Sent forward to shared lead along the rail, kept on going and held off a late challenge for 2nd.
Jumped well, slotted in to race in front of midfield, 3-3/4L off 2 wide, made ground and ran on strongly to the line.
Sent forward to share lead in a 2 wide position, one paced but kept on going to the line.
Jumped well, settled to race in midfield, 5L behind 2 wide, ran on steadily to the line on centre track.
Urged forward, remained prominent until checked near 800M, kept on until emptied at 150M.
Settled to race in midfield, 4-1/2L behind along the rail, saved minor ground and ran on.
Eased, then slotted in behind midfield, sat 6L behind 2 wide, improving steadily until awkward to heels at 100M.
Pushed forward to obtain the box-seat, kept on until flattened near 250M.
Niggled along, settled in one-off one-back, weakened soon after on straightening.
Bumped start, settled to race in behind midfield, one paced until flattened out near 200M.
Eased to be at the rear, stayed 1-2 wide, raced backward in the straight.
Taken back, raced close to the rear and remained 2 wide, did not improve and eased down at 200M.
Slow to jump, in behind midfield along the rail, raced greenly and eased down at 200M when found nothing.
Bumped start, positioned 3 lengths or so back on rail, saved ground on turn, no daylight until final 100M, finished off very strongly when clearthereafter to score.
Slowly away, raced at tail, 6 lengths back, improved from 650M, very wide turning in, finished off strongly to take 2nd, nearest on line.
Began well from a wide draw, raced 3 wide with cover, 1 to 2 lengths back, no cover on turn, kept on well in straight, took the lead near 100M, but couldn't hold off the first two late.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 wide with cover on turn, kept on evenly in straight to make frame.

Taken back from the widest draw, raced 2 wide at rear, 5 lengths or so back, there to turn, in traffic early in straight, angled near 300M and made contact with rivals, made good progress thereafter, awkwardly placed close home.

Taken back from a wide draw, positioned on rail at rear, 4 to 5 lengths back, saved ground on turn, no clear running early in straight, angled out after passing 200M and made some progress thereafter.
Moderately away from gate 1, sent forward to take the lead, shared lead on turn, kept on well early in straight, headed near 100M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Bumped start, inconvenienced near 1100M, positioned 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, no daylight early in straight, finished off evenly when clear thereafter.
Away with them, unable to slot in, raced very wide with no cover at rear, 5 lengths back, slightly improved on turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Jumped with them, brushed early, sent forward to race outside to the leader, shared lead on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter. (Lame left front leg.) (Blood in trachea.)
Moderately away from a wide draw, unable to slot in, raced very wide and without cover in midfield, still no cover on turn, weakened gradually in straight.

Began well, steadied off heels near 1250M, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 4 lengths back on turn, showed limited response early in straight, unbalanced near 300M and inconvenienced shortly thereafter, weakened from final 200M.
Jumped well, brushed near 1250M, raced 2 wide, 1 to 2 lengths back, weakened after turning in, eased final 100M.
Bumped start, raced wide with cover behind midfield, lost position on turn, emptied early in straight and eased, finished tailed out.
Chased leaders in 4th, ran on strongly hit the lead 200M, dashed clear final stages for 3 successive victories over Shatin 1000M. Won in very fast time.
Raced alone towards the center of track, up with pace, kept going soundly final 400M, no match with winner 200M.
Bumped at the start, failed to muster speed, settled midfield along stand's rail, awkwardly placed halfway and shifted out 400M to go forward, strong to the line and got up 3rd late.
Showed speed to be sharing the pace along stand's rail, couldn't lift when under siege 250M, one paced late on and lost 3rd last stride.
Slow to begin, held up behind midfield but never too far back, closed off mildly final 400M without threatening first 4.
In mid-division 2-3Ls off the pace, kept on one paced to the finish, never a serious threat.
Restrained to be 6th not far off leaders, chased one paced over final 400M, couldn't come on.
Guided to a midfield spot towards the outside of the group, held position to the 400M, didn't quicken under pressure.
Moved up to share the lead, gave limited response when placed under pressure 400M, got tired towards the finish. (Lame next day.)
Scrubbed along to hold a rail position behind leaders, battled away over final 400M without getting closer to leaders.
Moved across from low draw to be racing just off the pace, bustled along halfway but unable to quicken, wilted in the run home.
Bumped by rival after the start, in 12th place 4-5Ls back, struggled to stay in touch passing halfway, detached from main field.
Stood flat footed at the start and lost many lengths, 8Ls off the pace in the rear, not making up ground in straight and never involved.
Outpaced from the start, detached from main group in rear, didn't respond to urging, never in the picture. (Irregular Heart Rhythm / Bled 2nd time.)
Taken back from a tricky draw, positioned 7 to 8 lengths behind the leader on rail, hard ridden on turn but still 6 lengths back, finished off very strongly in straight and scored by a neck.
Average to begin, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, 3 to 4 lengths back, hard ridden from 700M, very wide turning in, finished off strongly in straight to take 2nd.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, 8 lengths or so back, hard ridden on turn but still 6 lengths back, finished off very strongly to be nearest on line, just missed 2nd.

Jumped with them, sent forward to race outside to the leader, a length behind the leader on turn, improved from 550M, took the lead early in straight, kept on well thereafter but just couldn't hold off the first few late.
Clean jump, raced 2 wide in midfield, similar position on turn, hard ridden from 550M, made good progress early in straight, peaked near 150M, kept on evenly to the line.

Bumped start and unbalanced, positioned on rail in midfield, travelled keenly near 1700M, gradually improved along the rail on turn, angled out near 550M, kept on well early in straight, peaked near 150M, weakened thereafter.
Began well from gate 1, travelled keenly early, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, showed limited response in straight, weakened close home. (See Racing Incidents.)
Crowded on jumping, raced wide with cover behind midfield, 4 to 5 lengths back, there to turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Jumped well, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, carried wider near 500M, weakened early in straight, eased final 200M.

Average to begin, raced at rear early, 6 to 7 lengths back, angled out 1200M, bumped and carried wider near 1100M, sent forward thereafter to race outside the leader, emptied early in straight and eased. (See Racing Incidents.)
Fast into stride, sent forward to take the lead, easy lead to near 900M, challenged on turn, emptied early in straight and eased. (See Racing Incidents.)
Away with them, unable to slot in, raced wide and without cover, 2 to 3 lengths back, weakened from 800M, eased turning in, finished tailed out, unacceptable performance.
Pushed forward early to be well placed 4th, but 3 wide with no cover. Cruised to lead at 350m. Never used the stick and pulled away easily, before easing before the 100m. Very easy.
Eased back early to settle towards the rear of the field. Widest in the straight, but stayed on strongly and flashed home to steal 2nd late.
Dropped back early, before settling just behind midfield. Wide on the turn. Showed good turn of foot from 250m, and was just beaten for 2nd late.
Pressed forward to share early lead, before being crossed at 900m. Battled on solidly early in the straight, but peaked in the last 50m and lost a place.
Bumped on jumping, but recovered to settle around midfield. Clear run in the straight and stayed on solidly without threatening a place.
Broke well, but eased forward soon after to settle forward of midfield. Battled on solidly early in the straight before running to the line 1 paced under minimal urging in final 150m.
Eased out early and settled towards the rear of the field. Came inside off heels after missing a run at 300m. Plugged away steadily without threatening in the straight and not pushed last 50m.
Cruised forward early and settled around midfield. Battled on fairly early in straight, before running 1 paced late.
Settled around midfield. Taken 3 wide no cover at 700m. Never responded in the straight and wasn't pushed out for last 175m.
Dropped back early from the wide draw to settle a clear 2nd last. Picked off some slower ones late, but never in it.
Pressed forward early to settle 5th/6th, on the fence. Never responded in the straight and dropped out quickly from 200m.
Pressed forward to share early lead, before being crossed at 900m. Never responded to pressure early in the straight, and was quietly ridden from the 150m.
Pushed forward from the wide draw to eventually lead passing 900m. Nothing in the tank late and dropped out quickly from 350m.
Dropped back early from the wide draw to sit long last. Struggled to keep up and compounded badly in the straight and was eased out. Jockey questioned. Unacceptable performance.
Tracked leader along the 2-path, took over top of straight, was strongly challenged final 200M, drifted out under pressure but fought courageously to hold on. (Protest from 2nd overruled.)

Assumed a midfield position, driven wide 550M to challenge, quickened up well to challenge eventual winner from 200M, fought neck to neck in closing stages, just held. (Protested on winner overruled.)
Held up behind midfield 6Ls off pace, saved ground along rail, improved to be 3Ls behind 400M, closed off well to be nearest at the finish.
Dropped back to race near the rear, crept closer home turn to be just over 4Ls off leader at 400M, stayed on moderately for non-threatening 4th.
Restrained behind midfield, brought wide into straight and kept on evenly to the line, not reach first 3.

Dropped back from wide barrier, 7-8Ls towards the rear on settling, went for inside run on straightening, held up to 300M then stayed on moderately to line. (Jockey questioned re his ride in the straight.)
Well away and worked forward to 1L lead on fence, headed 350M, faded away.
Jumped on terms, restrained from draw 12 to be 10th on settling, 6Ls off the pace making home turn, made limited progress only.
Up with early pace, reined back to be 5th making home turn, lacked a strong finish when asked, one paced over final 200M.
Bumped at the start, chased leaders along fence, couldn't go on inside 300M, faded towards the line.
Dropped back to be the back-marker almost 10Ls back in middle stages, moved a bit closer home turn, plodded on at same pace, never threatened.
Switched off to be 2nd last on settling, 8Ls off the pace middle stages, failed to run on in straight.
Never better than midfield, swung wide for home from 550M, couldn't come on, never threatened.
Caught 3-deep without cover from wide barrier, moved closer to pace passing 1000M, run ended soon after straightening, weakened to last.
