Soon came to share the pace 3-wide and then 2-wide, eventually obtained rails run coming out of back straight, kicked over 2L clear turning on straightening, held off runner-up's strong late challenge closing stages.
Jumped fairly, settled towards the rear on the rail, saved ground on the inside turning in, ran on under pressure and did best work late.
Broke well, niggled along wide in midfield, improved to 4th some 2.5L off the pace early in back straight, gained 2nd position from tiring runners 200 metres out, lost the placing final few strides.

Taken back from a wide gate, travelled wide towards the rear in 8th down back straight, commenced move home bend and widest turning in, sustained progress near the centre of home straight, nearest at finish. (Tactic questioned)
Soon dropped to wide in rear of midfield despite ridden along, commenced move 4-wide rounding home bend, kept on steadily without quickening in the straight.
Jumped fairly, soon came to join the leaders, shifted 2L back in 3rd on the rail over 800 metres out, in similar position turning in, faded inside the final 200 metres.
Well back, hampered and dropped to tail-end over 1000 metres out, switched off the rail for a run 400 metres out, fought on steadily under pressure inside the final 300 metres.
Broke well, settled within 3L of the pace in 5th on the rail, slightly further back coming onto home bend, kept on before finding no extra closing stages.
Mainly in midfield, came under pressure to challenge after straightening, ran home one-paced and hampered near the line.
Crowded at start settling one from last, checked 500 metres out, came under pressure rounding home bend, went wide into straight, kept on at the one pace.
Showed early speed, joined in the front coming onto back straight, shifted one back passing the 600 metres, folded up quickly shortly after straightening. (Tactic questioned) (Lame next day)
Settled in front, 2 wide, enjoyed by the slow tempo, ran on strongly 300M to score.
Bumped start, pushed to obtain box seat, blocked 350M, dashed well when clear for 2nd.
Eased back, took rail, raced keenly, not suited by the slow pace, lack room 4-2, unleashed strong finishing efforts when clear.
Pushed forward, sat 2 wide, benefited by the slow sectionals, weakened 150M.
Slow away, 2 wide at back, raced very keenly, lack room 4-2, dashed well when clear despite not suited by the slow pace.
Eased back, raced 3-4 wide throughout, harmed by the slow tempo, unleashed strong finishing efforts 250M.
Very slow away and then checked early, midfield along the fence, harmed by the slow pace, just held ground in straight.
Eased at start, 2-4 wide at back, dashed well 200M despite not suited by the slow pace.
Hard ridden to secure the lead, clocked very slow sectionals, however soon weakened 200M.
Hard ridden early, sat midfield 2 wide, not suited by the slow tempo, out of fuel 200M.
Eased at start, took cover at rear, 2-3 wide, harmed by the slow pace, taken very wide on straightening and checked, ran on fairly.
Hard ridden early, trapped 3-4 wide throughout in midfield, emptied 300M.
Settled midfield on rail, made ground passing 200M, travelled strongly to score.
Settled behind midfield, kept on rail at Home Turn to save ground, made up some nice late ground.
Failed to muster speed despite being ridden along, improved to outside the lead in the back straight, ran on in the straight, finished well.
Taken back at start, commenced to improve near 700M, quickened passing 100M.
Slow to begin and settled at back, widest on straightening, one-paced.
Ridden along to settle outside the lead, gave ground passing 150M.
Sat behind leaders, weakened in the straight.
Raced midfield, near 400M was crowded for room, no response in the straight.
Ridden along to race behind leaders on rail, weakened near 150M, failed to run on.
After 1400M was left racing wide and without cover, near 600M was checked when crowded for room, wide on straightening, no response in the straight.
Hard ridden to take lead, emptied near 200M.
Raced behind leaders, gave ground abruptly passing the 500M, must trial.
Bumped start, sent forward to take the rail, 2 lengths behind the leader, easy run to turn, finished off well to score by a neck.
Sent forward to take the lead from a wide draw, enjoyed the easy lead throughout, kept on well after turning in, but just couldn't hold off the winner late.
Jumped with them, positioned 2 wide, 3 lengths back, same margin back on turn, closed off well to take a place.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, 8 lengths back, slightly closer on turn, finished off strongly in straight to make frame, nearest on line.

Began fairly, showed no early speed, positioned on rail at rear, 7Ls back, 2W from near 700M, started to improve thereafter, very wide turning in, made good progress in straight to be nearest on line. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, 8 lengths back, slightly improved in the middle stages, 4 lengths back on turn, made some progress in straight without threatening.
Slightly slow out from gate 1, positioned 5 lengths back on rail, same position on turn, kept to inside after straightening and finished off evenly.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide at rear, 6 to 7 lengths back, 3 wide with cover on turn, finished off one-paced.
Jumped well, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths back, same position on turn, made contact and unbalanced near 250M, showed no response thereafter.

Average to begin, sent forward to race outside the leader in 2nd, a length or so back, there to turn, weakened early in straight, made contact and unbalanced near 250M, eased shortly thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)

Away with them, bumped early, difficult to settle near 1300M, trapped 3 wide early, raced 2 wide behind midfield after entering the back straight, weakened on turn, emptied near 400M, finished tailed out.
Began well, positioned on rail in midfield, 4 lengths back, same positon on turn, severely checked early in straight, eased thereafter.
Clean jump, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well throughout, kicked clear after turning in, kept on well to hold off the rival and scored.

Moderately away from gate 1, positioned 2 to 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, difficult to settle near 900M, awkwardly placed near 600M, saved ground to 400M, finished off strongly in straight to take 2nd, nearest on line.
Jumped well, positioned 2 wide, a length or so back, there to turn, kept on well in straight to take a place.
Bumped start and unbalanced, raced 5 lengths back at rear, hampered near 600M, slightly improved on turn, taken wide in straight and made very good progress to make frame.
Bumped on jumping, raced 2 wide better than midfield, there to turn, finished off evenly in straight without threatening.
Slowly away, raced at tail, 7 lengths back, same margin back on turn, made good progress in straight.
Began well from a middle draw, unable to slot in, positioned 3 wide and without cover, 2 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, failed to quicken under pressure in straight.
Bumped start, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, 3 lengths or so back on turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced 2 wide at rear, 6 lengths or so back, carried wider on turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Bumped start and unbalanced, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 4 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Began awkwardly, raced 4 lengths back on rail, hampered near 600M, lost position on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Fast into stride, sent forward to race prominently, got cover from 700M, peaked on turn, weakened early in straight and eased.
Pushed and raced in the box-seat, sat 2L off, showed good kick after 200M, battled on nicely to score by a neck.
Sent forward to take the rail and led by 1-1/4L, kept on until headed passing 50M, ran on to miss by a neck.
Niggled along and raced in one-off one-back position, sat 3L off the lead, closed off well to take 3rd.
Sent forward to race outside the lead, sat 1-1/4L off, in touch until emptied inside final 100M.
Pushed and settled to race in front of midfield, 4-1/4L off along the rail, kept on fairly to the line.
Lost ground at the start, made up to be just behind midfield, 5-1/2L behind along the rail, kept on one paced to the line.
Settled to race in behind midfield, 6-1/4L behind 2 wide, slight dash prior to 200M but was mostly one paced.
Crowded start, at the rear and detached until 700M, made ground in the straight but did not threaten.
Slow to muster, raced in front of midfield, however trapped wide and without cover, emptied at 150M.
Fractious and missed the start, settled in worse than midfield along the rail, failed to save ground.
Under whip after the start, settled 2 wide in midfield, dropped off from on straightening.
Taken back and then remained at the rear, gave ground from 400M.
Bumped on jumping, sent forward to take the lead, enjoyed the easy lead in the middle stages, kicked clear after turning in, kept on strongly to the line and scored.
Jumped with them, positioned on rail at rear, 5 lengths back, checked off heels near 800M, saved ground on turn, angled out early in straight and finished off very strongly to take 2nd.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide at rear, 5 to 6 lengths back, slightly improved from 800M, hard ridden on turn, made some progress in straight to take 3rd without threatening.
Began well from gate 1, positioned 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, easy run to turn, kept on evenly in straight, just missed 3rd on line.
Began fairly, positioned 3 lengths back on rail, saved ground on turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Jumped well, raced 2 wide better in midfield, 3 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, made minor progress in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)

Taken back from the widest draw, raced 3 wide with cover at rear early, moved closer in the back straight, 2 lengths or so back on turn, awkwardly placed near 200M, finished off one-paced thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Bumped start, raced 3 wide behind midfield, no cover from 1200M, moved closer in the back straight, 3rd on turn, peaked early in straight and weakened gradually thereafter.
Began only fairly, raced at tail, 6 to 7 lengths back, last turning in, finished off one-paced in straight.
Slightly slow out and bumped, recovered to race in 2nd, 2 wide, challenged the leader turning in, peaked early in straight and weakened gradually thereafter, eased final 50M.
Out in line, raced 2 wide, 4 lengths or so back, awkwardly placed near 800M and lost position, hard ridden from 450M, failed to close off in straight.

Bumped start, sent forward to race prominently, allowed the rival to cross on the first turn, sat 2 wide, 2 lengths back in the middle stages, peaked on turn, showed no response in straight, finished last.
Jumped on terms restrained 8th on settling, driven wide 400M, switched through his gears entering straight, hit lead 70M out, kept going for dominant victory.

From draw 12 shifted across behind runners early, in rear pair 6Ls off the steady pace, held up and unable to improve position from home turn to early straight, closed well final 250M to go 2nd near line but no match for winner.
Emerged as leader passing 950M, led steadily to straight, fought on well headed by winner 70M out, lost 2nd last stride.
Caught wide no cover from draw 11, pressed forward to race outside leader, didn't quicken on straightening but kept on evenly to hold 4th.
Slow to begin, recovered to be tracking leaders entering home turn, loomed a chance 250M, but held by leaders in the run home.
Settled down midfield just over 3Ls behind leader 400M, stayed on mildly, checked inside 150M losing momentum, ran on again towards the line.
Tracked leaders, unable to get closer to rail, caught 3 wide no cover from 600M, battled on one pace in the straight, out of contention 100M.
Began fast to lead early, sat back passing 900M behind leaders, couldn't muster speed to be closer turning in, plodded home.
Switched off to the rear to be 6-7Ls away from pace on settling, worked home fairly without threatening.
Assumed a 3-wide position in midfield, 9th on the turn 5Ls behind leader, didn't run on in the straight. Never a factor.
Dropped back to race near the rear along the 3-path, 6Ls to make up 400M, couldn't come on, made no real progress to the line.
Began only fairly, guided to a midfield spot along the fence, saved ground turning for home, right behind leader on straightening but failed to respond to the riding, faded out to be last.

Settled within striking distance in 5th, commenced move passing the 400 metres, fought on steadily to just get up on line.
Showed early speed racing greenly and all over the place, kicked over half a length clear 100 metres out only to be caught close home.
Disputed lead most of the way to the 200 metres, unable to sustain effort, forced to steady near the line.
Not far off on stands rail, ridden along coming onto course proper, kept on steadily without quickening.
Slowly away, settled second last, ran on well inside the final 300 metres, nearest at finish.
Settled within 2L of pace on stands rail and as close up as 4th over 200 metres out, unable to sustain effort inside the final 100 metres.
Began fairly, settled towards the rear on stands rail, baulked for a run about 70 metres out, no further impression.
Began fairly, settled mainly in midfield, ran home one-paced.

Slow out from a low draw, quickly taken out onto stands rail at the back, responded well over 200 metres out but ran into heels, made no further impression inside the final 100 metres. (Questioned for disappointing performance)
Began awkwardly, settled just off the pace in 4th, gradually faded under pressure inside the final 400 metres.
Sluggish at start, made steady headway under pressure to reach 4th some 1L back coming onto course proper, folded up quickly under pressure shortly after.
Broke well from the one draw, gradually drifted back to midfield coming onto course proper, gave ground steadily thereafter.
Slowly away, always at the back, never seen with a chance.
Jumped fairly, settled in worse than midfield near the centre of the track, dropped away quickly from half-way out.
Pushed forward, sat 2 wide, made early move 1000M to dictate the tempo, closed off strongly to score.
Pressed forward, box seat, not suited by the fast tempo, ran on well for 2nd.
Eased back, took rail, benefited by the fast sectionals, progressed steadily 400M for 3rd.
Midfield, along the fence, suited by the fast tempo, made steady ground 400M.
Eased back 2 wide benefited by the fast pace, progressed steadily 300M.
At back, on the fence, favoured by the fast tempo, made some ground 250M.
Midfield, 2 wide, benefited by the fast pace, just held ground in straight.
Eased back, 2-3 wide, benefited by the fast pace, lack turn of foot in straight.
Eased back, 2-3 wide, favoured by the fast pace, however no progress.
Pushed to take rail and lead, clocked fast sectionals, out of fuel 300M.
Pushed forward, sat 2 wide, harmed by the fast pace, emptied 400M.
Very slow away, at rear, suited by the fast pace, never improved.
Very slow away, never a factor.
Eased to sit in midfield early, however trapped 3 wide, moved forward 1700M to cross in front, not suited by the fast tempo, dropped off 600M, badly hampered 500M,
Fast out then ridden along to take lead, responded nicely in the straight, scored unchallenged.
Jumped nicely, raced in box seat, fought hard in the straight, finished nicely.
Began only fairly, urged to settle behind leaders, asked for effort passing 450M, ran on well.
Settled midfield, improved near 450M, worked home well.
Raced behind midfield, one-paced when asked for effort.
Settled midfield, one-paced.
Raced outside the lead, gave ground passing 300M.
Settled at rear, no response in the straight.
Very slow to begin, detached in early stages, no response in the straight, stalls test.
On jumping rider momentarily lost its left stirrup, raced at handy position, failed to run on. Lame left front next day.
Moderate start, always niggling, raced at rear, never in it.
Urged along to take forward position from widest barrier, travelled wide and without cover throughout the race, weakened passing 300M.
Began well, raced 2 wide, 1 to 2 lengths back, 3 wide on turn, took the lead early in straight, kept on well thereafter to score.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide in midfield, 2 to 3 lengths back, 3 wide turning in, finished off strongly to take 2nd.
Jumped well, positioned 2 to 3 lengths back on rail, angled out near 650M, made some headway early in straight, bumped near 150M, kept on evenly to the line.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 3 lengths or so back on turn, made good progress in straight to make frame. (See Racing Incidents.)
Away with them, sent forward to race 2 wide in 2nd, there to turn, peaked early in straight, stayed on evenly to the line.
Slowly away and bumped, raced 5 to 6 lengths back on rail, slightly improved along the rail in the middle stages, 3 lengths or so back on turn, taken wide in straight and finished off well.
Fast into stride, took the rail easily and sat right behind the leader, easy run on turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Began only fairly from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Bumped on jumping and unbalanced, recovered quickly and driven forward to take lead, challenged on turn, peaked and headed early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)

Away with them, raced 2W at rear, 5Ls back on turn, showed limited response in straight, eased after passing 100M. (Jockey reported his horse did not feel comfortable in its action over the concluding stages.) (Lame left front leg.)
Taken back from a wide draw, raced wide at rear, 7 to 8 lengths back, there to turn, failed to close off in straight.
Bumped start, failed to muster speed,raced 8 lengths back at rear, difficult to settle when checked off heels near 1200M, still well back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Jumped well from the widest draw, unable to slot in, raced 3 wide and without cover in midfield, similar positon on turn, weakened gradually in straight.
Bumped start and unbalanced, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, peaked on turn, emptied early in straight, finished last.

Crowded start, raced 9Ls back at rear, closer on turn but still 5Ls back, no clear running early in straight, finished off strongly when clear thereafter and scored narrowly. (Lost right front plate.)
Average to begin, raced 2 wide better than midfield, same position on turn, finished off very strongly but couldn't hold off the winner on line.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide in midfield early, found rail near 900M, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after straightening, made very good progress to take a place.
Began well, sent forward to sit outside to the leader, shared lead on turn, kept on well early in straight, headed after passing final 100M, stayed on for 4th.

Began awkwardly and unbalanced the rider, raced at tail, 11Ls back at 800M, moved closer thereafter, still 6 lengths back, very wide turning in, showed very good response early in straight, peaked near 150M, kept on evenly to the line.
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, easy run on turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Quickly into stride, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well throughout, peaked on run near 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Bumped start, position on rail in midfield, 4 lengths or so back, saved ground on turn, showed limited response in straight.
Jumped well, positioned on rail behind midfield, 6 lengths back turning in, made little progress in straight.
Shifted out abruptly on jumping, raced 2 to 3 wide at rear, travelled keenly near 1000M, 5 lengths back on turn, finished off one-paced in straight.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 6 lengths back, closer on turn, failed to close off in straight.

Taken back from the widest draw, raced wide with cover at rear, 10 lengths back at 800M, moved closer on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter. (Rider dropped right rein near 200M.)
Average to begin, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths back, there to turn, weakened early in straight, eased final 200M.
Jumped well from a wide draw, unable to slot in, raced wide and without cover in 3rd, peaked on turn, weakened in straight, finished last.
Rolled forward and raced in the box-seat, sat 1-1/2L off, pulled away near 200M and scored comfortably by 2-1/2L.
Settled in behind midfield, 3 wide before shifted to the rail at the 700M turn, improved and closed off strongly for 2nd.
Niggled and settled just in front of midfield, 3-3/4L behind 2 wide, continued on well to the line.
Raced in behind midfield along the rail, hampered near 700M, showed good dash and closed off well to the line.
Sent forward from barrier 1 to obtain the lead, flattened and headed near 150M.
Niggled along and settled in midfield, 5-1/4L behind 2 wide, kept on fairly to the line.
Slow to jump, remained at the rear, 9-1/2L behind along the rail, made nice ground in the straight.
Sent forward, settled in one-off one-back, sat about 1L off, couldn't find extra near 100M.
Hard ridden forward to sit outside the lead, stayed about 1/2L off, emptied approaching 200M.
Eased and then raced towards the tail, wide and without cover, found nothing.
Urged before settling close to the rear, 3 wide but with cover, did not improve.
Asked to be in midfield, pressured all along, not competitive.
Clean jump, sent forward to take the lead and dictate the tempo, travelled well throughout, kept on very well in straight to hold off the rival and scored.
Away with them, positioned 3 lengths behind the leader on turn, closer on turn, finished off strongly in straight to take 2nd.
Bumped start, positioned 2 wide in 3rd, 2 lengths or so back, 3 wide turning in, kept on very well in straight to take 3rd without threatening the winner.
Bumped start, sent forward to race in 2nd, 2 wide, same position on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked on run near 250M, stayed on evenly thereafter.
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned 4 lengths back on rail, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after straightening and finished off evenly.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 to 4 lengths back, similar position on turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Jumped well, positioned 5 to 6 lengths back on rail, 2 wide turning in, finished off evenly in straight. (Lost both front plates near 500M.)
Slightly slow out, raced 7 lengths back at rear, saved ground on turn, made no progress in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide at rear, 6 to 7 lengths back, similar position on turn, made no progress in straight.
Began only fairly, raced 2 wide behind midfield, difficult to settle near 1100M, 4 lengths back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Taken back from gate 11, raced 8 to 9 lengths back at rear, still well back on turn, showed no response in straight, finished last.
Settled down just ahead of midfield, ran on strongly through final 350M, led 150M out, clearing away towards the finish.
Held up along the fence behind midfield, drifted out 500M, did best work final 200M to go 2nd near line but couldn't reel in winner.
Sent forward, chased leader along the 2-path, ran on to hold every chance on straightening, kept going to the line but was no match for winner, headed by 2nd late.
In midfield early stages, caught wide no cover from 1000M, strode forward and reached lead 800M, kept going well until headed at the 150M and was outsprinted from there, lost 3rd close home.
Commenced only fairly, settled down behind midfield, 5Ls back home turn and under pressure 600M, boxed on steadily for non-threatening 5th. (Jockey : uncomfortable action at times)
Taken back for cover from wide draw, behind mid-division going into the bend, ran on mildly in straight didn't trouble the leaders.
Jumped only fairly, 6Ls off the pace in the rear, stayed on past tired runners in straight.
Driven forward to be leading until 850M, tracked leader from there and kept in touch until 150M, faded towards the line.
Raced ahead of midfield, never far off the pace, 3-wide no cover from 1300M, kept on same pace in straight, no extra 100M.
Chased pace early stages, shuffled back to midfield turning for home, battled on behind leaders inside 400M but was never in the hunt. (Mucus.)
Settled 3-wide in the rear, found nothing in straight, never involved.
Held up at the rear, under pressure home turn, never got going.
Began awkwardly, positioned a length or so back near to the stands rail, finished off very strongly final 400M to score easily.
Jumped well from gate 13, positioned 3 lengths behind the leader near to the stands rail, made good progress late to take 2nd without threatening the winner.

Away with them, sent forward to share the lead, near to the stands rail, travelled well throughout, peaked and headed near 150M, slightly weakened thereafter, just stayed on for 3rd. (Lost right hind plate.) (See Racing Incidents.)
Moderately away from gate 10, travelled in midfield, 2 away from the stands rail, no clear running from near 300M, finished off well when clear final 100M.
Clean jump, sent forward to take the rail and share the lead, peaked and headed near 200M, stayed on evenly to the line.
Average to begin, positioned on rail at rear, 3 lengths back at 400M, finished off well without threatening.
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned 2 lengths behind, 3 away from the stands rail, kept on evenly to the line.
Jumped with them, positioned 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on the stands rail, only showed limited response in the final 400M. (Blood in trachea.)
Average to begin, showed no early speed, raced at rear, nearer to the middle of the track, gradually improved in the middle stages, peaked on run near 300M, slightly weakened thereafter.
Out in line, raced behind midfield, 3 away from the stands rail, 4 lengths or so back at 400M, finished off evenly.
Away with them, raced 4 to 5 lengths back at rear, 2 away from the stands rail, taken to centre track after passing 400M, but failed to make any progress.
Jumped well, sent forward to race prominently, 2 away from the stands rail, peaked near 350M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Began only fairly, raced at tail, 5 lengths or so back, taken to the centre track after passing 700M, failed to make any impression final 400M.
Began fairly, raced at rear, nearer to the middle of the track, failed to make any progress final 400M, finished last.

Pressed forward early to settle forward of midfield, 3 wide with cover. Badly hampered 950m. Stayed on steadily in the straight, and lead 200m. Didn't show huge turn of foot, but just held out fast finishing challenger late.

Eased back early to settle worse than midfield, 3 wide with limited cover. Widest in the straight and stayed on steadily early. Huge turn of foot at 150m. Came home with a wing on each hoof and just missed the win.
Pushed forward early, before easing back to sit just forward of midfield. Severely checked and lost ground 950m. Battled on solidly in straight, but couldn't match winner and peaked late.
Dropped back early from the wide draw to sit last. Wider in the straight, but held up until after 300m. Came around heels 150m, and went to the line well when clear late.
Cruised forward early to settle around midfield. Wider on the turn. Stayed on solidly in the straight, but no place threat.
Pressed forward early to be well placed 3rd, in the box seat. In 2nd place early in the straight, but ran 1 paced late.
Eased forward early to settle around midfield. Severely checked and lost ground 950m. Plugged away steadily, but no threat.
Tried to press forward early. Stuck 3 wide with no cover and created carnage when trying to get cover at 950m. Plugged away in the straight, but gave nothing and wasn't pushed last 100m.
Crowded on jumping and eased back early. Hampered in the scrum at 950m. Wasn't going well enough to take run that presented itself 350m and was steadied at 250m. Ambled to the line late.
Settled at the rear of the field. Wider on turn, then came back inside. No threat.
Began awkwardly, but recovered well enough to settle just forward of midfield. Checked and lost ground at 950m. Didn't respond in the straight and dawdled to the line last 200m.
Pressed hard early to lead. Ran out of gas at 200m and not pushed from that point.
Pressed forward early to settle 2nd, a neck off the leader. Couldn't get out of his own way in the straight, and was eased before the 150m.
Awkward on heels early and settled back in the field. Checked in the melee at 950m. Slowly pushing forward in the straight, but steadied off heels 200 and awkwardly placed late.

Pressed forward from a wide gate, settled just better than midfield some 4L off the pace in 6th, similar to home bend but went wide into the straight, quickened well inside the final 200 metres for a commanding victory.
Slightly slow out, settled just worse than midfield on the rail, snuck up on the inside turning in, sustained headway after straightening to claim 2nd final strides but never a threat to the winner.
Worked his way forward from a wide draw to lead on the rail 1200 metres out setting a smart pace, led until headed under pressure over 100 metres out.
Jumped best but soon taken back to settle just under 4L off the pace in 5th, shifted wide for a run entering straight but inconvenienced over 250 metres out, fought on steadily closing stages.
Jumped fairly, in the front briefly before taken one back to 3rd coming onto the stables bend, came to challenge after straightening but unable to sustain effort inside the final 100 metres.
Moderate start from the one gate, taken two back to 4th within 3L of the pace, made modest headway under pressure early in straight but unable to sustain effort close to home.
Soon taken across to settle towards the rear in 9th, remained similar to the straight while saving ground on the home turn, ran home one-paced under pressure.
Moderate start, settled in rear of midfield, switched wide for a run turning into the straight, fought on steadily under pressure without threatening near the centre of the track.
Settled in last few from a wide gate, saved ground turning for home, ran home one-paced.
Amongst leaders early, settled just off the pace in 2nd one off the rail, soon faded in straight. (Mucus in trachea)
Jumped very awkwardly losing ground and jockey lost use of iron briefly, never seen with a chance as was always at the back. (Tactic questioned)
Began fairly from a wide draw, gradually drifted backward from wide in midfield to joint last into back straight, came under pressure approaching the 400 metres, found nothing. (Tactic questioned)
Pushed to take rail and led at good pace, made all.
At rear, trapped 3-4 wide, pace good, dashed well 200M for 2nd.
Hard ridden forward, sat 2 wide, pace good, ran on well for 3rd.
Very slow away, hard ridden to hold the rail in midfield, pace good, made steady ground 300M.
Eased back, 2 wide, pace good, lack room 300M, progressed steadily when clear.
Pushed early but lack speed, took rail at back, pace good, dashed well 200M, lack room 50M.
Hard ridden to keep up in midfield and stayed 3 wide, pace good, held ground in straight.
Hard ridden forward, hung out badly throughout and bumped another horse on a few occasions, weakened 300M.
Eased at start, raced 3-4 wide throughout, pace good, ran on well in straight despite the ground that it lost around the bends.
Very slow away, raced 3 wide at back, pace good, ran on fairly in straight.
Hard ridden forward, 2-3 wide, was bumped and badly hampered from 700-400M, emptied 300M.
Eased back, never competitive.
Ridden along to take lead, travelled strongly in the straight to score.
Urged to settle outside the lead, responded solidly in the straight.
Began awkwardly then taken back, settled behind midfield, wide on straightening, made up some nice late ground.
Crowded on jumping, raced behind leaders, ran on and finished well.
Fractious in barriers then began awkwardly, raced midfield, gained some ground passing 100M.
Ridden along after start, throughout the race travelled wide and without cover at handy position, lost right front place after 600M, finished OK.
Ridden at start, raced midfield on rail, kept on rail at Home Turn to save ground, gave ground passing 50M.
Moderate start, settled behind midfield on rail, one-paced.
Settled at rear, always niggling, limited response in the straight.
Hard ridden after start, raced midfield, widest on straightening, no response in the straight.
Always back, never in it.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 4 lengths back on turn, finished off strongly in straight to score.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, 7 to 8 lengths back, last turning in, made very good progress in straight to take 2nd, nearest on line.
Out in line, sent forward to take the lead, enjoyed the easy lead throughout, kicked clear after turning in, but couldn't hold off the first two late.
Began well, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, bounded near 1100M, similar position on turn, kept on evenly in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned 4 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, made reasonable headway in straight without threatening.
Away with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, wider on turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Average to begin, positioned on rail in midfield, 3 lengths or so back, saved ground on turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Taken back to race at rear, 6 lengths or so back, awkwardly placed near 450M, finished off one-paced.
Jumped with them, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, same position on turn, failed to close off in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back from the widest draw, raced 2 wide at rear, 6 lengths or so back, bumped and unbalanced near 450M, failed to close off in straight.

Bustled along after the start, inclined to hang in, shifted out by jockey to a 3-wide spot without cover near 1300M, pressed on to race outside leader 1000M, struggled passing 400M, soon weakened. (Lame LF leg.) (Lost left hind plate.)

Moderately away, struck heels and unbalanced early, raced 3 wide, 3 to 4 lengths back, no cover after entering the back straight, checked early in straight, eased thereafter. (Roarer.) (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped well, positioned on rail in midfield, easy run to turn, finished off very strongly in straight to score by a neck.
Began well from a wide draw, raced 2 wide better than midfield, there to turn, improved from 400M, took the lead near 200M, kept on well thereafter but couldn't hold off the winner.
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned 5 lengths back on rail, saved ground to near 400M, finished off strongly to take 3rd, nearest on line.
Began very awkwardly from the widest draw, raced 6 lengths back on rail, similar position on turn, made very good progress in straight to make frame.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide at rear, 5 lengths or so back on turn, taken wide in straight and finished off well.
Jumped well, positioned 1 out 1 back, steadied off heels near 750M, improved from 450M, finished off evenly in straight. (Bled.)
Taken back to race at tail, 10 lengths or so back, still well back on turn, finished off well in straight without threatening.
Began well, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, easy run throughout, failed to quicken under pressure in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Clean jump, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well throughout, peaked and headed near 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Taken back from a wide draw, 9 lengths back, still well back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Raced 2 wide in midfield, 4 lengths or so back, there to turn, showed no response in straight, emptied final 100M.

Jumped well from a tricky draw, sent forward to race prominently but wide, 2nd on turn, showed no response early in straight, weakened rapidly thereafter. (Irregular heart rhythm, lame left front leg.) (See Racing Incidents.)
Steadied after the start, settled in midfield, 3L behind 2 wide, fought on well to win with something in hand.
Sent forward to take the rail and lead, held on until caught by the winner late at final 25M.
Asked to take up the box-seat, sat 1-3/4L off the lead, continued on well but couldn't match the first two.
Urged along, settled to race outside the lead, kept on one paced to the line.
Pushed along and settled one-off one-back, sat 1-1/2L off the lead, showed no turn of foot in the straight.
Raced close to the rear, 5-1/4L behind 3 wide but with cover, swung widest and saved ground, finished off fairly.
Taken back to race at the rear, 7-1/2L behind along the rail, made ground along the inside track, kept on to the line.
Settled to race at the rear, 7-1/4L behind 2 wide, continued to save ground until held up inside final 100M.
Niggled along, settled in midfield along the rail, very much one paced.
Travelled in worse than midfield, stayed 2 wide throughout, did not improve.
Raced in just behind midfield, wide and without cover, found nothing in the straight.
Awkward to heels after start and lost ground, settled behind midfield along the rail, never featured.

Away with them, raced 2 wide behind midfield early, sent forward from near 900M, Inconvenienced near 800M, positioned 3 wide, 2 lengths back thereafter, finished off strongly to score. (Finished distressed.)
Average to begin, raced 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, there to turn, finished off well to take 2nd.
Jumped with them, sent forward to take the lead, headed near 850M, positioned a length behind the leader thereafter, easy run on turn, kept on well in straight to get 3rd.

Began well from gate 1, positioned 3L back on rail, 2W from near 800M, still 3L or so back on turn, made good progress early in straight, raced in restricted room thereafter, not able to be ridden out late. (Lost left hind plate.)

Taken back from the widest draw, positioned 9 lengths back at rear, improved from 1000M and took the lead at 800M, travelled well throughout, kept on well after turning in, just couldn't hold off the rivals final 50M
Began fairly from a middle draw, raced 2 wide in midfield early, 3 wide from near 800M, 4 to 5 lengths back on turn, taken wide in straight and made good progress without threatening.
Taken back from a wide draw, positioned on rail at rear early, 2 wide after entering the back straight, 5 lengths or so back on turn, no clear running in straight, not able to be fully tested.
Average to begin, positioned 5 lengths behind the leader on rail, there to turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Out in line, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, similar position on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Jumped with them, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, became 6th when pace slackened in the middle stages, 4 lengths back on turn, made no progress in straight, eased late.

Taken back from gate 9, raced at tail early, 10 lengths or so back, rolled forward when the pace slackened after entering the back straight, 4 wide in midfield on turn, failed to close off in straight.

Average to begin, raced 2 wide at rear, slightly improved after entering the back straight, but couldn't maintain position near 700M, 8 lengths back at tail on turn, showed no response in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
In touch early stages, improved to be 2nd back straight, went neck to neck with leader from 200M, gained upper hand 50M and held off late challenge to score.
Reserved towards the rear in 9th place, 5Ls off the pace 400M, closed off strongly to the line beaten by a diminishing neck.
Pressed forward from wide draw, crossed to the lead passing 1150M, fought on doggedly when tackled by rival from 250M, gave way near 50M, lost 2nd close home.

Taken back from wide draw, held up 2nd last 7Ls off pace, stayed on mildly entering straight, got up 4th just in time. (Inquiry into riding, Jockey had erred in not going for outside run from home turn to top of straight.)
Unable to slot in, raced 3-wide in midfield and no cover from 1200M-600M, stayed on moderately entering straight not posing serious threat to first 3.
Set early pace before tracking leader from 1150M, battled on early straight, outsprinted by leaders 200M.
Held up behind midfield, sat 5Ls off the pace entering final turn, swung wide home, stayed on steadily without serious threat.
Settled down in mid-division, moved out to 3-wide from 700M and crept closer to pace, kept on same speed only, no longer a threat mid-straight.
4th on settling never far off from leader, came under pressure 500M, failed to improve in straight.
Restrained in midfield along the fence, found no extra turning in, soon weakened. (Blood in trachea.)
Failed to muster speed despite ridden along, ended up in rear 9Ls off the pace, out of touch passing 600M, never involved.

Settled in last few in 7th over 5L off the pace, made rapid progress at the half-way mark to gain 2L lead passing the 1000 metres, hung on well in straight.
Settled within 3L of pace in 4th, became 5th when passed by eventual winner 1000 metres out, circled the field rounding home bend but unable to peg back the winner the length of the straight.
Settled not far off in 3rd, became 4L back in 4th when passed by the eventual winner on the bend, snuck up on the rail making home turn, one-paced from 3rd into straight.

Gradually worked his way forward early stages before settling in 2nd just off the pace on first bend, became 3rd when passed by eventual winner 1000M out, lost further ground under pressure from approaching home straight.
Settled in 6th in rear of midfield, shuffled backward when tempo quickened approaching the home bend, came under pressure entering home straight, plodded on.
Settled in 5th just over 3L back on the rail, shuffled backward when tempo quickened approaching the home bend, saved ground turning in, found nothing in straight.
Settled well back, plodded on. (Lame next day)
Settled well back, commenced move from approaching home bend but effort short-lived dropping to last 600 metres out.
Began well from a wide gate, soon came across to lead on the rail, ceded advantage passing the 1000 metres, dropped away quickly from 2.5L 2nd into straight. (Lame)
Behind midfield along the fence, benefited by the fast tempo, held up 4-2, progressed steadily when clear and scored.
Took rail and lead easily, clocked fast sectionals, hung on well until 50M overhauled, ran on for 2nd.
Pushed early, trapped wide in midfield, suited by the fast tempo, made steady ground 300M for 3rd.
Eased back, trapped wide, benefited by the fast pace, progressed steadily 300M, just missed by a narrow margin.
At rear, favoured by the fast pace, trapped wide, dashed well 200M.
Failed to muster at rear, suited by the fast tempo, lack room 4-2, made ground when clear.
At back, benefited by the fast tempo, however blocked all straight, not tested.
Hard ridden early but not muster, trapped very wide at back, favoured by the fast tempo, made steady ground 300M.
Eased back, on heels early, benefited by the fast tempo, made minor ground 200M.
Hard ridden forward, not suited by the fast pace, weakened 250M.
Pushed forward, harmed by the fast pace and trapped wide, emptied 200M.
Pushed forward, not suited by the fast pace, weakened 150M.
Pushed forward, not suited by the fast tempo, lack room 400M, no progress.
Hard ridden early but not muster, never improved.
Raced midfield, commenced to improve on straightening, quickened passing 200M, finished unchallenged.
Raced behind midfield on rail, passing 1000M was checked, kept on rail at Home Turn, made up some nice ground passing 200M.
Settled at back, improved at Home Turn, widest on straightening, gained some ground passing final 50M.
Raced midfield, near 1000M was checked, responded well in the straight.
Fast out, settled at handy position, one-paced.
Crowded after start, left racing wide and without cover after 900M in midfield, one-paced.
Gradually ridden to take lead after 800M, gave ground near 100M.
Taken back at start, limited response in the straight.
After start ridden to take forward position, near 1000M was checked then raced midfield on rail, failed to run on.
Ridden along and took lead near 1000M, then steadied to allow a runner to cross, emptied passing 150M.
Crowded start, raced at tail, slightly improved from 700M, but still 6 lengths back, finished off very strongly in straight and scored by a head.
Began well, sent forward to take the lead, easy lead on turn, kept on very well in straight, but just couldn't hold off the winner late.
Taken back from gate 13, raced 2 wide at rear, 6 lengths or so back, 3 wide with cover on turn, taken wide in straight and made very good progress to take 3rd, nearest on line.
Jumped well from the widest draw, raced prominently but trapped very wide, no cover on turn, kept on evenly to the line, finished 4th.
Began well from gate 1, positioned 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, finished off evenly.
Crowded out shortly after start, raced at rear, 5 to 6 lengths back, saved ground on turn, no daylight early in straight, made some headway when clear final 100M.
Bumped start and unbalanced, raced 4 wide in midfield, no cover on turn, 3 lengths back, failed to quicken in straight.
Taken back to race at rear, 7 lengths back, same margin back on turn, kept to inside after straightening and made minor progress.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 4 to 5 lengths back on turn, made some headway early in straight, checked off heels near 100M, one-paced thereafter.

Slightly slow out, raced 4Ls back on rail, saved ground on turn, no clear running early in straight, showed some response when clear near 300M, but held up for running again near final 100M, eased thereafter.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide, 3 to 4 lengths back, better than midfield, similar position on turn, in traffic early in straight, then steadied off heels near 100M, eased thereafter.
Bumped start and unbalanced, raced prominently but wide early, lost position on turn, 5 lengths or so back near 400M, showed no response in straight.
Jumped with them, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, got cover on turn, showed no response early in straight, weakened from 200M. (Swollen left front fetlock.)
Began well from a wide draw, raced prominently but wide, peaked turning in, weakened gradually in straight, eased final 150M.
Fast into stride, took the stands rail easily and lead, travelled well throughout, finished off very well and scored easily.
Average to begin, raced behind lead early, 2 away from the stands rail, moved closer from 600M, kept on well to the line and take 2nd.
Bumped on jumping, raced behind lead, near to the stands rail, awkwardly placed near 650M, showed good response final 400M to take 3rd, no threat to the first two.
Jumped well, raced prominently, closer to the middle of the track, peaked near 400M, kept on evenly to the line.
Began fairly from gate 10, showed no early speed, raced at tail, 5 lengths back to make up 400M, made very good progress thereafter to be nearest on line, no threat to the first few.
Bumped on jumping, raced prominently, near to the stands rail, peaked near 300M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Bumped start, no early speed, raced behind midfield nearer to the middle track, showed no response final 400M.
Bumped start, raced behind midfield in the middle of the track, made no impression final 400M.
Average to begin, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail early, showed no response and weakened from 600M, finished tailed out.
Slightly slow out, raced closer to the middle track, 2 lengths or so back, showed no response to riding final 400M and dropped away tamely, finished last.
Rolled forward to settle in one-off one-back, sat 2-1/2L off the lead, kicked away at 250M and held on to score by 1/2L.
Settled in worse than midfield, 5-1/2L behind 2 wide, stormed home from 200M to finish just 1/2L behind.
Awkward start and then steadied, at rear 8L behind along the rail, ran on well to the finish.
Niggled along before finding cover towards the rear, 6-3/4L behind 2 wide, commenced move at 650M, green but made nice ground.
Raced in front of midfield, 4-1/4L behind 2 wide, hampered just after 400M, ran on fairly.
Taken back to be at the rear, 8-1/4L behind 2 wide, bumped near 250M, made minor ground.
Sat just in front of midfield, raced wide and without cover, weakened out passing 200M. (Blood in trachea)
Travelled in worse than midfield, wide but with cover, remained one paced in the straight.
Niggled along, settled to race in behind midfield along the rail, very one paced.
Urged before settling to race outside the lead, remained in touch until just passing 300M only. (Blood in trachea)
Sent forward to obtain the rail and led, flattened and headed approaching 300M.
Travelled in front of midfield along the rail, found nothing in the straight.
Raced in about midfield along the rail, weakened badly passing 300M.
Pushed all the way from the start, in about midfield but trapped wide, gave ground after turn.
Clean jump, positioned 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, easy run on turn, angled out early in straight and finished off well to score on his debut.
Jumped well, positioned 2 wide, 1 to 2 lengths back, same position on turn, finished off well to take 2nd, just missed by narrow margin.
Began well, unable to slot in, raced 3 wide with no cover in midfield, 2 to 3 lengths back on turn, closed off well to take 3rd.
Quickly into stride, sent forward to take the lead, shared lead on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed near 150M, stayed on for 4th.
Taken back from the widest gate, raced 2 wide at rear, 5 to 6 lengths back, similar position on turn, taken wide in straight and finished off strongly to be nearest on line, just missed frame.
Began smartly, sent forward to race outside to the leader, shared lead on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed near 150M, slightly weakened thereafter.
Average to begin, positioned 2 wide in midfield, crowded near 900M, same position on turn, finished off evenly.
Bumped start and unbalanced, raced at tail, 7 lengths back, still well back on turn, passed some tired rivals in straight.
Began fairly from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, kept on evenly early in straight, weakened from final 200M.
Taken back from barrier 11, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, 5 lengths or so back, bumped and unbalanced near 900M, similar position on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Jumped with them, raced at rear, 5 to 6 lengths back, inclined to lay out and bumped near 800M, made no progress in straight.
Average to begin, raced 2 to 3 wide with cover at rear, 5 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, showed no response in straight, eased final 50M.
Wide no cover throughout chasing leaders, responded well to pressure inside 300M, challenged leader strongly final 100M and got up just before line.
Driven along and crossed to the lead 1000M, steadied the pace once in the lead, opened up 1.5L lead early straight, dug deep when challenged by winner 100M, conceded near post.
Towards the rear along the 2-path, brought wide 450M, stuck to task well on straightening, kept coming for placing, nearest finish.

Guided to a rail position behind midfield, shuffled further back passing 900M when pace slackened, angled out 400M, powered home down outside, made good progress late to finish just behind the placegetters.
Awkwardly away, chased leaders along the rail, not helped by the slackening tempo and lost ground passing 900M, held up early straight, kept on well behind leader but no clear run final 50M.
Reined back after the start, took closer order in midfield passing 1300M, held up early straight, chased hard final 300M but unable to close the gap on leaders.
Pushed up to occupy prominent position, raced keenly when leader steadied the tempo, held ground early straight, out of contention inside 200M. (Jockey questioned re tactics.)
Drifted back to the rear from wide barrier, settled down 5Ls off the pace, brought wide into straight but couldn't quicken in the run home.
Crowded for room after jumping, slotted into a 3-wde spot midfield, pushed out 500M but lacked the finishing effort.
Jumped fairly, restrained to be 2nd last along the rail 5L on settling, driven along 550M but struggled to make headway on the run home. Never threatened.
Chased the pace, shoved along 550M to maintain position, stopped at the 300M, dropped out rapidly to finish last.

Moderately away from gate 1, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, easy run on turn, kept to inside after straightening, no clear running until final 150M, finished off very strongly to score.
Bumped start, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well throughout, kept on well in straight but just couldn't hold off the winner late.
Moderately away from the widest draw, positioned 3 wide with cover, 3 lengths back, same margin back on turn, finished off well to take a place, nearest on line, good debut.
Began well from a tricky gate, sent forward to race outside the leader in 2nd, there to turn, kept on evenly in straight to make frame.
Began well, positioned 1 out 1 back, crowded near 900M and steadied off heels shortly thereafter, 2 lengths or so back on turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, 5 lengths or so back, inconvenienced near 750M, no clear running after turning in, made minor progress when clear final 100M.
Taken back on jumping, raced 4 lengths or so back at rear, 2 to 3 wide with cover, made some headway in straight without threatening.
Bumped start, unable to slot in, trapped wide in midfield, sent forward on turn, peaked near 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Clean jump, positioned 2 to 3 wide with cover behind midfield, 3 lengths or so back on turn, finished off evenly.
Jumped well and prominent, checked and unbalanced when rival crossed near 900M, 3 wide with no cover on turn, weakened gradually in straight, eased late. (See Racing Incidents.)
Raced 4 lengths or so back on rail, there to turn, showed no response in straight, finished last.

Cruised forward early to be handily placed 4th/5th. Forced a run at the top of the straight. Came off heels 350m. Strong to the line. Nosed in front at 50m, and was increasing the margin under hands and heels late.
Bumped and unbalanced on jumping, but recovered well to push forward and sit 2nd. Bumped and unbalanced 350m. Strong to the line and just overtaken in the shadow of the post.
Cruised forward early to settle around midfield, 3 wide with no cover. Wider on the turn. Minor interference at 350m. Solid run late and was making some ground on 2nd.
Taken up early to lead. Still in front at 150m but peaked soon after and missed a place late.
Began awkwardly, lost ground and settled around midfield. Stayed close to the rail in straight and stayed on OK, without threatening.
Cruised forward early to settle midfield. Bumped top of straight. Badly hampered 350m. 1 paced to the line late.
Cruised forward early to settle forward of midfield. Battled on fairly in straight, but no threat.
Taken forward early to be well placed 4th/5th. Off heels 350m, but 1 paced in the straight and eased last 50m.
Dropped back from the wide draw to sit at the rear of the field. Battled on 1 paced early in the straight. Already easing before being held up last 100m.
Eased back early to settle last. Widest on the turn, but made no impression in the straight.
Taken forward early to eventually settle 2nd passing 1100m. Gave nothing in the straight and eased last 75m.

Broke well, settled just off the pace in 4th and as much as 5L back when tempo quickened early far side, commenced move coming onto home bend, 3-wide turning in and hit the front shortly after, kept on well despite wandering about.
Settled mainly in midfield in 6th, commenced move leaving the Rock, sustained progress from 5th rounding home bend to reach 2nd passing the 200 metres, found winner too good.

Began awkwardly, soon taken across to the rail 2 back in 5th, further away from the lead when tempo quickened approaching the back straight, renewed effort rounding final bend and fought on steadily to reach 3rd late.
Crowded at start, settled in midfield or slightly worse on the rail, commenced move entering home straight, ran on steadily under pressure without threatening.

Pressed forward from the widest gate to join the lead, settled one back on the rail passing the 1200 metres, restrained behind fast pace early in back straight, hit the front briefly after straightening for home, soon weakened.
Moderate start from a wide gate, settled one off the rail in midfield or slightly worse, came under pressure approaching home straight, kept on steadily without quickening.

Ridden along from a wide gate, taken back for cover from wide in midfield, commenced run under pressure from towards the rear rounding home bend, sustained progress from widest turning in down the centre of home straight.

Settled just off the pace in 3rd on the rail, became 4th some 3L back passing the 800 metres, gained closer on the rail entering home straight but unable to sustain effort in the run to the line. (Lame next day)
Jumped fairly, soon dropped to last few despite niggled along, remained towards the rear on the rail most of the way to the straight, produced good late impression under pressure.
Moderate start, settled well back, saved ground on the inside turning for home, produced good late impression closing stages.

Broke well, given reminders and soon took up running, raced keenly setting fast sectionals around stables bend and early in back straight, led until headed turning for home, dropped away quickly inside the final 250 metres.
Settled at the back from a wide gate, made short-lived effort coming onto home bend, soon weakened after the 400 metres.
Hard ridden early but not muster, trapped 3 wide in midfield, pace good, progressed steadily 300M to score.
Very slow away, checked 850M, pace good, 2-4 wide, dashed well 300M for 2nd.
In front of midfield, 2 wide, blocked most straight, dashed well when clear.
Hard ridden forward, sat 2 wide, pace good, held ground in straight.
Hard ridden to take rail and led at good pace, out of fuel 150M.
Eased back, 2 wide, pace good, blocked most straight, progressed steadily.
Eased back, 2-3 wide, pace good, made some ground 200M.
Pushed to obtain box seat, pace good, no dash.
Hard ridden forward, trapped 3 wide throughout, pace good, weakened 100M.
Pushed early, took rail in midfield, pace good, checked 600M, held up in straight, made steady ground.
At back along the fence, pace good, lack room in straight, made some late ground.
Checked badly at start, took rail at rear, pace good, blocked most straight, not properly tested.
Crowded on jumping then raced at rear, very wide on straightening, quickened passing 100M to score.
Ridden along to race behind leaders, responded solidly in the straight.
Urged along to race behind leader, travelled nicely in the straight, finished well.
Travelled wide and without cover, widest on straightening, gained ground when placed pressure in the straight.
Raced midfield, travelled keenly and lay out in the middle stages, finished OK.
Moderate start, settled midfield on rail, fought hard but only one-paced.
Taken back at start, raced behind midfield, one-paced.
Settled behind midfield on rail, held up near 150M, limited response.
Began only fairly, raced at tail, held up near 100M then failed to run on.
Fast out then ridden along to take lead, faded out passing 200M.
Jumped with them, positioned 3 back on rail, saved ground throughout, finished off strongly in straight to score.
Bumped start and unbalanced, positioned 2 wide in midfield, same position on turn, showed good response early in straight, bumped near 200M, finished off strongly thereafter to get 2nd.
Jumped well from the widest draw, sent forward to race 2 wide in 2nd, a length back, same position on turn, kept on well in straight but unable to hold off the first two.
Slightly slow out, raced at rear, crowded near 1300M, positioned 6 to 7 lengths back on rail thereafter, there to turn, made very good progress in straight to make frame.
Slightly slow out, positioned on rail behind midfield, there to turn, angled out near 400M, made minor progress in straight without threatening.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 6 lengths or so back, carried wider turning in, made minor progress in straight.
Moderately away, positioned 2 wide better than midfield, same position on turn, kept on evenly early in straight, bumped near 200M, slightly weakened thereafter.
Away with them, sent forward to take the lead, enjoyed the easy lead to turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed near 150M, weakened thereafter.

Moderately away from gate 1, positioned 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, difficult to settle near 1400M, continued to travel keenly on the first turn, same position on turn, one pace in straight.
Average to begin, raced 3 wide, 8 lengths back early, 2 wide from near 1100M, 6 lengths back on turn, made no progress in straight.

Bumped shortly after start, raced wide at rear early, bumped and carried wider on the first turn, found cover near 1100M, 9Ls back in the middle stages, angled out near 500M, very wide turning in, failed to close off in straight.
Bumped start and unbalanced, raced at tail, crowded near 1300M, still well back on turn, showed no response in straight, eased final 100M.(Blood in trachea.)
Clean jump, sent forward from 1500M to take the lead, led by a length, travelled well throughout, kept on very well in straight and scored.

Began fairly, sent forward to race prominently, badly unbalanced when passing a shadow on the track near 1500M, positioned 1.5L behind the leader on rail thereafter, kept chasing hard to the line, but always held.
Average to begin, positioned on rail at rear, hard ridden from 500M, finished off strongly to take 3rd without threatening the first two.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide behind midfield, difficult to settle in the early stages, 3 wide from near 750M, hard ridden from 450M, peaked early in straight, finished off one-paced.
Began awkwardly, positioned on rail behind midfield, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Taken back to race at rear, 2 wide, 5 lengths or so back, still last turning in, made no impression in straight. (Lame left front leg next day.)
Moderately away from gate 9, raced 3 wide with no cover behind midfield, moved forward after entering the back straight, 3 wide in 3rd on turn, weakened gradually in straight.
Began well, raced 2 wide, 2 to 3 lengths back, similar position on turn, showed no response in straight. (Blood in trachea.)
Slightly slow out, recovered, positioned a length behind the leader on rail early, angled out near 1200M and moved closer to the new leader, peaked on turn, emptied early in straight and eased.
Travelled in front of midfield, 3-1/4L behind along the rail, battled on gamely to score by a neck.
Took the rail and led by 3/4L, fought on only to be caught by the winner inside final 50M, finished a neck behind.
Rolled forward from barrier 1 to obtain the box-seat, sat 1-3/4L behind, kept on and held off a late challenge for 3rd.
Settled to race just behind midfield, 6-1/4L behind 2 wide, ran on steadily to the line.
Sent forward to sit outside the lead, awkward to heels at 150M but was weakening out prior.
Rolled forward into one-off one-back position, found no extra to keep up passing 200M.
Jumped awkwardly, settled in about midfield along the rail, looked flat in the straight.
Taken back to be at the rear, niggled to keep up from 800M, showed no turn of foot.
Bumped start, then taken back to race near the rear along the rail, one paced only.
Feet off ground at start, raced towards the tail, did not improve. (Lame right front leg with sore both front fetlocks)
Bumped start, then pushed but settled in behind midfield only, trapped wide throughout, not competitive.
Settled in midfield, urged from 650M, faded out gradually. (Blood in trachea)
Jumped well, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, easy run throughout, angled out near 400M, hit the front early in straight, kept on well and just able to hold off the rival.

Bumped start, positioned on rail in midfield, 4-5Ls back, 2W from near 800M, there to turn, bumped and unbalanced early in straight, finished off strongly thereafter, just missed out in a close finish. (See Racing Incidents.)

Jumped well from the widest draw, raced prominently but 3 wide early, slightly taken back near 1000M to sit 2 wide, 3 lengths back, hard ridden from 450M, very wide turning in, made some progress to take a place.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide at rear, 7 lengths back, same margin back on turn, taken very wide in straight and finished off strongly to make frame.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 5 lengths or so back, there to turn, made some progress in straight without threatening.
Began only fairly and bumped, raced at rear, 10 lengths back, still well back on turn, finished off very strongly to be nearest on line without threatening the first few.
Moderately away from a middle draw, positioned 1 out 1 back, same position on turn, bumped early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Began only fairly and crowded, raced at tail, 10 lengths back, slightly closer on turn but still 8 lengths back, made minor progress in straight.
Away well, sent forward to race prominently, shared lead on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Jumped with them, positioned on rail in midfield, 4 lengths back, saved ground on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Bumped start and unbalanced, positioned on rail at rear, 6 to 7 lengths back, same position on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Quickly into stride, took the lead easily, shared lead on turn, peaked early in straight, dropped off tamely thereafter. (Lame right front leg next day.)
Jumped well to be chasing leaders, under gradual acceleration top of straight, led 120M out, raced away closing stages.
Gradually moved forward to be 2nd 700M chasing leader, looked to have his chance in the straight but couldn't match winner's kick final 150M.
Held up in mid-division, boxed on steadily to the line, got up for 3rd late.
Tracked leaders in 3rd, kept battling up the fence on straightening, one paced late and edged out of a placing near the line.
Began only fairly, from last position gradually improved to midfield but 3-wide no cover throughout, tried hard in the straight but couldn't reel in leaders.
Pressed forward, led uncontested at good tempo, held narrow lead turning in, faded away after being headed 150M. (Jockey reported saddle shifted after the jump and disadvantaged.)
Never far off from leaders, 3Ls off the pace 400M, only held ground in the straight, never a winning hope.
Dropped back to near the rear from wide barrier, 6Ls off leader over the turn, stayed on moderately from the back but never looked likely.
Switched off to the rear after jumping form wide draw, over 7Ls off leader middle stages, showed little turning in and failed to come into contention.
Not hurried after the start, reserved towards the rear, kept to inside on straightening but unable to quicken, plodded home. (Lame next day.)
Began awkwardly, raced at the rear, much further back than intended, couldn't come on in the straight, always back.
