Held narrow advantage on the rail early stages, ceded lead for one-back position on the rail passing the 1000 metres, tracked the leader into home straight, quickened well to hit the front just inside the 300 metres, won confidently.
Broke well, worked his way to the front over 1000 metres out, led the small field until headed inside the 300 metres. (Cast plate 1000 metres out)
Very slowly away, trailed the field in last of the 7 runners, saved ground turning for home and fought on steadily along the rail to be nearest at finish.

Soon taken back to 5th about 3L off the pace, gained 2L 4th coming onto home bend, switched out for a run entering straight, became 3rd some 3L back passing the 300 metres, kept on well but lost the placing closing stages.

Awkward at start losing ground, close up in 4th before crowded and shuffled back to 5th 800 metres out, hung out dropping to last of 7 entering home straight, fought on steadily past beaten horses in the run home.

Began awkwardly losing more than 2L, ridden along to recover to 5th over 3L back on the rail, inconvenienced coming onto home bend, kept on at the one pace under pressure without quickening in the run to the line.
Close up, given reminders when 2nd outside the leader 600 metres out, weakened noticeably after straightening.
Hard ridden forward, pace good, dominated from 500M.
Hard ridden to keep up in midfield, dashed well 200M for 2nd.
Pushed forward, pace good, ran on well to the line for 3rd.
Pushed to keep up in front of midfield, pace good, just held ground in final stages.
Led easily at good pace, hung on until 150M weakened.
Very slow away, hard ridden to keep up at back, pace good, ran on ok final furlong.
Behind midfield, pace good, ran on only fairly.
At rear, pace good, lack turn of foot.
Eased to sit in midfield, pace good, out of fuel 300M.
At back, pace good, no progress.
Hard ridden forward, pace good, soon emptied 450M.
Never a factor at rear.
Stumbled at start, never better than midfield.
Bumped badly at start, never competitive, tailed out.
Settled behind midfield, asked for effort passing 450M, quickened passing 100M to score.
Began awkwardly, raced at back, improved passing 500M, wide on straightening, travelled strongly in the straight, just missed by Neck.
Raced midfield, commenced to improve passing 500M, made up some nicely late ground.
Settled at handy position, passing 900M was left racing wide and without cover, fought hard and responded nicely in the straight.
Ridden along to take lead on one-off position, gave some ground passing 150M.
Taken back at start, widest on straightening, gained ground passing 100M.
Urged after start to take box seat, at entrance of the straight rider dropped his whip, finished OK.
Settled midfield on rail, battled hard entire straight.
Slow to begin, raced behind midfield on rail, one-paced.
Jumped well, raced behind the lead, gave ground passing 200M.
Settled at handy position, limited response when placed under pressure.
Began awkwardly then failed to muster speed despite being ridden along, never in it.
Bumped start, raced at rear, 4 lengths or so back on rail, saved ground on turn, angled out early in straight and finished off very strongly to score.
Bumped on jumping, raced at tail, 5 lengths or so back, still last turning in, finished off very strongly in straight to take 2nd.
Began well from gate 1, sent forward to take the lead, enjoyed the easy lead to turn, still led by a length at 400M, kept on very well early in straight, just couldn't hold off the first two.
Away nicely, positioned 2 wide, 4 lengths back, improved from 550M, made some progress in straight to make frame without threatening.
Jumped well, raced 2 wide, a length behind the leader, same position on turn, kept on evenly in straight.
Away with them, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, same position on turn, kept to inside after straightening, finished off one pace.
Jumped well, unable to slot in, travelled wide and without cover in 4th, there to turn, kept on evenly until near 200M, weakened thereafter.
Average to begin, failed to muster speed, raced 2 wide in midfield, hard ridden turning in, showed no response, eased final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Average to begin, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, finished off strongly to score by a head.

Jumped well from the widest draw, raced 3 wide, a length behind in the early stages, moved closer from 800M, sat outside the leader on turn, kept on very well in straight, just could not hold off the winner close home.
Away with them, sent forward to race prominently, took the lead near 800M, found rail near 700M, travelled well on turn, kept on very well in straight, just couldn't hold off the first two late.
Bumped start, raced 3 wide with cover better than midfield, no cover from 700M, moved closer turning in, kept on well in straight but always held.
Slightly slow out, positioned 3 lengths or so back on rail, angled out near 600M, same margin back turning in, made some progress in straight to be nearest on line.
Jumped with them, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, closer but wider on turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 5 lengths back at rear, checked off heels near 700M, 4 lengths or so back turning in, made minor progress in straight.
Began fairly, raced 2 wide, 4 lengths back, same position on turn, finished off evenly.
Began well, positioned 1 out 1 back, there to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter. (Sustained superficial abrasion to the right hind leg.)
Moderately away, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, 3 lengths back on turn, kept on evenly early in straight, weakened from final 200M.
Reared at start and lost ground, raced 5 lengths back at rear, checked off heels near 700M, same margin back on turn,failed to close off in straight.
Began awkwardly and bumped, raced 3 wide at rear, slightly improved from 600M, very wide turning in, weakened early in straight when hard run took effect.
Jumped with them, showed early speed to take the lead, headed near 850M, sat right behind the leader on turn, weakened early in straight.
Taken back from barrier 13, travelled wide and without cover at rear throughout, emptied early in straight when hard run took toll.
Travelled in midfield, 3-3/4L behind 2 wide, made nice progress in the straight to score by 3/4L.
Sat in front of midfield, 3L behind but wide and without cover, pushed winner to the line and finished 3/4L behind.
Sent forward to take the rail and led by 1/2L, built margin early in the straight, caught just before 50M, ran on.
In behind midfield, 4-1/2L behind 3 wide but with cover, saved ground before bumped at 150M, continued on well.
In worse than midfield, 5-1/4L behind along the rail, made ground steadily before was awkward to heels near the line.
Niggled along, in midfield initially but wide, improved to sit outside the lead near 900M, mostly one paced.
Pushed along to obtain the box-seat, remained in touch until approaching 150M.
Travelled at the rear along the rail, 7-1/4L behind at 400M, made minor inroad in the straight.
Rolled into position in midfield along the rail, emptied approaching 200M.
Settled in behind midfield and 2 wide, travelled keenly throughout, did not threaten. (Blood in trachea)
Slow to jump, remained at the rear throughout, never a factor.
Urged along, settled to race in one-off one-back, gave ground from 400M. (Heart irregularity)
Away with them, positioned on rail behind midfield, saved ground on turn, 2 wide from near 500M, still 8 lengths back turning in, finished off very strongly in straight to score by a nose.

Jumped well from the widest draw, sent forward to take the lead and set the tempo, enjoyed the easy lead on turn, kicked clear early in straight, kept on very well, just couldn't hold off the winner on line.
Taken back from barrier 13, raced 3 wide at rear early, 2 wide from near 1200M, 9 to 10 lengths back on turn, no daylight early in straight, finished off well when clear thereafter to take a place.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear, 11 lengths back, same margin back on turn, made very good progress in straight to be nearest on line.
Jumped with them, positioned on rail in midfield, 7 lengths back, 2 wide from near 600M, same margin back turning in, finished off evenly in straight.
Began well, sent forward to race 2 wide in 3rd in the early stages, found rail after passing 1000M, 5 lengths or so back on turn, peaked near 250M, slightly weakened thereafter.
Taken back from a wide gate, raced at tail, 12 lengths or so back, still at last on turn, kept to inside after straightening and made reasonable progress.
Slowly away, positioned on rail at rear, still 10 lengths back on turn, finished off evenly in straight. (Lame right front leg next day morning.)
Slightly slow out, raced 2 wide, 7 to 8 lengths back, carried wider near 600M, very wide turning in, peaked early in straight, kept on one-pace to the line.
Taken back to race 2 wide at rear, 12 lengths or so back, still well back on turn, made no real progress in straight.
Began well, raced 2 wide better than midfield, 7 lengths back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Clean jump from a middle draw, raced 2 wide at rear, 10 to 11 lengths back, same position on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned 4 lengths back on rail in the early stages, 8 lengths back on turn, showed no response early in straight, emptied 200M.
Average to begin, sent forward to race in 2nd, 2 lengths behind the leader, peaked turning in, weakened early in straight, eased final 150M.
Chased leader in slowly run race, moved closer 600M, cruised past leader 350M, drew nicely clear when asked, comfortably on top final 150M.
Led slowly by about 2L, quickened up 700M, couldn't repel winner 350M, kept grinding for 2nd, easily accounted the rest.
Settled last of 5, 9Ls off leader in slowly run race, crept closer home turn to be 5Ls behind 400M, stayed on mildly for 3rd but never near to challenge first 2.
In 3rd spot, 5Ls off the pace early stages, improved to a contending position 600M, outstayed by first 2 passing 300M, lost 3rd late.
In 4th place, 7Ls behind leader in a slowly run affair, couldn't pick up on straightening, never pose any threat.
Jumped well, raced 2 wide, 3 lengths or so back, there to turn, finished off strongly in straight to score.
Clean jump, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length on turn, kept on well in straight, but couldn't hold off the winner final 100M.
Restrained on jumping, raced 4 to 5 lengths back on rail, difficult to settle near 800M, similar position on turn, made good progress in straight to take a place.

Slightly slow out, raced 2 wide at rear, 6 lengths back, same margin back on turn, no clear running early in straight, finished off strongly thereafter to make frame. (Lost right front plate in the middle stages.)
Shifted outat startandmade contactwith rival, sent forward to race prominently but wide, no cover throughout, kept on evenly in straight.

Began well from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, 3 lengths or so back, tightened for room near 750M, saved ground on turn, no clear running early in straight, angled out near 200M and finished off evenly.
Jumped well, taken back to race 2 wide behind midfield, 4 lengths back on turn, angled out early in straight, made some progress thereafter without threatening.
Inconvenienced start, recovered, positioned 3 wide with cover, 3 lengths back, similar position on turn, peaked on run near 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Jumped well from a wide draw, raced prominently early, sat right behind to the leader on turn, kept on evenly to 200M, weakened thereafter.
Average to begin, sent forward to race outside to the leader, a length behind on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Fractious in gate and slowly away, raced at rear, 7 to 8 lengths back, still well back on turn, failed to close off in straight. (Laceration to the right hind stifle.)
Began awkwardly, raced 3 wide with cover, 4 lengths back, there to turn, showed no response in straight.
Reared at start and lost considerable ground, raced at tail throughout, never competitive.
Average to begin, raced at rear, 6 to 7 lengths back on rail, peaked on turn, emptied early in straight.

Crowded early, before dropping back to the rear of the field. Had a clear run from the top of the straight but bumped and unbalanced 350m. Showed good turn of foot from 200m. Was still pulling away despite being eased late.
Eased out early to settle midfield. Pushed forward to be well placed 5th at 800m. Strong early in the straight and nosed in front at 200m. Faded in the last 100m, but far enough clear to hold 2nd.
Dropped back early from the wide draw to sit 2nd last. Had clear running from 250m. Strong late and was making ground on 2nd.
Cruised forward to settle around midfield. Wider at 350m. Showed paced last 150m and was gaining on 3rd late.
Keen when being steadied for cover early, before settling 2nd/3rd, 1 off the fence. Led early in the straight, but couldn't maintain the effort and dropped out from 200m.
Dropped back early from the wide draw to sit worse than midfield. Came out off heels for run at top of the straight, but had to switch back in as that closed. Only stayed on 1 paced late.
Eased forward to settle midfield, 3-4 wide with no cover. Widest on the turn, bumped 350m but only went to the line 1 paced.

Slowly away but recovered well to settle around midfield. Severely checked and lost a couple of lengths at 900m. Struggled to get back into rhythm. Stayed on steadily in straight, but no hope of recovering.
Pushed forward early to sit 2nd. Checked off heels when crossed and tempo switched off at 900m. Showed no speed in the straight and dropped out from 250m.
Began awkwardly and dropped back to a clear last. 1 paced in the straight and only passed a couple that had packed up.
Pressed forward early to be well placed 3rd/4th on the fence. Checked and lost ground 900m. Already dropping out before the turn and was checked off heels 400m but made no impact in the straight.
Pushed forward to lead and was allowed to cross to fence 900m. Eased the pace at that point and caused carnage behind. Gave nothing in the straight and packed up at 200m.
Very wide in midfield, until pressing to share the lead at 900m. Dropped out very quickly from 400m and played no part. Vet- Blood in trachea.

Crowded for room after start, settled down behind midfield 5Ls off the pace, held up early straight, got split 300M, quickened away impressively to lead 200M out, drew well clear for a dominant victory.
Reserved behind midfield, about 5Ls off the pace home turn, pulled to the outside on straightening, ran on well late to go 2nd just in time but well beaten by winner.
Jumped well to be racing outside leader, found to be no match for winner mid-straight, kept grinding on to hold 2nd from 200M until headed near line.
Switched off after the start to race towards the rear, stayed on moderately but no clear run 200M-100M, found the line well again late to narrowly miss out on 3rd.
Moved up to share the lead on the inside, tried hard in straight but couldn't shake off pursuers, headed by winner 200M, fought on for minor placing but faded late and edged out to 5th close home.
Chased leaders in a steadily run race, battled steadily in the straight, lacked a strong kick, held ground over final 200M.
Reserved in midfield, switched 3-wide from 800M, swung wide into straight, kept battling away on same pace over final 200M.
Pressed forward but unable to cross, caught 3-wide no cover throughout, stayed in touch early straight, effort petered out 200M after difficult trip.
Began awkwardly, recovered to race in midfield 4Ls off the pace, blocked and unable to obtain clear running throughout in the straight, not tested.
Taken back to be 2nd last, well off the pace down the back straight but moved closer home turn, closed off mildly without threatening.
Away with them, settled down in 7th spot just ahead of midfield, laid in under pressure in straight, let down fairly lacked finishing effort.
Slow to begin then ridden along to go forward, 3-wide chasing leaders on settling, couldn't muster speed to be closer early straight, couldn't go on final 150M.
Raced ahead of midfield and saved ground along the rail, crept closer to leaders nearing top of straight, had his chance, faded out of contention 150M.
Dropped back early stages from wide draw, settled in rear almost 10Ls back at 1200M but moved closer home turn, driven out 400M but couldn't do much in the run home.

Began from the widest gate, travelled wide behind midfield far side, fought on well down the centre of the straight to prevail narrowly.
Hard ridden to hold prominent 2nd on the rail, hit the front upon straightening going about 2L clear early in straight, unable to sustain effort and caught close home.
Settled in midfield, came to challenge under pressure after straightening, ran on steadily to be nearest at finish.

Prominent early from a wide gate, soon dropped back to wide without cover in midfield, circled the field home bend, sustained steady progress from about 2L back into the straight to narrowly miss a placing.
Amongst leaders when given reminders early, settled just over 1L back in 3rd, lost position turning into straight, ran home one-paced.
Broke well from a middle gate, settled on the rail 2.5L back in 4th, in similar position entering straight, found no extra shortly after.
Prominent early, dropped quickly to the back end of the field before home bend, ran home one-paced.
Soon dropped to the tail-end, detached from the main body of the field most of the way to the straight, produced good late impression running past well-beaten horses inside the final 200 metres.
Slow out and slow to muster, trailed the main body of the field early stages, improving to 8th towards midfield coming onto home bend, one-paced under pressure in straight.
Never seen with a chance, ran home one-paced.
Prominent early from a wide gate before settling towards the rear, came under pressure turning into the straight, failed to make any impression.
Ridden to lead, dropped out sharply after straightening.
Hard ridden early but not muster, trapped 3 wide in midfield, slide forward 1000M when the pace slackened, ran on strongly to score.
Eased back, 2-4 wide, dashed strongly 300M despite not suited by the slow pace.
Took rail and lead easily, clocked advantageous slow sectionals, hung on well until 100M overhauled, ran on for 3rd.
In front of midfield along the fence, just held ground in straight.
At back, 2-3 wide, harmed by the slow pace, little dash 200M.
Eased back, trapped 3-4 wide, not suited by the slow pace, made early move 900M, weakened 250M.
Hard ridden forward, sat 2 wide, benefited by the slow tempo, out of fuel 250M.
Pushed early, behind midfield along the fence, harmed by the slow pace, ran on fairly.
At rear, raced 4 wide round the Home Turn, harmed by the slow pace, no dash.
Hard ridden forward, 2 wide, emptied 500M.
Never a factor at rear.
Trapped wide in midfield, faded quickly 500M.
Ridden along to take forward position, passing 900M lost right hind plate, travelled wide and without cover, responded solidly in the straight to score.
Hard ridden to settle behind leaders, improved near 400M, finished strongly.
Fast out, settled midfield, made up some nice late ground.
Raced at rear, wide on straightening, responded well when under pressure, gained ground passing 100M.
Settled in box seat, fought hard entire straight, finished OK.
Jumped nicely then urged along to take lead, gave ground passing 50M.
Began awkwardly, settled at back on rail, one-paced.
Raced behind midfield, always niggling, limited response in the straight.
Settled midfield on rail, passing 900M lost ground when racing tight, limited response.
Hard ridden then steadied to settle midfield, failed to run on in the straight.
Raced behind midfield on rail, gave ground rounding Home Turn, no response in the straight.
Nice early speed, travelled only fairly in the middle stages, weakened badly when placed under pressure rounding the Home Turn.
Moderately away, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, easy run on turn, finished off well to score.
Jumped well, sent forward to take the early lead, headed near 800M, 2nd on turn, kept on very well in straight, just couldn't hold off the winner late.
Began well, raced 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, checked near 700M, 3 lengths back on turn, made good progress in straight to take 3rd.
Jumped well from the widest draw, sent forward to race prominently, took the lead near 800M, peaked and headed near 300M, slightly weakened thereafter, missed 3rd on line.
Began awkwardly and bumped, raced at tail, 8 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, taken wide in straight and made good progress to be nearest on line.
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, 4 lengths back, same position on turn, finished off evenly.
Began very awkwardly and lost ground, raced at rear, 7 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, kept to inside after straightening and made minor progress.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, slightly hampered near 700M, wider on turn, finished off one-paced.
Bumped on jumping, raced prominently but wide, 2 wide from near 700M, peaked on turn, kept on evenly early in straight, weakened from final 150M.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide, 6 lengths or so back, there to turn, failed to close off in straight.
Away with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, 4 lengths back, travelled wide with no cover on turn, peaked on run near 200M, weakened thereafter.
Raced at rear throughout, never competitive.
Began well from a middle draw, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, there to turn, kept on very well in straight to score narrowly.

Jumped well from gate 13, raced prominently but wide early, positioned 2 wide in 4thafter entering the back straight, angled out near 800M, 3 to 4 wide with no cover on turn, kept on very well in straight, just narrowly beaten.

Began only fairly, raced wide with cover in midfield early, difficult to settle on the first turn, continued to travel keenly thereafter, 3 wide with some cover on turn, taken wide in straight and made good progress to take 3rd.

Jumped well, took the rail easily, sat a length behind the leader on rail, there to turn, hit the front near 250M, kept on well thereafter, but just couldn't hold off the first few close home. (Lost left front plate.)
Jumped with them, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, similar position on turn, bumped early in straight, finished off strongly thereafter to be nearest on line.
Jumped well from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, finished off evenly.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, angled out early in straight, tight for room near 200M,plodded on at same pace thereafter.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide at rear early, found rail after entering the back straight, 6 to 7 lengths back on turn, made some progress in straight without threatening.
Average to begin, positioned on rail behind midfield, there to turn, kept to inside after straightening, finished off one paced. (Lost right front plate.)
Bumped start, sent forward to race prominently, took the lead near 1200M, led by a length on turn, headed near 250M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Bumped on jumping, raced 2 wide at rear, 5 to 6 lengths back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Began fairly from the widest draw, raced 3 wide with cover at rear throughout, never a factor.
Taken back from gate 12, raced at rear throughout, never involved.
Jumped well from gate 9, unable to slot in, trapped 4 wide, moved closer after passing 950M, bumped near 800M, peaked on turn, emptied early in straight when hard run took effect, finished last.
Bumped start, raced in worse than midfield and stayed 2 wide, closed off strongly to score by a neck.
Urged to be prominent, took cover to be one-off one-back at 700M, produced good kick to finish 2nd inside final 150M.
Bumped start, settled to race in about midfield, 3 wide but with cover, ran on well for 3rd.
Pushed and then sat inside the lead along the rail, battled on hard but couldn't hold off the others.
Sent forward, trapped wide and improved to lead in 2 wide position at 700M, fought hard until flattened passing 100M.
Bumped start and lost ground, recovered to be in the box-seat, about 3L behind, finished off fairly to the line.
Pushed and was prominent before settling in front of midfield, wide and without cover, kept on one paced.
Shifted to the rail after the start, raced at the rear, made minor ground in the straight. (Lame left front)
Taken back to be at the rear, stayed 2 wide throughout, swung widest and made minor ground.
Asked but failed to muster, raced in worse than midfield, wide but with cover, did not threaten.
Stumbled at start, rolled forward to be in front of midfield, gave ground from 600M, tailed out.
Bumped start then raced in about midfield, gave ground from 600M, finished tailed out.
Jumped well, raced 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, travelled well on turn, angled out near 500M, finished off well to score.
Bumped shortly after start, sent forward to take the rail and sit a length behind the leader, easy run on turn, angled out near 450M, kept on well in straight to take 2nd.
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, taken wide in straight and finished off well to get 3rd.
Jumped well from the widest draw, sent forward to race prominently but wide, 2nd on turn, peaked early in straight, kept on evenly to the line.
Average to begin, raced at tail, 7 lengths back, same margin back on turn, made reasonable progress in straight without threatening.
Began well, raced behind midfield, 5 lengths back, angled out near 600M, 3 wide turning in, finished off evenly in straight.
Jumped well, positioned 2 wide in midfield, 4 lengths back, there to turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Taken back from gate 9, raced wide with cover at rear, 7 lengths back on turn, made no real progress in straight.
Raced at rear, 6 lengths back on rail, same margin back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Bumped shortly after start and unbalanced, sent forward to take the lead, enjoyed the easy lead on turn, peaked early in straight, headed near 300M, emptied shortly thereafter.
Began fairly, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 5 to 6 lengths back, peaked on turn, emptied early in straight, finished last.
Away smoothly to be chasing the pace, quickened up to lead inside 200M, held off challengers both sides late stages to score back to back win.
Chased leaders in a race ran at solid tempo, stuck to inside on straightening, came through narrow passage mid-straight to challenge but couldn't reel in winner.
Restrained to be 10th, behind midfield 6Ls off the pace, driven out 500M, came home well to be nearest at the finish, just missed out 2nd.
Assumed a midfield position along the rail, travelled well into straight, stayed on steadily to the line, restricted room late but didn't affect finishing position.
Began awkwardly and lost ground, held up 2nd last 7-8Ls behind leaders, closed off final 400M fastest, line came too soon just failed to make it to the top 4.
Pressed on from draw 1, led at good pace throughout, headed inside 200M, unable to hold off pursuers late.
Settled down behind midfield 6Ls behind leaders, saved ground on the inside, was finishing off the race well when no clear run nearing 100M, could have been closer.
From draw 10 couldn't get closer than 3-wide, positioned ahead of midfield, left with no cover from 800M, battled on in the straight without posing threat to leaders.
From draw 11 went forward after the start, travelled wide no cover until reaching the outside of leader 800M, held ground early straight, faded passing 200M.
Soon slotted into 2-wide spot in midfield from draw 14, raced a shade keen in middle stages, stayed on only fairly in the straight, never threatened.
From wide draw shifted across behind runners early stages, raced towards the rear, difficult to settle 1300M, widest rounding home turn, failed to run on in straight.
From wide draw taken back to race in last, about 9Ls off the good pace, ran past a couple of eased down rivals in straight only. Never involved.
Never far off the pace in 5th, couldn't hold his position passing 450M, beaten turning home, eased when no chance.
Held up 3-wide in midfield, under serious pressure home turn, lost touch turning in, heavily eased. (Irregular Heart Rhythm.)

Moderate start, settled 3-wide in midfield in 5th, commenced run rounding home bend sharing 3rd some 2L back into straight, sustained effort to assert authority 200 metres out.
Broke well from the widest gate holding narrow advantages, crossed to the rail in front over 1000 metres out, led until headed 200 metres out.
Ridden early, soon settled one back on the rail in 2nd, chased leader into straight, ran home one-paced.
Slightly slow out, quickly recovered to just worse than midfield on the rail, gained closer rounding home bend, fought on steadily from 3L in joint 6th into straight, never threatening.
Jumped fairly, held up in last few 3-wide, commenced move on top of home bend, some 3L back in joint 6th entering straight, fought on to reach 3rd momentarily 100 metres out but pipped late.
Slow out, settled in last few, commenced move over 300 metres out, ran on steadily to be nearest at finish.
Moderate start, settled just over 2L back in 3rd on the rail, held similar position rounding home bend and into the straight, weakened noticeably under pressure.
Jumped awkwardly and soon in last, trailed the field to approaching home turn, saved ground turning in, ran past well-beaten horses.
Settled just better than midfield in 4th, became 5th over 600 metres out, one-paced before weakening inside final 200 metres.
Settled in rear of midfield, hampered and lost position 1000 metres out, dropped towards the rear rounding home bend, made no impression in the run to the line.
Pushed early, settled in front of midfield, progressed steadily 400M to score with ease.
Eased back early, moved forward 1300M, took lead 1100M, hung on well until 200M overhauled, ran on for 2nd.
At rear, benefited by the fast pace, progressed steadily 300M for 3rd.
Pushed to obtain box seat, not suited by the fast tempo, ran on well until 100M weakened.
Eased to rear for cover, suited by the fast pace, made some ground 200M.
Hard ridden to hold the rail in midfield, benefited by the fast pace, just held ground in straight.
Hard ridden early, checked badly first turn, favoured by the fast tempo, however no dash in straight.
Behind midfield, trapped 3-4 wide throughout, no progress.
Pushed forward, 2-3 wide, harmed by the fast pace, out of fuel 300M.
Hard ridden forward, sat 2 wide, not suit by the fast pace, weakened 400M
Never competitive at back.
Never a factor, tailed out.
Eased back early but trapped wide, moved forward along back straight, emptied 400M.
Pushed forward, dropped off quickly 700M.
Ridden along to take lead from wide barrier, responded solidly in the straight and scored unchallenged.
Urged along to settle outside the lead, fought hard entire straight, finished solidly.
Settled behind midfield, wide on straightening, made up some nice late ground.
After start was hampered, raced midfield on rail, passing 950M was checked and lost ground, in the straight hung in and not fully tested.
Taken back at start, widest on straightening, gained ground passing 150M, finished well.
Raced in box seat, asked for effort on straightening, gave ground passing 50M.
Raced midfield, made some ground in the early part of straight, then weakened passing 100M.
Settled midfield, one-paced in the straight.
At start was heavily bumped and became badly unbalanced, raced at handy position, under pressure and one-paced.
Settled behind midfield, after 900M was left racing wide and without cover, limited response in the straight.
Throughout race travelled wide and without cover, weakened passing 300M.
After start was hampered, raced behind midfield, passing 950M was inconvenienced, no response in the straight.
Began awkwardly then bumped a runner heavily and lost ground, raced at back on rail, passing 950M was checked, failed to run on.
Taken back at start, never in it.
Began well from gate 1, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, saved ground throughout, awkwardly placed near 500M, finished off well to score easily.
Moderately away, sent forward to take the lead, shared lead on turn, headed early in straight, stayed on well thereafter to take 2nd.
Began well, raced 3 wide and without cover behind midfield, carried wider on turn, widest in straight, finished off very strongly to be nearest on line, good debut.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide in midfield, improved from 600M, kept on evenly in straight to make frame.
Clean jump from gate 11, sent forward to race prominently, 3 wide turning in, kept on evenly to the line.
Moderately away, positioned on rail behind midfield, gradually improved from 600M, no clear running in straight, not able to test properly.
Away with them, raced at rear on rail, inconvenienced near 1000M, angled out near 500M, made some headway in straight.
Jumped well from a wide draw, sent forward to race prominently but wide, shared lead on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide behind midfield, improved from 800M, very wide turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Taken back from the widest gate, raced 2 wide at rear, improved from 650M, very wide turning in, failed to close off in straight.
Moderately away, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths back, similar position on turn, brushed near 250M, weakened thereafter.
Fractious in the barrier and slow to begin, recovered to race 4 lengths back on rail, showed no response in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, 8 lengths back, still 6 lengths back turning in, failed to close off in straight.
Raced at rear throughout, never competitive.
Bumped start and unbalanced, positioned on rail at rear, 5 to 6 lengths back, angled out 800M, improved on turn, taken very wide in straight and finished off very strongly to score.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide at rear, 5 lengths or so back, slightly improved on turn, made very good progress in straight to take 2nd.
Began well from gate 1, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, saved ground to near 600M, took the lead near 300M, kept on well thereafter but just couldn't hold off the first two late.
Jumped well, sent forward to take the early lead, slightly headed after passing 1200M, same position on turn, kept on evenly in straight, just stayed on for 4th.
Slowly away, raced at tail, 7 to 8 lengths back, moved a bit closer approaching home bend, made very good progress in straight to be nearest on line.

Shifted out at start and bumped, raced 2 wide, a length or so back, difficult to settle for some distance after passing 1400M, awkwardly placed off heels near 700M, angled out turning in, finished off evenly.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, checked off heels near 700M, still 3 lengths back turning in, finished off evenly in straight.
Jumped well, positioned 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, finished off evenly.
Bumped start, sent forward to race prominently, took the lead after passing 1200M, 2 wide throughout, peaked and headed near 300M, weakened gradually thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Crowded out start, positioned 4 lengths or so back on rail, similar position on turn, finished off evenly.
Bumped on jumping, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, sent forward on turn, very wide into straight, weakened final 400M.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear, 7 lengths back, improved from 800M, bumped and carried wider near 700M, 4 wide turning in, failed to close off in straight.
Clean jump, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, failed to close off in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Moderately away from a wide draw, raced 3 wide behind midfield, no cover from 1100M, moved forward on turn, pressed leader near 600M, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter, eased final 100M.
Raced in just behind midfield, 4-3/4L off 2 wide, kicked clear from 200M to score comfortably by 3L.
Settled in just behind midfield, 4-1/2L behind 3 wide but with cover, kept on well but couldn't match the winner.
Eased back, raced in worse than midfield, 6-1/4L behind 2 wide, no clear running till 200M, closed off well thereafter.
Taken back to be at the rear, 7-1/2L behind and 4 wide at turn, made ground and ran on well to the line.
Niggled along and took one-off one-back position, ran on fairly until emptied late.
Sent forward to take the rail, shared lead at fast pace, weakened and headed near 200M.
Urged to be in front of midfield along the rail, continued on fairly to the line.
Raced in front of midfield 2 wide, one paced in the straight and eased late. (Rider concerned with horse's action)
Crowded after the start, raced at the rear 3 wide at turn, made minor ground.
Raced in just behind midfield along the rail, bumped at 200M, was one paced nonetheless.
Sent forward, sat 2 wide in the lead, ran at fast pace, emptied approaching 300M.
In behind midfield along the rail, did not threaten.
Prominent but trapped wide, weakened in the straight.
Began well, showed good speed to take the lead, found rail near 1000M, travelled well throughout, kicked clear after turning in and scored easily.
Slowly away, raced at rear, 5 to 6 lengths back, improved on turn, finished off very strongly in straight to take 2nd.
Jumped well from a wide draw, positioned 2 wide, a length or so back, same position on turn, kept on evenly in straight to take a place, no threat to the winner.
Began fairly, raced 2 to 3 wide with cover behind midfield, improved on turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Began well from gate 1, positioned 2 to 3 lengths back on rail, saved ground throughout, kept to inside after straightening and made minor progress.
Began fairly, raced behind midfield, closer on turn, angled out near 550M, no clear running early in straight, made minor progress when clear thereafter.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide in midfield, 2 to 3 lengths back, there to turn, no daylight early in straight, finished off evenly when clear thereafter.
Bumped start, raced wide with no cover in midfield, sent forward near 1050M, 3 wide in 3rd on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.(Lame right front leg next day morning.)
Taken back from gate 9, raced at tail, 6 to 7 lengths back, still last on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Jumped well, sent forward to race prominently, allowed the rival to cross near 1100M, sat a length behind the leader on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened from 250M, eased late.
Always prominent along stand's rail, bustled along halfway, gained lead 200M, held on well to the line.
Began only fairly, niggled along and improved to be 2L behind leader, tried hard final 400M but couldn't reel in winner.
Jumped on terms to lead, inclined to lay in throughout, unable to hold off winner 200M, fought on to line, lost 2nd close home but reasonably clear from rest.
In touch within 2Ls of leader, kept on evenly under pressure final 400M, not reached first 3.
Close up behind leaders, couldn't quicken with leaders passing 400M, awkwardly placed 200M, boxed on without threat.
From a low draw raced towards the outside of group, never far off from the pace, battled away only, tiring from 200M.
Sat just off the speed, worked home fairly without threatening.
Settled down 3-4Ls off the pace in mid-division, couldn't accelerate when required, never a winning chance.
Outpaced early, towards the rear 5-6Ls back, failed to pick up passing halfway, never involved.
Slow to begin, not hurried raced at the tail of the 13-horse field, 7-8Ls back in running, plodded past a couple of well beaten horses only.
Settled down 3Ls off the pace, couldn't quicken when driven out mid-way, not pressured after 200M when beaten.
Pressed forward from draw 1, couldn't hold his position passing halfway, weakened badly to finish tailed out. (Unacceptable Performance.)
Towards the rear along stand's rail, out of touch passing 500M, finished tailed out. (Unacceptable Performance.)
Bumped start and unbalanced, positioned 2 wide, 1 to 2 lengths back, there to turn, finished off strongly to score.
Jumped well, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, saved ground to 600M, kept on well in straight to take 2nd.

Began well, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, challenged the leader from 600M, took the lead early in straight, kept on well until headed near 150M, weakened thereafter, just stayed on for a place.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide, 4 to 5 lengths back, same position on turn, awkwardly placed early in straight, finished off strongly when clear thereafter to be nearest on line.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced 3 wide with cover at tail, 6 lengths back, same margin back on turn, made good progress in straight despite being difficult to ride.
Jumped well, taken back to race 3 wide with cover behind midfield, 4 lengths back on turn, made some progress in straight without threatening.
Jumped well from a tricky gate, unable to slot in, raced 3 wide with no cover in midfield, there to turn, ran home one-paced. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began awkwardly and crowded, raced 4 to 5 lengths back on rail, saved ground on turn, made some progress early in straight, peaked on run 150M, weakened thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Moderately away, raced 2 wide in midfield, same position on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened from final 200M.
Slowly into stride, raced at tail, 6 lengths back, same margin back on turn, failed to close off in straight. (Lame left front leg.)
Began fairly, positioned on rail in midfield, there to turn, failed to close off in straight.

Fast into stride, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, challenged by rival from near 600M, headed early in straight, dropped awayquickly thereafter, finished tailed out, unacceptable performance.
Broke well and pushed forward to eventually sit 2nd, 1 off the fence. Nosed in front at 300m, and ran strongly. Held off big challenge from 2nd late.

Cruised forward from the inside draw to settle 5th, on the fence. Raced tight when trying to come around heels at 350m. Strong to the line, and was gradually running down winner, but ran out of time late.
Pressed forward early, before easing back at 800m to worse than midfield. 4th last on the turn. Huge turn of foot in last 200m to take 3rd late and be rapidly chasing down first 2.
Eased forward to settle 4th, 1 off the fence. Ran steadily in the straight. Slightly 1 paced late to lose 3rd, and was being chased down from behind.
Eased out to settle just forward of midfield. Battled on solidly, but slightly 1 paced late.
Eased forward to settle around midfield. Solid effort in the straight and was making up some ground late.
Began awkwardly and settled at the rear of the field. Improved to be around midfield at 600m. Plugged on 1 paced for most of the straight, making some minor improvement late.
Eased out to settle midfield. No kick in the straight and eased out last 100m.

Began awkwardly, bumped and unbalanced. Dropped back early and settled at the rear of the field. Keen and had to check off heels 900, losing ground. Stayed on fairly and picked up some slower ones late.
Punched out early to be clear leader. Nothing left in the tank late and dropped out quickly from 200m.
Eased back to sit towards the rear of the field. Showed nothing in the straight and was eased late.
Early leader before dropping back to 3rd at 1000m. Raced tight at 350m, but dropped out quickly soon after and played no part. Unacceptable performance. Jockey questioned.
Travelled wide early. Tried to find cover at 900m, but trapped 3 wide with no cover. Gave ground in the straight, and played no part.
Bumped and unbalanced on jumping, before dropping back to sit last. Checked off heels and forced wider 900m. Gave nothing in the straight.

Settled towards rear on the rail from the widest gate, mainly in 9th in back straight, commenced move approaching the 400 meters, hung in and a difficult ride early in home straight, gained upper hand close to home.
Began fairly, pulled forward to 6th in midfield without cover, commenced move entering the straight, hit the front 150 metres out only to be headed close to home.
Taken back to rear of midfield in 8th from the one draw, raced keenly on the far side and shuffled slightly backward, swung wide into the straight, ran on steadily without threatening.

Ridden along from a middle draw, dropped to last few turning into back straight, remained similar and wide to the home turn, inconvenienced early in home straight, fought on steadily without threatening.
Pressed forward early sharing the pace on the rail, taken one back to 2L 3rd in back straight, fought on despite tight run early in home straight, unable to sustain effort inside the 100 metres.
Settled at the back, swung widest into the straight, made modest headway down the centre of the track.
Hard ridden early vying for the lead, settled 3L back in 4th in back straight, badly crowded early in home straight, weakened 200 metres out.
Moderate start, raced awkwardly at times in midfield in 7th on the rail, soon weakened after straightening.
Jumped fairly, shared early lead, restrained one back 2-wide turning into back straight, in similar position onto home turn, soon weakened under pressure.

Pressed forward from a wide gate to join the leaders going 6-wide onto the stables bend, eventually took up running on the rail turning approaching back straight, led until finding no extra inside the final 150 metres.
Settled the back, commenced run at the 600 metres circling the field on the bend, widest turning for home, soon weakened. (Mucus in trachea)
Well there early, settled just better than midfield in 5th on the rail, badly crowded approaching the 200 metres, never recovered.
Eased back, 2 wide, harmed by the slow pace, unleashed strong finishing efforts 300M to score.
Took lead easily, clocked slow sectionals until 800M to increase the speed, hung on well until 200M overhauled, ran on for 2nd.
Eased back, took rail, dashed strongly 200M for 3rd.
Pushed to occupy box seat, suited by the slow tempo, just held ground in straight.
Pushed forward, sat outside the leader, benefited by the slow tempo, ran on fairly.
At rear, 2-3 wide, harmed by the slow pace, dashed fairly.
Urged along to take lead from widest barrier, responded solidly and scored unchallenged in the straight.
Raced midfield on rail, asked for effort on straightening, battled well in the straight.
Ridden along after start, settled box seat, fought hard and finished well.
Settled midfield, made ground passing 150M, worked home nicely.
Raced at back, commenced to improve near 400M, made some ground passing 100M.
Settled at rear on rail, kept on rail to save ground at Home Turn, finished OK.
Travelled behind midfield, wide on straightening, made up some nice late ground.
Hard ridden to settle behind the leader, one-paced in the straight.
Settled at handy position, limited response when placed pressure.
Began awkwardly and lost ground, settled at back, failed to run on.
Travelled wide and without cover at handy position, weakened passing 100M.
Passing the 1000M was checked when crowded for room, faded out in the straight, must trial
Shifted out at start and made contact with rival, sat a length behind the leader on rail, saved ground to near 400M, finished off well to score.
Jumped well from gate 11, sent forward to take the lead, slightly headed on turn, kept on very well in straight to take 2nd.
Crowded out start, positioned 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, same position on turn, finished off well to take a place. (Saddle shifted back in the early stages.)
Jumped well from a wide draw, raced 3 wide in midfield, no cover after passing 600M, made some progress in straight to make frame.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Fast into stride, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, took the lead near 550M, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Bumped shortly after start and unbalanced, positioned 2 wide, a length or so back, there to turn, weakened gradually in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Steadied on jumping, taken back to race at rear, 6 lengths back on turn, made no real progress in straight.
Bumped on jumping, raced 3 wide with cover, 4 lengths or so back, there to turn, made no progress in straight.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 5 lengths back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Shifted out on jumping and made contact, failed to muster speed, raced at rear, 6 lengths or so back, race tight near 450M, showed nothing in straight.
Jumped well, took the lead easily, headed near 1100M, travelled nicely in 2nd thereafter, finished off strongly in straight and scored.
Began well from gate 1, positioned on rail behind midfield, there to turn, taken wide in straight and finished off very strongly to take 2nd.
Clean jump, positioned on rail better than midfield, 3 lengths or so back on turn, kept on evenly in straight to take a place.
Moderately away, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, angled out early in straight and made some progress to make frame without threatening.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 6 lengths back on turn, made contact early in straight, finished off evenly thereafter.
Bumped start, positioned on rail at rear, 8 lengths back on turn, angled out near 350M, made minor progress in straight.
Moderately away from a wide draw, raced 2 wide in 3rd, no cover throughout, 2-1/2L back on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final 150M.
Taken back to race at tail, 10 lengths or so back, still well back on turn, made no real progress in straight.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced 2 wide at rear, 10 lengths back, still 8 lengths back on turn, finished off one-paced in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Bumped start, raced 2 wide at rear, still 7 lengths or so back on turn, taken wide in straight but made no progress.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide in midfield, 5 to 6 lengths back, similar position on turn, crowded early in straight, showed no response thereafter.

Bumped start, sent forward to race prominently, travelled keenly after passing 1200M, took the lead shortly thereafter, led by 1 lengths on turn, got tired early in straight, dropped out rapidly final 200M.
In front of midfield, 3-1/4L behind along the rail, closed off strongly from 150M and won with something in hand.
Urged along until took position outside the lead near 700M, kept on well to finish 1/2L behind the winner. (Rein dropped passing 200M)
Eased to just behind midfield, 4-3/4L off along the rail, made nice ground and closed off well.
Niggled along to settle in midfield, 4-1/4L behind 2 wide, saved ground and ran on fairly well to the line.
Sent forward and raced the box-seat, sat 1-1/4L off, continued on one paced to the line.
Settled to race in one-off one-back position, sat 3L off, in touch to near 100M, found no extra.
Eased back, 7-1/4L behind along the rail, saving ground until on heels at 100M, continued on fairly thereafter.
Sent forward to take rail and led, stayed on until weakened out approaching 200M.
Raced in worse than midfield, 2 wide until taken wider near 400M, saved no ground.
Hampered at the start, sat towards the rear 2 wide, travelled keenly, failed to improve in the straight.
Hampered at the start, raced at the rear and 3 wide, crowded at 450M, did not feature.
At the rear and wide, improved and closest at turn, found nothing thereafter.
Began well from gate 1, raced prominently, took the lead near 450M, kept on very well in straight and scored easily.
Fast into stride, raced prominently but wide, bumped near 750M, 3rd on turn, finished off well to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.
Average to begin, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, same margin back on turn, kept on evenly in straight to take 3rd without threatening.
Away with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, raced tight near 600M, 4 lengths back on turn, made some headway in straight to make frame. (Lost right front plate after 900M.)
Jumped well, raced prominently but wide, slightly taken back 750M for some cover, 3 wide on turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Began very awkwardly, raced behind midfield, found rail near 600M, saved ground on turn, finished off evenly.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 4 to 5 lengths back, awkwardly placed rounding the home turn, made no progress in straight.
Began well, sent forward to take the early lead, bumped near 750M, headed near 450M, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Moderately away from a tricky draw, unable to slot in early, taken back to race 3 wide with cover behind midfield, made no progress in straight.
Slightly slow out, positioned on rail at rear, 7 lengths back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide at rear, still 7 lengths back on turn, failed to close off in straight. (Finished distressed.)
Raced at tail throughout, never a factor.
3-wide going into the 1st turn, no cover from 1400M and improved to be outside leader after 700M, fought on gamely in straight holding off pursuers from both sides to score.
Guided to the fence soon after the start, held up towards rear about 6Ls away, chased leaders willingly entering straight to be nearest at the finish.
Positioned ahead of midfield, remained in touch turning home, lay in under pressure 150M and had to be straightened up by jockey, re-grouped and found the line strongly late, just missed 2nd.
Tracked leaders along the fence, loomed a chance 200M, stuck to task well and only edged out to 4th in a close finish.
Crossed to the lead 1200M, had uncontested lead to 700M, kept battling away for the lead until faded final 50M.
Held up 2-wide in midfield 3-4Ls behind leaders, stayed on moderately to the line but well held by first few.
Guided to a midfield spot along the rails, 4Ls to make up 400M, brought wide, made some ground in the finish without seriously threatening.
Not hurried after the jump, settled down towards the rear 6Ls off the pace, made limited progress from 300M, never reached leaders.
Rolled forward after the jump, raced prominently just outside of leader, kept on same speed only entering straight, no longer a threat passing 200M.
Tracked the pace in 5th, always within 3Ls of leaders, under the pump 400M but found nothing, weakened away. (Lame LF leg.)
Dropped back from wide draw, in rear pair 8Ls off the pace, bustled along home turn but didn't pick up and never any impression.
Taken back from wide barrier to be racing at the back of the field 8-9Ls off the pace, didn't respond to urging passing 400M, never in the picture.

Jumped fairly, settled at the back of the small field near the centre of the track, commenced move from the half-way mark and hit the front 300 metres out, won comfortably.
Never far off, amongst leaders coming onto the course proper, failed to quicken under pressure inside the final 200 metres, held on for 2nd despite rider dropped rein near the 75 metres.
Began fairly, shared the pace on stands rail, came under pressure from the 300 metres, one-paced without quickening.
Soon dropped to last few travelling near stands rail, pulled forward nearing the course proper to within a length of the front-runners, unable to sustain effort inside the final 250 metres.
Settled off the pace and off the rails, gave ground under pressure from half-way out.
Disputed lead for the first 600 metres, weakened noticeably. (Questioned for disappointing performance)
Raced greenly early, well there to the 400 metres, folded up under pressure while hanging in.
Hard ridden forward, sat just off the leader 2 wide, ran on strongly from 600M to score.
Took box seat easily, lack room 500M, dashed well 300M for 2nd.
Midfield, trapped wide, dashed strongly 300M for 3rd.
Pushed forward, trapped 3 wide throughout, ran on well.
Midfield along the fence, just held ground in straight.
At back, trapped 2-3 wide, little dash 250M.
Hard ridden to keep up in midfield, just held ground in straight.
At back, little dash 200M.
At back, no progress in straight.
At rear, checked 700M, never improved.
Hard ridden to take rail and lead, hung on well until 250M dropped off quickly.
Slow away, never a factor.
Pushed early but not muster, never better than midfield
Pushed early but not muster, trapped wide, never competitive.
Jumped nicely then urged along to settle outside the lead, made nice ground in the straight, finished strongly to score.
Jumped well and settled in box seat, responded nicely in the straight.
Settled midfield on rail, made up some nice ground passing 200M.
Raced midfield, asked for effort passing 400M, over the final 100M lay in under pressure, finished well.
Travelled at back, commenced to improve near 500M, gradually made ground passing 200M.
Settled midfield, near 700 was taken wide and without cover, wide on straightening, worked home OK.
Settled behind midfield on rail, had some difficulty obtaining clear running in the early straight, made some ground passing 100M.
Ridden along from wide barrier then took lead after 1000M, gave ground passing 100M.
Taken back at start, widest on straightening, one-paced in the straight.
Hard ridden after start but failed to muster speed, travelled wide and without cover, weakened passing 150M.
Travelled behind midfield, no response when asked for effort, failed to make impression.
Raced at tail, under pressure but no response in the straight.
Raced at handy position, passing 600M tried to improve, faded out passing 200M.
Settled at handy position on rail, emptied passing 200M, failed to finish off.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide inmidfield, there to turn, angled out near 500M, finished off well to score.
Began well, raced 2 wide at rear, closer on turn, finished off well to take 2nd, solid debut. (Lost right hind plate.)
Bumped start, raced at tail, still last on turn, 5 lengths back at 400M,finished off very strongly in straight to take 3rd, nearest on line.
Slightly slow out, sentforward to race prominently early, 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back turning in, finished off evenly in straight.
Began awkwardly and bumped, raced at rear on rail, saved ground to 500M, no clear running early in straight,finished off evenly when clear thereafter.
Jumped well, positioned 2 lengths or so back on rail, savedground on turn, peakednear 300M, weakened thereafter.

Fast into stride, sent forward to take the lead, set a fast tempo, pressed by outside runner on turn, kept on well early in straight, headed near 200M, weakened gradually thereafter. (Lost left front plate.)
Jumped with them, positioned on rail behind midfield, there to turn, failed to close off in straight.
Bumped start and unbalanced, unable to slot in early, sent forward to race outside to the leader in 2nd thereafter, weakened gradually after turning in, finished last.
Quickly into stride, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well throughout, kicked clear after turning in, easily scored.
Began well, raced 2 lengths behind the leader, found rail near 900M, saved ground on turn, closed off well to take 2nd without threatening the winner.
Began awkwardly,raced 5 lengths back on rail, crowded and unbalanced near 900M, same margin back on turn, kept to inside after straightening, finished off well take 3rd.
Jumped well, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide from 900M, 3rd on turn, kept on evenly to the line. (Dropped right rein near 200M.)
Began fairly, raced 2 wide at rear, 6 to 7 lengths back, taken wide in straight and made some headway without threatening.
Away with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, finished off evenly.
Began well from gate 9, trapped wide early, sent forward after passing 1100M to sit outside to the leader, same position on turn, showed no response early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Moderately away from a wide draw, raced 3 wide in midfield, no cover after passing 900M, 5 lengths back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Raced at tail throughout, never competitive.
Average to begin, raced at rear on rail, still 7 lengths back on turn, showed no response early in straight, eased final 300M. (Irregular heart rhythm.) (Roarer.)
Raced in one-off one-back position, sat 1-3/4L off the lead, ran on and held off challenge to score by 1/2L.
Taken back, settled in behind midfield, 5-3/4L off 2 wide, continued on nicely and pushed the winner to the line.
Urged forward to share lead in a 2 wide position, continued on well to the line to take 3rd.
In behind midfield before dropping to the rear, 7-1/4L behind 2 wide, made nice ground and continued on strongly.
Rolled into position in about midfield, 3-3/4L behind 2 wide, did not improve but kept on going to the line.
Awkward start and lost ground, at the rear 7L behind along the rail, travelled keenly, made ground and closed off fairly.
Travelled in just behind midfield, 4-1/2L behind along the rail, improved slightly only.
Eased then slotted into midfield, wide and without cover, crowded at 400M, showed no turn of foot.
Sent forward to take the rail and led, headed passing 300 and weakened out gradually.
Settled in worse than midfield, 3 wide with cover, out of steam at 200M.
Urged forward, settled box-seat, flattened near 250M.

Began well from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, 2-1/2L back on turn, angled out early in straight, finished off strongly despite being bumped near 150M, scored by 3/4L. (Jockey dropped whip 100M.)
Jumped well, positioned 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, 2 wide on turn, still a length behind, hit the front near 200M but headed shortly thereafter, finished 2nd.

Moderately away from a tricky gate, unable to slot in, trapped very wide early, raced 3 wide, a length back in 3rd, no cover after passing 1000M, challenged the leader on turn, kept on well in straight to take a place.

Jumped with them, sent forward to race prominently but wide, took the lead after entering the back straight, challenged on turn, kept on well early in straight, headed after passing 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 3 wide with cover after 1000M, 3 lengths or so back on turn, made some progress in straight without threatening.
Taken back from gate 13, raced 3 wide at rear, 5 lengths or so back on turn, made some headway in straight without threatening.
Shifted out at start and bumped, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, got cover after passing 1000M, challenged the leader on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final 200M.

Bumped start and unbalanced, sent forward to take the early lead, headed after entering the back straight, positioned a length behind the leader on rail thereafter, only showed limited response in straight.
Hampered shortly after start, raced 2 wide at rear, moved closer on turn, 3 lengths or so back, finished off one-paced in straight. (Lost right front plate.)
Taken back from the widest draw, raced 6 to 7 lengths back at rear, same margin back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Began well from gate 11, raced 3 wide with cover, 2 lengths or so back, hard ridden turning in, showed no response, weakened gradually in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Moderately away, raced 2 wide, better than midfield, 3 wide on turn, weakened gradually in straight.
Taken back from a wide barrier, raced at rear, 5 to 6 lengths back, peaked on turn, emptied early in straight, finished tailed out.
Taken back from a wide draw, detached from the field throughout, never in the picture. (See Racing Incidents.)
Chased the pace, always in touch, moved up to challenge 300M and vied for the lead all the way to the line. Just prevailed.
Pressed forward to sit outside leader, took over 300M, went neck to neck with eventual winner all the way to the line, just held at the finish and well clear from remainders. Promising debut.
Away well, led evenly, lost lead 300M, battled on to hold 3rd.
Tracked leaders along the fence, switched out to center of track passing 350M, ran on moderately to line just failed to get up for 3rd.
Reserved near last early stages, raced keenly after 800M and commenced to lay out making home turn very wide, battled on same pace in the run home after difficult trip. (Unacceptable racing manners.)
Eased back to race near the rear, 5Ls off leader home turn, brought widest, stayed on moderately under mainly hands and heels riding. (Jockey and Trainer questioned.)
Settled down behind midfield 4Ls off the pace, stayed on fairly on straightening, checked close home.
Held up midfield along the inside, switched away from fence 500M, ran on one paced to the line.
From draw 11 raced wide without cover in midfield, couldn't finish off in the straight.
Began awkwardly and lost ground, raced near rear 4-5Ls off the pace, stayed on fairly in the straight, no threat.
Dropped back to last about 6Ls off leader, never got going in the straight, no impression.
Bumped start and unbalanced, raced 2 wide at rear, steadied off heels near 1000M, 4 to 5 lengths back on turn, taken wide early in straight, finished off very strongly to score.
Jumped with them, positioned 2 wide, 3 lengths or so back, awkwardly placed near 700M then shifted out off heels 600M, slightly improved thereafter, finished off well to take 2nd.
Began well from gate 1, positioned on rail behind midfield, saved ground on turn, made good progress in straight to take a place.
Jumped well from the widest draw, showed early speed to take the lead, travelled well throughout, kept on well in straight, just couldn't hold off the first few late.

Began well, sent forward to race in 3rd, 2 wide, awkwardly placed near 700M, angled out 500M, showed good response early in straight, peaked near 150M, kept on evenly to the line. (See Racing Incidents.)
Away with them, raced 3 wide behind midfield, 3 to 4 lengths back on turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Jumped with them, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after straightening, finished off evenly.
Slightly slow out, positioned on rail at rear, 6 to 7 lengths back, unbalanced near 700M, same position on turn, just passed some beaten horses in straight.
Fast into stride, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide from 900M, 2nd on turn, weakened early in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, bumped near 1000M, awkwardly placed near 700M, 6 lengths or so back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Bumped start and unbalanced, recovered to race 2 wide in midfield, 3 lengths or so back on turn, weakened early in straight and eased.
Jumped with them, taken back to race 3 wide with cover at rear, 5 to 6 lengths back on turn, emptied early in straight and eased.

Eased out early to settle worse than midfield. Became unsettled and was checked off heels 900m. Bumped when coming out at 500m. Steady early in the straight before kicking from 200m. Peaked late, but just held on.
Dropped back early to sit a clear last. Still last, and widest in the straight at 300m. Showed huge turn of foot from 200m and was making good ground on winner, but just ran out of time.
Kicked clear early to lead. Stayed on solidly in the straight, but slightly 1 paced. Couldn't match the kick of the first two, but clear 3rd late.
Broke well, before easing back to settle midfield. Ran well in the pack early in the straight. Came off heels to keep improving 150m and solid to the line late.
Dropped back from the wide draw to sit at the rear of the field. Inconvenienced at 900m. Last turning for home. Came to the inside rail and stayed on solidly late.
Began awkwardly, but managed to get to midfield, stuck 3 wide no cover. Plugged away solidly without threatening in the straight.
Pressed forward early to settle 2nd, on the leaders flank. Stuck his nose in front at 200m, but peaked soon after and dropped back quickly.
Cruised forward early to settle around midfield. Plugged away in the straight without threatening. Vet- Lame in off fore leg.
Bumped on jumping, before dropping back to sit towards the rear of the field. Bumped 500m. Came off heels 200m, but no threat in the straight. Vet- Lame off fore leg.
Taken up early to settle 3rd, on the fence. 1 paced early in the straight, before fading late.
Cruised out early to settle around midfield. 1 paced in the straight.
Not used too hard early to settle 4th, 1 off the fence. Loomed at 300m, but was a spent forced by 200m and dropped out quickly.
Slowly away and sat worse than midfield. Slightly closer when bumped and took turn awkwardly at 900m. Didn't run on in the straight. Vet-mucus in trachea.
Chased leaders 2-wide, quickened up to hit front jointly inside 200M, hard pressed to the wire and just prevailed in a photo finish.
Crossed to the rail 1000M sharing the lead at steady tempo, in a constant battle to lead entering straight, fought tenaciously to line only going down narrowly.
Settled down midfield 3-4Ls back, picked up well on straightening, brushed with rival a few times, kept finding to the line, got up late for 3rd.
From wide draw went forward to race outside leader, kept on well in straight, match strides with leaders until late stages, edged out to 4th in a photo.
Up with early pace, sat back to race ahead of midfield 3Ls away, ran on well in the straight despite bumping a few times with rival. Nearest finish, just missed the frame.
Within striking distance always, on the leaders back straightening, tried hard but held in the run home.
Eased back to race near last 8Ls off the pace, worked wide from 300M, surged late to be nearest at the finish.
Dropped back from wide draw, raced behind midfield along the 3-path, swung wide into straight, chased steadily without seriously threatening.
Began awkwardly, held up mid-division, couldn't find the necessary kick, plodded home.
Steadied to obtain cover, ended up in last, well off the pace straightening, failed to muster sufficient speed, made minor headway only.
Restrained in midfield, couldn't finish off in the straight, never in it.
Slow to begin, always towards rear, didn't let down passing 400M, never a factor. (Roarer / Mucus.)
Taken back from wide draw, settled down 11th, 5Ls off 400M but severely checked behind a weakening rival early straight, didn't run on when clear.
Bustled along to be chasing leaders along the 3-path, had no cover throughout, gave ground abruptly upon straightening, finished tailed off.
