Settled one back on the rail, became gradually shuffled backward to midfield by 800 metres, switched to challenge entering straight, fought on well to hit the front 100 metres out.

Shared early pace, took up running briefly passing winning post the first time, ceded lead for one back position on the rail over 1000 metres out, fought on under pressure but unable to peg back the winner.
Failed to muster despite early reminders, settled towards the rear, plugged on under pressure.
Settled at the back, quickened up in back straight to join the leaders approaching the Rock, weakened inside final 200 meters.
Prominent, held narrow advantage into the straight, faded under pressure inside final 150 metres.
Soon taken across for rails run from a wide draw, gradually dropped towards the rear on the far side, saved ground turning in, kept on steadily without quickening.
Dipped at start, settled in midfield, slightly worse when hampered 500 metres out, found nothing under pressure.
Pressed forward from a wide draw, took up running from the 1100 metres, led until headed into home straight, soon weakened.
Settled in last few near the rails from a wide draw racing wide most of the way, made no impression under pressure.
Ridden early before settling just off the pace, dropped to forward of midfield rounding stables bend, found nothing in straight.
Travelled wide in midfield or slightly worse, swung widest turning in, made no impression in home straight.
Vied for lead early from the widest draw, travelled wide without cover in better than midfield, dropped out from approaching home turn.
Pushed to sit in midfield, 2 wide, pace good, made early move 600M, closed off strongly to score by a narrow margin.
Hard ridden to take rail and led at good pace, under pressure from 500M, ran on strongly, just missed by a narrow margin.
Pushed to occupy box seat, pace good, held ground for 3rd.
Hard ridden to hold the rail in front of midfield, pace good, progressed steadily 250M.
Bumped start, pushed to take a midfield spot, pace good, made ground 200M.
Bumped start, at rear, 2 wide, pace good, made minor ground 200M.
Slow away, at rear along the fence, pace good, on heels 350M, ran on fairly.
Pressed forward, trapped 3 wide early, pace good, out of fuel 300M.
Pushed early but not muster, trapped 2-4 wide, pace good, no dash.
Pushed early, midfield, trapped 2-3 wide, pace good, no progress.
Never competitive.
Hard ridden forward, pace good, 2-3 wide, emptied 450M.
Urged and showed good early speed to take lead, responded nicely in the straight and finished unchallenged.
Taken back at start and raced at tail on rail, made up some nice ground, worked home solidly.
Began only fairly, settled behind midfield, gained ground passing 150M, came home nicely.
Fast out, raced midfield, responded well in the straight.
Ridden along to sit box seat, fought hard entire straight, gave some ground passing final 50M.
Travelled behind midfield on rail, kept on rail at Home Turn, ran on in the straight, finished OK.
Began only fairly, settled midfield, made some ground final 100M.
Began only fairly then taken back, under pressure but only one-paced in the straight.
Raced midfield on rail, battled hard entire straight, limited response in the straight.
Ridden for some distance after start to race behind the lead, weakened passing 200M, failed to run on.
Travelled behind midfield, widest on straightening, no response.
Stumbled at start, travelled wide and without cover in midfield, never in it.
Clean jump, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, finished off very strongly in straight to score.
Average to begin, positioned 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, 2 wide on turn, finished off well in straight to take 2nd, posed no threat to the winner.
Clean jump, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, took the rail 600M, easy lead on turn, headed near 200M, weakened thereafter, just stayed on for 3rd.
Began awkwardly, raced at rear on rail, 7 lengths back, same margin back on turn, made reasonable progress in straight to make frame. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back from gate 9, raced 6 lengths back on rail, saved ground on turn, finished off evenly.
Jumped well from gate 1, raced prominently, allowed rival to cross near 600M, 2nd on turn, found no extra gear in straight, finished off one-paced.
Began well, positioned in 3rd, 2-1/2L back on turn, hard ridden after passing 400M, peaked early in straight, kept on evenly to the line.
Jumped with them, positioned 2 wide in midfield, carried wider on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Moderately away from a wide draw, raced wide and without cover behind midfield, 5 lengths or so back on turn, finished off one-paced in straight.
Taken back to race 2 wide at rear, 6 to 7 lengths back, 3 wide on turn, taken widest in straight, failed to make any progress. (Jockey dropped whip 100M.)
Jumped well from the widest draw, taken back to race at tail, well back on turn, made no impression in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Average to begin, bumped early, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 6 lengths back on turn, failed to close off in straight, finished last.
Bumped start, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after straightening and finished off strongly to score by neck.
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned 2 to 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, easy run to turn, finished off very well, just couldn't hold off the winner late.
Clean jump, raced 2 wide in midfield, 4 lengths back on turn, finished off well to take a place.
Stumbled start and bumped, raced at rear, 5 to 6 lengths back on rail, same margin back on turn, made very good progress in straight to make frame, nearest on line.
Moderately away from the widest draw, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length, easy lead on turn, kept on well early in straight, headed and weakened after passing 100M.
Clean jump, raced 2 wide at rear, 6-1/2L back, same margin back on turn, made some progress in straight without threatening.
Average to begin, sent forward to race in 2nd, sat a length behind the leader, easy run on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Jumped with them, raced 3 wide behind midfield, 5 lengths or so back, very wide turning in, finished off evenly in straight.
Out in line, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 5 lengths or so back, angled out near 450M, very wide turning in, failed to quicken under pressure in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, 7 lengths or so back, still well back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Taken back from gate 9, raced wide with cover at rear, 7 lengths back, there to turn, made no progress in straight.
Shifted out on jumping and bumped, raced 3 wide with no cover until near 700M, 3 lengths back, peaked on turn, emptied early in straight, eased final 100M. (Lost right front plate.)
Ridden along early stages, no speed and settled towards rear, hard ridden to improve from 600m, still at rear on straightening, balanced up at 250m and made powerful run to win comfortably.
Taken back early to settle at rear, commenced to improve around runners at 600m, wide on straightening and finished strongly.
Ridden along early to hold midfield position on rail, travelling well approaching home turn, challenged strongly at 200m, swamped final 50m
Settled towards rear on rail, in need of run home turn, kept to inside and made steady ground to the finish.
Pushed along early to find lead, controlled tempo midrace, quickened nicely on straightening but overpowered final 100m
Settled worse than midfield on rail, travelling well home turn, kept to inside and made steady ground in straight.
Ridden along early to settle leaders back, one paced in straight.
Jumped well and settled in forward position, ridden along 450m but unable to quicken and gave ground in straight.
Unable to hold position early stages and settled towards rear, did not run on
Settled midfield, hampered 450m and 200m, did not run on.
Ridden along early from wide gate to settle outside leader, under pressure home turn and gave ground in straight. Vet: Irregular heart rhythm  must trial
Settled forward of midfield wide without cover, commence to give ground from 450m.
Jumped well from gate 1, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well throughout, kicked clear early in straight, easily scored.
Bumped on jumping, positioned 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, same position on turn, angled out early in straight, finished off strongly to take 2nd.
Bumped start, sat 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, easy run to turn, kept on well in straight to take a place.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide, 4 lengths or so back, same position on turn, angled out 400M, made very good progress in straight to be nearest on line.
Began well, positioned 2 wide, 3 lengths back, there to turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Clean jump, taken back to race 2 wide at rear, 6 lengths or so back, there to turn, no clear running early in straight, made minor progress when clear thereafter.
Out in line, showed no early speed, raced at rear, 6 lengths back, same margin back on turn, finished off evenly in straight. (Lost left front plate after the race.)
Bumped start, raced at tail, 7 to 8 lengths back, still last turning in, made some headway in straight without threatening.
Bumped start, raced at rear, 7 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, taken widest in straight and made minor progress.
Away with them, sent forward to race in 2nd, 2 wide, 3/4L back, same position on turn, weakened gradually in straight.
Began well from a tricky gate, raced in 3rd, no cover until near 600M, 2 lengths back on turn, weakened gradually in straight.
Jumped well from the widest draw, raced wide in midfield, 5 lengths back on turn, weakened early in straight when hard run took effect.
Held up in mid-division, 3Ls away at 400M, worked through his gears well, led inside 100M drawing away for consecutive win.
Had a ground saving trip from draw 1, settled ahead of midfield, loomed large behind leader 200M, bumped by rival 150M, fought on well to line but couldn't hold off winner final stages.
Assumed running in mid-division, niggled along 500M, kept working to the line and got up late for 3rd.
Up with pace along the rail, quickened to clear lead 300M, lay out under pressure in straight, caught by rivals 100M and yielded ground from there.
Quickly into stride, tracked leaders in 4th, swung wide into straight, chased steadily to the line but unable to get closer.
From draw 12 steadied shortly after the start to obtain cover, raced in last 7Ls back, made limited progress on straightening.
Shared the lead along the 2-path, ridden along home turn and stayed on same pace on straightening, out of contention passing 150M.
Dropped back from wide draw for cover, in 10th spot 6Ls away making the home turn, plodded past fading runners in the straight.
Chased leaders along the 3-path, made home turn awkwardly, widest on straightening, kept on fairly to the line.
Settled down behind midfield 4-5L behind leaders, couldn't get closer in the straight, eased when no chance 100M.
Dropped back to near the rear 7Ls off the pace, couldn't go on in the straight, never threatened.
From wide draw pressed forward, unable to cross, caught 3-wide outside the lead, gave ground turning in, weakened to last.

Well there, gained upper hand under pressure close to home.
Always thereabouts, fought on dourly, just failed to peg back the winner. (Rider lost whip 250 metres out)
Shared the pace most of the way, hit the front under pressure inside the 200 metres, just headed near finish.
Moderate start, soon came to join the leaders hitting the front momentarily over 500 metres out, unable to sustain effort inside the final 100 metres.
Ridden along but gradually picked up to about 2L off the pace near the centre of the track, made no further impression closing stages.
Broke well, settled just off the pace on stands rail, one-paced under pressure 300 metres out.
Soon dropped behind midfield, gradually shifted in towards the centre of the track for a run, ran home one-paced.
Travelled just off the pace, gradually faded under pressure inside the 400 metres.
Soon detached from the main body of the field in last few, never a factor.
Soon dropped back, never a factor.
Soon dropped to tail-end, never seen with a chance.
Hard ridden to hold the rail and lead, ran on well to score but only by a narrow margin.
Hard ridden early, 1 out 1 back, made early move 500M, closed off strongly, just missed by a narrow margin.
Hard ridden forward, sat 2 wide, held ground for 3rd.
Eased back, sat 2 wide, dashed strongly 250M.
Bumped start, hard ridden to keep up with the speed along the rails, out of fuel 200M.
Hard ridden to keep up in midfield, trapped 3-4 wide, little dash in straight.
Eased back, raced 4-5 wide, no dash.
Slow away, hard ridden at rear along the fence, no dash.
Hard ridden early but not muster, trapped 3-4 wide at back, no progress.
Hard ridden to keep up in midfield, 2-3 wide, never improved.
Hard ridden forward, trapped 3 wide, soon emptied 400M.
Eased back, never a factor.
Ridden along to take lead, responded strongly in the straight, scored unchallenged.
Urged to settle box seat, fought nicely in the straight, finished solidly to get 2nd.
Raced at handy position, asked for effort on straightening, made up some nice late ground.
Ridden along to race outside the lead, responded well in the early part of straight, gave some ground passing 100M.
Ridden along after start, settled midfield on rail, near 800m was checked away from heels, kept on rail at Home Turn, one-paced.
Throughout the race travelled wide and without cover outside the leaders, gradually gave ground in the straight when under pressure.
Slow on jumping, raced midfield, passing 800M was checked away from heels, wide on straightening, limited response in the straight.
At the start was crowded for room then failed to muster speed despite being ridden along, after 800M travelled wide and without cover, widest on straightening, limited response.
Began awkwardly then raced at back on rail, no response in the straight.
Taken back at start, raced at tail, never in it.
Slow to begin, always back, blood trachea.
Crowded on jumping, raced behind midfield, always niggled, never in it.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, there to turn, finished off very strongly to score narrowly. (Lost left front plate near 100M.)
Bumped start, positioned 4 lengths or so back on rail, saved ground on turn, no daylight early in straight, finished off strongly when clear thereafter, just beaten narrowly.
Bumped start, sat a length behind the leader on rail, easy run throughout, kept on very well in straight to take a place.

Bounded in air at the start and unbalanced rider, raced at tail, 4 to 5 lengths back on turn, angled out early in straight but got traffic, made some progress when clear thereafter to make frame, no threat to the first few.
Jumped well from a tricky draw, sent forward to take the lead, challenged by rivals on turn, kept on well early in straight, headed after passing 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Began well from the widest gate, trapped very wide early, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield after 900M, 3 lengths back on turn, bumped and unbalanced near 250M, one-paced to the line.
Fast into stride, sent forward to race outside to the leader, there to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Shifted in at start and bumped, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after straightening, finished off one-paced.
Began fairly, raced 2 wide, 3 lengths back, same margin back on turn, finished off one-paced in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide at rear, 5 lengths back, same margin back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Bumped on jumping, raced prominently, 3 wide, there to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Away with them, raced 3 wide with cover, 2 lengths back, similar position on turn, bumped early in straight, hampered near 250M, eased thereafter. (Blood in trachea.)
Out in line, positioned 2 wide, 1 to 2 lengths back, there to turn, bumped early in straight, crowded and steadied near 250M, eased thereafter. (Mucus in trachea.)
Jumped well, raced 2 wide in midfield, travelled keenly and awkwardly placed near 700M, 2 to 3 lengths back on turn, finished off strongly in straight to score.

Began well from a wide draw, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, challenged the leader on turn, took the lead early in straight, kept on well thereafter, but couldn't hold off the winner final 150M, stayed on for 2nd.
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, angled out early in straight, finished off very strongly to be nearest on line.
Slowly away, positioned on rail behind midfield, 4 lengths or so back, saved ground on turn, angled out in straight and made good progress to make frame.
Average to begin, sat 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, easy run on turn, no daylight until near 150M, finished off evenly thereafter.
Began well, raced 2 wide, 2 lengths back, same position on turn, kept on evenly to near 100M, weakened thereafter.
Slightly slow out, raced 2 wide at rear, raced tight near 650M, 3 wide turning in, finished off evenly. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began awkwardly, raced 3wide with no cover in midfield, moved closer on turn, peaked early in straight, slightly weakened thereafter.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, moved closer from 700M, 5 lengths back turning in, finished off evenly in straight.
Jumped well, sent forward to take the lead, challenged by rival on turn, headed early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Crowded on jumping, raced at rear on rail, 6 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Taken back from gate 12, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, raced tight near 650M, 4 wide turning in, emptied early in straight.
Crowded start, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, 3 to 4 lengths back on turn, emptied early in straight.
Urged and settled in front of midfield, about 1-1/2L off 3 wide and without cover, continued on nicely to score by 1L.
Inconvenienced at start, then pushed to be outside the lead, kept on well but couldn't catch the winner.
Awkward start and lost ground, recovered to be in midfield, about 3L behind 2 wide, kept on well to the finish.
Blundered at start before settling in midfield, about 3L behind 3 wide but with cover, continued on fairly.
Bumped start, raced towards the rear, 3-3/4L behind 2 wide, made ground and ran on the line.
Rolled forward to race in the box-seat, sat about 1-1/2L off, kept on one paced to the line.
Bumped start, then sent forward to take rail and led by about a neck, headed prior to 250M and then emptied.
Raced in one-off one-back position, about 1-1/2L off, couldn't sustain the challenge from about 150M.
At rear as its usual, 2-3 wide at turn, swung widest, only past tired runners.
In about midfield along the rail, found nothing and eased at about 150M.
Awkward start, asked but was towards the rear, wide and without cover, did not threaten.
Towards the rear along the rail, gave ground from 500M.
Crowded out start and unbalanced, recovered to race prominently near to the stands rail, travelled well throughout, took the lead near 100M, kept on strongly to the line and scored by a length.
Began smartly, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on the stands rail, improved from near 400M, finished off well to take 2nd.
Jumped well from gate 1, showed good speed to take the lead, near to the stands rail, headed after passing 150M, slightly weakened thereafter, stayed on for 3rd.
Moderately away, raced behind lead, 2 away from the stands rail, finished off evenly.
Bumped start, raced in midfield close to the stands rail, 2 to 3 lengths back, finished off evenly.
Bumped start, raced prominently in the middle of the track, peaked near 200M, slightly weakened thereafter.
Shifted out at start and bumped, raced in the middle of the track, 2 lengths or so back, kept on evenly to the line.
Began fairly from gate 12, showed no early speed, raced 4 to 5 lengths back at rear on rail, showed limited response final 400M.
Away with them, raced at rear, nearer to the middle of the track, made no impression final 400M.
Average to begin, raced behind midfield, closer to the middle of the track, showed no response to vigorous riding final 400M.
Shifted out at start and bumped, raced in the middle of the track, 3 lengths back, weakened gradually final 400M, eased after passing 150M.
Settled down ahead of midfield in a fast run race, never far off from leaders, quickened up well to lead near 200M, was strongly challenged late but held on well winning in class record time.
Jumped well to be racing in close 4th, held up turning in and no clear run until 250M, chased strongly when clear, just failed to reel in winner.
Held up 2-wide in mid-division, travelled keenly 1300M, kept responding to riding in straight, stayed on into 3rd late but not reached first 2.
Restrained in midfield early stages, no cover from 1200M strolled forward to join leader, took over straightening, kept battling after losing lead near 200M, edged out to 4th near line.
Eased back to a rearward spot after the start switched wide 500M, ran on mildly and lacked the winning ash.
Held up behind midfield, travelled keenly 1300M, 4Ls behind leaders home turn, had no clear run 300M-200M, kept plugging away final 150M. Awkwardly placed close home could have done better.
Went forward, vied for lead at fast pace along the fence, battled on at same pace entering straight, faded away final 150M.
Eased back after the start to be racing near the rear, 5Ls off the pace 400M, unable to quicken sufficiently, difficult obtain running passing 200M, stayed on without threat closing stages.
Dropped back from wide draw, 7Ls off the pace in last, brought wide in the straight but couldn't finish off.
Pressed forward to be tracking the pace, couldn't quicken turning in, began to feel the pinch 250M, weakened away to last. (Jockey : travelled keener than it had been in previous races.)
Clean jump, sent forward to take the lead, travelled comfortably throughout, kickedclear after turning in,easily scored.
Jumped well, positioned 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, easy run throughout, kept on very well instraight to take 2nd, nothreat to the winner.
Taken back from gate 9, raced 2 wide at rear, 4 to 5 lengths back on turn, made some progress instraight to take a place.
Checked at start, positioned 4 to 5 lengths back on rail, saved ground onturn, kept on evenly in straight to make frame.
Slightly slow out,positioned on rail in midfield, 3 lengths back, there to turn,lacked turn of foot but kept grinding away in run to line.
Taken back from a wide barrier, raced at rear on rail, still 5 lengths or so back on turn, kept to inside afterstraightening, only showed limited response.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide in midfield, wider from 550M, finished off evenly in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, still 7 to 8 lengths back on turn,passed a fewtired runners in straight.
Shifted out at start and bumped, raced 2 wide at rear, 6 lengths back on turn, finished off one-paced in straight.
Bumped start, unable to slot in, raced 3 wide, 4 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Began fairly, raced 2 wide better than midfield,angled out near 550M, peakedearly in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Average to begin, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, 6 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, taken widest in straight, failed to make any progress.
Jumped well from a wide draw,unable to slot in early, sent forward thereafter to race in 2nd, 2 wide, peaked on turn, emptied early in straight, eased after passing 300M, finished tailed out.
Pressed out early from the wide draw to assume the early lead, before easing the tempo at 900m. Looked to be fading at 200m, but found a second wind and cruised to the line late.
Taken forward early to be handily placed in 4th. Loomed up from 300m. Couldn't match winner when he kicked again at 150m, but had no threats for 2nd.
Pressed forward early to sit 2nd/3rd, 1 off the fence. Solid in the straight, but 1 paced late and was being chased down for 3rd.
Settled worse than midfield, 3 wide with no cover. Well placed on the turn. Ran on well in the straight and was quickly running down 3rd late.
Cruised forward early and settled around midfield. Came around heels 350m. Had whip knocked out at 150m, but still stayed on solidly late.
Eased out early to settle worse than midfield. Raced tight 650m. Wider in the straight. Stayed on solidly, but never threatened. Jockey questioned.
Not pressed early, and settled at the rear of the field. Plugged away steadily without ever threatening.
Dropped back from the wide draw to settle towards the rear of the field. Raced tight 650m, and came wide soon after to improve. Plugged away steadily without ever threatening.
Eased out to settle around midfield. Never responded to pressure in the straight.
Slowly away, then crowded on jumping before settling in midfield. Keen early/mid and was checked off heels at 700m. 1 paced in the straight and was eased out late.
Dropped back early to sit at the tail of the field. 1 paced in the straight and only picked up a couple of slower ones late.
Dropped back from the wide draw to share last place. Came widest in the straight, but made no inroads.
Cruised out early to settle towards the rear of the field. Keen from 1000m and checked off heels. Had nothing left in the straight and was eased from 100m.
Began awkwardly, but pushed forward to settle 2nd/3rd, on the fence. Never responded to riding in the straight and dropped out quickly.

Broke well settling mainly over 2L back in 4th on the rail, responded well after straightening to take charge 100 metres out.
Broke well, settled in rear of midfield in 7th, made swift progression passing the 1100 metres to lead on the rail 800 metres out, unable to sustain effort and headed 100 metres out.
Settled in last few, raced wide without cover in back straight, gained closer under pressure out wide rounding home bend, fought on steadily without threatening.
Settled towards the rear on the rail, took closer order 1100 metres out gaining one back position rounding home bend, unable to sustain effort after straightening.
Settled at the back, commenced move at the 1000 metres, fought on under pressure from 8th into straight to be nearest at finish.
Settled in last few, produced good late impression in the run up to the line.
Well there on the rail, held slender advantage throughout back straight, headed coming onto home bend, folded up quickly after straightening.
Settled in midfield or slightly worse on the rail, angled out for a run turning in, found nothing.
Settled wide in midfield after beginning from a wide gate, lost position passing the 1000 metres and dropped further backward to last place after steadied 600 metres out, never recovered.
Restrained to just off the pace in 3rd, came under pressure to hold place approaching home bend, dropped out from 2L 5th into the straight.
Vied for lead from the widest draw, settled outside the leader in 2nd in back straight, yielded ground steadily from half-way out. (Irregular heart beat) (Lame next day)
Eased back, benefited by the fast tempo, progressed steadily 400M to score.
At back, 2-3 wide, favoured by the fast pace, lack room 400M, progressed steadily when clear, just missed by a narrow margin.
Eased back, took rail, benefited by the fast tempo, lack room 4-2, made steady ground when clear.
Pushed to take rail and led at fast pace, hung on strongly until 50M overhauled.
At rear, 2-4 wide, benefited by the fast pace, progressed steadily 250M.
Hard ridden to hold the rail at back, benefited by the fast pace, lack room 400M, made some ground when clear.
Eased back, trapped 3-4 wide, suited by the fast pace, made ground 400M, run ended 100M.
Pushed forward, trapped 3 wide, harmed by the fast tempo, weakened 250M.
Hard ridden early but not muster, in front of midfield, 2 wide, no dash.
At back, 2 wide, favoured by the fast pace, lack room 4-2, held ground when clear.
Hard ridden forward, sat 2 wide, harmed by the fast pace, out of fuel 200M.
Hard ridden to keep up in midfield, trapped 3-4 wide, weakened 300M.
Hard ridden to obtain box seat, not suited by the fast tempo, soon emptied 400M.
Jumped well, allowed to settle midfield, improved wide with cover at 1200m, continued forward move at 800m when traveling strongly, took lead on straightening and was too strong final 200m.
Settled and rear and traveled nicely throughout, commenced strong run from 400m but winner too good.
Settled towards the rear, commenced to improve around runners making home turn and ran home okay.
Settled midfield on rail, followed leader into straight, rails run and finished off one paced.
Settled on pace 3 wide without cover, tried hard to issue challenge on straightening but one paced to line. Ride questioned.
Settled behind leaders in midfield position, ridden along home turn but could only finish off one paced.
Ridden along early to settle outside leader, pushed along home turn, gradually gave ground in straight.
Settled in front, quickly under pressure on straightening and gave ground.
Fast into stride, sent forward to take the lead, enjoyed the easy lead throughout, kicked clear early in straight, easily scored.
Away with them, bumped early, raced wide with no cover in 3rd, 2 lengths back on turn, kept on well in straight to take 2nd without threatening the winner.
Jumped well from gate 1, positioned 1 to 2 lengths back on rail, saved ground on turn, awkwardly placed near 400M, kept on evenly in straight to take a place.
Slightly slow out, raced 2 wide in midfield, angled out near 450M, brushed early in straight, made good progress thereafter to make frame.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide better than midfield, similar position on turn, finished off evenly.
Began only fairly, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, finished off evenly in straight,
Began awkwardly and bumped, raced at rear on rail, 5 lengths or so back, there to turn, made minor progress in straight.
Began well from a wide draw, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, travelled well to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Jumped with them, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, 5 lengths back on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter, eased late.
Taken back from gate 9, raced wide at rear throughout, never a threat.
Jumped well from the widest draw, showed no early speed, raced at tail, still 9 lengths back at 400M, failed to make any progress in straight.
Out in line, raced 2 wide at rear, peaked on turn, failed to close off in straight, eased late.
Away with them, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 4 lengths or so back, closer on turn, finished off very strongly in straight to score.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 lengths back, there to turn, angled out from 500M, made very good progress in straight to take 2nd.
Fast into stride, took the lead easily, travelled well throughout, kicked clear early in straight, peaked and headed near 150M, stayed on for 3rd.
Began awkwardly, recovered to race 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground to 600M, 2 to 3 wide turning in, finished off evenly in straight to make frame.
Began well from the widest draw, unable to slot in early, taken back to race 3 wide with cover at rear, 5 lengths or so back, taken wide in straight and made some headway without threatening.
Bumped start, raced 3 wide with no cover, 2 lengths back, got cover on turn, made some progress early in straight, one-paced in the final furlong.
Began fairly, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after straightening, finished off evenly.
Jumped with them, raced prominently, 2 wide, there to turn, peaked early in straight, slightly weakened thereafter.
Crowded on jumping, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, there to turn, taken wide in straight, finished off one-paced.
Crowded out start, raced at rear, 5 lengths or so back on rail, saved ground on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, 6 to 7 lengths back, there to turn, made no progress in straight.
Taken back to race 2 wide at rear, 5 to 6 lengths back, there to turn, failed to close off in straight.
Bumped start, unable to slot in early, trapped very wide with no cover, 2 to 3 lengths back, sent forward near 1100M, 3 wide on turn, weakened early in straight.
Taken back to race at rear, 6 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
In midfield, 4-1/4L behind 2 wide, kept going and gradually pulled away inside final 100M, scored by 1-3/4L.
Slotted in to be just behind midfield, 5-1/2L behind 2 wide, closed off strongly to beat the others to 2nd.
Asked to race in the box-seat, sat 2-1/4L off the lead, battled on nicely to hold off challenges for 3rd.
Sent forward to take rail and led by 1L, headed passing 100M, continued on well to the line nonetheless.
Pushed and raced in one-off one-back position, sat 2-3/4L off, kept on fairly.
Eased back and raced close to the rear, 7L behind and 2 wide throughout, saved good ground.
Allowed to be prominent, sat 2-1/4L off but wide and without cover, lost ground when hung in in the straight.
Settled to race in midfield along the rail, was one paced in the straight.
Raced at the rear along the rail, awkward to heels at 250M, showed no turn of foot nonetheless.
Raced in just behind midfield along the rail, did not improve.
Taken back to be at the rear, 2 wide throughout, never threatened.
Niggled to be outside the lead, weakened passing 350M.
Jumped well, raced in 2nd, travelled well throughout, hit the front near 200M, kept on strongly to score.
Taken back to race 2 wide behind midfield, moved closer on turn but still 4 to 5 lengths back, finished off very strongly in straight to take 2nd, nearest on line.
Began well, raced in midfield, 2 to 3 lengths back, easy run on turn, kept on well in straight to take a place.
Jumped well, raced in midfield, checked near 1200M, 3 lengths or so back on turn, made good progress in straight to be nearest on line, just missed 3rd.
Average to begin, raced at rear, 8 lengths back at 800M, improved along the rail on turn, made some progress in straight without threatening.
Moderately away, sent forward to take the lead, enjoyed the easy lead to turn, kept on well early in straight, headed near 200M, slightly weakened thereafter.
Began only fairly, raced at tail, 9 lengths back at 800M, moved closer on turn, made up some ground but set too great a task.
Away with them, raced 2 wide, 2 to 3 lengths back, travelled keenly after 1000M, awkward on turn, weakened early in straight, eased after passing 200M.
Away well to be tracking leader 2-wide, moved up and took over 500M, kicked clear 250M, dug deep late with strong determination late to hold off late challenge of runner-up.
From widest draw slotted into midfield spot along the 3-path, 3Ls to make up on leader 400M, finished off nicely in the straight, just couldn't reel in the winner.
Never far off form the pace, improved steadily passing 400M, kept chasing first 2 final 200M but held.
Held up behind midfield, waited with until 350M, stayed on to go 4th 50M out but not reaching top 3.
Chased leaders in 4th, had his chance turning home, kept grinding to the finish but couldn't match the finishing pace of top 3.
Caught wide no cover throughout, raced in midfield until halfway then crept closer to leaders, kept on evenly to the line, outpaced by leaders final 200M.
Pressed forward from wide draw, raced along the 3-path until crossing to the lead 700M, failed to respond when challenged by rival near top of straight, faded away mid-straight.
Began well, dropped back to race in midfield 4Ls back along the fence, stayed on only fairly in the straight, no threat to leaders.
Held up 2-wide in mid-division 4Ls away, fought on same pace turning in, weakened final 150M.
Crowded for room after the start, ended up 3-wide near the rear, couldn't finish off turning home, made no impression on debut.
Made the early running, relinquished the lead 900M, kept on same pace turning home, faded from 250M.
Began only fairly then blundered after the jump, towards the rear always, under the pump 500M, didn't respond to pressure.
Taken across behind runners, held up in rear pair, 7Ls to make up 400M, didn't pick up when driven, never in the picture.
Eased back towards the rear, 6Ls off the pace home turn, couldn't come on leaving the bend, weakened to last.
Jumped with them, positioned on rail behind midfield, 5 lengths or so back, saved ground on turn, finished off very strongly in straight to score by a neck.

Average to begin, positioned 3 lengths behind the leader on the inside, same margin back on turn, angled out early in straight, took the lead near 250M, kept on very well but couldn't hold off the winner late.
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, easy run on turn, kept on well in straight to take 3rd.
Shifted out at start and bumped, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, 2 wide on turn, made some progress in straight to make frame without threatening the first few.
Jumped well from a tricky gate, showed no early speed, raced wide with cover at rear, 6 lengths back, 2 wide on turn, made some headway in straight without threatening.
Slowly away, raced at tail, 9 lengths back, still well back on turn, taken very wide in straight and made minor progress.
Clean jump from a wide draw, unable to slot in early, raced very wide behind midfield, found cover near 800M, 3 wide turning, finished off one-paced in straight.

Moderately away from a middle draw, raced 3 wide with no cover, 3 to 4 lengths back, similar position on turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened from final 200M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began fairly from a wide draw, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, 7 lengths or so back, same position on turn, failed to close off in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped well from the widest draw, sent forward to sit outside to the leader, shared lead from 800M, peaked early in straight, headed near 250M, dropped away tamely thereafter.
Bumped start, sent forward to take the lead, shared the lead with rival from 800M, emptied early in straight and dropped away tamely thereafter.
Began fairly, raced 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, there to turn, eased early in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Eased out early to settle midfield. Boxed in and slightly tight at 300m, but clear soon after. Got to the lead 150m, pulled away easily late and only eased in the last couple of strides.
Pressed forward early to settle 2nd, on the leaders flank. Pressed to lead at 300m. Easily taken at 150m. Stayed on solidly late to hold 2nd.
Taken forward early to be handily placed 4th/5th, but 3 wide. No cover from 900m. Stayed on solidly, but lacked turn of foot and went to the line 1 paced.
Pressed forward early to settle 3rd. Slightly tight at 300m and came around heels soon after. Solid run late, and was making slow ground on 3rd.
Taken up early to lead and crossed to fence 1100m. Headed at 300m, and battled to the line late without threatening.
Cruised forward early to be well placed 4th/5th on the rail. Never kicked in the straight. Came around heels 150m, but only ran to the line 1 paced.
Attempted to go forward early, but trapped 4-5 wide and dropped back to just forward of midfield. Stayed on OK early in the straight, but plugged away late.
Found a position forward of midfield, but unsettled and got head up at 1300m. Only fair in the straight and raced with his head to the side in close quarters before fading late.
Eased forward from the inside draw to find a position behind midfield. Plugged away 1 paced in the straight.
Eased back early to share last place. Plugged away steadily in the straight and was no threat.
Slowly away and dropped back to last. Didn't give much in the run home, and only picked up a couple of slower ones late.
Crowded and lost ground on jumping, before settling worse than midfield. Made no inroads in the straight.
Dropped back from the wide draw to settle at the rear of the field. Gave nothing in the straight.
Eased back from the wide draw to settle midfield. Never responded to pressure and dropped out quickly from 200m.

Broke well, held narrow lead early, taken 2L back for cover on the rail in 2L 4th coming onto stables bend, produced for a run on top of home bend, fought on well from 3L back into straight to just get up on line.

Niggled at early settling in last few, took off at the 900 metres and hit the front 600 metres out, kicked 3L clear entering home straight and looked certain, tiring when collared in the shadow of the post.
Broke well, gradually settled in midfield on the rail, made headway under pressure from around home bend, ran on to be nearest at finish.

Ridden along to hold midfield position early, dropped to last few turning into home straight the first time, given reminders home bend, circled the field and widest runner turning in, produced good late impression.
Prominent early, drifted back to midfield over half-way out, dropped to last at the Rock before making headway rounding home bend, fought on steadily without threatening in straight.

Ridden to join the leaders, taken 2L back in 3rd coming onto stables bend, shuffled further back on the far side dropping to last onto home bend, kept on steadily under pressure without threatening in home straight.
Settled well behind, commenced move approaching the Rock travelling 4 wide home bend, made no impression in the run home.
Ridden along from a wide gate before settling wide in midfield, came under pressure at the Rock and soon yielded ground.

Wide towards the rear early, circled the field rounding home bend the first time, took up running at the 1400M but narrowly headed when steadied pace 900M out, gradually faded under pressure from home bend. (Tactic questioned)
Settled at the back, made swift progress rounding stables bend to hit the front early in back straight, headed 600 metres out and gradually faded.
Well there to the 850 metres, folded up quickly. (Tactic questioned)
Midfield early stages, drifted back towards the rear approaching stables bend, made rapid progress out wide down back straight reaching 3rd briefly 900 metres out, soon weakened.
Hard ridden to hold the rail in midfield, suited by the fast tempo, progressed steadily 300M to score but only by a narrow margin.
Pushed to take rail and led at fast sectionals, hung on strongly until last few strides, just missed by a narrow margin.
Pressed forward, settled along the fence, ran on well to the line for 3rd.
Eased at start, took rail, benefited by the fast tempo, progressed steadily 250M.
Pushed forward, 2 wide, not suited by the fast pace, held ground in straight.
Hard ridden early, 2 wide in midfield, favoured by the fast pace, no progress in straight.
At back, 2 wide, benefited by the fast tempo, made some ground 200M.
Eased at start, took rail, benefited by the fast pace, made steady ground 200M.
At rear, raced 3 wide, favoured by the fast tempo, made ground 200M.
Hard ridden forward, trapped 2-3 wide, harmed by the fast pace, faded quickly 500M.
Eased back, hung in badly and checked, 2-3 wide, never a factor.
Hard ridden to share the lead at fast pace, soon emptied 400M.
Crowded at 950 before settling in midfield position, travelling nicely making home turn, kept to inside on straightening, powered home final 150m for comfortable win.
Fast out to lead easily, kicked nicely on straightening and only run down late.
Ridden along early to settle leaders back, ridden along home turn to issue challenge, kept working to the line.
Ridden along early before settling off the pace, peeled out to challenge on straightening and finished strongly.
Taken back at the start, ridden along to stay in touch near 600m, last on straightening and ran home strongly.
Crowded at 950m and then settled worse than midfield, hard ridden at 400m and then ran home well over the final 100m.
Settled on rail behind midfield before finishing off okay.
Raced wide without cover in forward position, stayed on one-paced in the straight.
Crowded and checked at 950m and settled towards the rear, kept to rail in the straight and ran home fairly.
Fast out and settled outside the lead, pushed along to challenge at the home turn, quickly under pressure and gradually weakened.
Ridden along early to settle off pace, failed to run on in the straight.
Taken back at the start and remained there throughout.
Jumped well, sent forward to take the lead, enjoyed the easy lead throughout, kept on well in straight to hold off the rival.
Away with them, raced 2 wide, 3 lengths back, same position to turn, finished off well to take 2nd.
Slowly away, recovered to race in midfield, on rail, improved from near 450M, made some progress in straight to take 3rd, no threat to the first two.
Began well from gate 9, positioned 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, easy run on turn, peaked early in straight, kept on evenly to the line.
Steadied start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 6 lengths back, slightly inconvenienced near 500M, 4 wide turning in, made some progress in straight.
Clean jump from gate 1, positioned 3 to 4 lengths back on rail, saved ground on turn, finished off evenly.
Average to begin, showed no early speed, raced 7 lengths back on rail, same position on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, 9 to 10 lengths back, still well back on turn, taken wide in straight and passed a few horses in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear, 8 to 9 lengths back, same positon on turn, made no real progress in straight.
Jumped well from barrier 11, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, 2 lengths back on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Jumped with them, raced 3 wide at rear early, 2 wide from 1150M, 7 to 8 lengths back, there to turn, failed to close off in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Out in line, raced 2 wide in midfield, peaked on turn, weakened early in straight.
Jumped well, raced 2 wide in midfield, improved from 450M, took the lead early in straight, kept on strongly to score by 3-1/4L.

Began well from gate 1, positioned 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground throughout, kept to inside after straightening, closed off well to take 2nd without posing any threat to the winner.
Moderately away, positioned 3 to 4 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground to 400M, made some progress in straight to take a place.
Jumped with them, sent forward to race in 2nd, 2 wide, challenged the leader on turn, peaked early in straight, kept on evenly to the line.
Away with them, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 4 lengths or so back, closer on turn, finished off one-paced in straight.
Taken back from gate 9, raced 5 to 6 lengths back on rail, 4 lengths back on turn, failed to quicken under pressure in straight.
Out in line, raced 3 wide with no cover behind midfield, there to turn, weakened early in straight when hard run took effect.
Clean jump, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, challenged by rival turning in, headed early in straight, dropped away thereafter.
Taken back to race at rear, 5 to 6 lengths back, still last turning in, showed nothing in straight.
Pushed and settled outside the lead, sat about 1/2L off, continued on nicely to score by1/2L. (Blood in trachea)
Sent forward to take the rail and led, kept on until headed by the winner passing 50M, just hung on for 2nd.
Urged before settling just in front of midfield, about 2-3/4Loff and 3 wide at 400M, continued on nicely to the line.
Travelled just in front of midfield along the rail, closed gap in the straight and ran on fairly to the line.
No speed to take the lead, raced prominently but 3 wide and without cover throughout, very much one paced.
Raced towards the rear 2 wide, 6L behind at 400M, saved ground and closed off well to the line.
Settled in behind midfield, 2 wide at turn, travelled keenly near 500M, made minor ground.
Pushed and settled in one-off one-back position, flattened passing 150M. (Blood in trachea)
Raced towards the rear, 2 wide throughout, saved no ground.
Settled just behind midfield, 3 wide at turn, never threatened.
Asked to be in the box-seat, gave ground approaching 150M. (Bled from both nostrils)
Always at the rear, never a factor.
Bumped start, raced at rear, 7 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, taken wide in straight and finished off very strongly to score.

Bumped on jumping, raced wide with cover in midfield, 4 lengths or so back on turn, made very good progress early in straight, took the lead after passing 150M, kept on well but couldn't hold off the winner late.
Began well from a middle draw, positioned 2 wide, a length behind the leader, similar position on turn, kept on evenly in straight.
Crowded start, positioned 4 to 5 lengths back in midfield, hampered near 850M, 2 wide on turn, made some headway in straight to make frame.

Crowded shortly after start, showed no early speed, detached from the main group in the early stages, still 9 to 10 lengths back on turn, taken wide in straight and made very good progress in straight to be nearest on line.
Jumped well, raced prominently on rail, a length behind the leader on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually after passing 150M.
Fast into stride, sent forward to take the lead, 2 wide, found rail on turn, weakened gradually in straight. (Lame right front leg next day morning.)
Began awkwardly and lost ground, raced behind midfield, 6 to 7 lengths back, 3 wide with cover on turn, made no progress in straight.

Jumped with them, bumped and unbalanced early, positioned better than midfield, 3 lengths back, hung in badly after entering the back straight, made contact with the rail near 600M, weakened gradually in straight.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced 8 lengths back at rear, same margin back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Shifted in at start and made contact, raced 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, there to turn, emptied early in straight, eased final 100M. (Irregular heart rhythm.) (Bled.)

Away with them, crowded near 1100M, raced in midfield early, severely checked after entering the back straight, checked again near 550M, last turning in, showed no response early in straight and eased.
Crossed to the lead before 1st turn, led uncontested for the first half, quickened up pace from 800M, tackled by runner up over final 200M but kept finding to ward off late challenge.
In 3rd place tracking leader to the straight, strongly challenged eventual winner from 250M, just held.
Held up 2nd last over 9Ls off the pace early and middle stages, headway along inside from 400M, ran on well to claim 3rd but not getting to first 2.
Settled down in midfield 5Ls back, hard driven 500M, stayed on mildly towards the finish.
Pressed forward to be tracking leader along the 2-path, kept up the chase turning in, wilted final 150M
Awkwardly away, reserved in mid-division 5-6Ls behind leader, ran on mildly final 300M without threatening leaders.
Dropped back to race in the 9th spot, switched out 400M to improve, boxed on but never seriously threatened.
Bumped heavily at the start, raced further back in the field than had been hoped, 8Ls towards the rear throughout the race, brought wide into straight but couldn't come on.
Began well from draw one, tracked leaders in 4th, battling away on same pace leaving the bend, no impression on leaders.
Dropped back from wide gate, raced behind midfield 6-7Ls away, scrubbed along home turn, failed to improve in the straight.
Positioned ahead of midfield, under serious pressure 600M, commenced to give ground soon and already a spent force turning in.
Switched off to last after the start, over 10Ls off the pace on settling, couldn't keep up passing 700M and continued to lose ground despite being hard ridden, eased down.(Unacceptable Performance.)

Held up in midfield on the rail, commenced move entering home straight, ran on under pressure to assert authority near the finish.

Pressed forward from a wide gate, took up running on the rail passing the 1400 metres holding narrow advantage to the straight, drew 2L clear inside the 300 metres but unable to sustain effort and caught close to home.
Travelled wide in rear of midfield, widest runner turning for home, finished off race strongly.
Settled in rear of midfield, saved ground on the inside turning in, baulked upon straightening, ran on to be nearest at finish.
Jumped fairly settling in midfield, ran on steadily without threatening.
Settled wide in last few, ran on steadily under pressure in straight.
Chased leader to straight, found nothing under pressure.
Failed to muster early stages travelling in last few, came under pressure rounding home bend, kept on same pace without quickening.
Settled well behind from a wide gate, came under pressure from around home bend, went past well-beaten horses closing stages.
Travelled wide in midfield to straight, soon weakened.
Never far off on the rail to straight, weakened shortly after straightening.
Slightly slow out, soon recovered to just worse than midfield on the rail, yielded ground steadily from half-way out.
Ridden early for prominent position, settled just off the pace mainly in 5th to home bend, weakened from approaching home straight. (Questioned for disappointing performance)
Travelled keenly and wide prominently, gained 3rd within 2L of pace passing the 1000 metres, dropped out in straight.
Pushed forward, pace good, ran on strongly to score but only by a narrow margin.
Shared the lead at good pace, closed off strongly for 2nd.
Midfield, pace good, dashed well 200M for 3rd.
Hard ridden early, at back, pace good, dashed well 300M.
Settled in midfield, pace good, just held ground in final stages.
Pressed forward to share the lead at good pace, out of fuel 250M.
Pushed early, behind midfield, pace good, ran on ok, lack room 200M.
Hard ridden forward, pace good, emptied 350M.
Checked start, at back, pace good, no dash.
Hard ridden to keep up with the field, no progress.
Never a factor.
Raced behind leaders, commenced to improve near 600M, responded well in the straight, quickened passing 100M to score.
Travelled nicely to settle outside the lead, asked for effort near 400M, worked home solidly.
Settled behind midfield, wide on straightening, gained ground passing 150M.
Lost left front plate after start, then steadied to obtain cover, widest on straightening, made up some nice late ground.
Settled at box seat, under pressure but only one-paced in the straight.
On jumping was crowded for room, travelled midfield, one-paced.
Ridden along to take lead, under pressure after 600M, in the straight gave ground.
Raced behind midfield on rail, limited response in the straight. Lame left front after race.
Settled midfield on rail, faded out in the straight, must trial.
Quickly into stride, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, travelled well throughout, took the lead near 250M, kept on very well thereafter to hold off the challengers and scored.
Began well, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, there to turn, kept on well early in straight, bumped and unbalanced near 150M, finished off strongly to take 2nd, nearest on line.
Moderately from a wide draw, raced 3 wide with cover, 2 lengths back, same position on turn, finished off strongly despite being bumped near 150M, just narrowly beaten by the first two.
Bumped start, raced prominently, 3 wide, 3/4L back on turn, kept on very well in straight, just beaten by narrow margin.
Shifted out at start and bumped, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, made some progress in straight without threatening.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, 6 to 7 lengths back, same margin back on turn, taken wide in straight and finished off strongly to be nearest on line.
Clean jump, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, 4 to 5 lengths back on turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Began awkwardly and lost ground, raced at rear on rail, 5 lengths back, crowded near 900M, saved ground on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide at rear, difficult to settle near 900M, 5 lengths or so back on turn, finished off one-paced in straight.
Began well from gate 1, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, peaked early in straight, headed near 250M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced 3 wide with cover at tail, 6 lengths back on turn, bumped and unbalanced early in straight, made no real progress in straight.
Moderately away, sat 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened from final 200M.
Began fairly, positioned on rail in midfield, 4 lengths back, saved ground on turn, failed to close off in straight, eased after passing 100M.

Jumped with them, unable to slot in, raced 3 wide in midfield, weakened from 600M, bumped and unbalanced early in straight, eased thereafter. (Lame right front leg next day morning.) (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide, 2 to 3 lengths back, wider after entering the back straight, improved from 800M, took the lead near 500M, kept on strongly in straight to score.
Jumped well from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, 5 lengths or so back, saved ground on turn, made good progress in straight to take 2nd.
Began well from the widest draw, sent forward to take the lead, enjoyed the easy lead to turn, headed near 500M, kept on evenly in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw,raced at rear, 8 to 9 lengths back, 3 wide on turn, no clear running early in straight, made some headway when clear thereafter to make frame, no threat to the first few.
Slowly away, raced 2 wide at rear, still 8 lengths back at 400M, made some headway in straight without threatening.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, 7 lengths back on turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Began awkwardly,raced 2 wide in midfield, 6 lengths or so back on turn, finished off one-paced in straight.

Began well, positioned 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, peaked on turn, kept on one-pace early in straight, weakened final 200M. (Blood in trachea.) (Minor abrasions to the inside of the right hind leg.)
Jumped well, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, 2 wide from near 800M, shared lead on turn, weakened gradually in straight.
Moderately away, raced 3 wide in midfield, wider on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Raced wide at rear throughout, never competitive.
Began only fairly, raced at rear on rail, still well back on turn, showed no response early in straight, eased final 200M.
Jumped well from the middle draw, raced prominently, 2 wide, weakened on turn, eased early in straight.

Began fairly, failed to muster speed despite ridden along, raced at tail throughout, eased after turning in, finished tailed off. (Lame right front leg.) (Right front tendon injury reported following day.)
Raced in midfield, 4L behind along the rail, produced a strong finishing effort inside final 100M to score by a head.
Settled to race in the box-seat, sat 1-1/2L off the lead, battled on gamely to finish a head behind the winner.
Raced in front of midfield, 2-3/4L off 2 wide, kept on and held off a late challenge for 3rd.
Taken back and raced at the rear, 8-1/2L behind 3 wide, saved nice ground and ran on well to the line.
Sent forward to take the rail and led, kept on going until headed prior to final 50M.
In just behind midfield, 4-1/2L off 2 wide, saved ground and continued on until awkward to heels prior going to the line.
Raced towards the rear, 5-1/2L behind along the rail, made ground and ran on fairly.
Settled in front of midfield along the rail, in the straight was held up until 300M and again at 150M.
Niggled to be prominent, but trapped wide and without cover, one paced and emptied late.
Urged before settling in one-off one-back position, emptied passing 200M. (Lame right front)
Raced towards the rear, 2 wide throughout, one paced but ran on to the line.
Sat in behind midfield, wide but with cover, did not save ground.
In midfield, wide but with cover, showed nothing.
Sent forward and sat outside the leader, emptied at 300M. (Rider questioned and blood in trachea)
Jumped well from barrier 13, sent forward to take the lead, found the rail near 600M, kicked clear early in straight, kept on well to the line and scored.
Taken back to race at tail, 8 lengths back, still well back on turn, finished off very strongly in straight to take 2nd, nearest on line.
Away with them, raced 2 wide at rear, 6 lengths back on turn, made very good progress in straight to take a place.
Crowded shortly after start, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, same position on turn, made some headway in straight to make frame without threatening.
Taken back from gate 9, raced at rear, 6 to 7 lengths back, same margin back on turn, taken wide in straight and finished off strongly to be nearest on line.
Began well, raced in 2nd, on rail, travelled well throughout, peaked early in straight, kept on evenly to the line.
Jumped with them, positioned on rail behind the lead, 2 to 3 lengths back on turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Clean jump, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, failed to quicken under pressure in straight.

Moderately away from gate 1, no early speed, raced at rear on rail, 5 to 6 lengths back, saved ground to turn, unable to obtain clear running early in straight, checked after passing 200M, one-paced thereafter.
Crowded on jumping, recovered to race 3 to 4 lengths back on rail, saved ground on turn, failed to quicken under pressure in straight, eased after passing 100M. (Laceration to the left stifle.)
Moderately away from a wide draw, unable to slot in, raced 4 wide with no cover, a length or so back, 3 wide on turn, weakened early in straight when hard run took toll.
Average to begin, made contact early, raced 2 wide, 1 to 2 lengths back, similar position on turn, weakened early in straight, eased near 150M. (Lame right front leg.)
Jumped with them, raced 3 wide, a length or so back, bumped near 900M, peaked on turn, weakened early in straight, checked near 150M, eased thereafter.
Quickly into stride, vied for lead along the fence early stages then sat back behind leader from 750M, quickened well hitting the front near 200M, kicked away strongly to win by comfortable margin.
Chased leaders in 4th, always within striking distance, responded well to go 2nd near 200M, couldn't go on with winner final stages.
Vied for lead on the outside early stages, took outright lead passing 750M, headed by first 2 mid-straight, battled on to hold 3rd.
From wide draw caught 4-wide no cover in midfield, just over 4Ls behind leader 400M, stayed on moderately to the line, did well on debut off a tough run.
Began well from draw 1, settled down in midfield along the inside, battled away in the straight but couldn't quicken to challenge leaders, held ground to the line.
Gradually moved forward, caught wide no cover until reaching a trailing position behind leader 700M, kept on mildly turning home, held ground behind front runners.
From outside draw dropped back to race in last, 8Ls to make up 400M, took a while to get going, made good progress on outer over final 200M. Encouraging debut.
Settled down towards the rear, 7Ls off the pace turning home, stayed on past weakening runners but not enough to threaten.
Began very awkwardly, held up behind midfield along the inside, checked 700m when awkwardly placed behind rivals, failed to finish the race off when asked for an effort in the straight.
Settled down in mid-division along the 3-path, driven out 400M but responded only fairly and not mustered the pace to challenge.
Began only fairly, assumed a position head of midfield, failed to improve position turning in, plodded home. (Vetted - no significant findings.)
Held up behind midfield, crowded for room 700M, couldn't come on in the straight, ran another poor race.
Crowded for room at the start, ended up towards the rear, 8Ls off the pace 400M, never got going.
Towards the rear, 3-wide throughout the race, couldn't keep up passing 400M, soon detached from the field.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 lengths back on turn, finished off strongly in straight to score.
Moderately away from gate 10, positioned 3 wide with no cover, 1 to 2 lengths back, moved closer from 600M, took the lead early in straight, kept on well but just couldn't hold off the winner late.
Average to begin, raced wide with cover at rear, 5 lengths or so back, very wide turning in, made good progress in straight to take 3rd, no threat to the first two.
Moderately away, raced wide with cover in midfield, 3 lengths back on turn, made some headway in straight to make frame.

Began well from gate1, positioned in 2nd, 2 wide after entering the back straight, took the lead near 500M, headed early in straight, kept on evenly thereafter. (Lost right front plate in the early stages.)
Slightly slow out and bumped, raced at rear, 6 to 7 lengths back, 2 wide on turn, made minor progress in straight without threatening.
Slowly away, raced wide with cover at tail, awkwardly placed near 1400M, 6 lengths or so back on turn, made some headway in straight without threatening.
Jumped with them, raced 3 wide with cover at rear early, wider after entering the back straight, improved from 600M, very wide turning in, failed to quicken in straight.
Began well from a wide draw, raced 3 to 4 wide with no cover, better than midfield, peaked on turn, weakened in straight.
Bumped start and unbalanced, positioned 2 to 3 lengths back on rail, similar position on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Fast into stride, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length, challenged by the rivals on turn, headed near 500M, weakened early in straight.
Moderately away, showed no early speed, positioned on rail behind midfield, 4 to 5 lengths back, saved ground on turn, showed no response early in straight, eased thereafter.

Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear, 6 to 7 lengths back, very wide after entering the back straight, checked near 550M, showed no response thereafter. (Lost right front plate in the early stages.)
Began fairly from the widest draw, raced very wide with no cover in midfield, weakened on turn, eased early in straight.
Cruised forward to eventually sit 3rd/4th, 3 wide with no cover. Nosed in front at 300m, but never kicked clear. 1L clear of challengers at 50m, but slightly 1 paced and just held on at the wire.
Quickly found a position midfield, on the fence. Looked 1 paced early in the straight, but steadily worked his way into it. Good turn of foot in last 100m and was rapidly chasing down winner.
Dropped back from the wide draw to settle at the rear of the field. Came around the field to be the widest in the straight. Big turn of foot in the final 150m to grab 3rd on the line.
Cruised forward early to settle around midfield. Keen and awkward on heels early. Only fair early in the straight. Kicked last 100 to grab 4th in a tight finish.
Eased out early to sit around midfield, 3-4 wide with limited cover. Battled along steadily in the straight, before finishing strongly in last 100m.
Taken forward from the wide draw to settle 2nd, on the leaders flank. Stayed on OK early in the straight, but peaked late and was swamped.
Settled midfield. Loomed up menacingly at 150m, but 1 paced late and went to the line timidly.
Cruised up early to sit 5th, just forward of midfield. Well placed early in the straight, but never kicked and was swamped late.
Taken up early to settle 3rd/4th, on the fence. Checked and lost some momentum at 300m. Stayed on solidly late, but no threat.
Pressed forward early to assume the lead. Under pressure to hold his position early in the straight, and dropped out quickly last 150m.
Fractious in barrier, turned head and began awkwardly. Settled towards the rear of the field. Stuck to the rail in the straight, but 1 paced in the run home.
Eased away early to settle worse than midfield. Steadied off heels 1000m. Plugged away in the straight and faded in the last 100m.
Bumped on jumping and dropped back to settle last. Struggled to make inroads in the straight and was eased last 50m.
Bumped on jumping and only eased away to settle worse than midfield. Struggling to keep up before the turn and was eased a long way from home.

Bumped at the start, settled in last few, made steady headway on the rail rounding home bend, switched out for a run early in straight, ran on well to claim 2nd late.
Jumped well, shuffled back to forward of midfield on the rail about 3L off the pace, saved ground turning in, fought on steadily without threatening.
Crowded losing ground at start settling 2-wide in midfield, similar position turning in, baulked 100 metres out, ran on steadily without threatening.
Settled in rear of midfield, became worse rounding home bend and widest runner turning in, ran on quite well to be nearest at finish.
Broke well, settled within 2L of pace in 3rd on the rail, came under pressure to challenge upon straightening, unable to sustain effort closing stages.
Pressed forward from the widest draw, led on the rail until finding no extra 200 metres out.
Ridden along for 2L 4th early stages, held position under pressure early on straight, unable to sustain effort inside the final 200 metres.
Failed to muster settling in last few, hung in and did not find much room early in straight, kept on well.
Travelled wide without cover in midfield, similar turning for home, kept on before finding no extra closing stages.
Settled at the back on the rail, kept on without quickening under pressure.
Gradually settled at the back after beginning from a wide draw, remained well behind turning in, made no impression in the run home.
Pushed to obtain box seat, enjoyed by the slow tempo, closed off strongly to score.
Hard ridden forward to take the rail and led at advantageous slow sectionals, hung on well until 50M overhauled.
Eased back, 2 wide, harmed by the slow tempo, unleashed strong finishing efforts 250M.
Pushed to hold the rail in midfield, harmed by the slow pace, little dash in straight.
Behind midfield along the fence, not suited by the slow tempo, dashed well 200M.

Urged along after start to take lead, travelled nicely, responded strongly in the straight to score.
Hard ridden after start, passing 1100M was inconvenienced, settled in box seat, on straightening shifted in to obtain clear running, finished solidly.
Raced behind midfield on rail, steadied away from heels near 1000M, made some nice late ground.
Taken back at start, kept on rail rounding Home Turn to save ground, gained ground passing 150M, finished nicely.
Settled midfield on rail, fought hard in the straight, worked home well.
Raced midfield, wide on straightening, battled hard entire straight.
Settled at back, commenced to improve passing 400M, made ground passing 150M, finished OK.
After start bumped a runner and became badly unbalanced then taken back, fought hard but one-paced.
Travelled behind midfield, tried to improve passing 450M, limited response in the straight.
Urged along to share the lead at one-off position, weakened passing 200M, failed to run on.
Near 1100M was bumped and became badly unbalanced, near 700M was left racing wide and without cover, lay out after 700M and rounding Home Turn hung out, faded-out near 250M.
Raced behind leaders, came under pressure after 500M, passing 300M gave ground, lame left front after race.
Clean jump, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well throughout, kept on very well in straight to score.
Fast into stride, positioned a length behind the leader, bumped and unbalanced near 600M, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after straightening, closed off well to take 2nd, just beaten by a neck.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced 2 wide at tail, still 6 to 7 lengths back on turn, finished off very strongly in straight to take 3rd, nearest on line.
Away with them, raced 2 wide behind midfield, improved on turn, tried hard in the run home but broke down close home.
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, angled out after passing 600M, 3 lengths back on turn, made some progress in straight without threatening.
Bumped start, positioned on rail behind midfield, awkwardly placed near 700M, shifted out near 450M, taken wide in straight and made some progress. (Lost right front plate.)
Jumped with them, positioned 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Out in line, raced 2 wide better than midfield, 2 lengths back on turn, peaked early in straight, kept on one-pace to the line. (Blood in trachea.)
Shifted out at start and bumped, sent forward to race in prominently, bumped and unbalanced near 600M, 2nd on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail throughout, emptied early in straight.
Average to begin, failed to muster speed, raced 2 wide at rear, checked near 400M, failed to close off in straight.
Jumped with them, raced 3 wide and without cover, 5 lengths back, peaked on turn, emptied early in straight.
Jumped well, sent forward to take the lead, enjoyed the easy lead to 700M, shared the lead on turn, kept on very well in straight to score.
Began awkwardly and crowded, raced at rear early, sent forward after passing 900M, sat outside to the leader from 700M, shared lead on turn, kept on well in straight to take 2nd.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide at rear, sent forward near 800M, 3rd on turn, 3 wide, kept on evenly in straight to get 3rd.
Moderately away from a wide draw, sent forward to race prominently early, found rail near 1300M, 3 lengths back, saved ground to turn, 5 lengths back at 400M, made some headway in straight.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide in midfield, 4 lengths or so back on turn, made some progress in straight without threatening.

Began awkwardly, bumped and unbalanced early, raced 2 wide at rear early, carried wider from 1350M, sent forward after 1200M to take the 1 out 1 back position, found rail on the home turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final 100M.
Began well, positioned 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground throughout, 3 lengths back at 400M, finished off one-paced.
Bumped start, raced at tail, 8 to 9 lengths back, moved a bit closer after passing 800M, 6 to 7 lengths back on turn, finished off one-paced.

Bumped start, positioned on rail behind midfield early, angled out after entering the first turn, 6 lengths back on turn, kept on evenly early in straight, steadied off heels near 150M, eased thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)

Bumped shortly after start, positioned on rail in midfield early, awkwardly placed 1400M, 5-6Ls back on the 1st turn, kept same margin back when others improved in the middle stages, became last on turn, showed nothing thereafter.
Sent forward to take the rail and lead, held margin over the others in straight, scored by 2L.
Pushed and settled in one-off one-back position, sat 1-1/4L off, fought on but was no match to the winner.
Asked to take up racing in the box-seat, sat 2L off the lead, one paced but held on for 3rd.
Slotted into midfield, raced 4L behind 2 wide, continued on fairly to the finish.
Bumped start, taken back to be at the rear, 6-3/4L behind 1-2 wide at turn, made ground and closed off fairly.
Bumped start, niggled to be in front of midfield, 2 wide throughout, did not threaten.
Settled to race in behind midfield, 6L behind along the rail, made minor ground and kept on.
Travelled in worse than midfield and stayed 2 wide throughout, one paced in the straight.
Raced in about midfield, along the rail throughout, did not improve.
Bumped start and then eased, settled in behind midfield but wide, emptied passing 200M.
Sent forward, sat outside the leader, weakened badly passing 250M.
Failed to muster and raced detached throughout. Must trial. (Lame left front)

Clean jump, sent forward to sit 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground to near 450M, challenged the leader turning in, took the lead early in straight, kept on well thereafter and scored.
Began well from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, 3 lengths or so back, saved ground on turn, finished off well to take 2nd.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide at rear, 6 to 7 lengths back, sent forward near 600M, 3 wide on turn, made some headway in straight to take a place.
Bumped start and unbalanced, raced 2 wide better than midfield, similar position on turn, kept on evenly in straight, just missed 3rd on line.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide at tail, still 6 lengths back on turn, taken wide in straight and finished off very strongly to be nearest on line.
Bumped on jumping, positioned 5 lengths back on rail, saved ground on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Taken back to race at tail, 8 to 9 lengths back, still last on turn, made reasonable progress in straight without threatening.
Moderately away from a wide draw, sent forward to take the lead, enjoyed the easy lead to turn, headed early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter. (Jockey dropped whip 75M.)
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, 5 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Bumped shortly after start, raced at rear on rail, 6 to 7 lengths back, there to turn, failed to make any progress in straight.
Away with them, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, peaked near 400M, emptied early in straight. (Jockey concerned over the horse's action before the race.)
Settled midfield 4Ls off the pace, waited with until 300M, shifted into clear 200M and quickened up impressively to win going away.
Moved up to track leader along the 2-path, responded well turning in, hit the front near 150M but couldn't match winner's pace final 100M.
Taken back from wide draw, settled last 9Ls behind leader, driven widest passing 400M, ran on well and made it to 3rd place.
Took time to muster speed, held up midfield 5Ls of the good pace, chased on well inside 300M to go 4th near line.
Went forward to be tracking leaders on settling, kept on steadily entering straight but couldn't muster the speed to challenge leaders.

From wide draw taken across behind runners early stages, held up 2nd last until 650M then driven forward rounding the field, kept battling in straight but run ended 150M. (Jockey : didn't back up after racing last week.)
Crossed to the lead passing 1300M, took them along at good pace, battled on well entering straight, headed near 150M, faded towards the line.
Reserved towards the rear 7Ls off the pace, awkwardly placed from 500M and unable to obtain clear running until 200M, stayed on towards the line.
Towards the rear 7Ls away from leader, in similar spot 400M but failed to improve position in the straight.
Settled down behind midfield, saved ground on the inside, didn't respond under pressure in straight.
Went forward after the start, slotted in behind leaders, had to be scrubbed along 600M, weakened away from top of the straight.
Couldn't slot in from the wide draw, caught 3-wide no cover in midfield for most part of the race, dropped out of contention passing 300M.
