Pressed forward from the widest gate, virtually made all, drew clear after straightening to win comfortably.
Moderate start, settled in midfield, soon came to challenge passing the 400 metres, fought on under pressure to claim 2nd 100 metres out.
Ridden along before settling just worse than midfield, switched out for a run after straightening, made up good ground down the centre of track.
Jumped fairly settling just over 2L back in 3rd, came to challenge 3-wide entering home straight, kept on without quickening.
Settled in midfield on the rail, held 5th some 3L back rounding the bend, gained 2L 4th entering straight, kept on without quickening.
Hampered at start and remained well behind, met minor interferences and switched 200 metres out, did best work late.
Very awkward beginning losing ground, settled towards the rear on the rail to straight, fought on steadily without threatening.
Towards the rear, carried backward and dropped to last rounding home bend, ran on past well-beaten horses closing stages.
Badly unbalanced at start dropping to last few, took slightly closer order 3-wide rounding home bend, kept on same pace without quickening down the centre of the straight.
Ridden early to hold 2nd spot, switched off the rail to challenge approaching home straight, failed to make any impression in the run to the line.
Moderate start, gradually recovered to prominent position 3-wide, gave ground noticeably in straight. (Questioned for disappointing performance)
Hard ridden to secure box seat, ran on strongly 400M to score.
Hard ridden to hold the rail in midfield, dashed well 300M for 2nd.
Hard ridden to take rail and lead, hung on until 200M overhauled, ran on for 3rd.
Hard ridden early, trapped 4-5 wide at back, checked 700M, dashed strongly 200M.
Eased back, 2 wide, tightened for room 500M, dashed well 250M.
Hard ridden early but not muster, trapped 3-4 wide in midfield, ran on ok despite negative racing situations.
Hard ridden early, trapped 3 wide in midfield, made early move 500M, out of fuel 200M.
Failed to muster at back, trapped 3 wide, no dash.
Very slow away, at rear along the fence, no dash.
Very slow away, at back, no progress.
Hard ridden forward, sat outside the leader, emptied quickly 400M.
Pressed forward, soon dropped off 500M.
Raced midfield on rail, improved on straightening, quickened passing 200M, scored unchallenged.
Settled midfield, wide on straightening, gradually made ground in the straight, finished solidly.
Settled behind midfield, responded nicely when placed under pressure, made up some nice late ground.
Urged along to settle behind leaders, responded well in the straight.
Raced behind midfield, wide on straightening, battled hard to the line, finished OK.
Raced midfield, near 700M travelled wide and without cover, rounding Home Turn was taken wider, fought hard entire straight.
Ridden along to take lead, asked for effort passing 400M, gave ground passing 150M.
Taken back at start, near 300M was checked, after that only one-paced.
Raced at handy position, throughout the race travelled wide and without cover, limited response in the straight.
Slow out then was crowded for room, settled behind midfield on rail, near 1350 lost right front plate, weakened passing 150M.
Slow out then was crowded for room, settled behind midfield, no response in the straight.
Raced midfield, travelled keenly in the early and middle stages, gave ground passing 300M.
Jumped nicely and ridden along to settle outside the lead, faded out passing 150M.
Ridden to take box seat, emptied passing 200M.

Began well, sent forward to race prominently, allowed to cross near 1600M, positioned 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader thereafter, moved closer from 700M, 3/4L back turning in, finished off very strongly in straight to score.

Jumped well, sent forward to race prominently, took the lead on the first turn, led by a length, enjoyed the easy lead until challenged near 600M, kept on well in straight, but couldn't hold off the winner 200M. Stayed on for 2nd.

Began fairly, positioned on rail at rear, 7 to 8 lengths back, gradually moved closer along the rail, 3 lengths or so back turning in, kept to inside after straightening and made very good progress to be nearest on line.
Taken back to race at tail, 9 lengths back, moved closer in the middle stages, 4 lengths back on turn, made good progress in straight to make frame.
Jumped well, positioned 2 to 3 lengths back on rail, saved ground throughout, angled out early in straight, finished off evenly.
Crowded on jumping, raced 6 to 7 lengths back, moved closer in the middle stages, 2 wide, 4 lengths back on turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Shifted out at start and made contact, raced 2 wide, 3 lengths back, similar position to turn, failed to close off in straight.
Jumped well, unable to slot in early, raced 3 wide with no cover, sent forward after passing 1600M to race in 2nd, 2 wide, carried wider near 650M, weakened early in straight, eased final 100M.
Jumped well, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, easy run on turn, finished off strongly in straight to score by a neck.
Bumped start, sent forward to race in 2nd, 2 wide, shared lead turning in, kept on very well in straight but couldn't hold off the winner late.

Jumped well from the widest draw, unable to slot in, raced very wide behind midfield, improved on turn, brushed and carried wider near 550M, kept on well in straight to take a place without threatening the first two.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear on rail, saved ground on turn, steadied near 600M, made good progress in straight to make frame.

Average to begin, raced 2 wide, a length behind, bumped by the riderless horse near 900M, difficult to settle thereafter, angled out near 550M, showed good response early in straight, peaked 200M, weakened thereafter.
Taken back from gate 11, raced 2 wide at rear, moved closer on turn, kept on evenly in straight, crowded close home. (Lame left front leg next day.)
Began well from a tricky gate, unable to slot in, raced very wide in midfield early, still 3 wide on turn, peaked early in straight, kept on one-pace to the line.
Bumped start, raced 3 wide with cover at tail, 5 lengths back on turn, passed a few tired rivals in straight.
Shifted out at start and made heavy contact, raced 2 wide at rear, 4 lengths back, wider on turn, finished off one-pace in straight.
Slightly slow out, positioned on rail in midfield, 3 lengths back, saved ground on turn, laid in and unbalanced early in straight, showed little response thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Away with them, sent forward to take the lead, challenged by rival near 550M, weakened early in straight, finished last.

Placing: UR
Comment: Stumbled badly at start and rider being dislodged.
Raced in one-off one-back, about 1-3/4L off the lead, kept on challenging and finished off to score by 1/2L. (Blood in trachea)
Sent forward to sit about 1/2L off and outside the leader, continued on fairly to finish 1/2L behind.
Began only fairly, recovered to take rail and led by 1/2L, headed near 150M, fought on for 3rd.
Pushed to obtain the box-seat, sat about 1L off the lead, one paced but ran on.
Rolled forward, sat in front of midfield, wide and without cover, was one paced in the straight.
Bumped start, raced towards the rear, 3 wide but with cover, made ground and closed off fairly.
Slotted in to race in midfield along the rail, kept on one paced until flattened at 200M.
In worse than midfield, wide and without cover throughout, did not threaten.
Bumped start, settled midfield 2 wide, urged from 700M, showed nothing in the straight.(Whip dropped at 400M)
Urged but settled towards the rear along the rail, weakened badly near 250M.
Hard ridden but remained at the rear, finished tailed out.
Bumped start, settled towards the rear, 2 wide, eased down at home turn to finish tailed out. Must trial. (Reduced left laryngeal movement)
Fast into stride, positioned 2 wide, 1 to 2 lengths back, showed very good response after turning in, took the lead near 200M, kept on strongly to score.
Jumped well from the widest draw, raced prominently, 2 wide, there to turn, took the lead near 250M but headed shortly thereafter, stayed on for 2nd. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began well from a wide draw, sent forward to take the lead, enjoyed the easy lead to turn, kept on well early in straight, headed near 250M, kept on evenly to the line.
Began well, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, easy run on turn, angled out early in straight, made some late progress to be nearest on line.
Taken back to race at tail, 9 lengths back, closer on turn but still the last, no clear running early in straight, shifted in after passing 200M and closed off well thereafter to be nearest on line.
Began fairly, raced 2 wide, 6 lengths back, similar position on turn, finished off strongly in straight to be nearest on line.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide at rear, there to turn, still 4 to 5 lengths back at 400M, showed good response early in straight, peaked near 200M, slightly weakened thereafter.
Slowly away, positioned 6 lengths behind the leader on rail, angled out near 600M, finished off evenly in straight.
Away with them, raced 2 wide better than midfield, 3 lengths back, same margin back on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened close home.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, 5 lengths back, carried wider from 600M, failed to close off in straight.
Slow to begin, raced at rear on rail, 8 lengths back, moved closer along the rail on turn, showed no response in straight, eased final 100M.
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, weakened early in straight, eased after passing 200M. (Lame left front leg next day morning.)
Away well, sat just outside leader, vied for lead with that rival in the straight, gained upper hand inside 100M.
Driven to take the lead under 10lb claimer, set steady pace to straight, taken on by eventual winner from 400M, fought on well until giving way 100M. Gap to rest.
Began awkwardly, recovered to be 5th just over 2Ls behind leader, stayed on moderately for distant 3rd.
Held up in mid-division, 4Ls off the pace turning in, kept grinding to the line for distant 4th.
Went forward from draw 1 chasing leaders along the fence, kept on same pace turning in, wilted final 100M.
From wide draw couldn't get closer than 3-wide, no cover home turn, ran on same pace in the straight.
Caught wide no cover throughout chasing leaders, weakened away from 350M.
Restrained behind midfield, difficult to settle after 800M, kept on same pace in the straight, no threat to leaders.
From draw 12 caught wide no cover in midfield for most part of the race, lay out 700M, weakened away turning home.
Slow to begin, settled down 2nd last, lay out making the turn near 700M, couldn't finish off entering straight.
Failed to muster speed despite ridden along, at rear always, never in the picture.
Began only fairly, positioned at rear on rail, raced greenly throughout, 5 lengths or so back on turn, finished off very strongly in straight to score on his debut.

Bumped start and unbalanced, positioned on rail in midfield, 3 lengths or so back, saved ground on turn, no clear running early in straight, angled out after passing 200M, finished off well to take 2nd.
Jumped well from a tricky gate, sent forward to race prominently, 2 to 3 wide, shared lead on turn, kept on very well in straight but couldn't hold off the first two late.
Moderately away from a middle draw, took the 1 out 1 back position, same position on turn, kept on well in straight but always held.
Clean jump, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, there to turn, made minor progress in straight without threatening.
Bumped start, sat a length behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, no clear running early in straight, inconvenienced near 150M, no extra thereafter.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, 4 to 5 lengths back, similar position on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Taken back from a widest draw, raced 3 wide with cover at tail, 5 to 6 lengths back, finished off evenly in straight.
Average to begin, sent forward to race prominently but wide, no cover on turn, peaked near 400M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Taken back from gate 13, raced 2 wide at tail, 6 lengths back, taken wide in straight, steadied off heels near 250M, made no progress thereafter.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide at rear, found rail on turn, checked near 400M, eased thereafter.
Jumped well, sent forward to take the lead, challenged by rival on turn, headed early in straight, kept on evenly until inconvenienced near 150M, weakened thereafter and eased.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide in midfield in the early stages, travelled keenly from 950M, 4 lengths back on turn, made contact near 250M, showed nothing thereafter and eased.
Began awkwardly and crowded, raced 2 wide in midfield, travelled keenly and checked off heels near 650M, showed no response early in straight, weakened thereafter, eased final 100M.
Eased back early to sit worse than midfield. Progressed to 4th on the turn. Dropped whip 250m. Nosed in front 200m, and scooted in under hands and heels late.
Cruised forward from the inside draw to settle midfield. Got to the lead early in the straight, but tackled 200m. Couldn't match winner late, but had no threats for 2nd.
Pushed forward to be the early leader, before being crossed at 700m. Battled on solidly early in the straight to regain 3rd. No match for first 2, and 1 paced late. Just managed to hold onto 3rd.
Wide early before settling around midfield. Strong run in the straight and was rapidly running down 3rd late.
Eased back early to settle 2nd last. Stayed on solidly in the straight and made good ground, but no threat for a place.
Pushed hard from the wide draw to eventually lead passing 700m. No kick and went to the line 1 paced.
Pushed out early to settle 3rd, 1 off the fence. Battled on steadily early in the straight, before fading out late.
Began awkwardly and dropped back to the rear of the field. No dash in straight.
Cruised forward from the inside draw to settle around midfield. 1 paced and no threat.
Settled midfield, but stuck 4-5 wide with no cover. Gave ground in the straight and never involved.
Taken forward early to settle just forward of midfield. No kick early in the straight and faded out from 200m.
Crowded on jumping and eased to worse than midfield. Never kicked and eased a long way from home. Unacceptable performance.
Bustled along to take up a midfield spot along the 2-path, closed off strongly final 200M, hit the lead 50M out, won going away.
Shaken up after the start to be tracking leaders along the fence, stayed on well to go 2nd near line. Promising return after 6 months absence.
Held up 2-wide ahead of mid-division, pace strong middle stages, responded well turning in, loomed a chance 200M, couldn't match finishing pace of first 2 late stages.
Jumped well, vied for early lead until 1000M then sat back behind pace, moved up outside leader 500M before taking narrow lead 250M, outsprinted by first 3 late.
Began only fairly, urged forward, took outright lead 1000M setting good pace at the front, headed 250M, battled on to the line, pushed out to 5th final stages.
Restrained after the start, taken across to the rail to be 5L off the pace behind midfield, kept grinding to the line but always held by leaders.
Reserved in a 2-wide spot towards the rear, stayed on fairly over final 400M, not reach contention.
Crowded for room at the start, taken across to a rail spot, always near the rear in a strongly run race, stayed on past weakening runners but not enough to threaten.
Failed to muster speed, taken across behind runners for cover, in the rear first half then driven wide 600M, ran on same pace down outside of straight, no threat.
Settled down 3-wide in midfield, close enough to be 2Ls behind leader at 400M, had his chance in the straight but couldn't sustain run passing 200M.
From draw 11 driven forward but unable to lead, caught wide no cover throughout, came under pressure top of straight and didn't finish off. (Jockey questioned / Unacceptable Performance.)

Towards the rear in a 3-wide spot, found nothing when asked in straight, eased when no chance. (Jockey reported he did not feel as comfortable in its action compared to last start when performed well.)
Dropped back to race near the rear, under the pump home turn, couldn't finish off. (Jockey expressed concern regarding the action.)
Rushed forward after the start, 2-wide chasing leader on settling, gave way from 400M, weakened to last.

Taken back from gate 10, raced 2 wide at rear, 8 lengths back, 3 wide from near 600M, 4 lengths back turning in, finished off strongly in straight to take 3rd, nearest on line.

Bumped start, positioned 2 wide, 3 lengths back, similar position to turn, angled out near 450M, showed very good response early in straight, took the lead near 150M, but couldn't hold off the first few final 50M.

Average to begin, sent forward to race prominently, allowed the rival to cross on the first turn, sat right behind the leader to turn, peaked early in straight, kept on evenly to near 100M, weakened thereafter.
Jumped well, positioned 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, kept on evenly early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Out in line, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 5 lengths back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Bumped start, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, hard ridden on turn, weakened early in straight, hampered near 200M, eased thereafter.

Clean jump, positioned on rail in midfield, raced keenly on the 1st turn, slightly angled out after passing 800M, raced tight near 650M, 3 to 4 lengths back on turn, weakened early in straight, hampered near 200M, eased thereafter.
Pushed forward to take rail and led at good pace, kicked away 300M, hung on well to score.
Eased to sit in midfield, 2 wide, pace good, dashed well 300M for 2nd.

Hard ridden forward, sat 2 wide, pace good, out of fuel 150M.

Very slow away, took rail at back, pace good, ran on fairly.
Very slow away, at rear, 2 wide, pace good, no dash.
Very slow away, at back, trapped 3 wide, pace good, no progress.
Very slow away, pace good, never improved at rear.
Jumped well, raced behind leaders, issued challenge passing 150M, made up good late ground to score.
Ridden along to take lead, responded solidly in the straight, worked home nicely.
Ridden hard from wide barrier but settled at rear, responded well when asked for effort in the straight, finished solidly.
Raced midfield on rail, near 750M was steadied when crowded for room, battled hard entire straight, finished well, blood trachea.
Raced behind midfield, fought hard and made some ground passing 100M.
Settled midfield, widest on straightening, gained some ground passing 100M.
Settled midfield, tried to improve but only one-paced.
Settled at rear, made some ground in the final stages, rider questioned.
Began only fairly and then was crowded for room, after that ridden along to take box seat, gave ground passing 150M.
Urged along to settle outside the lead, weakened passing 100M.
Settled behind midfield, after 600M was left racing wide and without cover, no response in the straight.
Raced at back, wide on straightening, never in it.
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground to turn, angled out early in straight, finished off very strongly to score by a length.
Bumped start, raced 3 wide at rear, 6 lengths back, improved from 500M, very wide turning in, made good progress in straight to take 2nd.
Taken back to race at rear, 6 lengths or so back on rail, slightly improved along the rail on turn, kept to inside after straightening, finished off well to take 3rd.
Bumped start, raced 3 wide behind midfield, difficult to settle near 1300M, no cover after entering the back straight, slightly improved on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Jumped with them, positioned 2 wide, 4 lengths back, same margin back on turn, no daylight early in straight, made minor progress when clear thereafter.
Began well from a tricky gate, raced prominently but wide in the early stages, found cover after entering the back straight, 2 lengths back, same position on turn, finished off one-paced.

Shifted out at start and bumped, sent forward to race prominently, travelled keenly on the first turn, angled out after being crossed near 1000M, challenged the leader on turn, kept on well until passing 150M, weakened thereafter.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide at rear, 7 lengths back, still last turning in, no clear running early in straight, made no real progress when clear thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began awkwardly, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, found rail after the first turn, 1 to 2 lengths back, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Jumped well from the widest draw, trapped 4 wide early, sent forward on the 1st turn and took the lead 1100M, led by a length to home turn, headed near 400M, weakened from 150M.
Hampered on jumping, positioned 2 wide behind midfield, 4 to 5 lengths back, angled out on turn, showed no response in straight. (Blood in trachea.)
Crowded shortly after start, raced at rear on rail, 6 to 7 lengths back, angled out near 400M, awkwardly placed early in straight, finished off very strongly thereafter to score.
Moderately away from a wide draw, raced 2 wide behind midfield, improved on turn, finished off well to take 2nd.
Slightly slow out, raced 2 wide at rear, 6 lengths or so back, improved on turn, made good progress in straight to take a place.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, 7 to 8 lengths back, very wide turning in, finished off strongly to be nearest on line.
Began awkwardly, positioned on rail behind midfield, 6 lengths back on turn, made some progress in straight without threatening.

Began fairly from a wide draw, raced 3 wide in midfield, sent forward after entering the back straight, took the lead near 750M, led by 2L turning in, kicked clear early in straight, peaked near 150M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide, 1 to 2 lengths back, 3 wide turning in, finished off evenly in straight.

Reared at start and lost ground, recovered to sit 2 to 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground to turn, made some progress early in straight, weakened gradually close home. (Sore in both front fetlocks next day.)
Away with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 to 4 lengths back, same position on turn, showed limited response in straight, eased final 100M. (Irregular heart rhythm.) (Lame left front leg next day.)

Fast into stride, raced prominently on rail early, allowed rival to cross near 1100M, saved ground to turn, 2 wide 3 lengths back at 400M, made no progress in straight, eased final 100M. (Lame left front leg next day.)
Jumped well, sent forward to race prominently but wide, peaked on turn, weakened gradually in straight.
Crowded start, sent forward to race prominently, took the rail near 1100M, allowed rival to cross near 700M, 2 lengths back on turn, emptied early in straight.
Travelled in the box-seat, gradually kicked away from 150M to win with ease by 3L.
Rolled forward and settled in one-off one-back position, fought on gamely to take 2nd just before going to the line.
Hard ridden forward to sit outside the lead, continued on well for 3rd.
Sent forward to lead, along the rail throughout, headed by the winner passing 150M and emptied late.
Raced at the rear, 2 wide throughout, made ground and ran on fairly.
Urged to be prominent but wide and without cover, found no extra near 100M.
Awkward start, travelled in midfield 2 wide, pretty one paced in the straight.
Bumped start, then raced at the rear along the rail, did not threaten.
Settled in behind midfield along the rail, saved no ground and eased approaching 50M.
Took cover after bumped start, settled in behind midfield 2 wide, eased out after taken very wide at home turn.
In midfield, travelled wide but with cover, taken wider at home turn, found nothing and finished tailed out. Must trial.
Average to begin, positioned on rail in midfield, 3 to 4 lengths back, same margin back on turn, finished off very strongly in straight to score.
Jumped well, sent forward to race prominently, on rail, a length behind the leader on turn, kept to inside after straightening and finished off very well, but just couldn't hold off the winner late.
Began fairly, positioned 2 wide, 1 to 2 lengths back, there to turn, made some headway in straight to take 3rd.
Fast into stride, showed good speed to take the lead, 2 wide, found rail near 600M, challenged by rival on turn, kept on well early in straight, headed final 100M, stayed on for 4th.
Began awkwardly, recovered to race prominently but wide, challenged the leader 400M, kept on evenly to the line. (Jockey concerned over the horse's action before the race.)
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground throughout, showed limited response in straight.
Began only fairly, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, improved from 400M, failed to make any progress in straight. (Blood in trachea.)
Began fairly, showed no early speed, raced 2 wide at rear, 6 lengths back, there to turn, made no real progress in straight.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, 7 lengths back, still well back on turn, taken widest in straight and passed the tired ones.
Began awkwardly, raced wide with cover behind midfield, 4 lengths or so back, same position on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Began well from gate 11, raced 3 wide with cover, a length back, no cover from 600M, weakened gradually in straight.
Began very awkwardly and lost ground, raced at rear on rail, 6 lengths back, there to turn, showed nothing in straight, finished last.
Settled down behind midfield about 6Ls off leader, shifted wide 400M to commence his run, closed off strongly to get up last stride.
Chased leader in 3rd, kicked on well to wrestle the lead 150M, looked the winner only to be caught by fast finishing rival last stride.
Slightly slow out, rushed forward to be prompting the pace 2-wide, challenged for the lead turning in, kept on steadily for 3rd.
Shaken up after the start, soon crossed to the lead setting good pace in front, tackled by rivals on both sides passing 300M, fought on till 150M, faded late.
Taken back from wide draw, settled in last 8Ls behind leader, driven out 500M, made steady progress down the inside.
Assumed a midfield position 5Ls off the pace, ran on moderately on straightening and not enough to threaten.

Restrained behind midfield, 4Ls behind leader 400M, quickened up well in the straight, shifted out to continue 150M but gap closed and lost every chance. (Jockey questioned re his riding in the straight.)
Settled down in 10th 7Ls off the pace, made limited progress over final 300M, not reached leaders.
Began fairly, gradually improved to be 5th at 800M, battled on same pace early straight, couldn't sustain run passing 200M.
From draw 1 held up along the rail in mid-division, couldn't finish off in the straight.
Went forward, lay out making first turn, raced wide until 850M, lay out again 450M, already a spent force turning home, weakened rapidly.
Began only fairly, dropped back to near the rear, badly unbalanced in its action 550M, eased down by Jockey after. (Vetted no significant findings / Unacceptable Performance.)

Began well from the one draw, settled not far off in 5th, raced tight inside the eventual 3rd early in straight, fought on dourly to just prevail final strides.
Moderate start, settled in forward of midfield in 6th, switched wide for a run entering straight, ran on quite well but the post came too soon.
Ridden early, settled just over 2L back in 3rd, shaken up to challenge on straightening, ran on to hit the front briefly 150 metres out, caught final strides.
Slightly slow out, held up in last few, switched wideset into the straight, finished off race well down the centre of the track.
Jumped fairly, settled in midfield on the rail, gained slightly closer to 6th around the bend when pace slackened, fought on steadily down the inside of the straight.

Broke well, gradually worked his way across from the widest gate to lead on the rail 1400 metres out, steadied pace approaching home bend, headed narrowly on straightening, faded inside the final 150 metres.

Began awkwardly losing ground settling in rear of midfield, gained slightly closer rounding home bend, raced tight between runners early in straight, switched out for a run 150 metres out, kept on without quickening.
Began well from a wide gate settling just off the pace, gained upper hand briefly over 200 metres out only to be overhauled closing stages.
Settled within 3L of pace in 4th, became 5th passing the 1200 metres, no response under pressure in straight.
Jumped fairly settling in midfield, one-paced in straight.
Soon taken across from a wide gate settling at the back, ran past well-beaten horses in the straight.
Began awkwardly losing ground, soon recovered to the rear of the field, gained slightly closer to 10th 1000 metres out, found nothing in straight.
Settled well behind, never seen with a chance.
Moderate start from a wide gate settling towards the rear, dropped further back after straightening. (Blood in trachea)
Hard ridden to secure box seat, ran on well to score.
Hard ridden forward, sat 2 wide, kicked 400M, hung on until 100M overhauled.
Very slow away, at back along the fence, dashed well 250M for 3rd.
Hard ridden forward, trapped 3 wide in the lead, just held ground in final stages.
Very slow away, 2 wide in midfield, ran on ok in straight.
Hard ridden to sit in front of midfield, 3 wide, ran on until 150M weakened.
Hard ridden but not muster, trapped 3-4 wide in midfield, no turn of foot in straight.
Hard ridden to keep up in midfield, 3-4 wide, no dash.
Eased at start, 2 wide at back, never improved.
Never a factor at rear.
Midfield along the fence, emptied 200M.
Eased back, trapped 3-5 wide, never competitive.

Placing: PU
Comment: Midfield, eased out of race 300M.
Urged after start, raced midfield, wide on straightening, issued strong challenged passing 200M, finished solidly to score.
Settled midfield on rail, made good ground near 200M, worked home strongly.
Taken back at start, wide on straightening, made up some nice late ground.
On jumping was crowded for room, after start lost left front plate and near 1700M lost it right front plate, raced behind midfield on rail, fought hard entire straight, finished well.
Began awkwardly then urged along to take lead, under pressure, gave some ground passing 100M.
Ridden along after start, settled box seat, commenced to improve passing 500M, fought hard to the line.
Slow to begin and ridden along to make up ground, after 1000M was checked, settled midfield on rail, tried to improve passing 600M, worked home ok.
Raced behind leaders, tried to improve passing 700M, one-paced.
On jumping was crowded for room, ridden along to settle outside the lead passing 800M, gave some ground passing 100M.
Jumped well, urged along to race at handy position, limited response when asked for effort.
Taken back at start, raced midfield, lost right front plate near 950M, weakened passing 50M. Lame left front next day.
Raced at back, in the early part of the straight was steadied when disappointed for running, failed to run on.
After start was steadied when crowded for room, then taken back, widest on straightening, no response in the straight, must trial.
Jumped well, sent forward to race prominently, found rail near 900M, shared lead on turn, kept on well early in straight, headed near 200M but rallied gamely to regain lead final strides.

Began well from gate 1, raced prominently, allowed the rival to cross near 900M, sat a length behind the leader on turn, showed very good response early in straight, took the lead 200M but caught close home.
Away with them, raced 2 wide better than midfield, checked near 850M, angled out on turn, kept on well in straight to take a place.
Slightly slow out, positioned 3 to 4 lengths back on rail, slightly improved along the rail on turn, kept on well in straight to make frame.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide, 4 lengths back, travelled keenly near 800M, similar position on turn, made some progress in straight.
Bumped on jumping, taken back to race 3 wide with cover at rear, 4 to 5 lengths back on turn, taken very wide in straight and made some progress without threatening.
Moderately away from a wide draw, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, very wide turning in, passed a few tired runners in straight.
Average to begin, sent forward to race prominently, positioned 1 out 1 back after 800M, failed to quicken under pressure in straight.
Jumped with them, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, shared lead on turn, weakened gradually in straight, eased 150M. (Mucus in trachea.)
Began fairly, raced 2 wide in midfield, checked near 850M, 2 lengths or so back on turn, failed to close off in straight. (Blood in trachea.)
Bumped on jumping, raced 2 wide, 4 lengths back, similar position on turn, no clear running early in straight, hampered near 200M, eased thereafter.
Began fairly from a wide draw, positioned 3 wide, 2 lengths or so back, carried wider on turn, weakened early in straight, eased final 100M.
Began very awkwardly and bumped, lost considerable ground, raced at rear throughout, never in the hunt.
Bumped start, taken back to race at rear, well back on turn, showed no response in straight.
Jumped well, positioned 3 lengths or so back on rail, saved ground on turn, finished off very strongly in straight to score.
Bumped start and unbalanced, raced behind midfield, 5 lengths back, same margin back on turn, finished off well to take 2nd.
Jumped with them, unable to slot in early, sent forward to take the lead thereafter, led by a length on turn, kept on well in straight but could not hold off the first two late.

Stood flat-footed at start and lost ground, raced at tail, 7 to 8 lengths back, still well back on turn, no clear running early in straight, taken widest thereafter and finished off very strongly to be nearest on line.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced 2 wide at rear, 6 to 7 lengths back, similar position on turn, made some headway in straight without threatening.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 5 lengths or so back, angled out near 600M, very wide turning in, showed limited response in straight.
Jumped well, sent forward to race prominently but wide, 4 lengths back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Bumped start, raced at rear on rail, 6 lengths back, same margin back on turn, passed a few tired runners in straight.
Away with them, raced 2 to 3 wide with cover in midfield, 6 lengths back turning in, no clear running early in straight, made no progress when clear thereafter.
Began well from a wide draw, sent forward to race prominently, 3rd on turn, peaked early in straight, eased final 200M.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide better than midfield, 5 lengths back at 400M, failed to close off in straight.
Crowded on jumping, unable to slot in, raced 4 wide with no cover in midfield, there to turn, weakened gradually in straight, eased final 200M.

Fast into stride, sent forward to take the early lead, headed near 900M, positioned a length behind the leader on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter, eased 150M. (Lost right front plate.)

Shifted in at start and bumped, raced at rear, detached from field after passing 1100M, eased near 900M. (Jockey reported his horse did not feel comfortable in its action in the early stages.) (See Racing Incidents.)
Sent forward to take the rail and lead, was challenged all the way in the straight but held on to score by a head.
Rolled forward and obtained the box-seat, battled on gamely and pushed the winner all the way to the line.
Niggled along to be in midfield, 4-1/2L behind along the rail, ran on nicely and threatened the 2nd late.
Settled to race in midfield, 4-3/4L behind 2 wide, saved ground and ran on nicely along the inside rail.
Bumped start, and then raced at the rear along the rail, 5L behind at the exit, made ground and ran on fairly.
Awkward start, recovered to be in front of midfield, 3 wide with partial cover, one paced but continued on.
Pushed to settled in one-off one-back position, found no extra near 150M.
Bumped start then slotted into midfield, 3 wide but with cover, one paced.
Sat towards the rear and remained 2 wide throughout, did not save ground.
Raced in midfield, stayed 2-3 wide until assumed 2 wide position at home turn, never threatened.
Just in front of midfield, sat 2 wide throughout, flattened at 350M.
Sat towards the rear, 3 wide with cover, did not feature.
Failed to muster and settled in midfield, wide and without cover, wasn't in it.
Sat outside the lead, gave ground from on straightening and finished tailed out. Must trail.

Shifted out at start and bumped, sent forward to race prominently on rail, allowed the rival to cross near 1000M, sat right behind the leader on turn, finished off very strongly in straight to score easily.

Jumped with them, sent forward to take the lead, found the rail near 1000M, travelled well throughout, kept on well early in straight, headed near 150M, slightly weakened thereafter, just stayed on to take 2nd.
Began well from gate 12, unable to slot in, raced 4 wide at rear, no cover throughout, closer on turn, made very good progress in straight to take 3rd.
Jumped well from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, 6 to 7 lengths back, closer on turn, but still 5 lengths back, kept to inside after straightening and made some progress.
Taken back from gate 10, raced 3 wide at rear, 4 to 5 lengths back, there to turn, made some progress in straight without threatening.
Average to begin, positioned 3 wide, 2 lengths back, no cover after passing 1000M, similar position on turn, failed to quicken in straight. (Blood in trachea.)
Jumped well from the widest draw, unable to slot in early, taken back to race at rear, 6 to 7 lengths back, same margin back on turn, taken very wide in straight and passed a few tired runners.
Jumped well, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, showed limited response in straight.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide at rear, 5 lengths back, same margin back on turn, taken wide early in straight, only showed little response.
Began well from a wide draw, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, there to turn, failed to close off in straight.
Jumped well from gate 9, unable to slot in early, sent forward after passing 1200M to race in 2nd, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.

Slowly away, recovered to race 4 to 5 lengths back on rail, saved ground on turn, failed to close off in straight, eased near 100M. (Blood in trachea.) (Lost left front plate near 1450M and right front plate near 1150M.)
Bumped start, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths back, there to turn, weakened gradually in straight, eased after passing 200M. (Lost left front plate at start.)
Jumped well, restrained in the 4th spot 3Ls off leader, quickened up strongly when asked 400M, led inside 200M, drew away towards the line for hat trick of wins.
A bit slow away, took up the running from 1500M, led uncontested, kept going well turning in, no match when winner loomed 200M, held 2nd comfortably.
Chased leader along the fence, shifted out early straight to continue forward, stayed on for 3rd without threatening top 2. (Jockey dropped whip 200M.)
Bumped after the jump and got badly unbalanced, in 2nd place chasing the pace, hung in under pressure early straight, lacked a strong finishing kick, outsprinted by first 2, kept on mildly for 4th.
Checked on jumping, held up behind midfield 4-5Ls off the pace, tried hard in the straight but couldn't get closer to leaders.
Failed to muster speed despite ridden along, ended up towards the rear 6Ls behind leader, couldn't quicken up passing 400M, ran on same pace to line.
Taken back from wide barrier, settled down 6Ls back near last, couldn't muster the pace to challenge.
Held up behind mid-division, 4Ls off leader at 400M, plodded home, never involved.
Not hurried after the start, settled 3-wide in rear, brought wide home but failed to finish off.
Ridden along early stages but failed to muster, ended up 3-wide behind midfield, under serious pressure 500M, dropped away early straight.
Never far off on the rail, hit the front under pressure 300 metres out, soon drew clear for a comfortable victory.
Settled in midfield, wide into straight, ran on to grab 2nd over 50 metres out.
Attempted to make all, led until headed inside the 300 metres.
Slow to begin, settled behind midfield on the rail, made moderate progress for remote 4th under hands and heels riding. (Jockey said horse not comfortable with track condition.)
Well there niggling along, drifted back to 4th over 2L back rounding home bend, ran home one-paced.
Slow to begin, soon recovered to midfield along the rail, forced to steady 800 metres out but saved ground entering straight, soon found no extra.
Jumped fairly from a wide gate, settled wide in 5th about 3L off the pace, remained wide turning for home, found nothing under pressure.
Recovered quickly out wide from a moderate start improving to 2nd approaching the home bend, weakened under pressure soon after straightening.
Began from a wide gate, settled just worse than midfield wide without cover, taken further back rounding home bend, ran home one-paced.
Soon dropped to last few despite ridden early, made no impression in the straight.
Broke well settling just off the pace, shuffled over 3L back in forward of midfield rounding home bend, weakened under pressure in the straight. (Mucus in trachea)
Slow to begin, always in last few despite ridden along 1000 metres out, dropped out home bend.
Always in last few, dropped out in straight.
Towards the rear, dropped out into straight.
Pressed forward early to settle 3rd, 3 wide with no cover. Loomed up to lead 250m. Kicked clear late under hands and heels and was easing on the line.
Taken up early to sit 4th on the fence. Couldn't kick with winner when he went clear, but stayed on strongly in the straight to be a clear 2nd.
Fairly away, then bumped and unbalanced on jumping. Recovered to settle midfield. Stayed close to the rails and stayed on solidly to hold 3rd late.
Eased away and settled worse than midfield. Ran on strongly in the straight. No threat for a place, but was making up steady ground on 3rd.
Cruised forward early to settle around midfield. Stayed on solidly in the straight and made up some ground.
Bumped and unbalanced on jumping. Initially sat around midfield early, before dropping back to be a clear last. Widest in the straight and ran solidly to claim more than half the field late.
Bumped on jumping and hampered shortly after. Settled around midfield. Only fair in the straight and was no threat. Jockey questioned.
Dropped back early from the wide draw to settle towards the rear of the field. Battled on gamely in the straight, but no threat.
Pushed out early to lead. Gave nothing in the straight, and dropped out quickly from 250m.
Pushed out early to sit just forward of midfield. Only battled away fairly early in the straight, before being awkwardly placed on heels at 200m. Eased out late.
Taken forward early to settle just forward of midfield, 1 off the fence. Steadied off heels at 200m, but only battled away 1 paced in the straight and eased out late.
Pushed forward early to sit 2nd, on the leaders flank. Dropped out very quickly in the straight. Jockey questioned. Vet- roarer.
Began awkwardly and dropped back from the wide draw to sit at the rear of the field. Raced was run by the 150m and not pushed out late.
Cruised forward early to sit midfield and was stuck 4-5 wide with no cover. Gave nothing in the straight and was eased a long way from home.

Restrained after the jump, guided to a midfield position along the rail, picked up well to join leaders 300M, showed battling qualities and kept responding to pressure, just prevailed in a photo finish.

Bustled along to go forward in a fast run race, led passing 1000M and given breather home turn, joined by rivals both sides early straight, dug deep and vied for lead to the line, just touched off at the post.
Began well from draw 1, chased leaders in a fast run race, shifted out into clear 500M, loomed a strong threat, joined leaders 350M, fought on well, held over final 50M.
From wide draw shifted across behind runners early stages, held up in rear pair, brought wide 600M, stayed on well to go 4th passing 200M, tried hard but couldn't reel in first 3.
Dropped back to rear, pace fast early and 8Ls back at one stage, guided to outside 600M, ran on moderately down outside, not reach leaders.
Began only fairly, held up behind midfield 5Ls off the pace, stayed on mildly in the straight, no impression on leaders.
Went forward, crossed to the rail before home turn tracking the pace, outsprinted by rivals entering straight, plodded home.
Failed to muster speed despite vigorously ridden early stages, settled towards the rear, ran past one paced horses in the straight only. (Bled / Lame RF leg.)
Held up 3-wide in mid-division, couldn't finish off when asked.
Away well, restrained to be 4Ls off the pace in midfield, didn't respond under pressure, soon out of contention.
Never far off within 3Ls of leader, shifted wider 500M, failed to pick up entering straight.
Dropped back to race behind midfield, weakened turning home, never threatened.
Assumed running in midfield, caught 4 wide without cover from 900M, failed to muster the pace to challenge leaving the bend, never involved.
3-wide no cover chasing leaders, dropped right away entering straight, finished tailed out. (Unacceptable Performance.)

Began well from gate 1, sent forward to race prominently, 3 away from the stands rail, kept on very well final 400M but just couldn't hold off the winner.
Began fairly, raced closer to the middle of the track, 1 to 2 lengths back, kept on well to take 3rd.
Jumped well, raced behind lead on the stand side, kept on evenly to the line.
Began well, raced prominently near to the stands rail, kept on well until passing 200M, slightly weakened thereafter, just missed frame on line.
Jumped well, showed good speed to take the lead on the stands rail, peaked and headed after passing 400M, raced tight near 300M, difficult to ride thereafter, weakened close home.
Bumped start, positioned on the stands rail, 2 lengths or so back, raced tight after passing 400M, failed to make any progress in the concluding stages.
Average to begin, showed no early speed, raced at tail, still 8 lengths back at 400M, make little progress after passing 200M.
Began awkwardly and bumped, raced at rear near to the stands rail, made no progress final 400M.
Jumped with them, sent forward to race prominently, 2 away from the stands rail, weakened from 400M, eased after passing 150M.
Behind midfield along the fence, benefited by the fast pace, progressed steadily 300M to score.
Settled in front of midfield, 2 wide, closed off well for 2nd.
Box seat, not suited by the fast pace, held ground for 3rd.
Pushed to take rail and led at fast sectionals, hung on well until 200M flattened.
At back, took rail, benefited by the fast pace, progressed steadily 300M.
At back, trapped 3-4 wide, suited by the fast pace, ran on ok.
Pushed forward, sat 2 wide, harmed by the fast tempo, weakened in straight.
Eased at start, benefited by the fast pace, blocked and checked 300M, ran on fairly when clear.
Failed to muster, on heels early, at back 2-4 wide, suited by the fast pace, no progress.
Trapped wide 3 wide throughout, emptied in straight.
Raced behind midfield on rail, responded well in the straight, quickened passing 200M to score.
Taken back at start, asked for effort near 550M, made ground passing 200M, finished strongly.
Approaching 1100M was crowded for room then raced tight, widest on straightening, made up some nice late ground.
Ridden along to take lead, fought hard entire straight, gave ground passing 50M.
Sat box seat, under pressure but only one-paced.
Settled behind leaders, gave ground passing 150M. Blood trachea.
Began awkwardly, then urged along to settle outside the lead, weakened near 200M.
Bumped on jumping, raced 2 to 3 wide with cover in midfield, 3 lengths back, finished off very strongly in straight to score narrowly.

Average to begin, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, moved closer along the rail on turn, hit the front near 200M, kept on strongly thereafter, but just couldn't hold off the winner on line.

Bumped start and unbalanced, sent forward to race prominently, 1 out 1 back on turn, showed good response early in straight, peaked near 150M, inconvenienced near 75M, ran on to take 3rd. (Jockey dropped right rein 200M.)
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide better than midfield, similar position onturn, finished off evenly instraight.
Began well from gate 1, positioned on rail inmidfield, 4 lengths or so back, saved ground on turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 4 to 5 lengths back, similar position on turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Jumped well from gate 2, sent forward to take the lead, shared lead with rival on turn, peakedearly in straight, weakened from final 200M.
Bumped start, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, shared lead on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened from 300M, eased late.
Began well from a tricky gate, unable to slot in, travelled 3 wide and without cover, 2 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, no extra gear in straight and weakened gradually.
Began fairly, raced 2 wide, 7 to 8 lengths back at rear, found rail on turn, made no progress in straight.
Slowly away, raced at tail, 8 to 9 lengths back, still well back on turn, raced tight near 400M, finished off one-paced in straight.
Began awkwardly and bumped, raced 3 wide at rear, 8 lengths back, made no progress in straight.
Bumped on jumping, raced at rear, 8 to 9 lengths back, checked near 850M, last turning in, finished off one-paced in straight.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced 2 wide, 7 lengths or so back, there to turn, showed no response in straight, eased final 150M.
Moderately away from gate 9, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, travelled well throughout, kept on very well in straight and scored.
Began well, raced in midfield, 3 to 4 lengths back, saved ground on turn, angled out after passing 500M, finished off very strongly to take 2nd.
Jumped well, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well throughout, kept on well after turning in, headed near 150M, slightly weakened thereafter, just stayed on for 3rd.
Began awkwardly and bumped, positioned 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, easy run on turn, kept on well in straight to make frame without threatening.
Crowded on jumping, positioned on rail behind midfield, 5 to 6 lengths back, same position on turn, made some progress in straight without threatening.
Away with them, took the 1 out 1 back position, checked off heels near 950M, similar position on turn, peaked early in straight, just kept on evenly to the line.
Bumped start, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, angled out early in straight, finished off evenly.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide at rear, 7 lengths back, wider from 600M, made some headway in straight.
Taken back from gate 12, raced at rear on rail, 7 to 8 lengths back, there to turn, made little progress in straight.
Crowded on jumping, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 5 lengths back, same position on turn, failed to make any progress in straight.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, 9 lengths back, still last turning in, failed to close off in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 3 wide at rear, 7 lengths back, 2 wide from near 700M, showed nothing in straight.
Jumped with them, made contact early, raced 2 wide better than midfield, crowded near 950M, 3 lengths or so back on turn, emptied early in straight.
Settled in front of midfield, 2-1/2L off 2 wide, kicked away at 250M, held on late to score.
In about midfield, 3-1/4L behind 2 wide, continued on very nicely and held off challenge for 2nd.
Sat just behind midfield, 5-1/4L behind along the rail, saved ground and battled on to the line.
Urged forward, found the rail and raced in the box-seat after 800M, kept on one paced to the line.
Raced in midfield, 4-1/2L behind along the rail, made ground and ran on.
Reared and missed the start, at the rear 8-1/4L behind 2 wide, improved slightly.
Sent forward to take rail and led, headed passing 300M, faded thereafter.
In behind midfield, wide and without cover from 800M, did not improve.
Failed to muster and raced towards the rear, found nothing in the straight.
At the rear along the rail, not competitive.
Settled outside the lead, weakened at home turn and finished tailed out. Must trial.
Slightly slow out, settled in last few of the small field about 3L off the pace, switched right for a clear run 400 metres out, ran on under pressure to just get up on line.
Settled just off the pace, came under pressure coming onto course proper, hit the front momentarily passing the 100 metres, soon outsprinted.
Never far off, held every chance 200 metres out, but unable to sustain effort nearing finish.
Broke well from a low draw, soon led and crossed to stands rail, inclined to lay in 200 metres out, unable to sustain effort and swamped inside the final 100 metres.
Settled just off the pace, came under pressure inside the final 400 metres, faded close to home.
Began well, settled just off the pace on stands rail, awkwardly placed behind the leader over 400 metres out, one-paced closing stages.
Moderate start, jostled jumping out before settling just off the pace, fading when hampered and lost position 300 metres out, never recovered despite reminders.
Crowded at start, always struggling at the back, tailed-off under pressure.
Eased back from wide barrier, settled down 2nd last, pulled widest on straightening, closed off fastest from mid-straight , took lead inside 100M and always holding off runner up in the run home.
Dropped back to be last of 8, 6Ls off the pace in middle stages, crept closer from 600M, ran on well under top weight over an inadequate trip and only just held at the finish. Clear from remainders.
Shaken up early to be disputing the lead along the rail, fought on well turning home, headed by first 2 passing 100M, hung on for 3rd.
Settled down 6th of 8 towards the rear of the field, 3-4Ls to make up 400M, closed off mildly for non-threatening 4th.
Held up 3Ls behind leaders, brought wide 500M, closed off fairly without threat to first 2.
Hampered at the start, moved up to be vying for the lead on the outside, fought neck to neck with leader until weakening over final 150M.
Close up chasing the race, couldn't go on with leaders passing 400M. (Jockey : saddle shifted back slightly causing some inconvenience during race)

Vied for early lead, eased off to track leaders passing 850M, under heavy pressure from 500M, gave ground abruptly despite being ridden. (Jockey : may not have appreciated being ridden in a more forward position.)
Bumped start, raced 2 wide in midfield, angled out for a run turning in, finished off very strongly to score.
Average to begin, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, kept to inside early in straight, angled out near 200M, closed off well to take 2nd.
Shifted out at start and bumped, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, awkwardly placed off heels near 900M, saved ground on turn, kept on well in straight to get 3rd.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide, a length or so back, same position on turn, kept on evenly in straight.
Hampered at start, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, 3 to 4 lengths back on turn, made some progress in straight without threatening.
Hampered start, raced at tail, 6 lengths back, moved closer in the middle stages, very wide turning in, made minor progress in straight.
Shifted out at start, sent forward to take the lead, challenged on turn, kept on well early in straight, weakened gradually final 200M.
Crowded on jumping, raced 3 wide in midfield, no cover on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Began well from the widest draw, sent forward to race prominently, challenged the leader on turn, peaked early in straight, crowded near 200M, weakened thereafter.
Slightly slow out and bumped, positioned 5 lengths back on rail, same margin back on turn, showed nothing in straight.

Shifted out at start and made contact, raced 2 wide at rear, bumped near 1000M, 4 to 5 lengths back on turn, failed to make any progress in straight. (Jockey reported his horse did not feel comfortable in its action.)
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, 7 lengths back, still last turning in, taken widest after passing 300M, finished off very strongly to score by a nose.

Taken back from gate 13, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, 5 lengths or so back, taken wider turning in, showed very good response in straight, took the lead near 50M, but couldn't hold off the rival on line.

Average to begin, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, angled out after passing 500M, showed very good response in straight, took the lead near 200M, kept on well thereafter, just couldn't hold off the first two late.

Slightly slow out, raced 2 wide at rear, 6 lengths back, still 4 lengths or so back turning in, angled out early in straight, finished off well when clear final 150M, good debut. (Rider dropped right rein 350M.)
Began fairly, raced 4 wide at rear for the majority of the race, taken very wide in straight and finished off well.
Began well, positioned on rail in midfield, 2 lengths or so back, saved ground to 500M, made some progress early in straight, outpaced closing stages.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide better than midfield, 3 wide turning in, finished off evenly in straight.
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned on rail at rear, moved closer along the rail on turn, no clear running early in straight, made minor progress when clear final 150M.

Average to begin, raced 2 wide in midfield, difficult to settle near 1100M, 3 to 4 lengths back on turn, angled out near 500M, no daylight early in straight, but only finished off one pace when clear thereafter.
Fastest into stride, raced prominently but wide, no cover throughout, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Began fairly from a wide draw, unable to slot in, trapped 3 wide and without cover, 2 lengths back, wider turning in, kept on evenly early in straight, weakened gradually from 250M.
Away with them, sent forward to race prominently, allowed rival to cross after passing 1000M, 2 wide on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Began only fairly, sent forward to take the lead, found rail after passing 1000M, peaked after turning in, headed near 200M, weakened thereafter.

Jumped well, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, challenged the leader turning in, took the lead near 200M, kept on strongly to the line.
Away with them, positioned 3 to 4 lengths back on rail, saved ground throughout, kept to inside after straightening and finished off well to take 2nd.
Began well from gate 1, sat a length or so behind the leader on rail, easy run to turn, angled out near 350M, finished off evenly in straight.
Began awkwardly, raced at rear, 5 lengths back, same margin back on turn, taken wide in straight and made good progress to be nearest on line.
Taken back to race at tail, 6 lengths back, closer on turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Jumped with them, positioned 2 wide, 3 lengths or so back, there to turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Began fairly, unable to slot in, 3 to 4 wide early, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths back after passing 1200M, similar positon on turn, weakened in straight, eased final 100M.
Out in line, sent forward to race prominently, took the lead near 1200M, led by half length, challenged by rival near 400M, weakened gradually in straight. (Jockey dropped whip near 250M.)
Eased at start, took rail, harmed by the slow pace, unleashed strong finishing efforts 300M and scored.
Hard ridden to secure box seat, benefited by the slow tempo, ran on well for 2nd.
Hard ridden to take rail and led at advantageous slow sectionals, hung on well until 100M overhauled, ran on for 3rd.
Behind midfield, trapped 3-4 wide, harmed by the slow pace, dashed strongly 300M, run ended 100M.
Bumped start, took rail in midfield, held up 4-2, dashed well when clear despite not suited by the slow pace.
Pushed forward, sat 2 wide, ran on well until 150M weakened.
Eased at start, took cover, not suited by the slow pace, held up and checked 200M, not tested.
Eased early, trapped 3-4 wide in front of midfield, emptied 200M.
Bumped start, failed to muster, 2-3 wide at back, no dash.
Hard ridden forward, sat 2 wide, dropped off quickly 400M.
Settled at rear, widest on straightening, made impressive ground passing 150M to score.
Ridden along to take lead, asked for effort on straightening, responded solidly in the straight.
Raced at back, gradually made ground in the straight, finished nicely.
Raced midfield, made Home Turn awkwardly, gained some ground passing 100M.
Settled behind midfield, near 800M was checked away from heels, near 250M checked again then held up for running until near 200M, made some ground passing 150M.
Urged along after start, raced at handy position, one-paced in the straight.
Raced behind midfield, after 700M was left racing wide and without cover, wide on straightening, one-paced. Rider questioned.
Settled box seat, weakened passing 150M.
Travelled midfield on rail, no response in the straight.
Began only fairly then lost ground when crowded for room, failed to make impression, must trial.
Began well from gate 1, positioned 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, easy run to turn, kept to inside after straightening and finished off very strongly to score.
Jumped with them, sent forward to sit a length behind the leader on rail, travelled well throughout, kept on very well in straight, just narrowly beaten.
Began well, sent forward to take the lead, enjoyed the easy lead throughout, kept on well in straight but couldn't hold off the first two late, checked close home.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide at rear, difficult to settle early, awkwardly placed near 850M, very wide turning in, made good progress in straight to make frame. (See Racing Incidents.)
Bumped start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, awkwardly placed near 150M, 4 lengths back on turn, made some headway in straight.
Began well, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 to 4 lengths back, there to turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Taken back from gate 9, positioned 6 lengths behind the leader on rail, same position on turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Away with them, positioned on rail in midfield, 4 lengths or so back, saved ground on turn, finished off one-paced in straight.

Jumped well from a middle draw, raced 3 wide better than midfield early, slightly improved after entering the back straight to take a 2 wide spot, a length or so back on turn, weakened early in straight.
Began very awkwardly and made contact with rival, raced at tail throughout, never seen with a chance.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide in midfield, 4 lengths back, same position on turn, finished off very strongly in straight and scored.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide behind midfield, hard ridden on turn, made very good progress in straight to take 2nd.
Jumped well from a wide draw, sent forward to take the lead, enjoyed the easy lead throughout, kept on very well in straight, just couldn't hold off the first two late.
Away with them, raced 2 wide at rear, 7 lengths back, still well back on turn, finished off strongly in straight to be nearest on line.
Average to begin, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, similar positon on turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Taken back from gate 9, raced at tail, 8 to 9 lengths back, still well back on turn, made some headway in straight.
Average to begin, raced at rear on rail, awkwardly placed near 1200M, still 6 lengths back turning in, finished off evenly in straight.
Began fairly, positioned on rail in midfield, there to turn, finished off one-paced in straight.
Out in line, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, there to turn, kept on evenly early in straight, weakened after passing final 200M.
Began well, sat 2 lengths behind the leader, saved ground throughout, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Niggled along to take the rail and led, continued on all the way to score by 3/4L.
Rolled forward to be in front of midfield, 3L behind 2 wide, continued on nicely and held off a late challenge for 2nd.
In front of midfield along the rail, 3-3/4L behind, closed off nicely but just short in a late challenge for 2nd.
Asked to be in midfield, 4-1/2L behind and wide plus without cover, closed off well inside final 100M.
Crowded start, settled in midfield 4-3/4L behind 2 wide, closed off fairly to the line.
Stumbled at start but recovered to take the box-seat, kept on until the 100M. (Rider questioned)
Bumped start and then took cover in behind midfield, 7-1/4L behind 2 wide, made ground.
Sent forward and sat outside the lead, emptied when passing the 200M.
Eased back and raced at the tail, did not improve in the straight.
Bumped start and then taken back, remained at the rear and did not threaten.
Just behind midfield along the rail, returned as bleeder and was displaying an irregular heart rhythm.
Settled in midfield from a wide gate, one of the widest turning for home, quickened well to take command over 100 metres out.
Jumped well and ridden early, settled over 3L back in 4th, shaken up upon straightening and bumped 300 metres out, fought on steadily to reach 2nd final stages.
Soon took up running setting a standard pace, led the field until finding no extra inside the final 200 metres.
Taken back from the widest gate, trailed the field until home turn, finished off the race well.
Broke well, settled over 2L back in 3rd on the rail, saved ground to gain 2nd spot turning for home, found nothing under pressure.

Moderate start and failed to muster early stages, gained slightly closer from last few in back straight to reach 7th some 6L back at the Rock, switched out off heels for a run early in straight, kept on without quickening.
Moderate start, always in last few and never seen with a chance.
Moderate start, settled towards the rear on the rail, switched wide for a run entering straight, found nothing under pressure.
Pressed forward from a wide draw, travelled 2-wide alongside the 3rd just off the pace, weakened badly after straightening.
Slightly slow out, settled in forward of midfield in 5th on the rail, about 5L off the pace far side, slightly close up saving ground on home turn, dropped out under pressure after straightening.
Slightly slow out, raced wide without cover and never better than midfield, came under pressure on the bend but dropped away quickly inside the final 400 metres.
Restrained after the start, towards rear 5Ls off the slow pace, brought wide 450M, charged home strongly to get up last stride.
Held up in mid-division 3Ls off the slow pace, quickened up well to take lead near 50M, headed by winner last stride.
Away smoothly and led slowly, fought on well entering straight, headed by first 2 near 50M, hung on for 3rd.
Tracked leaders along the fence in a slowly run race, kept grinding to the line but always held by leaders in the run home.
Dropped back from draw 11, at the rear 6Ls off the pace middle stages, stayed on well final 250M to be nearest at the line.
Restrained to be racing towards the rear of midfield, 3-wide trip, stayed on moderately final 300M.
Always in touch, had every chance turning in, one paced final 150M.
Held up midfield, lost place 550M and got shuffled back, stayed on mildly in the run home but never dangerous.
Began awkwardly, settled down in last place 6Ls off the slow pace, ran on without threatening over final 300M.
Began fairly, urged forward to be outside of leader, outpaced 200M and out of contention. (Jockey unable to offer any explanation for the disappointing performance.)
Driven forward from draw 10, chased leaders in a 3-wide position without cover, struggled to keep up 500M, soon weakened on straightening.
