Jumped well from gate 1, quickly moved to the stands side and led, travelled well throughout, kept on very well final 400M to score.
Began well, raced closer to the middle of the track, 1 to 2 lengths back, slightly improved in the middle stages, kept on well to take 2nd without posing much of a threat to the winner.
Slightly slow out and crowded, raced behind midfield, 2 to 3 away from the stands rail, made some progress final 400M to take a place.
Quickly into stride, raced prominently on the stands rail, kept on well until peaked near 200M, weakened gradually thereafter. (Roarer.)
Bumped shortly after start and unbalanced, raced at rear nearer to the middle of the track, difficult to ride throughout, made some headway final 400M without threatening.
Began well, raced 2 lengths behind close to the stands rail, made some progress final 400M without threatening the first few.
Jumped with them, sent forward to race prominently early, sat 2 away from the stands rail, a length back in the middle stages, failed to make any progress final 400M.
Slowly away, raced at tail, still 6 lengths or so back at 400M, passed a few tired horses in the final furlong.
Bumped shortly after start, positioned a length behind the leader nearer to the middle of the track, failed to quicken near 400M, weakened gradually thereafter. (Lost left front plate near 600M.)
Jumped well, raced prominently on the stands side, peaked in the middle stages, weakened gradually final 400M.
Began fairly from gate 2, raced nearer to the middle of the track, 2 lengths back, peaked near 400M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Slowly away, raced at rear on the stands rail early, gradually moved to the middle of the track after passing 550M, weakened from 300M, eased final 100M.
Pushed to take rail and lead, clocked very slow sectionals, made all.
Eased back, harmed by the slow pace, unleashed strong finishing efforts 300M for 2nd.
Eased to take box seat, benefited by the slow tempo, ran on well for 3rd.
Sat outside the leader, favoured by the slow sectionals, no dash in straight.
At back 2 wide, harmed by the slow pace, never improved.
Urged to settle outside the lead, made good ground in the straight, finished strongly to score.
Ridden to take lead, travelled comfortably, responded solidly in the straight. Just missed by SH.
Taken back at start, gradually gained ground in the straight, worked home nicely.
Began only fairly, raced behind midfield, crowded for room near 900M, widest on straightening, made up some nice late ground.
Raced at rear, approaching 1100M travelled keenly, responded well in the straight, awkwardly placed near finishing line and not able to be ridden out.
Travelled midfield, near 900M lay out, passing 800M was taken wider then was left racing wide and without cover, gave ground passing 100M.
Began only fairly, settled behind midfield, one-paced.
Raced midfield on rail, weakened near 200M, failed to run on.

Bumped start, sent forward to race prominently, allowed the rival to cross near 900M, sat right behind the leader to 600M, challenged the leader turning in, kicked clear early in straight, kept on well to hold off the challenger late.
Bumped start, taken back to race at tail, 7 lengths back, still last turning in, kept to inside after straightening and finished off very strongly to take 2nd, nearest on line.
Jumped well, positioned 2 to 3 lengths back on rail, moved closer along the rail on turn, angled out early in straight, kept on evenly in straight to take 3rd without threatening the first two.

Slightly slow out, positioned on rail in midfield, travelled keenly when awkwardly placed after passing 1200M, continued to over-race until angled out near 950M, 2LS back on turn, wider 500M, finished off evenly in straight.
Taken back to race 2 to 3 wide with cover at rear, 7 lengths back, moved a little bit closer on turn, taken widest in straight and made some progress.
Bumped shortly after start, raced 3 wide behind midfield, 4 to 5 lengths back, there to turn, finished off evenly.
Shifted out at start and bumped, hard ridden for some distance to race wide in midfield, no cover throughout, moved closer on turn, peaked early in straight, ran on one pace.
Began only fairly, raced at rear on rail, 6 lengths back, moved closer along the rail on turn, weakened early in straight, eased late.

Began fairly from the widest draw, sent forward to race prominently, took the lead after passing 1000M, found rail near 900M, challenged by rivals turning in, headed and weakened early in straight, dropped off tamely thereafter.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide better than midfield, carried wider after passing 600M, 3 wide turning in, emptied early in straight, eased final 150M.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide in midfield, inconvenienced near 900M, 5 lengths back on turn, showed nothing in straight, eased final 200M. (Jockey concerned over the horse's action.)
Clean jump, sent forward to take the lead, found rail near 800M, travelled well on turn, kept on strongly in straight and scored.
Out in line, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground throughout, no daylight early in straight, bumped near 200M, finished off well thereafter to take 2nd.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 3 lengths or so back on turn, made good progress in straight to take 3rd, nearest on line.
Shifted out at start and bumped, raced 2 wide in midfield, closer on turn, finished off evenly in straight to make frame.
Crowded out start, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, 3 to 4 lengths back on turn, wider from 500M, made some progress early in straight, peaked near 150M, kept on evenly to the line.

Shifted out at start and bumped, positioned 4 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground throughout, kept to inside early in straight, angled out after passing 300M, made minor progress thereafter.

Jumped with them, sent forward to race prominently, allowed the rival to cross near 800M, sat right behind the leader on turn, peaked early in straight, bumped near 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Away with them, raced 3 wide in midfield, 3 lengths back, there to turn, failed to close off in straight.
Moderately away from a wide draw, taken back to race at tail, 5 lengths back on turn, taken wide in straight, made no progress.
Jumped with them, sent forward to race prominently but wide, no cover throughout, emptied early in straight, eased final 150M.
At the rear throughout, switched widest on straightening, continued to improve and closed off strongly to score.
Pushed to be prominent, wide and without cover however, closed off very well but had to settle for 2nd.
Obtained the lead in the 2 wide with ease, headed passing 100M, ran on for 3rd but was no match.
Niggled along to obtain the box-seat, ran on fairly to the line.
Sent forward, took rail and sat inside the lead, continued on one paced.
Bumped start, in worse than midfield 2-3 wide, only past tired runners.
Jumped only fairly, sat towards the rear along the rail, one paced.
Failed to muster and then travelled wide and without cover, did not run on late.
Awkward start then sat slightly in front of midfield, wasn't competitive.
Sluggish at start, travelled in last few on the rail, angled out for a run entering straight, responded well to hit the front inside the 200 metres, just fended off runner-up's strong late challenge.
Taken back to the rear from the widest gate, trailed the field into straight, obtained a clear run 300 metres out, quickened well to issue serious challenges but unable to peg back the winner.

Travelled wide in midfield early stages, settled behind midfield for rails run after the first 400M, commenced move on top of home bend, quickened under pressure to hit the front momentarily 200 metres out and soon headed.

Ridden early, 3-wide just off the pace before taken back for rails run in 6th within about 3L back, travelling well when forced to steady behind runners and switch 300 metres out, kept on well to the line.
Broke well, settled not far off in 4th or 5th to straight, came to challenge under pressure upon straightening, tightened briefly 200 metres out, kept on well to the line.
Raced wide in last few from a wide gate, remained well back and wide into straight, produced good late impression down the centre of the track, did best work late.
Began fairly and ridden along, steadily picked up to one back position on the rail, baulked for a run most of way in straight.

With leaders 2-wide, disputed lead rounding the home bend, gained slender advantage entering straight, unable to sustain effort & swamped inside the final 200M. (Questioned for disappointing performance) (Blood in trachea)
Held slender lead early stages, joined rounding home bend and narrowly headed into straight, fought on under pressure until swamped inside the final 200 metres. (Tactic questioned)
Began well from a wide gate, travelled wide without cover in 3rd most of the way to the straight, weakened under pressure. (Tactic questioned)
Soon led from draw 1 sharing the lead in a slowly run race, driven 1L clear 300M, challenged by runner up late but held on well.
Began awkwardly, held up in midfield, chased winner strongly from 200M, just held.
Settled down 2-wide in midfield, switched wide on bend over 500M out, stayed on moderately to go 3rd near 50M, not reached first 2.
Shared lead 2-wide in a slowly run race, raced keenly, always held by winner when driven out in the straight, kept on same pace final 200M, lost 3rd near 50M.
Tracked leaders along the fence in a slowly run race, driven out 450M but couldn't muster the pace to challenge leaders, no threat passing 200M.
Steadied early stages to obtain cover, held up towards the rear, took time to get going in the straight, did best work late.
Tracked leading pair in a slowly run race, in a striking position turning in, tried hard but ran on only one paced under pressure.
Dropped back to the rear from a wide barrier, brought wide into straight, stayed on only fairly, never close enough to challenge.
Slowly into stride, in the rear pair about 7Ls off the pace on settling, failed to make any progress turning home.
Eased back after the start, settled towards the rear 5Ls off the slow pace, plodded home only, finished near the tail.
Held up 2-wide ahead of midfield, failed to respond to urgings passing 400M, never a threat.
Away with them, taken back to race at rear, 6 lengths back, saved ground on turn, angled out in straight and finished off very strongly to score.

Bumped on jumping, positioned 2 lengths or so back in 3rd, there to turn, showed very good response early in straight, took the lead near 250M, kept on well thereafter, just couldn't hold off the winner late.
Bumped shortly after start, raced wide with no cover in 4th, 3 lengths back, same position on turn, finished off well in straight to take 3rd.
Bumped start, positioned 4 lengths back on rail, saved ground on turn, finished off evenly in straight to make frame without threatening.
Began well from the widest draw, unable to slot in early, raced very wide with no cover behind midfield, carried very wide turning in, made up some ground but set too great a task.
Bumped start and unbalanced, raced 2 wide at rear, angled out near 500M, blocked near 400M, made some progress when clear thereafter.
Slightly slow out and inconvenienced, raced very wide at rear, 8 lengths back on turn, made minor progress in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Shifted out at start and bumped, raced 3 wide in midfield, 3 to 4 lengths back, similar position on turn, failed to quicken in straight.
Average to begin, raced wide with cover at rear, hard ridden on turn but still 11 lengths back, failed to close off in straight.
Slightly slow out, recovered to race 2 wide in midfield, crowded near 500M, weakened early in straight. (Lame left front leg next day.)
Moderately away from gate 1, sent forward to race prominently, peaked early in straight, weakened and eased thereafter. (Irregular heart rhythm.) (Blood in trachea.)
Jumped with them, sent forward to race prominently, duel with rival for the rail, emptied early in straight, finished tailed out. (See Racing Incidents.)
Clean jump, positioned 2 wide, 3 lengths or so back, wider after passing 600M, finished off very strongly in straight to score by 2 lengths.
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground to near 600M, 2 wide turning in, no clear running early in straight, made good progress when clear final 200M to take 2nd.
Slightly slow out and bumped, recovered to race a length or so back in 3rd, got cover on turn, kept on evenly in straight to take a place.

Began awkwardly, raced 3W at rear, 5Ls or so back, bumped a few times near 950M, found rail after passing 550M, kept to inside after straightening but unable to obtain a clear run, made good progress when clear thereafter to make frame.
Bumped and unbalanced start, recovered to race prominently on rail, shared lead on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed near 150M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide at rear, 4 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, taken wide in straight and made some progress without threatening.

Shifted in at start and bumped, positioned on rail at rear, moved closer along the rail on turn, made some progress early in straight, awkwardly placed shortly passing 200M, finished off one-paced thereafter.
Began well from gate 11, showed early speed to race prominently, 2 wide, shared lead on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Crowded at start, ridden to better than midfield, 2 to 3 wide, peaked turning in, weakened gradually over the final furlong.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 4 wide at rear, bumped a few times near 950M, 6 lengths back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Began well from the widest draw, unable to slot in early, taken back to race very wide at rear, no cover throughout, failed to close off in straight.
Jumped well from the tricky gate, unable to slot in, taken back to race 3 wide behind midfield, carrier wider after passing 600M, emptied early in straight, eased final 150M.

Jumped well, took the lead easily, enjoyed the uncontested lead to turn, kicked clear early in straight, easily scored.
Out in line, raced 2 to 3 wide, 3 lengths back, same margin back on turn, closed off well to take 2nd without posing any threat to the winner. (See Racing Incidents.)
Bumped start, positioned on rail in midfield, 3 lengths or so back, slightly improved along the rail on turn, kept on evenly in straight, just missed 2nd on line.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 4 lengths back, same margin back on turn, finished off evenly.
Bumped start, no early speed, raced 2 wide at rear, 5 to 6 lengths back, there to turn, taken wide in straight and made minor progress.
Began awkwardly, raced at tail, 7 lengths back, still last turning in, failed to quicken in straight.
Began fairly, positioned on rail behind midfield, 5 to 6 lengths back, saved ground on turn, failed to make any progress in straight. (See Racing Incidents.) (Lame left front leg next day.)
Moderately away, sent forward to race in 2nd, a length behind the leader, there to turn, peaked near 400M, weakened gradually in straight, eased after passing final 100M.
Hard ridden to sit in front of midfield, 2-3 wide, dashed well 250M whilst hanging in, just won by a narrow margin.
Hard ridden forward, suited by the slow tempo but trapped 3 wide throughout, dominated 300M, just missed by a narrow margin in last few strides.
Pushed early, at back 2 wide, dashed well 250M despite not suited by the slow pace.
Hard ridden forward, box seat, benefited by the slow tempo, just held ground in straight.
Bumped start, at back, trapped 3 wide, not suited by the slow tempo, dashed well 200M.
Eased at start, took rail at rear, harmed by the slow pace, blocked most straight, not tested.
Hard ridden early but not muster, 2 wide at back, not suited by the slow tempo, dashed fairly.
Hard ridden forward, sat outside the lead, benefited by the slow sectionals, emptied 300M.
Hard ridden to keep up in midfield, 2 wide, harmed by the slow tempo, blocked 4-2 and checked badly, not tested.
Bumped start, eased back, 2 wide, not suited by the slow pace, lack room 4-2, little dash when clear.
Hard ridden to hold the rail in midfield, harmed by the slow pace, held up badly in straight, not tested.
Hard ridden forward, faded 400M.
Settled behind leader, quickened near 200M, worked home strongly to score.
Ridden along from widest gate, raced at handy position, responded solidly in the straight, missed by Neck.
Taken back at start, widest on straightening, made up some nice late ground.
Settled midfield on rail, asked for effort passing 400M, finished nicely.
Taken back at start, commenced to improve passing 450M, responded OK in the straight.
Travelled midfield, one-paced in the straight, awkwardly placed over concluding stages.
Taken back at start, limited response in the straight.
Took lead after start, faded out passing 200M.
Raced behind midfield on rail, weakened passing 100M.
Bumped start, sent forward to take the lead, found rail after passing 800M, enjoyed the easy lead on turn, kept on very well in straight to score.
Away with them, positioned 2 wide, 3 to 4 lengths back, similar position on turn, finished off strongly in straight to take 2nd.
Shifted in at start and bumped, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, there to turn, taken wider after passing 400M, made very good progress in straight to be nearest on line.
Fast into stride, sent forward to race prominently, positioned a length behind the leader on rail turning, kept on evenly to the line. (See Racing Incidents.)
Moderately away, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, same position on turn, angled out near 400M, finished off evenly in straight.
Jumped well from gate 1, positioned 2 to 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground throughout, failed to quicken under pressure in straight.
Taken back to race 4 lengths back at rear, saved ground to 400M, finished off evenly in straight.
Jumped with them, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, there to turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Out in line, raced 4 wide behind midfield, slightly taken back near 700M for a 2 wide spot, 5 lengths back on turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Average to begin, sent forward to race prominently but trapped wide, 2 wide from near 700M, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter, eased final 50M.
Moderately away from the widest draw, unable to slot in, raced very wide with no cover better than midfield, carried wider turning in, weakened gradually in straight.
Began awkwardly, raced at tail throughout, never competitive.
Bumped start and unbalanced, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 4 lengths or so back on turn, improved from 400M, finished off very strongly in straight to score.
Moderately away, positioned 3 lengths or so back on rail, saved ground throughout, angled out after turning in, made good progress in straight to take 2nd.

Average to begin, raced 3 wide with no cover in midfield in the early stages, sent forward to sit outside to the leader after entering the back straight, similar position on turn, stayed on well in straight to take a place.
Slightly slow out, raced 2 wide in midfield, same position on turn, raced tight early in straight, finished off evenly thereafter.

Shifted in at start and bumped, positioned 2 wide at rear, awkwardly placed near 800M, raced 3 wide thereafter, 5 lengths back on turn, taken very wide in straight and made some headway without threatening.
Began well from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground throughout, kept on well early in straight, blocked near 150M, finished off evenly when clear thereafter.
Jumped well, sent forward to take the lead, enjoyed the easy lead to 800M, led by 1/2L on turn, headed near 200M, weakened thereafter.
Taken back from a wide draw, positioned on rail behind midfield, angled out near 700M, 5 to 6 lengths back on turn, difficult to ride and made no progress in straight.
Jumped with them, sent forward to sit 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground throughout, kept on evenly early in straight, weakened final 200M.
Away with them, positioned 2 wide better than midfield, 2 lengths back on turn, weakened gradually in straight.
Crowded on jumping, raced at rear, 10 lengths back, still 7 lengths back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear throughout, showed nothing in straight.
In front of midfield, however wide and without cover, peeled away at 100M and ran on to score by 3/4L.
At the rear and detached in the middle stages, continued to make nice ground, finished 3/4L behind the winner.
Settled to race in front of midfield 2 wide, battled on well inside final 100M to take 3rd.
Raced towards the rear, rounded the turn 3 wide, made ground and closed off fairly.
Sent forward, raced prominently and 2 wide, slight dash at 150M, one paced but ran on.
Pushed forward, attempted to take cover but trapped wide in behind midfield, one paced to the line.
Sent forward to take the rail and led, broke away by 1-1/2L early in the straight but flattened out at 150M.
Taken back to be near the rear, made the turn 2 wide, made ground and closed off to the line.
Raced in midfield throughout, 2 to 3 wide at turn, no extra to keep up at 150M.
Settled in box-seat, looked to be in it until 150M, swamped thereafter.
Jumped only fairly, recovered to be in midfield along the rail, flattened passing 100M.
Began well, settled not far off in 4th or 3rd the rail, one off the pace on the rail turning in, quickened well to hit the front inside the 100 metres, won readily.
Ridden positively, travelled 3-wide in 2nd down back straight, gained closer to the rail 2-wide at the Rock, fought on steadily under pressure without threatening.
Pressed forward to lead, obtained rails run approaching the Rock, held 2L break rounding home bend and into straight, headed by the winner inside the final 100 metres.
Travelled keenly 2-wide in midfield, baulked for a run until the 200 metres, finished off race strongly.
Slightly slow out, settled in last few on the rail, snuck up on inside rounding home bend, made steady headway despite the tight rails run in straight.
Soon dropped to last despite ridden early, trailed the field to straight, finished off race well inside final 200 metres.
Jumped fairly from a wide gate, settled wide in 5thin midfield, one of widest turning for home, quickened under pressure early in straight but unable to sustain effort closer stages.
Jumped fairly, settled in midfield on the rail, saved ground on inside turning for home, did not find much room most of way in straight.
Travelled wide towards the rear, came under pressure rounding home bend, fought on steadily in straight without threatening.
Always in last few, made no impression in straight.
Taken back from a wide gate, came under pressure rounding home bend, widest runner into straight, did nothing.

Broke well sharing early pace, shifted 2 back to joint 3rd and then 4th at the Rock, lost a stride making home turn, gradually weakened in straight. (Jockey reported horse not comfortable in its action)
Crossed to a rail spot passing 1400M, checked 1300M, 3rd chasing leaders, took over 250M, kept on strongly to the line and always holding off the runner-up.
Sent forward, caught wide no cover until 900M, chased leader, ran on well passing 300M but always held by winner.
From draw 12 caught very wide early stages, eased back to race in midfield, swung wide home, stayed on well to be nearest at the line.
Slow to begin, over 7Ls off the pace in rear, picked up well on straightening, awkward placed behind the 3rd near 200M, shifted out and continued on well to the line, narrowed missed 3rd.
Restrained to race near the rear, ran on mildly final 300M but never a serious threat to leaders.
Up with early pace, chased leaders on settling, not going the pace to challenge in straight, faded late.
Slow to begin, held up towards the rear, driven out passing 300M, stayed on moderately between runners.
Eased back after the start, settled down 3-wide towards the rear 7Ls off the pace, wide into straight, stayed on fairly without threatening.
Restrained in mid-division, pushed along nearing 400M, ran home one paced, never threatened.
Raced along the fence in midfield. 4Ls off the pace home turn, not pace to challenge, plodded home.
Dropped back to race in midfield from draw 10 but couldn't get closer than 3-wide, no cover for part of the race, couldn't finish off in the straight.
Began well, proved difficult to settle and led reluctantly, soon weakened turning home, eased 200M.

Jumped well from a wide draw, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, bumped near 400M, showed very good response in straight to score by 2-3/4L.
Moderately away from the widest draw, raced 3 wide, 2 to 3 lengths back, no cover throughout, made good progress final 200M to take 2nd.
Away with them, sat right behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, angled out and bumped near 400M, finished off well but no match to the winner, lost 2nd late.
Bumped and unbalanced start, raced 2 wide, 4 lengths or so back, same position on turn, taken wide in straight and finished off well to make frame.
Bumped on jumping, unbalanced, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, there to turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide at rear, 5 to 6 lengths back, wider turning in, bumped near 250M, kept on evenly to the line.
Slowly away, raced at rear on rail, 6 to 7 lengths back, angled out on turn, bumped near 250M, finished off evenly.
Began well, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well throughout, peaked shortly after turning in, headed near 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Jumped well from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, easy run throughout, failed to quicken in straight.
Crowded on jumping, raced wide at rear, 7 lengths back, no cover on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Crowded out start, raced 5 lengths back on rail, there to turn, showed no response in straight and eased.

Box seat, not suited by the fast tempo, ran on well for 2nd.
At back, 2 wide, benefited by the fast pace, progressed steadily 300M.
Slow away, at rear, 2-3 wide, benefited by the fast pace, made steady ground 250M.
Hard ridden to take rail and lead, not suited by the fast tempo, weakened 250M.
Pressed forward, sat 2 wide, not suited by the fast pace, out of fuel 250M.
Failed to muster, at back, 3 wide, no dash.
Midfield, trapped 3-4 wide, ran on fairly.
Midfield, 2 wide, no turn of foot.
Midfield along the fence, suited by the fast pace, no progress.
Hard ridden forward, emptied 300M.
Never competitive.
Fast out, raced at box seat, responded solidly in the straight, finished strongly to score.
Taken back at start, held up for clear running in the early part of straight, made up nice ground after obtaining clear running.
Jumped nicely, took lead after 900M, worked home nicely.
Settled behind midfield, made up some nice late ground.
Slow out, raced midfield on rail, difficult to find clear running in the early part of straight, responded well passing 200M.
Began awkwardly, raced at handy position, gradually made ground passing 200M.
Slow out, settled midfield, passing 600M raced in restricted room, one-paced in the straight.
Settled at rear, one-paced when placed under pressure.
On jumped was crowded for room, travelled keenly and awkwardly placed in the early and middle stages, one-paced.
Raced outside the lead, gave ground passing 200M.
Began awkwardly, settled behind midfield, wide on straightening, failed to run on.
Travelled wide and without cover, in the straight gave ground, failed to make impression.
Difficult to settle in the early stages, raced behind midfield, no response in the straight.
Travelled wide and without cover, weakened in the straight. Bled.
Began well from a wide draw, raced 3 wide in midfield, 4 to 5 lengths back, there to turn, finished off very strongly in straight to score.
Bumped start, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well throughout, led by 2 lengths turning in, kicked clear early in straight, kept on well but couldn't hold off the winner late.
Bumped shortly after start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 6 lengths or so back, improved from 550M, finished off strongly in straight to take 3rd, nearest on line.

Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide at rear early, slightly improved after passing 1200M to race behind midfield, 6 lengths back on turn, angled out early in straight, finished off well to make frame.
Moderately away, showed no early speed, raced at rear on rail, still 8 lengths back on turn, angled out near 500M, made some headway in straight without threatening.
Began well, raced 2 wide in midfield, same position on turn, raced tight near 550M, finished off evenly in straight.

Commenced fairly before ridden up to position midfield. Enjoyed soft run in middle sections, before asked for effort from 400m. Slightly held up approaching 350m, before gaining clear running but only battled to the line.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide at rear, 7 lengths back, same margin back on turn, Steadied off heels early, awkwardly placed and unbalanced near 400M, finished off evenly thereafter.
Was slow to begin, conceding 2 lengths to remainder of field. Joined tail of the field at the 1350m but was too far back to threaten in a raced run well inside standard time.
Bumped on jumping, raced at tail, 10 lengths back, taken very wide turning in, passed a few tired runners in straight.
Began well from a tricky gate, sent forward to race 2 wide in 2nd, sat right behind the leader from 700M, weakened early in straight.
Jumped with them, raced 3 wide better than midfield, gradually moved forward after passing 1050M, sat outside the lead on turn, emptied early in straight, dropped off tamely.
Bumped shortly after start, raced 2 wide better than midfield, 3 to 4 lengths back on turn, weakened early in straight.
Average to begin, positioned 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, showed no response early in straight, eased after passing 150M.
Began well, sent forward to take the lead, enjoyed the easy lead throughout, kept on very well in straight to hold off the challenger.
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned nicely in 2nd, easy run throughout, fought hard final 200M but always held.
Jumped well, sat 2 to 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, angled out near 300M, finished off well to take a place without threatening.
Began well from a wide draw, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, same position on turn, kept on steadily until weakened final 50M.
Began fairly, positioned on rail in midfield, 5 lengths back, there to turn, finished off well in straight, nearest on line.
Slightly slow out, positioned on rail behind midfield, 6 to 7 lengths back on turn, made some progress in straight without threatening.
Shifted in at start and bumped, raced 2 wide in midfield, 6 lengths back, wider from 600M, finished off evenly in straight.
Bumped on jumping, raced 2 wide better than midfield, 4 to 5 lengths back on turn, failed to make any progress in straight.
Began only fairly, positioned on rail at rear, 8 lengths back on turn, angled out early in straight, finished off one-paced.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 7 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, finished off one-pace in straight.
Crowded on jumping, raced at tail, 11 lengths back, closer on turn but still 9 lengths back, finished off evenly in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide at rear, 9 lengths back, similar position on turn, failed to make any progress in straight.
Jumped well from the widest draw, unable to slot in, positioned 3 wide and without cover, 3 lengths or so back, peaked on turn, weakened early in straight.
Fractious in gate, lifted feet at start and lost ground, raced at rear, 10 lengths back, angled out near 600M, weakened early in straight, finished last.
Sent forward to take the rail and led, continued on nicely and fended off challenge to score by a neck.
Sat outside the lead, battled on gamely all the way to the line, finished a neck behind the winner.
In front of midfield, travelled wide and without cover after laying out at 700M, battled on to finish 3rd.
Bumped start and then was ridden along, however trapped wide and without cover, continued on to the line.
Settled in one-off one-back position, about 1-3/4L off, one paced before closing off fairly. (Rider questioned)
At the rear and stayed 2 wide until straightening, closed off fairly inside final 100M.
Taken out at the start, raced towards the rear, 3 wide at turn, widest in the straight and made minor ground early.
Raced behind the leaders along the rail, about 2L behind, only one paced to the line.
Travelled towards the rear along the rail, one paced and eased at final 50M.
Inconvenienced at start, settled in behind midfield 2 wide, did not feature.
Found cover in just behind midfield, laid out at turns, couldn't challenge.
Towards the rear, continued to lose ground throughout.

Niggled along before settling in 5th just over 2L off the pace, carried backward when pace slackened around the bend, switched in for a run upon straightening, quickened well to take charge over 70 metres out.
Ridden along from the widest gate before taken back for cover in joint 6th some 4L back, carried 5 wide and circled the field home bend, hit the front on straightening, headed over 70M out.
Settled in last few, switched wide to challenge entering straight, ran on under pressure without threatening.
Jumped well, taken back to settle in joint 6th within 4L of pace, made headway 4-wide rounding home bend to chase the leader into straight, faded under pressure inside final 150 metres.
Slowly away, settled in last few on the rail, gained close when pace slackened on home bend, baulked for a run early in straight, found nothing under pressure.
Lacked pace early, detached from the main body of the field until pace slackened on the bend, switched wide into straight, found nothing under pressure.

Crowded at start, hard ridden to be up with the leaders disputing leader on the rail from 1200 metres out, gained half a length advantage rounding home bend but soon headed entering straight, folded up quickly.
Ridden along to hold 4th on the rail just off the pace, dropped away quickly after straightening. (Jockey warned for his riding early stages.)
Led early stages, narrowly headed coming onto home bend, dropped out of contention upon straightening.
Well there when wide early stages, gradually shifted to one back position 3-wide without cover, dropped out from home bend. (Tactic questioned)
In mid-division 3-4Ls back, ridden and responded strongly passing 400M, wrestled the lead inside 100M, kept on well to score.
Travelled strongly behind leaders, driven to the lead 200M, outsprinted by winner inside final 100M.
Shifted across behind runners early, towards rear 5Ls off the pace, stayed on well for 3rd under top weight but well held by first two.
Dropped back towards the rear, niggled along from 700M, stayed on wellto claim 4th without troubling first two.
Shifted in abruptly at the start and bumped with rival, remained in touch, outsprinted by rivals 300M, kept on same speed to the line.
Away well and soon in clear lead, headed by rivals 150m, weakened towards the line. (Jockey reminded to ride out to the end of the race.)
Raced in mid-division towards the outside of the group, ran on same pace passing halfway, never a threat to leaders.
Bumped with rivals at the start, lacked early speed and detached from field, made some late progress but only passing beaten horses.
From draw 12 obtained a trailing position behind leaders along the stand's rail, under pressure 600M, didn't respond to riding, no extra inside 200M. (Jockey: didn't travel at any stage.)
Held up in midfield, struggled to keep up 500M, soon out of contention.
Began awkwardly, rushed forward chasing leader,under pressure 500M, weakened rapidly from 300M (Jockey: never travelled comfortably during the race.)
Raced along the stands' rail towards rear of midfield, couldn't keep up halfway, soon dropped out.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide in midfield, 5 lengths back, angled out after passing 500M, finished off very strongly in straight to score by a neck.
Jumped well, positioned 2 wide, 3 lengths back, same margin back on turn, finished off strongly to take 2nd.
Began awkwardly and unbalanced the rider, recovered to take the lead, challenged near 850M, travelled well on turn, kept on very well in straight but just couldn't hold off the first two late.
Taken back to race at rear on rail, 6 to 7 lengths back, saved ground on turn, angled out in straight but still couldn't find clear running until final 50M, finished off strongly to make frame.
Average to begin, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, got cover from 800M, 1 to 2 lengths back on turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Moderately away from a wide draw, trapped 3 wide with no cover, a length or so back, sent forward after passing 950 to race outside the lead, 2nd on turn, kept on evenly in straight.
Got head up early when being steadied to obtain cover, positioned 4 to 5 lengths back on rail, saved ground on turn, no clear running in straight, not able to be properly tested.

Jumped well from gate 9, taken back to race at rear, travelled keenly near 1100M, 8 to 9 lengths back on turn, bumped near 300M, angled out thereafter and finished off strongly. (See Racing Incidents.)
Moderately away from gate 1, sat 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, same margin back on turn, failed to quicken in straight.
Clean jump, taken back to race 3 wide with cover at rear, 6 to 7 lengths back on turn, showed limited response in straight.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear, 7 to 8 lengths back, similar position on turn, no daylight early in straight, bumped near 300M, finished off evenly thereafter.

Taken back from barrier 13, raced 2 wide at rear, 5 to 6 lengths back, angled out after passing 550M, showed some response early in straight, weakened from final 200M, eased final 100M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Bumped shortly after start, raced 3 wide in midfield, no cover after 850M, 4 lengths back on turn, weakened gradually in straight.
Away with them, slightly taken back to race 3 wide, 6 lengths back, same margin back on turn, weakened early in straight, eased final 150M.
Began only fairly, gradually recovered, took the lead after passing 1000M, easy lead on turn, kicked clear early in straight, kept on very well to score.
Began awkwardly, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, there to turn, finished off well to take 2nd.
Jumped well, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, same margin back on turn, made good progress in straight to take a place.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, 6 lengths back, awkwardly placed near 800M, a bit closer turning in, made good progress in straight to make frame without threatening the first few.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 4 to 5 lengths back, difficult to settle after passing 1100M, same margin back on turn, made some headway in straight.
Slightly slow out, positioned 4 lengths back on rail, angled out near 600M, no clear running until near final 100M, made some headway thereafter.
Began awkwardly, raced 3 wide at rear, 6 lengths back, there to turn, made some progress early in straight, crowded near 100M, kept on evenly in straight.
Taken back from gate 11, positioned 5 to 6 lengths back on rail, saved ground on turn, blocked near 300M, angled out thereafter and made some progress.
Jumped well, positioned on rail in midfield, 3 to 4 lengths back, finished off evenly in straight.
Jumped well, raced prominently but wide early, got cover from 850M, 2 lengths back on turn, kept on evenly early in straight, weakened from final 200M.
Began well from gate 13, sent forward to race prominently but wide, 2nd on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Jumped well from a middle draw, unable to slot in early, taken back to race 3 wide, 5 lengths back, raced tight near 600M, carried wider turning in, failed to close off in straight.
Began well from gate 9, showed no early speed, raced 4 wide at rear, no cover from 900M, very wide turning in, emptied early in straight when hard run took effect.
Average to begin, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, sat right behind the leader on turn, weakened early in straight, eased final furlong.

Ridden along then settled behind leaders, faded out passing 100M.
Raced midfield, always niggled, wide on straightening, limited response in the straight.
Settled midfield, after the 700M was left racing wide and without cover, wide on straightening, no response in the straight.
Ridden along in the early stages, was left racing wide and without cover until after 700M, came under pressure rounding Home Turn and in the straight gave ground, failed to make impression.
Urged along to take lead, in the straight no response, failed to run on.
Jumped well then eased behind the pace and travelled well 4th the fence. Improved into clear room at the 300m after travelling like the winner and sprinted away sharply for very easy score.
Jumped cleanly before being taken backwards across the tail of the field to settle in rearward position. Well back turning into the straight before working home in between runners.

Commenced fairly before being bumped on two occasions before positioning behind leading pair. Positioned outside winner in middle stages, before battling away in the straight to finish in 3rd position.

Commenced cleanly from outside barrier before working across midfield, travelling three wide with cover. Asked for effort before straightening and fought on soundly under heavy riding in the straight.
Ridden to get position in early stages but could not go pace before settling towards rear one off the fence. Shifted back to the fence in the straight and passed a few to the line.
Commenced quickly before going to the lead and setting quicker than standard first and third section. Headed just prior to straightening and weakened in the straight.

Commenced well from wide barrier before coming across face of the field and heading horse inside in fast first sectional before handing up lead at 800m. Was prominent until 200m before weakening noticeably last part.
Outpaced in early stages before settling midfield fence. Gained clear running when asked for effort in straight but ran on only moderately.
Commenced awkwardly before shifting inwards and bumping another runner. Settling worse than midfield, three wide with cover. Asked to improve from 400m and worked to the line fairly.
Jumped well, pressed forward but could not get cover and posted 3 wide throughout. Improved position outside leading pair before cornering awkwardly making up moderate ground in the straight.
Commenced fairly and then bumped after 50m, before settling midfield one off the fence. Asked for effort at 375m but failed to respond and well beaten.
Commenced slowly conceding field 4L, before positioning last on the fence. Was ridden along too stay in touch before weakening out in the straight.
Jumped with them, sent forward to race prominently, found rail near 1300M, sat 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader thereafter, easy run on turn, finished off strongly in straight to score.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 lengths or so back, 3 wide on turn, made good progress in straight to take 2nd without threatening the winner.
Away with them, raced 2 wide at rear, moved closer on turn, 4 lengths back at 400M, very wide turning in, closed off well to take a place. (Lost right front plate.)

Jumped well but didn't show much speed early, sent forward on the 1st turn, bumped near 1200M, took the lead after 1100M, still led by a length turning in, peaked early in straight, headed 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Slowly away, raced at tail, 7 to 8 lengths back, moved closer on turn, taken very wide in straight and made some progress to be nearest on line.

Began fairly from the widest draw, sent forward to take the early lead, headed near 1100M, raced 2 wide, a length or so back thereafter, hard ridden from 500M, failed to make any progress in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Moderately away, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, failed to quicken under pressure in straight.

Began well from gate 1, positioned 5 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, blocked early in straight, blocked for run in straight until passing 150M, angled out thereafter and ran on evenly to the line.
Jumped well, raced 2 wide, 2 lengths back early, 3 wide from 950M, moved a bit closer thereafter, 2nd on turn, weakened gradually in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began only fairly, raced at rear throughout, showed nothing early in straight, eased thereafter. (Irregular heart rhythm.)
Sent forward, crossed and assumed outright lead on the rail at 1000M, stayed on to score comfortably by 1-3/4L.
Pushed along to sit outside the lead, 1-1/4L off, battled on gamely but was no match to the winner.
Settled to be in midfield, 3-1/2L behind along the rail, continued on fairly to take 3rd.
Raced in one-off one-back position, sat 2-1/2L off the lead, kept on one paced.
Eased to race in behind midfield, 5-1/4L behind 2 wide, improved steadily until awkward to heels in final stages.
At rear initially, improved to midfield prior to 600M, made turn 3 wide, switched widest and kept on going to the line.
In worse than midfield, 5L behind along the rail, made minor inroad on the inside track.
Travelled in midfield, trapped wide throughout, kept on going to the line.
Slotted in to race in about midfield, 2 wide at home turn, one paced.
Rolled forward to take up the box-seat, one paced and then weakened in the last 100M.
Eased back and raced at the tail, barely improved.
Slow to begin then remained at the rear, never a factor.
Soon ridden to first few, with leaders on the rail before crossed rounding the bend, switched off the rail for a run entering straight, hit the front over 250 metres out and just held on to the line.
Crowded at start losing ground, remained in rear of midfield despite ridden along, saved ground on inside turning for home, ran on under pressure to just fail to get up on line.
With leaders early, taken back to 4th some 2L back on the rail, saved ground to gain 2nd 200 metres out, lost position late.
Settled in midfield in 6th over 5L back, commenced move rounding home bend and the widest runner turning for home, fought on steadily down the centre of the track without threatening.

Broke well, soon taken back to rear of midfield in 7th some 7L back, commenced move approaching home turn, improving when tightened and checked 200 metres out, quickly recovered and produced good late impression.
Moderate start, settled in last few, ran on past well-beaten horses in closing stages.
Sluggish at start, settled over 4L back in 5th, commenced move entering straight, ran home one-paced.
Settled well behind, made modest headway past well-beaten runners down the centre of the track final stages.

Jumped awkwardly losing ground, settled in last few on the rail, gained slightly closer passing the Rock, saved ground turning in but made no impression in the run to the line. (Irregular heart rhythm)
Broke well, shared pace before leading outright from the Rock, headed and dropped out 200 metres out.
Taken back to rear from the widest gate, remained well behind throughout, came under pressure rounding home bend, made no impression in the run home.

Pressed forward from a wide gate, held narrow advantage 3-wide briefly before taken back for cover in 3rd passing the Rock, wide rounding home bend, dropped away quickly in straight. (Questioned for disappointing performance)
Led at good pace, driven clear 300M, kept on well final stages to hold pursuers at bay.
Tracked leaders along the fence, checked 500M, angled out into clear 300M, stayed on without reaching winner, claimed 2nd in a 3-way photo.
Settled down midfield along the fence, tried hard in the straight but couldn't get to winner, hung out final 200M difficult to ride, lost 2nd near line. (Jockey dropped left rein 100M.)
Tracked leaders, in 5th position making home turn, kept on steadily final 300M and was just denied a placing in 3-way photo. (Jockey dropped left rein 100M.)
Held up behind midfield, brought wide 250M, stayed on mildly, not reached contention.
Held up towards rear, waited with until 300M, made some progress without threatening.
From wide draw steadied passing 1100M for obtain cover, settled down towards the rear on outside, responded mildly on straightening, never dangerous.
Outpaced early, held up near last, saved ground on inner, ran on same pace final 300M.
Tracked leaders in 3rd, ran on same pace under pressure in straight, weakened over final 200M.
Dropped back to last from wide draw, made limited progress in the straight passing a couple of beaten horses only.
From draw 9 sent forward to chased leader, dropped away 250M, eased when no chance.
Up with early pace then eased back to midfield, wide no cover from 600M, under pressure 450M out, soon weakened and eased. (Lame LF.)

Bumped start, raced prominently, 2 away from the stands rail, hard ridden from near 500M, finished off strongly to score.
Jumped well, positioned 3 away from the stands rail in midfield, 2 to 3 lengths back, finished off very strongly to take 2nd, nearest on line.
Clean jump from gate 12, positioned behind the lead on the stands rail, travelled well throughout, showed good response in the final stages to take a place, missed 2nd on line.
Bumped on jumping, showed good early speed to take the lead near to the stands rail, kept on well to the line but couldn't hold off the first few late.
Moderately away, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader near to the stands rail, finished off well, just missed frame on line.
Away with them, positioned 1-1/2 length behind the leader nearer to the stands side, kept on evenly the line.

Began awkwardly and bumped, raced at rear, 5Ls back, bumped and unbalanced near 600M, showed very good response after passing 400M, blocked near 100M, finished off evenly thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Slightly slow out and bumped, raced at rear, 4 to 5 lengths back, bumped and unbalanced near 600M, made no progress final 400M, just kept on evenly to the line.
Moderately away, raced in midfield nearer to the stands side, failed to quicken final 400M, only one pace to the line.
Began fairly, steadied off heels shortly after start, raced at rear, 4 lengths or so back, kept on evenly until final 100M, weakened thereafter.
Average to begin, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader early, gradually dropped away under pressure from near 650M, well beaten.
Began only fairly from gate 1, positioned behind midfield nearer to the middle of the track, weakened from 500M, eased final 200M.
Settled in midfield 2 wide, favoured by the fast pace, held up 4-2, closed off strongly when clear.
Eased back, 2-3 wide, benefited by the fast pace, progressed steadily 300M for 2nd, just missed by a narrow margin.
Pushed forward, trapped 2-3 wide, not suited by the fast tempo, ran on well for 3rd.
Hard ridden to take rail, shared the lead at fast sectionals, hung on well until 150M weakened.
At rear along the fence, benefited by the fast pace, lack room 400M, made steady ground when clear.
Midfield, trapped 3 wide, made ground 300M, run ended 150M.
Bumped start, at back, suited by the fast tempo, blocked most straight, not properly tested.
At back, 2-3 wide, favoured by the fast tempo, made steady ground 200M.
Pushed forward to share the lead in 2 wide, harmed by the fast pace, weakened 400M.
Box seat, raced keenly, not suited by the fast pace, out of fuel 300M.
Hard ridden forward, trapped 3 wide, harmed by the fast tempo, emptied 400M.
Eased back, trapped 3-4 wide, benefited by the fast pace, never improved.
Taken back at start, raced midfield on rail, quickened passing 200M, finished off strongly.
Travelled at handy position, until near 600M travelled wide and without cover, worked home solidly, just missed by Head.
Taken back at start, improved passing 500M, made up some nice late ground.
Ridden along to take lead, fought hard entire straight, gave some ground passing 50M.
Settled at handy position, commenced to improve near 500M, responded well in the straight.
Travelled behind midfield, always niggled, finished OK.
Raced in box seat, held in the early part of straight, one-paced.
Settled midfield, widest on straightening, one-paced in the straight.
Taken back at start, raced at rear, limited response in the straight.
Stuck wide then ridden along to take forward position after 800M, after that still raced wide and without cover, weakened near 200M.
Slow to begin, raced behind midfield on rail, no response in the straight.
Began awkwardly, near 1050M and passing 1000M was checked, made Home Turn awkwardly, never in it.
Jumped nicely, settled outside the lead, faded out passing 200M.

Jumped well before easing after 200m to position midfield, one off fence. Was shuffled back before entering straight but always travelled well, before easing around heels at 250m and finishing strongly.

Commenced fast before easing back from wide barrier. Raced wide with cover and commenced to improve from 800m. Entered straight the widest runner. Brushed when shifting in the straight before balancing and finishing well.

Began fast before ridden up into position, settling two pairs back off the fence. Commenced to improve from 550m. Kicked on in straight and looked winner inside last 150m before overhauled in last few strides.

Jumped well before easing back to midfield position. Was slightly eased at the 650m. Looked close enough to figure when entering straight but was cramped for room around the 375m and again approaching 200m.

Slow to jump before easing back across tail of the field before railing up to settle four from the tail in middle stages. Changed direction back to the inside when improving at the 275m before working home fairly last 150m.
Commenced fairly before hard ridden to share lead until 1000m when then crossed by another runner. Turned into the straight in third position before running on only fairly in the straight.
Started fairly before railing up to hold inside position and settling second behind leader. Came off leaders back at 475m and looked prominent until 200m when over run in later stages.
Began moderately railing up to position midfield on the fence. Enjoyed a soft run in transit before battling away in the straight. Was eased slightly over concluding stages.

Began awkwardly and struck heels of another runner before being eased to tail of the field. Shifted abruptly at the 650m when racing greenly. Entered the straight well back and passed a few in the run to the line.
Commenced fairly before settling midfield on fence. Was slightly eased before the 650m before entering straight on the inside and then crowded and blocked between the 250m and the 150m.
One of the slowest away before being dragged back to position last one off the fence. Was asked to improve position from the 550m but failed to respond.

Jumped fairly before ridden up to get position but could not get any closer than 3 wide throughout middle stages. Attempted to improve from the 500m, before being bumped at the 425m, and then bumped heavily again at the 375m.

Ridden hard from outside barrier and then continuing on from the lead just prior to the 1000m. Set up margin on chasing pair throughout middle stages, before railing into straight but weakening last 250m.
Commenced well then eased first 150m to position near the tail one off fence. Asked to improve at 650m before being eased, but was never a threat in the straight.
Taken back from gate 11, raced at tail, 8 lengths back, same margin back on turn, taken very wide in straight and finished off strongly to score, very impressive.

Away with them, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well throughout, led by 2 lengths turning in, kicked clear early in straight, kept on well to the line, just couldn't hold off the winner late.
Began fairly from gate 1, sat 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, easy run on turn, finished off evenly in straight to take a place.
Crowded on jumping, raced 2 wide, 5 lengths back, there to turn, unable to obtain clear running early in straight, made good progress when clear final 200M.
Average to begin, positioned on rail in midfield, angled out turning in, inconvenienced near 350M, finished off evenly.
Shifted out at start and made contact, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 to 4 lengths back, bumped near 350M, finished off evenly thereafter.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear on rail, 6 to 7 lengths back, angled out from near 500M, blocked near 300M, made minor progress when clear thereafter.
Began awkwardly and bumped, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, wider from 500M, showed minor progress early in straight, peaked near 200M, weakened thereafter.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 3 wide at rear, 6 to 7 lengths back, very wide turning in, only passed a few tiredrunners in straight.
Average to begin, positioned on rail behind midfield, 5 to 6 lengths back, saved ground on turn, finished off one pace in straight.
Began smartly, ridden to go forward but not enough speed, raced 3 wide, 2 lengths back, no cover from 800M, hard ridden from 500M but only showed little response, ran on one pace to the line.
Jumped with them, positioned 2 wide, 1 to 2 lengths back, 3 wide after passing 600M, failed to quicken under pressure in straight. (Blood in trachea.) (See Racing Incidents.)
Began fairly from the widest draw, raced at rear on rail, still 7 lengths back on turn, failed to make any progress in straight.
Jumped well from gate 12, raced prominently but wide, peaked turning in, emptied early in straight, eased final 150M.
Sent forward to take the rail and led, was challenged but held onto the lead to score by a short-head.
Urged to take up racing in the box-seat, sat 1-3/4L off, pushed winner all the way, missed by a short-head.
Raced towards the rear, 9-1/2L behind 2 wide, held up until 250M, finished off strongly inside final 150M. (Rider questioned)
Settled in worse than midfield, 3 wide and without cover, bumped at 350M, closed off well to the line.
Raced in front of midfield, 4-1/2L behind along the rail, kept on one paced to the line.
Jumped fairly only, raced in midfield along the rail, continued on one paced.
Eased after the start, raced at the rear 2 wide, 9-1/2L behind at 400M, saved ground in the straight.
Awkward start, recovered to be in behind midfield along the rail, made slight dash early in the straight.
Taken back and raced at the rear, 12-1/2L behind 3 wide but with cover, made ground inside final 200M.
Sat in just behind midfield, 2 wide throughout, bumped at about 300M, made no ground.
Took spot in midfield and in a 2 wide position, did not improve. (Lame left front the day after)
Taken back then travelled keenly in the early stages, 3 wide but with cover throughout, made no ground.
Niggled and took spot in front of midfield 2 wide, not competitive in the straight.
Asked to be prominent, pressured from 700M, gave ground thereafter and finished detached.
Tracked leader, came to challenge inside the 300 metres, gave upper hand 50 metres out.
Broke well, taken one back for cover in 3rd on stands rails, came to challenge passing the 200 metres but unable to peg back the winner throughout closing stages.
Hampered at start, settled in last few when mainly about 2L off the pace, improved to as close as 1.5L back in 4th coming onto course proper, unable to sustain effort near the finish.
Soon dropped to last of 7th over 4L off the pace, came under pressure to make ground inside the 400 metres, produced good late impression in closing stages.
Failed to muster early stages travelling some 3L back in last few, gradually improved to about 2.5L back in 5th inside the 200 metres, failed to make any further impression in closing stages.
Jumped fairly, settled mainly 2L back near stands rails, kept on same pace under pressure.
Made running to the 300 metres, folded up quickly.
Travelled well outside the leader, took over leaving the bend, raced to a 3L lead passing 200M, well in control thereafter. Impressive performance under top weight.
Restrained after the start, waited with in a rearward spot 6Ls off the pace, picked up strongly turning home, closed off fastest to claim 2nd inside 50M, not reached runaway winner.
Awkwardly away, recovered to race in 5th spot 3-4Ls off the pace, moved up to 2nd passing 200M, couldn't get closer to runaway winner, lost 2nd 50M out.
Slow to begin, held up behind midfield 6Ls off the pace, stayed on well to go 4th late.
With leaders early, sat in 4th passing 1000M, kept on steadily final 400M, not pace to challenge leaders. (lay out rounding home turn and in the straight.)
Bustled along to be leading along the fence, headed early straight, no extra late and swamped by rivals. (Lame next day.)
In mid-division 5Ls off the good pace, stayed on over final 400M without threat.
Ahead of midfield in 6th position, responded only fairly when driven along 500M, never dangerous.
Chased leaders in 3rd, well placed to strike 400M but ran on at same speed only.
Failed to muster speed early stages, raced back in the field 3-wide no cover, couldn't pick up turning in, never involved.
Eased back to race in the rear, 7Ls to make up 400M, made no real progress in the run home.
Held up in midfield along the inside, driven along near 400M but couldn't muster the speed to challenge, faded final 150M.
From wide draw taken across behind runners, settled near rear 7-8Ls back, failed to finish off in the straight.
Dropped back on jumping from wide draw, raced as the backmarker from 1000M, swung widest home, didn't respond to riding in the straight.
Moderately away, raced 3 wide, 5 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, finished off very strongly in straight to score.
Began smartly from the widest draw, sent forward to take the lead, easy lead on turn, kicked clear early instraight, kept on well but couldn't hold off the winner close home.
Average to begin, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, kept on very well in straight to take a place.
Jumped with them, positioned 2 wide, 4 lengths or so back, there to turn, angled out early in straight, finished off well to make frame.
Began well from a wide draw, raced 3 wide better than midfield, no cover throughout, made some headway early in straight, peaked near 150M, kept on evenly to the line.
Away with them, raced 2 wide, 6 lengths back, similarposition on turn, made some progress in straight without threatening.
Slowly away, raced at rear on rail, 6 lengths back, 2 wide from near 600M, same margin back turning in, blocked near 300M, made minor progress when clear thereafter.
Slightly slow out, recovered to sit 3 lengths behind the leader on rail,saved ground on turn,finished offevenly in straight.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide, 4 lengths or so back in the early stages, found rail near 900M, saved ground on turn, made some progress in straight.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide, 2lengths back, similarposition on turn, weakened gradually in straight.
Began well, raced 2 wide in midfield, wider from 700M, 4 lengths back turning in,failed to close off in straight.
Bumped start, raced at rear, 7 lengthsback, same marginback on turn, taken wide in straight and finished off evenly.
Moderately away from a wide draw, sent forward to race in 2nd, a length behind the leader on turn, weakenedgradually in straight.
Taken back from gate 13, raced at tail, 8 lengths back, still well back on turn, failed to make any progress in straight.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide, 2 to 3 lengths back, same position on turn, showed very good response in straight and scored easily.
Jumped well, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well on turn, kept on very well in straight, still headed near 100M, stayed on to take 2nd.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, 9 lengths back, still well back on turn, taken wide in straight and finished off very strongly to take a place, nearest on line.
Lifted front feet on jumping and away tardily, positioned 6 lengths or so back on rail, saved ground on turn, angled out early in straight, finished off well to make frame.
Bumped shortly after start, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, 7 lengths back, there to turn, made very good progress in straight.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear on rail, 9 lengths back, saved ground on turn, made good progress in straight without threatening.
Shifted out at start and bumped, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, there to turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Began well, raced 3 wide behind midfield, 2 wide turning, made minor progress in straight.
Began fairly, raced 2 wide in midfield, similar positon on turn, failed to quicken under pressure in straight.
Bumped shortly after start and unbalanced, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, outside the leader on turn, weakened gradually in straight.
Slightly slow out, positioned on rail in midfield, 4 lengths back, saved ground on turn, finished off evenly.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide behind midfield, awkwardly placed near 1000M, 6 to 7 lengths back on turn, failed to make any progress in straight.
Crowded out start, raced 4 wide behind midfield, 3 wide on turn, failed to close off in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Slightly slow out from gate 13, recovered to race prominently but 3 wide, slightly taken back near 800M to obtain cover, weakened early in straight, eased final 100M.

Jumped nicely from gate 10, sent forward to take the lead, enjoyed the easy lead throughout,still led by 1-1/2L turning in, kept on very well in straight, just held off runner-up's late challenge.
Began fairly, positioned 5 lengths behind the leader on rail, similar position on turn, angled out from 400M, finished off very strongly in straight to take 2nd.
Average to begin, raced 2wide better than midfield, 2 to 3 lengths back on turn, closed off well to take a placewithout threatening.
Jumped well from a middle draw, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, hard ridden on turn, peaked early in straight, kept on evenly to the line.
Beganawkwardly, raced 2 wide, 4 lengths or so back, improved from near 400M, made some headway in straightwithout threatening.
Moderately away from the widest draw, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, commenced move near 700M, 3rd on turn, 4 wide turning in, peaked early in straight, just kept on one pace to the line.
Jumped well from gate 1, sat 2 lengths behindthe leader on rail, same margin back on turn, kept on evenly early in straight, weakened from final 150M.
Average to begin, positioned on rail in midfield, 3 lengths or so back, there to turn, no clear running until after passing 100M, made no progress thereafter.

Lifted front feet on jumping and away tardily, raced at rear, 7 lengths back, moved slightly closer after entering the back straight, 5 lengths back on turn, failed to quicken under pressure in straight.
Slightly slow out, raced 2 wide behind midfield, moved closer after entering the back straight, peaked on turn,emptied early in straight.
Moderately away, unable to slot in, raced 3 wide and without cover, 2 lengths back, same position to near 600M, weakened gradually thereafter, emptied early in straight.
Slightly slow out, raced at tail throughout, never competitive.
Settled in midfield along the fence, pace good, progressed steadily 300M to score.
Pushed to sit in midfield, 2 wide, pace good, made steady ground 300M for 2nd.
At rear, 2 wide, pace good, progressed steadily 300M.
Eased at start, took rail, pace good, blocked 4-2, dashed well when clear.
Hard ridden forward, sat outside the leader, pace good, out of fuel 150M.
Pushed to take rail and led at good pace, hung on until 200M weakened.
Pushed to obtain box seat, pace good, soon emptied 300M.
Settled midfield on rail, asked for effort on straightening, made nice ground in the straight, finished unchallenged.
Ridden along to take lead, fought hard entire straight, finished solidly.
Raced in box seat, responded nicely in the straight, worked home well.
Raced midfield, made up some nice ground passing 100M.
Taken back at start, battled hard and gradually made ground in the straight.
Began only fairly, settled behind midfield on rail, widest on straightening, gained some ground passing 100M.
Settled outside the lead, asked for effort near 400M, one-paced.
Raced behind midfield, midrace moved to handy position, limited response in the straight.
Taken back at start, always back, limited response when placed pressure.
Raced at rear, no response in the straight.
After 900M proved difficult to settle then shifted out and raced wide and without cover, improved to outside the lead at 600M, after 600M under pressure and no response in the straight.
Was fairly away but then brushed and eased to last. Trailed field throughout and was last into the turn before pulling to middle of track and sprinting home over the top for narrow win.
Jumped well and ridden up to hold prominent position behind leading pair. Travelled well in middle stages before joining lead in inside final 150m.
Commenced quickly and maintained the rail position and lead. Quickened from 400m and broke clear inside 300m mark before overrun inside last 75m.
Ridden hard from inside barrier to hold prominent position on fence behind leading pair. Left slightly flat footed when pace quickened from 400m, before making good ground in final 200m.
Commenced well and ridden up to gain prominent position before easing at 750m mark to settle midfield. Asked for effort from 400m and battled away fairly in the straight.
One of the slowest into stride and settled third last on fence. Worked home fairly once got clear running. Was checked in the final few strides.
Commenced fairly before being eased across heels to obtain midfield position. Was under heavy pressure before straightening and worked home fairly to finish midfield.
Away moderately before being eased back to the rear of the field. Was eased slightly around the 350m before maintaining run on the fence but never threatening in the straight.
Jumped very fast before coming across the face of the field to position outside leader. Under pressure upon straightening and weakened out inside final 250m.

Only moderately away before being position one off the fence towards rear of the field. Covered additional ground in middle stages before moved out wide entering straight and only battled to the line.
Commenced fairly and settled on the fence in midfield position. Asked for effort from 500m to hold position in running, hung in slightly in the straight but was never a threat.
Commenced fairly from wide barrier before ridden up to go forward but caught in three wide position. Was asked to improve from 450m but weakened out in the straight after a tough run in transit.
Clean jump, raced 2 wide, 4 lengths or so back, 3 wide from near 700M, same margin back on turn, taken wide in straight and finished off very strongly to score.
Jumped well, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, angled out early in straight and finished off well to take 2nd.
Away with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, in traffic early in straight, blocked again near 200M, made some progress when clear thereafter to take a place.
Began well from the widest draw, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length, travelled well throughout, kept on well in straight, headed after passing 100M, just missed 3rd on line.
Moderately away from gate 11, sent forward to race in 3rd, 2 wide, a length or so back, there to turn, peaked early in straight, just kept on evenly to the line.
Slightly slow out, raced at rear on rail, 6 lengths back, same margin back on turn, angled out early in straight, finished off well without threatening.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, 7 lengths or so back, still well back on turn, made reasonable headway in straight without threatening.
Jumped well, raced 2 wide in midfield, same position on turn, angled out after passing 400M, failed to quicken under pressure in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Average to begin, raced 2 wide at rear, 6 lengths back, similar position on turn, made minor progress in straight.

Began well, sent forward to race in 2nd, took the rail near 800M, sat a length behind the leader thereafter, travelled well on turn, kept on evenly early in straight, weakened sharply from final 100M.
Began awkwardly, positioned 4 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, kept on evenly early in straight, weakened after passing final 150M.
Jumped with them, unable to slot in, raced 3 wide in midfield, no cover from 600M, carried wider turning in, weakened early in straight when hard run took effect.
In front of midfield, 4L off 2 wide, in tight battle until 100M, then pulled away and held onto a 1/2L winning margin.
Racing in the box-seat 1-1/4L off, couldn't settle in the middle stages, fought well on to take 2nd.
Niggled along to be in front of midfield, 5L off along the rail, dashed early and ran on well to the line.
In midfield, 6-1/2L off along the rail, continued on fairly but wasn't tested in final stages when awkward to heels.
Niggled along into the lead from barrier 1, headed passing 200M, one paced.
Bumped start, settled in just behind midfield, 7-3/4L behind 2 wide, made steady ground and closed off fairly.
Jumped awkwardly, then raced in midfield, 5-1/4L behind 2 wide, slight dash early then one paced.
Taken back, settled in behind midfield, 9-1/4L off along the rail, continued on fairly to the line.
Fractious and missed start badly, at the rear throughout before making ground in the straight.
Bumped start and then taken back, in behind midfield 9-1/4L off 2 wide, made minor ground throughout.
Niggled along, then sat 1L off and outside the lead, emptied at 200M.
Fractious and then lost ground at the start, wasn't in it thereafter.
Broke well, gradually taken back to forward of midfield some 3L off on the rail, commenced move approaching home turn, quickened well to take charge 150 metres out, won readily.
Hampered early stages, settled in rear of midfield, shaken up making home turn, ran on under pressure to be nearest at finish. (Rider dropped rein closing stages)

Niggled along among leaders early, settled for 5th some 3L back before first bend, drifted back to midfield in 7th for cover in back straight, went very wide turning for home, ran on quite well under pressure without threatening.
Began from a middle gate, obtained one back position on the rail coming out of home straight, remained similar thereafter, kept on same pace without quickening in final stretch.
Worked steadily from the widest gate to take up running after the first 200 metres, steadied pace coming onto back straight, led until finding no extra 150 metres out.
Settled well back, came to challenge upon straightening, made modest progress to be nearest at finish.
Began fairly, gradually drifted back to rear of midfield along the rail, saved ground on home bend to reach 3L 6th coming onto home turn, unable to sustain effort in the run to the line.
Slightly slow out, settled at the back, commenced move rounding home bend and very wide turning for home, ran on past well-beaten horses down the centre of the track.
Began from a wide gate, circled field on stables bend to reach 1L 3rd early in back straight, remained 3-wide without cover down far side, gradually faded under pressure in the run to the finish.
Moderate start, pressed forward to travel outside the leader in 2nd spot, soon weakened after home turn.
Hampered at start, travelled in last few throughout, never a danger.

Jumped well, settled in 4th within 2L of pace, became 5th when pace slackened coming onto back straight, dropped further back passing the Rock and carried wide onto home turn, dropped out under pressure.
Reserved in midfield, forced wide 600M, widest into straight, ran on strongly to lead close home.
Settled down 3-wide towards rear 5Ls off the pace 400M, not clear run early straight, ran on well when switched 150M, got up for 2nd close home
Led along the 2-path, lost lead entering straight but refused to give in, fought on gamely to line, no match with first 2 final stages. (Jockey questioned re his riding position.)
From wide draw eased back to near the rear, made steady progress on straightening, just missed 3rd.
Held up midfield on inner, saved ground, moved up to challenge leader 300M, outsprinted by rivals closing stages.
Taken back to the rear on jumping from wide barrier, 7Ls off leaders in middle stages, made mild progress along the inside from 350M but never reached leaders.
Tracked leaders, shifted wide passing 300M to challenge, kept on same pace.
Chased pace in a 3-wide position without cover, battled on one pace in the straight, no extra final 100M.
Tracked leaders, led from 350M, caught by rivals 100M and weakened rapidly, eased late stages. (Jockey unable to explain disappointing performance.)
Chased leaders early, eased back for cover near 700M but remained in touch, couldn't pick up turning in, soon beaten.
Slow to begin, towards the rear along fence, ran on one paced turning home and failed to reach contention. Awkwardly placed final 50M and eased.
Held up midfield, over-raced middle stages, wide into straight, failed to quicken. (Jockey expressed concern re action of his mount.)
