Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear, 8 lengths back, gradually improved after passing 850M, 4 lengths or so back turning in, finished off very strongly in straight, scored by 1-3/4L.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide, 4 to 5 lengths back, closer on turn, made very good progress in straight to take 2nd.
Moderately away from a middle draw, raced 2 wide, a length or so back, 2nd on turn, took the lead near 300M, headed 150M, stayed on for 3rd.
Away with them, sent forward to take the rail, allowed the rival to cross near 1100M, remained 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on turn, angled out near 500M, finished off evenly in straight.
Began well from gate 11, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well throughout, kept on well early in straight, headed near 300M, slightly weakened thereafter.
Began only fairly, showed limited early speed, raced 6 lengths back on rail, saved ground to near 600M, 4 lengths or so back turning in, made minor progress in straight.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide at rear, 6 to 7 lengths back, a bit closer on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, 2 wide on turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Jumped well, unable to slot in, raced 3 wide behind midfield, no cover from near 900M, closer on turn, very wide turning in, failed to quicken under pressure in straight.
Away with them, positioned 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground throughout, failed to make any progress in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, 8 lengths back, still last turning in, failed to close off in straight.
Out in line, raced 2 wide in midfield, 2 to 3 lengths back on turn, weakened early in straight, eased 150M.
In front of midfield, sat 2 wide, dashed strongly 300M, was hampered and carried in 100M.
Midfield, trapped 3 wide, harmed by the slow pace, dashed strongly despite all negative racing situations.
Slow away, midfield along the fence, not suited by the slow pace, lack room 300M, dashed well for 3rd.
Settled outside the leader, enjoyed the slow sectionals, ran on well until 100M weakened.
Pushed to take rail and led at advantageous slow sectionals, hung on well until 150M weakened.
Pushed to secure box seat, benefited by the slow tempo, emptied 150M.
Eased at start, took cover at back, not suited by the slow tempo, attempted to make ground 3-4 wide from 700M, ran on fairly.
At rear, along the fence, harmed by the slow pace, no dash.
At back, raced keenly, harmed by the slow pace, never improved.

Placing: UR
Comment: Rider being dislodged shortly after the start.
Ridden to take lead, raced on outside fence, travelled strongly, scored unchallenged.
Raced at handy position, responded well when asked for effort passing 400M, worked home solidly.
Settled behind leader to the middle of track, ran on nicely after 200M, just missed 2nd.
Travelled at rear close to outside rail, made good ground after passing 200M, finished nicely.
Settled behind leader, fought hard passing 400M, finished OK.
Taken back from inside barrier at start, gradually made ground, kept on to the line.
Raced behind leader, limited response in the straight.
Taken back from inside barrier at start, gave ground passing 150M.
Settled behind leader, faded out passing 300M.
Commenced well before positioning midfield on fence. Had soft run throughout middle stages before coming off heals at 325m to go on in straight.
Commenced awkwardly and slow away before making up ground to position at rear on the inside. Turned into straight well back before improving through the field to just miss.
Began well before ridden up to contest lead before easing behind eventual leader at 1000m. Eased across heals upon entering the straight before battling away in the straight.
Commenced fairly before ridden up to gain forward position. Outside leader in middle stages before running fairly in straight.
Ridden hard from outside barrier to assume lead from the 1100m. Turned in front before weakening in the later stages of the straight.
Began moderately before being eased in first 100m to position at the rear off the fence. Commenced to improve from the 650m, entering straight second widest runner. Never a winning threat.
Moderately away before easing back to position worse than midfield on fence. Had soft run in transit and offered little in the straight.
Began fairly before being eased in first 200m to position worse than midfield off the fence. Was shuffled back on entering the straight and was never a genuine winning threat.
Commenced well before electing not to contest lead, positioning midfield off the fence. Pulled around heals at 550m to commence run but yielded ground around the bend and in the straight.

Commenced well but was eased from wide barrier to position near the rear three horses off the fence. Improved from the 700m but was impeded at the 650m and again at the 425m. Too far back in straight to threaten.

Wasn't the fastest away and was then eased back across heals to the rear of the field. Attempted to improve from 650m before being pushed extremely wide on straightening before failing to flatter in straight.
Began only moderately before ridden up for 400m to position midfield off the fence. Had clear running on straightening but failed to respond and gave ground in straight.

Began only moderately before improving first 250m to position off the fence behind leading quartet. Was slightly crowded approaching 1000m before being asked for effort upon straightening but failed to respond.

Commenced only fairly and was ridden hard for first 250m to obtain position in first half. Was posted 4 runners wide and continued to race wide throughout middle stages before yielding ground from 500m to be well beaten.
Moderately away from gate 10, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 wide turning in, showed very good response in straight, took the lead near 150M, kept on strongly to the line.
Jumped with them, sent forward to race prominently, took the lead near 1100M, travelled well on turn, kept on very well in straight but couldn't hold off the winner.
Slightly slow out, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, no clear running early in straight, finished off well when clear final 150M to take a place, nearest on line.

Lifted front feet on jumping and away tardily, raced at tail, 5 to 6 lengths back, closer on turn, taken very wide after passing 500M, finished off very strongly in straight to make frame, nearest on line.
Jumped with them, unable to slot in, raced 3 wide better than midfield, improved on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked near 150M, slightly weakened thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Bumped on jumping, raced 2 wide better than midfield, there to turn, no daylight early in straight, finished off evenly when clear thereafter.
Average to begin, raced behind midfield, 4 lengths back, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after straightening and finished off evenly.
Began well from gate 1, sat right behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, kept on evenly early in straight, weakened gradually from 150M.
Taken back to race 2 wide at rear, 5 lengths back, slightly improved on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 3 to 4 lengths turning in, failed to make any progress in straight.
Jumped nicely from the widest draw, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, hard ridden turning in, weakened early in straight, eased thereafter.
Pushed and raced in the box-seat, sat 2L off, closed off nicely from 200M to score by 3/4L.
Jumped awkwardly, raced in just behind midfield 6-1/4L off and took rail near 1000M, ran on well to the line.
Lost ground at the start, settled at the rear, 9-1/4L behind 2 wide, ran on strongly in the straight.
Asked along and led by about 2L, headed at 200M, one paced in the straight.
Taken back and settled to race in behind midfield, 7L behind 2 wide, improved steadily to the line.
Raced towards the rear, 8-1/4L behind along the rail, made ground and ran on to the line.
Pushed to be in front of midfield, 4L behind 2 wide, found no extra approaching 100M.
Travelled in midfield along the rail, was one paced in the straight.
Failed to muster and raced at the rear, 9-3/4L behind along the rail, made marginal ground only.
Rolled into position in midfield, 2 wide throughout, found nothing and eased down at 200M.
Sent forward, sat 2L behind and outside the lead, faded near 300M.
Settled in rear, switched out for a run upon straightening, quickened to hold every chance throughout closing stages but hampered near the finish, finished 2nd, placed 1st.

Ridden positively before settling one back in 3rd, ran on under pressure to hit the front over 250 metres out, shifted out and bumped eventual winner nearing finish, first past the post but placed 2nd.
Settled at the back from the widest gate of the small field, saved ground on the rail turning in, ran on well to be nearest at finish despite interrupted passages close to home.

Taken back for rails run in 6th some 3L off the pace, held similar position turning for home, obtained a clear run on the rail over 250 metres out, fought on steadily without threatening. (Blood in trachea)
Began from a wide gate of the small field, took up running briefly early on home bend and shared the lead into straight, unable to sustain effort and faded gradually inside the final 250 metres.
Settled in 5th within 3L of pace and mainly 2-wide, finished off race well.
Broke well for slender lead on the rail, ceded advantage coming out of back straight, became a joint leader from approaching home straight, unable to sustain effort and swamped over 200 metres out.
Began well from the one draw, settled one back on the rail in 2L 4th, switched off the rail for a run entering straight, kept on before folded up quickly inside the final 200 metres.
Held up 3-wide in mid-division, driven along 350M, let down strongly to lead near 100M, kept on well to score on debut.
Began well, soon restrained to race in midfield, no clear run to 300M, chased well into 2nd last stride.
Chased leaders on inside, loomed a strong chance 250M, no match with winner final 200M, lost 2nd last stride.
Failed to muster despite ridden, held up behind midfield, no clear run early straight before peeling out for clear running 250M, ran on well to the line.
Taken back to race at the rear, switched wide leaving the bend, ran on well down outside producing good late impression.
Soon led, pressed by rival middle stages, ridden along 400M, headed 150M, faded towards the finish.
Began fairly, settled towards the rear 5Ls off the pace, brought wide home, made some progress final 400M but never threatened leaders.
Bustled along to be racing outside leader, drifted out when placed under pressure in straight, outpaced final 150M.
Slowly away, held up in midfield on inside, battled on same pace in the straight, no impression final 200M.
Settled down ahead of midfield, wide no cover during race, kept battling away early straight before weakening passing 200M.
Chased leaders 2-wide, fought on same pace early straight, weakened final 200M. (Jockey unable to offer explanation for poor run.)
Shifted out abruptly on jumping and lost ground, dropped back to race near the rear, kept on same speed turning home, never able to challenge.
From wide draw gradually dropped back to race at the rear, 8Ls off the pace in clear last at 400M, failed to quicken, soon beaten. (Jockey : didn't travel comfortably at any stage.)
Bumped start, raced 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, 3 wide turning in, finished off strongly in straight to score by a neck.
Commenced well from gate 9, raced prominently, 2 wide, travelled well throughout, hit the front near 200M, kept on well thereafter but couldn't hold off the winner late.
Clean jump, sent forward to take the lead, enjoyed the easy lead throughout, kept on well in straight but unable to hold off the first two.
Jumped well, positioned 4 lengths back on rail, angled out from near 550M, finished off well to make frame.
Bumped start, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, easy run on turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Taken back to race 3 wide at rear, moved a bit closer after entering the back straight, 4 wide on turn, kept on evenly early in straight, slightly weakened thereafter.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced 5 to 6 lengths back on rail, saved ground on turn, angled out near 400M, finished off evenly in straight.
Jumped well from gate 10, sent forward to race prominently but trapped 3 wide, no cover throughout, lost position on turn, no further impression thereafter.
Began awkwardly and bumped, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 4 to 5 lengths back turning in, failed to close off in straight.
Hampered at start, raced 2 wide at rear, 6 lengths back, same margin back on turn, failed to make any progress in straight.
Taken back to race at tail, 9 lengths back, still well back on turn, showed nothing in straight, finished tailed out, unacceptable performance.
Jumped well, took the rail easily, allowed the rival to cross near 900M, 2 wide in 2nd on turn, finished off strongly in straight to score.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide in midfield, closer on turn, finished off strongly to take 2nd on line.

Began well, sent forward to race prominently, took the lead after passing 1000M, found rail near 900M, travelled well on turn, kept on strongly early in straight but still headed after passing 200M, stayed on well to take a place.
Slowly away, raced at rear on rail, gradually improved along the rail on turn, 3 lengths back at 400M, no clear running early in straight, finished off strongly when clear after passing 200M.
Moderately away from a tricky gate, unable to slot in, raced 4 wide in midfield, 3 to 4 lengths back on turn, finished off very strongly to be nearest on line.
Average to begin, positioned on rail better than midfield, moved closer along the rail on turn, kept to inside after straightening, finished off evenly.

Moderately away from gate 11, unable to slot in early, taken back to race 3 wide at rear, closer on turn, in traffic early in straight, made some progress when clear thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 3 lengths or so back turning in, finished off evenly in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Bounded at start, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, improved from 550M, very wide turning in, made some progress early in straight, peaked near 200M, weakened thereafter.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide at rear, 5 lengths back on turn, no daylight early in straight, made some progress when clear thereafter without threatening.
Began only fairly, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, 4 lengths back, there to turn, failed to close off in straight.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, 8 lengths back, still well back on turn, taken widest in straight, failed to quicken in straight.
Away with them, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths back, carried wider on turn, weakened early in straight.
Fast into stride, raced 3 wide with no cover, 2 lengths back, carried wider on turn, emptied early in straight when hard run took effect. (Mucus in trachea.)

Taken back from gate 9, positioned on rail behind midfield, 4 lengths or so back on turn, no clear running early in straight, finished off very strongly when clear final 150M to take 2nd.
Jumped well from the widest draw, unable to slot in, raced 3 wide with no cover in midfield, closer on turn, kept on well in straight to take a place.
Average to begin, positioned on rail in midfield, 3 to 4 lengths back, saved ground throughout, finished off well in straight to make frame without threatening.
Away with them, sat 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, easy run on turn, kept to inside after straightening and finished off evenly.
Jumped well, raced prominently, 2 wide, same position on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide, 4 to 5 lengths back, improved from 450M, 4 wide turning in, failed to quicken under pressure in straight.
Clean jump, raced 2 wide better than midfield, travelled keenly early, 2 to 3 lengths back on turn, failed to quicken under pressure in straight.
Average to begin, raced at tail, 7 to 8 lengths back, carried wide turning in, failed to close off in straight.
Crowded on jumping, raced 2 to 3 wide with cover at rear, there to turn, failed to make any progress in straight.
Hard ridden to obtain box seat, benefited by the slow sectionals, closed off strongly 300M.
Pushed forward, benefited by the slow tempo, dominated from 300M.
Settled in midfield along the fence, harmed by the slow pace, dashed well 250M for 3rd.
Pushed forward, sat outside the leader, taken wider from 600M, held ground in straight.
Eased at start, took rail, not suited by the slow pace, dashed well 200M.
Eased back, 2-3 wide, harmed by the slow pace, little dash 250M, run ended 100M.
Eased to rear for cover, 2-3 wide, dashed well 200M despite not suited by the slow pace.
Hard ridden to take rail and led at advantageous slow sectionals, out of fuel 250M.
Midfield, 2 wide, raced keenly, harmed by the slow pace, checked 350M, no dash.
Hard ridden early but not muster, took rail at back, not suited by the slow tempo, never improved.
Eased back, 2-3 wide, harmed by the slow pace, no dash.
Hard ridden to sit in front of midfield, trapped 3-4 wide, emptied 300M.
Settled midfield, asked for effort passing 400M, quickened passing 100M to score.
Raced midfield, responded solidly in the straight and made up nice late ground.
Raced in the box seat, kept on rail at Home Turn, worked home nicely, just missed 2nd.
Settled behind leaders, niggled passing 600M, gained some ground passing 150M.
Hard ridden then took lead after 1300M, fought hard in the straight, gave ground passing 50M.
Ridden along but failed to muster speed, settled at back on rail, one-paced in the straight.
Raced at back, wide on straightening, one-paced, failed to make impression.
Urged to settle outside the lead, commenced to improve near 400M, weakened passing 150M.
Travelled behind midfield, steadied away from heels near 1400M, widest on straightening, limited response in the straight.
Began awkwardly then bumped a runner and lost ground, raced behind midfield on rail, weakened passing 100M.
Taken back at start, always back, never in it.
Jumped well and ridden forward to contest before easing out of speed battle to follow leading pair. Eased around heels upon straightening and was strong to the line.
Jumped fairly and was ridden up for first 200m to gain midfield position. Had soft run on fence following eventual winner. Came across heels and ran on well in straight.
Eased back across the rear of the field to position well back off the fence. Improved between runners approaching the straight and made good late ground in the run to the line.

Jumped well but could not cross early speed inside so elected to ease back to midfield three horses off the fence. Was asked to again improve from 600m before taking the bend wide and then making good ground in the straight.
Restrained right back to the rear of the field on the fence after jumping. Attempted to improve after the 400m but was badly inconvenienced, losing well over a length. Rallied late in the straight.

Commenced fast and led in early stages before challenged on outside. Maintained rail position in middle stages but absorbed too much pressure and gave ground inside final 200m. Rider expressed concern with horse's action.
Was ridden forward but did not have pace of first three, before settling in good position behind speed. Was brushed by another runner approaching turn but was never a genuine threat.
One of the slowest into stride before positioning third last on the fence. Was shuffled back to the tail approaching the straight and never flattered in the run to the line.

Taken back to the tail of the field shortly after the start, positioned one horse off the fence. Asked to improve from well back in the field but was pushed wide on straightening and never threatened.
Began moderately and was then ridden up to maintain just worse than midfield position one off the fence. Was niggled at to maintain position due to solid pace in early and middle stages.
Began well and showed customary fast pace to cross towards lead. Got to lead but could not get to rail so subsequently sat outside horse in second position. Weakened out from 200m.
Commenced well and was ridden forward before easing behind leading trio but positioned three horses off fence. Began to give ground from 450m and was never a threat.
Fast into stride, sent forward to race outside to the leader, there to turn, challenged the leader 400M, took the lead early in straight, kept on well thereafter and scored.
Average to begin, positioned 3 to 4 lengths back on rail, saved ground on turn, finished off strongly in straight to take 2nd.
Began well from gate 1, sat a length behind the leader on rail, saved ground to turn, angled out near 450M, finished off evenly in straight.
Jumped well, positioned 1 out 1 back, wider on turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Moderately away, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well throughout, challenged by rival turning in, headed early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 4 lengths or so back, made minor progress in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Slightly slow out, raced 2 wide at rear, 5 to 6 lengths back on turn, made little headway in straight.
Taken back to race at tail, 8 lengths back, still last turning in, kept to inside after straightening and finished off evenly.
Began awkwardly, positioned on rail in midfield, angled out on turn, weakened gradually in straight.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide in midfield, carried wider on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Began very awkwardly and lost ground, raced at rear on rail, saved ground on turn, weakened early in straight.
Moderately away from the widest draw, unable to slot in, raced 3 wide with no cover better than midfield, carried wider turning in, emptied early in straight.
Settled to race in behind midfield, 5L off along the rail, improved gradually before bumped at 100M, continued on thereafter and won with something in hand.
In midfield along the rail from barrier 7, 3-1/4L behind the lead, ran on well for 2nd despite badly hampered at 100M.
Bumped start, then raced in front of midfield, 3-1/4L off 2 wide, continued on well but shifted in along the straight.
Settled to race outside the lead, about 1/2L off, hampered after 100M but looked it was emptied passing 150M.
Hard ridden to take rail and led by 1/2L, held about a 1L margin until weakened and caught near 100M.
Raced in the box-seat, sat 2L behind the lead, kept on but run ended when checked passing 100M.
Raced towards the rear, 6-1/2L behind 2 wide, continued to make ground to the line.
Bumped start and then hard ridden to be in one-off one-back, kept going until steadied at 100M due to incident.
Taken back and raced at the rear, 7-1/2L behind 2 wide, made late ground.
Stumbled at start and lost ground, raced in worse than midfield, 5-1/2L behind 2 wide, one paced.
Lost ground at start, recovered to be in midfield but wide and without cover, dropped off in the straight.
At the rear, never a factor.
Persevered from a wide gate racing wide up with the pace before settling alongside the leader past the Rock, gained upper hand under pressure over 150 metres out and just held on to the line.
Jumped well, shared the pace early stages before taken one back to 3rd coming off the Rock, switched out to challenge entering straight, ran on well under pressure to just fail to get up on line.
Prominent and wide early, gradually shifted 3L back in joint 4th for cover, switched out for a run entering straight, ran on well.
Hampered at start settling in last few, finished off the race strongly down the centre of the track.
Taken back from the widest gate, travelled wide well back, commenced move on home bend and the widest runner turning in, finished off race strongly down the centre of the track.
Broke well and attempted to make all, held slender advantage on the rail most of the way until headed about 150 metres out.
Settled in midfield on the rail, gradually improved to just over 2L back on the rail, angled out for a run entering straight, kept on well under pressure without threatening.
Ridden along just behind the leaders in 5th within 2L of pace, lost a couple of lengths when carried backward near the Rock, dropped to 7th turning into straight, fought on well.
Slowly away and then crowded losing ground, travelled at the back on the rail, checked and lost position 500 metres out, produced some late impression.
Settled in midfield, steadied passing the 600 metres, saved ground turning for in, ran home one-paced. (Questioned for disappointing performance)
Awkward start and then hampered, ridden for speed before snatched back to 8th 800 metres out, forced wide without cover approaching home bend, gave ground under pressure in straight.
Held up in mid-division, pushed along 500M, led the chase on leader 200M, dug deep to get up last stride.
From wide draw ridden forward and crossed to the lead 1200M, led at good pace middle stages, established clear lead 400M, kept on well to the line only to be caught last stride.
Began well from draw 1, reserved towards the rear along the fence, switched out 450M, chased solidly in the straight and made it to 3rd.
Held up in midfield, ridden 400M out, made up good ground in the straight and not far off placing.
Eased back to race towards the rear, brought wide into straight, chased steadily to go 5th near line.
Began awkwardly and lost ground, held up at the rear, ridden under 2f out, stayed on final 300M without troubling the leaders.
Bustled along after the start to be chasing leaders along the fence, came under pressure 500M, battled on same pace in the straight, never dangerous.
Restrained to race in the rear pair, 7Ls off the pace middle stages, failed to pick up on straightening, never a threat.
From draw 12 driven along to chase the pace, caught 3-wide no cover until 600M, tired inside 250M.
Tracked leaders, under pressure from 600M, weakened over final 250M.
In midfield along the 3-path, outpaced passing 400M, soon beaten.
Crowded for room on jumping, settled down 3-wide towards rear of midfield, struggled to keep up nearing the straight, soon out of contention.

Began smartly, sent forward to race prominently, 4 off the fence, travelled well throughout, kept on strongly to the line and scored.
Moderately away, raced nearer to the middle of the track, a length back, showed very good response in the final 400M to take 2nd, nice debut.
Jumped well from the middle draw, raced prominently, 3 away from the stands rail, kept on very well final 400M to take a place, good debut.
Shifted out on jumping and bumped, raced in midfield, 4 off the fence, finished off well to make frame without threatening.
Began fairly from gate 12 and brushed, raced prominently on the stands rail, took the lead near 300M, peaked and headed near 150M, weakened thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Brushed at start, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on the stands rail, showed limited response final 400M, finished off evenly only.
Clean jump from gate 9, positioned near to the stands rail, half length back, failed to quicken under pressure final 400M, ran on one pace to the line. (See Racing Incidents.)
Away with them, positioned nearer to the middle of the track, two and a half length back, travelled keenly near 700M, failed to quicken final 400M.
Began fairly from gate 1, raced in the middle of the track, 1 to 2 lengths back, peaked 400M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Bumped on jumping, positioned 2 lengths behind, near to the stands rail, failed to quicken final under pressure 400M.
Slightly slow out, raced at rear throughout, never a threat.
Began awkwardly from gate 2, positioned 3 lengths behind in the middle of the track, failed to quicken final 400M, emptied near 200M, eased thereafter.
Hard ridden early, midfield 2 wide, not suited by the slow pace, dashed strongly 300M to score.
Eased back, unleashed strong finishing efforts 250M despite not suited by the slow pace.
Slow away, took rail at back, harmed by the slow pace, lack room 4-2, dashed strongly when clear.
Settled in front, 2 wide, enjoyed the slow tempo, ran on well until 50M run ended.
Eased to obtain box seat, on heels early, benefited by the slow sectionals, ran on well until 150M out of fuel.
Eased back, 2 wide, harmed by the slow pace, dashed well 250M, lack room 50M.
Took rail and lead easily, clocked slow sectionals but raced too keenly, emptied 300M.
Began only fairly then was crowded for room and lost ground, raced at tail, quickened passing 100M, finished strongly to score.
At the start was crowded for room, settled behind midfield, gradually made ground passing 300M, missed by SH.
Took lead with nice early speed, responded solidly in the straight, missed win by SH.
Ridden along then settled box seat, ran on nicely in the straight, worked home well.
Ridden along but failed to muster speed, settled at back, widest on straightening, gained ground passing 100M.
Urged to settle outside the lead, responded OK in the early part of straight, gave ground passing 100M.
Raced midfield on rail, near 200M was momentarily eased away from heels, one-paced.
Settled midfield, wide on straightening, limited response in the straight.
Began awkwardly, raced midfield, limited response, failed to make impression.
Settled at handy position, near 800M was left racing wide and without cover, faded out passing 300M.
Urged to settle behind leaders, made the home turn awkwardly, weakened passing 200M.
Raced at rear on rail, always back, never in it.
Jumped well from wide barrier before ridden hard across field to assume lead at 900m. Turned for home a length clear before getting clear inside 200m and fighting on for narrow win.

Only moderately into stride before ridden up for first 200m to position midfield. Ridden up again from 800m to improve position before entering the straight one of the widest runners. Sprinted well once balanced to just miss.
Away well before drifting back to worse than midfield on fence position. Improved position prior to straightening before getting a gap in between runners at the 250m and hitting line well.
Jumped ok and then eased back to the rear from wide barrier. Ridden hard from 550m to improve position before entering straight well back and making significant late ground.
Was one of the slowest into stride before ridden up to position midfield off the fence. Eased across heels to the outside after straightening and made good late ground over concluding stages.

Eased back after the start to position near the tail of the field. Stayed close to the rail on cornering and in the straight and was crowded for room from 250m to 150m before coming out and then hitting line strongly.

Commenced fairly and maintained rail position settling midfield three pairs back. Improved between runners at the 550m before taking the bend awkwardly. Battled on in the straight but found others stronger to the line.
Began well and came across to position just behind leading pair off the fence. Cornered in second position for boxing on in the straight but fading out last 150m.

Commenced well before being obtaining a forward position. Commenced to race ungenerously between 650m and 350m before attempting to come off the rail but losing a length before straightening. Didn't flatter in the run home.
Ridden hard from the start to come across and assume lead. Was headed for the lead after the 900m mark. Brushed running rail approaching 700m before weakening out in the straight.
Commenced slow before dropping to the tail. Lost touch with the field throughout middle stages travelling multiple lengths behind second last horse. Was never in the race.

Commenced awkwardly before improving to midfield. Commenced to hang out badly from the 600m when attempting to improve however lost ground throughout this section. Never looked comfortable and returned lame next day.
Jumped well from gate 10, raced 2 wide, 2 to 3 lengths back, angled out near 550M, finished off strongly to score.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide, 4 lengths or so back, there to turn, no clear running early in straight, finished off strongly when clear thereafter to take 2nd.
Bounded in the air on jumping, unbalanced the rider and lost ground, raced at tail, moved a bit closer on turn, made very good progress in straight to take a place, nearest on line.
Slightly slow out, raced at rear on rail, 6 lengths back, similar position on turn, no daylight early in straight, finished off strongly when clear thereafter to make frame.
Moderately away from gate 9, raced 3 wide at rear, 5 to 6 lengths back, similar position on turn, made good progress in straight.
Slightly slow out, hard ridden to recover, took the lead near 900M, led by a length on turn, kept on well early in straight, headed near 150M, slightly weakened thereafter.
Bumped start and unbalanced, raced 3 wide with cover, 4 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Moderately away from a wide draw, sent forward to take the early lead, headed near 900M, sat right behind the leader on turn, failed to quicken under pressure in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped well from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after straightening, steadied off heels near 200M, showed some response when clear close home.
Jumped with them, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, no clear running in straight, steadied off heels near 50M, not able to be fully tested.
Moderately away from gate 13, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, allowed rival to cross near 900M, 2 lengths back on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Began fairly from a middle draw, raced 3 wide with no cover, 3 lengths back, there to turn, weakened early in straight when hard run took effect.
Moderately away from the widest draw, unable to slot in, raced very wide in midfield, no cover, 4 wide on turn, weakened early in straight when hard run took toll.
Began very awkwardly, bumped and unbalanced, raced 2 wide at rear, 6 to 7 lengths back, very wide turning in, weakened early in straight.
Awkward start, then ridden to take rail and led by 3/4L, kicked away at 200M to score comfortably by 2L.
Raced in midfield, 3-1/2L behind along the rail, continued on well to the line but was no match to the winner.
Eased back and raced at the rear, 6-3/4L behind along the rail, ran on strongly to the line.
Jumped fairly, in worse than midfield, 4-3/4L off on the rail, interrupted run on inner straight, made slight ground.
Raced just in front of midfield, 2-3/4L behind 2 wide, pretty much one paced to the line.
Shifted ground at the start, then ridden to be in one-off one-back, flattened near 150M.
Bumped start, raced at the rear, 7L behind 2 wide, improved past tired runners only but ran on.
Settled to race in the box-seat, kept on going until weakened out passing 200M.
Crowded then hard ridden to be up with the speed, sat outside lead from 800M, weakened passing 250M.
Crowded at the start and lost ground, raced close to the rear, never improved.
Just behind midfield, 2 wide, raced ungenerously in the straight, wasn't in it.
In midfield, wide and without cover, gave ground in the straight.
Settled behind midfield in 8th, in similar position turning in, quickened well inside the final 200 metres to snatch victory final strides.
Jumped best, used natural speed to soon take up running, obtained rails run passing the 1000 metres, unable to sustain effort and pipped at post.
Jumped well from a wide gate, pressed forward to vie for lead settling 2-wide 1L back, fought on under pressure in straight but unable to peg back the winner throughout closing stages, lost 2nd late.
Jumped fairly, settled in forward of midfield, some 3L back in 5th turning in, bumped a few times early in straight, ran on well to be nearest at finish.
Never far off on the rail, came under pressure turning into straight, failed to get a clear passage despite attempts and forced to check 250 metres out, no further impression.
Awkward start losing ground, quickly recovered to rear of midfield, saved ground on inside straightening for home, finished off the race well.
Moderate start, ridden forward to join 2nd coming out of back straight, unable to sustain effort inside the final 200 metres after racing wide without cover throughout.
Ridden early travelling wide in midfield throughout back straight, widest runner turning for home, ran on past well-beaten horses but without threatening.
Soon taken back to race in rear, travelled one from last most of the way before running past well-beaten horses closing stages.
Moderate start from a wide gate settling well behind, ran on well past well-beaten horses in closing stages.
Ridden along before settling wide in forward of midfield, jockey renewed pressure rounding home bend, found nothing. (Bled)
Jumped fairly, soon taken back for rails run in midfield, yielded ground in straight.
Settled down behind mid-division, into clear top of straight, quickened up well to lead 150M, kept on well to line.
Steadied after the start to obtain cover, held up in rear 7Ls off the pace, made good progress when switched to outside in straight, got up for 2nd in blanket finish for the minor placings.
Emerged as the leader from 1200M, set good pace to straight, responded well when driven out 350M, headed near 150M, lost 2nd place near last stride.
Crowded for room on jumping, dropped back to 2nd last, brought wide in straight, ran on well to be nearest at the line, just missed placing.
Settled just behind the pace, within striking distance always, ran on mildly from 400M but well held by leaders.
Held up 2-wide in midfield, 3-4Ls off the good pace rounding home turn, ran on only fairly in straight, not reached leaders.
Pressed leader on outside, kept on same pace early straight before weakening final 200M.
Tracked leaders in a fast run race, responded only fairly turning in, weakened away inside final 200M.
Held up along the fence in mid-division, ridden out 450M, couldn't muster the finishing pace, never dangerous.
Chased leaders 3-wide, lost cover from 900M, weakened from 300M out.
Moderately away from gate 11, raced prominently but trapped wide early, found cover near 700M, a length or so back on turn,finished off very strongly in straight to score.
Jumped well, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 lengths back, same margin back on turn, angled out early in straight and finished off strongly to take 2nd.
Bumped start, unable to slot in early, slightly taken back near 800M for cover, a length behind the leader on rail turning, angled out early in straight, made some headway thereafter to take a place.

Shifted out on jumping and bumped, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, shared lead on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked after passing 200M, headed shortly thereafter, kept on evenly to the line.

Moderately away from a tricky gate, raced prominently but trapped 3 wide with no cover, shared lead on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed after passing 200M, slightly weakened thereafter.
Bumped start and unbalanced, raced at rear on rail, 4 lengths or so back, 2 wide on turn, made some headway early in straight, awkwardly placed near 150M, finished off evenly thereafter.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, 6 lengths back, same margin back on turn, made good progress in straight to be nearest on line.
Away with them, raced 2 wide at rear, 4 lengths or so back, 3 wide on turn, no clear running early in straight, finished off evenly when clear thereafter.
Began well from the widest gate, trapped very wide early,slightly taken back thereafter for cover, 3 wide with cover in midfield on turn,finished off evenly in straight.
Average to begin, raced 3 wide at rear, wider on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Shifted in on jumping and bumped, sent forward to race prominently on rail, shared the lead with the rivals on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Bumped start, positioned on rail in midfield, there to turn, failed to make any progress in straight.
Jumped well, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, there to turn,finished off very strongly instraight to score by a nose.
Away with them, raced 2 wide, a length or so back, hampered near 1100M, similar position on turn, finished off very strongly, just narrowly beaten.
Commenced well from the widest gate, raced prominently, 2 wide, shared lead turning in, took the lead early in straight, kept on well thereafter butcouldn't hold off thefirst two late.

Average to begin, positioned 3 to 4 lengths back on rail, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after straightening, blocked near 250M, angled out thereafter and finished off strongly when clear final 50M.
Moderately away fromgate 1,positioned 1 to 2 lengths behindthe leader on rail, easy run on turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Jumped with them, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well throughout, peaked early in straight, headed near 300M, kept on evenly to the line.
Out in line, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, bumped near 900M, checked off heels and unbalanced near 600M, very wide turning in, made minor progress in straight.

Crowded shortly after start, raced at rear on rail, 5 lengths back, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after straightening, made some progress before blocked near 100M, not able to be ridden out late.
Slowly away, raced 2 wide at rear, 5 to 6 lengths back, travelled keenly and bumped near 900M, still 4 to 5 lengths back on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Clean jump, raced 2 wide behind midfield, angled out 600M, awkwardly placed near 500M, finished off one-paced in straight.
Jumped well, positioned 2 wide, a length back, clipped heels and lost ground near 1100M, 3lengths back on turn, kept on evenly early in straight,weakened from final 150M.
Moderately away from a wide draw, raced 2 wide at rear, 3 wide on turn, failed to close off in straight. (Bled.)
Crowded shortly after start, raced at rear on rail, 5 lengths back turning in, failed to make any progress in straight.
Began fairly from gate 9, unable to slot in, raced 3 wide and without cover, 2 lengths back, moved closer on turn, weakened early in straight when hard run took toll, eased late.

Away with them, raced 2 wide, 4 lengths or so back, same position on turn, taken wide in straight and finished off very strongly to score by a narrow margin.
Jumped well from gate 1, took the lead easily, travelled comfortably throughout, kicked clear after turning in, kept on very well, just couldn't hold off the winner on line.
Jumped with them, sent forward to race a length behind in 2nd, 2 wide, there to turn, kept on evenly to the line.
Began only fairly, raced at tail, 5 to 6 lengths back, same margin back on turn, inconvenienced near 350M, finished off strongly to make frame, nearest on line.
Moderately away from the widest draw, raced 3 wide at rear, 5 lengths or so back, very wide turning in, made some progress in straight without threatening the first few.
Commenced well, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 lengths back, same position on turn, crowded near 400M, finished off evenly in straight.
Began well from a tricky gate, unable to slot in, raced 3 wide, 2 lengths back, no cover throughout, hung in early in straight, finished off evenly thereafter. (See Racing incidents.)
Average to begin, sat 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground throughout, finished off one-paced in straight.
Began fairly, positioned 3 to 4 lengths back on rail, steadied off heels near 600M, checked near 400M, no clear running in straight, not able to test properly.
Began fairly, raced at rear on rail, 5 lengths back, there to turn, took inside run in straight but found no daylight, not able to test properly.
Settled in box seat, enjoyed the slow sectionals, improved steadily 400M, closed off strongly to score.
Pushed forward, sat just off the leader in 2 wide, benefited by the slow pace, hung on well until 100M overhauled.
Prominent, 2 wide, favoured by the slow sectionals, hung in badly 250M, ran on for 3rd.
Slow away, hard ridden to keep up in midfield along the fence, not suited by the slow tempo, dashed well 200M.
Behind midfield, 2 wide, dashed well 200M despite not suited by the slow tempo.
Trapped 3 wide throughout in midfield, harmed by the slow pace, still held ground in straight.
At back, trapped 2-3 wide, harmed by the slow pace, little dash 200M, lack room 50M.
Pushed to take rail and led at advantageous slow sectionals, soon out of fuel 250M.
Eased at start, took rail at rear, harmed by the slow pace, little dash 150M.
Hard ridden to keep up at rear, not suited by the slow pace, never improved.
Took lead with nice early speed, travelled comfortably, responded solidly in the straight to score.
Near 1300M was inconvenienced, settled midfield on rail, wide on straightening, made nice ground passing 100M, worked home solidly.
Settled box seat, leaving 1100M was bumped and became badly unbalanced, gradually gained ground in the straight, finished well.
Settled at back, asked for effort passing 700M, made ground passing 100M, lame right front leg after race.
Began only fairly, then failed to muster speed despite being hard ridden, raced at back, one-paced in the straight.
Raced at rear, tried to improve on straightening, one-paced in the straight, rider questioned.
Taken back at start, widest on straightening, one-paced.
Raced midfield, improved passing 700M, gave ground passing 150M.
Difficult to settle in the early and middle stages, near 600M moved to outside the lead, weakened noticeably passing 200M, failed to make impression.
Settled outside the lead, hung in in the middle stages, no response in the straight.
Began well before positioning outside leader. Travelled well before hitting lead prior to straightening and then pinching a break in straight. Toughed it out to the line.

Jumped well before easing back to midfield to position on the fence. Had economical run throughout before improving from 400m into clear running and getting home strongly in the straight to just miss.

Jumped fairly before being eased back to midfield position off the fence. Improved from the 500m but still gave away big start to leaders upon entering straight. Made solid late ground in the run to the line.

One of the last into stride before being eased back across the tail of the field to settle on the fence. Was always well back in the run before staying closer to the inside in the straight where he made some late ground.

Was taken back to the rear of the field, positioning one horse off the fence. Commenced to improve from 650m before being forced to hold position approaching bend. Made good late ground to not be beaten far.

Commenced fairly before ridden up to position in prominent position. Travelled well throughout middle stages before being asked to quicken from 400m to keep in touch with leading pair but left slightly flat-footed.
Eased back after the start to position well off the speed. Attempted to improve to the outside at the 500m before making some late ground in the straight.
Ridden up to obtain midfield position before settling off the fence in middle stages. Came under pressure at the 500m before losing position and not flattering in the run.
Jumped well before coming across field to get uncontested lead. Travelled well in middle stages before weakening out in the straight.

Began well and held inside position behind the speed on fence. Blundered at the 1200m when not settling and racing tight between runners. Began to give ground before straightening and was well beaten.

Ridden hard from barriers to obtain forward position however was posted three wide without cover after speed inside held position. Began giving ground at the 600m and never threatened in the straight.
Was taken back to the tail of the field before slightly losing touch in middle stages. Entered the straight well back and was never a threat.
Jumped with them, positioned 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, moved a bit closer on turn, made very good progress in straight and scored.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide at rear, 6 lengths back, taken wide turning in, finished off very strongly in straight to take 2nd, just narrowly beaten.
Fast into stride, took the lead easily, enjoyed the easy lead to turn, kept on well in straight, headed after passing 100M, lost 2nd on line.
Away with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 to 4 lengths back, angled out near 450M, made some progress in straight to make frame without threatening.
Began only fairly, sat right behind the leader on rail, easy run to turn, made contact early in straight, finished off evenly thereafter.
Taken back from gate 9, raced at tail, 6 to 7 lengths back, still last turning in, made some headway in straight.

Average to begin, difficult to settle early, raced 2 wide behind midfield, improved after entering the back straight, raced 3 wide, 2 lengths back on turn, failed to quicken under pressure in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)

Began smartly, raced prominently but 3 wide, moved closer after passing 1250M, 2 wide thereafter, there to turn, peaked and made contact early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter. (Lame right front leg next day.)
Taken back from gate 8, positioned 5 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, failed to make any progress in straight.
Began fairly, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, allowed rival to cross near 1200M, 2 to 3 lengths back in the middle stages, carried wider turning in, failed to close off in straight.
Sent forward, settled to race outside the lead, pulled away from 150M and won comfortably by 1-3/4L.
Raced in midfield, 2 wide throughout, battled on to the line to take 2nd, 1-3/4L behind the winner.
Bumped start, raced in front of midfield, wide and without cover at turn, kept going and held onto 3rd.
Taken back to be at the rear, stayed one off, showed good kick from 200M and ran on well to the line.
Awkward start, in behind midfield, shifted to 3 wide at turn, made ground and continued on well to the line.
Steadied after the start, settled in just behind midfield along the rail, improved and closed off fairly.
Sent forward to take lead, took rail near 600M, headed passing 200M, continued paced.
Pushed and settled in one-off one-back, one paced and out of steam late.
Awkward start and lost ground, raced at the rear and 2 wide at turn, tight at 250M, one paced.
Travelled in midfield along the rail, was one paced in the straight. (Heart irregularity)
Asked to take the box-seat, kept on until flattened at 200M.
In midfield, wide but with cover, showed nothing.
Pressed forward from the widest gate before settling 2-wide in rear of midfield, soon came to challenge on straightening, quickened well to take charge inside the 100 metres, won readily.

Ridden positively from a wide gate, settled 2-wide in a distant 4th from the tear-away leader, gained 3rd leaving the Rock and narrow advantage entering straight only to be collared inside the 100 metres.

Broke well, soon taken back to forward of midfield in 5th on the rail, became 6th in a similar position coming off the Rock, commenced move entering straight gaining to 1L 3rd inside the 200M, unable to sustain effort close to home.

Jumped awkwardly losing ground, ridden along in rear of field on the rail, remained well behind in back straight, renewed pressure rounding home bend, finished off well when forced to check final stages.

Began fairly, settled a distant 3rd from the tear-away leader in back straight, switched wide for a run when within 2L of pace in 4th turning for home, kept on before finding no extra inside the final 200M. (Mucus in trachea)
Soon dropped to rear of midfield despite ridden early, came under pressure rounding home bend and saved ground turning in, kept on same pace in the run home.

Ridden positively from a wide gate, chased the pace-setter round the stables bend before settling 4L back in its own pace in back straight, saved ground as a close-up 3rd turning for home but soon weakened.
Slow away, settled in rear, commenced move rounding home bend and went wide into straight, produced good late impression.

Ridden forward from a wide gate to soon take up running, went clear in a quick pace in back straight, came back to the main body of the field coming onto home bend and folded up quickly after straightening. (Jockey warned)
Settled in last few, came under pressure rounding home bend, kept on one pace without quickening under pressure.
Ridden early before settling in 6th in midfield, similar though wider entering home straight, faded gradually. (Questioned for disappointing performance)
Soon dropped to last few, made no impression in the run home. (Mucus in trachea)
Broke well, eased to sit behind leaders, quickened up well to re-gain lead 150M, kept on strongly, edged clear inside 100M to win with something in hand.
From draw 12 bustled along to lead nearing 1000M, given a breather home turn, fought on well when tackled by eventual winner early straight, headed 200M, kept on for 2nd.
Sent forward to be chasing leader, had every chance turning in, held by first 2 in the run home.
Reserved in 2nd last, brought wide into straight, closed off well to claim 4th just in time, nearest finish. (Hung final 100M, difficult to ride.)
From draw 11 chased leaders in 4th place, kept on steadily in straight without troubling first few.
In mid-division 5Ls off the pace on settling, crept closer nearing top of straight, kept on same pace when driven out, held ground only.
Crowded for room at start, held up towards the rear, ridden 1 1/2f out, kept grinding away without threatening.
Chased leaders in midfield, saved ground on the fence but unable to quicken on straightening, faded final 150M.
Crowded for room on jumping, raced wide without cover throughout in midfield, moved closer from 500M, run ended 200M.
Held up behind midfield, 3-wide making the turn for home, bustled along 550M but couldn't pick up on leaders, weakened final 200M, never on terms.
Taken across behind runners from wide barrier, always at rear and never got going in the straight.
Settled towards the rear, 6Ls off the pace home turn, didn't respond and struggled to the line.

Taken back from a wide draw, positioned 5 to 6 lengths back on rail, closer on turn, angled out near 500M, made contact early in straight, finished off very strongly thereafter and scored.

Taken back to race at rear early, gradually moved closer along the rail on the first turn, 4 lengths behind the leader in the middle stages, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after straightening and take 2nd.
Jumped with them, taken back to race 2 wide at rear, 7 lengths back, improved from 550M, made contact turning in, made very good progress in straight to be nearest on line.

Moderately away, unable to slot in early, taken back to race at rear on rail, 7 lengths back, a bit closer on turn, blocked and bumped near 350M, finished off well when clear thereafter to make frame. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began well, raced 2 wide, 6 lengths back, closer on turn, crowded early in straight, finished off evenly thereafter.
Away with them, bumped early, raced 2 wide in midfield, 4 lengths back, closer on turn, made contact early in straight, failed to quicken under pressure thereafter.
Began fairly from gate 1, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length to turn, peaked early in straight, headed after passing 300M, weakened gradually thereafter.

Moderately away from a tricky gate, unable to slot in, trapped very wide early, settled 2 wide, 2 lengths back from near 1500M, there to turn, improved from 600M, peaked near 300M, weakened thereafter.
Average to begin, raced 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, there to turn, failed to quicken early in straight, weakened gradually from 250M, eased final 100M. (See Racing Incidents.)

Out in line, unable to slot in and bumped early, sent forward on the first turn and settled in 2nd, 2 wide, same position on turn, weakened early in straight, eased final furlong, finished tailed out.
Pushed forward to take rail and lead, clocked fast sectionals, hung on well to win.
At back, along the fence, benefited by the fast pace, progressed steadily 300M for 2nd.
Eased to sit in front of midfield along the fence, ran on well to the line for 3rd.
Pushed forward, sat 2 wide, not suited by the fast tempo, held ground in straight.
Eased to sit behind midfield, trapped 3 wide, suited by the fast pace, made steady ground 300M.
Eased back, trapped 3-4 wide, suited by the fast tempo, progressed steadily 250M.
Pressed forward, box seat, harmed by the fast pace, out of fuel 150M.
Slow away, at back, favoured by the fast tempo, made steady ground 300M, lack room 200M.
Eased back, 2 wide, benefited by the fast tempo, just ran on fairly.
Hard ridden forward, sat 2 wide, harmed by the fast pace, emptied 300M.
Hard ridden to keep up at rear, suited by the fast pace, no progress.
Eased back, 2-3 wide suited by the fast pace, never competitive.
Fast out, settled box seat, asked for effort passing 600M, gained ground passing 150M, finished strongly to score.
Raced midfield, in the straight gradually made ground, finished solidly.
Ridden along in the early stages, took lead after 800M, responded solidly in the straight, worked home well.
Taken back at start, gained nice ground passing 200M, finished well.
Taken back from widest gate, raced at tail, made up some nice late ground.
Began awkwardly and lost ground, settled behind midfield, wide on straightening, one-paced.
At start was crowded for room and became unbalanced, raced at back, made some ground passing 300M.
Raced at handy position, placed under pressure but only one-paced.
Began awkwardly then taken back, made some ground passing 200M, rider questioned.
Travelled behind midfield, took rail passing 700M, no response.
Raced behind the lead, gave ground passing 300M, failed to run on.
Settled midfield, passing the 700M was checked away from heels, no response, failed to make impression.
Settled midfield on rail, near 650M was crowded for room and lost ground, no response in the straight.
Raced midfield, widest on straightening, never in it.
Jumped well and took up lead. Carved out fast middle sections and left rivals floundering. Turned for home clear and kicked strong in straight for easy win.
Held position on leaders back. Came across heals in straight when horses outside weakened and ran home well. No match for winner but big gap to third.
Settled second last as per his pattern before directed to the outside on straightening. Made good late ground but was not a winning threat given race shape.
Settled midfield before improving position between runners at the 600m and looked like threatening upon straightening. Weakened out in the run to the line and was perhaps a little disappointing.
Taken back from barrier to position near the tail off the fence. Pulled out wider upon straightening and worked to the line fairly given the way the race was run.
Eased back after the start and raced three horses off the fence with cover until the 1100m. Positioned back closer to the fence from that point before being one paced in the straight.
One of the slowest away before ridden up to midfield off the fence. Looked close enough on straightening but was under pressure upon turning for the line. Hung in in straight and was well held.

Commenced well and was ridden up to forward position before ultimately settling outside the pace. Was under riding the length of back straight to hold position after posted wider by another horse. Weakened out in straight.

One of the slowest away before hard ridden to come across tail of field. Maintained 3 length margin on second last runner until 850m. Was still a clear last upon straightening and failed to flatter in the straight.

Sent forward from widest barrier before easing behind leading four but travelling a little wide in middle stages. Was slightly eased approaching 600m before coming under pressure at 500m. Weakened out in the run to the line.
Crowded start, raced at rear on rail, 6 to 7 lengths back, still last turning in, no daylight early in straight, finished off very strongly when clear final furlong, scored by a neck.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, 5 lengths or so back, same position on turn, finished off strongly to take 2nd. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began well from a wide draw, raced 3 wide, 2 lengths or so back, no cover from near 1000M, similar position on turn, finished off well to take a place.
Bumped start and unbalanced, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, there to turn, made good progress early in straight, peaked near 100M, kept on evenly to the line.

Bumped start, raced at rear on rail, 6 lengths back, saved ground on turn, angled out early in straight but only got restricted room, made some progress before checked near 100M, not able to be fully tested.
Taken back from the widest gate, raced 2 wide at rear, 7 lengths back, still 5 to 6 lengths back on turn, taken wide in straight and made good progress to be nearest on line.
Shifted out at start and bumped, sent forward to take the lead, travelled comfortably throughout, kept on well early in straight, peaked near 200M, headed 100M, kept on evenly to the line.
Shifted in at start and made contact, sat a length behind the leader on rail, easy run on turn, kept to inside after straightening and finished off evenly.
Bumped start, raced 4 lengths back on rail, saved ground on turn, angled out early in straight but still found no daylight, finished off evenly when clear thereafter.
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground throughout, no clear running after turning in, showed little response when clear close home.

Bumped start, raced 2 wide at rear, 5-6Ls back, travelled keenly and steadied off heels near 1000M, still 5Ls back on turn, no clear running early in straight, finished off evenly when clear thereafter. (Lame right front leg.)
Moderately away, raced 2 wide, 2 to 3 lengths back, similar position on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened from final 200M.
Away with them, raced 2 wide, 4 lengths back, awkwardly placed near 900M, same margin back on turn, showed limited response early in straight, crowded near 250M, one-paced thereafter.
Jumped well from a wide draw, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, there to turn, peaked near 300M, weakened gradually thereafter, eased late.
Eased back and raced close to the rear, 5-3/4L behind wide but with cover, closed off strongly to score by 1/2L.
Pushed before settling to race in the box-seat, 1-3/4L off the pace, looked likely until caught by the winner late.
Rolled into one-off one-back position, sat 1-3/4L off the lead, showed good kicks and kept on nicely to the line.
Raced in midfield, 3-1/4L behind 2 wide, ran on nicely to the line from about 150M though bumped at 75M.
Taken back and raced at the rear, 7-1/4L behind 2 wide, made nice ground all the way to the line.
Travelled in behind midfield, 4-1/4L behind 3 wide but with cover, made slight ground and ran on to the line.
In midfield initially but wide, then improved but continued to race wide, in touch until flattened passing 200M.
Failed to muster, settled in front of midfield, wide but with cover, bumped at 75M but was nonetheless one paced.
Rolled forward to take the rail and led, kept on until weakened and headed at 200M.
Travelled in midfield along the rail, 3-1/2L behind along the rail, continued on one paced to the line.
Taken back to race at the rear, 7L behind along the rail, ran on and closed off fairly.
Sent forward and settled to race outside the lead, weakened passing 250M.
Midfield until checked at 1300M, then travelled keenly in worse than midfield 2 wide, showed nothing.
Took cover and in behind midfield along the rail, made no ground and emptied near 200M.
Ridden to lead from a wide gate, obtained rails run passing the 1000 metres, joined briefly after straightening, hung on well to defy challengers inside the final 200 metres.
Settled in midfield on the rail, ran on steadily to claim 2nd final strides.
Moderate start, settled 2L back in 4th, kept on steadily to reach 2nd at the 200 metres only to be pipped for position at post.
Settled well behind, did not find much room early in straight, finished off the race well inside the final 200 metres.
Crowded at start, gradually improved to joint 7th on the rail behind midfield, fought on steadily without threatening.
Settled in midfield, ran home one-paced.
Settled just over 1L back in 3rd on the rail, baulked for a run after straightening, ran home one-paced.
Never better than midfield, made no impression in straight.
Began from the widest gate settling at the back, shaken up entering straight, never threatening.
Ridden early before settling outside the leader, drew level briefly after straightening, dropped out tamely inside the final 300 metres. (Questioned for disappointing performance)
Soon led, pressed by rival from 1300M setting fast pace in middle stages, shook off pursuers inside 400M, kept on well under top weight and had enough in hand to hold off 2nd late.
Reserved in midfield, about 2.5L to make up on winner early straight, did best work final 200M, nearest finish.
Held up near last, stayed on well between runners final 400M, got up for 3rd late but not reach first two.
Took keen hold behind leaders, moved up to 2nd passing 400M, tried hard to run down winner but always held, one paced final 200M.
Reserved towards the rear, 6Ls to make up 400M, stayed on moderately making late progress. Promising return.
From draw 1 tracked leaders along the inside, kept on same pace when driven out in the straight, faded out of contention final 150M.
Settled down in midfield 3-wide, stayed on over final 400M without any threat to leaders.
Slowly away, held up behind mid-division 5Ls off the pace, kept on only fairly in straight, never going the pace to challenge.
Slow out, held up 3-wide behind mid-division, wide into straight, made limited progress to the line, no impression.
Never far off from pace along the 3-path, lost cover passing 1000M, fought one same pace in straight before fading final 150M.
Dropped back from wide draw, held up in the rear 7-8Ls back , brought wide to challenge on straightening, not reach leaders.
Behind mid-division early stages, hampered 750M and shuffled back to rear, ran past a couple of beaten horses in the straight, never a threat.
Held up midfield along the fence, severely checked 750M and lost ground, kept on same pace early straight, weakened from 250M.
Pressed leader (the eventual winner) on outside, pace fast middle stages, found nothing when driven along 400M, weakened to last.
Began well, raced 2 wide, 2-1/2 lengths back, same position on turn, hard ridden from 300M, finished off very strongly and scored.
Clean jump, positioned 2 to 3 lengths back on rail, easy run on turn, finished off strongly to take 2nd.

Jumped well, sat right behind the leader on rail, there to turn, showed good response early in straight, took the lead near 200M but headed shortly thereafter, stayed on well to take a place, missed 2nd on line.

Bumped start and unbalanced, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length on turn, kept on well early in straight, headed near 200M, weakened gradually thereafter, just stayed on for 4th. (Lost left front plate.)
Away with them, raced 3 wide, 3 lengths or so back, found cover on turn, made minor progress in straight without threatening.
Bumped start and badly unbalanced, recovered to race prominently, 2 wide, peaked shortly after turning in, kept on evenly to the line.
Away with them, raced 2 wide at rear, 8 lengths back, similar position on turn, made some headway in straight without threatening.
Taken back from gate 13, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, travelled keenly near 700M, no cover thereafter, finished off evenly in straight.
Taken back from the widest gate, raced at tail, 11 lengths back at 800M, moved closer on turn but still last turning in, made some headway in straight.
Out in line, raced 2 wide, 6 lengths back, same margin back on turn, finished off evenly.
Bumped start and almost dislodged the rider, raced 3 wide in midfield, 5 lengths or so back, there to turn, failed to close off in straight. (Lame right front leg next day.)
Slightly slow out, raced greenly early, sat 5 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, failed to make any progress in straight.
Taken back to race at rear, 7 lengths back on rail, same position on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Away well, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, weakened early in straight, eased after passing 100M.
Moderately away, raced behind midfield, 4 lengths or so back, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after straightening, finished off strongly to score.
Moderately away from gate 10, raced 3 wide, 2 to 3 lengths back, no cover from near 900M, same margin back on turn, finished off well to take 2nd.
Commenced well, sat a length behind the leader on rail, easy run on turn, no clear running early in straight, angled out after passing 300M, finished off well thereafter to take a place.
Jumped well from the widest draw, sent forward to race in 2nd, 2 wide, a length back on turn, kept on well in straight but couldn't hold off the first few late.
Bumped shortly after start, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well throughout, headed near 250M, stayed on well to the line, just missed frame late.
Taken back from a wide gate, raced at tail, 7 lengths back, 3 wide turning in, bumped early in straight, finished off very strongly to be nearest on line.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 4 lengths back, there to turn, angled out and bumped early in straight, made minor progress thereafter.
Slightly slow out and crowded early, raced 2 wide at rear, 6 lengths back, same margin back on turn, no clear running early in straight, finished off evenly when clear thereafter.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 lengths back, same position on turn, finished off one-paced.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 3 wide at rear, closer on turn, 4 lengths or so back turning in, bumped early in straight, failed to make any progress thereafter.
Slowly away, raced at rear, 6 lengths back on rail, there to turn, failed to close off in straight.
Began fairly from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, weakened gradually after passing 300M, eased late.
Jumped well from a middle draw, raced 2 wide, 1 to 2 lengths back, got cover on turn, weakened early in straight, eased final 100M.
