Away with them, raced 2 wide, 3 to 4 lengths back, no cover from near 1200M, moved closer after passing 800M, a length or so back on turn, finished off strongly in straight to score.
Slowly away, raced 2 wide, 4 to 5 lengths back, moved closer on turn, finished off well to take 2nd.

Clean jump, sent forward to take the lead and set a fast tempo, led by 3 lengths in the middle stages, still held a length advantage turning in, headed near 200M, stayed on to take a place. (See Racing Incidents.)

Out in line, unable to slot in, raced 3 wide with no cover early, found cover on the first turn, settled 2 wide behind midfield, gradually improved after passing 600M, made some progress in straight to make frame.
Began fairly from gate 9, raced 2 wide, 8 to 9 lengths back, improved from near 550M, very wide turning in, finished off evenly in straight.
Commenced well, sat 3 to 4 lengths behind the leader, saved ground on turn, finished off evenly.
Bumped start, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, angled out near 400M, finished off one-paced.
Steadied off heels shortly after start, raced 9 to 10 lengths back at rear, taken very wide turning in, passed some tired runners in straight.
Taken back from gate 10, raced 2 wide at rear, 9 to 10 lengths back, moved a bit closer on turn, bumped and unbalanced near 200M, one-paced thereafter.

Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, still 8 to 9Ls back turning in, made some progress early in straight, angled out after passing 200M, awkwardly placed thereafter, not able to test properly. (See Racing Incidents.)
Shifted out at start and bumped, positioned on rail behind midfield, 6 lengths or so back on turn, blocked early in straight, failed to make any progress when clear thereafter.
Jumped well from the widest draw, raced in 2nd, 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader, peaked on turn, weakened gradually in straight, eased late. (Lame right front leg.)
Took rail and lead easily, made all.
Slow away, pushed forward, sat 2 wide, lost ground 500M, dashed strongly 200M for 2nd.
Box seat, raced very keenly throughout, held ground for 3rd.
Eased back, 2 wide, dashed strongly 200M.
Eased back 2-3 wide, made early move 700M, ran on well until 100M emptied.
Eased back, took rail and cover, worked around the field 600M in 3-4 wide, little dash 300M.
Eased to sit in midfield along the fence, checked 1800M, dashed fairly in straight.
Pressed forward, settled outside the leader, however soon weakened 300M.
Settled in front of midfield, gradually made ground in the straight, quickened passing 100M to score.
Ridden along to take lead, asked for effort passing 400M, responded solidly in the straight, worked home nicely.
Raced midfield, wide on straightening, gained ground passing 100M, finished well.
Settled behind midfield, widest on straightening, made up some nice late ground.
Sat in box seat, fought hard in the straight but only one-paced.
Travelled midfield on rail, tried to improve on straightening, one-paced in the straight.
Began awkwardly, raced behind the lead, lay out rounding Home Turn, gave ground passing 150M and failed to make impression, blood in trachea and must trial.
Settled behind midfield on rail, no response when placed pressure, mucus in trachea.
Awkwardly placed then taken back at start, always back, no response in the straight.
On jumping was crowded for room, raced at rear, never in it.
Jumped fast before coming across face of field to assume lead. Travelled comfortably in middle stage before straightening up 2 lengths clear and never looking like getting run down.
Jumped well and ridden up before being crossed and gaining position on leaders back. Came across heals after straightening and fleetingly looked like a challenger but was no match for winner.

Commenced fast before allowing others to assume lead and before settling in nice position one pair back. Was ridden up again from the 750m as outside challenger improved. Improved from the 400m but was no match for first two.
Jumped fast and was ridden up to come across face of field and sit outside leader. Was asked to improve from 400m to chase break away leader and fought on fairly in the straight.

Bumped and inconvenienced shortly after the start before settling in the last three. Was shuffled back to last at the 600m and entered straight in that position before making good late ground in the straight.
Eased back after 100m and settled last in middle stages. Ridden up from 600m to improve around field but entered straight the widest on the track before making good late ground.

One of the slowest into stride before taken across the back of the field to fence position. Was eased slightly after the 400m before entering straight up against the fence but only battled away in the run home.

Was bumped on jumping and then badly hampered within first 50m before ridden up to hold position worse than midfield. Was again ridden up inside 650m but entered straight well back. Didn't threaten in run to the line.

Bumped just after the start before having to ease back to obtain trailing position. Slightly eased around 450m when improving position before pulling out wider in the straight but failing to flatter in the run to the line.
Bumped on two occasions shortly after start and then eased back to midfield on fence. Stayed close to rail throughout but weakened out in the straight.

Moderately away before being hard ridden to obtain position but posted four wide without cover. Covered plenty of additional ground throughout middle stages before understandably weakening out from 450m.
Bumped straight after start before veering sideways and inconveniencing others before settling midfield three wide no cover. Ridden up from 500m to improve but began giving ground from that point.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, there to turn, no daylight early in straight, finished off very strongly when clear thereafter to score.
Commenced well from gate 1, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, easy run throughout, kept on very well in straight to take 2nd, just beaten by a neck.
Clean jump, sent forward to take the lead, found rail near 600M, kept on well after turning in, just couldn't hold off the first two late.
Began awkwardly, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, closed off well to make frame.

Crowded on jumping, raced 2 wide at rear, 6 lengths back, same margin back on turn, made very good progress early in straight, blocked shortly after passing 100M, not able to be ridden out thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Shifted out on jumping and bumped, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 4 lengths back on turn, no daylight early in straight, made minor progress when clear thereafter.
Bumped start and unbalanced, positioned 2 to 3 wide, a length or so back, got no cover on turn, finished off one-paced in straight.
Fast into stride, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide on turn, weakened gradually in straight.
Bumped start and unbalanced, raced at rear on rail, still well back on turn, failed to quicken under pressure in straight.
Jumped well from the widest draw, raced prominently but trapped very wide, no cover throughout, weakened early in straight when hard run took effect.
Bumped start, raced wide at rear, 5 lengths or so back, taken very wide in straight, failed to make any progress.
Clean jump, positioned on rail behind midfield, 5 lengths back on turn, showed nothing in straight, finished last.
Asked to go into the lead, held it by 3/4L, kicked away at 200M, won by 3L and with plenty in hand.
Sent forward and sat outside the lead, remained 3/4L off until 200M, kept on well to the finish.
Asked to take up the box-seat, sat 2-1/2L off the lead, finished off one paced.
Sent forward before taking cover to race in one-off one-back, raced flat to the line.
Travelled in front of midfield, 3-1/4L off 2 wide, lay in at turn, continued on one paced.
Taken back and raced towards the tail, 8L behind 2 wide, switched widest and closed off well to the line.
Awkward start and lost ground, in worse than midfield along the rail, made ground late.
Travelled in midfield, 2 wide throughout, very one paced in the straight.
Taken back, at the rear along the rail, dashed early before continuing one paced home.
Fractious and lost ground at the start, recovered to be in midfield along the rail, weakened out in the straight.
Eased to find cover in behind midfield, 2 wide, showed nothing.
In midfield, wide and without cover, faded in the straight.

Ridden amongst leaders early settling one-out-one-back in 4th, became 5th coming out of back straight before renewing effort around home bend, wide in 2L 5th entering turning in, fought on dourly to just get up on line.
Settled in midfield, finished off the race well to just fail to get up on line.
Settled in midfield on the rail, minor interference at the Rock, hugged inside rail turning for home, finished off the race well to just fail to get up on line.

Prominent early, difficult to settle when taken 2.5L back for 5th, travelled wide without cover down back straight, made swift progress and hit the front approaching home turn, lay in under pressure and collared close to finish.
Slowly away, settled in rear on the rail, hampered coming out of back straight, saved ground on inside turning in, ran on well to be nearest at finish despite forced to ease final strides.

Ridden positively from the widest gate to soon join the leader, lost position making home bend, renewed effort from 1.5L 3rd entering straight, forced to switch for a run 250 metres out and kept on same pace final stages.
Ridden in prominent position early before taken back to midfield remaining wide throughout, fought on steadily under pressure without threatening.
Began well from the one draw, settled just off the pace on the rail, soon weakened under pressure after straightening.
Settled in rear from a wide gate, widest runner turning for home, ran on steadily down the centre of home straight.

Very slowly away, trailed the field most of the way, hampered and lost further ground coming out of back straight, saved ground on the rail turning in, produced good late impression final stages despite hampered 150M out.
Ridden to lead from a wide gate, held narrow running until headed into straight, folded up quickly inside the final 200 metres.
Travelled keenly in last few racing wide without cover in back straight, remained wide rounding home bend, dropped out after straightening.
Tracked leaders in a fast run race, quickened to lead 200M, drew well clear for a commanding victory.
Held up in midfield, stayed on moderately to go 2nd near line, no chance with runaway winner.
Soon crossed to the rail and settled down in mid-division, kept on steadily turning home, no threat to clear winner.
Went forward from wide draw, disputed the lead with rival from 800M, headed 200M by eventual winner, faded away.
Positioned 3-wide in midfield, no cover from 800M, wide into straight, stayed on mildly without posing threat.
Emerged as the leader 1000M, pressed by rival from 800M, run ended mid-straight, weakened gradually.
Not far off leaders in a fast run race, kept on same pace when driven along 400M, never dangerous.
Settled down behind midfield, 5-6Ls off the pace middle stages, couldn't muster the pace to challenge turning for home, never in contention.
Began awkwardly, dropped back to race near the rear 5-6Ls off the pace, made up ground from 350M before running to the heels of rivals late stages.
Began awkwardly from draw 11, bustled along to chase leaders, run ended 200M and faded away.
Crowded for room on jumping, behind mid-division, couldn't quicken when asked, weakened final 200M.
Ended up in the last spot, detached halfway and gave no response when pushed along, well beaten. (Jockey reported his horse didn't travel comfortably / Irregular Heart Rhythm.)

Moderately away from gate 11, raced 2 to 3 wide with cover, 8 lengths back, sent forward after entering the back straight, took the lead near 700M, led by 3 lengths on turn, kept on very well in straight and scored.
Average to begin, positioned on rail in midfield, 5 lengths back, saved ground throughout, same margin back turning in, finished off well to take 2nd without posing any threat to the winner.
Commenced well, positioned 3 lengths or so back on rail, 2 wide from near 700M, 4 lengths back turning in, kept on evenly to the line and took a place.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear, 9 to 10 lengths back, still well back on turn, steadied off heels near 350M, made little progress in straight.

Began smartly & took the early lead, allowed rival to cross 1700M, sat 1-1/2L behind the leader thereafter, asked when pace slacked in the middle stages, but only showed limited response, 3Ls back on turn, weakened gradually in straight.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide, 5 lengths back, 3 wide from near 800M, 9 lengths back on turn, finished off evenly in straight.

Began awkwardly and lost ground, raced 2 wide at rear, 9 to 10 lengths back, moved closer after entering the back straight, raced 3 wide, 4 lengths back from near 600M, similar position on turn, weakened early in straight.
Away with them, raced at tail, more than 10 lengths back, moved a bit closer after entering the back straight, 3 to 4 wide at rear, 10 lengths back on turn, one-paced in straight.
Began fairly from gate 1, positioned 7 to 8 lengths back on rail, same margin back on turn, failed to close off in straight.

Commenced well, sent forward to race prominently, took the lead near 1700M, led by 1-1/2L, headed near 700M, hard ridden thereafter but only showed limited response, peaked on turn, emptied early in straight.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 7 lengths back, showed little response when pace slacken in the middle stages, last on turn, 11 lengths back, emptied early in straight.

Began well from a wide draw, sent forward to race prominently but trapped wide early, settled 2 wide, 3-4Ls back after 1700M, asked near 800M, but showed no response, lost position thereafter, eased near 350M. (Distressed.)
Hard ridden early, pace very fast, midfield 2 wide, made early move 800M, led 500M, hung on well to score.
Eased to sit just off the leaders, not suited by the fast tempo, closed off well 300M for 2nd.
Eased back, 2-3 wide, benefited by the fast pace, made steady ground 300M for 3rd.
Slow away, eased back, suited by the fast tempo, progressed steadily 250M.
Midfield along the fence, favoured by the fast tempo, just held ground in straight.
Eased at start, took cover at rear, 2 wide, benefited by the fast pace, made minor ground 200M.
Eased to sit in front of midfield, not suited by the fast pace, weakened 200M.
Eased to rear, raced 2-4 wide, suited by the fast tempo, no progress.
Hard ridden to share the lead at very fast tempo, out of fuel 300M.
Trapped 3 wide throughout, faded 400M.
Hard ridden to take rail and shared the lead at very fast sectionals, dropped off 600M.
Raced midfield on rail, made the turn near 500M awkwardly, gradually gained ground passing 200M, quickened passing 50M, finished strongly.
Raced at rear, wide on straightening, responded solidly and made good ground in the straight.
Began only fairly, raced midfield, commenced to improve passing 500M, made up some nice late ground.
Jumped nicely and took lead with early speed, lay out in the middle stages, responded well in the early part of straight, gave some ground passing 50M.
Jumped well, settled behind the lead, asked for effort near 500M, ran on well in the straight.
Taken back at start, settled behind midfield on rail, near 500M was steadied away from heels, limited response in the straight.
Raced in front of midfield, after the 700M was left racing wide and without cover, one-paced in the straight.
Urged along then settled box seat, weakened passing 150M.
Settled midfield, tried to improve near 500M, no response in the straight, failed to make impression.
Taken back at start, always back, never in it.
Settled behind midfield, no response, failed to run on.
Raced midfield, widest on straightening, faded out in the straight.

Commenced fairly before being ridden across to rail and settling midfield 3 pairs back on fence. Improved and became unbalanced when improving at 500m. Held tight at 400m before switching to inside and sprinting strongly.
Commenced well from inside barrier before settling third on fence behind leader. Was eased around 500m before staying close to fence in straight and fighting on gamely.

Worse than midfield after the start before being shuffled back to rear in middle stages. Attempted to improve from 600m on the back of rivals before being pushed wide on straightening. Made good late ground in run to line.
Ridden hard first 200m before coming across midfield one horse off the fence. Ridden up from 450m to get into race from rearward position before getting home well from back in field.

Eased back after the start to position near the rear before improved position from the 800m. Was posted three horses wide in middle stages and again improved prior to cornering. Ran home well considering tough trip.

Settled last in early stages before commencing sweeping run around the field from 800m. Were three and four horses wide in middle stages before joining leaders at 350m. Ran around in straight but was very brave considering.
Began awkwardly losing ground and settled near the rear. Was a clear last upon entering straight and passed a few in the run home.
Commenced well and was ridden forward to position outside leader. Sat one length off leader until 500m when improving to share the lead upon straightening. Battled away in the straight.

Jumped well before easing behind speed, two pairs back on outside. Ridden up from 500m before being inconvenienced at the 475m and losing position. Awkwardly placed in early stages of straight and not likely after passage.
Was ridden forward from start to take up leading position. Held margin of a length until the 500m when outside horse challenged before failing to flatter in the run to the line.
Ridden across from barrier to position worse than midfield off fence before then gaining fence position at 1200m. Stayed close to rail throughout running but never threatened in the run to the line.

Ridden forward to contest lead before easing out of that battle to get position one pair back at the 1200m. Was ridden up from 450m to improve position, however gave ground from 300m and was well beaten.
Jumped well, raced prominently but 3 wide in the early stages, 2 wide from 600M, took the lead near 200M, kept on strongly to the line and scored.
Taken back from gate 9, raced wide with cover at rear, improved from 400M, very wide turning in, finished off very strongly to take 2nd.
Hampered shortly after start, positioned 3 to 4 lengths back on rail, saved ground on turn, angled out early in straight, finished off well to take a place.
Shifted in at start and bumped, raced 2 wide, 2 lengths back, 3 wide turning, finished off evenly in straight.
Commenced well from a middle draw, raced prominently, 2 wide, raced tight near 550M, 2 lengths back turning in, finished off evenly. (Blood in trachea.)
Crowded on jumping, raced 2 wide, 3 lengths or so back, there to turn, finished off evenly.

Began well, raced 3 wide in midfield early, gradually moved closer after entering to the back straight, challenged the leader turning in, kept on well early in straight, peaked 150M, stayed on evenly to the line.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, 6 to 7 lengths back, moved a bit closer along the rail on turn, angled out near 350M, finished off evenly.
Bumped start and unbalanced, recovered quickly to take the lead, challenged by rivals turning in, headed near 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Hampered shortly after start, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, no clear running early in straight, weakened final 100M.
Average to begin, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, raced tight near 550M, carried wider on turn, weakened early in straight. (Blood in trachea.) (Lame left front leg next day.)
Moderately away from a wide draw, unable to slot in, raced 4 wide, 3 to 4 lengths back, no cover throughout, peaked turning in, weakened early in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Urged along, in lead until a runner crossed at 700M, kept on then closed off strongly from final 75M to score.
Sat outside the lead, 1-1/4L off, showed some kicks early, kept on but caught by winner in the final stages.
Knuckled at start, then ridden forward, crossed to rail and led at 700M, headed before 100M, battled on for 3rd.
In the box-seat until 700M when slotted one spot back, about 2-1/2L behind, continued on to the line.
Travelled in about midfield, shifted to the rail before 600M turn, ran on to the line.
Jumped fairly only, settled in worse than midfield, 5-3/4L behind 2 wide, ran on one paced.
Raced in one-off one-back, about 3-1/4L off the lead, one paced and emptied late.
Settled to race in about midfield, 5L behind wide and without cover, pretty one paced.
Travelled towards the rear, 7L behind 2 wide at turn, improved slightly in the straight.
Eased back, at the rear along the rail, made minor ground late.
Taken back and raced at the rear, 2 wide, did not threaten and eased at 100M.
In midfield along the rail, hung out at times, performance unacceptable. Must trial.
Began well, soon taken back for cover just worse than midfield in 7th, fought on dourly to assert authority inside the final 50 metres.
Soon came to dispute lead passing the winning post the first time, hit the front entering home straight only to be caught inside the final 50 metres. (Tactic questioned)
Settled in 8th towards the rear on the rail, came under pressure from rounding home bend, finished off the race well from over 3L back in 7th entering home straight, did best work late.
Settled near last, commenced move approaching the home turn and went widest into the straight, ran on well down the centre of the track to be nearest at finish.
Jumped in the air losing ground, trailed the field to home straight, saved ground turning in, fought on steadily without threatening.

With leaders early, taken back to over 2L back in 5th 2-wide, slightly closer to the pace past the Rock and reached 3rd within 2L of pace entering home straight, kept on until finding no extra inside the final 100 metres.
Settled 3-wide in midfield with cover, remained in similar position to home bend, dropped to last few when very wide turning in, kept on steadily without threatening.
Held narrow lead on the rail to the 400 metres, faded gradually in straight. (Questioned for disappointing performance)

Broke well from the one draw and but was sluggish and given a reminder, travelled 2L back in 4th on the rail most of the way to home straight, came to challenge under pressure but weakened inside the 200 metres.
Began well from the widest gate, travelled prominently and wide without cover most of the way to home bend, dropped out under pressure from over 400 metres out.
Emerged as leader from 800M, led at steady tempo, was challenged by the persistent runner up from 200M but held on well.
Bustled along after the start, tracked leader 2-wide from 700M, responded well to riding and kept coming to the line, held near finish.
Up with early pace before settling down in 4th, had over 3Ls to make up on race leader (the eventual winner) at 400M, ran on well under pressure to be nearest at the finish.
Guided to a rail position towards the rear of mid-division, boxed on well final 300M without troubling the top trio.
Settled down in midfield, 4Ls to make up on leaders 400M, kept on same pace to line, couldn't get closer.
Chased leaders along the rail, there to challenge passing 300M but failed to pick up on leaders, ran out of steam and faded final 150M.
Lost ground shortly after the start, shifted across behind runners to race in the rear, made limited progress on straightening, never dangerous.
Dropped back to the rear from draw 12, came widest in straight, made some progress but did not threaten.
Began awkwardly, held up behind midfield, didn't respond to pressure on straightening, no impression.

Slowly into stride, soon recovered into midfield, driven out early straight but made no progress, weakened final 200M. (Jockey : travelled only fairly and failed to finish off the race / Vetted no findings.)
Caught wide early, became difficult to settle from 800M when steadied for cover, 3rd last making the turn, found no extra on straightening. Never in the picture.
Began only fairly, wide no cover from 700M, couldn't finish off in the straight, soon weakened
Taken back from gate 10, raced 2 wide at rear early, 3 wide from near 800M, 4 to 5 lengths back on turn, finished off very strongly to score.
Commenced well, positioned on rail in midfield, 3 lengths back, saved ground to turn, angled out near 400M, no daylight early in straight, finished off strongly when clear final 150M to take 2nd.

Moderately away, raced 2W, 4Ls back, awkwardly placed on heels near 900M, angled out thereafter, 3W with cover on turn, made good progress early in straight, bumped and unbalanced after passing 150M, ran on evenly to the line.
Bumped on jumping, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, shared lead on turn, kept on evenly early in straight, headed near 150M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Shifted out at start and bumped, sent forward to race 2 wide, 1 to 2 lengths back, there to turn, finished off evenly in straight.

Moderately away from gate 1, raced 4 lengths back on rail, made contact and unbalanced near 900M, same margin back on turn, found no daylight after turning in, made some progress when clear final 100M.
Began fairly, raced 2 wide, 5 lengths back, severely checked near 900M, similar position on turn, no clear running after turning in, made minor progress when clear final 100M.
Bumped shortly after start, sat 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, kept on evenly early in straight, weakened final 100M.

Began well from a middle draw, raced 3 wide with no cover behind midfield, moved closer in the middle stages, a length back on turn, kept on evenly early in straight, bumped and unbalanced near 150M, eased thereafter.
Began fairly, raced at tail, 6 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, kept to inside early in straight, angled out near 200M, made no progress thereafter.

Shifted in shortly after start and made contact, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 lengths back, same margin back on turn, kept on evenly early in straight, severely checked near 150M, eased thereafter. (Blood in trachea.)
Bumped shortly after start, sent forward to take the lead, shared lead on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened from 200M, eased shortly thereafter.
Jumped well from a middle gate, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths back, there to turn, finished off strongly to score by a neck.
Moderately away from gate 9, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, shared lead on turn, took the lead early in straight, kept on well but couldn't hold off the winner late.
Average to begin, raced 3 wide in midfield, moved closer in the middle stages, a length behind on turn, closed off well to take 3rd.
Slowly away, positioned 5 lengths behind the leader on rail, same margin back on turn, angled out early in straight, made some progress thereafter to make frame.

Began fairly, showed no early speed, raced 3 wide at rear early, checked near 1000M, 8-9Ls back at tail thereafter, still well back on turn, taken very wide in straight and finished off very strongly to be nearest on line.
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, 3 lengths or so back, saved ground throughout, kept to inside after straightening, finished off evenly.
Slowly away, raced at rear, hampered near 1000M, checked off heels near 750M, 7 lengths back on turn, made some headway in straight.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced wide at rear, 6 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, finished off evenly.
Began well, sat right behind the leader on rail, there to turn, angled out near 400M, weakened gradually in straight.
Commenced well, sent forward to take the lead, found rail after passing 1000M, joined by outside horse on turn, headed early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Away with them, raced 2 wide, 4 to 5 lengths back, similar position on turn, weakened early in straight.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide behind midfield, struck on heels and blundered near 750M, 7 lengths back on turn, emptied early in straight. (Lost left hind plate near 1000M.)

Began smartly from gate 1, sat 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, challenged the leader turning in, took the lead near 200M, kept on well to the line and scored.
Jumped well, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well throughout, challenged by rival turning in, kept on well early in straight, headed near 200M, stayed on to take 2nd.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear on rail, improved from 500M, 3 wide turning in, made some headway in straight to take 3rd without threatening.
Bumped start, raced 3 wide behind midfield early, carried wider after entering to the back straight, 7 lengths back on turn, made some headway in straight to make frame.
Began fairly, raced 2 wide in midfield, moved a bit closer along the rail on turn, angled out early in straight, finished off evenly thereafter. (Finished distressed.)
Jumped with them, raced prominently but trapped 3 wide early, 2 wide from near 1000M, peaked on turn, weakened gradually in straight.

Shifted out at start and bumped, unable to slot in, trapped 4 wide in the early stages, settled 2 to 3 wide in midfield after entering the back straight, peaked on turn, weakened gradually in straight.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced wide with cover at rear, 10 lengths back turning in, failed to quicken under pressure in straight.
Taken back from gate 13, raced 3 wide at rear, still well back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Jumped well, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, peaked on turn, emptied early in straight and eased.
Average to begin, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield early, slightly lost position after entering to the back straight, 7 lengths back on turn, emptied early in straight.

Moderately away from a wide draw, unable to slot in, trapped 4 wide in midfield, moved closer after entering to the back straight, but still 3 wide, weakened on turn, emptied early in straight, finished tailed out.
Checked on jumping, raced 2 wide at rear, 5 lengths or so back, peaked on turn, emptied early in straight, finished tailed out. (Blood in trachea.)
Began very awkwardly and bumped, positioned on rail behind midfield, weakened from 700M, emptied early in straight, finished tailed out.
Hard ridden to take rail and lead, drifted away 400M to score.
Hard ridden to keep up in midfield, trapped 3 wide, dashed strongly 300M for 2nd.
Hard ridden to hold the rail in midfield, lack room in straight, dashed well.
Checked at start, took rail at rear, dashed strongly 300M.
Hard ridden forward, 2 wide, out of fuel 200M.
Hard ridden forward, sat 2 wide, weakened 200M.
Hard ridden to obtain box seat, lack turn of foot in straight.
Failed to muster at back, 2 wide, no progress.
Eased at start, trapped 4 wide, no dash.
Trapped 4 wide throughout in midfield, emptied 350M.
Hard ridden early but not muster, never competitive.
Never a factor.
Ridden along to take lead, improved after 400M, responded strongly and scored unchallenged.
Travelled behind midfield, made up some late ground, finished nicely.
Settled midfield on rail, gradually made ground in the straight, finished well.
Settled in box seat, after 1200M lay in and bumped the running rail, gave ground passing 100M.
Raced at handy position, asked for effort near 600M, one-paced in the straight.
Raced midfield, commenced to improve near 500M, limited response in the straight.
Taken back at start, always back, never in it, must trial.
Taken back at start, tried to improve passing 600M, no response in the straight, must trial.
Hard ridden to sit outside the lead, faded out passing 600M, must trial.
Jumped well and ridden hard to come across face of field to lead. Travelled well and set up margin coming into straight before holding out challengers in the run to the line.

Commenced well from wide gate before easing out of speed battle positioning slightly worse than midfield and three horses off the fence. Travelled well on cornering and made ground quickly before closing sharply in last 200m.

Commenced well before coming over and positioning behind leading pair. Moved closer to the rail at 700m before attempting to improve from 500m but still spotting leading pair big margin. Toughed it out gamely in the straight.

Ridden across from wide gate to position midfield off the fence. Shifted out at the 700m and improved close to heels at 400m. Bumped at the 250m and switched back towards rail before hitting the line strongly in later stages.

Slow to begin and subsequently positioned at the tail and was ridden up to maintain contact. Moved out wider on the track from the 500m but was still last upon straightening and made good ground in late stages.
Began moderately and did not have early speed before settling near the rear in the middle of runners. Entered the straight near the tail of the field and made some late ground in the run home.
Commenced moderately before positioning midfield one horse off fence. Was inconvenienced at 700m when horse in front lost ground and was not likely from that point.
Ridden hard from wide barrier to come across and position in second place, one length off lead. Was prominent in early stages of straight but weakened out from 200m.

Commenced well and went forward to hold position behind leading pair before being tightened at 700m and losing position. Looked under pressure from this incident but did battle away to the line fairly.
One of the last into stride before easing back behind the field to position second from last. Was pushed the widest runner upon straightening and never threatened to challenge in the straight.
Was slightly slow away before ridden up to maintain fence position, slightly worse than midfield before being eased at the 700m. Stayed close to fence throughout but never flattered in the straight.
Commenced moderately before ridden up to maintain prominent position in third behind leader. Was unbalanced approaching the 700m and was niggled along from 500m before dropping out in the straight.
Fast into stride, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, 3/4L back on turn, kept on very well in straight and scored by a neck.
Jumped well from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, 3 lengths back, same position on turn, finished off well to take 2nd, just beaten by a neck.
Commenced well, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well throughout, kept on very well after turning in, just couldn't hold off the first two close home.
Began well from the widest gate, failed to muster despite driven along early, trapped 4 wide in midfield early, moved closer on turn, kept on well in straight to be nearest on line.
Jumped with them, sat 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, easy run on turn, kept on evenly until passing 100M, weakened thereafter.
Jumped well from gate 11, unable to slot in, raced 3 wide, 2 to 3 lengths back, finished off one-paced.
Slightly slow out, raced at rear, 6 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, made some progress in straight.
Bumped start, raced at rear, 10 lengths back on turn, made some headway in straight.
Shifted in at start and bumped, raced 5 lengths back on rail, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after straightening but failed to make any progress.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide, 3 lengths back, there to turn, weakened gradually in straight.
Began awkwardly and bumped, raced 2 to 3 wide behind midfield, 5 lengths back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Slowly away, raced at rear throughout, never competitive.
Travelled in behind midfield, 6L behind the lead along the rail, kicked away from 250M, ran on nicely to score.
In box-seat, sat about 1-1/2L off, headed by winner near 250M, but battled all the way to finish 1/2L behind.
Checked at the post first time, settled in behind midfield, on rail and 7-3/4L behind before shifted away from it at 550M, closed off nicely inside 200M.
Settled to race in behind midfield, 7L behind and went wide when checked at 600M turn, ran on well to the line.
Raced close to the rear, 8-1/2L behind, wide but with cover at turn, dashed on fairly in the straight.
Travelled in midfield, on rail then shifted 2 wide before turn at 600M, kept on till about 100M.
Jumped fairly only and raced at the rear, 11-1/4L behind along the rail, made ground until run ended at 100M.
Ridden to be prominent, however trapped wide throughout, one paced and emptied in the latter stages.
Failed to muster and raced in about midfield, 2-3 wide, lost ground rounding turn, not competitive.
Asked and settled to race outside the lead, dropped off from 300M, was disappointing.
Sent forward to take rail and led, maintained lead till 250M when headed and weakened badly. (Blood in trachea)
One-off one-back, gave ground from 600M and finished tailed out, must trial.
Broke well and soon taken back, settled about 3L off the pace in 5th on the rail, commenced move entering home straight, quickened well to take charge 200 metres out.
Jumped in air and lost ground at start, settled well behind on the rail, made up a lot of ground inside the final 200 metres to claim distant 2nd.
Ridden positively and attempted to make all, led until overhauled 200 metres out.
Ridden forward early settling one back in 3rd on the rail, became 2nd approaching home straight, soon came to challenge after straightening but unable to make any impression.
Jumped fairly, settled not far off in 4th, became 5th in similar position approaching the 1000 metres, came under pressure rounding home bend, kept on before fading inside the final 200 metres.
Soon dropped behind midfield while racing awkwardly, made steady headway on the outside down far side, gained midfield coming onto home bend, kept on same pace.
Ridden forward from the widest gate, settled just off the pace 2-wide in 2nd, gradually weakened under pressure in straight.
Settled in the back, fought on steadily in home straight.
Settled in last few, gained slightly closer coming out of back straight, fought on steadily down the centre of the straight.
Awkward in midfield rounding first bend losing ground, shuffled further back towards the rear on the far side while remaining keenly, saved ground turning for home, found nothing under pressure.
Soon recovered from a moderate start to settle in midfield, came under pressure approaching home turn, soon weakened.
Pressed forward from a wide gate, travelled wide in midfield before moving forward 3-wide without cover, given reminders on the final bend, folded up quickly after straightening.
Ridden early, hampered and dropped behind midfield on the first bend, yielded ground steadily from approaching home bend.
Began from a wide gate settling towards the rear out wide, remained wide rounding home bend, folded up quickly upon straightening.
Quickly into stride, led early stages before overtaken by rivals nearing the turn, regained lead 250M, driven clear final 150M.
Taken back for cover, settled down 2nd last 6-7Ls off the pace, made good progress from off the pace to go 2nd near the line.
Never far off, settled down ahead of midfield along the fence, kept up the chase on straightening, always held by winner, lost 2nd near the line.
Chased leaders, had every chance turning in, stayed on steadily to the line, edged out to 4th close home.
Began fairly from draw 11, caught 4 wide in midfield, ran on moderately towards the finish.
Held up towards the rear, brought widest into straight, stayed on past beaten rivals but no impression on leaders.
Went forward from draw 12, caught 3-wide no cover outside the lead, kept on same pace early straight, weakened 150M, got unbalanced near 100M when brushed by rival.
Held up behind midfield along the fence, stayed on well from 300M but was severely checked 100M, lost all chance thereon.
Began awkwardly, rushed forward to take narrow lead before the turn, taken on by winner early straight, lost lead near 250M, weakened away.
Held up in midfield, made the turn after the 700M awkwardly, couldn't accelerate under pressure on straightening, never threatened.
Shifted across behind runners after the start, raced as the back-marker 8Ls off the pace, couldn't pick up pace to challenge, well beaten.
Slowly to begin, recovered to midfield, came under pressure 500M but failed to respond to riding, eased late stages when no chance.

Bumped start, raced prominently, 2 wide, slightly taken back to sit right behind the leader on turn, no daylight early in straight, finished off very strongly when clear final 100M, scored by a nose.
Commenced well, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well throughout, hard ridden from 300M, kept on very strongly, just couldn't hold off the winner on line.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide in midfield, same position on turn, finished off well to take a place.
Away with them, positioned 2 wide, 1 to 2 lengths back, easy run on turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Shifted in at start and bumped, raced prominently but trapped very wide early, 2 wide from near 700M, peaked shortly after turning in, kept on one pace to the line.
Began well from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, no clear running early in straight, finished off evenly when clear thereafter.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide at rear, 5 lengths back turning in, no daylight early in straight, finished off evenly when clear thereafter.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced wide at rear, 6 lengths back, similar position on turn, made minor progress in straight. (Dropped whipnear 50M.)
Crowded on jumping, raced 2 wide behind midfield, travelled keenly throughout, checked off heels near 800M, bumped near 600M, 3 lengths back turning in, failed to quicken under pressure in straight.
Slightly slow out, positioned on rail behind midfield, saved ground on turn, angled out near 500M, failed to close off in straight.
Taken back from gate 11, raced at tail, 7 lengths back, still last turning in, failed to close off in straight.
Clean jump from gate 9, raced 3 wide behind midfield, 4 lengths back, bumped near 600M, weakened gradually in straight, eased final 150M.
Hard ridden to keep up in midfield, progressed steadily 300M to score.
Pushed to lead and clocked fast sectionals, hung on well until 50M overhauled, ran on for 2nd.
Hard ridden throughout to keep up with the leaders, not suited by the fast sectionals, held ground for 3rd.
At rear, benefited by the fast pace, progressed steadily 200M.
Hard ridden to keep up in midfield, ran on well to the line.
Pressed forward, harmed by the fast tempo, out of fuel 200M.
Pressed forward, not suited by the fast sectionals, soon emptied 200M.
Eased back, favoured by the fast tempo, made steady ground 200M.
Slow away, at back, benefited by the fast pace, ran on ok final furlong.
At back, never improved.
Failed to muster speed, never competitive.
Very awkward away, never better than midfield.
Pressed forward, harmed by the fast tempo, faded rapidly 400M.
Hard ridden forward, dropped off quickly 400M.
Settled behind midfield on rail, commenced to improve passing 500M, continued to make ground in the straight, finished strongly.
Raced midfield on rail, held up for clear running in the early part of straight, responded solidly after 200M, just missed by neck.
Travelled at back, asked for effort passing 600M, wide on straightening, made up some nice late ground.
Settled at back, fought hard entire straight, gained ground passing 150M.
Settled in front of midfield with nice early speed, responded well in the straight.
Jumped nicely, settled outside the lead, gave some ground passing 50M.
Slow to begin, settled behind midfield, ran on to the line.
Raced at back on rail, battled hard but only gained limited ground.
Jumped OK then taken back at start, raced at tail on fence, kept on rail in Home Turn to save ground, one-paced in the straight.
Travelled wide and without cover in behind midfield, wide on straightening, steadied near 150M, limited response.
Urged along to take box seat, shifted out to improve in Home Turn, weakened passing 200M.
Taken back at start, widest on straightening, never in it, blood trachea.
Raced midfield, no response in the straight, bled.
Ridden along to take lead, faded out passing 300M, lame right front.
Settled midfield on fence. Had economical run before shifting away from fence at 500m. Looked flat at 400m but responded under heavy riding in last 200m to pick up leaders and score narrow win.

Sent forward before checked at 1400m before positioning three pairs back on the outside. Presented with clear running just after straightening and let down well but was just overhauled in last few strides.
Commenced fast before easing out of battle before lead but posted wide throughout. Entered straight widest runner and still gave a kick in straight but ultimately grabbed in last 50m.
Commenced fast before coming across from wide barrier and settling outside leader. Hit the front in early stages of straight and battled on gamely in the straight.

Gathered speed in early stages to go forward before settling one pair behind speed on the outside. Came around heals at 550m to improve position but looked off stride in the straight and looked beaten passing 200m.
Eased back from wide draw shortly after start to position next to last on the outside of runners. Was well back upon entering the straight and did manage to make up some ground in the straight.

Away fairly before mustering early speed and driving up to position leaders back. Looked to be travelling very well prior to straightening and managed to get clear running across heels at 300m but didn't threaten.
Moderately away before ridden up to position two pairs behind leaders in the fence. Looked to get clear running despite brushing with another horses and weakened out from 250m.
Not fast away before eased back worse than midfield and one horse off the fence. Travelled comfortably before entering straight well back and only making moderate ground up in the straight.

Slow away before being ridden up but positioned near the tail off the fence. Improved a few pairs around horses at 1000m before travelling three horses wide in middle stages. Ridden up from 550m before weakening last 300m.
Last horse into stride before maintaining fence position near the tail. Ridden hard prior to straightening and never threatened in the run home.
Ridden forward from barrier rise before coming across to take up lead. Travelled comfortably in middle stages but was immediately under pressure when headed in the early stages of the straight.
Eased back behind runners shortly after start and settled a clear last on fence. Came off fence at 900m but was still a last upon entering straight and failed to pass any runner in the run home.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, finished off very strongly to score by half length.
Began well from gate 9, sent forward to race prominently early, awkwardly placed near 1000M, raced 3 wide with no cover thereafter, 2 lengths back, there to turn, finished off well to take 2nd.
Average to begin, positioned on rail in midfield, angled out near 550M, finished off well to take a place, nice debut.

Bumped on jumping, raced prominently but trapped very wide early, moved closer after passing 1000M, 2 wide from 900M, challenged the leader turning in, took the lead 300M, kept on well but couldn't hold off the challengers final 50M.
Crowded start, raced at rear, 6 lengths back, moved closer along the rail on turn, kept to inside after straightening, closed off well without threatening the first few.
Shifted out at start and bumped, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, 4 to 5 lengths back on turn, taken wide in straight and made some progress.
Shifted in abruptly at start and bumped, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, 3 to 4 lengths back, improved from 550M, very wide turning in, finished off evenly.
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned 1-1/2 length behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, showed limited response in straight, weakened close home.
Taken back from gate 13, raced at tail, 7 lengths or so back, there to turn, made minor progress in straight.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, bumped near 900M, 3 to 4 lengths back on turn, showed limited response in straight, steadied off heels near 150M, ran on one-pace to the line.
Commenced well from gate 10, sent forward to take the lead, found rail near 1000M, challenged by rivals turning in, peaked and headed early in straight, weakened from 150M.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced wide with cover at rear, travelled keenly shortly after passing 800M, 4 to 5 lengths back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Jumped well, sent forward to race prominently, steadied off heels when crossed by rival near 1050M, sat 1 out 1 back on turn, angled out 550M, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Bumped start, raced 4 lengths back on rail, difficult to settle in the middle stages, saved ground on turn, showed nothing in straight, emptied final 150M.
Niggled along to be on pace along the outside rail, pulled away from 150M and scored with ease by 2-1/2L.
Sent forward, prominent and sat 1L off the pace on centre track, ran on well for 2nd but was no match.
In worse than midfield, about 1-3/4L behind on the outside rail, saved ground and ran on well to take 3rd.
Bumped start, raced in behind midfield, about 2-1/2L off towards the inside track, closed off fairly.
Settled to race in about midfield, 1-1/4L off near to the outside rail, ran on one paced to the line.
Sent forward, shared lead on inside track, kept on until 100M when emptied.
Awkward start but recovered to share lead close to the outside rail, showed no response when asked.
Slow to jump and travelled at the tail, 2-1/4L off on centre track, did not improve.
Raced towards the rear, about 1-3/4L off on inside track, did not threaten.
In midfield, about 1-1/4L off on inside track, found no extra passing 200M.
Jumped awkwardly and raced at the rear throughout, never a factor.
Crowded start, prominent and about 3/4L off on centre track, weakened approaching 300M. (Blood in trachea)
Crowded on jumping, prominent and about 3/4L off on centre track, gave ground prior to 400M.
Soon took up running on the rail despite the wide draw, pushed out to defy runner-up's strong late challenge. (Questioned for improved performance)
Tracked the leader, came to challenge under pressure after straightening but unable to peg back the winner throughout.
Settled well back on the rail, attempted to switch for a clear run early in straight, finished well inside the final 300 metres.
Settled well back, obtained clear passage passing the 300 metres, finished off the race well.
Settled just worse than midfield on the rail, fought on steadily without threatening in the run to the line.
Began fairly, settled just off the pace in 3rd on the rail, became 4th in a similar position rounding home bend, kept on from 3rd on straightening, found no extra inside the final 200 metres.
Jumped well settling in midfield in 5th, came under pressure rounding home bend, faded gradually in straight.
Wide in just worse than midfield early stages, improved steadily down back straight to reach 3rd some 1L back when 3-wide around home bend, faded soon after straightening.

Prominent in 4th when reluctant to travel approaching the course proper at 1600M dropping back to last few, produced short-lived effort after straightening, folded up quickly inside final 150M.(Questioned for disappointing performance)
Reserved in mid-division, awkwardly placed behind a weakening rival 500M, chased leader strongly on straightening, took over 50M and raced away to win well.
Never far off in 5th, quickened up well from 400M, led inside 300M, kicked away until overhauled by winner final 50M.
Slow to begin, held up at the back of mid-division, stayed on moderately on straightening, got up for 3rd 50M, not reach first 2.
Chased leading trio, switched out 500M, had his chance but couldn't get closer to leader, kept on same pace inside 150M.
Crossed to the lead passing 1200M, led them at a steady pace, quickened to a 2L lead 400M, headed passing 300M and faded towards the line.
From wide draw taken across behind runners after the start, held up near rear about 10Ls off the pace, ran on final 400M despite not clear run near 200M and 50M.
Settled down 2-wide in midfield, switched out 500M to challenge, had every chance on straightening, one paced final 150M and held. (Distressed post race.)
Held up in midfield, brought wide into straight, finished it off fairly, no serious threat to leaders.
Reserved in a rearward position, 7Ls off the pace home turn, wide into straight, stayed on only fairly, no impression.
Chased leader, held 2nd to 350M, faded in the run home.
Dropped back to last, over 10Ls off the pace middle stages, lacked a finishing kick on straightening, never near to challenge.

Held up near last, ridden along 550M but failed to respond, emptied upon straightening. (Unacceptable Performance / Jockey reported his horse didn't travel as well as it did when successful last start.)
Tracked leaders, couldn't keep up 500M, gave ground rapidly on straightening, finished tailed out. (Unacceptable Performance.)
Bumped start, recovered to sit on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after straightening, finished off strongly to score.
Made contact shortly after start, raced prominently, took the lead from 1100M, led by half length on turn, kept on very well in straight, just couldn't hold off the winner late.
Made contact on jumping, raced 3 wide in midfield, hampered and carried wider near 900M, 2 lengths or so back on turn, closed off well to take a place.
Bumped on jumping, raced 2 wide at rear, 4 to 5 lengths back on turn, made very good progress in straight to make frame, nearest on line.

Jumped well from gate 10, slightly taken back to race 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, no clear running early in straight, angled out after passing 200M, made contact near 150M, finished off evenly thereafter.
Began very awkwardly and bumped, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, 3 lengths or so back on turn, showed some response early in straight, made contact near 150M, kept on evenly to the line.
Made contact on jumping, positioned 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, no clear running early in straight, made minor progress when clear after passing 150M.
Taken back from gate 11, raced at rear on rail, 5 lengths back on turn, kept to inside after straightening, got no clear running, made minor progress when clear final 100M.
Jumped well, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, 1/2L back on turn, kept on evenly early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Crowded on jumping, positioned on rail behind midfield, 5 lengths back, moved closer along the rail on turn, angled out early in straight, finished off evenly.

Jumped well from gate 9, raced 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, difficult to settle in the early stages, shifted out off heels near 900M, moved a bit closer on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.

Bumped start and unbalanced, raced 2 wide, 1 to 2 lengths back, similar position on turn, no clear running early in straight, peaked near 200M, weakened thereafter. (Lost right front plate.) (See Racing Incidents.)
Crowded on jumping, raced wide at rear, no cover on turn, weakened early in straight.
Began awkwardly and bumped, raced at rear throughout, never a factor.
Clean jump, raced 2 wide at rear, improved from 550M, finished off very strongly in straight to score by a neck.

Began well, sent forward to race prominently, found rail near 900M, a length back on turn, took the lead early in straight, kept on well to the line, just couldn't hold off the winner late. (See Racing Incidents.)
Commenced well, raced at rear behind midfield, 6 to 7 lengths back, angled out near 550M, blocked early in straight, finished off very strongly when clear final 200M, nearest on line.
Checked on jumping, raced at tail, 11 lengths back, closer on turn but still the last, made good progress in straight to make frame without threatening the first few.
Jumped well from the widest draw, took the lead easily, led by a length on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Began awkwardly and lost ground, raced at rear, moved closer along the rail on turn, checked near 400M, no daylight early in straight, made some headway when clear thereafter without threatening.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide behind midfield, moved a bit closer on turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Jumped well, showed no early speed, raced 4 wide in midfield, no cover throughout, kept on evenly after turning in, weakened gradually after passing final 150M.
Began fairly from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, no clear running early in straight, failed to quicken when clear thereafter.
Commenced well, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, allowed rival to cross near 1000M, 2 to 3 lengths back on turn, weakened gradually in straight.
Began only fairly, raced 3 wide in midfield, there to turn, no clear running early in straight, steadied near 300M, showed little response when clear thereafter.
Made contact on jumping, taken back to race at rear, 3 wide with cover, 6 lengths or so back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Jumped well, raced 2 wide, 3 to 4 lengths back, 3 wide on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Average to begin, raced prominently on rail early, allowed rival to cross near 1000M, 3 lengths back on turn, weakened early in straight, eased final 150M.

Jumped well, sent forward to take the lead, enjoyed the easy lead on turn, kept on strongly in straight, easily scored.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 3 lengths or so back on turn, taken wide in straight and finished off very strongly to take 2nd.
Shifted out at start and bumped, positioned 2 to 3 lengths back on rail, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after straightening and finished off evenly.
Clean jump, positioned 2 wide, 1 to 2 lengths back, there to turn, finished off evenly.
Began awkwardly, showed no early speed, raced 3 wide with no cover at rear, carried wider on turn, made some headway in straight without threatening.
Bumped on jumping, raced prominently but 3 wide, a length or so back on turn, peaked early in straight, slightly weakened thereafter.
Moderately away from gate 1, sat 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Away with them, positioned on rail at rear, 5 lengths back on turn, finished off one-paced in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide at rear, lay out after passing 600M, 5 lengths back on turn, failed to quicken under pressure in straight.
Bumped start, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, a length back on turn, weakened early in straight.
Hard ridden to hold the rail in midfield, benefited by the fast tempo, progressed steadily 300M to score.
Eased back, took rail, benefited by the fast tempo, progressed steadily 300M, just missed by a narrow margin.
Pushed to take rail and led at fast sectionals, hung on well until 50M overhauled.
Pushed forward, one out one back, not suited by the fast pace, just held ground in straight.
Eased back, 2-3 wide, favoured by the fast pace, progressed steadily 200M.
Checked at start, took rail at rear, favoured by the fast pace, made steady ground 200M.
Pushed to obtain box seat, not suited by the fast tempo, weakened 200M.
Pushed to keep up in midfield, trapped 3 wide throughout, ran on fairly in straight.
Hard ridden forward to cross, sat outside the leader, harmed by the fast pace, out of fuel 200M.
Pushed to keep up in midfield, 2 wide, suited by the fast tempo, no dash.
Hard ridden early but not muster, never a factor at back.
Hard ridden forward, trapped 3-4 wide in midfield, harmed by the fast pace, emptied 350M.
Fast out and took lead with nice early speed, asked for effort on straightening, worked home strongly to score.
Sat in box seat, commenced to improve near 300M, responded solidly, just missed by SH.
Raced at handy position, gradually made ground in straight, finished solidly.
Settled midfield, improved near 450M, bumped near 25M, not fully test. Swollen right front fetlock next day.
Travelled behind midfield on rail, responded nicely, near 25M was steadied and bumped a runner, not fully tested.
Began awkwardly, settled midfield on rail, hold the rail at Home Turn to save ground, finished well.
Raced behind midfield, widest on straightening, made up some nice late ground.
Taken back at start, raced at tail, one-paced in the straight.
Taken back at start, travelled fairly, one-paced when placed under pressure.
Settled midfield, very wide on straightening, no response in the straight.
Ridden along to share lead in one off position, weakened near 200M.
Throughout the race travelled wide and without cover, raced in handy position, failed to run on.
Jumped quickly and assumed lead. Travelled well in middle stages before setting up break in early stages of straight and holding on bravely to win.
Began well and came across to challenge for lead but posted 3 wide in middle sections outside leading pair. Toughed it out in the straight but couldn't bridge margin on leader.
Began well before easing behind speed to position on leaders back. Was close enough to lead on cornering but couldn't quite close.

Eased back shortly after the start before shuffled back to third last in middle stages. Pulled out wider on straightening but was conceding a huge start but made excellent late ground to beaten less than one length.
Was slightly slow away before settling worse than midfield on the fence. Presented with clear running upon straightening and worked home fairly for debut run.
Began quickly before easing behind leading pair to position one length off lead on outside. Was ridden up prior to straightening and only battled away in the straight.
Commenced fairly before ridden for speed and getting outside leader. Raced keenly in middle sections before weakening out in the last 250m.

Wasn't fast away and was eased back but bumped heavily after 100m and subsequently lost a length and positioned worse than midfield. Was pulled wider on straightening but conceded big start and was fair in the straight.
Commenced well settling midfield but slightly wide on the track with cover. Was ridden prior to straightening and faded out in the straight.
Began well but allowed to find feet before ultimately settling second last on the fence. Was a clear second last upon entering the straight and maintained that position in run to the line.
Wasn't fast away but improved quickly in first 100m to position midfield one horse off the fence. Came under pressure before the 400m and weakened out in the straight.
Was slow away and ridden up early to keep in touch with field. Was a clear last through middle stages and entered straight well back. Never flattered in run home.
Jumped with them, sent forward to take the lead, led by 3/4L on turn, kicked clear early in straight, easily scored with still plenty gas in tank.
Away with them, sent forward to race outside the leader in 2nd, 3/4L back on turn, kept on well in straight to take 2nd without threatening the winner.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, 7 lengths back, moved a bit closer in the middle stages, taken wide in straight and made good progress to take a place.
Out in line, showed no early speed, raced at rear, 7 lengths back, same margin back on turn, made good progress in straight to make frame without threatening.
Began awkwardly then bumped, raced 3 wide with cover, 4 lengths back, same position on turn, made some headway in straight.
Jumped well, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, finished off one-paced in straight. (Bleeder.)
Shifted in abruptly and bumped, raced 3 wide, 3 lengths back, there to turn, finished off one-paced.
Made contact shortly after start, raced 2 wide, 5 lengths back, same margin back on turn, showed limited response in straight.
Out in line, sat 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.

Bumped start, sent forward to race prominently but trapped 3 to 4 wide early, slightly taken back after entering to the back straight to sit 1 out 1 back, similar position on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Slightly slow out from gate 1, positioned 5 lengths behind the leader on rail, there to turn, failed to close off in straight. (Jockey concerned over the horse's action.)
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, same position on turn, weakened early in straight. (Blood in trachea.)
Raced in midfield, 5-1/2L behind the lead 2 wide, maintained nice run to the line to score by 3/4L.
Shifted across and raced at the rear, 9-1/4L behind along the rail, switched widest and ran on strongly to the line.
Travelled in midfield, 4L behind the lead 2 wide, responded well in straight to take 3rd.
Taken back and raced at the rear, 8-1/4L behind 2 wide, swung wide and made good progress in the straight.
Travelled in midfield, 5-1/2L behind along the rail, made ground and continued on fairly to the line.
Bumped start and raced in front of midfield, 3-1/4L off along the rail, checked at 200M when no run, ran on well.
Raced close to the rear, 7-1/2L behind along the rail, held up near 200M, closed off nicely thereafter.
Rolled forward to race in the box-seat, sat 1-3/4L off, was one paced.
Stayed away from the rail to be in one-off one-back, sat 2-1/2L off, hung in in straight, particularly in final 100M.
Pushed and sat 1L off and outside the leader, in touch until near 100M when run ended.
Ridden to take rail and led, maintained lead until gave ground near 200M.
Bumped start, failed to muster and raced in worse than midfield 2 wide, did not improve.
Taken back to rear for rails run, improved swiftly to rear of midfield in 7th, saved ground on the rail turning for home, quickened well to snatch victory final strides.
Broke well and held narrow lead early stages, settled for 2nd outside the leader in back straight, gained upper hand from tiring leader 200 metres out only to be caught in the shadow of the post.
Soon taken back wide from the widest gate settling 9th or 8th, commenced move rounding home bend, ran on well under pressure down the centre of the straight.
Never far off, switched off the rail for a run turning into straight, fought on steadily without threatening.
Ridden positively from the one draw, took up running 1000 metres out, led until finding no extra inside the final 200 metres.
Settled in midfield on the rail, commenced move entering straight gaining 4th some 3L off the lead, unable to sustain effort inside the final 200 metres.
Crowded shortly after start, checked and dropped to last 1000 metres out, remained in last to the straight, made up some late ground on the rail.
Ridden forward after bumped at the start, settled mainly about 4L back in forward of midfield, ran home one-paced.
Broke well and taken back from a wide gate, travelled wide in last few, made up some late ground close to finish.
Jumped well, gradually dropped towards the rear on the rail, inconvenienced rounding home bend, made no impression in the run home.
Ridden positively from a wide gate, settled not far off in 3rd or 4th 2-wide, faded into straight.
Never seen with a chance.
From wide draw taken across behind runners, held up in last 6Ls off the pace and raced keenly with blinkers first time, charged to the line when clear passing 250M, proved too strong late.
Bustled along to chase leader after the jump, vied for lead from 400M, wrestled the lead inside 100M only to be caught by fast finishing winner near line.
From wide draw got into a midfield position on outside, moved closer to leaders home turn, ran on well in straight and loomed a threat 150M, kept on to go 3rd near line.
Taken across behind runners, settled 2nd last on the inside 5Ls off, shifted out into clear early straight, closed off well to be nearest at the line.
Broke well and quickly into the lead, took them along steadily, fought on well in straight, headed inside 100M, swamped late.
Badly unbalanced at the start and lost ground, raced back in the field subsequently, proved difficult to settle, brought wide into straight and worked home well from the rear, nearest finish.
In touch chasing leaders, had every chance on straightening but always held by leaders.
Jumped on terms, restrained to be 5th in midfield, only held ground in the run home. No impression.
Reserved towards the rear, made some ground on straightening but no threat to leaders.
Held up 3-wide in mid-division, kept on same pace in the straight, no threat to leaders.
Crowded for room on jumping, settled in midfield along the fence, couldn't quicken when driven passing 300M. (Jockey reported his mount felt flat.)
Chased leaders, soon weakened on straightening, eased when no chance final 150M.

Fast into stride, sent forward to take the lead, led by 1-1/2L, same margin lead to turn, headed near 600M, kept on evenly to the line.
Began awkwardly and bumped, positioned on rail in midfield, 3 to 4 lengths back, there to turn, finished off evenly, never a threat to the first few.
Commenced well, raced 2 wide in 3rd, 2 to 3 lengths back, hard ridden on turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Taken back to race at tail, 9 lengths back, moved closer on turn, only 5 to 6 lengths back, finished off evenly in straight.
Bumped on jumping, raced 2 wide in midfield, hard ridden from 700M but only showed limited response, finished off one-paced in straight.
Taken back to race 7 to 8 lengths back at rear, 2 wide, hard ridden after passing 800M but only showed limited response, failed to quicken under pressure in straight.
Average to begin, positioned on rail at rear, 6 to 7 lengths back, saved ground on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Pushed to sit in front of midfield on the rails, closed off strongly 300M to score.
At back along the fence, benefited by the fast tempo, lack room 400M, progressed steadily when clear.
Hard ridden to hold the box seat, checked early, not suited by the fast pace, held ground for 3rd.
Pushed to keep up in midfield, suited by the fast tempo, made ground 300M, run ended 100M.
Hard ridden to take rail and share the lead, harmed by the fast sectionals, weakened 200M.
At back, 2-3 wide, favoured by the fast pace, made ground 200M.
