Pushed early, sat in front of midfield, 2-3 wide, weakened 200M>
Pressed forward, 2 wide, not suited by the fast pace, emptied 250M.
Hard ridden to share the lead in 2 wide at fast sectionals, out of fuel 250M.
Eased back, never competitive.
Settled midfield, asked for effort near 600M, quickened passing 200M, scored unchallenged.
Began awkwardly then ridden along to sit outside the lead, responded solidly in the straight, finished strongly.
Ridden to settle in box seat, fought hard entire straight, finished nicely.
Hard ridden to race at handy position, responded well in the straight, finished OK.
Urged along to take lead, responded well in the straight, gave ground passing 100M, rider failed to ride out.
Settled at back, lay out making the turn, widest on straightening, one-paced in straight.
Travelled wide and without cover, settled at back, improved to midfield near 600M, one-paced.
At start was bumped and became badly unbalanced, raced midfield, gained some ground passing 100M.
Crowded and lost ground at start, raced behind midfield, limited response in the straight.
Stumbled at start, raced at tail, limited response.
Settled midfield on rail, no response when placed pressure, weakened passing 100M.
Hampered at start, settled behind midfield, raced keenly in middle stages, checked near 700M, never in it.

Ridden hard for first 100m to gain prominent position before settling 1 length behind speed. Shared lead upon straightening before fighting on bravely to hold of late challengers in the run to the line.

Jumped well before coming across from wide barrier and settling midfield on the outside, three horses off the fence but with cover. Conceded leaders around 3 lengths on straightening but sprinted hard late to just miss.
Commenced well and went forward to assume uncontested lead. Travelled well in the lead and was still prominent until caught right in final few strides.

Away fairly before being allowed to find feet and settling worse than midfield and off the fence. Pulled around heals at the 500m and entered the straight the widest runner before making good late ground.
Had economical run after positioning leaders back. Was presented with clear running shortly after straightening but could not capitalize. Was not beaten far.

Commenced fairly before being ridden forward. Couldn't quite cross to outside leader so raced three wide in middle stages. Slightly awkward when taking home corner before balancing up and working fairly to the line.

Eased back from wide barrier to position near the tail. Raced keenly after 300m and was bumped after the 500m mark. Came across heals after straightening and was widest runner before balancing and making some late ground.

Only moderately away before positioning midfield one horse off fence. Was niggled at in early stages before easing at the 750m. Stayed close to the fence in the straight but was mostly one paced in the straight.

Commenced very fast and was ridden hard to come across from wide gate but was stranded four wide when speed inside gathered momentum. Lost a length when cornering and conceded 2 lengths to leaders upon straightening.

Was eased back shortly after the start and remained worse than midfield between runners in middle sections. Had plenty of room after straightening to improve but only ground away. Looked to hand in later stages.

One of the slowest away before taken back and cross to the fence. Eased and slightly cramped at 650m and lost a length. Entered the straight in last position and failed to improve much in the run home.

Had no early speed and eased across to the tail. Was bumped and brushed on multiple occasions between 600m and 450m. Was well back on straightening and pretty much maintained that position in the run to the post.

Commenced well and ridden hard for first 100m before ultimately easing behind speed, positioning between runners in midfield. Improved closer to the speed at 600m but was under pressure upon straightening.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 wide from near 600M, finished off strongly to score.
Average to begin, no early speed, raced 2 to 3 wide at rear, taken wide after passing 500M, finished off very strongly to take 2nd, nearest on line.
Bumped on jumping, raced 2 wide behind midfield, angled out from near 600M, 3 wide turning in, made good progress in straight to take a place.
Jumped well, positioned on rail in midfield, 2 wide from near 600M, no clear running early in straight, made good progress when clear thereafter to make frame.
Shifted out on jumping and bumped, positioned on rail behind midfield, moved closer along the rail on turn, blocked near 300M, shifted out off heels near 100M, made some progress thereafter.

Away with them, raced 3 wide in midfield early, moved a bit closer after passing 1000M but still 3 wide and without cover, challenged the leader turning in, kept on well until near final 100M, weakened thereafter.
Jumped well from gate 9, sent forward to take the early lead, shared the lead with rival on turn, kept on well early in straight, headed near 150M, slightly weakened thereafter.
Moderately away from the widest draw, raced 2 wide better than midfield, there to turn, kept on evenly early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Shifted out at start and bumped, sent forward to race prominently but wide, shared lead turning in, kept on evenly early in straight, weakened close home.
Bumped start, raced 2 to 3 lengths back on rail, moved closer along the rail on turn, no daylight early in straight, finished off one-paced when clear thereafter.
Hampered start, taken back to race at rear, 8 lengths back, closer on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, 10 lengths back, still well back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Taken back from gate 12, unable to slot in, trapped 4 wide with no cover in midfield, there to turn, emptied early in straight when hard run took effect.
Away with them, raced 3 wide behind midfield, awkwardly placed near 600M, weakened early in straight, eased after passing final 200M.
Sat in just behind midfield, 5-1/4L behind 3 wide but with cover, battled on strongly to score by a head.
Travelled in midfield, 4-1/4L behind 2 wide, fought on nicely but headed by winner in final strides.
Raced in one-off one-back position, sat 2-3/4L off, stayed on well to finish 3/4L behind in 3rd.
Eased to be in behind midfield, 6L behind 2 wide, improved and continued to close off strongly.
Bumped start then taken back, 8-3/4L behind 3 wide but with cover, closed off nicely inside final 200M.
Bumped start then raced at the rear, 8L behind 2 wide, saved ground and continued on nicely.
In midfield but wide initially, moved forward to lead by 750M, headed at 150M and was one paced.
Slow to jump then raced in behind midfield, 6-3/4L behind along the rail, progressed steadily.
In box-seat, then shuffled one spot back at 750M to be 3-1/4L behind, was one paced.
Sent forward and settled 1-1/2L off and outside the lead, in touch until near 150M when weakened.
In midfield, 5-1/4L behind along the rail, improved slightly late.
Niggled along, gave up lead at 750M and dropped to the box-seat, emptied passing 300M.
Eased and raced towards the rear, 3 wide but with cover, did not improve.
In midfield, wide and without cover throughout, gave ground in the straight.
Soon recovered from a moderate start to share early pace, settled for one back position on the rail approaching home bend, renewed effort to hit the front inside the 200 metres.
Broke well and ridden positively from a wide gate, led on the rail approaching the 1000 metres, headed under pressure inside the 200 metres, eased up final strides.
Travelled in midfield, ran on inside the final 400 metres without threatening.
Settled well behind, trailed the field into the straight, widest runner turning for home, ran on well inside the final 300 metres without threatening.
Settled in last few, ran on steadily in straight without threatening.
Began well, settled just worse than midfield, saved ground turning for home, kept on one pace.
Crowded at start, settled in last few on the rail, switched out for a run on straightening, kept on.

Ridden along from a wide gate travelling wide without cover throughout, joint 3rd in back straight before drifting some 3L back in 6th approaching home bend, dropped further behind turning in, found nothing.
Travelled wide without cover in midfield, made no impression in straight.
Jumped fairly but soon dropped behind midfield despite niggling along, made no impression in straight.
Settled in midfield on the rail, faded into straight.
Not far off in 6th, improved to 1.5L back in 3rd 3-wide around home bend, faded gradually out of contention after straightening. (Tactic questioned)
Moderate start, gradually picked up to 2L 3rd on the rail, dropped back to 3L 5th rounding home bend, weakened further into straight.
Not far off until home bend, lost touch on straightening.
Reserved in midfield, 7th on settling, just over 3Ls to make up on leader at 400M, moved up steadily on straightening, found extra late and got up close home.
From draw 14 ridden forward to join leader on the outside, kicked on well passing 400M, just couldn't hold off the winner last few strides, huge run in defeat.
From draw 10 guided to a 2-wide spot towards the rear, 6Ls to make up top of straight, picked up well from 350M, closed fast final stages, nearest finish.
Chased leaders along the 2-path, moved up to 2nd nearing 300M, tried hard to reel in leader but effort levelled inside final 100M.
Positioned just ahead of midfield, had his chance in the straight but just battled away and well held by leaders, one paced late.
Failed to muster, raced towards the rear further back than intended, took a while to get going in straight, did best work over final 200M. (Jockey : may be better suited by stepping up in distance.)
Settled down rear of midfield, battled on well until last 150M when run ended.
5th on settling, always in touch, into clear 400M but couldn't quicken on the run home, faded closing stages.
From draw 1 held up in midfield along the rail 4-5Ls back, ran into heels of rival near 200M, shifted lane to continue but kept grinding away only.
Dropped back from wide barrier, raced near the rear always, ran on same pace in the straight, no serious threat.
Chased leaders, battled on same pace on straightening, no extra final 200M.
Blew the start, always near rear, couldn't pick up pace 400M, never involved.
Driven forward to share lead with rival, bustled along 500M to hold position, weakened rapidly passing 200M.
Taken back from draw 12, always at the rear over 9Ls off the pace middle stages, came under serious pressure 500M, well beaten.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, 8 lengths back, a bit closer on turn but still 6 lengths behind, finished off very strongly in straight to score by a neck.
Bumped start, positioned on rail in midfield, 2 to 3 lengths back, 2 wide on turn, finished off very well, just couldn't hold off the winner late.
Away with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, carried wider on turn, made good progress in straight to take a place.
Shifted out at start and bumped, sent forward to take the lead, challenged by rivals on turn, kept on well in straight, just couldn't hold off the challengers late.
Bumped start, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, challenged the leader turning in, peaked early in straight, just kept on evenly to the line.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear, 5 lengths or so back, closer on turn, taken wide early in straight, finished off well to be nearest on line.
Began only fairly and bumped, positioned on rail behind midfield, 5 lengths back, closer on turn, made some progress early in straight, weakened in the closing stages.
Jumped with them, raced wide at rear, 5 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, showed limited response in straight.
Began fairly, raced 2 wide behind midfield early, angled out near 800M, very wide turning in, showed little response in straight.
Blundered at start, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, failed to close off in straight. (Blood in trachea.)
Commenced well, raced 2 wide, a length or so back, bumped near 700M, 3 wide on turn, weakened early in straight. (Lame right front leg.) (Blood in trachea.)
Began well from a wide draw, raced 3 wide, 2 lengths back, sent forward after passing 700M, 4 wide turning in, weakened early in straight. (Lame left front leg next day.)
Taken back from gate 13, raced at tail, 10 lengths back, moved closer on turn but still the last, finished off impressively with the fastest last sectional of the race and scored.
Bumped start, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, 2 wide on turn, finished off strongly to take 2nd.

Jumped well, sent forward to race prominently on rail, allowed rival to cross near 1000M, angled out near 800M, moved closer on turn, took the lead early in straight, kept on well thereafter but couldn't hold off the first few late.
Began fairly from gate 1, positioned on rail better than midfield, shifted out off heels 700M, 2 wide turning, finished off well to make frame.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 wide turning in, finished off evenly in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear on rail, 5 lengths back on turn, angled out near 500M, made some progress in straight without threatening.
Began well, raced 2 wide better than midfield, carried wider on turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Taken back to race 2 wide at rear, 8 lengths back, closer on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Began well from gate 10, sent forward to race prominently, found rail near 1000M, sat right behind the leader on turn, no clear running early in straight, failed to quicken when clear thereafter.

Bounded in the air on jumping and lost ground, quickly recovered to a prominent position, took the lead after passing 1200M, challenged by rival turning in, headed early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Jumped with them, raced 3 wide with no cover in midfield early, found cover near 900M, 3 to 4 lengths back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Shifted out on jumping and bumped, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, got no clear running in straight, not able to test properly.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide behind midfield early, found rail near 1000M, saved ground on turn, failed to make any progress in straight.
Jumped well from the widest draw, unable to slot in, raced very wide and without cover in midfield, still 4 wide on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.

Commenced well, positioned 2 wide, 2 to 3 lengths back, closer on turn, finished off very strongly to score.

Began well, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, difficult to settle early, same position on turn, kept to inside after straightening, finished off very well to take 2nd, just beaten by a neck.
Began awkwardly, positioned on rail at rear, 2 wide from near 500M, taken wide in straight and finished off very strongly to be nearest on line.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide behind midfield, awkwardly placed near 1150M, difficult to settle shortly thereafter, improved from 500M, very wide turning in, closed off well to make frame.
Clean jump, positioned 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, same margin back on turn, angled out near 450M, finished off evenly in straight.
Jumped well from the widest draw, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length, challenged around home turn, headed after passing 200M, kept on evenly to the line. (Blood in trachea.)
Away with them, positioned on rail behind midfield, 4 lengths back on turn, kept battling in straight before racing tight final stages and not ridden out.
Moderately away from a wide draw, raced 2 wide in midfield, same position on turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Taken back from gate 9, raced at tail, still 6 lengths back on turn, made some progress early in straight, awkwardly placed close home, not able to be ridden out.
Began very awkwardly, raced 2 wide at rear, crowded near 1000M, carried wider on turn, bumped near 450M, finished off evenly in straight.
Jumped with them, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, challenged the leader turning in, weakened gradually after passing final 200M.
Average to begin, taken back to race at rear, detached from the field on turn, eased early in straight. (Lame left front leg next day.)
Pushed to sit just off the leaders, progressed steadily 300M to score.
Pushed forward, box seat, not suited by the fast pace, ran on strongly for 2nd.
Hard ridden forward, sat outside the leader, harmed by the fast sectionals, ran on strongly for 3rd.
Settled in midfield on the rails, benefited by the fast pace, made ground 300M but without threats.
Very slow away, took rail at rear, benefited by the fast pace, progressed steadily 300M.
At back, trapped 3 wide, suited by the fast tempo, made steady ground 200M.
Eased at start, 2 wide at rear, benefited by the fast pace, progressed steadily 200M.
Very slow away, at back along the rails, favoured by the fast pace, ran on fairly.
At back along the fence, benefited by the fast tempo, ran on fairly.
Slow away, behind midfield, 2-3 wide, never improved.
Hard ridden forward, sat 2 wide, harmed by the fast pace, out of fuel 400M.
Pushed to hold the lead, clocked very fast sectionals, soon emptied 250M.
Jumped nicely, settled midfield, wide on straightening, quickened passing 200M, finished strongly to score.
Hard ridden to take lead, asked for effort on straightening, worked home solidly.
Began awkwardly, settled behind midfield on rail, gradually made ground in the straight, finished solidly.
Urged hard to race in box seat, gained some ground passing 100M, came line nicely.
Raced midfield, made the turn after 600M awkwardly, widest on straightening, made some ground passing 100M.
Jumped well, hard ridden then settled midfield on rail, responded OK in the straight.
Urged along from the widest gate, settled at handy position, gave some ground approaching 50M.
Settled behind midfield, always niggled, one-paced in the straight.
Fractious in the barrier, began awkwardly and lost ground, raced at back, limited response.
Ridden along to settle at handy position, tried to improve passing 400M, weakened passing 200M, failed to make impression.
Raced behind midfield, no response when asked for effort, failed to run on.
Began only fairly, travelled at tail, weakened in Home Turn, never in it.
Moderately away before ridden up to position midfield on outside. Was niggled at middle stages before entering straight still 4L off lead. Worked home well last section.
Positioned worse than midfield on the outside. Was asked to improve well before straightening before entering the straight the widest runner and making good late ground.

Ridden forward before ultimately positioning outside 1L off leader to its outside. Entered the straight in prominent position before fighting on bravely but just being overhauled by back-markers in closing stages.

Started well before easing behind two speed horses to position perfectly behind leader. Was travelling extremely well 1 length off lead but was immediately under pressure on straightening. Boxed on fairly.
Ridden forward before settling behind leading trio 3L off speed. Entered straight conceding similar margin before battling away in the straight.
Didn't show a large amount of speed and ultimately settled worse than midfield on the inside. Still 5 lengths back upon straightening and made some ground in last section.
Had little early pace, settling second from last on the outside. Pulled the widest on straightening and made some late ground out wide.
Jumped fast and ridden hard to get lead. Bumped with another runner after 100m. Travelled in the lead and was still 1L clear on straightening before being headed at the 175m and tiring late.
Positioned midfield on fence only 3L from lead. Looked under pressure and was ridden up before cornering. Stayed close to fence but was only fair to the line.
Eased back after jumping and came across to the tail of the field after first section. Was conceding large start to leaders and was ridden hard to bridge gap before straightening.
Couldn't display an early speed and settled last in middle sections. Was at least 8 lengths from lead on straightening so made some ground close to fence but was never a live threat.
Was ridden forward from barrier but could not cross to lead so was subsequently three horses wide outside leader. Began to lose a ground upon cornering and weakened out in later stages.
Hampered on jumping, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, angled out after passing 400M, finished off strongly in straight to score.
Taken back to race 5 lengths back on rail, saved ground on turn, angled out early in straight, closed off well to take 2nd without threatening the winner.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, 3 wide on turn, made some headway in straight to take a place, just missed 2nd.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear on rail, still 5 to 6 lengths back on turn, made good progress in straight to make frame.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide, 2 to 3 lengths back, similar position on turn, showed good response in straight, checked near 100M, ran on evenly to the line thereafter.
Began well from the widest draw, sent forward to race in 2nd, 2 wide, same position on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked near 150M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Shifted out on jumping, sat 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, easy run to turn, kept to inside after straightening, finished off evenly.
Jumped well, raced 2 wide behind midfield, checked off heels near 1400M, 4 lengths or so back on turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Away with them, raced 3 wide with no cover behind midfield early, steadied near 1100M to obtain cover, positioned 7 lengths back at rear thereafter, there to turn, made no progress in straight.
Began fairly, sent forward to take the lead, travelled keenly in the middle stages, led by a length on turn, headed near 200M, weakened thereafter.

Out in line, raced wide at rear early, sent forward after passing 1100M, raced 3 wide, 2 to 3 lengths back in the back straight, gave ground from 500M, eased early in straight. (Irregular heart rhythm.)
Sent forward to lead but stayed one-off, outscored rival by a nose in a close battle that went to the wire.
Pushed then settled 1L off the lead along the rail, in tight battle to the finish, missed by a nose.
In midfield initially, improved to one-off one-back prior to 600M, ran on nicely to take 3rd.
Bumped start, settled in front of midfield, 3L off 2 wide, kept on fairly to the line.
Eased then raced towards the tail, 7L behind 2 wide, switched widest and closed off well inside final 100M.
Settled in just behind midfield, 4-1/2L behind along the rail, ran on okay.
Travelled in behind midfield, 5-3/4L behind 2 wide, ran home one paced on the outside track.
Raced at the rear, 7-3/4L behind 2 wide, slight dash when under whip after 200M.
In worse than midfield along the rail, continued on one paced home.
Pushed but had to settle in front of midfield along the rail at 600M, faded in the straight.(Lame left hind)
Taken back, at rear along the rail, did not improve. (Lame right front)
Bumped start, then raced in midfield 2 wide, never in it. (Lame left front)

Settled mainly in midfield, commenced move rounding home bend, ran wide into straight, hit the front narrowly over 150 metres out, just held on to the line despite racing tightly with runner-up throughout closing stages.
Began well, settled mainly just better than midfield on the rail, switched out for a run on straightening, hampered 200 metres out but fought on well to just fail to peg back the winner.
Broke well, settled just off the pace on the rail, hugged the rail turning in, fought on steadily to hold every chance in straight but unable to sustain effort closing stages.

Jumped fairly, settled in midfield early stages, shuffled backward in back straight, re-gained to midfield on home bend, switched wide for a run entering home straight, ran on to be nearest at finish.
Taken back for rails run from a wide gate, took closer order coming onto home bend, did not find much room after straightening until too late at the 80 metres.

Crowded at start, travelled in midfield early stages before pulling forward from the 1100M, hit the front briefly between 900M and 800M, disputed lead into straight when came under pressure, tired inside the final 200M.
Began from a wide gate, gradually obtained rails run in the front passing winning post the first time, led the field most of the way to the 200 metres when overhauled. (Lame)
Settled at the back after beginning from the widest gate, commenced move on home bend, ran on under pressure to be nearest at finish despite interrupted run in the straight.
Settled well behind, gained slightly closer and ridden along 4-wide in back straight, reached rear of midfield on home bend, swung widest turning in and made up some late ground.
Crowded at start, given a reminder early on before settling some 2L back in 4th, carried backward by a weakening horse and severely hampered and stumbled badly 700 metres out, never recovered.
Settled just worse than midfield, made mid-race move on the outside gaining to 2L back in 4th over 800 metres out, dropped out under pressure after straightening.
Not far off to the 850 metres, folded up quickly. (Heart irregularly) (Lame next day)
Restrained behind mid-division, 8th on settling, switched away from fence 400M, chased well and moved up alongside leader near 100M, got up close home.
Tracked leaders in 3rd, driven top of straight and quickened to lead nearing 200M, challenged by eventual winner 100M, headed close home.
Never far off the pace, in 4th chasing leaders rounding home turn, came through narrow passage to challenge 250M, not pace of first 2 final 150M.
Held up near the rear, 10th along the rail, ridden along passing 500M, stayed on final 300M making steady progress towards the line.
From wide draw taken back to last after the start, 6.5Ls to make up at 400M,ran on steadily over final 300M without threat.
Shifted across behind runners following an awkward start, held up 2nd last 7-8Ls off the pace, widest into straight, stayed on without threatening leaders.
Broke well from inside gate, led steadily, pressed by rival from 1200M, held lead until swamped passing 250M, faded away.
Caught wide early stages, improved to race outside leader 1200M, held position to 250M, found no extra under pressure.
Up with early pace, remained in touch on settling, battled on fairly inside 300M, no threat to leaders.
Settled down 2-wide in midfield, shuffled back entering home turn, couldn't finish off in the straight.
Held up towards the rear, brought wide into straight, didn't run on, eased over final 200M.
Ahead of midfield, caught wide no cover throughout the race, failed to improve position when driven along 500M, eased when no chance mid-straight.

Commenced well, raced 2 wide, 2 to 3 lengths back, same position on turn, bumped near 300M, finished off strongly to take 2nd.
Bumped on jumping, sent forward to take the lead, found rail near 850M, travelled well on turn, kept on well in straight, just couldn't hold off the first two late.
Bumped start and unbalanced, raced 2 to 3 wide with cover, 5 lengths back, 3 wide on turn, taken wide near 300M, made some progress before being crowded near 100M, finished off well thereafter.
Crowded on jumping, raced wide at rear, 7 lengths back, no cover on turn, improved from 600M, finished off well, just missed frame.
Moderately away from gate 1, sat on rail in midfield, 3-1/2L back, saved ground on turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Began well, raced 3 wide in midfield, there to turn, bumped near 300M, finished off evenly thereafter.
Jumped well, raced 2 to 3 wide, a length or so back, no cover on turn, kept on evenly early in straight, weakened close home.
Slowly away, raced at rear on rail, 5 lengths back on turn, kept to inside after straightening and made some progress.
Began well, raced prominently, allowed rival to cross near 850M, sat right behind the leader on turn, kept on well early in straight, hampered near 100M, not able to be ridden out.
Jumped well from gate 13, raced prominently but wide, 2 wide from 850M, 3/4L back on turn, peaked early in straight, kept on one-paced to the line.
Away with them, raced 2 wide behind midfield, inconvenienced near 1000M, 4 lengths back on turn, failed to quicken under pressure in straight.
Moderately away, unable to slot in early, taken back to race 3 wide at rear, 6 lengths back on turn, showed nothing in straight.

Placing: PU
Comment: Slowly away, showed no early speed, detached from the field before turn, eased after making the turn near 900M. (Lame left hind leg.)
Eased to sit 3 back on the fence, unleashed strong finishing efforts 250M to score.
Hard ridden to secure box seat, made early move 600M, closed off strongly for 2nd.
Hard ridden early, trapped 4 wide, moved forward gradually to sit outside the leader, held ground in straight for 3rd.
Hard ridden forward to take rail and lead, hung on well until 100M overhauled.
At rear, dashed strongly 300M.
Pushed early, at back, 2-3 wide, dashed well 300M.
At rear, made the move around the field in 4-5 wide, little dash 250M.
At rear, 2-4 wide, on heels 600M, ran on fairly.
Pushed to sit in front of midfield, 2-3 wide, lack turn of foot in straight.
Pushed early, midfield 2-3 wide, no dash in straight.
Eased back, trapped 4-5 wide throughout, no progress.
Checked early, at back, never improved.
Eased back, never competitive.
Pushed forward, 2 wide, soon emptied 500M.
Ridden along from widest gate, then steadied to obtain cover near 1600M, settled at tail, widest on straightening, responded strongly in the straight to score.
Settled midfield on rail, kept on rail at Home Turn to save ground, quickened near 200M, finished solidly.
Jumped nicely, settled in handy position, proved difficult to settle for some distance passing 1100M, ran on nicely in the straight, finished well.
Raced midfield on rail, near 1000M improved to box seat, commenced passing 450M, finished OK.
Settled midfield, asked for effort passing 450M, gained some ground passing 100M.
Raced midfield, after 900M was left racing wide and without cover, one-paced.
Taken back at start, niggled passing 900M, one-paced in the straight.
Settled behind midfield, tried to improve near 600M, limited response.
Hard ridden to take lead, difficult to settle passing 1400M, faded out passing 200M.
Shortly after that start steadied away from heels, raced in handy position, weakened near 300M, failed to run on.
Taken back at start, always back, never in it.
Veered out and bumped at the start before gathering momentum and speeding to lead. Travelled comfortably in middle sections before breaking away from challengers in last 200m to score easily.
Bumped shortly after the start before settling forward only 2 lengths off leaders. Was ridden up to challenge from the 350m and fought it out well to beat all bar the winner.

Was bumped heavily between runners just after the start. Settled behind the leading pair one horse away from the stand side rail. Was ridden forward from 400m when pace quickened and tried hard in the straight.

Not the quickest away but gathered speed quickly to come across to stand side and challenge for the lead. Was under pressure at 300m and couldn't go with winner but didn't give it away in the late stages.
Bumped after the start before settling midfield only 3 lengths off lead. Drifted back a further length inside 500m before shifting and making late ground inside the final 200m.
Didn't have early speed and settled near the tail of the field. Stayed close to the middle of the track in last 300m and made good ground inside the 250m.
Was fairly away before settling in the second half of the field. Was ridden up from 500m to hold position but then improved position in last 200m to not be beaten too far.
Showed good early speed to go forward before easing behind leading pair after 200m. Came across heels at the 275m and was looking threatening before tiring in the last 75m.
One of the last into stride before settling at the tail of the field after 300m. Changed direction and improved between runners at the 250m before tiring last 100m.
Slightly reared at the start and subsequently settled near the rear of the field. Ridden hard from the 400m to improve position but was a little flat footed when speed quickened.
Reared as the start and consequently lost a few lengths in early stages. Continually improved position in between 800m and 400m before just fading out in the last furlong.
Commenced fairly before drifting back in first 350m to position worse than midfield. Was under pressure from the 450m when pace improved and was never a threat in the run to the line.
Not quick away but gathered some speed to position in midfield closer to the middle of the course. Ridden hard from 400m before dropping out of the contest from the 350m.
Bumped heavily between runners at the start and subsequently lost a length before improving and settling only 3 lengths from lead. Ridden hard from the 500m before fading out from 300m.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear on rail, 8 lengths back, a bit closer on turn, 2 wide from near 600M, finished off very strongly in straight to score by head.
Crowded out start, raced 2 wide better than midfield, same position on turn, finished off very strongly, just couldn't hold off the winner late.(Finished distressed.)
Jumped well from gate 11, sent forward to take the lead, found rail near 1300M, travelled comfortably on turn, kept on well in straight, headed near 100M, stayed on well to take 3rd.
Commenced well, positioned 2 wide, 2 to 3 lengths back, 3 wide turning in, showed good response early in straight, peaked near 200M, kept on evenly thereafter.
Crowded on jumping, positioned on rail behind midfield, saved ground on turn, angled out early in straight and made some progress, no threat to the first few.
Bumped start and unbalanced, recovered quickly to race in 2nd, 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader, 2 wide on turn, peaked early in straight, kept on one-pace to the line. (Lost right front plate.)
Made contact on jumping, raced 2 wide in midfield, angled out after passing 600M, finished off evenly in straight.
Crowded start, positioned on rail in midfield, closer on turn, 2 wide from 550M, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Taken back to race at rear, 9 lengths back, a bit closer on turn, finished off one-paced in straight.
Shifted out abruptly at start and made contact, sat 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, moved closer along the rail on turn, failed to quicken in straight.
Taken back to race 2 wide behind midfield, 7 lengths back, hard ridden from 500M, showed nothing in straight.
Taken back from gate 10, raced at tail, 11 lengths back, still 7 lengths back on turn, emptied early in straight.
Opt out to lead due fast pace, improved to be outside lead prior to 900M turn, continued to the line unchallenged despite drifted out in straight.
In worse than midfield, 2 wide, assisted by the fast pace to fight on, headed initially but fought back to take 2nd.
At rear and 2 wide, helped by the fast pace, locked in close battle over last 150M, but just short of the 2nd prize.
Sat slightly behind midfield along the rail, did not benefit by the quick tempo, only one paced.
Bumped start, at the rear along the rail, helped by the fast tempo, made slight dashes in the straight.
Stayed 2 wide and got cover when the winner improved just before 900M turn, run ended after 200M.
In box-seat and followed the leaders at fast pace, found no extra approaching 200M.
Went forward to lead, set fast pace in early and middle stages, weakened at 400M.
Settled in rear, shaken up upon straightening, quickened well to take charge about 150 metres out.
Settled behind midfield, saved ground on inside turning for home, ran on well to hit the front briefly over 200 metres out, hung on well for 2nd.
Prominent early stages, settled some 4L back in 5th or 6th in midfield on the rail, baulked for a run passing the 400 metres, ran on without threatening.
Taken back from a wide gate, given a reminder approaching the home turn, produced good late impression inside the final 300 metres.
Niggled along in prominent position early, settled some 4L back in 5th approaching back straight, remained in midfield rounding home bend, kept on under pressure before fading closing stages.

Vied for lead early stages, settled outside the leader most of the way to home straight, came to challenge after straightening and hit the front momentarily 300 metres out, soon weakened. (Tactic questioned)

Crowded and blundered badly early, just worse than midfield before taking closer order in back straight reaching one-out-one-back position in 4th coming onto home bend, dropped away quickly after straightening.(Tactic questioned)
Travelled in prominent 3rd most of the way until folded up quickly inside the final 300 metres. (Questioned for disappointing performance)
Attempted to make all holding narrow advantage most of the way to the 400 metres, gradually weakened after straightening. (Questioned for disappointing performance)
Crossed to the lead 900M, led a steady gallop, kicked on well in straight and opened up 2Ls lead at 200M, found enough to hold off late challenge.
Away well, tracked leader, bumped 800M and wide no cover thereon, dug deep under strong determination over final 200M, came closest to winner at the line under 5lb penalty.
Never far off, looked a possible chance on straightening, tried hard but always held by winner.
Slowly into stride, raced at the back 4Ls off, saved ground on inside, ran on steadily under pressure but never looked like catching the leaders
Held up in midfield on outer, driven out 450M, took a while to get going, stayed on steadily towards the line.
Crowded for room at the start, improved to be about 5th on settling, raced keenly middle stages, kept on same pace passing 400M, faded late.
Went forward, commenced to prove very difficult to settle when crossed by rival 900M, switched to 2-wide making the turn for home, battled on to 150M then weakened.
Eased back to race near the rear on settling, found little in the run home, no impression. (Lame next day.)
Taken back from wide draw, held up 3-wide at the rear, couldn't pick up on straightening, no threat.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide, 4 lengths or so back, 3 wide from near 600M, finished off very strongly in straight to score by a nose.
Began fairly from gate 1, positioned on rail, 3 lengths or so back, saved ground on turn, finished off very strongly, just couldn't hold off the winner late.
Jumped well from a tricky gate, sent forward to race prominently but wide, 2 wide on turn, kept on well in straight to take 3rd.
Began smartly, sent forward to take the lead, travelled comfortably on turn, kept on well in straight, just couldn't hold off the first few final 100M.
Began fairly, raced 2 wide in midfield, 4 lengths back on turn, no daylight early in straight, made some progress when clear thereafter.
Shifted in at start and bumped, unable to slot in, raced very wide with no cover, 3 lengths or so back, 4 wide on turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Moderately away, sat 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Taken back to race 2 to 3 wide at rear, 6 lengths back on turn, made some progress in straight without threatening.
Taken back to race at rear on rail, 5 lengths back, same margin back on turn, kept to inside after straightening, finished off one-paced.
Bumped start, raced 3 to 4 wide behind midfield, 4 lengths back on turn, made no progress in straight.
Slightly slow out and crowded, soon recovered to race keenly in forward of midfield, 3 wide, 2 lengths back on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Commenced well, raced 3 wide in midfield, there to turn, showed no response in straight, eased final furlong.
Began well, raced prominently, 2 wide, dropped to midfield on turn, showed no response in straight. (Mucus in trachea.) (Lame right front leg with a stiff and restricted action next day.)
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail throughout, never a factor. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began fairly from gate 10, positioned 3 wide behind midfield, similar position on turn, finished off very strongly in straight to score.
Began nicely from gate 1, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, easy run on turn, finished off well to take 2nd, nice debut.
Commenced well, raced 2 wide better than midfield, there to turn, finished off well to take 3rd.
Taken back from gate 11, raced 2 to 3 wide with cover at rear, 6 lengths back, same position on turn, made very good progress in straight to make frame.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced wide with cover at rear, 7 to 8 lengths back, there to turn, made good progress in straight without threatening the first few.
Began well, sent forward to take the lead, led by 1 to 2 lengths on turn, kept on well early in straight, headed near 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 5 to 6 lengths back on turn, made some headway in straight.
Began smartly from gate 13, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, 1 to 2 lengths back on turn, peaked early in straight, kept on evenly to the line.
Got head up on jumping, positioned 4 to 5 lengths back on rail, saved ground on turn, finished off one-paced in straight.
Began fairly, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, finished off one-paced in straight.
Taken back from gate 9, raced 2 wide at rear, 7 lengths back on turn, only showed little response in straight.
Slightly slow out, raced at tail, still 7 to 8 lengths back on turn, showed some response early in straight, checked off heels near 150M, made no progress thereafter.
Jumped with them, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, same position on turn, failed to close off in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped well from the widest draw, raced 3 wide with no cover, 2 to 3 lengths back, still no cover on turn, weakened early in straight. (Rider dropped left rein near 400M.)

Away with them, raced wide with cover at rear, 4 lengths or so back on turn, improved from 400M, finished off very strongly to score.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 4 lengths back on turn, awkwardly placed on heels near 300m, closed off well to take 2nd.
Began well, sent forward to take the 1 out 1 back position, same position on turn, angled out near 400M, kept on well in straight to take a place.
Began only fairly, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 lengths back on turn, made some progress before checked 150M, ran on steadily thereafter.
Bumped start, sent forward to take the shared lead on the outside, there to turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Jumped well from gate 1, sent forward to take the shared lead on the inside, travelled well throughout, peaked early in straight, headed after passing 200M, kept on evenly to the line.
Shifted out at start and bumped, sat 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, easy run to turn, failed to quicken under pressure in straight.
Jumped with them, positioned on rail in midfield, 3 lengths back, angled out near 400M, blocked near 200M, no clear running thereafter, not able to test properly.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, 7 lengths back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Taken back from gate 9, raced 5 lengths or so back on rail, same margin back on turn, showed no response in straight, eased final 100M.
Commenced well, sent forward to race prominently but trapped very wide, slightly taken back to midfield after passing 1500M, still 3 wide with no cover, peaked on turn, emptied early in straight.
Pushed to take rail and lead, clocked fast sectionals, drifted away 300M to score.
Pushed to obtain box seat, ran on well to the line for 2nd.
Pushed forward, sat just off the leader, not suited by the fast sectionals, held ground in straight.
Pushed forward, sat 2 wide, just held ground in straight.
At rear along the fence, benefited by the fast pace, progressed steadily 200M.
Trapped 3 wide in front of midfield, held ground in straight.
Very slow away, at back along the fence, suited by the fast tempo, ran on fairly.
Eased back, trapped 3 wide, favoured by the fast pace, ran on ok.
Eased to sit behind midfield, 2 wide, suited by the fast pace, no dash.
Eased back, took rail, benefited by the fast tempo, no progress.
Failed to muster then took cover at the rear, found nothing in the straight.
Settled in box seat, always niggled, responded solidly in the straight, quickened passing 200M, finished unchallenged.
Raced midfield on rail, at 600M became unbalanced when crowded for room, always niggled, gradually made ground in straight, worked home solidly.
Settled midfield, improved passing 400M, made ground passing 150M, finished nicely.
Ridden along but took some time to muster speed, raced behind midfield, widest on straightening, made up nice late ground.
Travelled in handy position, fought hard in the straight, finished well.
Raced at tail, always niggled, made some ground passing 100M.
Taken back at start, steadied passing 1000M, at 600M was severely checked away from heels, limited response.
Slow out then steadied away from heels, settled at back on rail, one-paced.
After the start lost its left front plate, settled midfield, wide on straightening, limited response.
Ridden along to settle outside the lead, weakened near 150M.
Took lead with nice early speed, faded out passing 200M, failed to make impression.
Raced in handy position, weakened passing 200M, failed to run on.
Commenced very fast and came across to get uncontested lead. Travelled well and kicked clear upon straightening and didn't look like getting run down.

Was bumped on jumping before easing back to near the tail of the field on the outside. Moved three horses wide down the back straight before entering the straight the widest runner and making late ground in run to the line.
Commenced well before positioning behind the leader on the fence. Turned for home close enough but could not match finishing burst of leader.
Positioned worse than midfield on the fence and commenced to race ungenerously from the 600m. Stayed closer to the rail upon straightening and made some late ground in later stages.

Ridden forward to gain prominent position before ultimately settling second, one length behind and outside the leader. Flat footed when leader quickened and conceded 2L upon entering straight and battled away to the line.
Position midfield on the fence and raced a little keenly in early stages. Was held slightly tight upon straightening before getting clear room once balanced and working fairly to the line.
Settled worse than midfield in between runners. Was still conceding big start upon straightening and ran on fairly.
Not fast away but found feet to position one pair back on the outside. Was under pressure before straightening and conceded 4L to leader at top of lane. Didn't catch the eye in the run the post.
Ridden forward from widest barrier before settling three horses wide with cover in middle stages. Ridden hard from 400m to improve but weakened out following wide run in the straight.
Restrained after the start and was eased back across heals to position at the tail of the field. Was over 8 lengths off the lead when cornering and was never a threat in the run home.
Was bumped after the start and subsequently settled at the tail. Was niggled at from the 600m to improve position but was struggling from that point on.

Commenced fast and was ridden forward to be prominent but was caught three horses wide after the 1000m. Covered additional ground in middle stages and was ridden up from the 600m before weakening out in final 250m.
Average to begin, positioned 3 lengths back on rail, saved ground on turn, angled out early in straight, finished off strongly to score.
Commenced well, sent forward to race in 2nd, 2 wide, same position on turn, took the lead early in straight, kept on well thereafter, just couldn't hold off the winner late.
Jumped well from gate 1, sat 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, easy run on turn, finished off evenly.
Began fairly, positioned on rail at rear, 6 to 7 lengths back, same margin back on turn, made good progress in straight to be nearest on line.
Began well, raced 2 wide in midfield, 4 lengths back, there to turn, made minor progress in straight.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide better than midfield, 2 to 3 lengths back on turn, peaked early in straight, ran on one-paced.
Began awkwardly and bumped, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length, travelled well to turn, headed near 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear on rail, 8 lengths back, same margin back on turn, kept to inside after straightening and made minor progress.
Average to begin, taken back to race 2 wide at rear, 7 lengths back, there to turn, failed to close off in straight.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, 8 to 9 lengths back, still well back on turn, failed to make any progress in straight.
Away with them, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 5 lengths or so back, same position on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Slightly slow out and bumped, positioned 5 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, weakened early in straight. (Bled.)
Settled to race in midfield, 3-1/4L behind along the rail, ran on nicely along the rail to score by 3/4L.
In worse than midfield, 4-3/4L behind along the rail, found extra at 150M and finished off strongly to the line.
Rolled forward to race in the box-seat, sat 1-1/2L off, stayed on well to the line to take 3rd.
Awkward start then was crowded, at rear initially then moved after 900M to be prominent but wide, ran on fairly.
Bumped start, was behind midfield, improved to be outside lead by 800M, in touch until passing 100M.
Raced in one-off one-back, shuffled back at 800M, kept on one paced to the line.
In midfield until shuffled one spot back at 800M, 3 wide at turn, continued on one paced.
Taken back, raced at the rear along the rail, switched wide in straight, no progress.
Bumped start, ridden along before taking cover in worse than midfield, 2 wide, didn't make ground.
Rolled forward, trapped wide then improved to sit outside lead at 1200M, no extra at 150M.
Pushed along early, took rail and led from 1200M, run ended passing 200M. Must trial.
Awkward start, settled just in front of midfield, wide and no cover until 700M, never in it.

Settled towards the rear on the rail gaining gradually towards midfield down back straight, commenced move rounding home bend, stuck to inside of the track, quickened well to take command 100 metres out.
Travelled keenly just worse than midfield early stages, carried widest making home turn, ran on well down the centre of the straight and did best work late.
Settled some 2L back on the rail and mainly in 4th in back straight, gained 2nd under pressure on straightening, sustained headway to hold every chance passing the 200 metres but effort short-lived.
Settled in last few, saved ground on inside turning in, ran on along the rail inside the final 200 metres but without threatening.
Ridden positively to take up running over 1200 metres out, held rails run setting a smart pace, unable to sustain effort and faded under pressure inside the final 150 metres.
Settled well behind, saved ground on the rail turning for home, ran on well between runners in straight to be nearest at finish.
Settled in midfield on the rail after beginning from the one draw, saved ground turning for home but found nothing in run to the line.
Broke well, settled in 5th within 3L of pace, swung wide into home straight, headway early on but had to be straightened 250 metres out, unable to sustain effort in closing stages.
Jumped fairly from a wide gate, failed to muster and had to be settled in last few, became last over 400 metres out and only went past well-beaten horses inside the final 100 metres.
Settled in midfield, swung very wide entering home straight, made no impression in the run home.
Ridden positively from a wide gate, settled one back just off the pace, dropped out quickly after straightening.
Pressed forward from a moderate start racing 3-wide without cover in 3rd most of the way to the straight, folded up quickly after straightening. (Lame next day)
Restrained after the jump, settled 3rd last, driven along 400M, hit top gear mid-straight and came through strongly between runners to score.
Inconvenienced at the start, improved to midfield on settling, within striking distance top of straight, fought on well to claim 2nd late but not finishing pace of winner.
Broke well, went forward sharing lead on the inside, held narrow lead on straightening, kept finding under pressure, caught by first 2 late but hung on to 3rd in close finish.
Jumped on terms, chased leaders in 4th, worked home solidly on straightening, battled hard for the lead until swamped near line.
Away well to be tracking leaders in 3rd on settling, had every chance from top of straight, challenged hard for the lead, edged out to 5th late.
Away with them, reined in to be chasing leaders in 5th, driven along 400M, battled away to the line but always held by leaders.
Restless in barriers and consequently slow to begin, ridden along to hold a position behind midfield, chased steadily on straightening, no clear run final 50M behind leaders.
From wide draw crossed to race 2-wide in midfield, kept up the chase on leaders on straightening but unable to pinch much ground.
Bustled along after the jump, shared lead with rival on outside, remained prominent until 200M, no extra towards the finish.
Bumped rival after the jump and stumbled, raced near the rear, 8Ls to make up 400M, ran on only fairly, never threatened.
Steadied after the jump, settled down behind midfield 6-7Ls off the pace, on straightening didn't run on. No impression.
Dropped back to a position near the rear, came under pressure 600M, soon driven along but didn't respond.

Shifted out on jumping and bumped, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well throughout, kept on strongly to the line and scored.
Began awkwardly, raced nearer to the middle of the track, 4 to 5 lengths back, improved from 400M, finished off strongly to take 2nd.
Average to begin, sent forward to race prominently close to the stands rail, kept on evenly to the line.
Jumped with them, raced in midfield closer to the middle of the track, made some progress final 300M to make frame.
Slowly away, raced at rear on rail, 5 to 6 lengths back, gradually taken to centre track after passing 400M and made some progress to be nearest on line.
Began fairly, raced behind midfield closer to the middle of the track, 4 lengths back, showed some response after passing 400M, peaked 100M, kept on evenly thereafter.
Moderately away, sat 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader close to the stands rail, peaked on run near 300M, ran on evenly to the line.
Moderately away, raced closer to the middle track, 2 lengths or so back, peaked shortly after passing 400M, weakened gradually thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Average to begin, raced at rear nearer to the middle of the track, made minor progress before inconvenienced near 100M, ran on one-paced thereafter.
Clean jump, raced 3 to 4 lengths back on the stands rail, made minor progress before steadied near 200M, ran on one-paced thereafter.
Bumped start, raced behind midfield, 2 away from the stands rail, peaked near 500M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Began very awkwardly and bumped, raced at rear near to the stands rail, made no impression final 400M.
Bumped on jumping, positioned on the stands rail in midfield, 3 lengths back, weakened after passing 400M, eased thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped well from gate 1, sent forward to race prominently closer to the middle of the track, hard ridden after passing 500M but showed no response, weakened gradually thereafter, eased final 100M.
Hard ridden to take rail and led at fast sectionals, made all.
3 back on the fence, progressed steadily 300M for 2nd.
Pushed to occupy box seat, not suited by the fast sectionals, held ground for 3rd.
Very slow away, at back along the fence, benefited by the fast tempo, made steady ground 300M.
At rear, 2-3 wide, suited by the fast pace, progressed steadily 250M.
Eased back, 2-3 wide, favoured by the fast pace, made ground 300M.
Eased to sit in front of midfield, 2 wide, lack turn of foot.
Hard ridden forward, sat outside the leader, not suited by the fast tempo, emptied 300M.
Hard ridden forward, sat 2 wide, harmed by the fast pace, out of fuel 300M.
Trapped wide at back, never a factor.
Eased back, never a factor.
Never competitive.
Hard ridden to keep up in midfield, trapped 3 wide, emptied 500M.
Hard ridden early, trapped 3-4 wide, never better than midfield.
Taken back at start, Settled behind midfield, improved passing 400M, made good late ground to score.
Raced in handy position, responded solidly when asked for effort, finished solidly.
Ridden along to take lead on outside rail, lay out in the early and middle stages, fought well in the final stages, worked home solidly.
Settled behind leaders, always niggled, made up some nice late ground.
Hard ridden after start, settled inside the lead, gave some ground passing 150M.
Raced at back on outside rail, made limited ground passing 200M.
Raced midfield, one-paced when asked for effort.
Settled at back, no response when placed pressure.
Settled midfield in middle of track, weakened noticeably passing 200M, failed to make impression.
Travelled at back, never in it.
Commenced well from wide barrier before coming across to assume lead. Went very slow in front during middle sections before kicking clear on straightening on holding on easily.

Sent forward from wide draw and after being three wide in early section positioned outside leader from 1000m. Travelled comfortably, three quarters length off lead on cornering and tried hard but couldn't real in leader.
Commenced well before easing into third position on leaders back. Had clear running on straightening but could not sprint but instead ground to the line.
Started well before position one pair behind leaders on the outside. Maintained position upon entering the straight and battled hard but no match for first two.

Crowded on jumping before being eased back across to the fence after 200m. Worse than midfield and keen in middle sections due to slow pace. Stayed close to fence in straight & made some late ground in leader dominated race.

Allowed to find feet in first 300m before positioning midfield between runners around 4.5L off lead. Was ridden up prior to cornering to improve and did give short sprint before shifting around and tiring in last 200m.

Was bumped heavily shortly after the start before positioning worse than midfield around 6L off slow speed. Ridden up when speed quickened upon straightening but was always too far back to be a threat.
Commenced well before coming across to position two pairs back on the fence. Travelled well and wasn't far away from lead before straightening but weakened out in final section.

Was back and cross shortly after the start to position third last on the outside. Improved out wider on the track upon straightening but was always well back in the run and was not suited to slow mid race tempo.
Not fast away and eased back and across to the fence within first 100m. Was a clear last upon straightening before pulling wider on the track and attempting to improve position.

Ridden forward for first 300m but could not get cover and was posted three horses wide in middle sections. Improved slightly approaching 600m however came under pressure shortly after and weakened out in the straight.

Not fast away and was given a few reminders early before settling last. Pulled out wider from the 550m at the same time the speed increased and subsequently entered straight the widest runner but in second last position.

Commenced well before eased back after 150m, positioning slightly worse than midfield and three horses wide. Was around 4.5 lengths off lead and three wide with cover at 600m but couldn't quicken from that point on.

Slow away but gathered speed quickly to rail up to midfield position after 200m. Was keen in middle stages and improved close to heels near 600m. Was ridden up when sprint went on upon straightening but weakened late.
Commenced well, raced 2 wide in midfield, wider after passing 700M, improved from 550M, took the lead early in straight, kept on very well to score with still plenty gas in tank.
Shifted out on jumping and bumped, raced 2 wide behind midfield, carried wider on turn, finished off well to take 2nd without threatening the winner.
Began fairly, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, no daylight early in straight, made some progress when clear thereafter to take 3rd without threatening.
Fast into stride, sent forward to race in 2nd, 2 wide, half length behind the leader on turn, peaked early in straight, bumped near 100M, kept on evenly to the line.
Jumped well, raced 2 wide better than midfield, a length or so back on turn, finished off evenly in straight, bumped near 100M.
Moderately away, sat 1-1/2L behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, no clear running early in straight, finished off evenly when clear thereafter.
Slowly away, raced at rear on rail, 6 lengths back, moved closer on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Bumped start, positioned on rail behind midfield, 4 lengths or so back, 2 wide from near 700M, slightly improved on turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Began smartly, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, led by 1/2L, peaked and headed early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Taken back from gate 9, raced at tail, 7 lengths back, travelled keenly near 750M, taken very wide turning in, weakened early in straight.
Bumped start and unbalanced, raced 2 wide at rear, 5 lengths back on turn, showed no response in straight, eased final 200M.

Jumped with them, raced 3 wide in midfield, came under pressure and lost position home turn, showed nothing in straight, eased after passing 300M. (Irregular heart rhythm.) (Lame right front leg next day.)
Bumped on jumping, raced 3 wide better than midfield, steadied off heels near 1100M, no cover throughout, emptied early in straight and eased.
Sent forward to take the rail, led all the way to the line and scored by 3/4L.
Crowded start, then raced at the rear, 6L behind along the rail, made nice ground and closed off strongly.
Settled to race outside the lead, maintained 1L margin behind the winner all the way to the line.
Raced just in front of midfield, 3L behind along the rail, slightly held up early in straight before finishing off well.
Asked a little to take up box-seat, sat 1-1/2L off, ran on okay despite laying out in straight.
Jumped in at start, settled to race in midfield, wide but with cover, continued on fairly to the line.
Feet off at start and lost ground, recovered to be in behind midfield along the rail, ran on one paced.
Travelled in worse than midfield, 5L behind 2 wide, closed off okay inside final 150M.
Bumped start then taken back, at rear 2 wide, improved slightly only but ran on.
Pushed then travelled in front of midfield, trapped wide and without cover, found no extra passing 150M.
Urged along and raced in one-off one-back, faded gradually in the straight.
Jumped awkwardly, settled in midfield, 2 wide, asked at 600M, lost ground in the straight.
Raced towards the tail, 3 wide but with cover, did not improve and eased down near 150M.
Bumped start then taken back, wide and without cover, never a factor.
Broke well settling wide in midfield in 6th, gained slightly closer to 5th 3-wide rounding home bend, sustained effort in straight to just get up on line.

Jumped fairly, improved gradually along the rail to midfield some 4L back approaching home bend, baulked for a run early in straight, quickened well inside the final 250 metres to just fail to get up on line.
Settled in rear after beginning from a wide gate, pulled his way forward to midfield in 7th passing the 1200 metres, ran on under pressure early in straight.
Jumped well from a wide gate but soon taken back, remained in last few to the straight, ran on steadily but inconvenienced 50 metres out.

Taken back from the widest gate travelling wide in the rear, crossed to the rail approaching home bend, tight run early in home straight before making modest progress between runners without threatening.
Moderate start from a wide gate, settled wide in just worse than midfield, remained similar turning in, ran home one-paced.
Ridden to lead, obtained rails run 1200 metres out setting a steady pace, led until headed under pressure over 100 metres out.

Ridden along early in midfield dropping further back after the first 400 metres, in last few rounding home bend and into the straight, crowded for room over 200 metres out, produced some late impression.
Soon improved to first few settling in 4th about 3L off the pace, came closer turning into the straight, kept on before fading inside the final 200 metres. (Questioned for disappointing performance)
Settled in last few on the rail, kept on without quickening early in straight, inconvenienced 100 metres out.
Shared early pace, taken one back on the rail over 1200 metres out, faded under pressure soon after straightening. (Tactic questioned) (Lame next day)
Ridden prominently before settling 2-wide just over 1L back, folded up quickly shortly after straightening.
Driven forward becoming leader from 1000M, set slow pace in front, ridden and kicked on well on straightening, did enough to hold off runner up final stages.
Tracked leaders on the inside, responded well on straightening and chased winner but always held.
Restrained in midfield but no closer than 3-wide throughout, tried hard in straight, stayed on into 3rd 100M but couldn't reel in first pair.
Steadied after the start and shifted across behind runners, in 10th spot turning for home, switched wide 350M, kept grinding on to go 4th near line.
Held up midfield, ran on mildly when asked from top of straight, couldn't get closer to leaders.
Slow to begin, raced in the rear 6-7Ls off the slow pace, made some ground over final 300M but never close enough to challenge.
Settled down 3-wide behind midfield, driven 400M but failed to make appreciable ground, no impression.
Went forward and pressed leader on outside, challenged hard for the lead on straightening but peaked on its run 150M, weakened rapidly towards the line.
Crowded for room on jumping, recovered to race in midfield along the rail, ran on one-paced in straight and failed to look a winning chance.
From widest draw dropped back to race near the rear, widest into straight, passed a few tired runners late, no impression on leaders.
Close up behind leaders, failed to respond to riding on straightening, eased when no chance late stages. (Jockey: may not have handled the yielding track conditions.)
Chased leaders in a 3-wide spot without cover, weakened mid-straight, eased when well beaten final 100M.
Moderately away from a wide draw, raced wide with cover in midfield, slightly improved on turn, finished the race well to score.
Began smartly from the widest draw, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, kicked clear early in straight, kept on well but unable to hold off the winner late.
Jumped well, raced in midfield on the inside, angled out after passing 500M, made very good progress in straight to take place, nearest on line.
Away with them, raced wide with cover behind midfield, moved closer on turn, finished off well in straight to make frame.
Bumped start, raced prominently but wide, no cover after passing 1100M, 2nd on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Jumped with field, raced at rear, 6 to 7 lengths back, angled out after passing 650M, made some headway in straight without threatening.
Began fairly, settled better than midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, no clear running early in straight, made no progress when clear thereafter.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide better than midfield, 3 lengths or so back on turn, failed to make any progress in straight.
Began well, raced prominently on rail, made contact with the riderless horse near 1100M, a length or so back on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Average to begin, raced at tail, 10 lengths back, moved closer along the rail on turn, angled out from 500M, weakened early in straight. (Jockey stated didn't handle track.)
Bumped on jumping, raced 2 wide at rear, 7 to 8 lengths back, carried wider on turn, weakened early in straight.
Commenced well, sent forward to race prominently, carried wider near 1100M, 2 wide on turn, weakened early in straight.
Taken back from gate 9, raced at rear, 8 to 9 lengths back, very wide turning in, emptied early in straight, finished tailed out.

Placing: UR
Comment: Stumbled at start and rider being dislodged.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 7 lengths back at rear, same margin back on turn, finished off very strongly in straight to score by a neck.

Jumped well from a wide draw, unable to slot in, raced 4W better than midfield, no cover throughout, showed very good response early in straight, took the lead after passing 200M, kept on well, just couldn't hold off the winner late.
Began well, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, easy run on turn, angled out early in straight, finished off evenly to take 3rd.
Moderately away from the widest draw, sent forward to race prominently but wide, shared lead on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed after passing 200M, ran on evenly to the line.
Average to begin, raced wide with cover behind midfield, crowded near 1200M, 6 lengths back on turn, made some headway in straight without threatening.
Commenced well, sent forward to take the lead, shared lead with rival on turn, peaked early in straight, headed near 250M, weakened thereafter.
Shifted in at start and bumped, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, allowed rival to cross near 900M, 2 lengths back on turn, failed to quicken in straight.
Began fairly, showed no early speed, raced at rear on rail, still well back on turn, failed to quicken in straight. (Jockey stated didn't handle track.)
Hampered start, raced at rear, 6 lengths back, same margin back on turn, awkwardly placed near 500M, failed to close off in straight. (Lame right front leg next day.)
Jumped with them, raced 2 to 3 wide better than midfield, got no cover on turn, weakened early in straight.
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, there to turn, showed nothing in straight.
Bumped shortly after start, raced 2 wide in midfield, peaked on turn, weakened early in straight, eased final furlong.
Jumped well, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, same position on turn, showed no response early in straight, eased after passing 300M. (Bled.)
