Shifted out at start and bumped, raced prominently on rail, shared lead on turn, kept on very well in straight despite being bumped near 200M, scored by a neck.

Bumped shortly after start, raced 4 lengths back on rail, saved ground on turn, stayed on fence after straightening, blocked for run near 100M, angled out thereafter and finished off strongly to take 2nd.
Commenced well, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, improved from 400M, made very good progress in straight to take 3rd, nearest on line.
Began fairly from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, kept on well in straight to make frame.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, finished off well in straight.
Bumped start, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, shared lead on turn, kept on well early in straight, bumped near 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, 6 lengths back, same margin back on turn, made some progress early in straight, blocked near 150M, finished off well when clear thereafter.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide, 4 lengths or so back, awkwardly placed near 400M, made minor progress in straight.
Clean jump from a middle draw, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, 5 lengths back on turn, failed to quicken in straight.
Bumped start and unbalanced, raced 4 wide 3 to 4 lengths back, peaked on turn, ran home one-paced.

Jumped well from gate 11, raced prominently but trapped 4 wide, awkwardly placed shortly after entering the back straight, 2 lengths or so back thereafter, peaked early in straight, gradually dropped away.
Made contact on jumping, sent forward to race prominently but trapped 3 wide, slightly taken back after passing 800M, still no cover on turn, emptied early in straight.
Eased to sit in midfield, 2-3 wide, benefited by the fast tempo, progressed steadily 300M to score.
Pushed to obtain box seat, harmed by the fast pace, closed off strongly for 2nd.
Hard ridden to take rail and lead, clocked fast sectionals, made early move 600M, hung on until 100M overhauled, ran on for 3rd.
Eased back, benefited by the fast tempo, progressed steadily 300M.
Awkward away, behind midfield, 2-3 wide, suited by the fast pace, made some ground 200M.
Eased at start, took rail at rear, benefited by the fast tempo, made steady ground 200M.
At back, 2-4 wide, suited by the fast pace, ran on ok.
Pushed to hold the rail in front of midfield, emptied in straight.
Pushed forward, sat 2 wide, not suited by the fast sectionals, weakened in straight.
Eased back, benefited by the fast pace, no progress.
At back, suited by the fast pace tempo, never improved.
Pushed forward, harmed by the fast pace, dropped off quickly 400M.
Settled behind midfield, improved passing 450M, quickened passing 100M, finished strongly to score.
Raced in box seat, asked for effort near 300M, responded nicely, worked home solidly.
Travelled at back, widest on straightening, made up some nice late ground.
Taken back at start, kept close to rail rounding home turn to save ground, responded nicely in the straight.
Settled midfield, near 450M was checked away from heels, gradually made ground in the straight.
Slow out, settled at back on rail, made ground after commencing to improve near 400M, finished OK.
Ridden along to take lead, tried to improve passing 400M, gave ground passing 200M, failed to make impression.
Crowded after start, travelled wide and without cover in midfield, lost left hind plate rounding Home Turn, wide on straightening, weakened badly passing 200M, failed to run on.
Urged to race outside the lead, gave ground abruptly near 450M, rider and trainer questioned, lame left front next day, must trial.
Commenced fast from wide barrier and ridden forward. Was 3 wide for first 500m before getting outside leader at 700m. Gave a strong kick after straightening to score well.

Began well and positioned midfield before racing keenly and travelling 3 wide from 750m. Hung out and was awkward from the 600m until straightening. Entered straight 2 lengths from lead and fought hard to the line.
Was one of the slowest into stride before coming across to near the rear off the fence. Ridden hard from 400m when still 6 lengths off lead and closed off well down the center of the track.
Began well and was outside leader until being crossed at 700m. Travelled well behind leading pair and entered straight 1.5 lengths from lead. Battled away in straight.
Was one of the last away before being eased back and across behind runners to settle near the tail on the fence. Turned for home last of all and made some ground in the sprint to the line.

Began well before positioning on leaders back after start. Drifted a further pair back after 600m before entering the straight on the fence 3 lengths of lead. Stayed close to the fence in the straight but never a threat.
Began fairly before position midfield on the fence. Travelled comfortably but was conceding six lengths on straightening and never threatened in the straight.
Showed very good early speed to come across and assume lead. Travelled well but was headed in early stages of straight before weakening out.

Allowed to find feet after the start before settling midfield on outside. Commenced to race keenly down at midway and was pulled 3 horses wide as a result. Continued to travel wide upon cornering and weakened out last 300m.
Taken back to last after 200m. Conceded around 8 lengths to leaders on straightening and didn't really threaten in the straight.
Didn't show any early speed before settling worse than midfield on the fence. Was well back on straightening and didn't get the most room in the straight but still not a genuine threat.
Was ridden fairly prominently in early stages before settling two pairs back in midfield. Was 3.5 lengths off lead upon cornering before weakening out in the straight.
Average to begin, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground throughout, finished off strongly to score.
Bumped start and unbalanced, raced 2 wide at rear, 6 to 7 lengths back, there to turn, closed off well to take 2nd.
Moderately away, positioned 2 wide, 4 lengths or so back, 3 wide after entering the back straight, same margin back on turn, made some headway in straight to take a place, no threat to the first two.
Began well, sat 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, there to turn, 2 wide from 400M, kept on evenly in straight.
Began very awkwardly and bumped, raced 2 wide, 2 to 3 lengths back, there to turn, angled out near 450M, failed to quicken under pressure in straight.

Began awkwardly, raced 2W behind midfield, moved a bit closer after 1600M, sat 3W in midfield, sent forward after entering the back straight, took the lead 600M, led by 2Ls turning in, headed 200M, weakened thereafter.
Average to begin, positioned on rail behind midfield, 5 lengths back on turn, peaked early in straight, ran on one-paced to the line.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, 7 to 8 lengths back on turn, failed to make any progress in straight.
Bumped shortly after start, raced 3 wide with no cover in midfield early, gradually moved forward after passing 1600M, 2 wide in 2nd from 1200M, weakened on turn, emptied early in straight.

Commenced well, raced in 2nd, 2 wide in the early stages, allowed rival to cross near 1250M, positioned 2 to 3 lengths back in the middle stages, no cover on turn, emptied early in straight, finished tailed out.

Began well from gate 1, sent forward to take the lead, travelled comfortably in the middle stages, headed near 600M, weakened on turn, emptied early in straight, finished tailed out. (Lame right front leg next day.)
Slow to jump, recovered to be in midfield, 4-1/2L behind along the rail, closed off nicely from 100M to score.
Sat in just behind midfield, 5-1/4L behind 2 wide, kept on well to the finish to take 2nd.
Sent forward and raced outside the lead, battled on until headed by the first two inside approaching final 50M.
Pushed forward and settled to race in box-seat, sat 1-1/4L off, maintained nice run to the finish.
Raced just in front of midfield, 2-3/4L behind along the rail, ran on to the line fairly.
Urged forward to take rail and led, kept on until emptied and headed passing 100M.
Found cover in worse than midfield, 6L behind 2 wide, made ground and soldiered on.
Taken back and raced at the rear, 7L behind 2 wide, made nice ground and stayed on well to the line.
Pushed, settled in one-off one-back, about 2L off, in touch until 100M.
Bumped start, sat in front of midfield 2 wide, travelled keenly, emptied at 150M.
Slow to jump then raced in worse than midfield, along the rail, made no ground but ran on.
Stumbled badly at start and lost ground, remained at rear and finished tailed out. Must trial.
Pressed forward to soon join the leader, disputed lead into the straight, asserted authority inside the 200 metres.
Jumped awkwardly losing ground, soon recovered to midfield, came to challenge 4-wide upon straightening, ran on to be nearest at finish.
Began well, travelled wide without cover prominently in 3rd, remained in same position turning for home, kept on steadily without threatening.
Jumped fairly from the one draw, amongst the leaders early before shifting one back just off the pace, angled out for a run 250 metres out but failed to quicken to threaten.
Soon taken back from a wide gate travelling worse than midfield, soon came to challenge after straightening, ran on to be nearest at finish.
Ridden forward from a moderate start, gained narrow advantage on the rail approaching the Rock, led until finding no extra over 200 metres out.
Moderate start, trailed the field to the straight, saved ground turning for home, produced good late impression.
Ridden early in close up position, gradually lost touch after straightening.
Broke well but soon taken back just worse than midfield on the rail, gained closer while keen around the Rock, saved ground turning in, ran home one-paced. (Lame next day)
Jumped fairly, settled in midfield, wide into home straight, made no impression
Travelled wide in last few after beginning from the widest gate, never a factor.
Settled in 4th, stayed in touch all the way, driven to lead 100M, forged clear for a good win.
Away well, tracked leaders in 3rd, moved up to take lead passing 200M, couldn't hold off winner final stages.
Jumped only fairy, settled in midfield along the rail, kept on soundly on straightening to take 3rd.
In touch in midfield, ridden 2f out, headway approaching final furlong, chased solidly over final 250M, just missed 3rd in photo.
Held up in midfield, 5Ls off the pace at 400M, stayed on mildly to the finish.
From draw 12 used early to obtain the lead, set fast pace early and middle stages, tired passing 200M, weakened towards the line.
Slow to begin, held up in last 10Ls back, made some progress on straightening but from too far back.
Settled worse than midfield, couldn't pick up passing 400M when the pressure went on, no threat to leaders.
Taken across behind runners, held up behind midfield 6Ls off the pace, made steady progress up the rail on straightening, not clear run behind weakening rival passing 150M, might have been closer.
Up with the fast early pace, tracked leader into the straight, every chance and kept going until no extra 150M.
Taken across behind runners, settled 2nd last, never ran on, eased final stages.
In midfield position 3-wide without cover, under pressure middle stages and dropped towards rear home turn, soon beaten.

Bumped start and unbalanced, sent forward to took the lead, headed after passing 950M but retook the lead 700M, kicked clear after turning in, kept on very well to score.
Bumped shortly after start, raced 3 wide with no cover in midfield, moved a bit closer after passing 1000M but still 3 wide, hard ridden from 600M, kept on well in straight to take 2nd.
Began very awkwardly and bumped, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, crossed by rival near 900M, 3 wide turning in, kept on well in straight to take a place, just missed 2nd.
Moderately away from gate 1, sat 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground to turn, peaked early in straight, kept on evenly to the line.
Average to begin, raced at tail early, 6 lengths or so back, improved after entering the back straight, took the lead 900M, headed near 700M, peaked on turn, one-paced in straight.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 5 lengths or so back on turn, finished off one-paced in straight.
Began only fairly, positioned on rail, 4 lengths or so back, angled out from 600M, failed to make any progress in straight.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide better than midfield, hard ridden from 800M, peaked on turn, made no progress in straight.
Bumped shortly after start, raced at rear throughout, never a factor. (Blood in trachea.)
Hard ridden to take rail and led at slow sectionals, drifted away 300M to score.
Pushed to occupy box seat, benefited by the slow tempo, just held ground for 2nd.
Very slow away, midfield along the fence, harmed by the slow tempo, dashed strongly 250M for 3rd.
Eased back, 2-3 wide, dashed strongly 300M despite not suited by the slow pace.
Hard ridden to hold the rail in front of midfield, no dash.
Hard ridden forward, parked outside the leader, benefited by the slow tempo, weakened 150M.
Eased at start, took rail, harmed by the slow pace, ran on fairly.
Very slow away, pushed forward, sat 2 wide, soon emptied 300M.
Eased at start, 2 wide, not suited by the slow tempo, never improved.
Never better than midfield.
Very slow away, never competitive.
Urged to take lead, improved on straightening, responded solidly, scored unchallenged.
Raced outside the lead, asked for effort near 600M, worked home solidly in the straight.
Raced in box seat, shifted out to improve rounding Home Turn, made ground in the straight, worked home nicely.
Slow out, settled midfield on rail, gradually made ground in the straight, finished well.
Travelled wide and without cover until near 900M, raced in front of midfield, commenced to improve passing 600M, one-paced.
Raced behind midfield, fought hard but only one-paced.
Ridden along but fail to muster speed, raced at tail on rail, tried hard but only limited response.
Taken back at start, settled behind midfield, limited response in the straight.
Settled midfield, gave some ground passing 700M, no response in the straight.
Always back, widest on straightening, never in it.

Commenced well and ridden forward before positioning on the outside one pair behind lead. Travelled well and was within 2 lengths on cornering before striking lead halfway down straight and going on to win.

Was the slowest into stride and despite being hard ridden early settled near the tail. Moved away from the rail before straightening but still conceded six lengths to leader at 400m. Made good late ground out wider on track.

Hard ridden for first 150m before settling midfield off the fence, 3.5 lengths from lead. Stayed closer to the rail on cornering before coming around heels at 300m to close in 2.25 lengths on the line.
Away fairly and ridden across before positioning around midfield off the fence conceding 5 lengths at 800m. Moved out 3 wide upon cornering and made some late ground once balanced.

Had no early speed despite being ridden along before positioning at the tail three horses wide. Improved around runners from the 800m before entering the straight the widest runner and still 5L from lead. Made some late ground.

Wasn't the quickest away and was ridden up for first 300m to hold place, ultimately positioning worse than midfield conceding around 7L at 800m. Never travelled strongly and was conceding large margin before making good late ground.
Ridden hard from wide barrier before shifting across to position outside leader at 900m. Hit the lead at 275m but was passed shortly after and tired out over last 200m.

Fairly away and was ridden for pace before being crossed by rivals and ultimately getting leaders back after 200m. Was close enough on straightening and didn't get a lot of room from 300m but did fade out of contention last 250m.

Only moderately away but ridden hard until improving position to be three horses wide 3 lengths from lead. Continued to race wide before coming under pressure on straightening before weakening out last 250m.

Did not have early speed of rivals and as a result positioned worse than midfield on the fence, conceding 7L at the 750m. Moved away from the rail at 450m but did not improve strongly enough after straightening to be a threat.

Allowed to find feet after the start and was eased back after 150m to be closer to the tail. Lost a further length at the 600m and was a clear last upon cornering and was always well back in the run to the line.
Ridden hard from the start to obtain the lead and shifted across to the rail after 200m. Held lead until 275m but then weakened out badly from that point.
Began well, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, kicked clear early in straight, held rivals comfortably to score in good style.
Bumped on jumping, raced 2 wide in midfield, 5 lengths back on turn, made good progress in straight to take 2nd without threatening the winner.
Jumped well, positioned 2 to 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, kept on evenly to the line.
Commenced well from gate 11, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, challenged the leader on turn, peaked early in straight, kept on evenly to the line, just stayed on for 4th.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, wider on turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Began only fairly, raced 2 wide at rear, 8 lengths back on turn, bumped early in straight, made some progress last 300M but never really threatened.
Began fairly from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Began awkwardly, raced at rear on rail, angled out after passing 600M, 8 lengths back turning in, bumped early in straight, finished off evenly. (Irregular heart rhythm.)
Jumped well, positioned 2 wide behind midfield, found rail near 700M, saved ground on turn, failed to quicken in straight.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide better than midfield, peaked on turn, weakened gradually in straight.
Turned its head to the left when the gates opened, left a long way behind, never recovered. (See Racing Incidents.)
Bumped on jumping, unable to slot in, raced 3 wide and without cover in midfield, peaked on turn, weakened early in straight.
Raced in front of midfield, stand side, shifted out to get run near 300M, finished gamely thereafter to score.
In front of midfield, stand side, led and made a spirited run from 250M till 50M, only headed by the winner.
Niggled along and sat behind the lead, stand side, weakened at 100M but battled on to hold onto 3rd.
Sat towards the rear, stand side initially, commenced good run home from 250M on centre track.
Travelled in about midfield, stand side, shifted to centre track from 400M, kept on to the line.
Raced towards the rear, stand side, ran on steadily on centre track from 500M.
Sat in just behind midfield, stand side till shifted centre track at 400M, improved slightly but emptied at 200M.
In about midfield, along the outside rail, remained one paced to the line.
Slow to jump and remained at rear, on centre track, only past beaten runners.
Raced in worse than midfield, on centre track, slight dash but ran on till about 100M only.
Began only fairly, ridden to be behind the lead, stand side, run ended after the 250M.
Sent forward to take the outside rail, led until weakened badly near 250M. Bled.
Crowded at start, improved steadily to take up running passing the 800 metres, drew clear closing stages.
Soon took up running, led the field until narrowly headed passing the 800 metres, fought on nicely to maintain clear 2nd.
Broke well from a wide gate, settled in 3rd some 2L back over 800 metres out, in similar position turning for home, ran home one-paced under pressure.
Settled in midfield, fought on steadily without threatening. (Lame next day)
Settled in last few from a wide gate, ran on steadily to be nearest at finish.
Prominent in 3rd on the rail early, became 4th in a similar position after first 200 metres, ran home one-paced.
Awkward start, travelled wide without cover in midfield, fought on under pressure without threatening.
Taken back from a wide gate, tailed-off in back straight, produced good late impression closing stages.
Recovered quickly from a moderate start to just worse than midfield on the rail, saved ground turning for home, made no impression in the run home.
Moderate start from a wide gate, travelled towards the rear, never seen with a chance. (Lame next day)
Taken back from the widest gate, never seen with a chance.

Placing: FE
Comment: Crowded and lost rider after first 100 metres.
Began awkwardly, held up near last 5-6Ls off the pace, let down strongly from 300M, led 100M out and gave a kick to beat off runner up.
Restrained in midfield 3-4Ls off the pace, made good progress down outside passing 400M, loomed a strong chance mid-straight, lay in final 200M and outsprinted by winner late stages.
Held up in midfield, driven along 500M to chase leaders, kept on well to the line but not pace of first 2 late stages.
Settled near last, on straightening chased solidly, just missed 3rd.
Crowded for room after the jump, shifted across behind runners for cover, last of 11 and widest on straightening, stayed on well to be nearest at the finish.
From draw 1 went forward sharing the lead along the fence, kicked on well early straight, caught near 100M, weakened.
Tracked leaders on settling, battled on same pace early straight, weakened final 150M.
Caught wide towards rear of midfield, couldn't get much closer when driven out leaving the turn. No impression.
Up with early pace, eased off to track leaders from 1200M along the rail, raced keenly middle stages, driven out 400M but couldn't muster the speed to be closer, faded mid-straight.
From draw 10 made some early use to go forward, raced outside leader from 1100M, tired passing 250M, faded away. (Jockey : travelled too keenly and not able to finish off.)
Held up in midfield along the 3-path, couldn't go on passing 500M, soon left behind on straightening, eased.
Slightly slow out, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, awkwardly placed on heels near 700M, easy run on turn, finished off strongly to score.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 5 to 6 lengths back at rear, checked off heels near 700M, same margin back on turn, made very good progress in straight to take 2nd without threatening the winner.
Began fairly, raced 2 wide, 1 to 2 lengths back, similar position on turn, made some progress in straight to take a place.
Began awkwardly, raced prominently but trapped wide early, slightly taken back near 900M, 3 lengths back on turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Jumped well, sent forward to take the lead, shared the lead with rival on turn, headed near 250M, kept on evenly to the line.
Slowly away, raced in midfield on the inside, checked near 700M, 5 lengths or so back on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Away with them, raced prominently but trapped wide early, slightly taken back after passing 1000M, 3 to 4 lengths back on rail turning, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Fast into stride, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, shared lead on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Taken back to race at rear, 8 lengths back on turn, made some headway in straight before run closed, not ridden out late. (See Racing Incidents.) (Lame left front leg next day.)
Bumped start, raced prominently but trapped very wide, 3 wide in midfield on turn, peaked early in straight, kept on one-paced to the line. (Lame right front leg.)
Bumped on jumping, showed no early speed, raced 2 to 3 wide with cover behind midfield, 7 lengths back on turn, failed to make any progress in straight.
Slowly away, raced at tail throughout, never competitive.

Commenced well from gate 1, positioned 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, no daylight early in straight, finished off well when clear after passing 300M, scored by a head.
Jumped well, positioned 2 wide better than midfield, 2 lengths or so back on turn, hit the front near 300M, kept on very well to the line, just couldn't hold off the winner late.
Slightly slow out, raced 3 wide with no cover better than midfield, slightly taken back after passing 1100M, 2 wide on turn, finished off well to take a place.
Slowly away, recovered to race on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, no clear running early in straight, closed off well when clear thereafter to make frame.
Slightly slow out, showed no early speed, raced at rear on rail, gradually moved closer along the rail on turn, made good progress in straight to be nearest on line.
Out in line, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 6 to 7 lengths back on turn, made good progress in straight to be nearest on line.
Began awkwardly, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, peaked early in straight, headed near 250M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Began well from a wide draw, sent forward to race prominently but wide, 2nd on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Began fairly, raced 2 wide in midfield, checked off heels near 900M, 4 lengths or so back on turn, failed to quicken after straightening, weakened gradually after passing 200M.
Crowded out start, raced at rear, 8 to 9 lengths back, there to turn, failed to close off in straight.
Began fairly from the widest draw, raced 3 wide at rear early, travelled keenly after 1100M, 7 to 8 lengths back on rail turning, finished off one-paced in straight.
Average to begin, raced 3 wide in midfield, travelled keenly after passing 1100M, 5 to 6 lengths back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Bumped start and unbalanced, raced 3 to 4 wide behind midfield in the early stages, awkwardly placed near 900M, 3 wide turning, weakened early in straight.
Jumped with them, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, 8 to 9 lengths back, failed to close off in straight.

Jumped well, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 5 lengths back, same margin back on turn, no daylight early in straight, angled out near 250M, finished off strongly to score.
Away with them, raced 2 wide, 3 to 4 lengths back, there to turn, closed off well to take 2nd.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide at rear, 6 to 7 lengths back, similar position on turn, blocked early in straight, finished off well when clear thereafter.
Bumped on jumping, positioned on rail in midfield, 4 lengths back, same margin back on turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Shifted out at start and bumped, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, 5 lengths back on turn, finished off evenly in straight.

Taken back from gate 10, raced at rear, 6 to 7 lengths back, similar position on turn, blocked near 250M, shifted in thereafter and made some progress before racing tight final stages and not ridden out.

Began well, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, led by 2 lengths at 400M, kept on well early in straight, headed near 100M then raced tight shortly thereafter, not able to be ridden out near the finish.
Bumped shortly after start, raced 2 wide better than midfield, 3 wide on turn, made some headway early in straight, crowded near 150M, weakened thereafter.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear, 3 to 4 wide on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Bumped shortly after start, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, peaked on turn, bumped early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Moderately away from gate 1, sat 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, easy run on turn, weakened early in straight. (Bled.)
Jumped well from a tricky gate, raced 3 wide better than midfield, no cover throughout, weakened on turn, eased early in straight.
Pushed to take rail and led at advantageous slow sectionals, made all.
Pressed forward, sat 2 wide, favoured by the slow tempo, ran on well for 2nd.
Midfield, 2 wide, not suited by the slow pace, lack room 4-2, dashed strongly when clear.
Settled in front of midfield, 2-3 wide, ran on strongly until 100M run ended.
Box seat, benefited by the slow tempo, just held ground in straight.
At back, 2 wide, harmed by the slow pace, lack room 4-2, unleashed strong finishing efforts when clear.
Eased to sit in midfield, trapped 3 wide, harmed by the slow tempo, little dash 250M.
Eased back, trapped 3 wide, dashed well 200M despite not suited by the slow pace.
Behind midfield along the fence, not suited by the slow pace, dashed fairly.
Eased back, took rail, harmed by the slow pace, dashed fairly.
Eased at start, 2-3 wide, not suited by the slow tempo, little dash 200M.
Eased back, trapped 3-4 wide throughout, harmed by the slow pace, no progress.
Taken back at start, improved near 400M, widest on straightening, quickened strongly passing 200M to score.
Ridden along then steadied to sit in box seat, fought nicely in the straight, finished solidly, missed by SH.
Settled midfield on rail, responded nicely in the straight, gained ground passing 150M.
Raced midfield, asked for effort passing 400M, battled well in the straight, finished nicely.
Settled in front of midfield, made ground passing 150M, worked home well.
Jumped nicely, raced in front of midfield on rail, fought well in the straight.
Very slow out, raced at back, wide on straightening, made some ground passing 100M, stalls test.
Began awkwardly then taken back, settled behind midfield, one-paced in the straight.
Hard ridden to take lead, weakened passing 150M.
Crowded on jumping, travelled at back on rail, kept on rail to save ground at Home Turn, one-pace in the straight.
Urged along to race outside the lead, gave ground in the straight, bled.
Reared at start and lost considerable ground, took no part, barrier trial.

Was allowed to find feet after the start before positioning midfield off the rail. Improved position before cornering but still conceded 5Ls on straightening before sprinting powerfully to strike lead inside final 100m and win.
Away well and showed good speed despite being bumped heavily in first 100m. Positioned close to the speed in middle sections before striking the lead at the 150m but was overhauled in last 100m.

Had no early speed and settled at the tail. Conceded at least 10 lengths on cornering before being pulled out wider on the track after straightening and made large amount of late ground in the run to the line.
Began fast from wide barrier before coming across to share lead in first 300m. Assumed outright lead around 600m out and was still prominent until being overrun in final 200m.

Wasn't the quickest into stride but before making up some ground in first 200m to settle worse than midfield on the fence. Was 7 lengths off lead on cornering and made good late ground but was never a winning threat.
Showed good early speed to assume lead before being joined for lead after 200m. Was then headed and was tightened for room on the point of the bend before battling away fairly in the straight.

Was ridden prominently in early stages before settling right behind leaders but slightly over racing after 300m. Was around 2.5 lengths off lead on cornering and did not threaten in the run to the line.
Was very slow into stride missing the start around 3 lengths. Tacked onto the back of the field after 250m but was always at the back due to slow get away.

Was heavily bumped after 100m before settling midfield in the clear. Was ridden up to improve position before cornering. Was still 6 lengths off lead on cornering and effectively maintained that margin in the run to the line.
Was away well but did not have the early speed of rivals and settled in the final few. Conceded a large margin on cornering never really threatened to challenge in the run to the line.
Began well from inside draw but could not get to lead, instead settling behind leading pair. Was within 2.5L on cornering in but faded out in the final section.
Was allowed to find feet after the start and positioned near the tail after 200m. Never really improved position in middle stages and failed to catch the eye in the final section.
Began smartly from the widest gate, sent forward to take the lead, enjoyed the easy lead throughout, kicked clear early in straight, kept on well to score.
Shifted out at start and made contact, positioned 2 wide in midfield, wider on turn, finished off well to take 2nd.
Clean jump, raced at rear, 8 lengths back, same margin back on turn, taken wide in straight and made good progress to take a place, no threat to the first two.
Crowded start, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, 6 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, made good progress in straight to make frame without threatening.
Bumped start, raced 3 wide with no cover in midfield, 4 lengths back, carried wider on turn, kept on evenly to the line.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, 9 lengths back, still well back on turn, made some headway in straight.
Began well, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, peaked on turn, one-paced in straight.
Crowded on jumping, positioned 6 lengths back on rail, saved ground on turn, slightly blocked near 200M, finished off evenly thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Average to begin, raced 2 wide, 5 lengths back, same margin back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Moderately away, sat 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, 2 wide from near 600M, failed to quicken early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Crowded start, positioned on rail in midfield, there to turn, weakened gradually in straight.
Jumped with them, raced prominently, 2 wide, 2 lengths back on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Sent forward and raced prominently, sat 1L off and outside the lead, continued on nicely to score by 1/2L.
Sent forward to take the rail, held lead by about 1L, headed at 150M but kept on to finish in 2nd.
Niggled along and settled to be in front of midfield, 4L off 2 wide, maintained good progress to take 3rd.
Raced in midfield, 5-1/2L behind along the rail, kept on well in the straight.
Travelled in midfield, 5-1/4L behind 2 wide, continued on well to the line.
Bumped start, then asked to be in one-off one-back, sat 2-1/2L off, ran on fairly to the line.
Settled to race in the box-seat, sat 1-1/4L off the lead, found no extra at 150M.
Fractious and slow to jump, taken back to be at rear, 9-1/2L behind 2 wide, saved ground.
Sat near the rear, 8L behind 2 wide, began to close off at 100M until checked at 50M when shifted in abruptly.
Awkward start and then crowded, made turn at rear and along the rail, made minor ground only.
Jumped well but then eased back, in worse than midfield and trapped wide, did not improve.
Bumped start and then failed to muster, raced in worse than midfield along the rail, never threatened.
Settled in midfield in 6th on the rail, became 5th going up the Rock, switched out to challenge upon straightening, ran on under pressure to just get up on line.
Pressed forward to lead from a wide gate, obtained rails run over 900 metres out, led until narrowly headed final strides while drifting.
Settled in rear on the rail, gained slightly closer turning into back straight, saved ground making home turn, ran on under pressure to be nearest at finish.

Began from the middle gate, travelled wide without cover in midfield early stages but gradually taken back to last few, renewed effort rounding home bend and swung wide into the straight, finished off the race well.
Broke well, soon taken back on the rail to 2L 4th, became 3rd going up the Rock, failed to quicken under pressure.
Taken back to the rear from the widest gate, ran on to be nearest at finish despite not finding much room 200 metres out.
Began well to vie for lead settling inside the leader on the rail rounding stables bend, shifted one back turning into back straight, faded under pressure in the run home.
Settled towards the rear from a wide gate, went widest into home straight, kept on before finding no extra inside the final 100 metres.
Pressed forward from a wide gate, settled 2-wide in 3rd within 2L of pace, drifted back to 4th going up the Rock, found no extra in home straight.
Settled in rear of midfield in 7th, yielded ground steadily rounding home bend, found nothing in the straight.

Settled just off the pace, steadied passing the winning post the first time dropping 3L back to 5th and wide without cover, became 6th at about the Rock, dropped out under pressure inside the 400 metres.
Jumped well but soon dropped well behind, tailed-off from back straight.
Quickly crossed to the rail, tracked leader in a slowly run race, quickened to a decisive lead passing 200M, kept on well to the line.
Crowded for room at start, taken back to the rear 8-9Ls off the pace, wide into straight, finished off strongly to go 2nd 50M, nearest finish.
Jumped evenly, held up in midfield in a slowly run race, bustled along nearing 400M, closed off well to be nearest at the line.
From draw 12 crossed to the lead 1300M, led them along at a slow pace, headed near 200M, weakened late just held on for 4th.
Began awkwardly, went forward to be tracking leader, pressed along 500M but couldn't muster the finishing pace, battled on final 300M without threatening.
Reserved towards the rear, stayed on mildly on straightening, not reached first 3.
Positively ridden to be 4th on settling, pace slow middle stages, kept on evenly passing 300M, never seriously threatened.
Hampered at the start, dropped back to the rear 9Ls off the slow pace, made some ground final 300M but never close enough to challenge.
Held up behind midfield, pushed along inside 400M, kept on one pace to the finish.
Settled down in 8th worse of midfield, 3-wide no cover from 800M, closed off the race only fairly. No impression.
From draw 1 raced along the fence in 5th spot, enjoyed a smooth run but couldn't quicken when asked. (Jockey unable to offer any explanation for the disappointing run.)
Towards the rear, remained in the 10th spot until home turn, swung wide for home, failed to finish off.
Away with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, improved after passing 700M, 3 wide turning, finished off very strongly to score.
Began well from gate 1, positioned 2 to 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after straightening and finished off well to take 2nd.

Jumped well, sent forward to race prominently but trapped wide early, took the lead near 1000M and found rail after passing 800M, challenged on turn, showed good response early in straight, headed 200M, stayed on well to take 3rd.
Jumped with them, positioned on rail in midfield, 4 lengths back, same margin back on turn, made some headway in straight to make frame without threatening.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, improved after passing 800M, challenged the leader on turn, kept on well until near 150M, slightly weakened thereafter. (Lost left front plate.)
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear on rail, 8 lengths or so back, moved a bit closer on turn, made some headway in straight.
Bumped shortly after start, sent forward to race prominently on rail, headed near 1000M, a length behind on turn, one-paced in straight.
Bumped start, positioned 6 lengths behind the leader on rail, 2 wide after passing 700M, very wide into straight, only passed some weakened rivals in straight.
Taken back from gate 9, raced at tail, 9 lengths back, improved from 700M, awkwardly placed turning in, failed to close off in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Average to begin, raced 2 wide at rear, 7 lengths back, moved closer in the middle stages, 4 wide turning, failed to close off in straight.
Jumped well, raced 2 wide, 2 to 3 lengths back, peaked on turn, weakened gradually after passing 200M.
Moderately away, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, allowed rival to cross on the first turn, sat 2 lengths behind thereafter, peaked on turn, emptied early in straight, eased final 150M.

Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, 7 lengths back, moved a bit closer on turn, finished off very strongly in straight to score.
Jumped well, raced 2 wide, a length or so back, there to turn, angled out near 550M, took the lead early in straight, kept on well thereafter, just couldn't hold off the winner.
Commenced well, taken back to race 2 to 3 wide with cover at rear, improved from 500M, finished off well in straight to take a place.
Began awkwardly and bumped, sent forward to race outside the leader, shared lead on turn, headed after passing 300M, kept on evenly to the line.
Slightly slow out, raced 6 lengths back at rear, there to turn, no clear running early in straight, made very good progress when clear final 200M to be nearest on line.

Began fairly, raced 5 lengths back on rail, saved ground on turn, unable to obtain clear running early in straight, then raced tight near 150M, finished off strongly when clear final 50M. (Lame left hind leg next day.)
Began well, raced 3 wide with cover better than midfield, same position on turn, finished off evenly in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Moderately away from a wide draw, sent forward to race prominently but trapped wide, 3 wide on turn, no cover throughout, weakened gradually in straight.
Away with them, sent forward to take the lead, shared lead turning in, headed early in straight, kept on evenly to near 100M, weakened thereafter.
Jumped well, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, 3 to 4 lengths back on turn, failed to quicken in straight.
Commenced well, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, unable to obtain clear running early in straight, weakened final 200M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Slightly slow out, sat 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, easy run on turn, failed to make any progress in straight.
Jumped with field, raced 2 wide in midfield, same position on turn, weakened early in straight.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 4 lengths back, same margin back on turn, weakened early in straight.
Pushed early, 3 wide in front of midfield, pace good, drifted away 300M to score.
Settled in front, 2 wide, pace good, ran on well for 2nd.
Pushed to keep up in midfield, 2 wide, pace good, lack room 400M, made steady ground when clear.
Eased back, took rail, pace good, lack room 4-2, progressed steadily when clear.
Hard ridden early, midfield, trapped 4 wide, pace good, made some ground 200M.
Eased to take box seat, raced keenly, pace good, weakened 150M.
Eased to rear, 3-4 wide, pace good, made steady ground 250M.
Eased back, 3-4 wide, pace good, made ground 300M, run ended 150M.
Behind midfield along the fence, pace good, lack room 4-2, no dash when clear.
At rear, 2 wide, pace good, no progress.
At back, 3 wide, pace good, never improved.
Pushed forward, sat 2 wide, out of fuel quickly 350M.
Pushed to take rail and led at good pace, soon emptied 350M.
Eased back, never a factor.
Moderate start, settled midfield, asked for effort passing 600M, quickened passing 150M, finished strongly to score.
Raced behind midfield on rail, gradually made ground in the straight, worked home solidly.
Began only fairly, settled midfield, placed pressure passing 300M then responded solidly, came line nicely.
Travelled in handy position, fought hard in the straight, made up some late ground.
Settled behind midfield, wide on straightening, made some ground passing 100M.
Settled at back, widest on straightening, limited response in the straight.
Jumped nicely, raced in box seat, tried to improve near 500M, one-paced.
Raced at tail, wide on straightening, gained ground passing 100M.
Ridden along to take lead, faded out passing 100M.
Travelled midfield on rail, kept on rail rounding the Home Turn, one-paced.
Urged to settle outside the lead, niggled passing 800M, weakened passing 200M, failed to make impression.
Jumped well, travelled wide and without cover in handy position, gave ground passing 300M.
Slow to begin, raced midfield on rail, no response in the straight.

Began well and was allowed to stride forward in first 200m before coming across and positioning outside lead. Assumed the lead shortly after the 400m. Shared lead at 175m & was bumped at that stage before kicking back to win.

Eased back and across before settling third last. Moved three horses wide prior to the 1200m. Improved position from 600m before entering straight 5 horses wide before sprinting strongly in the straight. Joined lead at 175m.

Strode forward early before being tightened for room near the 2100m, positioned prominently one pair behind lead on outside. Travelled well and was only 1.5 lengths from lead on straightening, fought well in last section.

One of the slowest away & was keen early before easing back to worse than midfield. Shuffled back to near last, 5 lengths from lead on straightening before shifting out at the 300m and making some late ground in last section.

Not bustled early before coming across to the rail after 200m to position midfield. Shifted away from the rail at the 550m before being badly checked at the 450m and again cramped for room at 300m. Worked home well last 300m.

Fairly away before being crossed after and not bustled before positioning two pairs back on the fence. Shifted away from the rail at the 500m and again further at the 450m before only working home fairly in final 300m.
Positioned midfield but 3 horses wide after the first 600m. Ridden up from 750m to improve position before being pushed 4 horses wide on cornering, before weakening out in the final 400m.

Commenced a little slow and veered out at the start before being eased back and across to last after 300m. Was at the back throughout and was six lengths off lead on cornering before shifting out wider but not threatening.

Ridden positively first 200m before being crowded at 2100m and forced three horses wide. Continued to race wide in middle sections before improving position at 700m. Was 1 length off lead on cornering but tired out from 350m.
Jumped well and assumed lead after 250m. Was joined in the lead shortly after straightening before weakening out from the 350m.

Wasn't fast away and was steadied after 300m before positioning midfield one horse off the rail. Moved out wider at the 550m but conceded six lengths on cornering. Was crowded at the 200m but was not a threat at that stage.
Began well before going forward and getting third on the fence after 600m. Travelled well but yielded ground from 350m when pressure was turned up.

Was prominent before being crowded and racing keenly after 300m. Settled midfield one horse away from the fence in middle stages. Was three lengths from lead on straightening before being bumped and badly checked at 400m.
Had no early speed and was eased back and across after 300m. Was ridden up from 500m to get into race but effectively took no part from that point onwards. Returned with irregular heart rate.
Jumped well, positioned 1 out 1 back, travelled nicely throughout, there to turn, finished off strongly in straight to score.
Made contact at start, sat a length behind the leader on rail, easy run to turn, no clear running early in straight, finished off very well when clear thereafter to take 2nd.
Jumped with field, positioned 3 wide with cover behind midfield, 3 lengths back on turn, finished off strongly in straight to take a place.
Away with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, same position on turn, no daylight early in straight, made good progress when clear thereafter to make frame.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide behind midfield early, found rail after passing 900M, saved ground on turn, made reasonable progress in straight to be nearest on line, no threat to the first few.
Began well, sent forward to race prominently, shared lead on the outside turning, kept on well early in straight, peaked near 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide, 4 lengths back, same margin back on turn, made some progress in straight.
Began awkwardly, raced 3 wide in midfield, no cover after 800M, 2 lengths back on turn, failed to quicken under pressure in straight.

Jumped well from a wide draw, sent forward to take the lead, found rail near 900M, shared lead on turn, kept on well early in straight, headed near 200M, weakened gradually thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Slightly slow out from gate 1, raced at rear on rail, 4 to 5 lengths back, saved ground on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Slowly away, raced at rear, 5 lengths or so back, 3 wide on turn, failed to make any progress in straight, finished last.
Settled fore of midfield, 2-1/4L behind 2 wide, fought all the way and fended off challenge to score by a nose. (See Incident Report)
Raced in front of midfield, 2-1/2L off 3 wide but with cover, battled on gamely to the line, missed by a nose. (See Incident Report)
Travelled in midfield, 3-3/4L behind 2-3 wide, raced ungenerously, continued on well to the line.
Awkward start, in behind midfield, 5-1/4L off along the rail, ran on well despite making contact at 200M.
Taken back and raced at the tail, 7-1/2L behind 2 wide, shifted widest at 200M and closed off strongly.
Awkward start, then crowded, recovered to race prominently but wide, kept on going to the line.
Jumped well but then taken back, at rear 6-3/4L behind 3 wide but with cover, continued to improve to the line.
Eased back to be close to the rear, 6-1/4L behind 2 wide, saved ground and closed off fairly.
Raced in the box-seat, sat 2L off the lead, raced tight at 200M before continuing on to the line.
In behind midfield, 5-1/4L off 2 wide, raced keenly, found no running after 200M, closed off thereafter.
Settled to race in midfield, 3-3/4L behind along the rail, slight dash early and ran on.
Sent forward, took rail and led by 3/4L, found no extra approaching 100M.
Rolled forward and settled outside the lead, about 3/4L off, in touch until emptied at 150M.
Taken back and raced towards the rear, 5-1/4L behind 3 wide but with cover, saved ground in straight.
Shared pace out wide in early stages after beginning from a wide gate, obtained rails run in the front coming onto home bend, drew clear inside the 250 metres, won unextended.
Began fairly, settled wide in rear of midfield, remained wide into straight, ran on under pressure to snatch 2nd final strides.
Niggled at and amongst the leaders early, taken some 2L back in 5th after the first 200 metres, became 4th approaching home turn, fought on to reach distant 2nd briefly 100 metres out.
Slowly away, settled at the back, ran on under pressure inside the final 400 metres.

Jumped awkwardly from a wide gate, settled wide in last few in straight, commenced move approaching the home turn and the widest runner turning in, unable to sustain effort inside the final 200 metres.

Jumped best from a wide gate and led the first 200 metres before taken back to midfield 3-wide, gained slightly closer when without cover rounding home bend, reached 2nd briefly passing the 200 metres and soon swamped.
Awkward start losing ground settling well behind, went wide into straight, did not find much room early on, kept on without quickening inside the final 200 metres.
Settled in last few on the rail, angled out turning in, made up some late ground in closing stages.
Prominent early stages, gradually drifted back to midfield onto home bend, switched towards the rail for a run after straightening, failed to quicken under pressure.
Broke well sharing early pace, shifted one back behind eventual winner rounding home bend, kept on before fading inside the final 200 metres.

Niggled along after a moderate start, clipped heels at about the 1350 metres, travelling keenly when drifted back to rear of midfield in 10th approaching home bend, fought on steadily until forced to steady 100 metres out.
Ridden for the first 200 metres and hit the front narrowly 1200 metres out, snatched 1L back 2-wide coming onto home bend, kept on before weakening out of contention inside the final 200 metres.
Settled in midfield on the rail, came under pressure after straightening, tightened on the rail 300 metres out.
Jumped fairly, travelled not far off the pace in 4th on the rail, dropped away quickly inside the final 200 metres.
Driven forward soon after the start, led unchallenged, fought off a persistent challenge on straightening, made all.
Held up behind midfield in 5th, 5Ls to make up on leader (eventual winner) 400M, closed off strongly final 250M to go 2nd near line within 1L of winner.
Tracked leader in a steadily run race, loomed up 350M, tried hard but couldn't reel in leader, lost 2nd near line.
In 4th, settled midfield, 4Ls to make up on winner at 400M, ran on mildly under pressure, not quite able to challenge.
In 3rd chasing leaders, hard driven but couldn't get closer to first 2 on straightening, kept on steadily to line, lost 2 placing final stages.
Dropped back to race in the rear over 10Ls off the pace, made limited progress on straightening, never a threat to main rivals.
Settled towards the rear 10Ls off the pace, plodded on without threat in the straight.
Slowly away, given a patient ride at the rear, well off the pace middle stages, responded only fairly on straightening, not reached leaders.
A bit slow away, held up towards rear over 10Ls behind leader early stages, ridden along 500M, kept on one paced, weakened late stages.
Commenced well from a wide draw, raced prominently but trapped 3 to 4 wide, no cover throughout, kept on strongly after turning in, took the lead near 250M and held on to win by a narrow margin.

Jumped well from gate 1, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, easy run on turn, no clear running early in straight, angled out near 350M, finished off strongly to take 2nd, narrowly beaten. (Rider dropped whip near 200M.)
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide, 3 lengths back, there to turn, made very good progress in straight despite tight run near 250M.
Began well, sent forward to race prominently on rail, shared lead on turn, kept on well early in straight, headed near 250M, slightly weakened thereafter, just stayed on for 4th.
Crowded on jumping, raced at rear on rail, 4 to 5 lengths back, there to turn, kept to inside after straightening and finishing off very strongly to be nearest on line.
Fast into stride, raced 2 wide, a length or so back, same position on turn, angled out early in straight, raced tight near 250M, kept on evenly thereafter.
Began only fairly, positioned on rail in midfield, awkwardly placed near 750M, saved ground on turn, kept on well early in straight, raced tight near 250M, ran on evenly thereafter.
Shifted out at start and bumped, raced 2 to 3 wide with cover behind midfield, difficult to settle throughout, finished off evenly in straight. (Lame left front leg next day.)
Average to begin, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, 2 to 3 lengths back on turn, peaked early in straight, ran on one-paced.
Bumped start, raced 4 wide behind midfield, no cover throughout, failed to close off in straight.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear, 7 lengths back, a little bit closer on turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Bumped start, raced wide with cover at rear, 5 lengths back on turn, taken wide in straight and finished off evenly.
Shifted in at start and bumped, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, shared lead on turn, peaked early in straight, dropped away thereafter.
Jumped with field, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, there to turn, improved from 600M, hit the front early in straight, kept on strongly to the line, scored by 2-1/2L.
Began well from gate1, positioned 2 to 3 lengths back on rail, saved ground to turn, angled out near 600M, finished off well to take 2nd without threatening the winner.

Jumped well from gate 13, sent forward to take the lead, travelled comfortably throughout, challenged by rival turning in, kept on well early in straight, headed near 250M, stayed on for 3rd thereafter.
Shifted out at start and bumped, raced 2 wide in midfield, carried wider after passing 600M, made some progress in straight to make frame without threatening.
Bumped start, sat right behind the leader on rail, easy run on turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Commenced well, taken back to race 3 wide behind midfield, no cover throughout, 4 wide turning, finished off evenly in straight.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, 5 to 6 lengths back on turn, made some progress in straight.
Shifted out at start and made contact, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, there to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Crowded out start, raced at rear on rail, closer on turn, 2 wide from near 600M, no daylight early in straight, finished off evenly when clear final 200M.
Crowded on jumping, raced 2 wide at rear, travelled keenly on turn, 3 wide turning in, no clear running early in straight, finished off evenly when clear thereafter.
Clean jump, positioned on rail behind midfield, 4 to 5 lengths back, saved ground on turn, angled out near 550M, failed to close off in straight.
Crowded on jumping, positioned 5 to 6 lengths back on rail, saved ground on turn, made no progress in straight.
Bumped start and unbalanced, raced 2 wide behind midfield, similar position on turn, failed to close off in straight. (Blood in trachea.)
Crowded start, raced at rear throughout, never a threat.

Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide at rear, 7 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, finished off very strongly in straight to score.
Moderately away, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, 3/4L back on turn, kept on well in straight to take 2nd.
Bumped on jumping, positioned on rail in midfield, 4 lengths back, saved ground on turn, closed off well to take a place, nearest on line.
Fast into stride, sat 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, easy run throughout, kept on well in straight to make frame.

Bumped start, positioned on rail behind midfield, difficult to settle early, shifted out off heels 900M, 7Ls back on turn, made good progress early in straight, steadied 50M, not able to be ridden out near the finish.

Began only fairly, positioned on rail behind midfield, 5 to 6 lengths back, saved ground on turn, made good progress early in straight, awkwardly placed near 100M, not able to be ridden out thereafter.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 5 lengths back on turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Shifted out at start and bumped, raced 2 wide better than midfield, difficult to settle for a short distance near 1300M, 3 to 4 lengths back on turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, 9 lengths back, still well back on turn, taken wide in straight and made some progress.

Shifted out at start and bumped, sent forward to race prominently on rail, travelled well to turn, led by 3/4L turning in, kept on well early in straight, headed after passing 150M, weakened thereafter.
Began well, raced 2 wide, 2 lengths back, there to turn, weakened early in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear throughout, never a threat.
Hard ridden early but failed to cross in front, eased to sit in midfield, 2 wide, progressed steadily 250M to score.
Eased to obtain box seat, pace good, led 200M, hung on until 100M overhauled.
Took rail in midfield, pace good, made steady ground 250M for 3rd.
Hard ridden early, 2 wide at back, pace good, progressed steadily 300M.
Hard ridden forward, sat 2 wide, pace good, emptied 200M.
Checked at start, too rail, pace good, made some ground 200M.
Hard ridden to take hold the rail and led at good pace, ran on until 200M weakened.
Eased at start, 2-3 wide, pace good, made ground 200M.
Slow away, 2 wide at rear, pace good, ran on fairly.
At back along the fence, pace good, no progress.
Pushed forward, sat 2 wide, pace good, emptied 300M.
Hard ridden to keep up in midfield along the rails, pace good, out of fuel 300M.
At start bumped heavily with a runner and became unbalanced, settled midfield, commenced to improve near 600M, wide on straightening, quickened passing 150M, made good late ground to score.
Urged along to take lead, responded strongly in the straight, just missed by Head.
Settled close to midfield on rail, improved near 500M, quickened passing 100M, worked home solidly.
Crowded on jumping, raced in handy position, asked for effort passing 600M, fought well in the straight, finished solidly.
Settled midfield on rail, niggled passing 800M, improved on rail in the straight, worked home OK.
Settled in box seat, travelled keenly in middle stages, fought hard but only limited response.
At start bumped heavily with a runner and became unbalanced, after that ridden along but failed to muster speed, raced close to midfield, widest on straightening, made some ground passing 100M.
Crowded at start, raced at tail, made limited ground in the straight.
Taken back at start, settled at back, one-paced in the straight.
Settled in front of midfield on rail, gave ground passing 200M, failed to make impression.
Taken back at start, no response when placed pressure.
Began awkwardly, ridden along then failed to muster speed, always back, did not stretch out at any stages, OVE.

Began well and was outside leader before easing after 900m to position behind leading pair off the fence. Eased slightly before cornering and bumped in early stages of straight before forging forward to win.
Began well before being eased back to midfield one horse off the fence. Moved out wider on the track from the 350m and was within three length son cornering before making good late ground.
Away fairly before coming across from out wide to be midfield 3 horses wide. Was five lengths from lead on cornering and closed strongly from rearward position in final section.

Fairly away settling 2 lengths from speed before travelling keenly after the 1000m and then moving three horses wide at the 750m. Made corner 4 horses wide only 2 lengths from lead. Battled hard to line but tired last 150m.
Began fast and held lead for first 300m before being headed at 900m. Railed back to join lead again at 650m. Held lead until 200m before weakening out from there.

Slow away before maintaining rail position midfield. Over raced between the 600m and 450m. Bumped at the 275m and was crowded for galloping room shortly after dipped badly at on two occasions at 230m.
Veered out and bumped at the start before being shifted across behind runners to settle in last 3. Shifted away from the rail on cornering and worked away fairly to the line.

Away well and ridden forward before racing 3 wide with cover, before being left 3 wide without cover from 800m. Improved position to be within 1 length of lead at 500m before joining lead on cornering. Weakened out last 150m.
Away well from the inside and positioned up leaders back in first 250m. Stayed close to the fence after straightening but tired out from the 300m.

Clearly the last into stride and settled at the rear on the fence. Was over 5 lengths from lead on cornering before being pulled out wider after straightening but failing to bridge and part of that margin.

Not bustled early and was ridden across behind runners to settle at the tail one horse off the fence. Was over 5 lengths off speed when the last one to corner only maintained that margin in the straight.

Veered out and bumped after start before gathering speed and challenging leaders. Assumed lead at 900m before crossing to one horse off fence at 850m. Shared lead from 650m. Under pressure from 400m & faded out last section.
Taken back from gate 11, raced at rear, 8 lengths back, improved from 700M, 3 wide turning, finished off strongly to score.

Slightly slow out and bumped, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 5 to 6 lengths back, similar position on turn, no daylight early in straight, angled out after passing 200M, finished off strongly to take 2nd.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced 2 wide at rear, 6 lengths or so back, 3 wide from 800M, moved closer thereafter, 4 lengths back on turn, closed off well to take a place.
Jumped well from gate 9, sent forward to race prominently but trapped 3 wide, found a 2 wide spot after passing 1200M, 2 lengths or so back on turn, kept on evenly to the line.
Bumped start, positioned on rail behind midfield, there to turn, made good progress in straight.
Slightly slow out, recovered quickly to take the lead, travelled well to turn, led by 1-3/4L at 400M, kept on well early in straight, headed after passing 100M, weakened thereafter.
Began well from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground to turn, unable to obtain clear running until final 100M, showed some response thereafter.
Away with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, checked early in straight, steadied off heels near 200M, finished off evenly thereafter.
Bumped start, raced 3 wide in midfield, no cover from 1200M, wider from near 700M, 2 lengths back on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter, eased final 100M.
Began well, sat 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, same margin back on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Crowded on jumping, raced at rear throughout, never competitive.
Shifted out at start and bumped, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, weakened from near 700M, eased 400M, unacceptable performance.
Sent forward to take the rail and led by 3/4L, led all way and scored without being challenged.
Bumped start, travelled in midfield, 3-1/2L behind along the rail, fought on gamely but was no match to winner.
Slotted into position in midfield, 3-3/4L behind 2 wide, ran on well to the line.
Bumped start, then asked before shifted in to take the box-seat, sat 2L off, continued on one paced.
Settled in one-off one-back position, sat 2-1/2L off the lead, ran on one paced to the line.
Raced in worse than midfield, 5-1/4L behind along the rail, saved ground and closed off fairly.
Travelled in behind midfield, 5L behind 2 wide, improved position slightly late.
Sent forward, sat 3/4L off and outside the lead, weakened passing 150M.
Taken back and raced at the rear, wide but with cover, made minor ground only.
Bumped start, then took back to be at rear and on the rail, did not improve.(See Racing Incident Report)
At rear, 2 wide throughout, never in contention.
Eased after start, sat in behind midfield but wide, unbalanced and lay out in back straight, never in it. (Must trial at HV before racing there again)
Broke well sharing early pace, shifted one back to be 3rd with rails run, angled out to challenge upon straightening, responded well to assert authority over 100 metres out.
Close up and wide early, taken back to settle in 5th some 3L off the pace, came to challenge upon straightening, finished off the race well inside the final 200 metres.
With leaders early, hit the front briefly approaching the Rock, regained lead entering home straight, unable to sustain effort and swamped inside the final 150 metres.
With leaders early settling some 3L back in 4th on the rail, switched in for a run over 250 metres out, finished off the race nicely.
Settled towards the rear from a wide gate travelling wide throughout, commenced move rounding the home bend, ran on well down the centre of the straight to be nearest at finish.
Moderate start, settled in rear of midfield on the rail, met minor interference 500 metres out, saved ground on the inside turning for home, fought on steadily without threatening.
Jumped awkwardly losing ground, settled towards the rear on the rail, switched wide into the straight, finished off the race well inside the final 200 metres.
Settled wide in midfield, forced to check 200 metres out, kept on well to the line.
Settled in midfield, one-paced under pressure in the run home.
Crowded at start and dropped to the rear, never seen with a chance.
Ridden positively from the widest gate, travelled wide without cover before gaining narrow lead coming out of back straight, lost advantage swinging for home, soon dropped out.
Crowded and unbalanced at the start after beginning from a wide gate, dropped to tail-end coming onto home bend.
Hampered at start, held up in midfield 6Ls back from leader, wide into straight, ran on best final 200M, got up just in time.
Tracked leader from 1400M, loomed early straight, quickened to lead near 200M, caught last stride.
Reserved in midfield 4-5Ls back along the fence, moved into a striking spot 350M, ran on mildly to go 3rd near line.
Always in touch, moved up to 3rd passing 700M, kept on steadily on straightening, always held by winner, lost 3rd last stride.
From wide draw dropped back towards the rear of midfield, made early bid 500M and swung wide into straight, run peaked 150M, no extra close home.

Steadied to obtain cover after the jump, settled down 2-wide in midfield, held up for clear running near 200M, shifted lane to improve but again no clear run late stages. (Jockey questioned re his riding in the straight).
Rushed forward from wide draw and crossed to the lead 1400M, led steadily before quickening up home turn, headed 200M, faded towards the line.
Chased leaders in a steadily run race, bustled along 500M but couldn't muster the speed to challenge, ran home one paced, raced tight passing 100M.
Hampered at start, settled towards the rear 8Ls off the pace, made limited progress in straight, never a threat.
Shifted across behind runners, ended up near last 8-9Ls back, ridden and no impression from 400M out.
Taken back from wide draw, raced as the back-marker 10Ls behind leader, didn't respond to pressure on straightening, never involved.
Held up behind midfield, came under pressure 500M, soon beaten leaving the bend.
