Away with them, taken back to race at rear, 4 lengths back in the middle stages, improved from 650M, 4 wide turning in, took the lead near 300M, kept on strongly to score with still plenty gas in tank.
Began well, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, travelled keenly in the early stages, saved ground on turn, finished off evenly, no threat to the winner.

Commenced well, sent forward to take the lead, travelled keenly in the early stages, challenged by rivals turning in, peaked early in straight, headed near 300M, slightly weakened thereafter, just stayed on for 3rd.
Shifted in at start and bumped, raced 2 wide, 2 to 3 lengths back, improved from near 650M, 3 wide turning in, peaked early in straight, kept on evenly to the line.
Bumped start, positioned on rail at rear, 4 lengths or so back, a bit closer on turn, made no progress in straight.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide, a length or so back, same position on turn, weakened gradually in straight.
Hard ridden to secure box seat, benefited by the slow tempo, closed off strongly 300M to score.
Hard ridden forward to share the lead at slow sectionals, hung on well until 150M overhauled, ran on for 2nd.
Midfield, 2 wide, not suited by the slow tempo, held ground for 3rd.
Pushed to keep up in midfield, on heels early, trapped 4 wide throughout, harmed by the slow tempo, unleashed strong finishing efforts 200M.
Slow away, raced very keenly at back, 2 wide, not suited by the slow tempo, dashed well 300M.
Eased back, trapped 3 wide, lack room 4-2, dashed strongly despite not suited by the slow pace.
Pushed to take rail and shared the lead at slow sectionals, out of fuel 200M.
Eased back, trapped 3-4 wide, harmed by the slow tempo, little dash 200M.
Very slow away, at back, 2 wide, harmed by the slow pace, no dash.
Hard ridden forward, 2 wide, benefited by the slow tempo, emptied 300M.
Hard ridden to keep up in midfield, not suited by the slow pace, no progress.
Very slow away, never competitive.
Settled behind the lead with nice early speed, improved passing 400M, worked home strongly to score.
Settled midfield, asked for effort passing 400M, gained good ground passing 200M, finished strongly, just missed by SH.
Ridden along to take lead on outside rail, responded nicely when asked for effort, finished solidly.
Settled in front of midfield, made ground passing 300M, came home nicely.
At start reared and lost ground, settled behind midfield on rail, made up some late ground.
Raced in front of midfield, passing 500M was checked, one-paced when placed pressure.
Jumped nicely, settled inside the lead, gave some ground passing 300M, mucus trachea.
Travelled in front of midfield, worked home one-paced.
Slow to begin, raced at tail, limited response when placed pressure.
Settled in handy position on outside rail, gave ground passing 200M, lame left front next day.
Moderate start, raced behind midfield, limited response.
Urged along but no early speed, raced at back, never in it.
Travelled midfield, weakened passing 200M.
Began only fairly, raced behind midfield, failed to run on.
Ridden very hard from the start tom come across and lead after 150m. Travelled well in middle sections before breaking clear inside the final 300m to win.

Was away well but didn't have the speed of others and settled midfield one horse off the fence. Was ridden up before cornering before pulling out wider in the straight and making good late ground in the final 300m.
Came across to midfield but was posted three horses wide without cover in middle stages. Was 2.5 lengths of lead on cornering and maintained that margin in the final section.

Was the last into stride before making up that ground in first 400m to settle midfield on the fence. Moved away from the fence at the 550m before entering the straight the second widest runner. Boxed on in the last section.

Was fairly away before coming across and slotting in behind leading pair one horse off the fence. Moved around heals after the 600m to be close to leading pair. Shifted some ground in the straight before tiring out the last 150m.
Held fence position to be third behind the leader in early and middle stages. Travelled comfortably up to the corner and was presented with clear running after the 400m but tired out the final 200m.

Wasn't fast away and had no early speed, subsequently settled at the tail of the field after 300m. Raced a little keen between the 750m and 600m. Stayed close to the rail on cornering and never threatened in the run to the line.

Was slightly awkward to begin & subsequently was eased back to settle at the rear of the field. Moved three horses wide at the 800m. Was a clear last on cornering around 5.5L from lead. Didn't make any impression in the run to the line.
Began well and came across to position outside the leader. Travelled comfortably in early and middle stages before weakening out from the 350m.
Away with them, taken back to race at rear on the inside, 4 to 5 lengths back on turn, in traffic early in straight, finished off very strongly when clear thereafter to score.
Bumped start, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, no daylight early in straight, finished off well when clear final 200M to take 2nd.
Shifted out at start and bumped, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, easy run on turn, unable to obtain clear running until passing 150M, made some progress thereafter to take a place.

Jumped with them, sent forward to take the lead, travelled keenly in the early stages, led by half length on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked after passing 200M, headed 100M, weakened thereafter.
Commenced well, showed no early speed, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, improved from 550M, very wide turning in, made good progress in straight to be nearest on line.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, 5 lengths or so back on turn, made some headway in straight without threatening.
Began well from a wide draw, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, 1/2L back on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.

Moderately away from a wide draw, unable to slot in early, positioned 3 wide with cover better than midfield in the middle stages, 2 lengths back on turn, kept on evenly early in straight, weakened final 100M.
Began only fairly, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, there to turn, finished off one-paced in straight.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide, 3 to 4 lengths back, similar position on turn, no clear running early in straight, made no progress when clear thereafter.
Jumped well, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, weakened early in straight.
Began well from gate 11, raced prominently but trapped 3 wide, no cover throughout, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Taken back to race at rear on rail, moved a bit closer along the rail in the middle stages, 4 lengths back on turn, failed to make any progress in straight.
Began awkwardly and lost ground, raced 2 wide at rear, 5 lengths back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
In midfield, 3-3/4L behind 2 wide, fought well to chase down leader, took lead near 50M and ran on to win.
Pushed early to take the rail and led by 3/4L, maintained advantage until caught by the winner approaching 50M.
Sat in front of midfield, 2-1/2L off along the rail, no running early but ran on well once cleared passing 250M.
Settled in one-off one-back, sat 2-1/4L off the lead, kept on one paced to the line.
In midfield, 4L off along the rail, crowded at 150M, ran on well thereafter until awkward to heels on the line.
Raced in worse than midfield, 5-1/4L behind 2 wide, improved steadily to the line.
Taken back and raced at the rear, 7L behind along the rail, made ground from 250M and ran on fairly.
Settled outside the lead, sat 3/4L off, run ended when had to be corrected when shifted in abruptly after 200M.
Taken back and raced at the rear, 7L behind 2 wide, ungenerous in the middle stages, made minor ground.
Jumped fairly only, settled to race in box-seat, kept on until crowded at 150M.
Awkward start and lost ground, recovered to in worse than midfield along the rail, emptied at 350M.
Began well, settled within striking distance on the rail, steadied behind pace rounding home bend, switched out for a clear run at the 200 metres, quickened well to snatch victory near the line.
Ridden early before taken one back after the first 200 metres, came to join the leaders entering home straight and hit the front briefly 150 metres out only to be caught close home.
Moderate start, ridden to rear of midfield, gained closer when pace slackened around the bend, switched out to challenge entering home straight, made moderate progress without threatening.
Ridden to lead from a wide gate, steadied pace on the rail over 1000 metres out, came under pressure to hold pace early in straight, unable to sustain effort and headed inside the final 200 metres.
Began from a wide gate, always thereabouts, held every chance early in straight but unable to sustain effort inside the final 200 metres.
Midfield early stages, carried backward to rear of the field approaching home bend, shifted wide entering straight, ran on well down the centre of the track to be nearest at finish.
Soon dropped to last few despite niggling along, saved ground on inside turning for home, finished off the race nicely inside the final 200 metres.

Jumped awkwardly losing ground, travelled keenly 3-wide towards the rear, made forward move approaching home turn and the widest runner into straight, kept on before finding no extra inside the final 100 metres.
Settled wide in midfield, shuffled backward entering home straight, made no impression.

Moderate start, soon picked up to forward of midfield in 6th, shuffled slightly backward when pace slackened coming onto home bend, dropped further backward entering home straight, made no impression.
Taken back from the widest gate, circled the field when pace slackened on the bend, amongst the leaders briefly turning in, dropped away quickly.
Slightly slow out, always well behind and never seen with a chance.
Broke well from a wide gate, gradually taken back but without cover in 5th some 2L off the pace, swung wider turning for home and folded up quickly.
Chased leaders early before settling down in midfield, into clear 350M and responded well to urging, got up close home.
Restrained near last, 5Ls to make up top of straight, chased well on inner final 200M, just held at the line.
From wide draw sent forward and crossed to the lead just before home turn, driven out near 300M, drifted out from rail under pressure, caught by first 2 late.
Crowded for room at start, recovered to race in midfield, held up for clear running early straight, did best work late, nearest finish.
In 4th place settled ahead of midfield, had every chance in straight, not reached leaders.
From wide barrier shifted across behind runners, held up in rear pair 7Ls off the pace, fanned wide home, stayed on final 400M without serious threat to leaders.
Began well from draw 1, tracked leader from 900M, kept on same pace in straight, no extra final stages.
Up with early pace, chased leader from 900M, tried hard in straight but couldn't muster the finishing pace, weakened final 150M.
Away well enough, eased back to a position behind midfield, saved ground on inner, ran on same pace final 400M. No threat.
Crowded for room at start, ended up in rear 7Ls off the pace, couldn't finish off in the straight. Never near to challenge.
From draw 12 caught wide no cover in midfield, battled on same pace early straight, weakened 200M.
Settled 3-wide towards the rear, under pressure from 600M, soon struggling.
Commenced well, raced 2 wide better than midfield, raced tight near 900M, a length behind on turn, took the lead early in straight, kept on strongly to the line, easily scored.
Began well, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, finished off strongly to take 2nd without threatening the winner.
Began awkwardly, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield early, found a 2 wide spot after passing near 1000M, 4 lengths or so back on turn, made good progress in straight to take a place.
Began awkwardly, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, shared lead on turn, headed near 300M, ran on evenly thereafter, just missed 3rd on line.
Began awkwardly, raced 2 wide at rear, 5 lengths back on turn, made good progress in straight, nearest on line.
Taken back to race at rear, 10 lengths back in the middle stages, still last turning in, taken wide in straight and finished off strongly to be nearest on line.
Began well from the widest draw, slightly taken back to race 3 wide better than midfield, raced tight near 900M, no cover on turn, finished off evenly.

Moderately away from a wide draw, sent forward to race prominently but trapped wide, found cover near 900M, a length behind the leader on turn, no daylight early in straight, made no progress when clear thereafter.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide at rear, 6 to 7 lengths back on turn, ran past a few weakening rivals in straight.
Clean jump, positioned on rail behind midfield, saved ground on turn, awkwardly placed near 500M, failed to close off in straight.
Began awkwardly and lost ground, positioned on rail behind midfield, 6 to 7 lengths back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Moderately away, positioned on rail better than midfield, 4 lengths back on turn, weakened early in straight.
Began only fairly, sent forward to take the lead, challenged by rival turning in, emptied early in straight.
Jumped well, sent forward to race in 2nd, a length behind the leader, travelled well to turn, hit the front early in straight, kept on very well to the line and scored.
Bumped on jumping, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths back, there to turn, finished well to take 2nd.
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned 3 to 4 lengths behind the leader on rail, closer on turn, angled out early in straight, made some progress to take 3rd.
Began well, positioned 2 to 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, moved closer along the rail on turn, finished off evenly.
Shifted in at start and bumped, raced 2 wide better than midfield, 3 lengths or so back on turn, finished off evenly.
Fast into stride, showed good speed to take the lead, travelled well to turn, headed near 300M, kept on one pace to the line.
Crowded on jumping, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear, 10 lengths back, still 7 lengths back on turn, taken wide in straight and made some progress. (Rider dropped whip near 250M.)
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide behind midfield, there to turn, finished off evenly.
Taken back from gate 11, raced 2 wide, 8 to 9 lengths back, a little bit closer on turn, made no progress in straight.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 wide from near 600M, carried wider turning in, kept on well early in straight, weakened gradually final 200M.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, still well back on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear throughout, never competitive.
Average to begin, raced at rear on rail, 5 to 6 lengths back on turn, kept on evenly early in straight, weakened final furlong.

Began well & allowed to stride forward before being crossed & settling midfield on the fence after 250m. Shifted off the fence at 800m between runners. Travelled very strongly entering the straight before dashing away to win.

Commenced well and strode forward before coming across to position midfield 4L from lead on the outside. Moved 4 horses wide prior to straightening. Sprinted hard in the final 300m but couldn't reel in winner.

Not fast away but got to position quickly settling midfield on the inside 5.5 lengths from lead. Moved away from the fence just prior to straightening before shifting out further on balancing. Ran home well in final section.
Began fast and ridden for speed before coming across to assume lead after 200m. Travelled well and was over 1 length clear on cornering before being overtaken halfway up the straight.

Began awkwardly and bumped before settling midfield off the fence. Raced ungenerously and checked at the 950m. Switched back to the prior to straightening before coming around heels at the 250m and making some ground late.

Was away only fairly before being eased across to be slightly worse than midfield on the outside. Moved out the widest runner on cornering still 4 lengths from lead. Ran home evenly in the final section.

Was only fairly away but had no early speed and drifted back third from last off the fence. Maintained rearward position and was 5L from lead on cornering. Stayed close to the fence in the straight and passed a few.

Was slow to begin and could not muster any speed before ultimately settling at the tail. Moved three horses wide prior to straightening but was still a clear last. Got past a few tiring runners in the run home.

Began well and was ridden forward before being crossed at the 1000m and positioning on leaders back from that point. Moved off the fence in cornering but came under pressure shortly after and weakened out from the 300m.

Bumped after the start but mustered early speed before easing at the 1000m when crossed. Shifted to the outside of the leader & travelled a touch keen in middle section before coming under pressure & weakening out from 400m.
Had no early speed and drifted back to be second from last on the fence after 200m. Was ridden up in straightening but did not respond in the straight.

Commenced fast from out wide and was across before settling 2.5 lengths form the lead on the outside. Was forced out 3 wide at the 800m and raced wide from that point. Was pushed 4 wide on cornering before weakening out in last section.

One of the last into stride and subsequently settled near the tail and three horses away from the fence. Continued to race wide in middle sections. Was second last on turning and didn't make any impression in the run home.

Jumped well, made contact shortly after start, raced at rear on rail, 4 lengths or so back, moved closer along the rail on turn, finished off strongly to score.
Began well, sat a length behind the leader on rail, easy run to turn, 2 wide from near 500M, took the lead early in straight, kept on very well, just couldn't hold off the winner late.
Began only fairly, positioned on rail in midfield, 2 wide on turn, finished off evenly.
Moderately away from gate 1, took the lead easily, led by 1/2L on turn, headed near 300M, weakened gradually thereafter, just stayed on for 4th.
Moderately away from the widest draw, unable to slot in early, taken back to race at tail, 4 to 5 lengths back, same margin back on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Shifted in at start and made contact, raced 3 wide in midfield, no cover from 1000M, moved a bit closer after passing 800M, 4 wide on turn, failed to close off in straight. (Blood in trachea.)
Hampered start, raced 2 wide, 4 lengths back, moved a bit closer after passing 700M, very wide turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.

Bumped start and unbalanced, unable to slot in early, raced wide with no cover better than midfield, found a 2 wide spot at 1000M, hard ridden on turn but only showed limited response, emptied early in straight. (Lame right front leg.)
Began fairly, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, peaked on turn, emptied early in straight, eased final furlong.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, weakened from 600M, emptied early in straight.
Eased back, 2 wide, benefited by the fast pace, progressed steadily 300M to score.
Hard ridden forward, not suited by the fast pace, bumped 700M, trapped 3 wide, closed off strongly for 2nd.
Hard ridden to keep up with the field, on the fence, benefited by the fast pace, progressed steadily 300M for 3rd.
Hard ridden forward, sat 2 wide, lack room 300M, made steady ground when clear.
Hard ridden to keep up in midfield along the fence, lack room 300M, progressed steadily when clear.
Hard ridden to take rail and led at fast sectionals, hung on well until 100M weakened.
Hard ridden to obtain box seat, not suited by the fast tempo, hung out around the bend, emptied 300M.
Hard ridden forward, trapped 3 wide, just held ground in straight.
Hard ridden to hold the rail in midfield, no dash.
Eased back, made steady ground 300M.
At rear, suited by the fast tempo, no progress.
Very slow away, never a factor.
Taken back at start, raced at tail, commenced to improve passing 800M, wide on straightening, quickened passing 200M, worked home strongly to score.
Raced at back, after 800M was left racing wide and without cover, improved to handy position near 700M, gained ground passing 200M, finished solidly.
Settled midfield, asked for effort passing 700M, fought well to the line.
Settled behind midfield on rail, rounding Home Turn kept improving on rail to save ground, in the straight gained some nice late ground.
Taken back at start, placed pressure near 400M, made up some late ground.
Raced midfield and wide, improved into lead near 1000M, gave ground passing 100M.
Jumped nicely, raced midfield on rail, rounding Home Turn kept improving on rail, one-paced in the straight.
Travelled keenly in the early stages, near 1000M was left racing wide and without cover, near 800M improved position to outside the lead, weakened near 200M.
Travelled behind midfield, near 900M was left racing wide and without cover, widest on straightening, no response in the straight.
Raced in handy position, fade out in the straight, lame left front next day, must trial.

Began well and ridden for speed before obtaining the lead after 200m. Crossed to the rail at the 900m. Was over a length clear before cornering very well and then sprinting 3 lengths clear inside the last 250m.

Away fairly before positioning midfield on the fence 3.5 lengths from lead at 800m. Travelled comfortably before badly held up for clear running 250m to the 150m. Got clear shortly after and hit line strongly along the fence.

Jumped well before being midfield one horse away from fence and 3.5 lengths from leader at 800m. Was 5.5 lengths from lead on cornering after pace quickened before making some late ground down the center of the track.

Ridden hard in early stages before crossing to one horse from fence at 750m. Moved 3 wide at 470m. 2.5 lengths from lead on cornering. Tried hard in straight, no match for winner but only relinquished second in final 25m.

Began well before positioning 2.5 lengths from lead & one away from the fence at 800m. Drifted further back as pace quickened in middle 400m. 4.5 lengths from lead on cornering. Battled on in straight. Lame day after racing.

Ridden hard early but could not gather any speed before positioning midfield, three horses wide. Was 5.5 lengths from the lead on cornering but continued to race wide. Ran home fairly in last section. Lame day after racing.

Was clearly the slowest away before maintain rail position to be third from last 5.5 lengths from lead at 800m. Lost sight of the speed after pace improved in middle section before not making any impression in the straight.

Ridden hard from wide barrier before coming across to position outside the leader at the 900m. Positioned at leaders girth at 600m but was under pressure from the 450m when the leader upped tempo. Weakened out final 300m.

Wasn't fast away and settled worse than midfield around 5 lengths from lead at 800m. Hung out noticeably from the 700m and lost position. Was a long way from leader on cornering and didn't catch the eye last section.

Was shifted back and across behind runners in early stages. Was awkwardly placed near heels at the 700m before shifting wider shortly after. Conceded big margin to leader at the top of the straight and was never likely.

Not fast out but gathered speed before being crossed at the 900m. Had to be ridden up to hold position just after the 600m. Was 4.5 lengths from lead on cornering but weakened out in the final 400m. Irregular heart rhythm.
Was crowded on jumping and didn't have much early pace before positioning last after 200m. Turned for home near the tail and made little impression in the straight.
Commenced well, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well throughout, kicked clear early in straight, kept on well to the line and scored.
Moderately away from gate 10, raced in midfield, 4 to 5 lengths back, same margin back on turn, finished off very strongly to be nearest on line, just beaten by narrow margin.
Began well, raced 2 wide in midfield, wider on turn, finished off strongly to take a place, nearest on line.
Jumped well, positioned on rail better than midfield, 2 wide on turn, made good progress early in straight, weakened gradually final 100M. (Lame right front leg.)
Began well, sent forward to race in 2nd, 2 wide, half length behind the leader on turn, kept on evenly in straight.
Away with them, positioned 1 out 1 back, similar positon on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened close home. (Lame right front leg.) (Rider expressed concern with horse's action.)
Began only fairly, raced at rear on rail, 7 lengths back, 2 wide on turn, made some headway in straight without threatening.
Stumbled start, positioned on rail behind midfield, 7 lengths back on turn, made minor progress in straight. (See Racing incidents.)
Taken back from the widest draw, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 6 lengths back on turn, finished off one-paced in straight.
Lifted front feet on jumping and away tardily, raced at tail, 10 lengths back, still well back on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Taken back to race at rear, 8 to 9 lengths back, still well back on turn, finished off one pace in straight.
Average to begin, sat a length behind the leader on rail, weakened on turn, emptied early in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Raced close to the rear, 7-1/4L behind 2 wide, continued on well and held of challenge to score by a neck.
In worse than midfield, 6-1/4L behind along the rail, battled gamely and pushed winner all the way to the line.
Sent forward and sat in front of midfield, left wide and without cover at 800M, ran on nicely to the line for 3rd.
Urged forward, in lead until slotted back in box-seat at 800M, continued fairly along the rail in straight.
Taken back to race at the rear, 8L behind along the rail, ran on nicely inside final 200M.
Travelled in midfield, 4L behind 2 wide, held up early in straight, closed off fairly thereafter.
Bumped start before slotting into one-off one back, sat 2-1/4L off, continued on well until emptied near 150M.
In box-seat until 800M, very awkward when unable to improve at 450M, showed nothing in the straight.
Bumped start, settled in midfield, 5L behind along the rail, trouble getting run at 200M, one paced thereafter.
In behind midfield, 5-1/2L behind 2 wide, ran home pretty one paced.
Rolled forward into a prominent position, wide until shifted to sit outside the lead at 800M, dropped off rounding home turn. (See Racing Incident Report)
Asked to go forward, travelled in the lead keenly, weakened passing 250M. (See Racing Incident Report)
Settled wide in midfield early stages, commenced move 800 metres out, joined the leaders 3-wide rounding home bend and hit the front about 300 metres out, won easily.
Broke well, held slender lead early stages and obtained rails run over 800 metres out, amongst the leading trio turning for home but soon outsprinted by the eventual winner.
Began fairly, settled in forward of midfield within 3L of pace, travelled 3-wide rounding home bend, kept on steadily without quickening.
Settled well behind from a wide gate, saved ground on the rail turning in, switched out for a run upon straightening, did best work late.
Slightly slow out, recovered swiftly to be just off the pace on the rail, within striking distance in 4th entering straight but ran home one-paced.
Moderate start from a wide gate settling wide towards the rear, gained closer 3-wide rounding home bend, ran home one-paced.
Broke well from the widest gate, disputed lead in back straight, gained slender advantage rounding home bend but headed after straightening and soon weakened.
Ridden along in midfield on the rail, came under pressure approaching home turn, found nothing.
Settled in 4th within 2L of pace, hampered 700 metres out coming onto home bend and soon came under pressure to maintain position, weakened noticeably after straightening.
Sluggish at start, gradually improved under pressure to reach rear of midfield briefly on home bend, found no extra in the run to the line. (Lame)
Dipped at the start, soon dropped to last few, never seen with a chance.
Soon dropped to the rear despite ridden along, never a danger.
Held up midfield early stages, moved up to challenge passing 500M, quickened to lead inside 300M, strode clear mid-night before easing off late, comfortably.
Settled 3rd last, 6Ls off the pace 400M, ran on well to go 2nd 150M, no chance with runaway winner.
Failed to muster speed, held up towards rear of midfield, stayed on steadily from 400M, no threat to first 2 but well clear from rest.
Chased leaders in 4th, not finishing pace of first 3 on straightening, kept on mildly for non-threatening 4th.
From draw 12 settled down 4Ls off the pace in midfield, ran past one paced horses on straightening, never troubled leaders.
Taken back from wide draw, settled in rear 7Ls behind leader in a fast run race, ran past beaten rivals only on straightening, no impression on leaders.
Reserved in midfield 4Ls back along the fence, kept on one pace in straight, never involved.
Bustled along after the start, vied lead on outside, briefly took over on straightening, headed by winner 300M, weakened final 200M.
From wide draw shifted across to a 3-wide spot in midfield, ran on fairly early straight before short of room from 200M, should have done better than the margin suggested.
Chased leaders, left flat footed when driven along 400M, no extra final 150M (Jockey : off the bridle 400M, didn't finish off.)
Slow to begin, soon ridden along but failed to muster, ended up in rear 6Ls back, was making some progress when steadied 150M and lost his chance.
Emerged to lead passing 1100M but soon pressed by rival, couldn't go on inside 350M, weakened badly.

Began only fairly from gate 1, raced at rear, closer to the middle of the track, 4 lengths or so back, improved from 400M, finished off very strongly to score.
Commenced well from gate 10, positioned a length behind the leader near to the stands rail, showed good response in the final 400M to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.
Bumped shortly after start, raced closer to the middle of the track, 3 lengths or so back, hard ridden from near 500M, closed off well to take a place.
Began awkwardly and bumped, positioned 1-1/2L behind the leader, 2 away from the stands rail, kept on evenly to the line.
Began smartly, sent forward to race prominently, hard ridden from 400M, led narrowly after passing 300M, headed near 150M, weakened thereafter.
Away with them, raced in midfield, 2 away from the stands rail, finished off evenly.
Made contact at start, showed no early speed, raced at rear on the stand side, 5 lengths back, made minor progress in the final 400M.
Bumped start and unbalanced, raced at rear, nearer to the middle of the track, made no impression final 400M.

Shifted out at start and made contact, sent forward to take the lead on the stands rail, hard ridden from near 400M, peaked and headed 300M, weakened gradually thereafter. (Lame left front leg next day.)
Average to begin, raced in midfield, closer to the middle of the track, no cover throughout, hard ridden from 400M but only showed limited response, weakened gradually after passing 200M.
Began well from gate 11, positioned a length behind the leader on the stands rail, peaked near 500M, weakened thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Eased to sit 1 out 1 back, benefited by the slow sectionals, ran on strongly to score but only by a narrow margin.
Settled just off the leader, 2 wide, benefited by the slow tempo, closed off well, just missed by a narrow margin.
Hard ridden to take rail and lead, clocked slow sectionals, hung on until 200M overhauled, ran on for 3rd.
Pushed to secure box seat, favoured by the slow tempo, just held ground in straight.
Eased back, trapped 3 wide throughout, harmed by the slow pace, dashed well 300M despite not suited by the negative racing situations.
Eased to sit in midfield, on the fence, not suited by the slow pace, just held ground in straight.
Slow away, at back, 2-3 wide, little dash 200M despite not suited by the slow tempo.
Slow away, at back along the fence, not suited by the slow tempo, little dash 200M.
At back, 2 wide, harmed by the slow pace, little dash 200M.
Eased back, not suited by the slow pace, no progress.
Settled box seat, commenced to improve on straightening, quickened passing 200M, worked home strongly to score.
Jumped well, ridden along to take lead, responded nicely in the early part of straight, gave some ground passing 50M.
Travelled midfield on rail, commenced to improve near 400M, made up some nice late ground.
Began only fairly, settled midfield, gained ground passing 200M.
Raced outside the lead, fought hard in the straight, gave some ground passing 100M.
Raced at tail, widest on straightening, one-paced in the straight.
Settled at back on rail, no response when asked for effort.
Slow out, settled midfield, weakened passing 300M.
Began very fast from wide barrier before coming across to the fence after 250m. Controlled speed in middle sections. Turned one length clear and ran strongly to the line.

Wasn't fast away before settling midfield one horse away from rail. Was ridden along mid-race to hold position. Conceded 6 lengths on cornering. Continued to make ground under hard riding, straight closing well last 300m.

Slow away before improving to midfield six lengths from lead at 1000m on rail. Raced ungenerously approaching 800m. Moved away from rail at 500m before improving between runners and then making good ground in last section.

Eased back and across behind runners after the start. Travelled in last position on the fence and would have been at least 10 lengths from lead on cornering. Continued to make up ground between runners in final section.
Began well and showed some speed before easing into fifth on the fence 3.5 lengths from lead. Moved around heals shortly after straightening but only ground home in final 300m.

Was allowed to find feet early and then drifted back to third from last. Was in last position on cornering between runners. Moved out to be the widest runner and made some headway into the large head-start conceded.
Wasn't bustled from the barriers and subsequently settled with only three behind at the 1000m. Made some ground in last section but was never a threat to winner.

Was ridden early to gain forward position before easing at 1100m and positioning nicely in forth on the outside. Moved three wide on cornering and looked threatening before weakening out in final 200m.

Threw its head at the start and lost ground. Made up some ground in first 400m to be third from last before moving three wide at 600m and then continuing to improve out wider 6 lengths from lead on cornering. Tired last 250m.

Began well but didn't have the speed of others before easing to be worse than midfield off the fence 7.5 lengths from lead at 1000m. Moved out wider in the straight but couldn't chip into substantial margin.

Allowed to stride forward from wide barrier before coming across to position midfield before clipping heals at the 1100m and losing some momentum. Moved four horses wide on cornering but weakened out from 275m.

Began well and had natural early speed and settled leaders back after being crossed after 250m. Had room to improve after straightening but could not capitalize when leader sprinted and weakened out from 350m.

Crowded on jumping and lost ground before gathering speed to position slightly worse than midfield on the fence. Stayed close to the fence on cornering and didn't have the clearest run in the straight but was never a threat.

Ridden up in first 200m before positioning in second on the outside 2 lengths from leader at 1000m. Crept closer and was within one length from lead on cornering but weakened out from straightening to finish long last.
Jumped well, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, shared lead turning in, kept on strongly in straight, scored by 3/4L.
Clean jump from gate 10, raced 2 wide behind midfield early, found rail near 1000M, 2 to 3 lengths back on turn, finished off strongly in straight to take 2nd.

Began well from a middle draw, sent forward to race prominently but trapped wide, slightly taken back near 1000M to obtain cover, 3 wide with cover in midfield on turn, made very good progress in straight to take 3rd.
Commenced well, raced 2 wide, 3 lengths back, there to turn, angled out near 500M, made good progress in straight to make frame.

Moderately away from gate 1, sent forward to take the lead, led by 3/4L on turn, challenged by rival from 500M, peaked and headed 300M, awkwardly placed near 150M, weakened thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Average to begin, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, a bit closer on turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Slowly away, raced at tail, 9 lengths back, still last turning in, made some headway in straight without threatening. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide at rear, 5 to 6 lengths back turning in, made minor progress in straight.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear, 8 to 9 lengths back, very wide turning in, passed some tired rivals in straight.
Jumped well from a wide draw, taken back to race 2 wide with cover behind midfield, 4 to 5 lengths back on turn, angled out near 500M, failed to close off in straight.

Began fairly, sent forward to race prominently but trapped wide, made contact and carried wider near 900M, 4 wide on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Away with them, raced prominently, 3 wide, slightly shifted out and made contact near 900M, still 3 wide on turn, weakened early in straight.
Taken back from gate 9, positioned on rail behind midfield, 5 lengths or so back, moved closer along the rail on turn, weakened early in straight.
Slowly away, recovered to race 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, same position on turn, weakened early in straight, eased after passing 200M.
Bumped start, in midfield 5L off 3 wide but with cover, battled on gamely and won with something in hand.
Travelled in midfield, 5L behind 2 wide, steadied at 175M, hit the line strongly nonetheless.
Bumped start, settled in behind midfield, 6-1/2L off 2 wide, improved and continued on nicely to take 3rd.
Eased and raced towards the rear, 7-3/4L off 3 wide but with cover, saved ground and closed off well to the line.
Pushed and settled to race in the box-seat, sat 2-3/4L off, ran on but couldn't find extra for final 150M.
Sent forward into the lead, raced keenly throughout, emptied and headed at 100M.
Taken back and raced at the rear, 9-1/2L behind 2 wide, kept saving ground to the finish.
Travelled in midfield, along the rail, continued on one paced to the line.
Pressed forward, sat 2L off and outside the lead, emptied passing 250M.
In worse than midfield, along the rail, continued on until run ended after 250M.
Bumped start, at rear along the rail, did not make an impression.
Urged and then slotted in front of midfield, 2 wide throughout, faded gradually.
Pushed and was prominent, however was wide and without cover, run ended at 350M.
Fractious and lost ground at start, recovered to be front of midfield but wide, found nothing in straight.

Settled in 6th some 4L off the pace in rear of midfield, steadied at about the 1100 metres, obtained a clear passage on the inside upon straightening, quickened well to take command passing the 200 metres.

Set steady pace for the first 800 metres, quickened up in the middle stages, came under pressure to hold challenges early in home straight, unable to sustain effort and overshadowed inside the final 200 metres.
Tracked the leader, commenced move rounding home bend, drew level upon straightening, unable to sustain effort inside the final 200 metres.
Travelled 3-wide without cover prominently, in similar position entering home straight, kept on same pace without quickening under pressure.
Settled just over 2L off the pace in back straight, in similar position turning for home, one-paced under pressure in the run to the line.
Settled in last few, swung widest into home straight, kept on steadily without quickening down the centre of the wet track.
Settled in 5th on the rail within 3L of pace, gained closer rounding home bend, gradually faded in the straight.
Settled in rear early, took closer order at the 1200 metres, travelled wide around home bend and went wider entering home straight, found nothing under pressure.
Settled well behind, saved ground on the rail turning for home, soon weakened. (Questioned for disappointing performance)
Ridden positively from draw 14, vied for lead 2-wide, driven out 300M, fought back when challenged on both sides, locked horns with runner-up late, just held on.
Settled ahead of midfield, wide no cover from 800M, quickened up nicely in straight, loomed 200M, tried hard to reel in winner, just denied in photo-finish.
Held up towards the rear, in 12th spot 4Ls off the pace leaving the turn, ran on well final 300M, nearest finish.
Began only fairly, recovered to race in midfield, moved up to challenge leader 250M, peaked on its run late, lost 3rd near line.
Bustled along after the start, settled in midfield, 4-wide no cover from 800M, boxed on well despite tough trip, just missed 4th.
Crowded for room at start, ended up towards rear along the rail, held up until 300M, ran on moderately to the line, held ground final stages.
Away with them, eased back to the rear, swung widest home, 5Ls to make up 400M, stayed on without threatening.
Held up in midfield along the inside, had every chance from 400M, no extra and outpaced by rivals final 150M.
Dropped back to near the rear after the start, struck heels of rival 900M and blundered, ran on fairly on straightening, never dangerous.
From draw 12 crossed to track leaders before home turn, kept on same pace when driven out top of straight, faded towards the finish.
Slow out, rushed forward, hampered 800M and lost ground, found little in straight, weakened 250M. (Wounds to outside LH cannon.)
From draw 13 couldn't get closer than 3-wide, in midfield early stages but shuffled back to near the rear form 850M, couldn't quicken on straightening. No impression.
In mid-division, came under pressure 500M, ran on same pace, emptied passing 200M and eased.
Sent forward and vied lead on inside, outpaced from 300M, weakened badly.
Average to begin, positioned 1-1/2L behind the leader near to the stands rail, no clear run from near 400M, finished off very strongly when clear final 150M, scored by a narrow margin.
Jumped well from gate 1, raced closer to the middle of the track, a length or so back, finished off very well to take 2nd, just narrowly beaten.
Made contact shortly after start, positioned 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader, 1 away to the stands rail, finished off strongly to take a place, narrowly beaten.
Commenced well, raced prominently on the stand side, took the lead near 450M, headed near 200M, stayed on well to make frame.
Average to begin, raced closer to the middle of the track, 3 lengths back, showed good response in the final 400M to be nearest on line.
Bumped on jumping, raced closer to the middle of the track, 3 lengths or so back, made minor progress in the final 400M.
Moderately away from gate 12, raced prominently on the stands rail, weakened gradually from 250M.
Bumped start, raced in the middle of the track, 3 lengths or so back, kept on one-paced to the line.
Jumped well, sent forward to race prominently, closer to the middle of the track, ridden and outpaced near 400M, weakened gradually from final 200M.
Began well, raced prominently, nearer to the middle of the track, no response to riding final 400M and dropped away.
Jumped with them, raced prominently, 2 away from the stands rail, peaked near 400M, weakened thereafter, eased final 100M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Raced at rear throughout, never competitive.
Began well from gate 11, sent forward to race prominently in the early stages, 2 wide, travelled well throughout, took the lead early in straight, kept on very well thereafter, scored by a length.
Away with them, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, improved from near 500M, 4 wide turning in, closed off strongly to take 2nd.
Commenced well from a middle draw, raced 3 wide better than midfield, 1 to 2 lengths back on turn, kept on very well in straight to take a place.

Hampered start, raced at tail, 9 lengths back, moved a bit closer in the middle stages, 5 to 6 lengths back turning in, made very good progress in straight to make frame without threatening the first few.
Jumped well from gate 13, taken back to race 4 wide behind midfield, a bit closer on turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Jumped with field, hard ridden early to take a prominent position, took the lead after passing 1000M, led by 1/2L turning in, headed near 300M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Began well, raced at rear on the inside, 6 lengths or so back, saved ground on turn, awkwardly placed early in straight, made minor progress thereafter.
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, 3 lengths or so back on turn, showed limited response in straight. (Mucus in trachea.)
Average to begin, positioned 2 wide better than midfield, 2 lengths back on turn, kept on evenly early in straight, weakened gradually final furlong.
Bumped heavily at start, raced 2 wide at rear, 6 to 7 lengths back in the middle stages, taken very wide turning in, finished off evenly.
Began fairly, raced 2 wide in midfield, travelled keenly in the early stages, 4 lengths back on turn, hung in and difficult to ride in straight, made no progress.
Taken back to race at rear, 8 lengths back, taken very wide turning in, failed to make any progress in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear throughout, never a threat.
Shifted in abruptly at start and bumped heavily, recovered quickly to take the lead, headed near 1000M, sat a length behind the leader on turn, weakened early in straight, eased late.

Gear: Comments on Running is not available for this race.

Commenced well, positioned a length behind the leader in the early stages, took the lead after passing 900M, led by a length on turn, kicked clear early in straight, scored by 2-1/2L.
Made contact at start, raced 2 wide, 2 lengths back, closer on turn, kept on evenly in straight to take 2nd.
Jumped well from gate 1, positioned 2 to 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground throughout, made some progress in straight to take a place.
Bumped shortly after start, raced at rear on rail, 5 lengths or so back on turn, blocked and made contact early in straight, finished off well when clear thereafter to make frame without threatening.
Away with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, same position on turn, lay in under pressure proving difficult to ride, finished off evenly.
Slightly slow out and made contact, positioned on rail behind midfield, angled out near 400M, bumped near 250M, finished off evenly thereafter.
Made contact at start, raced 2 wide at rear, 5 to 6 lengths back on turn, very wide turning in, finished off evenly in straight.
Made contact at start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, there to turn, carried wider from 400M, failed to close off in straight.
Began well, sent forward to take the early lead, headed near 900M, sat a length behind the leader on turn, weakened early in straight.
Hard ridden forward, sat just off the leaders, made early move 500M, hung on well to win.
Eased to sit in midfield along the fence, benefited by the fast pace, held up badly 5-3, made steady ground when clear.
Eased to sit in midfield, 2 wide, benefited by the fast tempo, made steady ground 300M for 3rd.
Eased back, 2 wide, hung in badly around the bends, suited by the fast pace, progressed steadily 250M.
Pushed forward, sat 2 wide, not suited by the fast tempo, just held ground in straight.
Hard ridden forward, harmed by the fast pace, led 500M, out of fuel 200M.
Eased back, benefited by the fast pace, on heels 500M, ran on ok in straight.
Eased back, suited by the fast tempo, ran on fairly.
Hard ridden to take rail and led at fast sectionals, soon emptied 500M.
At rear, never a factor.
Settled behind midfield, improved passing 550M, 4 wide rounding the Home Turn, quickened passing 200M, finished strongly to score.
Jumped nicely, ridden along to take lead, asked for effort passing 400M, responded solidly in the straight, missed by 1/2L.
Taken back at start, difficult to settle near 800M, improved passing 500M, widest on straightening, made up some nice late ground.
Ridden to race in front of midfield, commenced to improve near 400M, gained some late ground in the straight.
Taken back at start, asked for effort passing 550M, made some ground passing 150M.
Missed the start and raced at back on rail, wide on straightening, made limited ground in the straight.
Urged along to race outside the lead, travelled keenly in middle stages, gave ground passing 200M, rider and trainer questioned.
Settled in front of midfield on rail, placed pressure but only one-paced in the straight.
Ridden along to race in box seat, tried to improve passing 450M, faded out near 100M.
Raced midfield on rail, fought hard but only one-paced in the straight.
Travelled midfield, tried to improve near 500M, gave ground passing 100M.
Taken back at start, always back, never in it.
Began well and held rail position before settling behind the leader after 400m. Move around heels shortly after straightening before striking lead inside 200m and holding on from fast finisher.

Lifted feet at the start and subsequently 1 length slow away before gathering speed to position midfield one horse away from the fence. Moved out wider on cornering and sprinted hard in final 250m to just miss.

Began well and was ridden forward from middle barrier before coming across but being posted three horses wide from the 700m. Continued to cover ground and was 4 wide on cornering, before fighting hard in the straight.

Was fairly away before being ridden for speed early before positioning third 2 lengths from the lead at the 600m. Was ridden up before cornering when 2 lengths from lead before getting tired last 150m.

Had limited early pace and subsequently settled at the rear on the rail. Was five lengths from lead at 600m. Stayed close to the rail on cornering before shifting out at the 300m and making sound ground over the final 150m.

Was only moderately away but gathered speed quickly to be midfield on the fence, 3.5L from lead at 600m. Stayed close to the fence on cornering and was following eventual winner before maintaining margin to the line.

Shifted out slightly at the start before gaining customary early speed to come across & assume lead after 100m. Crossed over to the fence at the 600m. Was over 1 length clear in the straight before being caught at the 200m.

Eased across behind runners after 300m to be worse than midfield on the outside. Raced keenly for some distance approaching the 400m. Was around 5 lengths from lead on cornering and wasn't a major threat in the straight.
Didn't have much early speed and subsequently settled second last on the fence around 7 lengths from lead at 600m. Stayed close to the fence in the straight but was never a winning chance.

Was taken back and across from wide barrier after the start to position midfield three horses wide with cover at the 600m. Was 4.5 lengths from the lead on cornering and failed to improve that margin in the straight.

Was the last horse into stride and subsequently settled last on the outside. Raced greenly when cornering at the 600m and continued to race greenly in the straight. Didn't catch the eye in the final section.

Began awkwardly before continuing to be ridden for speed but posted five horses wide & 3 lengths from lead at the 600m. Continued to race extremely wide in middle stages. Yielded ground from the 600m and was never likely.
Jumped well from gate 1, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, easy run on turn, finished off strongly to score.
Average to begin, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, closed off well to take 2nd on line.
Began well, sent forward to race prominently, travelled well throughout, kept on well in straight, just couldn't hold off the first two late.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide in midfield, steadied off heels near 550M, 4 lengths back on turn, made very good progress in straight to make frame.
Commenced well, raced 2 wide better than midfield, steadied off heels near 600M, 3 lengths back on turn, made some progress in straight.
Began smartly, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, led by 3/4L on turn, kept on well early in straight, headed near 100M, slightly weakened thereafter.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, 7 lengths back on turn, made reasonable headway in straight without threatening.
Hampered shortly after start, raced 2 wide at rear, 6 lengths back on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Made contact at start, raced 2 to 3 wide with cover behind midfield, slightly improved from 450M, very wide turning in, finished off evenly.
Began awkwardly then hampered, raced at rear on rail, 5 lengths back on turn, finished off evenly.

Shifted out at start and made contact, raced prominently but 3W, slightly taken back after passing 700M, found cover near 600M, a length behind on turn, kept on evenly early in straight, weakened final 50M. (Lost left front plate.)
Shifted out shortly after start and made contact, trapped very wide early, raced 3 wide in midfield after entering the back straight, no cover on turn, weakened early in straight.
Pushed to obtain the rail and led by 1/2L, maintained lead and fended off a late challenge to score by a head.
Sent forward and raced outside the lead, sat 1/2L off, battled on nicely and challenged winner late.
Travelled in just behind midfield, 4-1/4L behind wide and without cover, closed off nicely to take 3rd.
Niggle along and settled in one-off one-back position, sat 2L off, finished off well.
Settled to race in midfield, 3-1/2L behind 2 wide, closed off fairly until awkward on heels prior going to the line.
Sat just in front of midfield, 3L behind along the rail, ran on fairly until awkward on heels prior going to the line.
Sent forward and took up the box-seat, sat 1-1/2L off, continued on one paced to the line.
Jumped awkwardly, settled just behind midfield along the rail, was one paced.
Awkward start, then raced near the tail along the rail, hardly improved.
Eased after the jump, settled in behind midfield, 2 wide, did not improve.
Sat near the rear, 2 wide at turn, saved no ground.
Always at rear and wide, finished tailed out. Must trial.
Settled better than midfield in 6th on the rail, came off the rail leaving the Rock and swung the widest into home straight, quickened well to take charge 100 metres out, won convincingly.
Settled just worse than midfield, ran on well between runners upon straightening, did best work late.
Ridden positively to take up running on the rail after the first 400 metres, ceded lead for box seat turning into back straight, not far off onto final bend, fought on steadily without threatening.

Ridden positively from the widest gate, settled for midfield 2-wide before the first bend, rushed up at the Rock to lead by 2L 500M out and maintained the high speed on home bend, unable to sustain effort and swamped 100M out.
With leaders early stages, settled for 5th within 3L of pace coming on to first bend, commenced move entering home straight, fought on under pressure without threatening.
Settled in last few, fought on well in straight to reach remote 6th closing stages.
Settled just worse than midfield on the rail, came to challenge under pressure after straightening, hampered and lost position 200 metres out, made no impression thereafter.
Vied for lead after beginning from Gate 11, obtained rails run in the front 900 metres out, led until headed and hampered about 500 metres out, swamped for 2nd placing inside the final 200 metres.
Broke well from the one draw, with leaders before taken back to 4th on the rail, shuffled further back to 6th some 4L back leaving the Rock, made no further impression.
Slowly away, never a danger.
Crowded and then stumbled shortly after the start, detached from the main body of field most of the way, never a factor.
With the leaders 4-wide onto first bend, settled one-out-one-back in 3rd turning into back straight, folded up quickly inside the final 400 metres. (Jockey reported pace and trip not suit)
Soon got across from draw 9, settled in 4th, made his move nearing top of straight, led 250M, kept on well to hold off rivals late stages.
Guided to a 2-wide spot in midfield, chased winner from top of straight, kept finding to the line but always held.
Reserved near last, 6Ls to make up 400M, widest into straight, stayed on well to go 3rd near 50M, nearest finish.
From wide draw crossed to the rail 1300M, tracked leaders into straight, stuck to his task in the straight but not pace of first 3 final 200M, honest effort.
Held up towards the rear, 6Ls behind leader going into home turn, made some ground final 300M, not reached leaders.
Jumped on terms, reserved in midfield 4Ls off leader, pushed along 450M but only plugged away to the line, no threat to first 4.
Settled worse than midfield, saved ground on the inside, tried hard in straight but kept on same pace to line only, no threat to leaders.
Held up behind mid-division, 5Ls off the pace at 400M, clear running form top of straight but only battled to the line.
Went forward from wide draw, caught wide before crossing to the lead 1200M, collared 250M, weakened rapidly late stages.
Pushed up from outside draw and tracked leader from 1300M, couldn't pick up when placed under pressure early straight, faded final 200M.
Lacked early speed, ended up towards the rear, wide no cover from 900M, couldn't get close turning home, no impact.
Switched off to rear after the jump, detached early stages, got back to the field halfway, scrubbed along home turn but couldn't make much headway, never involved.

Jumped well, positioned 2 to 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, easy run on turn, finished off very strongly to score.
Began smartly, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, led by a length at 400M, kept on well in straight, just couldn't hold off the winner late.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide at rear, improved on turn, very wide turning in, kept on well to take 3rd, no threat to the first two.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide, 3 to 4 lengths back, improved from near 500M, very wide turning in, finished off evenly in straight.
Stumbled at start and made contact, raced at tail, 6 lengths or so back, hard ridden from 550M, still 4 to 5 lengths back turning in, made some headway in straight without threatening.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide better than midfield, 2-1/2L back on turn, failed to close off in straight. (Blood in trachea.)
Moderately away from gate 9, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, found rail near 700M, angled out near 500M, a length behind turning in, weakened early in straight.

Began awkwardly and lost ground, gradually recovered on the first turn, continued to improve after entering the back straight, settled 2 wide in 2nd after passing 900M, peaked on turn, emptied early in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Shifted out at start and made contact, positioned on rail behind midfield, travelled keenly after 1400M, 4 lengths back on turn, showed nothing in straight.
Pushed early but not muster, took cover at rear, 2-4 wide, unleashed strong finishing efforts 300M to score.
Eased back, trapped 3-4 wide, pace good, dashed well 300M for 2nd.
Eased to sit just off the leaders, 2 wide, pace good, made steady ground 400M, run ended 100M.
Pushed early, took rail at back, pace good, held up 4-2, progressed steadily when clear.
Pushed to keep up in midfield, trapped 3-4 wide, pace good, held ground whilst hanging in badly in straight.
At rear, took rail, pace good, blocked most straight, not fully tested.
Hard ridden to take rail and led at good pace, emptied 200M.
Eased to sit just off the leaders, 2 wide, pace good, out of fuel 200M.
Pushed early, at back 2 wide, pace good, lack room and hung in badly in straight, no progress.
Pushed to hold the rail in midfield, pace good, emptied 250M.
Never competitive.
Hard ridden forward, trapped wide, trapped 3 wide, dropped off quickly 400M.
Raced in handy position, commenced to improve passing 500M, quickened passing 200M, finished strongly to score, trainer questioned improved performance.
Settled midfield on rail, gradually made ground in the straight, made solid late ground, just missed by SH.
Ridden along then took lead passing 800M, asked for effort on straightening, responded solidly in the straight.
Settled midfield, asked for effort passing 600M, made up some nice late ground in the straight.
Raced behind midfield, held up for running from passing 350M to near 200M, made nice ground after obtaining clear run.
Taken back at start, settled behind midfield on rail, worked well to the finishing line.
Travelled at back, always niggled, one-paced in the straight.
Ridden along after start, passing 800M travelled keenly when being steadied to obtain box seat, weakened passing 150M, bled.
Taken back at start, wide on straightening, limited response in the straight.
Raced at tail, always back, no response in the straight, bled.
Settled in front of midfield, passing 800M was left racing wide and without cover, widest on straightening, no response in the straight.
Ridden along then travelled keenly outside the lead, faded out passing 300M, rider questioned, must trial.
Was eased across shortly after the start to be worse than midfield away from the fence. Moved three horses wide before cornering and then made good ground in final section to win.

Steadied & travelled keenly approaching the 1300m. Raced wide & improved position around the outside in middle stages, 2L from lead on cornering. Raced tight before sprinting well to lead in straight before joined at 150m.

Had no early speed and subsequently settled second last on the outside. Was 6 lengths from the lead approaching the turn before pulling out 4 wide on straightening and making up a large amount of ground in final section.

Began well and was ridden across to position one horse away from fence and 3 lengths from lead after 400m. Raced tight with another runner after straightening but then had room from 350m and battled hard to the line.

Showed speed to dispute lead in early stages before getting on leaders back from 850m. Travelled well behind leader before staying close to fence on cornering. Difficulty gaining clear running at 400m and raced tight at 300m.

Began fairly and held fence before being crossed at the 1000m and settling midfield on the fence. Was 3.5 lengths from the lead on straightening. Moved away from the fence after cornering and worked to the line evenly.
Began well and showed some early speed before easing into midfield one horse away from the fence at the 1000m. Shifted 3 horses wide after the 500m mark before running on evenly in the last section.

No early pace and was ridden to hold position at the tail in early and middle sections. Continued to be hard ridden from 700m & was around 8 lengths from lead. Pulled the widest runner on cornering and made good late ground.
Was the last horse into stride and subsequently settled at the tail between runners. Moved out a little wider on straightening but didn't flatter in the run home.
Wasn't fast away and settled worse than midfield on the fence at the 1000m. Was 5 lengths from the lead on cornering before shifting out wider but not able to make up any ground in the straight.

Jumped well but was eased back from wide barrier worse than midfield three horses wide and six lengths from lead at 1000m. Followed winner in middle section before moving wider on cornering. Was only one paced in the final section.

Showed early speed and continued on in early stages to be three horses wide & two lengths from the lead after 600m. Continued to race wide & improved to make a line of three at the front at the 500m before weakening out late.

One of the last away but hard ridden early to be prominent & continued to challenge for the lead until crossing to fence at 900m. Joined in the lead at the 500m. Saddle slipped rounding home turn. Weakened out last section.

Fairly away before being ridden forward to challenge for lead. Headed at 950m & then crossed at 900m. Travelled well into the straight, unbalanced at 300m before losing position & not tested from that point. Lame after race.
Began well from gate 1, raced in the middle of the track, 2 to 3 lengths back, hard ridden from near 400M, finished off strongly to score.
Jumped with them, raced prominently, closer to the middle of the track, hard ridden from 400M, kept on well to the line, just couldn't hold off the winner final 50M.
Began smartly from gate 14, showed good speed to take the lead, hard ridden from 350M, headed after passing 200M, stayed on for 3rd.

Out in line, positioned closer to the middle of the track, 2 lengths or so back, awkwardly placed near 600M, showed good response after passing 400M, steadied off heels near 200M, finished off evenly thereafter.
Moderately away from gate 13, positioned a length behind the leader on the stands rail, showed limited response in the final 400M.
Stumbled at start, raced prominently, 1 away from the stands rail, peaked shortly after passing 400M, slightly weakened thereafter.
Shifted in at start and bumped, raced prominently, nearer to the stands rail, peaked on run near 300M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Began awkwardly, positioned 2 away from the stands rail, 2 lengths or so back, made no impression final 400M.
Began fairly, raced at tail in the middle of the track, 5 lengths back, made minor progress in the final 400M.
Average to begin, raced at rear, closer to the stands rail, showed some response after passing 400M, no clear run final 150M.
Jumped with them, positioned a length behind, near to the stands rail, showed limited response after passing 400M, steadied off heels near 150M, made no impression thereafter.
Average to begin, raced in the middle of the track, a length or so back, peaked on run after passing 400M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Began fairly, raced closer to the middle of the track, 2-1/2L back, showed no response to vigorous riding final 400M, weakened final furlong.
Began awkwardly and bumped, raced prominently, closer to the middle of the track, peaked on run near 500M, weakened thereafter, eased after passing 300M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Raced in midfield, shifted 3 wide when making the turn at 700M, charged home from 300M unchallenged.
Slotted in to race in midfield along the rail, found extra to close off very nicely inside final 150M.
Lifted foot off at start and lost ground, recovered to be in behind midfield, 3 wide at turn, made nice ground and closed off well to the line.
Asked before settling in one-off one-back position, continued on fairly to the line.
Sent forward, led along the rail, one paced until headed when found no extra near 150M.
Rolled forward and sat outside the lead, kept on until emptied at about 150M.
Jumped awkwardly, sat in front of midfield, 2 wide, crowded at 150M, was one paced anyway.
Awkward start then taken back, in behind midfield along the rail, found no daylight till late, not properly tested.
Raced in front of midfield, along the rail, emptied at 200M.
In about midfield, 2 wide, did not improve.
Eased then raced close to the rear, 2 wide throughout, no daylight at 300M, ran on thereafter.
At rear, 3 wide but with cover, made no impression.
In front of midfield, trapped when failed to find cover, dropped out prior to 300M.
Bumped start, settled to race in box-seat, weakened badly at 350M and finished tailed out. Must trial.
Jumped fairly, settled within striking distance, hit the front under pressure over 200 metres out, just fended off runner-up's strong late challenge.
Waited with, switched off the stands rails to challenge passing the 400 metres, quickened well inside the final 100 metres, did best work late.
Broke well, settled in midfield just over 2L back near the stands rails, quickened to hold every chance inside the final 200 metres, unable to sustain effort nearing finish.
Settled better than midfield some 2L off the pace, came under pressure to challenge 400 metres out while racing greenly, ran home one-paced inside the final 100 metres.
Began well, travelled prominently to about 300 metres out, found no extra under pressure.
Moderate start, soon dropped to the rear, produced good late impression inside the final 150 metres, nearest at the finish.
Slightly slow out, settled just worse than midfield, gained slightly closer to 7th some 3L back over 500 metres out, kept on steadily without quickening closing stages.
Soon took up running, gradually shifted across and obtained stands rails run about 600 metres out, led until headed inside the final 200 metres.
Stumbled at start, settled just worse than midfield down the centre of the track, faded under pressure inside the final 200 metres.
Began from the one gate, soon came forward to join the leaders down the centre of the track, unable to sustain effort inside the final 200 metres.
Moderate start, always in last few and never seen with a chance.
Began well from draw 1, settled down in midfield 5Ls behind leader in a strongly run race, peeled out 500M to challenge, stayed on well to lead inside 200M, kicked clear for a comfortable win.
Reserved behind midfield, enjoyed a ground saving run along the rail, gave a decent kick inside 350M to finish off pleasingly, went 2nd 100M but couldn't get near to winner.
Crowded for room on jumping, held up behind mid-division, 9th home turn, stayed on moderately to claim 3rd, hung under pressure.
Positioned just ahead of midfield, crept closer to be 4th passing halfway, loomed a chance early straight, peaked on its run 150M, held ground late.
Crowded for room on jumping, settled 2-wide in midfield 5Ls back, worked home fairly, never a serious threat.
Ridden forward, strode to the front from 1650M, over-raced in the lead, headed inside 200M, faded towards the line.
Restrained after the start, held up near the rear, switched wide from 600M, kept trying but couldn't finish well enough.
Soon crossed to the rail, tracked leader in a fast run race, fought on same pace early straight, held 2nd spot to 250M, weakened late.
From widest draw taken across behind runners, settled in last over 10Ls off the fast pace, passed a few in straight but never a factor.
Crossed to the rail passing 1800M, settled 3-4Ls off the fast pace, short of room early straight but failed to run on when clear, held up again over final 50M, not ridden out late.
Bustled along from wide draw, chased leader in fast run race, couldn't accelerate when driven out 500M, soon passed by looming runners.
Reserved in 2nd last, scrubbed along from 800M, widest into straight, couldn't pick up and soon struggling from 400M.
Failed to muster despite ridden along, settled midfield, left racing wide without cover from 1700M, dropped out on straightening. (Lame next day.)
Moderately away from a wide draw, raced 3 wide with no cover, 2 lengths or so back, there to turn, finished off very strongly in straight to score. (See Racing Incidents.)

Commenced well from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, 3 lengths back, saved ground on turn, no daylight early in straight, angled out after passing 200M, finished off very strongly thereafter to take 2nd.
Began well, positioned 1-1/2L behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, kept on well in straight to take a place.
Began awkwardly and bumped, raced at tail, 7 lengths back, a bit closer on turn, still 5 lengths back at 400M, finished off very strongly to make frame, nearest on line.
Moderately away, raced 3 wide in midfield, awkwardly placed near 900M, positioned 2 wide thereafter, 2 lengths back on turn, finished off evenly.
Crowded shortly after start, raced at rear on rail, 4 lengths back on turn, angled out early in straight, made some progress final 200M without threatening.

Shifted out at start and bumped, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, led by a length at 400M, kept on well early in straight, peaked near 200M, headed shortly thereafter, then dropped away tamely.
Shifted in at start and made contact, raced 2 wide, 4 lengths back, there to turn, finished off evenly.
Moderately away, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, a length back on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually after passing 200M.
Crowded start, raced 2 wide at rear, 6 lengths back, same margin back on turn, failed to close off in straight. (A small wound on the right hind coronary band.)
Jumped well from a tricky draw, taken back to race wide at rear, 8 lengths back on turn, failed to make any progress in straight.
Bumped start, unable to slot in, trapped 4 wide better than midfield, peaked on turn, weakened early in straight, eased final furlong.
Began well, positioned on rail in midfield, 2 to 3 lengths back on turn, no clear running early in straight, finished off very strongly when clear final 300M, scored by a neck.
Clean jump, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 4 lengths or so back on turn, made very good progress in straight to take 2nd despite crowded near 250M.
Bumped start, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, 3 lengths back, same position on turn, made good progress in straight despite being bumped near 250M.
Began awkwardly, showed no early speed, raced at tail, 7 lengths back, a bit closer on turn, taken wide after passing 500M, finished off strongly to make frame without threatening the first few.
Away with them, raced 2 wide at rear, 5 lengths or so back on turn, no daylight early in straight, finished off strongly when clear final 200M.
Slowly away, raced at rear on rail, 5 lengths back on turn, made good progress in straight.

Jumped well from a wide draw, sent forward to take the lead, found rail near 900M, challenged by rival turning in, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed near 200M, kept on evenly thereafter.
Began smartly from gate 13, sent forward to race prominently but wide, challenged the leader turning in, kept on well early in straight, peaked near 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.

Moderately away, sent forward to race prominently on rail, allowed the rival to cross near 900M, sat a length behind the leader on turn, angled out early in straight, peaked near 300M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Taken back to race 3 wide with cover at rear, travelled keenly throughout, 4 to 5 lengths back on turn, made no progress in straight.
Made contact at start, raced 4 wide, 4 lengths back, no cover on turn, weakened early in straight when hard run took effect.
Moderately away, positioned on rail behind midfield, 3 to 4 lengths back on turn, in traffic early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Commenced well, raced prominently early, allowed rival to cross near 1000M, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths back on turn, kept on evenly early in straight, bumped near 250M, weakened thereafter.
Jumped well from the widest gate, unable to slot in, raced wide and with cover, 2 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, emptied early in straight.
